NK095(ce)001:1: // sa rba d+ha rma ma h+aa sa n+ti bo d+hi
NK095(ce)001:2: tsi t+ta ku la ya r+aa dza t+ai ka sa
NK095(ce)001:3: ma n+ta ra sha y+aa lam k+aa ra na ma
NK095(ce)001:5: chos thams cad rdzogs pa chen po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:6: sems kun byed rgyal po'i 'grel pa kun bzang dgongs
NK095(ce)001:7: rgyan zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK095(ce)001:9: na mo gu ru ar+ya many+dzu sh+r+ai ye /
NK095(ce)001:10: shes bya'i mkha' dbyings sgrib pa med spyan ji snyed ji bzhin gzigs gyur cing //
NK095(ce)001:11: phan bde'i 'od zer shin tu mtha' yas sa gsum skye rgu'i bla mar gshegs //
NK095(ce)001:12: gdod ma'i mgon po kun tu bzang de sku gsum mdzad pa'i phrin las can //
NK095(ce)001:13: ma lus srid zhi'i dpal du gyur la kun nas dga' ba'i gtsug gis mchod //
NK095(ce)001:14: gang gi rang bzhin gdod nas spros bral nang gsal chos sku'i rang gdangs nyid //
NK095(ce)001:15: ma 'gags ye shes kun nas rang gsal thugs rje'i
NK095(ce)001:16: rol pa'i cha gang zhig /brjod med brjod pa kun
NK095(ce)001:17: gyi gzhir gyur brjod bral a ti'i rgyud rgyal nyid
NK095(ce)001:18: // zhu dang sdud po'i tshul du rang snang sems dpa' rdo rje nyid la 'dud //
NK095(ce)001:19: dag pa gnyis ldan chos sku'i dbyings nas mkhyen brtse'i 'od zer stong 'bar ba //
NK095(ce)001:20: gdul bya'i dpal du 'gog med 'char mdzad thugs bskyed smon pa'i rnam 'gros can //
NK095(ce)001:21: 'gro ba'i yid kyi mun pa ma lus cig car sel ba'i rta bdun dbang //
NK095(ce)001:22: dga' rab dpa' bo dgyes pa rdo rjes byang chub bar du bdag rgyud skyongs //
NK095(ce)001:23: mkhyen rab ye shes thugs kyi mkha' la brtse ba'i sprin tshogs rab 'khrigs shing //
NK095(ce)001:24: mthu stobs nus pa'i glog gi phreng bas rnam bzhi'i phrin las rab tu ngom //
NK095(ce)001:25: gsang chen dbyar rnga'i sgra chen sgrogs bzhin phan bde'i gru char 'beb mkhas pa //
NK095(ce)001:26: mkhas grub yongs kyi gtsug gi rgyan gcig rgyal dbang pad+mas shis pa stsol //
NK095(ce)001:27: mdo rgyud spyi dang khyad par nges gsang rdzogs pa che //
NK095(ce)001:28: gangs ljongs snang ba'i dpal du 'dren pa'i shing rta
NK095(ce)001:29: mchog /sh+r+ai seng b+ai ma bee ro g.yu sgra ska
NK095(ce)001:30: cog sogs // bsgyur mdzad sprul pa'i lo pan rnams kyang gtsug tu mchod //
NK095(ce)001:31: ye grol lta ba'i rtsal chen rab rdzogs pas //
NK095(ce)001:32: theg mchog gangs ri'i spo la gnas bcas te //
NK095(ce)001:33: rnam dpyod rigs pa'i g.yu ral sprugs mdzad pa //
NK095(ce)001:34: smra ba'i seng ge rong zom chen por 'dud //
NK095(ce)001:35: gdod ma'i mgon po'i ye shes rang rtsal nyid //
NK095(ce)001:36: thugs rje sprul pa'i ngo bor yongs shar nas //
NK095(ce)001:37: sgrib bral chos sku'i rang zhal ston mdzad pa //
NK095(ce)001:38: klong chen rab 'byams snying gi pad+mora rol //
NK095(ce)001:39: rab 'byams rtsa gsum rgyal ba'i spyi gzugs mchog /gang 'dul gdul bya'i dpal du yongs snang ba //
NK095(ce)001:40: bka' drin 'gran bral rtsa ba'i bla ma de //
NK095(ce)001:41: byang chub bar du rigs kyi bdag por brten //
NK095(ce)001:42: kun tu bzang mo'i ye shes sgyu 'phrul gar //
NK095(ce)001:43: srid zhir dbang bsgyur rgyal kun skyed pa'i yum //
NK095(ce)001:44: ka dag dbyings kyi rje mo ral gcig mas //
NK095(ce)001:45: deng 'dir bka' 'di bkrol la gnang ba stsol //
NK095(ce)001:46: sems nyid rang bzhin gzod nas 'od gsal rang bzhin gzhi yi kun tu bzang //
NK095(ce)001:47: mnyam nyid dri med chos sku'i mkha' dbyings spros kun rab zhi'i ngang nyid las //
NK095(ce)001:48: gdangs kyi ye shes sems dpa' rdo rje yul drug mdzin pa'i rnam par shes //
NK095(ce)001:49: gzung dang 'dzin pa gnyis su med gang kun byed rgyud rgyal gsal bar bya //
NK095(ce)001:50: 'dir rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po /
NK095(ce)001:51: lung thams cad kyi rtsa ba /
NK095(ce)001:52: man ngag thams cad kyi nying khu /
NK095(ce)001:53: bstan pa thams cad kyi snying po /
NK095(ce)001:54: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK095(ce)001:56: lta ba thams cad kyi me long /
NK095(ce)001:57: rgyud dang mdo sde kun gyi spyi 'grel /
NK095(ce)001:59: rgyal ba thams cad bskyed par byed pa'i yum /
NK095(ce)001:60: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel bar byed pa /
NK095(ce)001:61: ye shes chen po'i snang ba 'char bar byed pa /
NK095(ce)001:62: nyon mongs pa'i phreng thag gcod par byed pa /
NK095(ce)001:63: sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho 'dral bar byed pa /
NK095(ce)001:65: skal ldan thams cad dus gcig la grol bar byed pa'i rgyud /
NK095(ce)001:66: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po /
NK095(ce)001:67: lta ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa /
NK095(ce)001:68: sems nyid bya btsal med pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:69: chen po 'di 'chad par byed pa la gsum ste
NK095(ce)001:70: / bshad pa la 'jug pa'i rgyu dang /
NK095(ce)001:71: rgyud dngos ji ltar bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:72: yongs su rdzogs pa'i don no //
NK095(ce)001:76: dang po la mtshan rgya skad ltar smos pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:79: mtshan gyi don bshad pa dang bzhi las /
NK095(ce)001:81: rgya gar gyi yul na skad rig chen po mi
NK095(ce)001:82: 'dra ba bzhi yod pa las khyad par du 'phags
NK095(ce)001:83: pa legs sbyar sam skri ta lha'i skad du rgyud
NK095(ce)001:84: kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid kyi mtshan la
NK095(ce)001:85: / sarba d+harma ma h+aa san+ti bo d+hi tsi t+ta ku la ya r+aa dz+aa /
NK095(ce)001:87: gnyis pa de bod skad du bsgyur na chos thams
NK095(ce)001:88: cad rdzogs pa chen po byang chub kyi sems kun
NK095(ce)001:89: byed rgyal po / zhes gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:90: gsum pa skad de gnyis shan sbyar na /
NK095(ce)001:91: sarba d+harma ni chos thams cad dang /
NK095(ce)001:92: de bzhin tu ma h+aa san+ti rdzogs pa chen po /
NK095(ce)001:93: bo d+hi tsit+ta byang chub kyi sems /
NK095(ce)001:94: ku la ya r+aa dz+aa kun byed rgyal po zhes pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:95: bzhi pa mtshan de'i don ni /
NK095(ce)001:96: spyir mtshan gyi 'dogs tshul la sa lu ljong pa'i
NK095(ce)001:97: mdo ces pa lta bu dpe la btags pa dang
NK095(ce)001:98: / sher phyin 'bum pa lta bu tshad kyi sgo nas btags pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:99: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo lta bu gang zag gi ming gis btags pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:100: dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su 'dzin pa'i mdo zhes pa lta bu byed las las btags pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:101: lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo lta bu yul gyi sgo nas btags pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:102: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo lta bu dus kyi sgo nas btags pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:103: ting 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo lta bu don gyi sgo nas btags pa rnams yod pa las /
NK095(ce)001:104: 'dir ni brjod bya'i don gyi sgo nas mtshan btags pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:105: 'di ltar gzhi lam 'bras bu'i bsdus pa'i chos thamsa
NK095(ce)001:106: cad da lta'i rang sems ma bcos mnyam pa chen
NK095(ce)001:107: po ka dag skye ba med pa 'di nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:108: klong du rang byung lhun grub kyi tshul du ma
NK095(ce)001:109: 'dres par yongs su rdzogs shing 'dus pas na rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:112: snang srid snod bcud thams cad dang //
NK095(ce)001:113: sangs rgyas sems cad thams cad dang //
NK095(ce)001:114: bstan pa'i theg pa thams cad kun //
NK095(ce)001:117: rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me long las /
NK095(ce)001:118: rdzogs chen theg pa'i nges tshig ni /
NK095(ce)001:119: rig pa bya bral ngang la ye shes rdzogs pas rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:120: bsgom pa rtog med ngang la ye shes dri med rdzogs pas rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:121: spyod pa bcos med ngang la ye shes brdal ba rdzogs pas rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:122: lta ba dgag bsgrub med pa'i ngang la ye shes rtogs med rdzogs pas rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:123: 'bras bu dmigs med ngang la ye shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs pas rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:124: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar la /
NK095(ce)001:125: de lta bu'i sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:126: srid zhi kun khyab chen po 'di las thob bya'i
NK095(ce)001:127: 'bras bu mthar thug pa gzhan med pa dang theg
NK095(ce)001:128: pa kun gyi rtse mor gyur pa yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:131: theg pa kun gyi rtse mor gyur pas che //
NK095(ce)001:132: gnas lugs don la yengs ba med pas che //
NK095(ce)001:133: lta ba kun gyi rtse mor gyur pas che //
NK095(ce)001:134: sgom pa kun gyi rtse mor gyur pas che //
NK095(ce)001:135: spyod pa kun gyi rtse mor gyur pas che //
NK095(ce)001:136: 'bras bu kun gyi rtse mor gyur pas che //
NK095(ce)001:137: 'gyur med ngang la 'gag med rtsol bas che //
NK095(ce)001:138: 'dzin med ngang la rtog med gsal bas che //
NK095(ce)001:139: zhen med ngang la chags med gsal bas che //
NK095(ce)001:140: brjod med ngang la bde chen gsal bas che //
NK095(ce)001:141: rnam dag byang chub brdal ba'i snying po yin pas che //
NK095(ce)001:142: bya btsal bral ba'i rig pa dngos med yin pas che //
NK095(ce)001:143: bde chen ngang las mi g.yo mnyam par gnas pas che //
NK095(ce)001:144: snying po'i don la mi g.yo mnyam par gnas pas che //
NK095(ce)001:145: 'dzin pa'i spyod yul ma yin kun la yod pas che //
NK095(ce)001:146: tshig dang yi ges gtan la mi pheb kun gyi snying po yin pas che //
NK095(ce)001:149: rdzogs pa ni lhag ma ma lus pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:150: chen po ni ma byas pa dang gong na med pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:152: de lta bu'i stong gsal 'dus ma byas pa'i sems
NK095(ce)001:153: nyid rang byung gi ye shes 'di la ye nas
NK095(ce)001:154: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i chos kyi ma gos pas byang
NK095(ce)001:155: ba dang / yon tan thams cad ma btsal lhun gyis grub pas chub ces gsungs shing /
NK095(ce)001:156: thugs rje 'gag pa med pa'i rtsal gdangs so so
NK095(ce)001:157: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal snang 'gags med
NK095(ce)001:160: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:161: rang byung ye shes gzhi klong yangs pa la //
NK095(ce)001:162: ye nas dri med 'khor bas ma gos byang //
NK095(ce)001:163: yon tan lhun grub rgyu 'bras 'das pas chub //
NK095(ce)001:164: rang rig snying po 'od gsal dag pas sems //
NK095(ce)001:166: gnas lugs rang byung gi ye shes de nyid 'khor
NK095(ce)001:167: 'das kyi chos ma lus mi lus lus pa med
NK095(ce)001:168: pa kun gyi byeda pa por gyur pa'am 'di nyid
NK095(ce)001:169: kyi rtsal las shar ba'i mnyam pa chen po gcig
NK095(ce)001:170: gi rang bzhin yin zhing rang gi ngo bo ye
NK095(ce)001:171: nas lhun grub 'dus ma byas pa yin pas rgyu
NK095(ce)001:172: rkyen gzhan gang gis kyang bya mi dgos par byed
NK095(ce)001:173: pa'i mkhan po kun las rgyal po ru gyur pa
NK095(ce)001:174: yin phyir blang dor 'bad rtsol dang bral bar bstan
NK095(ce)001:175: pa ste / de ltar don gyi sgo nas mtshan smos pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:176: de ltar yang rgyud 'di nyid las /
NK095(ce)001:177: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK095(ce)001:178: ma lus kun byas byed cing byed 'gyur te //
NK095(ce)001:179: nyid la bya mi dgos te lhun grub pas //
NK095(ce)001:180: kun byed rgyal po zhes su bstan pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:182: de ltar mtshan btags zhing klad du smos pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:183: dbang po rab kyis chos thams cad ye nas bya
NK095(ce)001:184: btsal med par byang chub sems kyi ngo bor sangs
NK095(ce)001:185: rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du go nas rgyud don yongs
NK095(ce)001:186: su rtogs pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:187: dbang po 'bring gis don gyi phyogs tsam rtogs pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:188: dbang po tha mas kyang sman snod la kha byang
NK095(ce)001:189: btags pa ltar glegs bam btsal sla ba'i dgos pa
NK095(ce)001:190: yod do // gnyis pa phyag gi don ni /
NK095(ce)001:191: de la bcom ldan 'das zhes pa ni spyir bdud
NK095(ce)001:192: bzhi la sogs pa mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad
NK095(ce)001:193: bcoma pa ni spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa dang
NK095(ce)001:194: / legs pa'i yon tan drug dang ldan pa ni rtogs pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:195: 'khor 'das dang rtag chad la sogs pa'i spros pa'i
NK095(ce)001:196: mtha' thams cad las 'das pa ni zhi ba'i mtshan
NK095(ce)001:197: nyid can te / phal po che las /
NK095(ce)001:198: srid dang zhi las rnam grol zhing //
NK095(ce)001:199: yon tan rgya mtsho gnyis su med //
NK095(ce)001:200: spros pa kun las rab 'das pa'i //
NK095(ce)001:201: bcom ldan 'das ni mkha' rab zhi //
NK095(ce)001:203: de las kyang 'dir chos sku la sbyar na /
NK095(ce)001:204: rig pa byang chub kyi sems skye 'gags mtshan ma'i
NK095(ce)001:205: chos su ma grub pas skye shi dang bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:207: yul med zang thal chen po'i ngo bor gnas pas lha bu'i bdud bcom /
NK095(ce)001:208: rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i bdag nyid yin pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK095(ce)001:209: ka dag gzhi rtsa dang bral ba'i bdag nyid yin pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:211: chos sku skye med 'gags pa med pas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK095(ce)001:212: mtshan ma med pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK095(ce)001:213: de gnyis su med pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud dang lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK095(ce)001:214: de ni ngang gis bcom pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:216: legs pa'i yon tan drug gi bdag nyid sku lnga
NK095(ce)001:217: ye shes lnga yi ngo bor ye nas bzhugs pa
NK095(ce)001:220: chos sku yon tan sgo yangs bas //
NK095(ce)001:221: ye shes lnga dang sku lnga ldan //
NK095(ce)001:223: de yang legs pa'i yon tan drug ni /
NK095(ce)001:225: dbang phyug dang ni gzugs bzang dang //
NK095(ce)001:226: dpal dang grags dang ye shes dang //
NK095(ce)001:227: brtson 'grus phun sum tshogs pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:228: drug po rnams la ldan zhes bya //
NK095(ce)001:229: zhes pas chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i dbang
NK095(ce)001:230: phyug ni ngo bo nyid kyis dag pa chos kyi
NK095(ce)001:231: sku dang chos dbyings ye shes so //
NK095(ce)001:232: mtshan dpe'i gzugs bzang ba ni longs spyod rdzogs sku dang me long ye shes so //
NK095(ce)001:233: legs pa'i yon tan kun gyi dpal dang ldan pa
NK095(ce)001:234: ni mngon par byang chub pa'i sku dang mnyam pa
NK095(ce)001:236: phyogs bcu'i zhing rnams kun tu grags shing snang ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:237: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa' ye shes dang ldan
NK095(ce)001:238: pa ni sprul pa'i sku dang so sor rtogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:239: ye shes so // 'gro ba'i don la g.yel ba
NK095(ce)001:240: med pa'i brtson 'grus phun sum tshogs pa ni dbyings
NK095(ce)001:241: las 'pho 'gyur med pa mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku
NK095(ce)001:242: dang phrin las tshad med pas 'gro don rtsol med
NK095(ce)001:243: du mdzad pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so
NK095(ce)001:245: gi phyogs su ma lhung zhing spros pa'i mtshan ma
NK095(ce)001:246: kun las 'das pa'i don yin te /
NK095(ce)001:248: chos sku mtha' rnams kun las 'das //
NK095(ce)001:250: yang rnam pa gcig tu na /
NK095(ce)001:251: gnas lugs ji bzhin rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis ma
NK095(ce)001:252: rig log rtog gi bdud bcom zhing mkhyen pa' ye
NK095(ce)001:254: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog gi mtha' las 'das pas na yang de skad ces gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:256: rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis log par rtog pa'i bdud bcom ste /
NK095(ce)001:257: mkhyen pa'i stobs dang ldan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:258: gzung 'dzin gyi mtha' las 'das pas na bcom ldan 'das so //
NK095(ce)001:260: de ltar spang rtogs kyi yon tan mtha' phyin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:261: bdag nyid can gdod nas ye sangs rgyas pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:262: bzhin rig pa byanga chuba kyi sems dang po'i sangs
NK095(ce)001:263: rgyas kun tu bzang po'am 'khor 'das kyi chos kun
NK095(ce)001:264: la dbang bsgyur bar byed pas kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:265: de la rnam snang sprul pa'i lo ts+aa chen pos
NK095(ce)001:266: 'gyur la bar chad med cing mthar phyin pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:267: du 'khor gsum dmigs mtha' dang bral bas phyag 'atshala
NK095(ce)001:268: lo zhes rgyud 'di bsgyur ba'i thog mar 'gyur phyag
NK095(ce)001:269: mdzad pa ste / ched du brjod pa'i tshoms las /
NK095(ce)001:270: bsod nams bsags pa'i mi dag la //
NK095(ce)001:271: gzhan las gyur pa'i gnod pa'am //
NK095(ce)001:272: lha 'am bdud kyi rigs rnams kyis //
NK095(ce)001:273: bar chad bya bar mi nus so //
NK095(ce)001:274: zhes yul khyad par can la phyag mdzad pas bsod
NK095(ce)001:275: nams kyi tshogs rdzogs shing bsod nams dang ldan pa
NK095(ce)001:276: la gzhan gyis bar chad mi nus pas so //
NK095(ce)001:278: rtsa rgyud thos pa'i shes rab la gdams pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:279: phyi ma bsam byung gi shes rab la gdams pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:280: phyi ma'i phyi ma bsgom byung gi shes rab la gdams pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:282: gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa'i tshul gyis rgyud mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:283: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'i tshul gyis rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:284: snying po phun sum tshogs pa'i tshul gyis don bsdu ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:289: phun sum tshogs pa lnga yi rang bzhin mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:290: de'i bye brag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:292: de la 'di skad ces smos pa ni 'og nas
NK095(ce)001:293: 'byung ba'i rgyud don yongs su rdzogs pa la go
NK095(ce)001:294: dgos pas chos phun sum tshogs pa bstan la /
NK095(ce)001:295: bashada pa'a tshig gis sdud pa po sems dpa' rdo
NK095(ce)001:296: rje nyid ston pa phun sum tshogs pa nyid yin
NK095(ce)001:297: par zhal gyis bzhes pas ston 'khor gnyis ka bstan
NK095(ce)001:298: pa ste / de la thos pa zhes mi smos
NK095(ce)001:299: pa ni theg pa thun mong pa'i skabs su ston
NK095(ce)001:300: 'khor rgyud tha dad du snang ba las khyad par
NK095(ce)001:301: du 'phags pa 'dir ston 'khor dbyer med du ston
NK095(ce)001:302: pa'i tshig yin par sngon gyi mkhas dbang rig 'dzin
NK095(ce)001:303: gong ma rnams kyis gsungs pa ltar 'dir yang yin
NK095(ce)001:304: pa ste / de / 'og min chos sku'i zhing
NK095(ce)001:305: khams de na bdag gzhan tha dad du phye ba
NK095(ce)001:306: med par chos thams cad ston pa kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:307: po'i thugs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes gcig
NK095(ce)001:308: gi rang bzhin du bstan pa'i phyir te /
NK095(ce)001:310: nga ni ye nas kun byed rgyal po yin //
NK095(ce)001:311: ston pa bstan pa 'khor dus nges byas nas //
NK095(ce)001:312: ston pa'i ston pa yang ni nga yis byed //
NK095(ce)001:313: bstan pa nga yi rang bzhin de ston la //
NK095(ce)001:314: 'khor yang nga yi ngo bo de byung nas //
NK095(ce)001:315: dus gnas nga yi rang bzhin de rgyud ni //
NK095(ce)001:316: kun byed nga yi rang bzhin bstan pa las //
NK095(ce)001:317: nga min chos ni gcig kyang bstan pa med //
NK095(ce)001:318: sems dpa' chen po rdo rje khyod nyid kyang //
NK095(ce)001:319: kun byed nga yi rang bzhin bstan pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:320: khyod kyang nga las nga yis phyung ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:321: kun byed nga ni chos kyi snying por zhog /ces gsungs pa ltar dang /
NK095(ce)001:322: dus na zhes pas dus bzhi mnyam pa chen po
NK095(ce)001:323: ka dag skye ba med pa'i ngang na 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:324: dang dus gsum gyi dbye ba med pas 'od gsal
NK095(ce)001:325: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus phun sum tshogs pa
NK095(ce)001:326: bstan la / de ltar chos kyi sku yi ston
NK095(ce)001:327: 'khor bstan pa rnams gang du snang ba'i gnas de
NK095(ce)001:328: nyid chos dbyings don gyi 'og min chen por lhun
NK095(ce)001:329: gyis grub pa yin pas na gnas phun sum tshogs
NK095(ce)001:330: pa nyid don gyi shugs las bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:331: de lta bu'i phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan
NK095(ce)001:332: pa'i chos sku'i zhing khams de nyid phyogs ga shed
NK095(ce)001:333: na gnas ris chad can du ci yang med par
NK095(ce)001:334: nam mkha'i khams dang chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab
NK095(ce)001:335: par chos sku'i zhing khams kyis khyab cing /
NK095(ce)001:336: chos sku'i gar khyab par longs sku dang sprul sku'i
NK095(ce)001:337: zhing khams kyang 'gog pa med pas dper na dung
NK095(ce)001:338: la ser snang ltar du sems can rnams la rang
NK095(ce)001:339: rang gi rtog pa'i dbang gis ma dag pa ltar
NK095(ce)001:340: du snang na yang don la ma dag pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:341: su grub pa rdul tsam yang med par sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:342: rgyal ba'i zhing khams chen po gcig gi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:343: las ma 'das pas na ngo bo la dag pa
NK095(ce)001:344: nyag gcig gi rang bzhin yin te /
NK095(ce)001:345: 'di ltar dri ma med par grags pa'i mdo las /
NK095(ce)001:346: btsun pa sh+aa ri'i bus smras pa /
NK095(ce)001:347: bdag gis sa chen po 'di mtho dman dang g.yang
NK095(ce)001:348: sa dang ljan ljin gyis gang bar mthong ngo zhes
NK095(ce)001:349: zer ro // sangs rgyas mya ngan med pa'i zhing
NK095(ce)001:350: nas 'ongs pa'i tshangs pa ral pa can gyis smras
NK095(ce)001:351: zer ro // pa / bdag gis ni bcom ldan
NK095(ce)001:352: 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i zhing 'di nyid gzhan 'phrul dbang
NK095(ce)001:353: byed kyi lha'i gnas kyi bkod pa phun sum tshogs
NK095(ce)001:354: pa bzhin tu yongs su dag par mthong ngo zhes
NK095(ce)001:355: zer ro // pa / zer ro // de nas
NK095(ce)001:356: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor rnams la
NK095(ce)001:357: sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di'i rang bzhin bstan par mdzad
NK095(ce)001:358: zer ro // pa / zer ro // pas /
NK095(ce)001:359: thams cad kyis shar phyogs kyi sangs rgyas rin po
NK095(ce)001:360: che'i rgyan bkod pa'i zhing khams bzhin yongs su dag
NK095(ce)001:361: par mthong bar gyur pa de'i tshe /
NK095(ce)001:362: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK095(ce)001:363: nga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di ni rtag tu 'di 'dra ste /
NK095(ce)001:364: khyod rnams kyis mi mthong ngo //
NK095(ce)001:366: 'on kyang gnas lugs mthar thug pa'i dbang du na
NK095(ce)001:367: de ltar dag dang ma dag gi dbye ba tsam
NK095(ce)001:368: yang med par spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad ngang
NK095(ce)001:369: gis zhi ba chos sku thig le nyag gcig gis
NK095(ce)001:370: rab tu phye ba tsam las ci yang med de
NK095(ce)001:371: / bang mdzod 'phrul gyi lde mig las /
NK095(ce)001:372: rgyu nyid gser du gcig pa las //
NK095(ce)001:373: bzo yi las kyis bsgyur byas te //
NK095(ce)001:374: chol zangs dri snod byas tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:375: gser yang ngan pa'i rgyu ru snang //
NK095(ce)001:376: sku gzugs mchod rten byas tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:377: gser yang bzang po'i rdzas su snang //
NK095(ce)001:378: gser gyi rgyu la bzang ngan med //
NK095(ce)001:379: de bzhin chos nyid rgyud gcig pas //
NK095(ce)001:380: rnam rtog 'khrul pas brtags tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:381: yul yang ma dag 'jig rten khams //
NK095(ce)001:382: ngan grog g.yang sa lung khung snang //
NK095(ce)001:383: ye shes can gyi ngo gang la //
NK095(ce)001:384: yul yang zhing khams dag pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:385: bde ba can gyi gnas su snang //
NK095(ce)001:386: chos nyid rang gi ngo bo la //
NK095(ce)001:387: snang dang mi snang gnyis su med //
NK095(ce)001:389: de ltar 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bzang ngan
NK095(ce)001:390: dang tha dad du grub pa med par sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:391: kun byed rgyal po gcig gi bdag nyid yin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:392: phyir na da lta sems can rnams kyi dbang po
NK095(ce)001:393: sgo lngar snang ba 'di las phun sum tshogs pa
NK095(ce)001:394: lnga zhing gzhan du med par la bzla bar yang
NK095(ce)001:395: gsungs te / la zlo gsang ba'i 'khor lo las /
NK095(ce)001:396: ston pa dang ni bstan pa 'khor dus gnas //
NK095(ce)001:397: rang byung chos kyi dbyings su la bzlas pas //
NK095(ce)001:398: rang byung ngo bo mngon du phyung ba la //
NK095(ce)001:399: phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa lnga po yang //
NK095(ce)001:400: rang la rdzogs shing rang la tshang bar ston //
NK095(ce)001:401: rang la dmigs su med par dbyings su la zlo yin /
NK095(ce)001:403: mig gi dbang pos gzugs rnams cir yang ston //
NK095(ce)001:404: kun byed rgyal po'i sku ru bstan pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:405: de las gzhan pa'i ston pa dmigs su med //
NK095(ce)001:406: de las ston pa rang la tshang zhes gsungs //
NK095(ce)001:407: lces ni snang srid tshig dang yi ger brjod //
NK095(ce)001:408: sgra rnams bsgrags pa ston pa'i gsungs yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:409: bstan pa'i chos zhes kun la grags pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:410: rna bas sgra rnams ji ltar gsan pa yang //
NK095(ce)001:411: kun byed rgyal po'i sgra bsgrags gsan pa las //
NK095(ce)001:412: de las gzhan pa'i sgra ni thos pa med //
NK095(ce)001:413: de thos 'khor gyi dam par byung ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:414: dri rnams sna tshogs ji ltar byung ba yang //
NK095(ce)001:415: sna yi dbang po gcig las ma 'das pas //
NK095(ce)001:416: dbyer med dus gsum gcig tu bstan pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:417: mig dang rna ba sna dang lce la sogs //
NK095(ce)001:418: thams cad lus la gnas pas gnas su bstan //
NK095(ce)001:419: lus gnas pa la kun kyang gnas pa las //
NK095(ce)001:420: lus mi gnas na su yang gnas pa med //
NK095(ce)001:421: de bas lus 'di gnas su bstan pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:424: gnas dang 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:426: de la spyir 'og min zhes pa'i don ni de
NK095(ce)001:427: nyid las gong na gzhan med pa'am 'og tu ma
NK095(ce)001:429: de la bye brag tu dbye na /
NK095(ce)001:430: chos dbyings don gyi 'og min dang /
NK095(ce)001:435: 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min dang drug tu gsungs pa las 'di ni snga ma gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:437: chos sku'i gnas bsam brjod las 'das pa chos dbyings don gyi 'og min no //
NK095(ce)001:439: gsang 'grel phyogs bcu mun sel las /
NK095(ce)001:440: rig pa'i 'og min dngos po'i gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin rtogs pa'i rig pa'i ye shes te /
NK095(ce)001:441: dag pa gnyis ldan gyi chos sku'i bzhugs gnas yin
NK095(ce)001:442: zhing 'di'i gong na rig pa gzhan med pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:443: ro // zhes gsungs pa ltar la /
NK095(ce)001:444: de yang yul yul can tha dad du grub pa
NK095(ce)001:445: med par ye nas dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:446: pa'i gnas lugs de nyid gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i spros
NK095(ce)001:447: pa gang gi yang 'og tu ma gyur pas na
NK095(ce)001:448: 'og min / rgyal ba thams cad gnas lugs de
NK095(ce)001:449: nyid kyi ngang las skad cig kyang mi g.yo bar
NK095(ce)001:450: bzhugs pas gnas zhes gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:451: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs spros bral rang byung
NK095(ce)001:452: gi ye shes chos nyid skye ba med pa de
NK095(ce)001:453: nyid kyi don ji lta ba bzhin du rtogs pa
NK095(ce)001:454: las dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad 'byung ba'
NK095(ce)001:455: gnas su gyur pas na dus gsum rgyal ba'i bskyed
NK095(ce)001:456: yum stong chen rdo rje btsun mo'i mkha'a yang de
NK095(ce)001:457: nyid yin la / ji ltar snang ba'i 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:458: kyi chos thams cad 'byung yang chos nyid skye ba
NK095(ce)001:459: med pa de nyid kyi ngang las 'byung zhing gnas
NK095(ce)001:460: kyang de'i ngang las 'da' ba med par gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:461: nyid yin la / dang / grol kyang de'i ngang
NK095(ce)001:462: du grol bas dbyingsa nyid kyi klong zhes gsungs te
NK095(ce)001:463: nyid yin la / dang / / chos dbyings mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:464: mnyam nyid gcig la cir snang 'byung bas dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:465: yon tan thams cad bskyed par byed pas gzhi //
NK095(ce)001:466: thams cad bya byed med par grol bas klong //
NK095(ce)001:467: kun 'byung snying por shar bas byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:468: mkha' 'dra gdod nas dag pa shes par bya //
NK095(ce)001:470: des na de lta bu'i chos dbyings don gyi 'og
NK095(ce)001:471: min chen po de nyid sems nyid rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:472: ye shes chos sku kun byed rgyal po nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:473: bzhugs gnas yin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:475: ston pa chos sku'i gnas ni 'di lta ste //
NK095(ce)001:476: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang ste //
NK095(ce)001:477: yang dag don gyi 'og min de ru bshad //
NK095(ce)001:478: ces gsungs pa de lta bu'i zhing khams de na
NK095(ce)001:479: ye shes rang snang ba la chags thog gi sgrib
NK095(ce)001:480: pa mi mang'a ba'i 'od gsal ba'i gzhal yas khang
NK095(ce)001:481: na zhes 'dir sangs rgyas kyi rang snang nyag gcig
NK095(ce)001:482: yin pas de la gzigs bya gzigs byed sogs gnyis
NK095(ce)001:483: chos gang yang mi mnga' bas dkyil 'khor gyi dbyibs
NK095(ce)001:484: dang bkod pa rgyan dang kha dog la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:485: mtshan ma ris chad can du snang ba yang med
NK095(ce)001:486: mod / 'on kyang sems nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK095(ce)001:487: par dag pa chos nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK095(ce)001:488: po'i rtsal las rang shar ba' 'od gsal lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:489: kyi bkod pa tshad med pas brgyan pa'i gzhal med
NK095(ce)001:490: khang na ston 'khor thams cad snang cha ma 'dres
NK095(ce)001:491: par bzhugs yod par yang gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:492: rdzogs pa chen po bkra shis mi 'gyur ba'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:493: chos kyi dbyings kyi ngang dpe las /
NK095(ce)001:494: bde bar gshegs pa bcom ldan 'das //
NK095(ce)001:495: sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po dpal //
NK095(ce)001:496: rdo rje sku gsung thugs kyi bdag /bde chen lhun gyis rdzogs pa yis //
NK095(ce)001:497: phyogs dus bde gshegs kun bdag nyid //
NK095(ce)001:498: dkyil 'khor chen pos mdzes par brgyan //
NK095(ce)001:499: snang ba rnam par 'phrul ba yi //
NK095(ce)001:500: ma 'gags che bar rab tu bkod //
NK095(ce)001:501: dkyil 'khor kun 'byung bzang mo'i mkha' //kun bzang cho 'phrul ma 'gags par //
NK095(ce)001:502: sna tshogs kha dog rnam gsal zhing //
NK095(ce)001:503: sna tshogs dbyibs brgyan tha dad pa'i //
NK095(ce)001:504: so so'i bya rtsal 'gags med chos //
NK095(ce)001:505: sgrib med nor bu'i mdangs lta bu //
NK095(ce)001:508: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun rig rgyal po ste //
NK095(ce)001:509: rang byung sems la ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK095(ce)001:510: de nyid chos sku ston pa kun tu bzang //
NK095(ce)001:511: 'og min bde chen gnas mchog chos kyi dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:512: phyi nang med par mdzes shing 'od gsal ba'i //
NK095(ce)001:513: yid bzhin rgyan gyi spras shing blta na sdug /yangs dog med pa'i gzhal yas khang na bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:514: zhes gsungs pa des na tshur mthong gi blos mtha' gcig tu gzhal ba'i yul las 'das pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:515: gnyis pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:516: snang srid gdod nas dag pa sku gsum gyi 'khor dang /
NK095(ce)001:517: lam mngon par snang ba rnal 'byor bzhi'i 'khor dang /
NK095(ce)001:518: 'bras bu gzhi thog tu grol ba dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi 'khor ro //
NK095(ce)001:524: de lta bu'i chos dbyings don gyi 'og min na
NK095(ce)001:525: bzhugs pa'i sku gsum gyi rgyal ba ma lus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:526: ston pa rang byung gi sangs rgyas kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:527: po nyid la / rang snang ma 'gags pa'i rtsal
NK095(ce)001:528: las rang shar ba'i 'khor gyi tshogs ni ston pa
NK095(ce)001:529: byang chub kyi sems nyid kyi rang bzhina gyi 'khor
NK095(ce)001:530: chos kyi sku zhes bya ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:531: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi 'khor longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhes bya ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:532: nyid kyi thugsa rje ye shesa kyi 'khor sprul pa'i sku zhes bya ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:533: de ltar ston pa nyid kyi thugs rig pa rang
NK095(ce)001:534: byung gi rtsal las mngona du phyunga ba'am mngon du
NK095(ce)001:535: snang ba'i 'khor sku gsum po ni 'chad 'gyur 'di
NK095(ce)001:538: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa stong pa nyid chos sku'i 'khor dang /
NK095(ce)001:539: ngo bo 'byung ba lngar snang ba gsal stong longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i 'khor dang /
NK095(ce)001:540: thugs rje rig pa'i ye shes khams gsum sems can du snang ba sprul sku'i 'khor ro //
NK095(ce)001:542: de la byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:543: nyid kyi gnas lugs sam rang bzhina yod med dang
NK095(ce)001:544: rtag chad skye 'gag la sogs pa'i spros pa thams
NK095(ce)001:545: cad dang bral ba rnam kun mchog ldana gyi stong
NK095(ce)001:546: pa nyid kyi 'khora ni chos kyi sku zhes bya
NK095(ce)001:547: ba'i 'khor dang / zhes 'dir rang bzhin stong pa
NK095(ce)001:548: dang ngo bo gsal ba'i cha la bzhag pa'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:549: ba'i 'khor dang / ni / gnas lugs rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:550: rang bzhin stong ngo bo gsal ba ni gshis dang de'i snying por dbye ba'i skabs yin la /
NK095(ce)001:551: ngo bo stong rang bzhin gsal ba ni dbyings dang dbyings kyi snying po ston par phye yang /
NK095(ce)001:552: don la stong pa chos sku /
NK095(ce)001:554: 'char tshul sprul skur gcig pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:555: zhes gsungs pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK095(ce)001:557: byang chub kyi sems nyid kyi ngo bo snang srid
NK095(ce)001:558: dag pa chen por rang shar ba ni rang las
NK095(ce)001:559: shar ba'i snang ba la rang gi longs spyod pas
NK095(ce)001:560: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i 'khor du bzhag pa ste
NK095(ce)001:561: / de yang snying po rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:562: ston pa kun byed nyid kyi ngo bo'i 'khor longsa
NK095(ce)001:563: spyod rdzogsa pa'i sku sra zhing 'thas pa'i mtshan nyid
NK095(ce)001:564: dang ldan pas thams cad brten pa'i don byed pa
NK095(ce)001:566: nyida kyi ngo bo'i 'khora longs spyod rdzogsa pa'i sku
NK095(ce)001:567: rlan zhing gsher ba'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pas thams
NK095(ce)001:568: cad sdud pa'i don byed pa chu zhes bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:569: 'khor dang / nyid kyi ngo bo'i 'khor longs spyod
NK095(ce)001:570: rdzogs pa'i sku tsha zhing bsreg pa'i mtshan nyid dang
NK095(ce)001:571: ldan pas thams cad smin pa'i don byed pa me
NK095(ce)001:573: nyid kyi ngo bo'i 'khora longs spyoda rdzogsa pa'i sku
NK095(ce)001:574: yang zhing g.yo ba'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pas thams
NK095(ce)001:575: cad 'degs pa'i don byed pa rlunga zhesa bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:576: 'khora dang / nyid kyi ngo bo'i 'khora longsa spyod
NK095(ce)001:577: rdzogsa pa'i sku kun la khyab cing thogs reg med
NK095(ce)001:578: pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pas thams cad la go
NK095(ce)001:579: 'byed pa'i don byed pa nama mkha' zhes bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:580: 'khor dang lnga po de ni byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:581: ngo bo rgyal ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur ye
NK095(ce)001:582: nas sangs rgyas pa yin par gsungs ste /
NK095(ce)001:584: snang ba'i chos dang srid pa'i chos //
NK095(ce)001:585: de yang snang ba'i 'byung chen lnga //
NK095(ce)001:586: nam mkha' snang byed khyab pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:587: sems nyid ma bsgrib kun la khyab //
NK095(ce)001:588: de bas nam mkha' byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:589: snang byed khyab pas mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:591: byang chub sems kyi ye shes rlung //
NK095(ce)001:592: ye shes rlung gi kun 'degs pas //
NK095(ce)001:593: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:594: thams cad sdud pa'i 'byung ba chu //
NK095(ce)001:595: ye shes thugs rje'i rlan gyis sdud //
NK095(ce)001:596: de bas byang chub sems kyi chu //
NK095(ce)001:597: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:598: mngon sum snang ba sra byed pa //
NK095(ce)001:599: thams cad 'degs pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:600: de bas sems kyi sa de la //
NK095(ce)001:601: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:602: thams cad drod snyom tsha ba'i me //
NK095(ce)001:603: pad+ma rnam dag ye shes de //
NK095(ce)001:604: de bas sems nyid rnam dag pas //
NK095(ce)001:605: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:606: 'byung chen lnga yi sangs rgyas lnga //
NK095(ce)001:607: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:610: gong du bstan pa'i 'khor de dag las gazhana yang
NK095(ce)001:611: sems nyid rang byung gi rol pa thugsa rje 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:612: ba med pa'i ye shes kyi rnam 'phrul mngona du
NK095(ce)001:613: phyunga ba'i sprul pa'i 'khora ni 'di lta ste /
NK095(ce)001:614: 'dod pa'i 'dod chags dang ldan pas 'dod pa'i khamsa
NK095(ce)001:615: kyi gnas ris nyi shu'i semsa can zhes bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:616: 'khor dang / bsam gtan gyi bde ba dang ldan
NK095(ce)001:617: pa'i dngas ma 'od kyi lus dang ldan pas gzugs
NK095(ce)001:618: kyi khams kyi gnas ris bcu bdun gyi sems can
NK095(ce)001:620: gnas gzugs rag pa dang bral bas gzugas med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:621: khams kyi skye mched mu bzhi'i sems can zhes bya
NK095(ce)001:622: ba'i 'khor dang / gsum po de ni sprul sku'i 'khor yin no //
NK095(ce)001:623: 'di ltar khams gsum na 'khor ba'i sems can rang
NK095(ce)001:624: rgyud pa de dag sangs rgyas rang snang gi 'khor
NK095(ce)001:626: 'dir ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la bzang
NK095(ce)001:627: ngan gnyis su med par kun byed byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:628: kyi rol rtsal mnyam pa chen po gcig gi rang
NK095(ce)001:629: bzhin yin pas chos dbyings don gyi 'og min na
NK095(ce)001:630: chos sku gdod ma'i mgon po dang 'byed pa med
NK095(ce)001:631: par thabs gcig tu bzhugs pa yin par gsungs te
NK095(ce)001:636: rang byung ma bsgribs pa'i gzhal yas khang na dus gsum gcig pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK095(ce)001:637: mi skye lam la blta ba'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:638: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:639: nges pa thob pa rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:640: snying pos bsdus pa'i srid pa gsum yan chad /
NK095(ce)001:641: 'byed pa mi mnga' ba'i thugs rje'i dbang gis thabs gcig go //
NK095(ce)001:643: de bzhin du khams gsum po 'di nyid kun byed
NK095(ce)001:644: byang chub sems kyi sku gsung thugs su sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:648: 'dod pa'i khams ni ma rig pa //
NK095(ce)001:649: phye ba med par kun la rmongs //
NK095(ce)001:650: mi rtog gti mug chos kyi sku //
NK095(ce)001:651: gzugs kyi khams ni chags pa'i gnas //
NK095(ce)001:652: nga rgyal chags pa mngon grub pas //
NK095(ce)001:653: gzugs la nga rgyal blta mi ngom //
NK095(ce)001:654: ltung ba chags med ye shes sku //
NK095(ce)001:655: gzugs med khams ni dngos ma grub //
NK095(ce)001:656: yid yul chos la mu bzhi blta //
NK095(ce)001:657: gzung 'dzin med par rig pa'i chos //
NK095(ce)001:658: ming dang mtshan ma'i yul 'das thugs //
NK095(ce)001:659: de bas snang srid snod bcud kun //
NK095(ce)001:660: byang chub sku gsung thugs su 'dus //
NK095(ce)001:661: zhes gsungs pa des na bzang ngan blang dor du
NK095(ce)001:662: bstan pa thams cad theg pa 'og ma'i lugs yin
NK095(ce)001:663: pas 'dir rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga
NK095(ce)001:664: ni de las khyad par du 'phags so //
NK095(ce)001:666: bzhi rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i 'khor de
NK095(ce)001:667: las gazhana yang lam mngon par snang ba'i 'khor ni
NK095(ce)001:668: 'di ltar chos thams cad gdod nas spros bral rang
NK095(ce)001:669: byung gi ye shes kyi rang bzhin kun byed byang
NK095(ce)001:670: chub kyi sems nyid kyi rang bzhina dmigs bsam brjod
NK095(ce)001:671: bral thams cad dang bral ba la blta bya ba
NK095(ce)001:672: blta byed gnyis su grub pa med kyang gdul bya'i
NK095(ce)001:673: rim pas de la lta ba'i 'khor rnam pa bzhi
NK095(ce)001:675: theg pa thams cad kyi rtse mor gyur cing mtshan
NK095(ce)001:676: ma med pa'i rdzogs rim mthar thug pa yin shin
NK095(ce)001:677: tu rnal 'byor a ti yo ga zhes bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:679: ma ba skyed rdzogs dang de yin don la 'jug pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:680: rdzogs pa a nu'i ming gi nges tshig yin //
NK095(ce)001:681: zhes pa ltar snying po brjod pa tsam gyis lha yongs su rdzogs par bsgom pas sam /
NK095(ce)001:682: shes rab rjes chags kyi lam gtso bos ston pas
NK095(ce)001:683: yongs su rnal 'byor ram rjes su rnal 'byor a
NK095(ce)001:684: nu yo ga zhes bya ba'i 'khor dang /
NK095(ce)001:685: shin tu rgyas pa chen po'i bskyed rim nyid gtso
NK095(ce)001:686: bor ston pas rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo
NK095(ce)001:688: phyi'i spyod 'grogs tsam du byas nas nang sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:689: sgom pa gtso bor ston pas sems dpa'i rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:690: phyi rgyud sde gsum zhes bya ba'i 'khor dang bzhi
NK095(ce)001:691: po de ni 'og nas kyang rgyas par 'byung ngo
NK095(ce)001:692: // gsum pa gong gi sku gsum 'khor gyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK095(ce)001:693: gong du bstan pa de ltar kun byed byang chub
NK095(ce)001:694: kyi sems gdod nas rang byung stong gsal thugs rje
NK095(ce)001:695: khyab brdal chen po nyid kyi rang bzhin gnas lugs
NK095(ce)001:697: nyid kyi ngo bo snang lugs longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK095(ce)001:698: nyid kyi thugs rje 'char lugs sprul pa'i sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:699: gyi rang bzhin ston pa kun byed nyid las ston
NK095(ce)001:700: 'khor tha dad du ma grub cing 'byed pa mi
NK095(ce)001:701: mnga' bas thabs gcig go zhes lhan gcig tu mnyam
NK095(ce)001:702: pa chen por dgyes par bzhugs so //
NK095(ce)001:703: sa bcad 'di cung zad dkrugs nas rnal 'byor bzhi'i
NK095(ce)001:704: mthar gsungs pa ni snang tshul tsam la lam mngon
NK095(ce)001:705: par snang ba'i cha nas rnal 'byor bzhi logs su
NK095(ce)001:706: bgrangs kyang don la sku gsum las ma 'das par
NK095(ce)001:707: ston pa'i ched yin par mngon no //
NK095(ce)001:708: gsum pa dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi 'khor ni /
NK095(ce)001:709: de ltar gzhi rang bzhin gyis dag pa dang lam
NK095(ce)001:710: mngon par snang ba'i 'khor de dag las gzhan yang
NK095(ce)001:711: rtsol sgrub blang dor la ltos pa med par ye
NK095(ce)001:712: gdod ma nyid nas gzung 'dzin rnam rtog gi dri
NK095(ce)001:713: mas ma gos shing yon tan thams cad lhun gyis
NK095(ce)001:714: rdzogs par mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid rig
NK095(ce)001:715: pa byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po nyid
NK095(ce)001:716: kyi rang bzhina ma nor bar rtogsa pas yang sangs
NK095(ce)001:718: sngar byon 'das pa'i sangs rgyas byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:719: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i gdod ma'i 'od
NK095(ce)001:720: gsal chen po nyid kyi ngang la skye 'gags 'pho
NK095(ce)001:721: 'gyur dang bral bar rtag tu gnas shing bzhugs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:722: 'khor dang / da ltar chos kyi dbyings dang nam
NK095(ce)001:723: mkha'i mthas klas par sku 'tsho zhing gzhes te mngon
NK095(ce)001:724: sum du bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas chos sku kun byed
NK095(ce)001:725: rgyal po nyid kyi thugs rje'i rtsal 'gags pa med
NK095(ce)001:726: pa las shar ba rnams kyis gdul bya'i sems cad
NK095(ce)001:727: ma lus pa kun gyi don rtag khyab lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:728: kyi tshul du dngos su mdzad pa'i 'khor dang /
NK095(ce)001:729: slad nas sam phyi nas 'byon pa'i sangs rgyas kun
NK095(ce)001:730: byed byang chub kyi sems nyid kyi rang bzhin mngon
NK095(ce)001:731: sum du rtogs pa las 'byung bar 'gyur ba'i 'khor
NK095(ce)001:732: dang / rnam pa gsum po de yang ni rig
NK095(ce)001:733: pa rang byung gi ye shes sam byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:734: sems kyi dbyings na dus gsum 'du 'bral med par
NK095(ce)001:735: dbyer med gcig tu bzhugs pas 'byed pa mi mnga'
NK095(ce)001:736: ba'i rang bzhin gyis thabs gcig par bzhugs so zhes
NK095(ce)001:737: dang / gsungs so // de ltar sngar mdor bstan
NK095(ce)001:738: gyi skabs su bstan pa dang ston pa dus phun
NK095(ce)001:739: sum tshogs pa gsum gtso bor bstan nas gzhan gnyis
NK095(ce)001:741: rgyas bshad kyi skabs 'dir gnas dang 'khor phun sum
NK095(ce)001:742: tshogs pa gnyis gtso bor bstan te gzhan gsum shugs
NK095(ce)001:743: la bstan pa'o // de ltar phun sum tshogs pa lnga po bstan pa'i dgos pa yang /
NK095(ce)001:744: spros bral don gsal chen po'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:745: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa smos pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:746: gang zag rig bcos ma yin par //
NK095(ce)001:747: sangs rgyas zhal nas gsungs par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:748: mi bslu bden pa'i gtan tshig dag tu 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:749: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa smos pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:750: bab bcol ma yin don dang ldan par yid kyang ches /
NK095(ce)001:751: 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs smos pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:752: kun gyi thun mong ma yin pa'i /
NK095(ce)001:753: nges par ston pas gsungs par yid kyang ches /
NK095(ce)001:754: gnas kyi bye brag gsungs pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:755: gzhan du bstan pa'i snying po ma gsungs par //
NK095(ce)001:756: nges pa'i gnas der gsungs par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:757: gnas kyi bye brag gsungs pa'i dgos pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:758: gzhan du bstan pa'i snying po ma gsungs par //
NK095(ce)001:759: nges pa'i gnas der gsungs par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:760: dus kyi phun sum tshogs pa smos pa'i dgos pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:761: gnas skabs snga phyi ma brgal bar //
NK095(ce)001:762: dus tshod mtshungs shing zin pas yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:764: gnyis pa gleng ba slang ba la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:765: ston pas dgongs don gyi ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag pa /
NK095(ce)001:766: de las nyid kyi thugs rje rig pa'i 'khor sems dpa' rdo rje sprul te bkod pa /
NK095(ce)001:767: de nyid kyis zhus shing lan gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:769: de ltar gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa mngon par
NK095(ce)001:770: snang ba de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byeda
NK095(ce)001:771: rgyal po des rang snang ma bcos don gyi 'khor
NK095(ce)001:772: tshogs thams cad ston pa nyid kyi rang bzhin rig
NK095(ce)001:773: stong gnyis su med pa'i ye shes nang dbyings ka
NK095(ce)001:774: dag chen po gcig tu byin gyis brlab pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:775: du rtsal snang 'gags pa med pa'i 'khor thams cad
NK095(ce)001:776: kun rdzogs mnyam pa chen po spros bral thig le'i
NK095(ce)001:777: rang bzhin chos sku kun byed nyid kyi sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:778: rang byung ye shes kyi thugs dmigs bsam brjod pa
NK095(ce)001:779: las 'das pa'i dbyings la thim par mdzad do //
NK095(ce)001:780: zhes phyi gsal rtsal snang gi rol pa thams cad
NK095(ce)001:781: rig pa byang chub kyi sems ma bcos mnyam pa
NK095(ce)001:782: chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang la gnyis med
NK095(ce)001:784: tshul de yang don gsal las /
NK095(ce)001:785: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das rig stong kun tu bzang
NK095(ce)001:786: po de nyid 'khor shes rig sna tshogs pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:788: 'khor thams cad nyid kyi thugs la thim zhing sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK095(ce)001:789: de ltar ston pa nyid kyis dgongs don la mnyam
NK095(ce)001:790: par bzhag pa'i ngang nas 'khor rnams kyi thugs la
NK095(ce)001:791: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes bsgribs med mngon
NK095(ce)001:792: sum du gsal bar mdzad do zhes rtsal las shar
NK095(ce)001:793: ba'i rol ba'i ye shes thams cad rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:794: ye shes gcig gi ngo bor gyur ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:795: de ltar 'od gsal byang chub sems kyi dgongs pa
NK095(ce)001:796: gsal bar mdzad pa de nas snying po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:797: sems kyi rtsal snang gi chos thams cad dbyings chos
NK095(ce)001:798: nyid skye ba med pa gcig gi rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:799: ldan par bya ba'i phyir du rtsal snang gi rol
NK095(ce)001:800: pa de thams cad ka dag skye ba med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:801: ngang du bsdus nas nang dbyings thig le chena po
NK095(ce)001:802: nyag gcig tu bzhugs so zhes snga ma byang chub
NK095(ce)001:803: sems kyi ngo bo lhun grub 'od gsal gyi cha
NK095(ce)001:804: nas dang / phyi ma 'di byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:805: rang bzhin skye med ka dag gi cha nas bstan
NK095(ce)001:806: yang don la tha dad med par dbyings ye gnyis
NK095(ce)001:807: su med pa'i dgongs don la mnyam par bzhag pa'o
NK095(ce)001:809: dgongs don la mnyam par bzhag pa de nas ston
NK095(ce)001:810: pa nyid dang lhan gcig pa'i rig pa'i 'khor sems
NK095(ce)001:811: dpa' rdo rje de nyid ston pa nyid kyi thugs
NK095(ce)001:812: rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba thig le chen
NK095(ce)001:813: po gcig tu bzhugs pa'i dgongs pa mi g.yo ba'i
NK095(ce)001:814: ngang de las gzugs sku'i rol bar byung ba'am chos
NK095(ce)001:815: nyid kyi rang mdangs su shar nasa /
NK095(ce)001:816: byang chub kyi sems ston pa kun byed rgyal po'i
NK095(ce)001:817: spyan sngar rgyal sras sems dpa' rdo rje nyid rtsol
NK095(ce)001:818: med a ti'i theg pa 'byung ba'i dus la bab
NK095(ce)001:819: par mkhyen pas thugs shin tu dgyes shing dga' ba'i
NK095(ce)001:820: sems kyis mtshan dpa'i gzi byin rab tu 'bar ba'i
NK095(ce)001:821: zhal dang ba'i mdangs phyung ste 'khod pas byang chub
NK095(ce)001:822: kyi sems ston pa kun byed rgyal pos sems dpa'
NK095(ce)001:823: rdo rje la skye med don gyi gsung gis smras
NK095(ce)001:824: pa / ston pa rang nyid kyi rtsal las byung
NK095(ce)001:825: ba'i sems dpa' rdo rje nyid sgra tshig brjod pa
NK095(ce)001:826: las 'das pa yang gsang a ti yo ga'i rgyud
NK095(ce)001:827: sde rnams gsung bar bskul ba po 'khor gyi tshul
NK095(ce)001:828: du rang snang ba la dgyes shing ngo mtshar bas
NK095(ce)001:829: e ma ho zhes spyir bstan nas /
NK095(ce)001:831: rtsol bral a ti'i chos ston pa'i dus la babs
NK095(ce)001:832: par gzigs nas ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i thugs
NK095(ce)001:833: zag med rang byung gi ye shes nyid dgyes shing
NK095(ce)001:834: dga' ba'i semsa skyes pa la ngo mtshar ba'i gsung
NK095(ce)001:835: gis e ma ho zhes brjod pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:836: mtshan dpe'i zhal gyi dkyil 'khor ston zla gsal ba'i
NK095(ce)001:837: ngos ltar dang ba'i mdangs phyung ba la ngo mtshar
NK095(ce)001:838: bas e ma ho zhes pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:839: de yang gzhan du grub pa med par gzhi med
NK095(ce)001:840: rtsa ba dang bral ba rig pa rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:841: ye shes ston pa kun byed rgyal po nga las
NK095(ce)001:842: gzhi snang lhun grub kyi snang char sems dpa' rdo
NK095(ce)001:843: rje khyod nyid chos nyid rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs
NK095(ce)001:844: pa phyi rabs rjes 'jug rnams la snang ba'i don
NK095(ce)001:845: du gzugs sku'i ngo bor byung ba e ma ho
NK095(ce)001:847: zhes gsungs pas ston pa'i tshig gi mdun bsu ba'i sgo nas go phyes so //
NK095(ce)001:849: chos kun grub bsal med pa ye nas thig le
NK095(ce)001:850: gcig gi rang bzhin la phun sum tshogs pa lnga
NK095(ce)001:852: dbyings gcig de bzhin nyid chos thams cad kyi 'byung
NK095(ce)001:853: gnas sam ngo bor gnas pa de'i 'thad pa kun
NK095(ce)001:854: byed nyid du gsungs tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:856: de ltar ston pa'i tshig gis mdun bsus pa'i rjes
NK095(ce)001:857: de nas sems dpa' rdo rje ston pa kun byed
NK095(ce)001:858: rgyal po la gleng slong ba'i tshig dngos su zhus
NK095(ce)001:859: pa / kye zhes rang las mtho ba'am che ba la 'bod pa'i tshig ste /
NK095(ce)001:860: de yang don la ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:861: yin pas mtho dman dang bzang ngan sogs med kyang
NK095(ce)001:862: snang ba'i ngos nas ston pa dang 'khor ltar snang
NK095(ce)001:863: ba'i phyir de ltar gsungs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:864: phyi rabs rjes 'jug rnams kyis chos smra ba'i bla
NK095(ce)001:865: ma la gus pa byed dgos par yang don gyis
NK095(ce)001:866: ston to // de ltar gus pa'i tshig gis mdun
NK095(ce)001:867: bsus nas ston pa'i ston pa zhes ston pa sku
NK095(ce)001:868: gsum gyi yang ston par gyur pa chos sku kun
NK095(ce)001:869: byed rgyal po lags zhes smos pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:870: de la sku gsum gyi ston pa gang zhe na
NK095(ce)001:871: nang rgyud sde gsum gyi ston pa chos kyi sku
NK095(ce)001:872: dang / phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi ston pa longs sku dang /
NK095(ce)001:873: mtshan nyid sde gsum gyi ston pa sprul pa'i sku ste gsum yin la /
NK095(ce)001:874: 'o na kun byed rgyal po rang nyid chos sku
NK095(ce)001:875: min nam de chos sku'i ston par ji ltar 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:876: snyam na / 'dir ston pa kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:877: ni ye nas 'khrul ma myong ba'i sangs rgyas dus
NK095(ce)001:878: gsum gyi rgyal ba kun gyi sngon rol du mngon
NK095(ce)001:879: par byang chub pa gdod ma'i mgon po kun tu
NK095(ce)001:880: bzang po yin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:882: thog ma kun gyi sngon rol du //
NK095(ce)001:883: rang snang gzhi la mthar phyin te //
NK095(ce)001:884: sngar sangs snga nas rgyas pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:885: thog ma'i kun tu bzang po ni //
NK095(ce)001:888: nga'i 'khor du gsungs pa'i sku gsum ni ston pa
NK095(ce)001:889: de nyid kyis lam mngon par bstan pa la brten
NK095(ce)001:890: nas phyi nas sangs rgyas pa rnams te /
NK095(ce)001:892: ston pa 'di yod pas 'khor 'das gdod mar grol
NK095(ce)001:893: ba'i lam ston pa byung ste dus gsum gyi rgyal
NK095(ce)001:895: de lta ma yin na 'jig rten du sangs rgyas 'byung ba'ang mi rigs te /
NK095(ce)001:896: thams cad sems can du mnyam pa la gcig gis
NK095(ce)001:897: gcig la lam ston par mi shes pa nyid dang
NK095(ce)001:898: / la la sangs rgyas shing la la 'khor ba mi rigs so //
NK095(ce)001:900: de lta bu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ston pa
NK095(ce)001:901: gdod ma'i mgon po kun byed rgyal po nyid la
NK095(ce)001:902: sems dpa' rdo rjes 'di skad ces zhus te /
NK095(ce)001:903: ci stona pa nyid kyang mtshan rtog gi spros pa'i
NK095(ce)001:904: grwa zur thams cad dang bral bas kun zlum thig
NK095(ce)001:905: le chen po nyag gcig spros pa med pas gnyis
NK095(ce)001:906: snang gi yul du grub pa med dam ste med
NK095(ce)001:908: nyid kyi rtsal las shar ba'i 'khor rnams kun kyang thig le spros meda kyi rang bzhin nyid dam /
NK095(ce)001:909: gzhan yang kun byed nyid kyis bstan pa dam pa'i chos kun kyang thig le spros med nyid dam /
NK095(ce)001:910: phun sum tshogs pa rnams snang ba'i dus dang gnas
NK095(ce)001:911: nyid kyang thig le spros med kyi rang bzhin mtshan
NK095(ce)001:914: ngag gis brjod du med pa /
NK095(ce)001:915: dpe yis mtshon du med pa sogs snang ba'i chos gang du'ang grub pa med dam ste /
NK095(ce)001:916: de ltar 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi ngo
NK095(ce)001:917: bo phun sum tshogs pa kun kyang ye nas spros
NK095(ce)001:918: pa'i gra zur thams cad dang bral bas spros med
NK095(ce)001:919: thig le'i rang bzhin grub bsal 'pho 'gyur med pa
NK095(ce)001:920: zhig yin na / de las ches zab pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:921: zhig mi srid pas sku gsum gyi ston pa'i ston
NK095(ce)001:922: pas 'khor rnams la chos ci zhig ston para madzada
NK095(ce)001:923: de spros pa med pa thig le'i rang bzhin yin
NK095(ce)001:924: zhig yin na / pa'i phyir dang / nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:925: 'khor du lhan gcig tu 'dus shing 'khor ba'i don
NK095(ce)001:926: ni ci la 'khor zhing 'tshogs te spros pa med
NK095(ce)001:927: pa la de ltar mi 'thad pa'i phyir dang /
NK095(ce)001:928: gal te 'khor du 'dus su chug kyang de la
NK095(ce)001:929: bstan pa ci zhig ston par byed de smra brjod
NK095(ce)001:930: kyi spros pa med pa'i phyir dang /
NK095(ce)001:931: ston 'khor bstan pa gsum po lhan du tshogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:932: dus dang gnas ni gcig pa ru ji lta bu
NK095(ce)001:933: yi phyir na 'gyur te chos nyid ye nas gcig
NK095(ce)001:934: dang tha dad la sogs pa'i dmigs bsam spros pa
NK095(ce)001:935: thams cad las 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:936: des na tshul ji lta bu yin pa ston pa
NK095(ce)001:937: nyid kyis gsungs par mdzad du gsol zhes zhus so
NK095(ce)001:939: de ltar 'khor gyis zhus pa'i don ston pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:940: kyi gsan nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:941: po des slar yang sems dpa' rdo rje la sgra
NK095(ce)001:942: tshig dang bral ba'i brjod med don gyi gsung gis
NK095(ce)001:944: ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med la mchog dman med
NK095(ce)001:945: pa'i phyir kye zhes pa'i 'bod tshig sbyar te sems
NK095(ce)001:946: dpa' chen po khyod kyis yida kyi rnam par shes
NK095(ce)001:947: pa sgra la chug cig gam sgra la gtad nas
NK095(ce)001:948: don ma nor bar zung zhig dang /
NK095(ce)001:949: ston pa kun byed des ji ltar zhus pa'i zab
NK095(ce)001:950: mo'i don rnams chos nyid don gyi rang sgrar spros
NK095(ce)001:951: nas bshad kyis zhes snod kyi skyon dang bral bas
NK095(ce)001:952: nyan par bskul ba'i tshul gyis gang zhig gsung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:953: don ni / kye sems dpa' chen po sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:954: rang byung gi ye shes ston pa kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:955: po nga nyid kyi rang bzhin ni dbyings gcig de
NK095(ce)001:956: bzhin nyid chos rnams thams cad kun gyi 'byung gnas
NK095(ce)001:957: su gyur pa snying po ste ngo bor gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:958: yin kyang 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams snang ba'i dus
NK095(ce)001:959: nyid nas snying po byang chub kyi sems nyid ni
NK095(ce)001:960: gang du'ang ma spros shing 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:961: na ye nas chos nyid mnyam brdal chen po kun
NK095(ce)001:962: khyab thig le nyag gcig gi rang bzhin du gnas
NK095(ce)001:963: don ni / pa yin te / ci'i phyir na
NK095(ce)001:964: thiga le zhes pa ni ye shes spros pa yi
NK095(ce)001:965: grwa zur med pa'i chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa
NK095(ce)001:966: srid zhi kun khyab chen po'i don yin pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:967: don ni / pa yin te / te / kun gsal las /
NK095(ce)001:969: mi 'gyur ba mi 'gag pa khyab par bshad do //
NK095(ce)001:971: de bzhin du rgyal ba sku gsum gyi ston pa
NK095(ce)001:972: rnams dang ni de dag gis gsungs pa'i bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:973: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:974: ston pa gsum po de nyid kyi 'dus pa'i 'khor
NK095(ce)001:975: rnams dang de rnams lhan du tshogs pa'i dus dang
NK095(ce)001:976: gang du tshogs pa'i gnas phun sum tshogs pas bsdus
NK095(ce)001:977: pa'i chos thams cad snying po kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:978: nga las byung bas na ye nas spros bral thig
NK095(ce)001:979: le yi ngo bor brjod pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:980: de yang rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir na de dag gang
NK095(ce)001:981: las byung ba'i gzhi kun byed byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:982: nga yi rang bzhina spros med thig le yi ngo
NK095(ce)001:983: bo nyid yin par bstan pa yin pa'i phyir ro
NK095(ce)001:985: le'u'i mtshan byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:986: las gleng gzhi dang gleng slong gnyis ka yin kyang
NK095(ce)001:987: brjod bya ming gi cha nas gleng gzhi'i sgrar smos
NK095(ce)001:988: pa ste de yang gang zhig gleng ba ni bstan
NK095(ce)001:989: pa rgyud kyi don la de nyid 'byung ba'i gzhir
NK095(ce)001:990: gyur pas de skad du smos la le'u ni sde
NK095(ce)001:991: tshan so so ma 'dres par mtshams gcod pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:992: te / de las rigs kyi bu le'u zhes pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:993: so so'i sa mtshams dang chos gzhan dang ma 'dres te /
NK095(ce)001:994: gang mtshon pa'i don gtsor bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:996: de las 'dir le'u brgyad cu rtsa bzhi yod pa'i
NK095(ce)001:997: nang nas thog ma yin pas na dang po'i 'grel
NK095(ce)001:998: ba'o ////don gnyis pa bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:999: tshul gyis rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:1000: phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i rang bzhin ji ltar bkod cing byung ba'i tshul bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:1001: gnas lugs rgya cher bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:1002: tshig don bsdus te dgrol ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:1004: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gdod nas
NK095(ce)001:1005: phun sum tshogs pa lngar bkod tshul bstan pa dang
NK095(ce)001:1006: / de nyid gshis kun byed de bzhin nyid kyi ngang las byung tshul bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1007: dang po ni le'u gnyis pas bstan pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:1008: le'u la 'jug pa'i rgyu'i tshul gyis mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1009: de nyid rgya cher bshad pas rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1011: de ltar gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:1012: ston 'khor gnyis kyis gleng bslang ba'i rjes de nas
NK095(ce)001:1013: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po des 'khor
NK095(ce)001:1014: 'das kyi chos thamsa cad nyid las byung ba'i rang
NK095(ce)001:1015: bzhin dmigs bsam spros pa dang bral ba'i ngo bor
NK095(ce)001:1016: gzigs pa'i dgongs pa las mi g.yo ba'i ting nge
NK095(ce)001:1017: 'dzin stong gsal brjod med blo 'das chen po'i rang
NK095(ce)001:1018: bzhin can gyi ting nge 'dzin ces bya ba la
NK095(ce)001:1019: mnyam par bzhag nas gnas par mdzad do //
NK095(ce)001:1020: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:1021: rig pa'i sems dpa' nyid 'khor du bkod pa'i don zhus pa /
NK095(ce)001:1022: de bzhin nyid kyi ston pa'i ngang las phun sum tshogs pas bsdus pa'i chos nyid bkod pa /
NK095(ce)001:1023: de'i don dri lan du bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1025: ston pas dgongs don gyi ting nge 'dzin la mnyam
NK095(ce)001:1026: par bzhag pa de nas 'khor gyi tshogs rnams chos
NK095(ce)001:1027: dbyings mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du rang bzhina gcig
NK095(ce)001:1028: tu bzhugs pa las sems dpa' rdo rje dgongs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1029: klong nas rtsal gyi ngo bor langs nas ston pa
NK095(ce)001:1030: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po'i zhal mngon
NK095(ce)001:1031: sum du phyogs pa'i mdun du sku gangs dkar shel
NK095(ce)001:1032: gyi ri bo la nyin byed 'bum gyis 'khyud pa
NK095(ce)001:1033: lta bu'i zhal gyi mdangs phyung ste mi 'gyur brtan
NK095(ce)001:1034: pa'i ri rab bzhin du 'khod nas skye med rang
NK095(ce)001:1035: byung gi ye shes kyi gsung phyung ste zhus pa
NK095(ce)001:1036: / kye chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa'i sku can ston pa'i ston pa kun byeda rgyal po lags /
NK095(ce)001:1037: ston pa khyod kyi 'khor du nyid kyi thugs rje
NK095(ce)001:1038: ye shes kyi rtsal las shar ba'i bdag cag rig
NK095(ce)001:1039: pa'i sems dpa' rnams 'dus shing 'khod pa ste lhan
NK095(ce)001:1041: bdag cag 'dus pa rnams kyis ni 'tshal ba'am shes
NK095(ce)001:1042: par bya ba'i don ni chos rnams kyi gnas lugs
NK095(ce)001:1043: bsal bzhag bral ba'i ye shes rdzogs pa a ti
NK095(ce)001:1044: yo ga'i dgongs pa de ci lta bu zhig mchis
NK095(ce)001:1045: pa'am bdag cag rnams kyis shes par 'tshal ba'i dgongs
NK095(ce)001:1046: don de ni ston pa kun byed khyod kyis bstan
NK095(ce)001:1047: par mdzad du gsol zhes zhus so //
NK095(ce)001:1049: gdod ma'i gzhi kun byed nyid sku gsum du bkod pa /
NK095(ce)001:1050: de las rang byung gi ye shes lnga bkod pa /
NK095(ce)001:1051: de las srid gsum snod bcud kyi rang bzhin bkod pa /
NK095(ce)001:1052: de ltar dag ma dag sna tshogs su snang dus
NK095(ce)001:1053: nyid nas rang bzhin spros pa'i mtha' bral du gnas
NK095(ce)001:1055: sems dpa' rdo rjes dgos don zhus pa'i rjes de
NK095(ce)001:1056: nas gdod ma'i gzhi byang chub kyi sems kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1057: rgyal po des nyid kyi rang bzhin chos nyid ye
NK095(ce)001:1058: stong chen po spros bral ka dag gi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:1059: rgya chad phyogs lhung dang bral ba ni stong pa
NK095(ce)001:1061: nyid kyi ngo bo 'od gsal lhun grub kyi snang
NK095(ce)001:1062: ba ma 'gag cir yang 'char ba'i gzhir gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:1063: ni gsal ba longs sku dang /
NK095(ce)001:1064: nyid kyi thugs rje rig pa'i ye shes gsal stong
NK095(ce)001:1065: zung 'jug gi rtsal las cir yang 'char ba'i ye
NK095(ce)001:1066: shes ni gnyis med sprul pa'i sku ste gsum po
NK095(ce)001:1067: de phun sum tshogs pa'i chos thams cad kyi 'char
NK095(ce)001:1068: gzhi dbyings de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin du bkod
NK095(ce)001:1069: pa ste zhes nang gsal gyi ye shes gsum po
NK095(ce)001:1070: de chos thams cad kyi 'char gzhi bstan pa yin
NK095(ce)001:1071: te / mthar thug don gyi snying po las /
NK095(ce)001:1073: gos pa med pa'i sngon rol na //
NK095(ce)001:1074: rang byung ye shes ka dag nyid //
NK095(ce)001:1075: ngo bo stong pa mtshon brjod 'das //
NK095(ce)001:1076: rang bzhin 'od las gting gsal tshul //
NK095(ce)001:1077: thugs rje rig pa'i snying po can //
NK095(ce)001:1078: nang dbyings ka dag chen por gnas //
NK095(ce)001:1081: thugs rje thugs te rig par gnas //
NK095(ce)001:1082: sku ru nas kyang zhal phyag med //
NK095(ce)001:1083: 'od du gnas kyang kha dog med //
NK095(ce)001:1085: rang ngo nang gsal 'char gzhi'i cha //
NK095(ce)001:1086: sku las sku gsum nyid dang ni //
NK095(ce)001:1087: 'od las lhun grub longs spyod rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:1088: thugs rje rig pa ye shes su //
NK095(ce)001:1089: ngang gi 'char ba'i gzhi mor gnas //
NK095(ce)001:1090: 'di ni gdod ma'i gnas lugs so //
NK095(ce)001:1093: de lta bu'i stong gsal thugs rje gsum po de
NK095(ce)001:1094: las chos thams cad bkod pa ni zhes spyir bstan
NK095(ce)001:1095: nas bye brag tu ston pa kun byed nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:1096: thugs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen po
NK095(ce)001:1097: gcig gi rtsal 'gags pa med pa las rang byung
NK095(ce)001:1098: gi ye shes chen po lnga byung ba ni 'di
NK095(ce)001:1099: lta ste sems khong nas 'khrugs pa'i bdag nyid can
NK095(ce)001:1100: gyi mnar sems pa'i zhe sdang rang ka mar snang
NK095(ce)001:1101: ba 'di nyid rgyu rkyen la ltos pa med par
NK095(ce)001:1102: rang byung gi ye shes chen po yi rtsal 'gags
NK095(ce)001:1103: pa med pa rang gsal gyi tshul du shar ba
NK095(ce)001:1104: yin pas spong 'gog sbyangs bsgyur sogs la mi ltos
NK095(ce)001:1105: par ye nas rang byung ye shes kyi ngo bor
NK095(ce)001:1108: chags sdang nga rgyal phrag dog rmongs //
NK095(ce)001:1109: rang rig shar phyir don mi spong //
NK095(ce)001:1112: rang byung rgyu rkyen med par byung ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:1113: ye shes 'gags pa med par gsal ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:1115: de bzhin du 'og ma rnams la yang sbyar te /
NK095(ce)001:1116: yul dang du len pa'i rang bzhin can gyi 'doda chags rang byung ye shes chen po dang /
NK095(ce)001:1117: blang dor mi 'byed pa'i rang bzhin can gyi gti mug rang byung ye shes chena po dang /
NK095(ce)001:1118: dmigs yul khong du mi shong ba'i rang bzhin can phrag doga rang byung ye shes chen po dang /
NK095(ce)001:1119: sems mtho ba'i rnam pa can gyi nga rgyal rang
NK095(ce)001:1120: byung ye shes chen po dang lnga mngon du byung
NK095(ce)001:1122: de lta bu'i rang byung gi ye shes rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:1123: lnga po de'i rtsal las rgyan gyi rgyu 'byung ba
NK095(ce)001:1124: chen po lnga ni phyung ste zhes /
NK095(ce)001:1125: de la rgyan gyi rgyu zhes gsungs pa ni 'byung
NK095(ce)001:1126: ba chen po lnga po de nyid rang byung ye
NK095(ce)001:1127: shes kyi rtsal gyi rol pa'am rgyan du shar ba
NK095(ce)001:1128: yin pas rgyan zhes gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:1130: de yang rig pa'i rang gzugs stong gsal zang thal chen po cir yang ma grub pa'i ngang nas /
NK095(ce)001:1132: phyi yul snang lus dang bcas par grub pas rang snang gi rgyan du shar /
NK095(ce)001:1133: ye shes kyi rol bar shar /
NK095(ce)001:1134: 'gag med kyi rtsal du shar yang //
NK095(ce)001:1135: snang la bden pas ma grub pa //
NK095(ce)001:1136: dpe rmi lam gyi snang ba yul med rang snang
NK095(ce)001:1137: gi rtsal dang rgyan dang rol bar shar ba bzhin
NK095(ce)001:1139: de ltar 'byung ba lnga po de 'byung 'gyur kun
NK095(ce)001:1140: gyi rgyu yin zhing khyab pa rgya che bas rgyu
NK095(ce)001:1142: gzhan yang mthar me chu rlung gis 'jig cing stong
NK095(ce)001:1143: par byed pa phyi snod dang de la rten dang
NK095(ce)001:1144: brten pa'i tshul du gnas pas nang bcud de snod
NK095(ce)001:1145: bcud kyis bsdus pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams chen po
NK095(ce)001:1147: de las bye brag tu rang byung ye shes kyi
NK095(ce)001:1148: rgyan gyi rgyu'i lus snga dus gcig tu blang ba
NK095(ce)001:1149: ni 'di lta ste zhes 'byung lnga'i rang bzhin las
NK095(ce)001:1150: grub pa'i rgyud lnga'i sems can nam 'gro ba drug
NK095(ce)001:1151: gi lus snang bar bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:1152: de yang rgyan gyi rgyu'i lus sra ba'i khams sa zhes bya ba'i lus dang /
NK095(ce)001:1153: de bzhin du rgyan gyi rgyu'i lus rlan zhing gsher ba'i khams chu zhes bya ba'i lus dang /
NK095(ce)001:1154: rgyan gyi rgyu'i lus drod kyi khams me zhes bya ba'i lus dang /
NK095(ce)001:1155: rgyan gyi rgyu'i lus g.yo ba'i khams rlung zhes bya ba'i lus dang /
NK095(ce)001:1156: rgyan kyi rgyu'i lus bu ga nam mkha' yi khams
NK095(ce)001:1157: zhes bya ba'i lus re re la lnga ga tshang
NK095(ce)001:1158: bas gcig tu 'dus pa rigs drug gi lus thams
NK095(ce)001:1159: cad blangs ba'am snang bar gyur to //
NK095(ce)001:1160: de dag kun byed byang chub kyi sems gcig gi
NK095(ce)001:1161: rang bzhin yin pa la ye shes lnga'i rigs so
NK095(ce)001:1162: sora phye ste snang ba ni /
NK095(ce)001:1163: rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes gsal stong
NK095(ce)001:1164: zhe sdang gi rang bzhin yul yongs su 'jom par
NK095(ce)001:1165: byed pa rdo rje'i rigs dang /
NK095(ce)001:1166: rang byung 'gag pa med pa'i ye shes bde stong
NK095(ce)001:1167: 'dod chags kyi rang bzhin yul la yid 'ong gi
NK095(ce)001:1168: rnam pas dang du len pa pad+ma'i rigs dang /
NK095(ce)001:1169: rang byung dmigs gtad dang bral ba'i ye shes rig
NK095(ce)001:1170: stong gti muga gi rang bzhin kun gyi khyab byed
NK095(ce)001:1171: du gyur pas bud+d+ha'i rigs dang /
NK095(ce)001:1172: rang byung mnyam pa med pa'i ye shes dran stong
NK095(ce)001:1173: phrag dog gi rang bzhin dmigs yul khong du mi
NK095(ce)001:1174: shong bas las kyi rigs dang /
NK095(ce)001:1175: rang byung skye ba med pa'i ye shes snang stong
NK095(ce)001:1176: nga rgyal gyi rang bzhin che ba'i yon tan la
NK095(ce)001:1177: dmigs nas / gzhan las mtho bar blta bas rin po che'i rigs dang /
NK095(ce)001:1178: de lta bu'i rang byung ye shes lnga'i rigs can
NK095(ce)001:1179: gyi lus blang ba ni rgyud lngas bsdus pa'i 'gro
NK095(ce)001:1180: ba rnams kyi lus dang so sor sbyar te /
NK095(ce)001:1182: srid gsum lam lnga'i chos lnga yang //
NK095(ce)001:1183: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:1184: de yang ji lta bu zhe na //
NK095(ce)001:1185: bskam chags lnga yi rnam smin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:1186: lam sgo lnga ru zhugs phyin na //
NK095(ce)001:1187: mi bde sdug bsngal lnga la spyad //
NK095(ce)001:1188: zhe sdang lam gyis sgor zhugs pas //
NK095(ce)001:1189: dmyal ba'i gnas su tsha grang spyod //
NK095(ce)001:1190: snga phyi med pa'i chos spyod kyang //
NK095(ce)001:1191: snga ma'i las kyi rnam smin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:1192: tsha dang grang ba'i nyams myong ste //
NK095(ce)001:1193: snying po byang chub sems de la //
NK095(ce)001:1194: tsha grang nyams des bskyod pa med //
NK095(ce)001:1195: de bas zhe sdang mi gnas stong //
NK095(ce)001:1196: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:1197: 'dod chags lam gyi sgor zhugs pas //
NK095(ce)001:1198: yi dwags gnas na bkres skom spyod //
NK095(ce)001:1199: bsngosa pas tshim pa'i chos yod kyang //
NK095(ce)001:1200: snga ma'i las kyi rnam smin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:1201: bkres dang skom pa'i nyams myong ste //
NK095(ce)001:1202: snying po byang chub sems de la //
NK095(ce)001:1203: bkres dang skom pas bskyod pa med //
NK095(ce)001:1204: de bas 'dod chags mi gnas stong //
NK095(ce)001:1205: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:1206: gti mug lam gyi sgor zhugs pas //
NK095(ce)001:1207: byol song gnas na glen lkugs spyod //
NK095(ce)001:1208: rig pa phra mo'i chos spyod de //
NK095(ce)001:1209: snga ma'i las kyi rnam smin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:1210: blun zhing lkugs pa'i nyams myong ste //
NK095(ce)001:1211: snying po byang chub sems de la //
NK095(ce)001:1212: blun lkug nyams des bskyod pa med //
NK095(ce)001:1213: de bas gti mug mi gnas stong //
NK095(ce)001:1214: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:1215: phrag dog lam gyi sgor zhugs pas //
NK095(ce)001:1216: mi yi gnas su dge sdig spyod //
NK095(ce)001:1217: dge sdig las kyi chos yod kyang //
NK095(ce)001:1218: mi dge shas chung rnam smin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:1219: mi rtag 'gyur ba'i nyams myong ste //
NK095(ce)001:1220: snying po byang chub sems de la //
NK095(ce)001:1221: mi rtag nyams des bskyod pa med //
NK095(ce)001:1222: de bas phrag dog mi gnas stong //
NK095(ce)001:1223: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:1224: nga rgyal lam gyi sgor zhugs pas //
NK095(ce)001:1225: lha yi gnas dang longs spyod kyis //
NK095(ce)001:1226: ma rig ltung ba'i sdug bsngal myong //
NK095(ce)001:1227: bsam pas 'grub pa'i chos spyod kyang //
NK095(ce)001:1228: ma rig le lo'i rnam smin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:1229: ltung ba'i sdug bsngal nyams myong ste //
NK095(ce)001:1230: snying po byang chub sems de la //
NK095(ce)001:1231: ltung ba'i nyams kyis mi bskyod de //
NK095(ce)001:1232: des na nga rgyal mi gnas stong //
NK095(ce)001:1233: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:1234: zhes gsungs pa de lta bu'i phyir na zhe sdang
NK095(ce)001:1235: la sogs pa'i rang byung ye shes lnga po de
NK095(ce)001:1236: las byung ba'i rgyan gyi rgyu 'byung ba lnga'i lus
NK095(ce)001:1237: can gyi 'gro ba lam rgyud lnga'i sems can du
NK095(ce)001:1238: snang ba 'di rnams kyang don la gdod nas skye
NK095(ce)001:1239: ba med pa chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:1240: kun byed byang chub sems kyi rol pa'am rgyan du
NK095(ce)001:1241: bkod pa yin pas na 'khor ba'i chos su snang
NK095(ce)001:1242: ba 'di thams cad skye 'gag 'gro 'ong dang bral
NK095(ce)001:1243: ba rang byung ye shes gcig gi bdag nyid du
NK095(ce)001:1246: bskam chags lnga las 'byung lnga grub //
NK095(ce)001:1247: 'byung ba lnga las rang byung skyes //
NK095(ce)001:1248: snang ba'i chos dang srid pa'i chos //
NK095(ce)001:1249: mi rtog pa yi rgyu rkyen gyis //
NK095(ce)001:1250: bskyed nas ji ltar 'byung na yang //
NK095(ce)001:1251: don dam skye ba med pas na //
NK095(ce)001:1252: spros pa med pa'i don du bstan //
NK095(ce)001:1255: de ltar sku gsum ye shes lnga srid gsum snod
NK095(ce)001:1256: bcud la sogs pa dag pa dang ma dag pa
NK095(ce)001:1257: sna tshogs su bkod cing snang ba'i dus nyid nas
NK095(ce)001:1258: gang gis 'god pa byang chub kyi sems kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1259: rgyal po de nyid kyang ston pa nyid kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:1260: bzhin 'khor 'das sna tshogs su snang ba 'di kun
NK095(ce)001:1261: gyi chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba ye stong
NK095(ce)001:1262: skye ba med pa'i ngang tshul las skad cig kyang
NK095(ce)001:1263: g.yo ba med la de nyid kyis gang zhig bkod
NK095(ce)001:1264: pa yi chos rnams kyang de bzhin du bzhugs so
NK095(ce)001:1265: zhes chos nyid skye ba med pa spros bral rang
NK095(ce)001:1266: byung gi ye shes las g.yo ba med par bstan
NK095(ce)001:1267: to // gsum pa de'i don dri lan gyi tshul du bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:1268: de ltar bkod pa'i don dri ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:1269: gang gis bkod pa mtshan gyi don rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1271: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa'i chos rnams bkod pa
NK095(ce)001:1272: de nas sems dpa' rdo rje de nyid byang chub
NK095(ce)001:1273: kyi sems ston pa kun byed rgyal po'i spyan sngar
NK095(ce)001:1274: slar yang gus 'dud dang bcas pas 'dug nas zhus
NK095(ce)001:1275: pa / kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po lags /
NK095(ce)001:1276: nyid kyi thugs nyag gcig spros pa dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:1277: rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes 'gyur ba
NK095(ce)001:1279: rang byung gi ye shes rnam pa lnga rtsol med
NK095(ce)001:1280: du byung nas de las rgyan gyi rgyu 'byung ba
NK095(ce)001:1281: chen po lnga byung nas ni /
NK095(ce)001:1282: de la brten te ye shes lnga yi rigs can gyis lus lnga blangs ba'am bkod pa 'dis /
NK095(ce)001:1283: ston pa kun byed rgyal po'i mdzad pa phrin las
NK095(ce)001:1284: kyi dgos pa ci zhig che ba'am dgos pa ci
NK095(ce)001:1285: zhig yod lags zhes zhus so //
NK095(ce)001:1287: sems dpa' rdo rjes phun sum tshogs pa bkod pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1288: dgos don ji ltar yin zhus pa'i rjes de nas
NK095(ce)001:1289: ston pa byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:1290: des slar yang lan gsungs pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:1291: kye rig pa'i ngo bo rgyal sras sems dpa' chen
NK095(ce)001:1292: po de ltar phun sum tshogs rnams bkod pa'i dgos
NK095(ce)001:1293: pa ni / 'di ltar snang srid 'khor 'das kyis
NK095(ce)001:1294: bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ni kun byed rgyala po
NK095(ce)001:1295: byed mkhan nga las ni ma gtogs pa yi byed
NK095(ce)001:1296: mkhan gzhan na su yang med do zhes chos thams
NK095(ce)001:1297: cad chos nyid byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin gzhi
NK095(ce)001:1298: med rtsa bral chen po'i klong nas shar ba'i med
NK095(ce)001:1299: snang stong gzugs tsam las bden par grub pa'i dngos
NK095(ce)001:1300: po gcig kyang med par bstan to //
NK095(ce)001:1301: des na chos rnams kyi chos nyid gnas lugs 'dus
NK095(ce)001:1302: ma byas pa khyab brdal nam mkha' lta bu'i rang
NK095(ce)001:1303: bzhin byed pa po yang ni ston pa nga yi
NK095(ce)001:1304: rang bzhin gdod nas de ltar gnas pa las gzhan
NK095(ce)001:1306: sku gsum ston pa gsum yang 'god par byed pa
NK095(ce)001:1307: po nga yi rang bzhin dang ngo bo dang thugs
NK095(ce)001:1308: rje gsum gyi rtsal las de ltar shar ba ma
NK095(ce)001:1309: gtogs byed mkhan gzhan med la /
NK095(ce)001:1310: rgyal ba sku gsum po de dag gi 'khor gyi
NK095(ce)001:1311: tshogs su 'dus pa yang 'god par byed pa po
NK095(ce)001:1312: sngar smos pa ltar ston pa nga las med pa
NK095(ce)001:1313: dang / de bzhin du ston pa sku gsum gyis
NK095(ce)001:1314: bstan pa'i chos tshul nyid 'god pa yang kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1315: nga yi rtsal las rang shar ba ma gtogs gzhan
NK095(ce)001:1316: med do zhes chos thams cad la bzang ngan dbye
NK095(ce)001:1317: bsal med par byang chub kyi sems gcig gi rang
NK095(ce)001:1318: bzhin du gsungs pas ye nas kun byed kun tu
NK095(ce)001:1319: bzang po'i dgongs klong las ma 'das par bstan pa'o
NK095(ce)001:1321: de ltar chos thams cad kun byed byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:1322: kyi rang bzhin yin pa'i rgyu mtshan des na sems
NK095(ce)001:1323: dpa' rdo rje khyod la ston pa kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:1324: yis ni nga yi rang bzhin nam yin lugs ma
NK095(ce)001:1325: nor ba ji lta ba bzhin du khyod la bstan
NK095(ce)001:1326: par bya ste de bstan pas chos thams cad kyi
NK095(ce)001:1327: rang bzhin rtogs par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:1328: de yang ji ltar zhe na kun byed byang chub
NK095(ce)001:1329: kyi sems nga la rang bzhina ma bcos pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:1330: ni rnam pa gsum yod de /
NK095(ce)001:1331: nga yi rang bzhina rnam pa gsum po de gang zhe na byang ba'i rang bzhin dang /
NK095(ce)001:1333: sems kyi rang bzhin dang rnam pa gsum yin no //
NK095(ce)001:1334: de la byang ba dag gi rang bzhin bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:1335: ni ston 'khor bstan pa ste phun sum tshogs pa
NK095(ce)001:1336: rnam pa gsum gyi rang bzhin chos nyid ka dag
NK095(ce)001:1337: dri bral gyi ngo bor gnas pa 'di nyid ni
NK095(ce)001:1339: chub pa dag gi rang bzhin bstan pa ni dgos
NK095(ce)001:1340: pa thams cad phun sum tshogs pa ston 'khor bstan
NK095(ce)001:1341: pa rnam pa gsum gyis zhes ston pa snang bas
NK095(ce)001:1342: gdul byas blang dor gyi dmigs 'byed pa'i dgos pa
NK095(ce)001:1343: dang / 'khor yod pas lam bstan pa don med du mi 'gyur ba'i dgos pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1344: bstan pa yod pas ston 'khor tshogs pa don med
NK095(ce)001:1345: du mi 'gyur bar gdul bya'i don yongs su rjogs
NK095(ce)001:1346: pa'i dgos pa gsum yod pas de ltar gsungs la
NK095(ce)001:1347: / de lta bu'i phun sum tshogs pa gsum gyis
NK095(ce)001:1348: ni nam mkha' yi khams bzhin du gdul bya sems
NK095(ce)001:1349: can gyi khams kun la khyab par gnas shing snang
NK095(ce)001:1350: ba'i rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'i cha nas chub pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1351: / don dang / semsa zhesa bya ba'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:1352: bstan pa ni byang chub sems kyi rtsal thugs rje'i
NK095(ce)001:1353: rol pa mi 'gag par shar ba'i snang srid 'khor
NK095(ce)001:1354: 'das kyi chos ma lus pa thams cad kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1355: rgyal po yi thugs rje'i rol rtsal yin pa'i cha
NK095(ce)001:1356: nas ni sems zhes bya ste /
NK095(ce)001:1357: de ltar na byang ba dang chub pa dang sems
NK095(ce)001:1358: gsum po de nyid rang bzhin stong pa chos sku
NK095(ce)001:1359: dang / ngo bo gsal ba longs sku dang //
NK095(ce)001:1360: thugs rje kun khyab sprul pa'i sku gsum gyi cha la btags pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:1366: des na snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos kun de
NK095(ce)001:1367: gsum gyi gdangs las shar ba yin pas kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1368: rgyal pos byas pa yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:1369: de ltar na 'khor 'das thams cad snang dus nyid
NK095(ce)001:1370: nas rang bzhin ngo bo thugs rje ste sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:1371: gyi ngang las 'da' ba med pas blang dor bsal
NK095(ce)001:1372: bzhag gi 'bad rtsol gang yang mi dgos par ma
NK095(ce)001:1373: bcos ye bab sor bzhag gi dgongs pa la rtag
NK095(ce)001:1374: tu gnas shing de las 'da' ba med pa ni
NK095(ce)001:1375: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi gnas lugs su 'khor
NK095(ce)001:1376: 'das kyi chos ma lus pa byas pa'i dgos pa
NK095(ce)001:1378: le'u'i mtshan byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:1379: las chos nyid kyi rang mdangs mngon du phyung nas
NK095(ce)001:1380: bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'i 'grel ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:1381: don gnyis pa byung tshul bshad pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:1382: le'u gsum pas bstan pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:1383: le'u la 'jug pa'i rgyu'i don mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1384: de gnyis rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1386: de ltar phun sum tshogs pas bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:1387: kyi chos thams cad ji ltar bkod tshul bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:1388: de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:1389: des srid zhi gnyis kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:1390: kyi sngon rol du de dag kun gyi byed pa
NK095(ce)001:1391: po snying po rang byung gi ye shes rig pa
NK095(ce)001:1392: byang chub kyi sems kun byed nga nyid byung ba
NK095(ce)001:1395: ston pa nyid kun gyi sngon rol nas gzhi de bzhin nyid du gnas tshul /
NK095(ce)001:1396: snang brtags ye shes las 'phros pa'i chos kyi dri lan /
NK095(ce)001:1397: thams cad rang byung gi ye shes gcig gi rol par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1399: kye sems dpa' chen po rig pa stong gsal 'gag
NK095(ce)001:1400: med la yid ces brjod pa de nyid rna ba'i
NK095(ce)001:1401: dbang po la zhugs shing gtod cig /rna ba'i dbang
NK095(ce)001:1402: po ye shes pas ji skad brjod pa'i tshig gi
NK095(ce)001:1403: sgra don la rtogs par gyis shig dang bshad par
NK095(ce)001:1404: bya'o // zhes nyan par bskul te /
NK095(ce)001:1405: kye sems dpa' chen po ston pa nga ni kun
NK095(ce)001:1406: byed rgyal po ste zhes chos kun gyi byed pa
NK095(ce)001:1407: po mchog tu bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1408: nga ni kun byed byang chub kyi sems zhes pas
NK095(ce)001:1409: chos kun gyi snying po'am gnas lugs su bstan nas
NK095(ce)001:1410: / de lta bu'i ston pa kun tu bzang po
NK095(ce)001:1411: rang byung gi ye shes nga ma byung ba'am med
