NK095(ce)001:1413: snang srid snod bcud la sogs pa'i sku gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:1414: chos rnams 'byung ba'i snying po med cing ma grub
NK095(ce)001:1415: la zhes gdod ma'i spyi gzhi'i dus na 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:1416: ming med chen po'i rang bzhin du bstan pa ste
NK095(ce)001:1417: / de bzhin du ston pa nga nyid med pa
NK095(ce)001:1418: yi sngon rol na chos kun la dbang bsgyur bar
NK095(ce)001:1419: byed pa'i rgyal po med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1420: nga med pa yi sngon rol na kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:1421: po des gang la dbang bsgyur bar bya'i ston pa
NK095(ce)001:1422: sku gsum zhes bya ba yang ye nas med pa
NK095(ce)001:1423: dang / nga med pa yi sngon rol na sku
NK095(ce)001:1424: gsum gyi ston pa ngos bstan pa dam pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:1425: zhes bya ba yang ye nas med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1426: nga med pa yi sngon rol na chos de rnams
NK095(ce)001:1427: gang la ston pa'i yul 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs zhes
NK095(ce)001:1428: bya ba de thams cad ye nas med pas /
NK095(ce)001:1429: sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis chos rnams la yod
NK095(ce)001:1430: med dang bzang ngan blang dor sogs kyi tshul ji
NK095(ce)001:1431: lta bu yin nam snyam pa'i rtog pa ma skye
NK095(ce)001:1433: de ltar chos gzhan rnams yod med sogs spros pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1434: mtha' gang du'ang grub pa med par ma zad sems
NK095(ce)001:1435: dpa' chen po khyod nyid kyang ston pa kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1436: nga yi ngo bo las rtsal du shar ba'i sprul
NK095(ce)001:1437: pa las yod pa tsam ma yin pas kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1438: rgyal po nga ni gdod ma'i gzhi dbyings chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:1439: de bzhin nyid kyi ngang las g.yo ba med par
NK095(ce)001:1441: de ltar yang mdo bcu las /
NK095(ce)001:1442: byang chub sems kyi bde chen las //
NK095(ce)001:1443: rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:1444: snang dang srid pa gnyis su med //
NK095(ce)001:1445: snod dang bcud kyang gnyis su med //
NK095(ce)001:1446: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis kyang med //
NK095(ce)001:1447: dge dang sdig pa gnyis kyang med //
NK095(ce)001:1448: phyi nang smos pa'i chos kyang med //
NK095(ce)001:1449: med pa'i don gyi snying po la //
NK095(ce)001:1450: yod pa'i sgro skur gdab mi bya //
NK095(ce)001:1452: gnyis pa snang brtags ye shes las 'phros pa'i chos kyi dri lan la gnyis /
NK095(ce)001:1453: phun sum tshogs pa lnga gcig tha dad kyi dri lan dang /
NK095(ce)001:1454: bgrod lam de bzhin nyid kyi dri lan no //
NK095(ce)001:1457: chos can tha dad du snang yang chos nyid de bzhin nyid gcig las ma 'das par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1459: ston pa'i gnas tshul bstan pa'i rjes de nas sems
NK095(ce)001:1460: dpa' rdo rjesa ston pa byang chub kyi sems kun
NK095(ce)001:1461: byed rgyal po la slar yang zhus pa /
NK095(ce)001:1462: kye ston pa kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:1463: sems rig pa rang byung gi ye shes khyod ni
NK095(ce)001:1464: ye gdod ma nas 'khor 'das kyi chos kun gyi
NK095(ce)001:1465: spyi gzhi chos kyi dbyings nam mkha' chen po lta
NK095(ce)001:1466: bu yina zhing / sku gsum gyi ston pa dang
NK095(ce)001:1467: ni de dag gi bstan pa dang 'khor dang la
NK095(ce)001:1468: sogs pa'i khungs nas dus dang gnas ma lus pa
NK095(ce)001:1469: yang chos rnams kun byed pa'i mkhan po ston pa
NK095(ce)001:1470: byang chub kyi sems khyod kyis byas pa yin pas
NK095(ce)001:1471: bu yina zhing / na / phun sum tshogs pa
NK095(ce)001:1472: lngas ma bsdus pa'i chos gcig kyang med phyir ji
NK095(ce)001:1473: ltar snang ba'i chos rnams ma lus pa kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1474: mkhan kun byed rgyal po khyod kyis byas par snang
NK095(ce)001:1475: bu yina zhing / na / na / khyod kyis
NK095(ce)001:1476: byas pa'i ston pa sku gsum po de rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:1477: gcig gam rnam pa du ru yod pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1478: de bzhin du ston pa de dag gi bstan pa gcig gam rnam pa du ru yod pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1479: 'khor rnams kyang gcig gam rnam pa du ru yod ces zhus so //
NK095(ce)001:1480: 'di skabs gzhung na phun sum tshogs pa gsum las ma bstan kyang /
NK095(ce)001:1481: kun mkhyen bla mas sa bcad du phun sum tshogs
NK095(ce)001:1482: pa lnga gcig tha dad kyi dri lan dang gsungs
NK095(ce)001:1483: pas dus dang gnas gnyis kyang shugs bstan du bzhed
NK095(ce)001:1484: par gsal lo // gnyis pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:1485: de ltar zhus pa'i rjes de nas byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:1486: sems kun byed rgyal posa sems dpa' rdo rje la
NK095(ce)001:1487: slar gsungs pa / kye sems dpa' rdo rje 'di
NK095(ce)001:1488: ltar chos nyid kyi ngos nas rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:1489: shes 'od gsal bde gshegs snying po dbyings ye zung
NK095(ce)001:1490: du 'jug pa 'di nyid 'khor 'das kun gyi ston
NK095(ce)001:1491: par snang ba gcig pu las tha dad pa'i dbye
NK095(ce)001:1492: slar gsungs pa / ba med mod / 'on kyang
NK095(ce)001:1493: chos can snang ba'i ngos nas ston pa nga yi
NK095(ce)001:1494: rang bzhin nam gshis lugs rang bzhin ngo bo thugs
NK095(ce)001:1495: rje ste rnam pa gsum gyi rtsal las snang ba
NK095(ce)001:1496: la ston pa'i grangs ni chos sku longs sku sprul
NK095(ce)001:1497: sku ste rnam pa gsum du byung ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:1498: nga ni chos rnams kyi chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:1499: kyi rang bzhin du rnam dbyer med pa gcig pu'i
NK095(ce)001:1500: rang bzhin du bzhugs pa las tha dad pa med
NK095(ce)001:1501: la / de bzhin du ji ltar snang ba'i chos
NK095(ce)001:1502: rnams kun gyi chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyang nga
NK095(ce)001:1503: nyid kyi rang bzhin rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:1505: de lta na yang nga las byung ba'i ston pa
NK095(ce)001:1506: sku gsum gyis gdul bya rnams rim gyis drangs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1507: thabs su rang rang gi 'khor gyi tshogs la kun
NK095(ce)001:1509: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa /
NK095(ce)001:1510: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa ste bstan pa rnam pa gsum du bstan pa yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:1511: ston pa sku gsum gyi 'khor tshogs kyang kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1512: nga yi dbyings skye ba med pa gcig gi rang
NK095(ce)001:1513: bzhin du gnas pa las mngon du phyung nas ni
NK095(ce)001:1514: snang ba yin pas de ltar snang ba'i dus nyid
NK095(ce)001:1515: na'ang nga yi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'i snang ba
NK095(ce)001:1516: gcig tu bstan pa'i phyir na tha dad kyi dbye
NK095(ce)001:1517: ba med par kun byed nga yi 'khor du kun
NK095(ce)001:1519: snang tshul la nga las byung ba'i ston pa sku
NK095(ce)001:1520: gsum gyisa gdul bar bya ba'i 'khor gyi bye brag
NK095(ce)001:1521: rnam pa gsum du yod do //
NK095(ce)001:1523: gnyis pa bgrod lam de bzhin nyid kyi dri lan la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:1524: de bzhin nyid kun byed rgyal po'i sar bgrod lam yod med kyi dri lan /
NK095(ce)001:1525: sku gsum ston pa'i sar bgrod pa'i lam bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1528: gshis la lam med par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1530: sems dpa' rdo rje yang ston pa kun byed nyid la zhus pa 'di ltar /
NK095(ce)001:1531: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po lags /
NK095(ce)001:1532: ston pa khyod las byung ba'i ston pa sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:1533: gyi bstan pa la chos sku kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:1534: khyod nyid kyi sar 'gro ba'i lam ni yod dam
NK095(ce)001:1535: med / gal te med na khams gsum gyi sems
NK095(ce)001:1536: can rnams kun byed khyod kyi sa'am kun bzang chos
NK095(ce)001:1537: sku'i sa ru phyin par 'gyur ram 'on te mi
NK095(ce)001:1538: med / phyin par 'gyur / gal te bgrod pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1539: lam yod na lam de nyid bgrod pa'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:1540: 'bras bu'i sar phyin nam 'on te ma bgrod par
NK095(ce)001:1541: phyin pa yin zhes dris so //
NK095(ce)001:1543: de ltar dris pa la ston pas lan tu gsungs
NK095(ce)001:1544: pa kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1545: nga las byung ba'i ston pa sku gsum gyi /
NK095(ce)001:1546: bstan pa la kun bzang gdod ma'i mgon po nga
NK095(ce)001:1547: yi sa ru bgrod par byed pa'i lam ni med
NK095(ce)001:1548: de / ci'i phyir na chos thams cad nga yi
NK095(ce)001:1549: rang byung gi ye shes 'od gsal 'dus ma byas
NK095(ce)001:1550: pa gdod nas lhun grub chen po'i rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:1551: bstan pa yin pa de las gzhan du bgrod de
NK095(ce)001:1552: 'gro sa med pa'i phyir ro zhes so //
NK095(ce)001:1558: de ltar rang byung gi ye shes las gzhan pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1559: lam med pa'i rgyu mtshan de bas na rgyal ba
NK095(ce)001:1560: sku gsum gyi ston pa de yi 'khor du 'dus
NK095(ce)001:1561: pa rnams la gshis chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1562: ngos na rang byung ye shes kyi bdag nyid ye
NK095(ce)001:1563: nas sgrib bral ka dag gi ngo bor gnas pas
NK095(ce)001:1564: rnam par thar pa'i lam ni ye shes rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:1565: lnga po 'di las gzhan du med pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:1566: 'di nyid kho na dus gsum du gshegs bzhugs 'byor
NK095(ce)001:1567: 'gyur gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi lam du bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:1568: yin no // de la rang byung 'dus ma byas
NK095(ce)001:1569: pa'i ye shes lnga yi lam lnga po de ni
NK095(ce)001:1570: yin no // gang zhe na / 'di ltar chos
NK095(ce)001:1571: nyid kyi ngang las nam yang mi 'da' ba'i 'doda
NK095(ce)001:1572: yin no // gang zhe na / chags dang ni
NK095(ce)001:1573: / gzung 'dzin gyi chos la mi gnas pas zhe
NK095(ce)001:1574: yin no // gang zhe na / chags dang ni
NK095(ce)001:1575: / sdang dang / blang dor gyi rtog pa med
NK095(ce)001:1577: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes chos rnams kun
NK095(ce)001:1578: las khyad par du gyur pas nga rgyal dang ni
NK095(ce)001:1579: / chos nyid kyi phrag tu mtshan ma'i chos mi shong ba'i phrag dog dang rnam pa lnga ste /
NK095(ce)001:1580: de lta bu'i rang byung ye shes rnam pa lnga
NK095(ce)001:1581: po de ni sku gsum gyi ston pa'i 'khor rnams
NK095(ce)001:1586: sku gsum gyi ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:1587: po lags de ltar ranga byung ye shes kyi lam
NK095(ce)001:1588: lnga sku gsum gyi ston pa'i 'khor rnams la bstan
NK095(ce)001:1589: pa yin na / 'o na de la rang byung
NK095(ce)001:1590: zhes bya ba de ni tshul ji ltar byung ba
NK095(ce)001:1591: la de ltar brjod pa lags pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1592: de bzhin du ye shes zhes bya ba'i ming gi
NK095(ce)001:1593: brjod pa de gtan tshig gam rgyu mtshan ci la
NK095(ce)001:1594: gadgas pa dang / lam zhes bagyi ba'am btags pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1595: don nam rgyu mtshan ni gang la dgongs nas de
NK095(ce)001:1596: ltar bstan par bgyi ba'i tshul rnams rgyas par dbye
NK095(ce)001:1597: ba'i sgo nas 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti
NK095(ce)001:1598: mug dang nga rgyal dang phrag dog la sogs zhes
NK095(ce)001:1599: pa'i khungs nas de lnga yi rtsal las shar ba'i
NK095(ce)001:1600: kun rtog brgyad khri bzhi stong thams cad don la
NK095(ce)001:1601: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes las ma 'das
NK095(ce)001:1603: de dag thams cad tshur bsdus na rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:1604: ye shes lnga po de la 'dus pas rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:1605: lnga po de lam lnga yin pa'i don ni ston
NK095(ce)001:1606: pa nyid kyis bshad du gsol /
NK095(ce)001:1609: ston pa kun byed nyid kyis ji ltar dris pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1610: don bka' stsal pa kye sems dpa' chen po rang
NK095(ce)001:1611: byung ye shes rnam pa lnga po de yi lam
NK095(ce)001:1613: 'di lta ste rang byung zhes su brjod pa ni
NK095(ce)001:1614: rgyu rkyen gang gis gsar du bskyed pa med par
NK095(ce)001:1615: ye nas rang byung 'dus ma byas pa rig pa
NK095(ce)001:1616: byang chub sems kyi rtsal 'gag med du shar zhing
NK095(ce)001:1617: byung ba yin la zhes ngo bo skye med kyi
NK095(ce)001:1619: ye shes zhes pa ni gdod nas 'gag pa med
NK095(ce)001:1620: par rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ma bcos lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:1621: chen por bstan pa yin no zhes gdangs 'gag med
NK095(ce)001:1622: kyi cha nas bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:1623: des na gsal stong dbyer med pa rang byung ye
NK095(ce)001:1624: shes chen po spros bral mtshan ma med pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:1625: bzhin du gnas pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:1626: de lnga la lam du bzhag pa'i rgyu mtshan ni
NK095(ce)001:1627: bgrod bya bgrod byed thams cad rgyu rkyen gyis gsar
NK095(ce)001:1628: du bskyed pa med par ma bcos ye shes bla
NK095(ce)001:1629: ma'i sa ru ye nas lhun gyis grub zin pas
NK095(ce)001:1630: na da gsar du bgrod mi dgos te /
NK095(ce)001:1631: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa las /
NK095(ce)001:1632: rtog pas ma bcos bla ma'i sa //
NK095(ce)001:1633: 'khor ba nyid na ye sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:1635: rgyu mtshan des na ma bgrod mi bgrod bgrod par
NK095(ce)001:1636: mi 'gyur ba'i rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i ye
NK095(ce)001:1637: shes lnga la lam lngar bshad pa yin te 'khor
NK095(ce)001:1638: 'das thams cad snang ba'i rgyu'am 'char ba'i lam ni
NK095(ce)001:1641: skye dang brten pa mi 'bral bas //
NK095(ce)001:1643: zhes pa ltar la de lta bu'i ye shes lnga po yi so so'i nges tshig ni /
NK095(ce)001:1644: de la 'dod pa zhes smos pa ni 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:1645: kyi chos rnams thams cad rang byung ye shes chen
NK095(ce)001:1646: po rigs pa byang chub sems kyi bdag nyid gcig
NK095(ce)001:1647: tu 'dod pa'am grub pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:1648: chags pa ni chos nyid byang chub kyi sems bdag
NK095(ce)001:1649: tu 'dod pa'am bdag nyid chen po'i ngo bor bzhag
NK095(ce)001:1650: pa de la chags pa'am de las 'da' ba med
NK095(ce)001:1651: pa dang / zhi ba zhes pa ni blo'am sems
NK095(ce)001:1652: kyi ming yin zhing sems de ni gdod nas skye
NK095(ce)001:1653: ba med pa'i rang bzhin la gnas pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1654: sdang ba ni sems kyi cho 'phrul 'khor ba'i snang
NK095(ce)001:1655: ba sna tshogs su shar ba de gnas lugs la
NK095(ce)001:1656: grub pa med pas sdang zhing rgyab kyis phyogs pa
NK095(ce)001:1657: yin no // gati mug ces pa ni rnam par
NK095(ce)001:1658: mi rtog pa yi ting nge 'dzin gyis chos can
NK095(ce)001:1659: gyi snang ba thams cad chos nyid mnyam pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:1660: kyi ngo bor gyur pa de'i ngang la dbye bsal
NK095(ce)001:1662: nga zhes brjod pa ni gnas lugs ma nor ba
NK095(ce)001:1663: yi rang bzhin byang chub kyi sems nyid yin la
NK095(ce)001:1664: / de ni chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:1665: bzhin du ye nas gnas pas ma dag mtshan ma'i
NK095(ce)001:1666: chos dang rtsol bcas kyi theg pa kun las rgyal
NK095(ce)001:1668: phrag dog zhes pa ni snang srid 'khor 'das kyi
NK095(ce)001:1669: chos thams cad chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang
NK095(ce)001:1670: du spros bral blo 'das chen po gciga tu gnas
NK095(ce)001:1671: pa la yod med dang rtag chad yin mina la
NK095(ce)001:1672: sogs pa'i sgro skur 'debs pa thams cad gnas lugs
NK095(ce)001:1673: kyi ngang la de ltar grub pa med pas phrag
NK095(ce)001:1674: dog byed pa'am chos nyid kyi phrag tu mtshan ma'i
NK095(ce)001:1675: chos mi shong bar dog pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1677: sems dpa' rdo rjes yang gsol ba //
NK095(ce)001:1678: nyid kyi byang chub sems gcig ni //
NK095(ce)001:1679: nyon mongs dug lnga'i rang bzhin sa //
NK095(ce)001:1680: de don bdag gis rtogs gyur te //
NK095(ce)001:1682: chags pa chos nyid ngang la chags //
NK095(ce)001:1683: sems ni 'dod chags yin par rtogs //
NK095(ce)001:1684: zhe ba byang chub don la zhe //
NK095(ce)001:1685: sdang ba 'khor ba'i chos la sdang //
NK095(ce)001:1686: sems ni zhe sdang yin par rtogs //
NK095(ce)001:1687: gti ba chos nyid don la gti //
NK095(ce)001:1688: mug pa 'khor ba'i chos la mug /sems ni gti mug yin par rtogs //
NK095(ce)001:1689: nga ni byang chub sems yin la //
NK095(ce)001:1690: rgyal ni theg pa kun las rgyal //
NK095(ce)001:1691: sems ni nga rgyal yin par rtogs //
NK095(ce)001:1692: phrag ni chos nyid dbyings kyi phrag /dog pa mtshan
NK095(ce)001:1693: ma kun la dog /sems ni phrag dog yin par
NK095(ce)001:1695: tshul de dag gi bgrod du med pa'i rang byung
NK095(ce)001:1696: ye shes kyi lam lnga yi nges tshig bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:1697: yin no // gsum pa thams cad rang byung ye shes su bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:1698: khams gsum rang byung gi ye shes su bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1701: kye sems dpa' chen po khyod nyon cig ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:1702: snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa 'khor ba'i chos dang
NK095(ce)001:1703: zhi ba myang 'das kyi chos rnams thamsa cad kun
NK095(ce)001:1704: rang byung ye shes kyi lam lnga po 'di las
NK095(ce)001:1705: byung ba yin pas na 'di ltar 'dod pa'i khams
NK095(ce)001:1706: su snang ba 'di nyid kyang rang byung ye shes
NK095(ce)001:1707: kyi ngo bo de ltar snang ba yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:1708: gzugs kyi khams kyang rang byung gi ye shes kyi rang rtsal mngon du snang ba yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1709: gzugs med pa'i khams kyang rang byung ye shes yin te /
NK095(ce)001:1710: de rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir na thams cad kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1711: rgyal po byang chub kyi sems nga yis byas pa
NK095(ce)001:1712: yin pa'i phyira na ngas byas pa'i chos 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:1713: thams cad rang byung ye shesa kyi ngo bor ye
NK095(ce)001:1714: nas gnas par bshad pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:1715: khams gsuma gyi sems can mtho ris gsum dang ngan
NK095(ce)001:1716: 'gro gsum ste rgyud drug gis bsdus pa thams cad
NK095(ce)001:1717: kun kyang rang byung gi ye shes min pa gcig
NK095(ce)001:1718: kyang yod par kun byed rgyal po ngas ma bshad
NK095(ce)001:1719: de / des na khams gsum rgyud drug tu snang
NK095(ce)001:1720: ba de las ma gtogs pa yi byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:1721: sems ni sangs rgyas kun gyi mes po ston pa
NK095(ce)001:1722: kun byed rgyal po ngas ma bshad do zhes so
NK095(ce)001:1724: de la khams gsum zhes bya ba'i nges tshig gang
NK095(ce)001:1725: zhe na kun byed rgyal po nga yi ranga bzhin
NK095(ce)001:1726: la stong gsal thugs rje ste chos nyid rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:1728: de la rang bzhin gdod nas skye ba med pa'am
NK095(ce)001:1729: ma skyes pa yi chos nyid spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:1730: bas dngos po'i chos su mi snang ba'i cha nas
NK095(ce)001:1731: byang chub kyi sems de la ni gzugs med kyi
NK095(ce)001:1732: khams zhes su bstan pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:1733: ngo bo snang cha ma 'gag par skye ba'i cho
NK095(ce)001:1734: 'phrul gzugs su snang ba yi cha nas ni byang
NK095(ce)001:1735: chub kyi sems de ni gzugs kyi khams zhes su
NK095(ce)001:1737: thugs rje ma 'gag pa'i rtsal snang ye shes kyi
NK095(ce)001:1738: ngo bo mngon du phyung nas 'bras bu bde sdug
NK095(ce)001:1739: dang rgyu dge sdig gi las sna tshogs su snang
NK095(ce)001:1740: ba de nyid thugs rjes zad par bya ba'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:1741: 'dod pa'i khams ni rang rtsal 'gag pa med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1742: thugs rjes mngon du phyung zhing sprul par shar ba
NK095(ce)001:1743: yin pa'i phyir de ltar du bstan to zhes gsungs
NK095(ce)001:1745: byanga chuba kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las chos
NK095(ce)001:1746: thams cad kun byed rgyal pos byas pa las ji
NK095(ce)001:1747: ltar byung ba'i khungs bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1748: 'grel ba'o // don gnyis pa gnas lugs rgya cher bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:1749: chos thams cad gdod nas dag pa kun byed nyid du bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:1750: chos nyid sgrub bsal las 'das par bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:1751: bya btsal mtshan ma'i yul las grol ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:1752: dang po la dbyings kyi le'u bdun las /
NK095(ce)001:1753: dang po rtsa ba sems su 'dus pa kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1754: mngon du phyung ba'i le'u bzhi pa la gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:1756: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1757: dang po ni byung tshul bstan pa'i rjes de nas
NK095(ce)001:1758: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po des nyid
NK095(ce)001:1759: kyi rang bzhin gsal bar byed pa'i mtshan gyi chos
NK095(ce)001:1760: rgya cher bshad pa 'di gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:1762: thams cad kun byed nyid du 'dus par rtogs shig par gdams pa /
NK095(ce)001:1764: de nyid rtogs na thams cad lhun rdzogs gcig tu grub pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1766: kye sems dpa' chen po rdo rje khyod nyon cig
NK095(ce)001:1767: /ston pa kun byed nga ni ye nas rgyu rkyen
NK095(ce)001:1768: gang gis kyang 'dus ma byas pa rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:1769: ye shes te zhes mtshan gyi rnam grangs dang po
NK095(ce)001:1770: bstan pa dang / nga ni ye nas snang srid
NK095(ce)001:1771: snod bcud kyi chos kun gyi snying po'am bcud yin
NK095(ce)001:1772: no zhes mtshan gyi rnam grangs gnyis pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1773: nga ni kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:1774: yin no zhes mtshan gyi rnam grangs gsum pa ste
NK095(ce)001:1775: / de ltar nga yi mtshan gyi rnam grangs rnam
NK095(ce)001:1776: pa gsum po 'di sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis
NK095(ce)001:1778: nga yi mtshan rnam pa gsum po 'di yi don
NK095(ce)001:1779: semsa dapa'a rdo rjes ma nor bar rtogs par gyur
NK095(ce)001:1780: na ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad ma
NK095(ce)001:1781: lus pa yi rang bzhin rtogs par 'gyur gyis de'i
NK095(ce)001:1782: phyir na mtshan gyi don 'di rnams ji bzhin tu
NK095(ce)001:1785: thams cad rang byung gi ye shes su bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:1786: de nyid phun sum tshogs pa kun gyi rang bzhin tu bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:1787: mtshan gyi nges tshig bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1789: de la nga zhes bya ba'i don ni snying po yi don ste /
NK095(ce)001:1790: de gang gi snying po yin zhe na 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:1791: kyi chos rnams kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas
NK095(ce)001:1793: rang byung zhes ni bya ba ni dang por bskyed
NK095(ce)001:1794: pa'i rgyu dang tha ma 'jig pa'i rkyen med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1795: rang bzhin 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid chos can
NK095(ce)001:1796: snang ba'i dngos po kun gyi snying po 'am gnas
NK095(ce)001:1797: lugs yin pas sgo gsum gyi rtsol sgrub kun las
NK095(ce)001:1798: 'das pa yi don yina pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1799: ye shes zhes ni bya ba yi don ni skye
NK095(ce)001:1800: ba ma grub pas mthar 'gag pa med cing rang
NK095(ce)001:1801: bzhin 'dus ma byas pa la bsgrib bya sgrib byed
NK095(ce)001:1802: kyi chos su grub pa med pas ma bsgribs pas
NK095(ce)001:1803: sam yang na skye ba'i cho 'phrul 'gag pa med
NK095(ce)001:1804: cing rang bzhin 'od gsal gyi snang cha ma sgrib
NK095(ce)001:1805: pas chos kun ma lus pa'i rol pa rtsal snang
NK095(ce)001:1806: 'gag med du ston para byed pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1808: nga zhes 'dogs pa'i yul ni chos thams cad kyi
NK095(ce)001:1809: snying po rig pa byang chub kyi sems la 'dogs
NK095(ce)001:1811: ye nas zhes bya ba'i don 'di ni dang po
NK095(ce)001:1812: zhes sam thog ma nyid nas gnas pa'i don dang
NK095(ce)001:1813: / chos kun zhes su ni brjod par bya ba
NK095(ce)001:1814: yi don ni 'khor 'das kyi chos ma lus pa
NK095(ce)001:1815: / ste / de dag tshur bsdus na phun sum
NK095(ce)001:1816: tshogs pa lngar 'dus pas 'dir de'i sgo nas bstan
NK095(ce)001:1817: pa ni ston pa sku gsum po kun kyang chos
NK095(ce)001:1818: nyid ye stong chen po byang chub sems kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:1819: / ste / bzhin yin la / de bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:1820: ston pa de dag gis bstan pa rnam pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:1821: po kun kyang chos nyid gnyug ma'i ye shes 'di
NK095(ce)001:1822: las gzhan du yod pa ma yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:1823: 'khor rnams dang gnas dus kun kyang chos nyid stong
NK095(ce)001:1824: gsal brjod med blo 'das chen po'i rang bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:1825: yin te / des na chos nyid stong pa chen
NK095(ce)001:1826: po byang chub kyi sems ma yin pa'i 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:1827: kyi chos gcig kyang med par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1828: snying po zhesa bya ba'i don 'di ni chos rnams thams cad gang las 'byung ba'i snying po ste /
NK095(ce)001:1829: ji ltar na byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin cir
NK095(ce)001:1830: yang grub pa med pa las cir yang 'char ba'i
NK095(ce)001:1831: tshul du sku gsum gyi ston pa gsum yang de
NK095(ce)001:1833: ston pa de dag gis gsungs pa'i bstan pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:1834: yang de las byung ba dang de dag la 'dus
NK095(ce)001:1835: pa'i 'khor dang gang du bzhugs pa'i gnas dang ston
NK095(ce)001:1836: 'khor tshogs pa'i dus rnams kyang de las byung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:1837: phyir na byang chub kyi sems 'di ni chos thams
NK095(ce)001:1838: cad gang las 'byung ba'i snying po yin par bshad
NK095(ce)001:1839: pa yin no // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:1840: phun sum tshogs pa'i nges tshig dang //
NK095(ce)001:1841: byang chub sems kyi nges tshig go //
NK095(ce)001:1843: 'di ltar ston pa rang byung gi ye shes nga
NK095(ce)001:1844: ni chos rnams kun gyi snying po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:1845: sems nyid yin la de nyid kyis srid dang zhi
NK095(ce)001:1846: ba'i chos rnams ma lus pa kun byed pa yin
NK095(ce)001:1847: te / des na kun zhes bya ba'i don ni chos rnams thams cad kun yin la /
NK095(ce)001:1848: chos rnams kun zhes su brjod pa de yang gang dang gang la brjod pa yin zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:1849: de ni tshur bsdu na phun sum tshogs pa lngas
NK095(ce)001:1850: ma bsdus pa'i chos gang yang med pas na ston
NK095(ce)001:1851: pa dang ni de dag gi bstan pa dang 'khor
NK095(ce)001:1852: dang gnas dang dus ni thams cad la kun zhes
NK095(ce)001:1854: byed ces su bya ba ni de dag byed pa'i mkhan po yi don bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:1855: des na sku gsum gyi ston pa dang ni de
NK095(ce)001:1856: rnams kyis bstan pa'i chos theg pa gsum dang gdul
NK095(ce)001:1857: bya'i 'khor dang bzhugs pa'i gnas dang phun sum tshogs
NK095(ce)001:1858: pa'i dus ste rnam pa lnga po ni ma lus
NK095(ce)001:1859: pa kun byed pa'i mkhan po yin pas na rang
NK095(ce)001:1860: byung ye shes de la mkhan po zhes brjod pa
NK095(ce)001:1861: yin no // rgyal po zhes su ni bya ba
NK095(ce)001:1862: yi don ni snying po rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:1863: stong gsal brjod bral de nyid ni tshul gang gis
NK095(ce)001:1864: kyang bcos bsgyur byed mi nus pas byed pa'i mkhan
NK095(ce)001:1865: po kun las rgyal te gang gis kyang dbang byed
NK095(ce)001:1866: pa'i yul du ma grub pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1867: phar chos rnams thams cad byed mkhan rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:1868: ye shes 'di nyid gcig pu las med pas na
NK095(ce)001:1869: chos rnams kun las kyang rgyal bas na rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:1870: zhes gsungs so // 'di la sa bcad du phun
NK095(ce)001:1871: sum tshogs pa'i nges tshig ces gsungs phun sum tshogs
NK095(ce)001:1872: pa kun byed pa'i chos sku kun byed rgyal po'i
NK095(ce)001:1875: de la byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ba'i nges tshig ni ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:1876: 'di ltar byung ba zhes bya ba'i don ni 'di lta ste /
NK095(ce)001:1877: chos rnams thams cad 'byung ba'i snying po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:1878: kyi sems de ni tshogs gnyis sogs rgyu rkyen la
NK095(ce)001:1879: brten nas gsar du dag par byas lta bu ma
NK095(ce)001:1880: yin par rig pa rang byung gi ngo bor ye
NK095(ce)001:1881: nas rnam par dag pa yin pas rgyu kun byed
NK095(ce)001:1882: rgyal po des byas pa yi chos rnams kun kyang
NK095(ce)001:1883: spyod yul kun tu rnam par dag pa'i kun bzang
NK095(ce)001:1884: bde ba chen po ka dag spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:1885: ba'i klong nyid du rnam par dag pa nyag gcig
NK095(ce)001:1886: tu gnas pas byang zhes bya bar bshad pa yin
NK095(ce)001:1887: la / chub ces bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK095(ce)001:1888: snying po rang byung gi ye shes kun khyab bde
NK095(ce)001:1889: bar gshegs pa'i snying po des rang gi rtsal las
NK095(ce)001:1890: shar ba'i chos snang ba 'byung lngas bsdus pa dang
NK095(ce)001:1891: ni / srid pa phung lngas bsdus pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1892: de bzhin du phyi snod dang nang bcud kyis bsdus pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1893: dus gsum du byon pa'i sangs rgyas thamsa cad dang /
NK095(ce)001:1894: khams gsum gyis bsdus pa'i rgyud drug gi sems can rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:1895: de bzhin nyid sogs 'dus ma byas ni thams cad la ste /
NK095(ce)001:1896: mdor na 'dus byas 'dus ma byas kyis bsdus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1897: chos kun la snying po chos nyid kyi tshul du
NK095(ce)001:1898: chub ste nam mkha'i khams bzhin du khyab par gnas
NK095(ce)001:1899: pa des na chub ces bya bar bshad pa dang
NK095(ce)001:1900: / sems zhes brjod pa nyid kyi don ni 'di lta ste /
NK095(ce)001:1901: snying po rang byung gi ye shes de'i rtsal gdangs
NK095(ce)001:1902: 'gag pa med pa so sor rtog pa'i shes rab
NK095(ce)001:1903: ma 'gags par gsal ba des snang srid snod bcuda
NK095(ce)001:1904: thams cad la thogs pa med par 'jug cing dbang
NK095(ce)001:1905: bsgyur ba'i sgo nas gsal bar gcod pa des na
NK095(ce)001:1906: sems zhes bya bar bshad do //
NK095(ce)001:1907: de ltar rgyu rkyen med pa'i rang byung ye shes
NK095(ce)001:1908: chen po chos kun gyi snying po 'am snying po'i
NK095(ce)001:1909: tshul du bzhugs pa des snang srid 'khor 'das kun
NK095(ce)001:1910: la dbang bsgyur zhing thams cad byed pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:1913: kye sems dpa' chen po rdo rje kun byed byang
NK095(ce)001:1914: chub kyi sems rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:1915: nga yi rang bzhin chos sku stong gsal chen po
NK095(ce)001:1916: / gang yin gyi gza' gtad med pa /
NK095(ce)001:1917: 'di yin gyi ngos bzung med pa /
NK095(ce)001:1918: bya rtsol gyi yul du med pa /
NK095(ce)001:1919: mtshan 'dzin gyi blo dang bral ba /
NK095(ce)001:1920: gnyis snang gi mtha' las grol ba /
NK095(ce)001:1921: gnyis med kyi ngo bo med pa /
NK095(ce)001:1922: snang ba la rang bzhin med pa /
NK095(ce)001:1923: stong pa la 'gag pa med pa /
NK095(ce)001:1924: zung 'jug gi gzhi rtsa med pa /
NK095(ce)001:1925: bzang ngan dang blang dor med pa /
NK095(ce)001:1926: rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med pa khyab brdal nam
NK095(ce)001:1927: mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin 'di'i lta ba bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:1928: rtogs par gyur na sku gsum gyi ston pa kun
NK095(ce)001:1929: gyi chos nyid kyang rtogs par 'gyur la /
NK095(ce)001:1930: de dag gi bstan pa kun gyi don kyang rtogs par 'gyur ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:1931: 'khor gyi bsam pa yi bye brag ma lus pa yang rig par 'gyur la /
NK095(ce)001:1932: dus dang gnas kun gyi rang bzhin kyang gcig tu
NK095(ce)001:1933: 'gyur ba'i chos nyid dbye bsal med pa'i don rig
NK095(ce)001:1935: kyi chos rnams thamsa cad kun kyang kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:1936: yi rtsal dang rol par shar ba kho na yin
NK095(ce)001:1937: par 'gyur te / pas so // de ltar rig
NK095(ce)001:1938: cing rtogs pa la dgos pa'am yon tan ci yod
NK095(ce)001:1939: par 'gyur te / pas so // snyam na /
NK095(ce)001:1940: nga yi rang bzhin yin lugs ma nor ba 'di
NK095(ce)001:1941: ji bzhin du rig cing rtogs par gyur na 'khor
NK095(ce)001:1942: 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyi
NK095(ce)001:1943: rang bzhin ye grol bsal bzhag dang bral ba'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:1944: ma nor bar rig par 'gyur bas bya byed rtsol
NK095(ce)001:1945: sgrub kyi sbros pa kun las 'das te /
NK095(ce)001:1946: re dogs dang dgag sgrub gang yang med pa mi
NK095(ce)001:1947: rtsol lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul du kun bzang chos
NK095(ce)001:1948: sku'i rgyal sa ru da lta nyid nas gtan srid
NK095(ce)001:1951: le'u'i mtshan byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:1952: las nga nyid kyi mtshan gyi don rgya cher bshad
NK095(ce)001:1953: pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'i 'grel pa'o ////gnyis pa thams
NK095(ce)001:1954: cad kun byed nyid las byung ba'i le'u lnga pa
NK095(ce)001:1955: la gnyis te / 'jug tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:1956: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1958: de ltar mtshan gyi rnam grangs bshad pa de nas
NK095(ce)001:1959: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal pos thugs sras
NK095(ce)001:1960: sems dpa' rdo rje la sogs pa'i 'khor tshogs rnams
NK095(ce)001:1961: la ston pa nyid kyi rang bzhin bstan pa'i mdo
NK095(ce)001:1962: thams cad sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes chos
NK095(ce)001:1963: nyid rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs pa gcig tu 'dus
NK095(ce)001:1966: dbyings de bzhin nyid las theg pa du mar bstan yang rang bzhin chos nyid las ma g.yos pa /
NK095(ce)001:1967: de'i don nam mkha' lta bur bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:1968: kun dpe chos nyid du nges par byed pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:1970: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig ston pa rang
NK095(ce)001:1971: byung gi ye shes nga yi rang bzhin 'di lta
NK095(ce)001:1972: ste yoda ni chos nyid byang chub kyi sems rig
NK095(ce)001:1973: pa rang byung gi ye shes gcig las med pa
NK095(ce)001:1974: ste chos thams cad ye nas ma grub par chos
NK095(ce)001:1975: sku thig le nyag gcig gi rang bzhin du gnas
NK095(ce)001:1977: de lta na yang sems can rnams kyis rgyu lhan
NK095(ce)001:1978: gcig skyes pa dang rkyen kun tu brtags pa'i ma
NK095(ce)001:1979: rig pa gnyis kyis dbang gis yod pa chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:1980: kyi don ma rtogs par med pa 'khor ba'i 'khrul
NK095(ce)001:1981: snang sna tshogs la spyod pa la gnas lugs rang
NK095(ce)001:1982: byung gi ye shes de rtogs byed kyi thabs su
NK095(ce)001:1983: gdul bya rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams par bstan
NK095(ce)001:1984: pa'i theg pa'i rnam grangs ni 'jig rten pa'i theg
NK095(ce)001:1985: pa dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa rnam
NK095(ce)001:1986: pa gnyis su bstan pa yin te mdo bcu las
NK095(ce)001:1987: / gnyis ni rnam pa'i bye brag ste //
NK095(ce)001:1988: theg pa rnam pa gnyis su bstan //
NK095(ce)001:1989: 'jig rten pa yi theg pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:1991: zhes gsungs pa ltar la de las 'jig rten 'das
NK095(ce)001:1992: pa'i theg pa la nang gses kyi dbye ba du
NK095(ce)001:1993: zhig byung na ni gdul bya dbang po rab 'bring
NK095(ce)001:1994: tha ma gsum la rab kyi rab sogs nang gses
NK095(ce)001:1995: gsum gsum dbye ba'i dgu yod pa la ltos nas
NK095(ce)001:1996: theg pa rim pa dgu ru byung ba yin kyang
NK095(ce)001:1997: de rnams thams cad tshur bsdus na snod bcud thams
NK095(ce)001:1998: cad nam mkha'i klong du 'dus pa ltar theg pa'i
NK095(ce)001:1999: rnam grangs de rnams kyang 'dus ni chos nyid rang
NK095(ce)001:2000: byung gi ye shes lhun grub rdzogs pa chen por
NK095(ce)001:2001: dbye bsal med par gcig tu 'dus pa yin te
NK095(ce)001:2003: snang srid snod bcud thams cad dang //
NK095(ce)001:2004: sangs rgyas sems can thams cad dang //
NK095(ce)001:2005: bstan pa'i theg pa thams cad kun //
NK095(ce)001:2008: 'di ni kun bzang nga yin te //
NK095(ce)001:2009: sangs rgyas kun gyi ston pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:2012: de ltar theg pa kun gyi don rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:2013: por 'dus pa yin na 'o na rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:2014: po'i don ni ji lta bu zhig yin snyam na
NK095(ce)001:2015: de ni sngar bstan pa'i byang chub kyi sems 'di
NK095(ce)001:2016: nyid yin te zhes chos rnams kyi gnas lugs rig
NK095(ce)001:2017: pa rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngo bo ngos
NK095(ce)001:2018: bzung ba dang / de'i mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:2019: du byang chub kyi sems de gnas ni chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:2020: skye ba med pa stong chen dbyings kyi ngang la
NK095(ce)001:2021: rtag tu gnas shing de las 'da' ba med la
NK095(ce)001:2022: bzung ba dang / / gsal ni rig pa byang
NK095(ce)001:2023: chub sems kyi ngo bo 'od gsal lhun grub kyi
NK095(ce)001:2024: snang cha 'gag pa med par dbyings skye ba med
NK095(ce)001:2025: pa'i nam mkha' la ye nas sgrib pa med par
NK095(ce)001:2027: khyab ni chos kyi dbyings dang nam mkhas gar khyab
NK095(ce)001:2028: pa'i phyi nang snod bcud kyi khams kun la chos
NK095(ce)001:2029: nyid kyi tshul du ye nas 'du 'bral med par
NK095(ce)001:2030: khyab pa dang / de'i gdangs 'gag pa med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2031: rol rtsal las byung ba ni snang srid snod bcud
NK095(ce)001:2032: sogs 'khor 'das kun gyi rnam rol du byung ba
NK095(ce)001:2033: khyab pa dang / yin kyang / de lta na'ang
NK095(ce)001:2034: rang gi ngo bo 'di lta bu'o zhes bstan du
NK095(ce)001:2035: gtubs pa'i rang bzhin can mtshan ma'i dngos po can
NK095(ce)001:2036: du grub pa gang yang med la /
NK095(ce)001:2037: des na rtog med kyi shes pas mngon sum du
NK095(ce)001:2038: mthong du yang med de dmigs pa'i yul du grub
NK095(ce)001:2039: pa'i rang mtshan dang bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK095(ce)001:2040: rtog bcas kyi blo yis lung dang gtan tshig sogs
NK095(ce)001:2041: la brten nas rjes dpag gi tshul du shes su
NK095(ce)001:2042: yang med de tshig tu brjod par byed par gzhan
NK095(ce)001:2043: sel don spyi'i ngo bo tsam du'nga grub pa med
NK095(ce)001:2044: pa'i phyir ro // rgyu mtshan de lta bu'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:2045: na bskyed byed kyi rgyu las ma byung ba rang
NK095(ce)001:2046: byung 'dus ma byas pa chos kun gyi snying po
NK095(ce)001:2047: byang chub kyi sems 'di nyid yod med yin min
NK095(ce)001:2048: 'khor 'das bzang ngan la sogs spros pa'i mtha' gang
NK095(ce)001:2049: du 'ang grub pa med pas 'di dang 'di lta
NK095(ce)001:2050: bu'o zhes sgra tshig gi sgros kyis btags pa kun
NK095(ce)001:2051: dang brala bas chos nyid dmigs bsam las 'das pa
NK095(ce)001:2052: mtha' grol phyogs yan chen po'i rang bzhin du bstan
NK095(ce)001:2053: pa'i phyir ro // pa yin no // gsum pa
NK095(ce)001:2054: kun dpe chos nyid du nges par byed pa la
NK095(ce)001:2055: pa'i phyir ro // pa yin no // gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:2056: / dpe don rtags gsum gyis nges par bya ba
NK095(ce)001:2057: pa'i phyir ro // pa yin no // gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:2058: / dang / de las gzhan pa'i dpes mi rtogs
NK095(ce)001:2059: pa'i phyir ro // pa yin no // gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:2060: / dang / par bstan pa'o // dang po ni
NK095(ce)001:2061: pa'i phyir ro // pa yin no // gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:2062: / dang / par bstan pa'o // / gong du
NK095(ce)001:2063: bshad pa'i kun byed byang chub sems kyi don 'di
NK095(ce)001:2064: nges par ste ma nor ba ji lta ba bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2065: du rtogs par 'dod na dpe don rtags gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:2066: sgo nas rtogs par bya dgos te /
NK095(ce)001:2067: de la sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes mtshon
NK095(ce)001:2068: par byed pa'i dpe ni nam mkha' lta bur brtags
NK095(ce)001:2069: par bya ste / byang chub sems kyi mdo las /
NK095(ce)001:2070: chos kun dpe ni nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2072: chos kun snying po byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2074: rgyu med pa yi byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2075: ma skyes pas na nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2076: rkyen med pa yi byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2078: gnyen po med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2080: mtshon du med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2081: bstan du med pa'i nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2082: ma sgrib pa yi byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2083: kun tu gsal bas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2084: thams cad bskyed pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2085: snang srid bskyed pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2086: rang byung zab mo'i don gzhig na //
NK095(ce)001:2087: don dam ma skyes nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2088: snang dang srid dang yod pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:2089: btags shing chags pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:2090: don dam rang bzhin ma skyes pas //
NK095(ce)001:2091: skye med dpe ni nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2092: nam mkha' lta bu'i chos kun brtags //
NK095(ce)001:2094: dpe des mtshon par bya ba'i don ni 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:2095: kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyi chos nyid dam
NK095(ce)001:2096: 'byung gnas su gyur bas chos kyi dbyings spros bral
NK095(ce)001:2097: rang byung gi ye shes gdod nas skye ba med
NK095(ce)001:2098: pa'i rang bzhin du mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i bdag
NK095(ce)001:2099: nyid du shes par bya ste /
NK095(ce)001:2101: dpe de 'dra ba'i don chos ni //
NK095(ce)001:2102: yin pa dag la don zhes gdags //
NK095(ce)001:2103: don ni skye ba med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:2104: skye med pa yi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2105: rgyu med pa las skye med pas //
NK095(ce)001:2106: sems la rgyu med skye ba med //
NK095(ce)001:2107: srid pa'i chos la rgyus bskyed kyang //
NK095(ce)001:2108: chos kyi dbyings la rgyu med pas //
NK095(ce)001:2109: skye ba med pa'i don yin no //
NK095(ce)001:2110: thams cad chos ni skye ba med //
NK095(ce)001:2111: skye med byang chub mngon sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:2113: de ltar sems nyid 'dus ma byas pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2114: chos dbyings skye ba med pa spros bral nam mkha'
NK095(ce)001:2115: lta bu'i rang bzhin te nges par byed pa'i rtags
NK095(ce)001:2116: ni sems nyid gdod nas skye ba med pa de
NK095(ce)001:2117: nyid kyi gdangs rtsal 'gag pa med par rang shar
NK095(ce)001:2119: de ltar yang chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las //
NK095(ce)001:2120: rtags ni rtsal las cir yang 'char ba ste //
NK095(ce)001:2121: shar ba'i dus na shar sa shar mkhan med //
NK095(ce)001:2122: shar zhes ming tsam brtags na nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2123: ris med mnyam pa chen por 'ub chub bo //
NK095(ce)001:2125: de ltar dpe don rtags gsum gyis snang srid kyi
NK095(ce)001:2126: chos thams cad nam mkha' lta bu'i chos nyid skye
NK095(ce)001:2127: med bsam brjod dang bral ba'i rang bzhin la nam
NK095(ce)001:2128: mkha' lta bu'i dpe yis mtshon par byed cing /
NK095(ce)001:2129: mtshan 'dzin gyi rtog pa'i yul du dmigs su med
NK095(ce)001:2130: pa'i chos nyid la snang yang rang bzhin med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2131: rtsal snang 'gag pa med pa'i rtags kyi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:2132: ngos bzung gi tshul du dmigs su med par mtshon
NK095(ce)001:2134: tshig tu brjod du meda pa'i don chos nyid bsam
NK095(ce)001:2135: brjod las 'das pa la smra bsam brjod pa dang
NK095(ce)001:2136: bral ba'o zhes pa lta bu'i brjod du med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2137: tshig gis brjod de dmigs med spros bral don gyi
NK095(ce)001:2138: ngo bora bstan pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:2139: de ltar chos nyid byang chub sems kyi gnas lugs
NK095(ce)001:2140: te dpe don rtags gsum du bsdus te bstan pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2141: don 'di yis ni kun byed byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:2142: rang bzhin nam don gyi ngo bo 'grel zhing bstan
NK095(ce)001:2143: pa ste / des na dpe don rtags gsum po
NK095(ce)001:2144: 'di yis kun don skye ba med pa kun byed
NK095(ce)001:2145: nga yi don 'di yang dag par rtogs par gyis
NK095(ce)001:2146: pa ste / shig ces pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:2147: gong du ji skad bshad pa'i dpe don rtags gsum
NK095(ce)001:2148: po 'di yis kun byed rgyal po nga yi don
NK095(ce)001:2149: stong gsal spros pa dang bral ba' ye shes te
NK095(ce)001:2150: rtogs par byed dgos kyi gal te dpe don rtags
NK095(ce)001:2151: gsum po 'di lta bu yis nga yi don 'di
NK095(ce)001:2152: ma rtogs na de las gzhan pa'i don gyi gnas
NK095(ce)001:2153: lugs 'di mtshon byed kyi dpe dang brjod byed sgra
NK095(ce)001:2154: tshig ci dang gang bstan kyang nga nyid byang chub
NK095(ce)001:2155: sems chos sku kun byed rgyal po'i dgongs pa dang
NK095(ce)001:2157: cis phyir na dmigs bsam spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:2158: ngang tshul de las brgal te gzhan du ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:2159: bsam ji ltar brtags kyang kun byed nga yi dgongs
NK095(ce)001:2160: pa brjod med blo 'das chen po las gzhan du
NK095(ce)001:2161: gol la nga yi rang bzhin yid dpyod mtshan ma'i
NK095(ce)001:2162: rtog pas bsgribs te mi snang ba yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:2163: chos rnams kyi snying po rig pa rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:2164: ye shes ji bzhin pa mthong bar mi 'gyur ro
NK095(ce)001:2166: le'u'i mtshan byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:2167: las don gyi 'grel ba'i le'u ste lnga pa'i 'grel
NK095(ce)001:2168: ba'o ////gsum pa kun byed de bzhin nyid phun sum
NK095(ce)001:2169: tshogs pa'i ngo bor bstan pa'i le'u drug pa la
NK095(ce)001:2170: gnyis te / 'jug tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2171: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2173: de ltar theg pa thams cad kyi spro gzhi chos
NK095(ce)001:2174: nyid rdzogs pa chen po kun don skye ba med
NK095(ce)001:2175: pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa de nas byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:2176: sems kun byed rgyal po des 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:2177: thams cad nyid kyi rang bzhin la ye nas ma
NK095(ce)001:2178: btsal lhun gyis grub pas rtsol bral rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:2179: po yi don de bstan par byed pa'i tshig 'di
NK095(ce)001:2183: kun gyi thog mar gshis de bzhin nyid ye nas gnas pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2184: de nyid dri lan gyi tshul gyis rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2186: kye sems dpa' chen po rdo rje ji skad bshad
NK095(ce)001:2187: pa'i tshig 'di nyon la yid la zhog cig kun
NK095(ce)001:2188: byed rgyal po nga yis ni nga yi ngo bor
NK095(ce)001:2189: shar ba'i chos rnams thams cad dang por rol rtsal
NK095(ce)001:2190: 'gag pa med pa'i rten 'brel du bkod pa la
NK095(ce)001:2191: don gyi dgos pa ci zhig yod snyam na /
NK095(ce)001:2192: nga yi ngo bo phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i chos
NK095(ce)001:2193: rnams mngona du phyung ba la ston pa nga yi
NK095(ce)001:2194: ngo bo ji bzhin pa sems dpa' rdo rje khyod
NK095(ce)001:2195: la sogs pa'i 'khor tshogs rnams la bstan par bya
NK095(ce)001:2197: de ltar ngo bo bstan pa la brten nas nga yi rang bzhin kyang bstan par 'gyur te /
NK095(ce)001:2198: 'di ltar ngo bo snang ba'i chos mngon sum pa
NK095(ce)001:2199: 'di rnams la brten nas ni de nyid rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2200: med par ston pa'i tshig dang sgras kyang rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2201: skye ba med pa'i don te mtshon par byas nas
NK095(ce)001:2202: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo 'di ltar snang ba'i
NK095(ce)001:2203: chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin pa bstan par
NK095(ce)001:2204: byas pas sems dpa' chen po khyod kyis chos rnams
NK095(ce)001:2205: thams cad stong gsal brjod pa dang bral ba rang
NK095(ce)001:2206: byung ye shes nyag gcig gi rang bzhin du mthong
NK095(ce)001:2207: bar 'gyur te / dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK095(ce)001:2208: snang de cis phyir stong pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:2209: stong de cis phyir snang ba'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:2210: ces gsungs pa ltar la 'di ni thun mong gi theg pa las kyang gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:2212: tha snyad bden pa thabs su gyur pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:2213: don dam bden pa thabs byung gyur pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:2214: de gnyis rnam dbye gang gis mi shes pa //
NK095(ce)001:2215: de dag rnam rtog log pa'i lam ngan zhugs //
NK095(ce)001:2216: zhes gsungs zhing dpal ldan na g+aa rdzu nas chos
NK095(ce)001:2217: thams cad skye med du gtan la dbab par byed
NK095(ce)001:2218: pa'i rten 'byung chen po'i rig pa'i gnad kyang tshul
NK095(ce)001:2220: de ltar byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin rig stong
NK095(ce)001:2221: 'dus ma byas pa dmigs mtshan spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:2222: ba'i tshul de bstan par byas pas chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:2223: a don skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin ma bcos
NK095(ce)001:2224: mnyam pa chen po'i don de mngon sum thad drang
NK095(ce)001:2225: du rig par gyur ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:2226: de nyid ston par byed pa'i tshig rnams ngag tu
NK095(ce)001:2227: brjod par byas pas phyi rabs rjes 'jug rnams kyis
NK095(ce)001:2228: kyang don rnams thams cad sgrar brjod pa thos pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2229: sgo nas a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs pa
NK095(ce)001:2230: ji bzhin rtogs pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK095(ce)001:2231: zhes gsungs nas don la sgra tshig bsam brjod dang
NK095(ce)001:2232: bral ba brjod med blo las 'das pa mtshon pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2233: brdar cang mi gsung bar chos thams cad kyi ngo
NK095(ce)001:2234: bora gnyis med mnyam pa nyid kyi dgongs pa la
NK095(ce)001:2235: bzhugs so // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:2236: dris pa'i don zhus cig par gdams pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2238: de'i lan rgya cher gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2240: de nas bka' yi bsdu pa po sems dpa' rdo
NK095(ce)001:2241: rje de nyid 'khor gyi nang nas rang gi gdan
NK095(ce)001:2242: las langs nas ston pa byang chub kyi sems kun
NK095(ce)001:2243: byed rgyal po'i zhal du byad kyi madngas phyung ste
NK095(ce)001:2244: 'khor pas ston pa kun byed rgyal pos bka' stsal
NK095(ce)001:2245: pa / kye sems dpa' chen po khyod kyis nga
NK095(ce)001:2246: yi zhal la 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta zhing 'khod
NK095(ce)001:2247: pa de khyod kyis don zab mo ci dang gang
NK095(ce)001:2248: zhu bar 'dod pa de nga la gsol cig dang
NK095(ce)001:2249: ji ltar zhus pa'i don rnams lung bstan par bya'o
NK095(ce)001:2252: ston pas zhus cig par gnang ba stsal ba de nas sems dpa' rdo rjes zhus pa /
NK095(ce)001:2253: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po lags
NK095(ce)001:2254: 'di ltar 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:2255: rnams thams cad chos sku kun byed rgyal po khyod
NK095(ce)001:2256: kyi rang bzhin ye stong spros pa dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:2257: yin na khyod kyi ngo bo ston pa dang bstan
NK095(ce)001:2258: pa dang 'khor dang gnas dus rnams su bkod pa
NK095(ce)001:2259: la dgos pa ci zhig yod pa lags de rnams
NK095(ce)001:2260: lhan gcig tu phun sum tshogs pa'i dgos pa ci
NK095(ce)001:2261: zhig yod pa lags zhes zhus so //
NK095(ce)001:2262: gsum pa lan la lnga ste /
NK095(ce)001:2263: de bzhin nyid phun sum tshogs pa'i rang bzhin du mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2264: gnas dang gzhal yas khang bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:2265: 'khor dang ston pa so sor brjod pa /
NK095(ce)001:2266: srid pa'i khams rgyas par bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:2267: chos phun sum tshogs pa ji ltar bkod pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2269: de ltar 'khor gyis phun sum tshogs pa'i dgos don
NK095(ce)001:2270: zhus pa'i rjes de nas byang chub kyi sems kun
NK095(ce)001:2271: byed rgyal pos ji ltar dris pa'i don 'di skad
NK095(ce)001:2272: ces gsungs so // kye sems dpa' chen po khyod
NK095(ce)001:2273: nyon cig 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad
NK095(ce)001:2274: ston 'khor gnas dus la sogs pa'i phun sum tshogs
NK095(ce)001:2275: par bkod pa ni kun byed byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:2276: nga nyid ye nas phun sum tshogs pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2278: de lta bu'i nga yi rang bzhin phun sum tshogs
NK095(ce)001:2279: pa lngar gnas pa'i tshul 'di sems dpa' rdo rje
NK095(ce)001:2280: khyod la bstan par bya'o zhes so //
NK095(ce)001:2282: de bzhin nyid byang chub chen po'i gnas dang /
NK095(ce)001:2283: stong gsal rang byung ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2285: 'di ltar ston pa kun byed nga yi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2286: stong gsal brjod med bsam 'das kyi ye shes 'di
NK095(ce)001:2287: nyid dbyings spros pa dang brala ba chos nyid de
NK095(ce)001:2288: bzhin nyid dang ye nas dbyer mi phyed pa'am 'du
NK095(ce)001:2289: 'bral med pas 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi gnas
NK095(ce)001:2290: chen po 'di nyid kun byed nga yis byas pa
NK095(ce)001:2291: yin la / kun byed byang chub kyi sems rig
NK095(ce)001:2292: pa rang byung gi ye shes nga nyid gdod nas
NK095(ce)001:2293: 'pho 'gyur med par bzhugs pa las chos dbyings spros
NK095(ce)001:2294: pa dang bral ba'i gnas de na gzhan mtshan ma'i
NK095(ce)001:2295: spros pa can gyi ston 'khor su yang mi bzhugs
NK095(ce)001:2296: zhing med pas chos nyid mnyam pa chen po gcig
NK095(ce)001:2297: gi rang bzhin du gnas so //
NK095(ce)001:2299: kun byed nga yi rang bzhin zang thal gnyug ma'i
NK095(ce)001:2300: ye shes sgrib byed gang gis ma bsgribs par 'khor
NK095(ce)001:2301: 'das kun la khyab pas stong zhing gsal ba'i rang
NK095(ce)001:2302: bzhin spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i ngo bor gnas
NK095(ce)001:2303: pa de ni ye shes rang snang gi gzhal yas
NK095(ce)001:2304: khang yin la de na yang ston pa rang byung
NK095(ce)001:2305: gi ye shes chos sku kun byed rgyal po nyid
NK095(ce)001:2306: las gzhan su yang mi bzhugs pas chos sku thig
NK095(ce)001:2307: le nyag gcig gi rang bzhin yin no //
NK095(ce)001:2310: dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi 'khor gyi rang bzhin dang /
NK095(ce)001:2311: mi gnas spros pa dang bral ba ston pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2313: 'di ltar ston pa kun byed nga ni chos thamsa
NK095(ce)001:2314: cad 'byung ba'i snying po yin pa'i rgyu mtshan de
NK095(ce)001:2315: bas na 'byung ba chen po lnga dang khams gsum
NK095(ce)001:2316: rgyud drug gi sems can rnams ni kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:2317: yi sku gsung thugs las gzhan du log na med
NK095(ce)001:2318: pas ye nas nga yi rang bzhin du gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:2319: nyid nga yis ngo bo snang ba'i chos su rtsol
NK095(ce)001:2320: med du bkod pa yin no zhes pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2321: de ltar yang chos chen po rmad du byung ba las /
NK095(ce)001:2323: stong gsum gyi stong chen po 'jig rten gyi khams
NK095(ce)001:2324: 'di dag thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi
NK095(ce)001:2326: thugs nyid las ma gyur ba med do //
NK095(ce)001:2327: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams zad pa'i mtha' med pas /
NK095(ce)001:2328: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK095(ce)001:2329: mtha' yas mu med pa yang zad cing med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2330: dus med do / stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:2331: 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas mu med pa la
NK095(ce)001:2332: zad cing stong pa'i dus med pa ni bde bar
NK095(ce)001:2333: gshegs pa rnams kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs nyid
NK095(ce)001:2334: dus med do / yin te / sku gsung thugs
NK095(ce)001:2335: zad cing stong pa'i dus med pa nyid rmad du
NK095(ce)001:2339: rgyu mtshan des na 'das ma 'ong da lta ste
NK095(ce)001:2340: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang khams gsum gyi bsdus
NK095(ce)001:2341: pa'i sems can 'di ma lus pa yang ston pa
NK095(ce)001:2342: nga yi rang bzhin khyod la mngon du bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:2343: yin gyi gzhan ni ci yang med do //
NK095(ce)001:2346: sangs rgyas sku dang ye shes dang //
NK095(ce)001:2347: sems can lus dang bag chags dang //
NK095(ce)001:2348: snang dang srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:2349: byang chub sems dang dbyings su 'dus //
NK095(ce)001:2352: de la ston pa nga yi rang bzhina ni ji lta bu yin zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:2353: de ni ye nas ma skyes zhing spros pa'i mtha'
NK095(ce)001:2354: kun dang bral ba'i phyir na gang la'ang mi gnas
NK095(ce)001:2355: shing dmigs pa'i spyod yul kun las 'das pa yin
NK095(ce)001:2356: pa dang mtshan ma ris can du mi snang ba'i
NK095(ce)001:2357: ngo bo yin pas ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgom sgrub
NK095(ce)001:2358: byed pa la sogs pa'i yul las kyang 'das pa
NK095(ce)001:2360: gong du bstan pa de lta bu'i phyir na kun
NK095(ce)001:2361: byed nga yi rang bzhin dngos su ni sems dpa'
NK095(ce)001:2362: rdo rje khyod la mi snang yang nga yi ngo
NK095(ce)001:2363: bo rol rtsal 'gag pa med pa'i cha 'di khyod
NK095(ce)001:2364: la snang bar byas pas de la brten nas nga
NK095(ce)001:2365: yi rang bzhin ma nor bar rtogs pa'i dgos pa
NK095(ce)001:2366: yod pas 'di ltar du rtogs par gyis shig /de
NK095(ce)001:2367: yang 'di ltar 'dod khams dang gzugs khams gzugs med
NK095(ce)001:2368: kyi khams gsum dang 'byung ba chen po lnga dang
NK095(ce)001:2369: rgyud drug gi 'gro ba rnams su snang ba'i rang
NK095(ce)001:2370: bzhin 'di nyid ni byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2371: ye shes lnga po 'di las byung ba yin te
NK095(ce)001:2372: / tshul de ji ltar byung na rgyu rkyen med
NK095(ce)001:2373: pa'i rang byung gi ngo bo chos rnams kyi snying
NK095(ce)001:2374: po ye shes rnam pa lnga po 'di nyid mngon
NK095(ce)001:2376: ye shes lnga po de yi rtsal las yul gzugs
NK095(ce)001:2377: sgra la sogs pa lnga yang gsal bar byung la
NK095(ce)001:2378: / de byung bas yul lnga po de la brten
NK095(ce)001:2379: nas yul yid 'ong la 'dod pa'i sred pa dang
NK095(ce)001:2380: yid du mi 'ong pa la 'jigs sred la sogs
NK095(ce)001:2381: pa dug lnga'i ngo bor gyur pa phra ba'i cha
NK095(ce)001:2383: de nyid je rags su song ba'i skam zhing chags
NK095(ce)001:2384: pa'i nyon mongs pa lnga byung nas chags pa lnga
NK095(ce)001:2385: po de yi dbang gis dge sdig mi g.yo ba'i
NK095(ce)001:2387: de ltar las bsags pa de dag so sor smin
NK095(ce)001:2388: pa'i 'bras bu ni lha la sogs pa 'gro ba
NK095(ce)001:2389: drug gi khyad par gnas ris dang bde sdug tshe
NK095(ce)001:2390: tshad la sogs pa mi 'dra ba so sor snang
NK095(ce)001:2391: ba'i ngo bo ma 'gag par 'di ltar du snang
NK095(ce)001:2392: ba thams cad kun byed nga yis sems dpa' rdo
NK095(ce)001:2393: rje khyod la nga yi ngo bo bstan pa yin
NK095(ce)001:2394: no zhes snang srid 'khor 'das thams cad sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:2395: kyi rol pa las gzhan du med par bstan pa'o
NK095(ce)001:2398: de nyid gang gis bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:2400: rnam grangs rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2402: 'di ltar chos phun sum tshogs pa rnams kyang kun byed byang chub sems kyis bkod pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:2403: de yang ji ltar na ston pa sku gsum gyis
NK095(ce)001:2404: so so'i rang 'bras nges par thob par byed pas
NK095(ce)001:2405: nges thob kyi theg pa rnam pa drug tu bstan
NK095(ce)001:2406: pa yin no // gnyis pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:2407: de ltar sku gsum gyi bstan pa thams cad don
NK095(ce)001:2408: la kun byed nga yis bstan pa kho na yin
NK095(ce)001:2409: mod / sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis de ltar ma mthong ste ston pa sku gsum dang /
NK095(ce)001:2410: kun byed byang chub kyi sems gnyis tha dad du
NK095(ce)001:2411: bzung na yang don la ston pa kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:2412: yi rtsal las shar ba'i ston pa sku gsum po
NK095(ce)001:2413: de re re bzhin du kun byed nga yi rang
NK095(ce)001:2414: bzhin nas chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba ka
NK095(ce)001:2415: dag dbyings kyi cha re re yod la /
NK095(ce)001:2416: de re re bzhin du nga yi ngo bo mi 'dra ba re re snang ste /
NK095(ce)001:2417: de yang mtshan nyid theg pa'i skabs su sprul sku
NK095(ce)001:2418: thub pa'i dbang po lta bu'i sku re dang ni
NK095(ce)001:2419: // mtshan nyid sde gsum lta bu'i gsung re dang /
NK095(ce)001:2420: ji lta ji snyed kyi ye shes kyi thugs re snang ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:2421: phyi rgyud kyi skabs su longs sku rnam par snang mdzad lta bu'i sku re dang /
NK095(ce)001:2422: kri yog sde gsum lta bu'i gsung re dang /
NK095(ce)001:2423: ye shes rnam lnga lta bu'i thugs re snang ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:2424: nang rgyud kyi skabs su khyab bdag rigs drug pa lta bu'i sku re dang /
NK095(ce)001:2425: ma h+aa a nu lta bu'i gsung re dang /
NK095(ce)001:2426: dbyings nang gsal gyi ye shes gsum lta bu'i thugs re'am /
NK095(ce)001:2428: sems nyid sku gsung thugs 'di yis //
NK095(ce)001:2429: sku gcig sku gsung thugs ston te //
NK095(ce)001:2430: de yang ji lta bu zhe na //
NK095(ce)001:2431: sprul pa sku yi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2432: bden pa bzhi yi chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:2433: dbu zlum zhabs rjen brtul zhugs kyis //
NK095(ce)001:2435: sprul pa sku yi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2436: sprul pa gsung gi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2437: brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:2438: dbye bsdu rgyu 'bras gnyen po la //
NK095(ce)001:2439: dgongs te sde snod gsum gsungs pa //
NK095(ce)001:2440: sprul pa gsung gi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2441: sprul pa thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2442: chos nyid stong pa bden gnyis kyis //
NK095(ce)001:2443: rtog pa kun tu 'od kyi sa //
NK095(ce)001:2444: mi dmigs ye shes mngon pa thugs //
NK095(ce)001:2445: sprul pa thugs kyi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2446: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2447: gza' skar dus tshig bzang sgo nas //
NK095(ce)001:2448: dag pa gsum spyod rigs gsum bsgrub //
NK095(ce)001:2449: rgyan dang cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin //
NK095(ce)001:2450: longs spyod sku yi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2451: longs spyod gsung gi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2452: kri ya yo ga phyi nang gsum //
NK095(ce)001:2453: dam tshig bsgrub dang grub pa yis //
NK095(ce)001:2454: tan+t+ra sde gsum gsungs pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:2455: longs spyod gsung gi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2456: longs spyood thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2457: mtshan med sgo nas stug po bkod //
NK095(ce)001:2458: phyag rgya bzhi ldan dpal be'u ni //
NK095(ce)001:2459: longs spyod thugs kyi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2460: chos kyi sku yi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2461: sku gsum sa yi lam sbyangs nas //
NK095(ce)001:2462: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:2463: bdag nyid chen por chos skur 'dod //
NK095(ce)001:2464: chos kyi sku yi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2465: chos nyid gsung gi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2466: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen gsum //
NK095(ce)001:2467: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK095(ce)001:2468: chos nyid gsung gi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2469: chos nyid thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:2470: gzung 'dzin med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2471: sgro skur bral ba'i ye shes thugs //
NK095(ce)001:2472: ye nas rang byung ye shes so //
NK095(ce)001:2473: chos sku thugs kyi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:2474: chos sku'i rang bzhin byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2476: theg pa dgu yi snying po ste //
NK095(ce)001:2477: nga las ma byung gcig kyang med //
NK095(ce)001:2478: da ni kun gyi rang bzhin ston //
NK095(ce)001:2479: thams cad nga yin shes par bya //
NK095(ce)001:2480: zhes gsungs pa de lta bu'i sku gsum gyi gdul
NK095(ce)001:2481: bya'i 'khor kun gyis de ltar mthong ba'i ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:2482: mi 'dra ba re re yod pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2483: des na de ltar snang ba de yang gzhan zhig
NK095(ce)001:2484: min par kun byed nga yi rang bzhin bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:2485: yin gyis gnas lugs yang dag pa chos rnams kun
NK095(ce)001:2486: gyi ngo bo kun byed byang chub kyi sems ngas
NK095(ce)001:2487: bstan pa min pa'i chos ni gcig kyang yod pa
NK095(ce)001:2488: ma yin no // de bzhin du spros pa'i mtshan
NK095(ce)001:2489: ma med pa don dam dbyings kyi ngo bo yang
NK095(ce)001:2491: de'i rtsal las shar ba'i sku gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:2492: kun gyi 'byung gnas chen po yang nga nyid yin
NK095(ce)001:2493: pas gzhan du med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2494: dbyings de nyid kyi rol pa khams gsum dang rgyud
NK095(ce)001:2495: drug gis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba ma lus pa yang
NK095(ce)001:2496: kun byed nga las shar ba yin la /
NK095(ce)001:2497: 'gro ba de dag gi bde ba dang sdug bsngal
NK095(ce)001:2498: rnams dang de'i rgyu las dge sdig sogs kyi khyad
NK095(ce)001:2499: par mi 'dra ba sna tshogs su snang ba ste
NK095(ce)001:2500: kun kyang yang dag don gyi gnas lugs ma nor
NK095(ce)001:2501: ba nga yi thugs rje yi rol rtsal 'gags med
NK095(ce)001:2504: de ltar chos thams cad byang chub sems kyi ngo
NK095(ce)001:2505: bor ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin kyang 'di ltar
NK095(ce)001:2506: blo dang khams dbang shin tu dman pas rgyu dang
NK095(ce)001:2507: 'bras bu'i blang dor la zhen pa'i theg pa 'og
NK095(ce)001:2508: ma'i rigs can rnams la kun byed nga yi lung
NK095(ce)001:2509: chos thams cad ye nas rig pa byang chub se
NK095(ce)001:2510: mas kyi ngo bor grol zin pas da gsar du
NK095(ce)001:2511: rgyu 'bras 'bad rtsol la ltos mi dgos pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:2512: zab mo 'di bstan par mi bya bar gsang bar
NK095(ce)001:2513: bya ste / gal te ma gsang bar nga yi
NK095(ce)001:2514: lung 'di ngesa par te sgra ji bzhin du bstan
NK095(ce)001:2515: par byas na dge sdig gi las la rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:2516: kyi smin so bslu med du yod do zer nas
NK095(ce)001:2517: bya ste / / rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub kun las
NK095(ce)001:2518: 'das pa gnas lugs yang dag pa'i don kun byed
NK095(ce)001:2519: nga yi dgongs pa la rgyu 'bras blang dor la
NK095(ce)001:2520: sogs pa yod par sgro 'dogs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2521: nges gsang snying po'i chos la lam yang dag min
NK095(ce)001:2522: par skur ba btab te log rtog sna tshogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2523: d+r+wa bar tshud pas yang dag don gyi gnas lugs
NK095(ce)001:2524: kun byed nga dang ji srid skal pa'i yun du
NK095(ce)001:2525: 'phrad par mi 'gyur ba'i nyen chen po yod pa
NK095(ce)001:2527: bzhi pa rnam grangs rgya cher bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK095(ce)001:2528: thams cad kun byed nyid kyi byas pa /
NK095(ce)001:2529: kun byed de bzhin nyid kyi rol pa las gzhan du brtags pas 'khrul ba /
NK095(ce)001:2530: rang bzhin gcig la snang srid 'khor 'das thams cad brten tshul /
NK095(ce)001:2531: de nyid ma rtogs pas rnal ma'i don dang mi 'phrad pa /
NK095(ce)001:2532: thams cad byang chub sems su bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2534: 'di ltar ston pa nga ni kun byed byang chub
NK095(ce)001:2535: kyi sems te de yang byang chub kyi sems la
NK095(ce)001:2536: kun byed rgyal po zhes su ci'i phyir brjod snyam
NK095(ce)001:2537: na de ni chos thams cad kun byed pa'i rgyal
NK095(ce)001:2538: po yin pa'i phyir na de ltar brjod pa ste
NK095(ce)001:2539: zhes 'dir chos thams cad kyi byed po yin par
NK095(ce)001:2542: sa ni chu la chu rlung dang //
NK095(ce)001:2543: rlung ni mkha' la rab tu gnas //
NK095(ce)001:2544: mkha' ni rlung dang chu dag dang //
NK095(ce)001:2545: sa yi khams la gnas ma yin //
NK095(ce)001:2546: de bzhin phung po khams dbang rnams //
NK095(ce)001:2547: las dang nyon mongs dag pa brten //
NK095(ce)001:2548: las dang nyon mongs tshul bzhin min //
NK095(ce)001:2549: yid la byed pa rtag tu gnas //
NK095(ce)001:2550: tshul bzhin ma yin yid byed ni //
NK095(ce)001:2551: sems kyi dag pa la rab gnas //
NK095(ce)001:2552: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ni //
NK095(ce)001:2553: thams cad la yang gnas ma yin //
NK095(ce)001:2554: zhes gsungs pa ltar sems nyid 'od gsal ba chos
NK095(ce)001:2555: nyid byang chub sems kyi rtsal las rol ba'i ngo
NK095(ce)001:2556: bor snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad 'gags
NK095(ce)001:2557: med shugs 'byung gi tshul du shar zhing de ltar
NK095(ce)001:2558: shar ba'i dus nyid nas chos nyid ye stong chen
NK095(ce)001:2559: po sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i dbyings nas 'da' ba
NK095(ce)001:2560: med pa gzhi med stong gzugs kyi rol pa tsam
NK095(ce)001:2561: la go bar bya ste dper na nam mkhas chos
NK095(ce)001:2562: thams cad 'byung ba'i go 'byed par byed do zhes
NK095(ce)001:2564: khams gsum chen po lnga dang rgyud drug rnams //
NK095(ce)001:2565: snang ba'i rang bzhin byang chub sems lnga las //
NK095(ce)001:2566: rang byung snying po ye shes lnga byung bas //
NK095(ce)001:2567: ye shes lnga yi yul lnga gsal byung bas //
NK095(ce)001:2568: 'dod pa lnga byung chags pa lnga byung nas //
NK095(ce)001:2569: chags lnga so sor smin pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NK095(ce)001:2570: 'gro ba drug gi khyad par so sor snang //
NK095(ce)001:2571: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan pa ltar la rgyas
NK095(ce)001:2572: par na gzhi las gzhi snang 'char tshul gyi sgo
NK095(ce)001:2573: nas shes par bya dgos kyi de las gzhan du
NK095(ce)001:2574: phyi rol pas dbang phyug dang gtso bo sogs snod
NK095(ce)001:2575: bcud kyi byed pa por rlom pa lta bur byang
NK095(ce)001:2576: chub kyi sems zhes pa ngo bo 'gyur ba med
NK095(ce)001:2577: pa'i rtag pa yang yin la 'khor 'das thams cad
NK095(ce)001:2578: byed pa'i dngos po zhig kyang yod par bzung na
NK095(ce)001:2579: ni phyiin ci log tu 'khyams pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2580: de ltar nges par byas nas de yang chos gang
NK095(ce)001:2581: dang gang byas pa yin zhe na dus gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:2582: sangs rgyas 'gro ba'i ded dpon du byon pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:2583: kyang byang chub sems kyis byas pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:2584: khams gsum gyi sems can rnams kyang byang chub sems kyis byas pa yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2585: snang srid snod bcud kun kyang byang chub sems kyis byas pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:2586: rgyu 'bras dang dpe don gtan tshigs rnams kyang /
NK095(ce)001:2587: rgyu dang 'bras bu mi 'gal par mthun pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2588: dpe dang don mi 'gal bar mthun pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2589: sgrub byed kyi gtan tshigs kyang bsgrub bya'i don dang mi 'gal bar mthun par byas pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:2590: de yang rgyu yi dus na 'byung ba chen po rnam pa lnga byas pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:2591: 'bras bu'i dus na rgyu 'byung ba de dang ngo
NK095(ce)001:2592: bo'i mtshan nyid mthun pa 'byung 'gyur gyi dngos po
NK095(ce)001:2593: khams gsum sems can rnams kyi gnas lus longs spyod
NK095(ce)001:2594: rnams dang / rnam par shes pa rnams kyang rang rang gi rgyu dang mthun par byas pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2595: dpe yi dus na chos kun skye med du mtshon
NK095(ce)001:2596: par byed pa'i dpe nam mkha' lta bu'o zhes ston
NK095(ce)001:2597: par byed pa'i dpe de yang kun byed nga yis
NK095(ce)001:2599: don gyi ngo bo ston pa'i dus na chos thams
NK095(ce)001:2600: cad kun don skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:2602: rtags kyi dus na kun byed byang chub sems kyi rol rtsal 'gag pa med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2603: gtan tshigs kyi dus na rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:2604: yin par ston pa'i gtan tshigs kyis chos kun skye
NK095(ce)001:2605: med du bsgrub par bya ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:2606: de yang ngag don du 'god na 'di ltar /
NK095(ce)001:2607: byang chub sems kyi rol rtsal las shar ba'i 'khor 'das kyi snang ba thams cad chos can /
NK095(ce)001:2608: gdod nas skye ba med pa gzhi med rtsa bral
NK095(ce)001:2609: chen po nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin yin te
NK095(ce)001:2610: / kun byed byang chub kyis byas pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK095(ce)001:2611: zhes pa ste de ltar byang chub sems kyis byas
NK095(ce)001:2612: pa yin na chos kun skye med du grub pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2613: rgyu mtshan nam gtan tshigs ci yod snyam na /
NK095(ce)001:2614: de ni 'di ltar byang chub kyi sems rgyu rkyen
NK095(ce)001:2615: gyis ma bskyed pa rang byung gi ye shes yin
NK095(ce)001:2616: pa'i gtan tshigs kyis grub te /
NK095(ce)001:2617: 'di ltar rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa'i rang byung
NK095(ce)001:2618: yin na skye ba med pa yin par grub la
NK095(ce)001:2619: / de ltar rgyu byang chub kyi sems skye med
NK095(ce)001:2620: du grub na de'i byas pa'am rtsal las shar ba'i
NK095(ce)001:2621: chos kun kyang skye med du grub pa'i gnad kyis
NK095(ce)001:2623: rtsa ba byang chub sems 'di ni //
NK095(ce)001:2624: kun gyi rang bzhin 'dis byas pas //
NK095(ce)001:2625: thams cad byed pa'i rgyal po yin //
NK095(ce)001:2626: byed pa'i rgyal pos kun byas pas //
NK095(ce)001:2627: dngos su grub pa gang yang med //
NK095(ce)001:2629: 'di la kun mkhyen chen pos chos dbyings mdzod 'grel du /
NK095(ce)001:2630: rig pa'i ngo bo chos can /
NK095(ce)001:2631: skye med nam mkha' ltar bsam brjod las 'das pa'i tha snyad du brjod du rung ste /
NK095(ce)001:2632: khyod dang ngo bo gcig ngang nas rtsal du shar
NK095(ce)001:2633: ba'i sems la ngo bo ngos bzung gang yang med
NK095(ce)001:2634: par nam mkha' ltar ye stong spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:2636: zhes gsungs pa rtsal las shar ba'i chos la skye ba med pa'i rtags kyis /
NK095(ce)001:2637: 'char gzhi'i rig pa nyid de skye med du sgrub pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:2638: 'dir ni 'char gzhi'i rig pa skye ba med pa'i rtags kyis /
NK095(ce)001:2639: de las shar ba'i chos rnams skye med du bsgrub tshul las don 'dra'o //
NK095(ce)001:2640: de ltar rgyu 'bras dpe don gtan tshigs thams cad
NK095(ce)001:2641: mthun pa'am mtshungs par byas pas na byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:2642: kyis chos can snang ba'i dngos po kun byas kyang
NK095(ce)001:2643: / chos nyid byang chub kyi sems rang gi ngo
NK095(ce)001:2644: bo gcig pu ni sus kyang ma byas pa ste
NK095(ce)001:2645: / / chos can kun byas pa ni rig pa
NK095(ce)001:2646: byang chub kyi sems nyid kyi rang bzhin gzhi med
NK095(ce)001:2647: rtsa ba dang bral ba 'khor 'das ming med chen
NK095(ce)001:2648: / / po / ye grol ka dag gi rang bzhin /
NK095(ce)001:2649: mtha' grol phyogs yan chen po /
NK095(ce)001:2650: rgya grol gtad yal chen po /
NK095(ce)001:2651: phyi nang yul med chen po /
NK095(ce)001:2652: skye med rang byung gi ye shes khyab brdal blo las 'das pa /
NK095(ce)001:2653: yul med zang thal gyi ngo bo /
NK095(ce)001:2654: ma bcos mnyam pa chen po'i ngo bo ru byas pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:2655: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems rang gi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:2656: gcig pu sus kyang ma byas pa nyid la ni
NK095(ce)001:2659: bya mi bya'i rtsis med pas na gang yang bya
NK095(ce)001:2660: mi dgos par ye nas lhun grub chen po'i rang
NK095(ce)001:2663: 'khor 'das kun gyi gzhi ni byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2664: byang chub sems kyi gzhi ni lhun gyis grub //
NK095(ce)001:2665: lhun gyis grub pa'i don ni ma skyes pas //
NK095(ce)001:2666: skye med lhun grub snga phyi thog mtha' bral //
NK095(ce)001:2667: 'khor 'das kun gyi ngo bo byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2668: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ma nges shar //
NK095(ce)001:2669: nges pa med pa'i gzhi ni lhun gyis grub //
NK095(ce)001:2670: nges pa med pa'i don ni ma skyes pas //
NK095(ce)001:2671: skye med ma nges snga phyi thog mtha' bral //
NK095(ce)001:2672: 'khor 'das kun gyi don ni byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:2673: byang chub sems kyi don ni skye ba med //
NK095(ce)001:2674: skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin lhun gyis grub //
NK095(ce)001:2675: skye ba med pa'i ngo bo ma nges te //
NK095(ce)001:2676: skye ba med pa'i don ni ma skyes pas //
NK095(ce)001:2677: skye med ma skyes snga phyi thog mtha' bral //
NK095(ce)001:2680: de nyid ma rig pas srid par 'khyams pa /
NK095(ce)001:2681: de bzhin nyid du blang dor byas pa'i nyes dmigs /
NK095(ce)001:2682: rgyu 'bras kyi 'khrul ba rgyun mi 'chad pa /
NK095(ce)001:2683: blang dor med pa'i don mi mthong ba /
NK095(ce)001:2684: rtsol sgrub 'das pa'i chos nyid las ring ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:2686: 'di ltar ston pa kun byed rgyal po nga yi
NK095(ce)001:2687: rang bzhin ye stong spros bral chen po dgag sgrub
NK095(ce)001:2689: dmigs gtad dang ngos bzung las 'das shing re dogs
NK095(ce)001:2690: dang rtsol sgrub kyi yul las 'das pa'i gnas tshul
NK095(ce)001:2691: ma bcos ji bzhin pa la ma brtags pa'am don
NK095(ce)001:2693: nga yi byas pa'i chos 'khor 'das kyi snang ba
NK095(ce)001:2694: med snang stong pa'i rang gzugs sgyu ma'i grong khyer
NK095(ce)001:2695: lta bu la bdag gzhan dang bzang ngan bden rdzun
NK095(ce)001:2696: dang dga' sdug la sogs pa sna tshogs su mi
NK095(ce)001:2697: bden pa la bden par bzung /
NK095(ce)001:2699: nges pa med pa la nges bzung byed /
NK095(ce)001:2700: min pa la yin par bzung /
NK095(ce)001:2701: mi 'thad pa la 'thad par bzung zhing yin min
NK095(ce)001:2702: nges nges ltar brtags zhing zhen pas dgra gnyen la
NK095(ce)001:2703: sogs pa'i yul la skam zhing chags pa'i nyon mongs
NK095(ce)001:2704: dug lnga rang rgyud du skye zhing de'i dbang gis
NK095(ce)001:2705: rgyud drug 'khor ba'i snang ba 'di thams cad bden
NK095(ce)001:2707: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:2708: snang bar med la sna tshogs snang bar shar //
NK095(ce)001:2709: stong bar med la mtha' dbus khyab par gdal //
NK095(ce)001:2710: gzung 'dzin med la nga bdag so sor zhen //
NK095(ce)001:2711: gzhi rtsa med la tshe rabs brgyud mar snang //
NK095(ce)001:2712: dgag sgrub med la bde sdug blang dor byed //
NK095(ce)001:2713: phar bltas skye 'gro'i snang ba mtshar re che //
NK095(ce)001:2714: mi bden bden par zhen pas bden bden 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2716: nges med nges par bzung bas nges nges 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2717: yin min yin par bzung bas yin yin 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2719: sna tshogs col chung yul gyis sems khrid nas //
NK095(ce)001:2720: don med rig pa skad cig brgyud mar mthud //
NK095(ce)001:2721: nyin zhag zla ba lo dang mi tshe 'das //
NK095(ce)001:2722: gnyis med gnyis su bzung bas 'gro ba bslus //
NK095(ce)001:2724: de ltar zhen cing chags pa'i yul du gyur pa
NK095(ce)001:2725: snang srid snod bcud kyi dngos po 'di rnams ni
NK095(ce)001:2726: don la mi rtag sgyu ma'i rang bzhin lta bu
NK095(ce)001:2727: las bden par grub pa rdul phra rab kyi cha
NK095(ce)001:2728: tsam yang med par skad cig gis 'jig par 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:2730: thog med nas goms pa'i a 'thas zhen 'dzin gyi
NK095(ce)001:2731: dbang gis de ltar bden med yin pa'i tshul la
NK095(ce)001:2732: 'dris cha med pas mi shes pa'i 'gro ba rnams
NK095(ce)001:2733: ni yang dag lta ba'i 'dren byed ldongs pas khungs
NK095(ce)001:2734: long ngam dmud long lta bu'i rang bzhin yin no
NK095(ce)001:2736: des na chos thams cad chos sku kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:2737: pos byas pa yin pas bzang ngan blang dor med
NK095(ce)001:2738: par chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin las
NK095(ce)001:2740: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyis blang dor byas pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK095(ce)001:2741: 'di ltar nyan rang rnams kyis chos thams cad kun
NK095(ce)001:2742: byed rgyal pos byas pa chos nyid byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:2743: kyi rang bzhin yin par mi cha ba'am thag ma
NK095(ce)001:2744: chod par mig sogs dbang po drug la gzugs sogs
NK095(ce)001:2745: yul drug gi rnam pa mi 'gag par rang byung
NK095(ce)001:2746: ye shes kyi rol par shar zhing snang ba la
NK095(ce)001:2747: zag bcas sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin du mthong nas
NK095(ce)001:2748: / de'i rgyu kun 'byung las dang nyon mongs pa
NK095(ce)001:2749: rnams spang ba'i phyir du dbang po la brten pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2750: tshogs drug gi shes pa yul la 'jug tu mi
NK095(ce)001:2751: ster bar 'gegs par byed pa'i thabs la brten pa
NK095(ce)001:2752: des ni yul dang yul can la sogs pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:2753: thams cad kun byed byang chub sems kyis byas pa
NK095(ce)001:2754: ye shes nyag gcig gi rol pa yin par mi
NK095(ce)001:2755: cha bas blang dor byas pa'i dbang gis mthar thug
NK095(ce)001:2756: nyan rang gi dgra bcom thob par gyur kyang ma
NK095(ce)001:2757: rig bag chags kyi sa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2759: yid kyi rang bzhin gyi lus dang /
NK095(ce)001:2760: bsam mi khyab 'gyur gyi 'chi 'pho rnams yod par
NK095(ce)001:2761: gsungs pa bzhin skye 'gag mtshan ma'i spros pa med
NK095(ce)001:2762: pa rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i bdag nyid ma
NK095(ce)001:2763: btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras bu ni lam de
NK095(ce)001:2764: la brten nas thob pa med do //
NK095(ce)001:2766: de bzhin du chos thams cad kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:2767: byang chub kyi sems ni nges pa don gyi bden
NK095(ce)001:2768: pa thig le nyag gcig gi rang bzhin yin pa
NK095(ce)001:2769: la mtshan nyid byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ba
NK095(ce)001:2770: rnams kyis de ltar ma shes par kun rdzob sgyu
NK095(ce)001:2771: ma ltar bu dang don dam nam mkha' lta bu'i
NK095(ce)001:2772: bden pa gnyis su so sor dbye ba'i rtog pa
NK095(ce)001:2773: byung zhing de la brten nas rgyu 'bras blang dor
NK095(ce)001:2774: gyi sgo nas lam bsgrub par byed na yang kun
NK095(ce)001:2775: byed nga yis byas pa'i chos nyid la don dam
NK095(ce)001:2776: dang kun rdzob kyi bden pa gnyis su grub pa
NK095(ce)001:2777: med pas na / gang zag gi blo la de
NK095(ce)001:2778: 'dra'i rtog pa byung bas chos nyid rang gi ngo
NK095(ce)001:2779: bo la bden pa gnyis kyi mtshan nyid can gyi
NK095(ce)001:2780: rgyu 'bras skye 'gag gi dngos po zhig yongs mi
NK095(ce)001:2781: mnga' ba'am yongs su grub par mi 'gyur te chos
NK095(ce)001:2782: nyid rang gi ngo bo sus kyang bsgyur du mi
NK095(ce)001:2784: des na kun byed byang chub kyi sems rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:2785: rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i 'bras bu rang gnas phyal
NK095(ce)001:2786: ba'i ye shes de rgyu 'bras blang dor can gyi
NK095(ce)001:2787: lam la zhugs pa'i gang zag de la mthong ba'i
NK095(ce)001:2789: rgyu 'bras kyi 'khrul ba rgyun mi 'chad pa'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:2791: 'di ltar kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2792: ye grol cog bzhag chen po'i ngo bor gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:2793: las gzhan pa'i 'bras bu zhig thob tu med pa
NK095(ce)001:2794: la med par ma shes par phyi rgyud sde gsum
NK095(ce)001:2795: gyis gsar byung gi 'bras bu zhig tshol ba yi
NK095(ce)001:2796: ched du sgo gsum ma dag pa'i cha sbyangs shing
NK095(ce)001:2797: dag pa'i ngo bo lha'i sku gsung thugs su bsgom
NK095(ce)001:2798: pa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon byang lnga'i tshul gyis bsgom
NK095(ce)001:2799: pa dang / chos nyid de bzhin nyid la cho
NK095(ce)001:2800: 'phrul 'byung ba'i yul dang 'byung ba'i dngos po gang
NK095(ce)001:2801: yang ma grub pas mi 'byung ba'i rang bzhin yin
NK095(ce)001:2802: pa la de ltar ma rtogs pas ting 'dzin lha'i
NK095(ce)001:2803: cho 'phrul sogs cho 'phrul bzhi'i mtshon pa'i lam gyi
NK095(ce)001:2804: yan lag kun bsgom pa la mngon par 'chel ba'i
NK095(ce)001:2805: blang dor mnga' bas na blang dor med pa'i 'bras
NK095(ce)001:2806: bu thob pa med par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:2808: don rang byung gi ye shes gcig gi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:2809: la ma h+aa a nu gnyis kyis chos sku de
NK095(ce)001:2810: bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin sogs ting nge 'dzin rnam
NK095(ce)001:2811: pa gsum sgom par byed pasa gzhi byas te /
NK095(ce)001:2812: bsnyen sgrub kyi yan lag rnam pa bzhi ci tsam
NK095(ce)001:2813: sgrub pa'i yun dang bstan te rim par sgom par
NK095(ce)001:2814: byed pas gzhung bsrangs ba sogs rtsol sgrub kyi sgo
NK095(ce)001:2815: nas 'bras bu thob par re bas rdzogs chen rtsol
NK095(ce)001:2816: sgrub las 'das pa'i 'bras bu byar med re dogs
NK095(ce)001:2817: dang bral ba'i dgongs pa ni de la yang med
NK095(ce)001:2818: par gsungs te / mdo bcu las /
NK095(ce)001:2819: dper na phyi nang chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:2820: gang rgyu de la grub pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:2821: rgyu 'bras gcig pa'i don yin te //
NK095(ce)001:2822: 'gro ba'i sems kyi phyin ci log /brkam chags lnga yi sdug bsngal rgyus //
NK095(ce)001:2824: de la 'bras bur ming mi gdags //
NK095(ce)001:2826: spang dang 'gog dang sel ba dang //
NK095(ce)001:2827: lam la mngon du byed pa yang //
NK095(ce)001:2828: nyon mongs lnga bcom 'bras bu ste //
NK095(ce)001:2830: bden pa gnyis kyi rtog dpyod kyis //
NK095(ce)001:2831: mi rtag sdug bsngal stong bdag med //
NK095(ce)001:2832: mdo chen bzhi yi don rtogs te //
NK095(ce)001:2833: chos nyid stong pa'i 'bras bu de //
NK095(ce)001:2835: phyi yi tan tra sde gsum yang //
NK095(ce)001:2836: byang chub yan lag kun bsgooms nas //
NK095(ce)001:2837: rdo rje 'dzin dang stug po bkod //
NK095(ce)001:2838: thob pa rdo rje'i 'bras bu ste //
NK095(ce)001:2839: blang dor med pa'i 'bras bu min //
NK095(ce)001:2840: nang pa bskyed dang rdzogs pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:2841: rnam pa gsum gyi don sbyar na //
