NK095(ce)001:2842: rang rgyud dag pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK095(ce)001:2843: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi yi cho gas ni //
NK095(ce)001:2844: bdag nyid lhun grub byed pa'ang //
NK095(ce)001:2847: gsum pa rang bzhin gcig la snang srid 'khor 'das thams cad brten tshul la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:2850: snang srid ye nas sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:2853: de la dbyings stong gsal 'gag pa med pa'i ye
NK095(ce)001:2854: shes byang chub kyi sems ni gdod nas lhun gyis
NK095(ce)001:2855: grub pas bya byed kun dang bral ba ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:2856: skye ba med pa dpes mtshon du med pa ming
NK095(ce)001:2857: tshig gis gdags su med pa'o zhes pa de lta
NK095(ce)001:2858: bu'i smra bsam brjod pa dang bral ba'i tshig de
NK095(ce)001:2859: brjod pas yod par sgro 'dogs pa dang med par
NK095(ce)001:2860: skur ba 'debs pa gnyis dang bral ba'i brjod med
NK095(ce)001:2861: blo 'das chen po de rig par byed cing de
NK095(ce)001:2862: las gzhan du bya byed rtsol sgrub thams cad dang
NK095(ce)001:2863: bral ba ni ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras
NK095(ce)001:2865: sems nyid rang byung ye shes la //
NK095(ce)001:2866: ye nas btsal zhing bsgrub med pas //
NK095(ce)001:2867: rtsol sgrub gnyis kyi spros dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:2868: lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras bu yin //
NK095(ce)001:2871: 'di ltar snang srid 'khor 'das su snang ba'i chos
NK095(ce)001:2872: 'di thams cad kun ni gzhan du grub pa ci
NK095(ce)001:2873: yang med par byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin med
NK095(ce)001:2874: snang stong gzugs kyi rol pa tsam yin la byang
NK095(ce)001:2875: chub kyi sems de mtshon par byed pa'i dpe ni
NK095(ce)001:2876: chos kun skye med du ston par byed pa'i dpe
NK095(ce)001:2877: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin du chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:2878: kun 'byung ba'i gzhi dbyings rig pa byanga chub sems
NK095(ce)001:2879: kyi don yang gdod nas skye ba med pa gzhi
NK095(ce)001:2880: med rtsa bral gyi rang bzhin du de bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:2881: mtshon par byed pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:2882: de ltar yang la zlo las /
NK095(ce)001:2883: chos nyid byang chub sems ni nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:2884: nam mkha' kun khyab bdag tu 'dzin pa med //
NK095(ce)001:2885: chos nyid byang chub sems kyang kun gyi rang bzhin te //
NK095(ce)001:2886: bdag dang bdag tu grub pa rdul tsam min //
NK095(ce)001:2887: nam mkha'i ngang na sna tshogs kun khyab gnas //
NK095(ce)001:2888: 'khor dang myang 'das chos nyid dbyer mi phyed //
NK095(ce)001:2889: sna tshogs ji ltar shar yang nam mkha'i ngang du rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:2890: ngan rtog bde dang sdug bsngal chos rnams kyang //
NK095(ce)001:2891: sems nyid skye med dbyings su ma rdzogs med //
NK095(ce)001:2894: gong du bshad pa de lta bu'i gzhi dbyings lhun
NK095(ce)001:2895: grub chen po kun byed byang chub sems kyi ngo
NK095(ce)001:2896: bo gdod nas skye ba med pa nam mkha'i dpes
NK095(ce)001:2897: mtshon te bstan pa de nyid kyi rtsal las shar
NK095(ce)001:2898: ba'i snang srid thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2901: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK095(ce)001:2902: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK095(ce)001:2903: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK095(ce)001:2904: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK095(ce)001:2905: sa chu spyan dang ma ma ki //
NK095(ce)001:2906: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK095(ce)001:2907: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK095(ce)001:2908: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK095(ce)001:2909: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK095(ce)001:2910: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK095(ce)001:2911: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK095(ce)001:2914: nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NK095(ce)001:2915: srid gsum sems can ma lus kun //
NK095(ce)001:2916: gzugs su snang ba ji snyed pa //
NK095(ce)001:2917: sna tshogs phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK095(ce)001:2918: sgra ru grags pa ci snyed pa //
NK095(ce)001:2919: thams cad ma lus sngags kyi tshig /sems kyi rtog pa ji snyed pa //
NK095(ce)001:2921: dge dang mi dge'i las gang rnams //
NK095(ce)001:2922: thams cad sangs rgyas mdzad spyod de //
NK095(ce)001:2923: kun nas kun tu thams cad kun //
NK095(ce)001:2924: dngos po la sogs brtan g.yo kun //
NK095(ce)001:2925: thams cad rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK095(ce)001:2926: zhes gsungs pa ltar phyi snod kyi 'jig rten nam
NK095(ce)001:2927: mkha' rlung chu sa me yi rnam par snang ba'i
NK095(ce)001:2928: 'byung ba lnga po 'di yang rig pa byang chub
NK095(ce)001:2929: kyi sems gdod ma'i chos sku chen po'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:2930: las gzhan du ma dag pa'i snang ba rdul phra
NK095(ce)001:2931: rab tsam yang med par ye gdod ma nyid nas
NK095(ce)001:2932: ngo mtshar rmad byung gi bkod pa mngon par sangsa
NK095(ce)001:2933: rgyas pa'i bdag nyid yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:2934: de bzhin du srid pa gsum dang lam rgyud lnga
NK095(ce)001:2935: dang 'gro ba drug gi snang ba thams cad ma
NK095(ce)001:2936: lus pa yang dge sdig gi rnam par smin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2937: las kyis mi bskyod pa'am mi gos pas na sdig
NK095(ce)001:2938: pas ngan du mi 'gro srid gsum ka dag gi
NK095(ce)001:2939: rang bzhin / dge bas bzang du mi 'gro khams gsum yongs grol gyi dgongs pa /
NK095(ce)001:2940: dge sdig gnyis su med pa gzhi med rtsa bral gyi rang bzhin /
NK095(ce)001:2941: thams cad mngon sangsa rgyas pas bzang ngan spang blang dang bral ba /
NK095(ce)001:2942: re dogs rtsol sgrub las 'das pas byar med ye grol gyi klong chen po ste /
NK095(ce)001:2943: mdor na khams gsum gyis bsdus pa 'gro ba'i gnas
NK095(ce)001:2944: ris drug gi sems can 'di thams cad ye nas
NK095(ce)001:2945: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin rgyal ba kun tu
NK095(ce)001:2946: bzang po'i sku gsung thugsa gsum gyi ngo bo ste
NK095(ce)001:2947: / de yang 'dod khams snang ba'i rang bzhin sku
NK095(ce)001:2948: rdo rje gzugs khams gsal ba'i rang bzhin gsung rdo
NK095(ce)001:2949: / rje / gzugs med mi snang ba'i rang bzhin thugs rdo rje 'am /
NK095(ce)001:2950: yang na lus snang ba 'dod pa'i srid pa sku rdo rje /
NK095(ce)001:2951: ngag phyed snang gzugs kyi srid pa gsung rdo rje /
NK095(ce)001:2952: yid mi snang ba gzugs med pa'i srid pa thugs
NK095(ce)001:2953: rdo rje gsum gyi ngo bor sangs rgyas pa yin
NK095(ce)001:2955: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:2956: lnga'am ye shes bzhi yis khyab //
NK095(ce)001:2957: 'dod pa'i khams kyang kun tu bzang po nga //
NK095(ce)001:2958: gzugs med khams kyang kun tu bzang po nga //
NK095(ce)001:2959: gzugs kyi khams kyang kun tu bzang po nga //
NK095(ce)001:2960: ngas khyab thams cad bde gshegs snying po'am //
NK095(ce)001:2961: kun gyi thig le sa bon tshul du'o //
NK095(ce)001:2964: de ltar snang srid thams cad ye nas byang chub
NK095(ce)001:2965: sems kyi klong du mngon par sangs rgyas pa de
NK095(ce)001:2966: bas na snang srid snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:2967: 'di thamsa cada kun nam mkha'i nganga na mi gnas
NK095(ce)001:2968: pa gcig kyang meda pa bzhin du chos dbyings 'dus
NK095(ce)001:2969: ma byas pa rig pa byang chub semsa kyi klong
NK095(ce)001:2970: chen po ni / chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:2971: phyogs med kun khyab brdal ba'i sa gzhi la //
NK095(ce)001:2972: 'khor 'das ris med byang chub sems kyi mkhar //
NK095(ce)001:2973: chos nyid klong yangs rtse mo lhun mtho zhing //
NK095(ce)001:2974: ma byas rang bzhin phyogs bzhi yangs pa'i dkyil //
NK095(ce)001:2975: rim rtsol bral ba'i 'jug sgo shin tu yangs //
NK095(ce)001:2976: lhun grub 'byor ba'i bkod pas brgyan pa der //
NK095(ce)001:2977: rang byung ye shes rgyal po gdan la bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:2978: 'du 'phror snang ba ye shes rtsal rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:2979: blon por gyur pas yul la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK095(ce)001:2980: rang gnas bsam gtan btsun mo dam pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:2981: dgongs pa rang shar sras dang bran g.yog bcas //
NK095(ce)001:2982: bde chen klong dkyil rang gsal rtog pa med //
NK095(ce)001:2983: mi g.yo bsam brjod bral ba'i ngang nyid las //
NK095(ce)001:2984: snang srid snod bcud kun la mnga' dbang bsgyur //
NK095(ce)001:2985: chos dbyings yangs pa'i yul khams rgya che'o //
NK095(ce)001:2986: zhes gsungs pa ltar yul gyi rang bzhin rgya che
NK095(ce)001:2987: bas sangs rgyas dang sems can snang srid dang snod
NK095(ce)001:2988: bcud kun kyang bzang ngan dbye bsal med par chos
NK095(ce)001:2989: nyid mnyam pa chen po gcig gi klong du gnas
NK095(ce)001:2990: pa yin pas na dpe nam mkha' dang chos mtshungs
NK095(ce)001:2992: bzhi pa de nyid ma rtogs pas rnal ma'i don dang mi 'phrad pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:2993: de ltar chos thams cad byang chub sems kyi klong
NK095(ce)001:2994: las 'da' ba med pa de'i phyir na snang srid
NK095(ce)001:2995: kyi chos thams cad ye nas rnam par dag pa'i
NK095(ce)001:2996: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa la 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:2997: dang bzang ngan sogs gnyis chos su grub pa rdul
NK095(ce)001:2998: phra ba tsam yang med la /
NK095(ce)001:2999: de med pas dmigs pa'i spyod yul thams cad las 'das zhing /
NK095(ce)001:3000: sgro skur kun dang bral ba zhig yin pa la
NK095(ce)001:3001: gal te rnal 'byor pa gang gis smra bsam brjod
NK095(ce)001:3002: pa dang bral zhing yod med sgro skur logs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3003: rtog pas bslad pa med pa'i rang bzhin snying po
NK095(ce)001:3004: byang chub kyi sems rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das
NK095(ce)001:3005: pa'i gnas lugs 'di ma mthong na /
NK095(ce)001:3006: de las gzhan du 'bad rtsol ji tsam byas kyang
NK095(ce)001:3007: bskal pa du mar ste bskal pa mang po'i yun
NK095(ce)001:3008: du yang dag gi don dang 'phrad par mi 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:3009: bas na rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub dang bral ba'i byar
NK095(ce)001:3010: med ye grol chen po gsang chen a ti'i dgongs
NK095(ce)001:3011: pa 'di la yid ches kyi dad pa dang ldan
NK095(ce)001:3013: lnga pa thams cad byang chub sems su bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:3014: rtsa ba kun byed nyid du bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:3016: ji ltar snang yang rtsa ba chos nyid las gzhan ma yin pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3017: dang po ni 'di ltar snang srid 'khor 'das kyis
NK095(ce)001:3018: bsdus pa'i chos can gyi snang ba mi 'dra ba
NK095(ce)001:3019: sna tshogs su snang ba kun kyang /
NK095(ce)001:3020: gang las byung ba'i gzhi 'am rtsa ba sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:3021: bde gshegs snying po rig pa byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:3022: klong du gnyis su grub pa med par byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3023: kyi sems gcig pu'i rang bzhin yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:3024: de lta bu'i sangs rgyas dang sems can snang srid dang snod bcud kun ste /
NK095(ce)001:3025: mdor na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gang las
NK095(ce)001:3026: 'byung ba'i gzhi ma kun byed byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:3027: chos kun gyi snying po rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:3028: de yi rang gi ngo bo la gcig tu grub
NK095(ce)001:3029: pa'i chos kyang med na gnyis dang gsum la sogs
NK095(ce)001:3030: pa du ma'i chos su grub pa ji ltar yod
NK095(ce)001:3031: de med mod / 'on te de'i rtsal las shar
NK095(ce)001:3032: ba'i chos can gyi ngos nas bsgrangs na bsam gyis
NK095(ce)001:3033: mi khyab cing brjod kyis mi lang ste /
NK095(ce)001:3034: 'di ltar sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku gsung thugs sogs
NK095(ce)001:3035: zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos khams rgya
NK095(ce)001:3037: semsa can rnams kyi lus ngag yid gsum sogs 'khor
NK095(ce)001:3038: ba'i chos su snang ba ji snyed pa kun kyang
NK095(ce)001:3039: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir te
NK095(ce)001:3041: byang chub sems kyi don 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:3042: gcig ni kun gyi rang bzhin te //
NK095(ce)001:3043: chos kyi dbyings sam byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:3044: yin pas rtsa ba'i don du bzhag /gcig pa'i don ni 'di lta ste //
NK095(ce)001:3045: sangs rgyas sku dang ye shes dang //
NK095(ce)001:3046: sems can lus dang bag chags dang //
NK095(ce)001:3047: snang dang srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:3048: byang chub sems dang dbyings su 'dus //
NK095(ce)001:3050: de yang byang chub sems kyi mdo de nyid las /
NK095(ce)001:3052: chos kun rtsa ba sems su gcig /rtsa ba gcig la don gnyis ni //
NK095(ce)001:3053: bde dang sdug bsngal theg pa gnyis //
NK095(ce)001:3054: phun sum tshogs pa gsum tshang bas //
NK095(ce)001:3055: yo ga bzhi yi bye brag byed //
NK095(ce)001:3056: khyad par 'phags pa'i che lnga ston //
NK095(ce)001:3057: gol sgrib drug drug skyon yon sel //
NK095(ce)001:3058: gtan la rnam pa bdun gyis 'bebs //
NK095(ce)001:3059: nges pa'i man ngag brgyad du ston //
NK095(ce)001:3060: bden pa'i tshig dgu mthun smras nas //
NK095(ce)001:3061: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mdo bcu ni //
NK095(ce)001:3062: gcig gi rang bzhin ston par byed //
NK095(ce)001:3063: ces gsungs pa ltar gcig mdo byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:3064: mdo la sogs pa rnam pa bcu bstan pa las
NK095(ce)001:3065: sa bcad 'di'i khungs nas gcig mdo byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:3066: kyi mdo nyid bstan pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:3067: gang du bstan pa de ltar chos thams cad byang
NK095(ce)001:3068: chub sems kyi rang bzhin yin pa'i rgyu mtshan des
NK095(ce)001:3069: na gnyis chos kyi snang ba thams cad gnyis med
NK095(ce)001:3070: byang chub sems kyi klong du ye nas grol zin
NK095(ce)001:3071: pa yin pas gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i spros pa kun
NK095(ce)001:3073: de lta bu'i gzung 'dzin kun dang bral ba rang
NK095(ce)001:3074: byung gi ye shes bcos bsgyur spang blang las 'das
NK095(ce)001:3075: pa'i don de gang zag gang gis grub pa yin
NK095(ce)001:3076: kyang / de ltar grub pa'i gang zag des ni
NK095(ce)001:3077: lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan ma lus pa kun
NK095(ce)001:3078: grub pa yin te chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba
NK095(ce)001:3079: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes gdod nas ye
NK095(ce)001:3080: sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin can de mngon du grub
NK095(ce)001:3081: kyang / pas so // gnyis pa la brgyad de /
NK095(ce)001:3082: theg pa du ma ston pa'i rgyu brjod pa /
NK095(ce)001:3083: phun sum tshogs pa gsum du snang tshul /
NK095(ce)001:3087: rtsol sgrub tu zhen pa dor ba /
NK095(ce)001:3091: 'o na chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems gcig
NK095(ce)001:3092: gi rang bzhin yin na de la du mar bsgrangs
NK095(ce)001:3093: shing bstan pa'i rgyu mtshan ci yin zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:3094: 'di ltar kun byed byang chub sems kyi mdo rtsa
NK095(ce)001:3095: gcig pu ru chos thams cad ye nas 'dus shing
NK095(ce)001:3096: gnyis su med pa yin mod /
NK095(ce)001:3097: 'on kyang de yi don la sems shing bzang ngan
NK095(ce)001:3098: blang dor yongs su rtog pa la dga' basa te
NK095(ce)001:3099: dga' ba'i gdul bya spros pa la 'chel ba rnams
NK095(ce)001:3100: kyi ngor theg pa'i rnam grangs rnam par bsgrangs shing
NK095(ce)001:3101: bstan pa ni / 'jig rten pa dang mya ngan
NK095(ce)001:3102: las 'das pa'i theg pa gnyis dang gzhan yang theg
NK095(ce)001:3103: pa'i rim pa dgu la sogs pa'i grangs la dga'
NK095(ce)001:3104: ba rnams rdzogs pa chen po'i don la rim gyis
NK095(ce)001:3105: drang ba'i ched du kun byed nga yis bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:3106: yin no zhes gnyis mdo rnam par bgrangs ba'i mdo'i
NK095(ce)001:3107: bstan pa ni / don bstan pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:3108: chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3109: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems chos sku thig le
NK095(ce)001:3110: nyag gcig gi rang bzhin du gnas pa la ldog
NK095(ce)001:3111: cha'i sgo nas sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:3112: de la stong gsal thugs rje yi rang bzhin rnam
NK095(ce)001:3113: pa gsum du snang bas rang bzhin gsum po de
NK095(ce)001:3114: nyid kyi rtsal las ni rtsol med shugs 'byung du
NK095(ce)001:3115: bkod pa'i ngo bo ston pa phun sum tshogs pa
NK095(ce)001:3116: sangs rgyas dang / bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa dam chos dang /
NK095(ce)001:3117: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa dge 'dun gyi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:3118: yin pas mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin du snang ba
NK095(ce)001:3119: ste / de rnams ni theg pa'i rim pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:3120: gang las 'byung ba'i gzhi phun sum tshogs pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:3121: rnams ji ltar snang ba'i tshul nyid do zhes gsum
NK095(ce)001:3122: mdo phun sum tshogs pa'i mdo nyid bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3124: 'di ltar byang chub kyi sems gnyis su dbye ba
NK095(ce)001:3125: med par rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes
NK095(ce)001:3126: gcig gi rang bzhin la lam la bsgrod par byed
NK095(ce)001:3127: pa'i rnal 'byor ba kun 'brel zhing nyams su blang
NK095(ce)001:3128: bas chos nyid byang chub kyi sems rnal ma gcig
NK095(ce)001:3129: pu'i rang bzhin la blo 'byor tshul gyi sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:3130: sems dpa'i rnal 'byor phyi rgyud sde gsum dang /
NK095(ce)001:3131: rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK095(ce)001:3132: rjes su rnal 'byor a nu yo ga dang /
NK095(ce)001:3133: shin tu rnal 'byor a ti yo ga ste dbye
NK095(ce)001:3134: ba rnam pa bzhi ru byung ba yin na yang
NK095(ce)001:3135: / de dag gis rtogs bya chos kyi dbyings sam
NK095(ce)001:3136: chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes la tha dad
NK095(ce)001:3137: med pas rnal 'byor rnam pa bzhi po de yi
NK095(ce)001:3138: yul du chos nyid byang chub kyi sems 'di nyid
NK095(ce)001:3139: gcig pu bstan pa yin no zhes des ni bzhi
NK095(ce)001:3140: mdo bye brag 'byed pa'i mdo'i don bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3142: 'di ltar ngo bo sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:3143: shes gcig gi rang bzhin yin pa la ldog pas
NK095(ce)001:3144: dbye na che ba rnam pa lngar bstan te /
NK095(ce)001:3145: ji ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad spong 'gog sbyong
NK095(ce)001:3146: la mi ltos par mngon sum par sangs rgyas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3147: che bas ni mtshan nyid sde gsum las grol zhing
NK095(ce)001:3149: phyi rgyud kyi skabs su gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa
NK095(ce)001:3150: log pa dor byar lta ba'i chos de nyid ye
NK095(ce)001:3151: nas sangs rgyas pa yin pa'i che bas ni kri
NK095(ce)001:3152: yog sde gsum las khyad par du 'phags pa dang
NK095(ce)001:3153: / de yang rtsol sgrub kyi gzhan dbang la rag
NK095(ce)001:3154: ma lus par chos thams cad rang byung ye shes
NK095(ce)001:3155: kyi bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che bas
NK095(ce)001:3156: ni ma h+aa yo ga las khyad par 'phags pa
NK095(ce)001:3157: / dang / de yang rgyu 'bras kyi mtshan ma
NK095(ce)001:3158: kun las 'das de thams cad chos kyi dbyings su
NK095(ce)001:3159: sangs rgyas pa'i che bas ni a nu yo ga
NK095(ce)001:3161: sangs rgyas zhes pa de yang ming gi bla dwags
NK095(ce)001:3162: tsam las med pas sangs rgyas med pa'i che bas
NK095(ce)001:3163: ni / a ti yo ga rang gi chos thams
NK095(ce)001:3164: cad sangs rgyas par blta ba'i zhen pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:3167: mngon par sangs rgyas che bas ni //
NK095(ce)001:3168: gsum grol rang gzhung a ti dngos //
NK095(ce)001:3169: thams cad de yin blang dor bral //
NK095(ce)001:3170: yo ga a ti ra la bazla'o //
NK095(ce)001:3171: rtsol sgrub mi gnas bdag nyid che //
NK095(ce)001:3172: ma h+aa a tir la bazla'o //
NK095(ce)001:3174: a nu a tir la bazla'o //
NK095(ce)001:3175: thams cad bla dwags rgyas btab pas //
NK095(ce)001:3176: sangs rgyas med pa'i che ba ste //
NK095(ce)001:3177: a ti yo ga'i a ti'o //
NK095(ce)001:3179: de ltar che ba lnga bstan pa de byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3180: sems kyi rang bzhin la de lta bu'i yon tan
NK095(ce)001:3181: lnga dang ye nas ldan pa yin pas rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3182: lnga po de la che ba lngar ming du btags
NK095(ce)001:3183: nas bstan pa yin te 'dis ni lnga mdo che
NK095(ce)001:3184: ba lnga yi mdo bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3186: chos thams cad byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin nges
NK095(ce)001:3187: pa'i don gyi bden pa gcig gi rang bzhin yin
NK095(ce)001:3188: pa la theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyis de
NK095(ce)001:3189: ltar ma rtogs par rang rang gi grub mtha' la
NK095(ce)001:3190: zhen nas dngos po'i gnas tshul dang mthun pa'i yang
NK095(ce)001:3191: dag pa'i don yin min du lta ba'i dgag sgrub
NK095(ce)001:3192: kyi sgros te sgro btags sna tshogs pa byung bas
NK095(ce)001:3193: gol sa dang sgrib pa rngam po che dang the
NK095(ce)001:3194: tshom gyi rtog pa bsam yas pa zhig byung ba
NK095(ce)001:3195: kun ni tshur bsdu na nges thob kyi theg pa
NK095(ce)001:3196: drug la ltos pa'i gol sgrib drug tu bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:3197: de dag gi gnyen po ni kun byed byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3198: kyi sems rtsol sgrub dang blo rnam par rtog pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3199: yul las 'das pa'i rang bzhin ma nor bar mthong
NK095(ce)001:3200: bas sel bar byed pa yin no zhes pa ste
NK095(ce)001:3201: de ni drug mdo gol sgrib bstan pa'i mdo'i don
NK095(ce)001:3202: no // des na de lta bu'i yod med sgro
NK095(ce)001:3203: skur gyi mtha' la zhen pa dang the tshom gyi
NK095(ce)001:3204: rtog pa thams cad bsal ba'i phyir du chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:3205: de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin snying po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3206: kyi sems de nyid rgyu 'bras spang blang thams cad
NK095(ce)001:3207: las 'das pas cir yang rnam par mi rtog pas
NK095(ce)001:3208: sam mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis ma nor ji bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3209: du nges pa'i lung de gtan la 'bebs par gsungs
NK095(ce)001:3210: pa ni bdun mdo gtan la 'bebs pa'i mdo las
NK095(ce)001:3211: no // bstan te / de ltar yang byang chub sems kyi mdo de las /
NK095(ce)001:3212: lung gsum man ngag bzhi bdun gyis //
NK095(ce)001:3213: nges par gtan la 'bebs par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:3214: ces gsungs pa ltar lung gsum dang man ngag bzhi ste bdun gyi gtan la dbabs par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:3215: de la lung gsum ni snyan khungs brgyud pa'i lung dang /
NK095(ce)001:3216: mngon du phyung ba'i lung dang /
NK095(ce)001:3217: gtan la 'bebs pa'i lung gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:3218: de las dang po la'ang chos sku'i byin gyis rlabs
NK095(ce)001:3219: kyis bshad pa la sogs pa ston pa sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:3220: gyis rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i chos rnams gsungs
NK095(ce)001:3221: pa ni 'phags pa'i ye shes kyi snyan khung du
NK095(ce)001:3222: rgyud pa dang / sangs rgyas rab bdun la sogs
NK095(ce)001:3223: pas 'khor gyis gang zag rnams kyi skal pa dang
NK095(ce)001:3224: 'tshams par theg pa thun mong pa'i chos rnams gsungs
NK095(ce)001:3225: pa gang zag rna ba'i dbang po brgyud pa ste
NK095(ce)001:3227: gnyis pa ni chos nyid mngon du phyung ba'i lung
NK095(ce)001:3228: theg pa'i rim pa rnams te de yang tshig dang
NK095(ce)001:3229: yi ges mtshon du yod par gsungs pa thams cad
NK095(ce)001:3231: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin sgra dang
NK095(ce)001:3232: tshig gis mtshon du med par bstan pa rnams nges
NK095(ce)001:3233: pa'i lung dang rnam pa gnyis su gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:3234: gsum pa ni rtsol bcas kyi theg pa 'og ma
NK095(ce)001:3235: pa rnams kyis chos nyid kyi don ji bzhin gtan
NK095(ce)001:3236: la ma pheb pa a ti rdzogs pa chen pos
NK095(ce)001:3237: chos thams cad rgyu 'bras spang blang la mi ltos
NK095(ce)001:3238: par sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes gcig tu
NK095(ce)001:3239: 'dus par bstan pas chos rnams kyis yin lugs ji
NK095(ce)001:3240: bzhin par gtan la pheb par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3241: man ngag bzhi la bzhi tshan gnyis su gsungs pa las /
NK095(ce)001:3242: dang po bzhi ni nges pa bzhi yi man ngag dang /
NK095(ce)001:3243: mi rig rig par bshad pa gsum dang /
NK095(ce)001:3244: skabs dang phyag rgya'i man ngag gnyis dang /
NK095(ce)001:3245: de nyid lam gyi man ngag dang bzhi'o //
NK095(ce)001:3246: de las dang po nges pa bzhi ni ye shes la spang len med par nges pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3247: snying rje phyogs ris med par nges pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3248: 'byung lnga sangs rgyas nyid du nges pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3249: rgyu rkyen bral ba'i sems la gnyen po med par nges pa bzhi'o //
NK095(ce)001:3250: mi rigs rigs par bshad pa gsum ni /
NK095(ce)001:3251: sems las ma byung ba'i sangs rgyas /
NK095(ce)001:3252: rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu /
NK095(ce)001:3253: lung las ma byung ba'i man ngag gsum 'og ma'i
NK095(ce)001:3254: blo la mi 'thad cing rdzogs pa chen po'i man
NK095(ce)001:3255: ngag gis rigs shing 'thad par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3256: skabs dang phyag rgya'i man ngag las skabs nyi shu rtsa bdun ni /
NK095(ce)001:3258: rang bzhin du gnas pa'i skabs dang /
NK095(ce)001:3259: btsal ba dang bral ba'i skabs la sogs pa nyer bdun ste /
NK095(ce)001:3261: ci ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:3262: ye nas 'dus byas ma yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:3263: chos nyid dag tu gnas pa de //
NK095(ce)001:3264: chos nyid skabs zhes bstan pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:3265: zhes sogs kyis bstan pa ltar la /
NK095(ce)001:3267: mtshan ma'i yul las 'das pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK095(ce)001:3268: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i phyag rgya /
NK095(ce)001:3269: dbyings ye gnyis su med pa'i phyag rgya la sogs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:3270: de las mtshan ma'i yul la mi gnas te /
NK095(ce)001:3271: ye shes chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK095(ce)001:3272: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa //
NK095(ce)001:3273: ye shes chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK095(ce)001:3274: ces pa la sogs pas bstan pa ltar ro //
NK095(ce)001:3275: de nyid lam gyi man ngag la rnal 'byor rnam
NK095(ce)001:3276: pa bzhi po re re bzhin du sems dang chos
NK095(ce)001:3277: dang ye shes dang ngo bo dag gi man ngag
NK095(ce)001:3278: bzhi ra ra phye bas de nyid rnam pa bcu
NK095(ce)001:3280: de las shin tu rnal 'a byor de nyid ni /
NK095(ce)001:3281: rnam pa bzhi ru bgrangs par bya //
NK095(ce)001:3282: sangs rgyas sems can rgyud drug kun //
NK095(ce)001:3283: ma bcos sems kyi de nyid do //
NK095(ce)001:3284: snang srid snod bcud thams cad kun //
NK095(ce)001:3285: ma bcos chos kyi de nyid do //
NK095(ce)001:3286: dus gsum bskyod pa nges pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:3287: ma bsgribs ye shes de nyid do //
NK095(ce)001:3288: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:3289: ngo bo dag gi de nyid do //
NK095(ce)001:3290: kun tu rnal 'byor de nyid ni //
NK095(ce)001:3291: rnam pa bzhi ru bgrang bar bya //
NK095(ce)001:3292: chos dbyings ji ltar rig pa de //
NK095(ce)001:3293: de ni sems kyi de nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:3294: dbyings nyid cir yang bcos med pas //
NK095(ce)001:3295: de ni chos kyi de nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:3296: dbyings dang ye shes gsal ba ni //
NK095(ce)001:3297: de ni ye shes de nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:3298: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med pas //
NK095(ce)001:3299: de ni ngo bo de nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:3300: rnal 'byor chen po'i de nyid kyang //
NK095(ce)001:3301: rnam pa bzhi ru shes par bya //
NK095(ce)001:3302: yi ge h+aum la sogs pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:3303: de las thams cad bskyed pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:3304: sems kyi de nyid yin par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:3305: phung po 'byung ba rnam shes yul //
NK095(ce)001:3306: snang la rang bzhin med pas ni //
NK095(ce)001:3307: ye nas chos nyid de nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:3308: de ltar ma bsgribs gsal ba ni //
NK095(ce)001:3309: ye shes dag gi de nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:3310: bdag nyid chen por grub pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:3311: ngo bo dag gi de nyid do //
NK095(ce)001:3312: sems dpa'i rnal 'byor de nyid kyang //
NK095(ce)001:3313: rnam pa bzhi ru bgrang bar bya //
NK095(ce)001:3314: gang zhig ting 'dzin sdom gnas nas //
NK095(ce)001:3315: sdom de yid la gang gnas pa //
NK095(ce)001:3316: sems kyi de nyid yin par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:3317: ting 'dzin chags pa med pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:3318: chos kyi de nyid yin par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:3319: rigs dang kha dog so sor gsal //
NK095(ce)001:3320: ye shes dag gi de nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:3321: rigs bzhi phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK095(ce)001:3322: ngo bo dag gi de nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:3323: de nyid rnam pa bcu drug ni //
NK095(ce)001:3324: lam gyi lung du shes par bya //
NK095(ce)001:3327: byang chub sems kyi man ngag dang //
NK095(ce)001:3328: sbyor ba med pa'i man ngag dang //
NK095(ce)001:3329: dus gsum gtan tshig man ngag dang //
NK095(ce)001:3330: lung chen khungs kyi man ngag bzhi las /
NK095(ce)001:3331: dang po ni chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas snying
NK095(ce)001:3332: po byang chub kyi sems nyid gzung 'dzin spros pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3333: mtshan ma kun las 'das pas blang dor thams cad
NK095(ce)001:3335: gnyis pa ni chos thams cad byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:3336: rang bzhin las gnyis chos su grub pa gang yang
NK095(ce)001:3337: med pas thabs dang shes rab /
NK095(ce)001:3340: rgyu dang 'bras bu la sogs gnyis su sbyar ba gang yang med par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3341: gsum pa ni sems nyid skye 'gag med pa 'dus
NK095(ce)001:3342: ma byas pa'i rang bzhin la dus gsum gyi dbye
NK095(ce)001:3344: bzhi pa ni sems nyid rdzogs pa chen pos chos
NK095(ce)001:3345: thams cad gtan la 'bebs par bstan pa ste rgyas
NK095(ce)001:3346: par rgyud de las rtogs par bya'o //
NK095(ce)001:3348: gong du bstan pa de ltar byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:3349: gshis lugs sgro skur dang bral bar ma nor nges
NK095(ce)001:3350: pa'i don ji bzhin du gtan la phab pa de
NK095(ce)001:3351: nyid la yid ches mngon sum du bstan pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:3352: du rang bzhin bcu la rtsol zhing bsgrub tu med
NK095(ce)001:3353: par la dor bar byed pa'i man ngag ni /
NK095(ce)001:3355: sems kyi rang bzhin 'di lta ste //
NK095(ce)001:3356: lung chen rnam pa bcur snang ste //
NK095(ce)001:3357: rdzogs chen shin tu rnal 'byor gyi //
NK095(ce)001:3358: lta ba bsgom du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:3359: dam tshig bsrung du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:3360: phrin las btsal du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:3361: ye shes sgrib pa med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:3362: sa la sbyangs du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:3363: lam la bgrod du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:3364: phra ba gzung 'dzin bral ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:3365: rgyud kyi rang bzhin 'brel ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:3366: lung gi rang bzhin thog tu 'bebs //
NK095(ce)001:3367: man ngag dag gis la yang bzla //
NK095(ce)001:3368: rdzogs chen shin tu rnal 'byor gyi //
NK095(ce)001:3369: rang bzhin bcu ni de ltar ro //
NK095(ce)001:3370: zhes gsungs pa lta bu'i yid ches pa yi nges
NK095(ce)001:3371: pa'i lung bcu bstan pa yis blang dor rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:3372: kyi bya ba med pa'i don bstan pa de la
NK095(ce)001:3373: yid ches pa'i nges shes gting nas 'drongs pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:3374: du brgyad mdo nges par bstan pa'i mdo las med
NK095(ce)001:3375: pa'i man ngag rnam pa brgyad dang /
NK095(ce)001:3376: nges pa lnga dang ma nges gsum ste brgyad tshan gnyis su bstan te /
NK095(ce)001:3377: de la med pa'i man ngag brgyad ni /
NK095(ce)001:3378: de las sems la skye 'jig med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3379: don la bsgom du med pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3380: spyod pa blang dor med pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3381: lam la bsgrod du med pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3382: rnam pa bgrang du med pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3383: sems la ngo bo med pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3384: chos nyid mtshon du med pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3385: sgro skur gdags su med pa brgyad //
NK095(ce)001:3386: ces de dag gi rgyu mtshan dang bcas gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:3387: brgyad tshan gnyis pa la nges pa lnga dang /
NK095(ce)001:3388: ma nges pa gsum ste brgyad las /
NK095(ce)001:3391: nges pa lnga ni gang zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:3392: dus la khyad par med par nges //
NK095(ce)001:3393: bla ma mchod par mnyam par nges //
NK095(ce)001:3394: mchod pa bsngo ru med par nges //
NK095(ce)001:3395: dka' sla mtshon du med par nges //
NK095(ce)001:3396: bde dang sdug bsngal rgyu mthun nges //
NK095(ce)001:3400: chos kyi rang bzhin ma nges dang //
NK095(ce)001:3401: blo yi rang bzhin ma nges dang //
NK095(ce)001:3402: ye shes rang bzhin ma nges gsum //
NK095(ce)001:3403: ces gsungs la rgyas par rgyud de nyid du blta bar bya'o //
NK095(ce)001:3405: 'di ltar chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:3406: byang chub kyi sems la rgyu 'bras blang dor cir
NK095(ce)001:3407: yang mi dmigs pas de la bgrod par byed pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3408: theg pa'i dbyer med par grub kyang gdul bya rnams
NK095(ce)001:3409: kyi chos nyid kyi don rang rang gis ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:3410: mthong tshul bzhin bden pa'i ngag gis theg pa'i tshig
NK095(ce)001:3411: dgu smras pa ni chos rnams kyi snying po byang
NK095(ce)001:3412: chub kyi sems gcig po la so so'i blos mthong
NK095(ce)001:3413: ba'i tshul gyis yul dgu byung ba bzhin rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:3414: rang res te rang rang so sos ji ltar mthong
NK095(ce)001:3415: ba'i don rnams brjod byed kyi bden pa'i tshig dgu
NK095(ce)001:3416: smras pa de thams cad don la sems nyid rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:3417: pa chen po'i byin brlab las byung ba yin par
NK095(ce)001:3418: dgu mdo theg pa yas 'bubs kyi mdo las gsungs
NK095(ce)001:3420: kye 'dus pa'i tshogs chen da nyon cig /chos nyid rang bzhin sems nyid de //
NK095(ce)001:3421: sems nyid rang bzhin rdzogs pa che //
NK095(ce)001:3422: rdzogs chen chos nyid skye med las /
NK095(ce)001:3424: longs spyod rdzogs sku sprul pa'i sku //
NK095(ce)001:3425: sum brgyad dgu phrug rnam sprul pa //
NK095(ce)001:3426: tshig dang yi ge dgur grags te //
NK095(ce)001:3427: theg pa rnam pa dgu ru bstan //
NK095(ce)001:3428: de yang gang dang gang zhe na //
NK095(ce)001:3429: nyan thos rang rgyal theg chen gsum //
NK095(ce)001:3430: sprul pa'i sku yi gsung du bstan //
NK095(ce)001:3431: kri ya yo ga phyi ba gsum //
NK095(ce)001:3432: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i bstan par grags //
NK095(ce)001:3433: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen gsum //
NK095(ce)001:3434: chos kyi sku yi gsung du bstan //
NK095(ce)001:3435: sku gsum y+aa na rnam pa dgu //
NK095(ce)001:3436: rdzogs pa chen po'i byin gyis rlobs //
NK095(ce)001:3439: de ltar dbye ba sna tshogs byas kyang don la
NK095(ce)001:3440: kun byed byang chub kyi sems srid zhi kun khyab
NK095(ce)001:3441: chen po rig pa rang byung gi ye shes nga
NK095(ce)001:3442: la 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:3443: thams cad lus pa med par 'dus shing rdzogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3444: phyir na byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ye grol
NK095(ce)001:3445: bsam brjod las 'das pa'i don bcos bsgyur spang blang
NK095(ce)001:3446: dang bral ba 'di nyid ji bzhin du shes na
NK095(ce)001:3447: chos thams cad kun rang byung ye shes chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:3448: bdag nyid du gdod nas mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3449: tshul kyang shes par 'gyur bas na 'di nyid shin
NK095(ce)001:3450: tu gal che bar shes par gyis shig ces pa
NK095(ce)001:3451: ste / de ltar yang bcu mdo yongs su rdzogs pa'i mdo las /
NK095(ce)001:3452: ci ltar snang ba'i chos rnams ni //
NK095(ce)001:3453: byang chub sems la rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:3454: byang chub sems 'di shes par gyis //
NK095(ce)001:3455: byang chub sems 'di shes pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3456: chos kun rang la rdzogs par shes //
NK095(ce)001:3457: rang las byung ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:3458: rang byung ye shes sems su shes //
NK095(ce)001:3459: rang byung byang chub sems 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:3460: ma yin pa yi chos med pas //
NK095(ce)001:3461: sems ma yin gyi chos yod min //
NK095(ce)001:3463: de yang 'dir kun byed byang chub kyi sems la
NK095(ce)001:3464: chos thams cad rdzogs par gsungs pa de nyid kun
NK095(ce)001:3465: bzang gdod ma'i mgon po'i thugs rig pa rang byung
NK095(ce)001:3466: gi ye shes zhes pa zhing gzhan du med par
NK095(ce)001:3467: da lta sems can rnams kyi rang rang gi rgyud
NK095(ce)001:3468: na sems kyi chos nyid rig pa bde gshegs snying
NK095(ce)001:3469: po spros bral rang byung gi ye shes gsal khyab
NK095(ce)001:3470: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin du bzhugs pa 'di
NK095(ce)001:3471: nyid sku gsum gyi rgyal ba ma lus pa'i thugs
NK095(ce)001:3472: rang byung gi ye shes dang ye nas dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:3473: gcig gi ngo bor gnas shing de'i klong du 'khor
NK095(ce)001:3474: 'das kyi chos kun kyang ma bcos mnyam pa chen
NK095(ce)001:3475: po'i ngo bor rdzogs pa yin par bstan pa ste
NK095(ce)001:3477: chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems la rdzogs par
NK095(ce)001:3478: bstan pa'i 'phror 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs rnams kyis slar
NK095(ce)001:3479: yang zhus pa / e ma ho /
NK095(ce)001:3480: sems dpa' rdo rje kun tu bzang //
NK095(ce)001:3481: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:3482: sems yin sems min chos med na //
NK095(ce)001:3483: bdag cag 'dus pa'i tshogs kyi sems su yang //
NK095(ce)001:3484: chos kun rab tu 'dus lags sam //
NK095(ce)001:3486: de las sems dpa' chen pos don 'di gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:3489: 'di yi don kun rig par gyis //
NK095(ce)001:3490: snang chos rgyu ni 'byung chen lnga //
NK095(ce)001:3491: 'byung lnga rgyu ni byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:3492: sems kyis chos rnams snang bar byed //
NK095(ce)001:3493: sems mi snang la chos mi snang //
NK095(ce)001:3494: des na chos rnams sems su 'dus //
NK095(ce)001:3495: sems la gcig las yod ma yin //
NK095(ce)001:3496: sems gcig kun la khyab pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:3497: sangs rgyas ye shes thugs kyang sems //
NK095(ce)001:3498: sems can bag chags yid kyang sems //
NK095(ce)001:3499: sangs rgyas nyid la mi rtog rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:3500: sems can rang rtogs bag chags bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:3501: rang byung sems de mi gnyis gcig /gcig phyir dus gsum sangs rgyas dang //
NK095(ce)001:3502: 'dus tshogs khyed sems dbyer med pas //
NK095(ce)001:3503: sems nyid rdzogs pa chen po ni //
NK095(ce)001:3504: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mdo zhes bya //
NK095(ce)001:3506: gsum pa ji ltar snang yang rtsa ba chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:3507: las gzhan ma yin par bstan pa la gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:3508: thams cad sems kyi rang bzhin du bstan pa dang
NK095(ce)001:3509: / sems las gzhan pa'i chos su ma gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3511: gong du bshad pa de ltar chos rnams kun gyi
NK095(ce)001:3512: rtsa ba kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:3513: 'di nyid yin pa'i phyir na snang srid snod bcud
NK095(ce)001:3514: la sogs pa ji ltar snang ba thams cad kun
NK095(ce)001:3515: byed nga yi ngo bo snang ba yin la chos
NK095(ce)001:3516: nyid skye med kyi dbyings las rtsal snang 'gag med
NK095(ce)001:3517: kyi rol pa ji ltar byung ba thams cad ston
NK095(ce)001:3518: pa kun byed nga yi cho 'phrul lam sprul pa
NK095(ce)001:3519: yin pa dang / de bzhin du zin pa dang
NK095(ce)001:3520: ma zin pa'i sgra tshig ji ltar byung zhing grag
NK095(ce)001:3521: par snang ba thams cad kun ston pa nga yi
NK095(ce)001:3522: byang chub sems kyi don brjod du med pa'i klong
NK095(ce)001:3523: nas chos nyid kyi rang sgra brjod byed kyi tshig
NK095(ce)001:3524: dang yi ge'i sgrar byung ba yin /
NK095(ce)001:3525: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku
NK095(ce)001:3526: dang ye shes la sogs pa'i yon tan rnams dang
NK095(ce)001:3527: / sems can rnams kyi gnas don lus kyi rnam
NK095(ce)001:3528: pa mngon sum du snang ba de dang mngon du
NK095(ce)001:3529: ma smin pa bag chags kyi tshul du yod pa
NK095(ce)001:3530: la sogs pa snang srid snod bcud kyis bsdus pa
NK095(ce)001:3531: thams cad kun byed byang chub kyi semsa kun byed
NK095(ce)001:3532: rgyal po nyid kyi ngo bo ye nas de ltar
NK095(ce)001:3533: gnas pa yin par gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3535: des na ji ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad rang
NK095(ce)001:3536: gi sems las byung zhing sems nyid kyi ngo bor
NK095(ce)001:3537: ma gtogs pa yi chos gzhan rnams ni gcig kyang
NK095(ce)001:3538: yod do zhes ston pa nga nyid las byung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:3539: sangs rgyas sngar 'das pa rnams la kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:3540: po nga yis lung ma bstan la /
NK095(ce)001:3541: da ltar dngos su bzhugs pa dang slad kyis 'byon
NK095(ce)001:3542: pa yi sangs rgyas rnams la yang kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:3543: po byang chub sems kyi lung mi ston no zhes
NK095(ce)001:3545: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las rtsa
NK095(ce)001:3546: ba gcig pa'i le'u ste drug pa'i 'grel ba'o ////bzhi
NK095(ce)001:3547: pa chos thams cad gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3548: rang sems ston par mngon du phyung ba'i le'u bdun
NK095(ce)001:3550: le'u'i don mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3553: de ltar chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3554: sems su gcig par bstan pa de nas byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3555: kyi sems kun byed rgyal pos nyid kyis byas pa
NK095(ce)001:3556: yi rgyu las byung ba'i snang srid 'khor 'das kyi
NK095(ce)001:3557: chos rnams so sor rnam par dbye ba 'di gsungs
NK095(ce)001:3558: so // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:3559: chos nyid dmigs su med pa las chos can snang
NK095(ce)001:3560: ba'i rang bzhin bkod pa'i tshul gsungs pa bstod cing
NK095(ce)001:3561: dri ba'i tshul gyis 'khor 'das kyi rang bzhin zhu
NK095(ce)001:3562: ba / de'i lan rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3564: kye sems dpa' chen po zhes pos nas /
NK095(ce)001:3565: 'di ltar chos thams cad kyi chos nyid rig pa
NK095(ce)001:3566: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni spang blang bcos
NK095(ce)001:3567: bsgyur thams cad dang bral ba chos nyid ye ji
NK095(ce)001:3568: bzhin pa yi ngo bo ste de lta bu'i gshis
NK095(ce)001:3569: lugs 'gyur ba med pa chos nyid ji bzhin pa
NK095(ce)001:3570: gnyis chos su grub pa med pa'i rang gnas phyal
NK095(ce)001:3571: ba'i ye shes mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po
NK095(ce)001:3572: la 'khor 'das kyi rol pa cir yang mi 'gag
NK095(ce)001:3573: pas snang ba'i rnam pa kun gyi mchog dang ldan
NK095(ce)001:3574: pa yin mod / 'on kyang de ltar du snang
NK095(ce)001:3575: ba'i dus nyid nas gzung 'dzin gyi mtshan mar snang
NK095(ce)001:3576: ba'i rnam pa kun yongs kyis te ye nas med
NK095(ce)001:3577: pa spros bral nam mkha'a bzhin du rang byung 'dus
NK095(ce)001:3578: ma byas pa skye med bsam yul dang bral bar
NK095(ce)001:3579: ye nas gnas pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:3581: dper na nam mkha'i gzugs gcig la //
NK095(ce)001:3582: chu nang gzugs brnyan bsam mi khyab //
NK095(ce)001:3583: de bzhin rig pa gcig pa la //
NK095(ce)001:3584: rigs pa'i rtsal shugs bsam mi khyab //
NK095(ce)001:3585: dper na chu nang zla ba yang //
NK095(ce)001:3586: snang yang de la rang bzhin med //
NK095(ce)001:3587: de bzhin rig pa'i rtsal snang ba //
NK095(ce)001:3588: snang yang de la rang bzhin med //
NK095(ce)001:3590: des na chos nyid thig le nyag gcig tu gnas
NK095(ce)001:3591: pa de la mtshan 'dzin gyi dmigs pa'i yul las
NK095(ce)001:3592: 'das pa'i phyir na gcig ces brjod pa la sogs
NK095(ce)001:3593: pa'i grangs kyis bsgrangs zhing tha dad du dbye ba
NK095(ce)001:3594: byar med mod / 'on kyang byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:3595: kyi rang gi ngo bo la bsgrangs zhing mtshon du
NK095(ce)001:3596: med pa de lta na'ang sems kyis byas pa'i snang
NK095(ce)001:3597: ba snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams la dbye
NK095(ce)001:3598: ba'i rnam grangs mang du byung ba yin no //
NK095(ce)001:3599: de yang sems kyis byas pa yi chos de gang
NK095(ce)001:3600: dang gang yin zhe na 'di ltar snang zhing srid
NK095(ce)001:3601: pa'i dngos po snod bcud du snang ba rnams dang
NK095(ce)001:3602: / de bzhin du dag pa sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK095(ce)001:3603: sku dang ye shes dang ma dag sems can rnams
NK095(ce)001:3604: kyi gnas lus longs spyod sogs su snang ba 'di
NK095(ce)001:3605: thams cad la byed po gzhan gang yang med par
NK095(ce)001:3606: sems kyi rang bzhin gdod nas skye ba med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3607: rang mdangs ngo bo 'gags pa med pa'i gdangs rtsal
NK095(ce)001:3608: de las byas shing chos can snang ba'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3609: sna tshogs su bkod pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:3610: des na sems kyis byas nas kun la mngon du
NK095(ce)001:3611: phyung ste bstan pa ni snang ba snod kyi 'jig
NK095(ce)001:3612: rten 'byung ba chen po lnga dang /
NK095(ce)001:3613: srid pa bcud kyi sems can 'groo ba rigsa drug tu snang ba rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:3614: gdul bya'i sems can de yi don mdzad pa'i sangs
NK095(ce)001:3615: rgyas longs sku dang sprul sku ste gzugs sku rnam
NK095(ce)001:3616: pa gnyis su snang ba thams cad ni gzhan du
NK095(ce)001:3617: ci yang med par rig pa byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:3618: rang bzhin skye ba med pa las rtsal snang 'gag
NK095(ce)001:3619: med kyi ngo bor mngon sum dag tu phyung nas
NK095(ce)001:3620: grangs su bgrangs ba'i rnam par bstan pa yin par
NK095(ce)001:3621: shes par bya'o // zhes bka' rtsal to //
NK095(ce)001:3623: de ltar chos can gyi ngo bo ji ltar bkod
NK095(ce)001:3624: tshul bstan pa de nas sems dpa' rdo rjes rnam
NK095(ce)001:3625: par bsgrangs pa'i mdo'i don zhus pa /
NK095(ce)001:3626: kye byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po yi
NK095(ce)001:3627: ngo bo cir yang ma grub pa rang bzhin skye
NK095(ce)001:3628: med kyi gdangs las rol pa 'gag med kyi rnam
NK095(ce)001:3629: pa 'khor 'das kyi chos kun mngon du byung zhing
NK095(ce)001:3630: snang ba la ngo mtshar bas e ma ho zhes
NK095(ce)001:3631: pa dang / de ltar snang ba'i dus nyid nas
NK095(ce)001:3632: ma dag mtshan ma'i chos su grub pa rdul tsam
NK095(ce)001:3633: yang med par kun tu bzang po dag pa nyag
NK095(ce)001:3634: gcig gi rol par shar ba la ngo mtshar bas
NK095(ce)001:3635: e ma ho zhes pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3636: de lta bu'i chos rnams kyi snang gzhir gyur pa
NK095(ce)001:3637: kun byed byang chub kyi sems khyod kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3638: de yod ni gcig kyang grub pa med pa ye
NK095(ce)001:3639: nas rnam par dag pa yin pa la snang ni
NK095(ce)001:3640: 'khor 'das kyi chos sna tshogs su snang zhing mnyam
NK095(ce)001:3641: rdzogs lhun grub chen por gnas pa de e ma
NK095(ce)001:3642: ho zhes ngo mtshar ba'i tshig gis mdun bsus te
NK095(ce)001:3643: / dang por 'khor 'das gang yang ma byung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:3644: thog mar gzhi dbyings khyab gdal chen po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3645: kyi sems spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang nas
NK095(ce)001:3646: gzhi snang lhun grub kyi rol pa rang rtsal 'gags
NK095(ce)001:3647: med kyi rnam par langs nas mngon du snang ba
NK095(ce)001:3648: la rang dang chos rnams thams cad tha dad du
NK095(ce)001:3649: bzung bas chos nyid byang chub kyi sems gcig gi
NK095(ce)001:3650: rol rtsal yin pa rang ngo ma shes nas 'khrul
NK095(ce)001:3652: las dang skal bar ldan pas da lta kun mkhyen
NK095(ce)001:3653: rgyal ba'i dbang po ston pa kun byed khyod kyi
NK095(ce)001:3655: nyid la chos nyid zab mo'i don de ji bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3656: du zhu ba'i dmigs ni mi cha bas sam zhu
NK095(ce)001:3657: bar ma nus pa la ston pa kun mkhyen gyis
NK095(ce)001:3658: dgongs pa rang byung du bka' stsal pa snang srid
NK095(ce)001:3659: 'khor 'das kyis chos rnams thams cad mdo rtsa gcig
NK095(ce)001:3660: tu 'dus par ston pa'i phyir du ni gcig mdo
NK095(ce)001:3661: byang chub sems kyi mdo gong du bstan pa de
NK095(ce)001:3662: ltar bka' stsal pa yin na de ltar chos thams
NK095(ce)001:3663: cad byang chub kyi sems gcig yin pa la lhun
NK095(ce)001:3664: grub spyi gzhi'i ngang nas thugs rje'i rol pa so
NK095(ce)001:3665: sor snang ba gnyis su bstan pa yi rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:3666: grangs su bsgrangs pa'i don 'di ji ltar lags pa
NK095(ce)001:3667: gsung du gsol zhes zhus so //
NK095(ce)001:3668: gsum pa de'i lan rgya cher bshad pa la drug ste /
NK095(ce)001:3669: kun gyi thog mar lhun grub spyi gzhi bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:3670: de las thugs rje rig pa nyid shar bas so sor snang ba'i don nyon cig par gdams pa /
NK095(ce)001:3671: blo la ltos pa'i chos tshul dbye ba /
NK095(ce)001:3672: rgyu 'bras theg pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa thams cad
NK095(ce)001:3673: kun 'dus rdzogs pa chen por gtan la phab pa
NK095(ce)001:3674: / de nyid rtogs pa'i gang zag basngagasa pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3676: de ltar sems dpa' rdo rjes rnam par bgrangs ba'i
NK095(ce)001:3677: mdo zhus pa'i rjes de nas byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:3678: kun byed rgyal pos ji ltar zhus pa'i don de
NK095(ce)001:3680: kye chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs rang byung 'dus
NK095(ce)001:3681: ma byas pa'i ye shes kun byed byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:3682: sems nga ni sems can kun gyi rgyud la ye
NK095(ce)001:3683: nas 'du 'bral med par lhun gyis grub pa yin
NK095(ce)001:3684: kyang rang snang rang ngo ma shes pa'i dbang gis
NK095(ce)001:3685: mngon du mi snang bar bag chags 'khrul pa'i sbubs
NK095(ce)001:3687: rang byung bde ba'i 'khor lo las /
NK095(ce)001:3688: da yang rdo rje sems dpa' nyon //
NK095(ce)001:3689: sems can lus kyi tshor ba la //
NK095(ce)001:3690: rang rig ye shes rgyun mi 'chad //
NK095(ce)001:3692: de phyir nyon mongs sbubs nang na //
NK095(ce)001:3693: kun bzang ye shes sems la gnas //
NK095(ce)001:3694: nges don lung bstan don rtogs nas //
NK095(ce)001:3695: de don gzhan nas bsgrub mi dgos //
NK095(ce)001:3696: sems can byang chub su 'dod pa //
NK095(ce)001:3697: kun gzhi'i gseb nas dol tshol la //
NK095(ce)001:3698: de yi ngang la gnas par gyis //
NK095(ce)001:3699: de don rgyal ba'i dgongs pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:3700: bde gshegs rnams kyi snying po yang //
NK095(ce)001:3701: sems can lus la yod mod kyang //
NK095(ce)001:3702: shes pa ma mthong tsam du bas //
NK095(ce)001:3703: de mthong nges pa'i gdams ngag la //
NK095(ce)001:3704: shes pa rtag tu 'bral ba med //
NK095(ce)001:3705: da yang 'dus pa'i snying po nyon //
NK095(ce)001:3706: ma rig 'khrul pa yong bzhin du //
NK095(ce)001:3707: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thugs la gnas //
NK095(ce)001:3708: de phyir gzhan nas 'byung ba med //
NK095(ce)001:3709: thog ma ma yin dus 'dir rang //
NK095(ce)001:3710: de yang rang rig ye shes ni //
NK095(ce)001:3711: til la mar gyis khyab pa bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:3712: 'gro drug kun la rang rig khyab //
NK095(ce)001:3713: skye 'gag med par rgyun du gnas //
NK095(ce)001:3716: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ngas //
NK095(ce)001:3717: sangs rgyas sems can thams cad la //
NK095(ce)001:3718: til la mar gyis khyab bzhin gnas //
NK095(ce)001:3719: thams cad byams pa'i sems kyis nyid //
NK095(ce)001:3720: rgyu rkyen med pa'i snying po ste //
NK095(ce)001:3722: de lta bu'i gzhi gnas chos sku'i rig pa de
NK095(ce)001:3723: mngon du gyur pa las gzhan pa'i sangs rgyas zhig
NK095(ce)001:3724: med pas na kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:3725: sems nga ni dus gsum du gshegs shing byon pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3726: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs rig pa rang byung
NK095(ce)001:3727: gi ye shes ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i snying
NK095(ce)001:3728: po'ang yin te / de nyid las /
NK095(ce)001:3729: sangs rgyas sems can mes po nga //
NK095(ce)001:3730: nga ni rang byung ye shes te //
NK095(ce)001:3731: nga ni chos kun snying po yin //
NK095(ce)001:3732: nga ni kun gnas rtsa ba bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:3733: snying po rang byung ye shes ngas //
NK095(ce)001:3734: snang ba dang ni srid pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3735: snod dang bcud kyis bsdus pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:3736: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK095(ce)001:3737: khams gsum rgyud drug sems can dang //
NK095(ce)001:3738: de bzhin du ni thams cad la //
NK095(ce)001:3739: ma lus kun khyab 'ub chub bo //
NK095(ce)001:3742: rang rgyud rig pa'i ye shes ni //
NK095(ce)001:3743: sprin med mkha' la nyi shar bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:3744: 'dus ma byas pa'i klong dkyil na //
NK095(ce)001:3745: rang rig ye shes chos sku bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:3748: de lta bu'i snying po rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:3749: nga ni thugs rje'i rtsal gdangs 'gag pa med pa
NK095(ce)001:3750: 'od gsal lhun grub kyi snang cha thams cad kyi
NK095(ce)001:3751: 'char gzhi'i ngo bo spros bral dbyings kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3752: gdod nas skye ba med pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:3753: de las gdul bya'i 'gro ba rnams la 'dul byed
NK095(ce)001:3754: kyi thabs theg pa'i rnam grangs gang la 'gro ba
NK095(ce)001:3755: gang zhig dga' zhing spro ba'i dus su ni rang
NK095(ce)001:3756: snang phyogs lhung dang bral ba 'dzin med spro bsdu
NK095(ce)001:3757: bral ba'i ngang las gdul bya gang zhig theg pa
NK095(ce)001:3758: gang la dga' ba yi don bya'i ste don bsgrub
NK095(ce)001:3759: par bya ba'i phyir du kun byed nga yi rol
NK095(ce)001:3760: rtsal du theg pa'i rnam grangs so sor byung ba'am
NK095(ce)001:3761: byas pa'i don bstan par bya ba yin gyis sems
NK095(ce)001:3762: dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis tshul bzhin du nyon cig
NK095(ce)001:3763: ces gdams pa'o // gsum pa blo la ltos pa'i chos tshul dbye ba la gsum te /
NK095(ce)001:3764: shin tu spros pa med pa la chos gcig dang bzhin gyis rnam par dag par bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:3765: sna tshogs spros pa la dga' ba'i ngor theg pa du ma bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:3766: de gnyis kyi rang bzhin dbye ba tha dad du
NK095(ce)001:3767: smos kyang don la gcig tu 'du ba'i rgyu mtshan
NK095(ce)001:3769: de la gang zag dbang po yang rab shin tu
NK095(ce)001:3770: spros pa med pa chos sku thig le nyag gcig
NK095(ce)001:3771: gi don la dga' ba'i rnal 'byor pa de la
NK095(ce)001:3772: ni snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams thams cad
NK095(ce)001:3773: spros bral stong gsal rang byung gi ye shes gcig
NK095(ce)001:3774: tu 'dus pa'i phyir na rig pa byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:3775: kyi ngo bo gcig pu bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:3776: de yang sems kyi ngo bo chos kyi dbyings rang
NK095(ce)001:3777: bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba rnam dag byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:3778: kyi rang bzhin de la kun byed rgyal po zhes
NK095(ce)001:3779: pa'i ming gis mtshon te bstan pa bzhin du rtogs
NK095(ce)001:3780: pas rtsol sgrub gzhan la rag ma lus par grol
NK095(ce)001:3781: bar 'gyur te / rig pa rang shar las /
NK095(ce)001:3782: rig pa'i chos nyid dbye ba na //
NK095(ce)001:3783: gcig la thams cad rdzogs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3784: nyon mongs stong phrag brgyad cu yang //
NK095(ce)001:3785: gcig ma shes pas byung ba ste //
NK095(ce)001:3786: gcig shes pas ni grol bar 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:3789: de las gzhan pa mtshan ma grangs kyi chos sna
NK095(ce)001:3790: tshogs la dga' ba yi gdul bya rnams la ni
NK095(ce)001:3791: ston pa kun byed rgyal pos byas pa'am rtsal gyi
NK095(ce)001:3792: cho 'phrul du shar ba yi theg pa sna tshogs
NK095(ce)001:3793: brjod kyis mi lang bar bstan pa de yang kun
NK095(ce)001:3794: byed nga yi rang bzhin las lhun grub rtsal gyi
NK095(ce)001:3795: rol pa 'gags med sna tshogs su bstan pa yin
NK095(ce)001:3797: 'on kyang de ltar gdul bya'i blo la ltos nas
NK095(ce)001:3798: spros bcas dang spros med kyi dbye ba tha dad
NK095(ce)001:3799: du bstan kyang don la de ltar tha dad du
NK095(ce)001:3800: grub pa med de 'di ltar shin tu spros pa
NK095(ce)001:3801: med pa'i chos gcig tu bstan pa ni kun byed
NK095(ce)001:3802: nga nyid ces ngos bzung gi tshig gis bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:3803: ste / de lta bu'i tshig gis brjod par bya
NK095(ce)001:3804: ba'i yul de gang zhe na chos thams cad kyi
NK095(ce)001:3805: snying po byang chub kyi sems sam rig pa rang
NK095(ce)001:3806: byung gi ye shes ma bcos ji bzhin pa ste
NK095(ce)001:3807: ste / / de'i rtsal 'gags pa med pa las
NK095(ce)001:3808: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis su byung ba ni
NK095(ce)001:3809: ston pa kun byed nga yis gdul bya'i blo dang
NK095(ce)001:3812: sems can blo 'di ma zad pas //
NK095(ce)001:3813: theg pa zad pa med par gsungs //
NK095(ce)001:3814: nyon mongs brgyad khri bzhi stong gi //
NK095(ce)001:3815: gnyen por chos sgo de snyed gsungs //
NK095(ce)001:3817: des na nga yi byas pa'i chos la theg pa'i dbye ba tha dad du bgrangs ba yina la /
NK095(ce)001:3818: de ltar grangs kyis bsgrangs pa'i don ni gcig dang
NK095(ce)001:3819: gnyis zhes dbye ba tha dad du smras pa yin
NK095(ce)001:3820: kyang dngos po'i gshis la gnyis chos kyi dbye ba
NK095(ce)001:3821: gang yang med pas grangs kyi mtha' ni chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:3822: spros pa dang bral ba blos bsam gyis mi khyab
NK095(ce)001:3823: cing ngag gis brjod du med pa la thug pa
NK095(ce)001:3824: yin zhing de lta bu'i smra bsam brjod du med
NK095(ce)001:3825: pa yi rang bzhin de ni chos rnams kyi snying
NK095(ce)001:3826: po'am gshis lugs ji bzhin pa yin pas gnas skabs
NK095(ce)001:3827: su gdul bya'i blo la ltos nas dbye ba tha
NK095(ce)001:3828: dad du bstan pa de dag kun kyang mthar thug
NK095(ce)001:3829: gi don la chos nyid brjod du med pa snying
NK095(ce)001:3830: po rang byung gi ye shes gcig tu 'du zhing
NK095(ce)001:3831: theg pa'i dbye ba tha dad du med par bstan
NK095(ce)001:3833: blo med 'khrul chos sangs pa na //
NK095(ce)001:3834: theg pa med cing 'jug pa med //
NK095(ce)001:3836: bzhi pa rgyu 'bras theg pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:3837: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa bden gnyis su dbye bas mdor bstan /
NK095(ce)001:3838: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa rgyur bzhag pa'i tshul dang /
NK095(ce)001:3839: sngags kyi theg pa 'bras bur bzhag tshul rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3841: 'di ltar chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin nam ngo
NK095(ce)001:3842: bo gcig tu bstan pa ni kun byed byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3843: kyi sems yin la des byas pa'i chos ni rnam
NK095(ce)001:3844: pa gnyis su dbye bas rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg
NK095(ce)001:3845: pa dang 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa ste rnam
NK095(ce)001:3846: pa gnyis su yod pa las gnas lugs don dam
NK095(ce)001:3847: pa'i bden pa rgyu 'bras gnyis med du ston pa
NK095(ce)001:3848: gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3849: snang tshul kun rdzob kyi bden pa rgyu 'bras blang
NK095(ce)001:3850: dor can du ston pa mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg
NK095(ce)001:3851: pa ste de ltar rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis
NK095(ce)001:3852: po bden pa rnam pa gnyis kyis zhes gnyis kyi
NK095(ce)001:3853: sgo nas dbye bar bya zhing 'chad 'gyur ltar so
NK095(ce)001:3854: so'i dpe don dang mthun par rtags dang gtan tshigs
NK095(ce)001:3855: kyis yongs su brtags te nges pa'i lung rdo rje'i
NK095(ce)001:3856: theg pa dang / drang ba'i lung mtshan nyid theg pa gnyis su dbye bar bshad do //
NK095(ce)001:3858: rgyu snga ma las 'bras bu phyis grub pa'i rgyu mtshan dgod pa /
NK095(ce)001:3859: de nyid drang ba'i don du bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:3862: dper na rgyu ni 'byung ba chen po sa chu
NK095(ce)001:3863: sogs rnam pa lnga la 'bras bu khams gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:3864: sems can rnams grub cing snang ba yin pa'i rgyu
NK095(ce)001:3865: mtshan de lta bus phyir na don khams gsum kyi
NK095(ce)001:3866: sems can rnams rgyu ru byas nas lam nyams su
NK095(ce)001:3867: blang bas 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang 'thob
NK095(ce)001:3868: po zhes ming btags te rgyu 'bras kyi dpe don
NK095(ce)001:3869: gnyis po de lta bu ru gtan tshigs kyis brtags
NK095(ce)001:3870: te bstan pa ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'o
NK095(ce)001:3872: de ltar rgyu ni khams gsum gyi sems can rnams
NK095(ce)001:3873: kyis lam tshogs gnyis la rim par slob pa'i sgo
NK095(ce)001:3874: nas skal pa grangs med mang po'i mthar 'bras bu
NK095(ce)001:3875: sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang de gdod 'grub par lung
NK095(ce)001:3876: bstan pa de lta bu ni gdul bya rnams rim
NK095(ce)001:3877: gyis drang ba'i ched du bstan pa dgongs pa can
NK095(ce)001:3878: gyi lung du bshad pa yin te gzhi 'bras dbyer
NK095(ce)001:3879: med du ston par byed pa'i nges don zab mo'i
NK095(ce)001:3885: de la rgyu 'bras rnam pa gnyis su dbye bar
NK095(ce)001:3886: bya ba la rgyu ni 'byung ba chen po rnam
NK095(ce)001:3888: rgyu des byas pa'i chos snang srid snod bcud sna
NK095(ce)001:3889: tshogs su ni snang ba 'di thams cad ni don
NK095(ce)001:3890: la sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes 'gyur ba
NK095(ce)001:3891: med pa'i rtsal mngon du phyung ba yin kyang sems
NK095(ce)001:3892: can rnams kyi rang ngo ma shes pa'i dbang gis
NK095(ce)001:3893: rigs drug gi snang ba sna tshogs su shar ba
NK095(ce)001:3894: la mtshan nyid theg pa bas dngos po rang mtshan
NK095(ce)001:3895: par bltas nas rgyu 'bras blang dor la brtson par
NK095(ce)001:3897: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:3898: gshis ma rig pas 'jig rten du grub pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3899: de nyid 'khrul bas sdug bsngal du grub pas 'khor ba spang byar bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3900: mya ngan las 'das pa blang byar bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3901: theg pa de'i nges tshig brjod pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3903: de ltar snod bcud sna tshogs su snang ba de
NK095(ce)001:3904: dag thams cad gnas lugs de bzhin nyid kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:3905: bzhin du ma gtogs pa'i gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i chos
NK095(ce)001:3906: su grub pa gang yang med kyang sems can rnams
NK095(ce)001:3907: kyis de ltar du ma rtogs par rgyu lhan gcig
NK095(ce)001:3908: skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3909: skyen kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa gnyis kyi
NK095(ce)001:3910: dbang gis yang dag pa'i don la phyin ci log
NK095(ce)001:3911: tu rtog pa'i gzung 'dzina gyis gzugs sgra la sogs
NK095(ce)001:3912: pa'i yul drug gi chos la nges par brtags zhing
NK095(ce)001:3913: zhen pa mthu bltas pas rigs drug gi gnas snod
NK095(ce)001:3914: mi brtan par 'jig pa drug dang de la brten
NK095(ce)001:3915: cing gnas pa yi bcud 'gro ba drug gi gnas
NK095(ce)001:3916: lus sna tshogs su snang ba la snod dang bcud
NK095(ce)001:3917: kyi 'jig rten du grub pa zhes su bshad pa
NK095(ce)001:3919: de ltar gzugs sogs yul drug po la zhen cing
NK095(ce)001:3920: chags pa drug la brten nas nyon mongs pa ser
NK095(ce)001:3921: sna la sogs pa skam chagsa drug skye zhing de
NK095(ce)001:3922: dag gi sgo nas las sna tshogs bsags pa'i dbang
NK095(ce)001:3923: gis rigs drug gi sdug bsngal 'jigs su rung zhing
NK095(ce)001:3924: ya nga ba myong ba la mya ngan mya ngan
NK095(ce)001:3925: zhes su btags shing de nyid spang bya'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:3926: du bshad do // gsum pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:3927: de lta bu'i rigs drug gi sdug bsngal zab cing
NK095(ce)001:3928: rgya che la yun ring ba'i mya ngan gyis gdung
NK095(ce)001:3929: ba'i steng du sdug bsngal phyi ma phyi mas gtses
NK095(ce)001:3930: shing mya ngan chen pos gdung ba las 'das shing
NK095(ce)001:3931: thar ba mngon du thob pa zhes bya ba ni
NK095(ce)001:3932: yul drug gi chos la zhen cing chags pa'i sems
NK095(ce)001:3933: kyi mi rtog cing las nyon bag chags dang bcas
NK095(ce)001:3934: pa zad pas skye gnas rnam pa bzhis bsdus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3935: rigs drug 'khor ba' gnas su mi skye ste rgyu
NK095(ce)001:3937: des na rigs drug gi sdug bsngal drug po de
NK095(ce)001:3938: las 'das pa'i phyir na mya ngan las 'das pa
NK095(ce)001:3939: zhes bya ba ni de la bya zhing brjod pa
NK095(ce)001:3941: de la mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa zhes brjod
NK095(ce)001:3942: pa'i nges tshig ni dbyings spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:3943: gnas lugs ji bzhin pa snying po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:3944: sems las rgyu rkyen rtsol ba'i sgo nas ma btsal
NK095(ce)001:3945: bar rang bzhin du shar ba yi rgyu 'byung ba
NK095(ce)001:3946: chen po lnga po yanga rang rang gi mtshan nyid
NK095(ce)001:3947: me'i rang bzhin tsha zhing bsregs pa la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:3948: rang rang gis 'dzin pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:3949: de lta bu'i rgyu 'byung ba dang bcas pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:3950: thams cad gang las 'byung ba'i snying po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:3951: kyi sems kyis kyang rang gi mtshan nyid spros pa
NK095(ce)001:3952: thams cad dang bral bas dmigs su med pa'i ngo
NK095(ce)001:3953: bo 'dzin pa de la mtshan nyid mtshan nyid ces
NK095(ce)001:3955: de yang bskyed byed kyi rgyu gzhan la ma ltos
NK095(ce)001:3956: par byang chub sems kyi rtsal las rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:3957: shar ba'i 'byung ba chen po lngas snang srid kyi
NK095(ce)001:3958: chos kun bskyed pa'i phyir na snying po yin par
NK095(ce)001:3959: bshad pa ste / snying po de yis bskyed pa'i
NK095(ce)001:3960: 'bras bu khams gsum gyi sems can rnams kyang don
NK095(ce)001:3961: la rgyu las ma byung ba'i rang byung ye shes
NK095(ce)001:3963: de ltar yin par ma shes pa'am mi rtog par
NK095(ce)001:3964: rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub la spyod pa'i lam de la
NK095(ce)001:3965: rgyur bltas nas rgyu de nyams su blang ba las
NK095(ce)001:3966: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:3967: 'byung bar 'doda pas rgyu zhes ming du btags pa
NK095(ce)001:3968: yin zhing / de ltar rgyu la rtsol bas 'bras
NK095(ce)001:3969: bu byang chub gsum po gang zhig thob par byed
NK095(ce)001:3970: pa'i lam de la theg par bshad pa ste des
NK095(ce)001:3971: na mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa zhes gsungs so
NK095(ce)001:3972: yin zhing / // de lta bu'i theg pa de
NK095(ce)001:3973: la dbye na las nyon spongs bar byed pa nyan
NK095(ce)001:3974: yin zhing / // thos dang / 'gegs par byed pa rang rgyal dang /
NK095(ce)001:3975: sbyong bar byed pa byang sems kyi theg pa zhes
NK095(ce)001:3976: bya ba rnam pa gsum po de rnams su bstan
NK095(ce)001:3977: pa yin no // gsum pa sngags kyi theg pa 'bras bur bzhag pa'i tshul la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:3978: 'bras bur bzhag pa'i nges tshig dang /
NK095(ce)001:3979: rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:3981: de la sngags kyi theg pa la 'bras bu zhes
NK095(ce)001:3982: su ming gis btags pa yi nges tshig ni chos
NK095(ce)001:3983: rnams kyi snying po rang byung gi ye shes sam
NK095(ce)001:3984: byang chub kyi sems ni rgyu dang de las mthar
NK095(ce)001:3985: thug gi 'bras bur ste 'bras bu 'byung bar bshad
NK095(ce)001:3986: pa de yang don la rgyu 'bras tha dad du
NK095(ce)001:3987: med par / dper na rdzas kyi rdo rje de
NK095(ce)001:3988: nyid gang gis kyang gzhom gzhig mi nus pa ltar
NK095(ce)001:3989: don chos nyid snying po'i rang bzhin stong gsal spros
NK095(ce)001:3990: mtha' dang bral ba de la ni 'dus byas kyi
NK095(ce)001:3991: rgyu rkyen la brten nas dang por skye ba dang
NK095(ce)001:3992: tha ma 'jig pa med pa'i rang bzhin yin pas
NK095(ce)001:3993: stong chen 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes 'bras bu'i
NK095(ce)001:3994: ngo bor gnas pa de la rdo rje zhes btags
NK095(ce)001:3995: pa de nyid lam du byed pa'i phyir na 'bras
NK095(ce)001:3996: bu rdo rje'i theg pa zhes su bshad pa yin
NK095(ce)001:3997: med par / no // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:3998: phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa gnyis spyir bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:3999: nang pa sngags kyi theg pa bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4001: gong du bshad pa'i mtshon bya don gyi rdo rje
NK095(ce)001:4002: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de nyid mngon
NK095(ce)001:4003: du sgrub par byed pa'i theg pa de la yang
NK095(ce)001:4004: phyi nang gnyis su yod pa las /
NK095(ce)001:4005: dang po thub pa chags bral gyi rnam pas dngos
NK095(ce)001:4006: su gsungs pa phyi mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang
NK095(ce)001:4007: tshul mthun par phyi'i spyod pa gtso bor ston pas
NK095(ce)001:4008: phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa zhes grags pa
NK095(ce)001:4009: kri ya dang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud gnyis kyis rang
NK095(ce)001:4010: gi sgo gsum lha'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo
NK095(ce)001:4011: rje gsum gyi bdag nyid ye shes kyi ngo bor
NK095(ce)001:4012: ni bsgrub pa'i phyir du lta spyod blang dor la
NK095(ce)001:4013: brtson par byas pa'i sgo nas ni 'bras bu mthar
NK095(ce)001:4014: thug lha sku snang yang rang bzhin med pa chu
NK095(ce)001:4015: zla bzhin du grub par 'dod pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4016: 'dir phyi rgyud gnyis su bstan pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:4018: u pa ya la lta ba gzhung tshugs med //
NK095(ce)001:4019: ces gsungs pa ltar u pa ya'i spyod pa kri ya dang /
NK095(ce)001:4020: lta ba yo ga las gzhan du med pa'i phyir na 'dir kri yog gnyis su gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:4021: gnyis pa nang ba la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:4022: bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi rang bzhin brjod pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4023: a ti gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4024: de la theg pa 'og ma drangs pa'i phan yon bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4025: dang po ni 'di ltar snang tshul la 'khor ba'i
NK095(ce)001:4026: chos phung khams skye mched du snang ba'i dngos po
NK095(ce)001:4027: 'dir thams cad gnas tshul la ye nas dag pa
NK095(ce)001:4028: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po'i rang bzhin yin par
NK095(ce)001:4029: shes pa'i lta ba dang ldan pas chos gang la'ang
NK095(ce)001:4030: blang dor med par 'jug nus pa'i nang pa bla
NK095(ce)001:4031: na med pa'i theg pa las bskyed pa ma h+aa
NK095(ce)001:4032: yo ga bas ni chos sku de bzhin nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:4034: longs sku kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK095(ce)001:4035: sprul sku rgyu yi ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa
NK095(ce)001:4036: gsum la brten nas snod bcud lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK095(ce)001:4038: a nu yo gas lha'i snying po'am rtsa sngags brjod
NK095(ce)001:4039: pa tsam la brten pa yis bdag nyid lha'i dkyil
NK095(ce)001:4040: 'khor du bsgom par byed pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:4041: de yang yul chos kyi dbyings stong pa nyid rgyu
NK095(ce)001:4042: dang yul can rang byung gi ye shes 'bras bu
NK095(ce)001:4043: gnyis ye nas dbyer med pa bde chen byang chub
NK095(ce)001:4044: sems kyi dkyil 'khor du blta zhing bsgom par byed
NK095(ce)001:4046: a ti yo gas blang dor dang bskyed rdzogs la
NK095(ce)001:4047: sogs pa'i thabs tshul gang la'ang mi brten par gnyis
NK095(ce)001:4048: su med pa'i rang bzhin sems nyid rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:4049: ye shes ma bcos rnal du 'jog pa las bya
NK095(ce)001:4050: byed gang la yang ltos pa med pa 'di ni
NK095(ce)001:4051: chos kun gyi snying por gyur pa yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:4052: re dogs rtsol sgrub la sogs pa'i bya ba gang
NK095(ce)001:4053: yang med par ma bcos lhun grub kyi ngang du
NK095(ce)001:4054: 'jogs pa yin pa'i phyir na mdzad spyod kyi 'phrin
NK095(ce)001:4055: las bsgrub pa kun las 'das pa'i byar med blo
NK095(ce)001:4056: 'das chen po'i rang bzhin du brtan pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:4057: // gsum pa a ti yo ga la theg pa 'og ma drangs pa'i phan yon la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:4061: gong du bstan pa de lta bu'i spang blang gi
NK095(ce)001:4062: bya ba gang yang med pa nges gsang a ti
NK095(ce)001:4063: yo ga'i lam gyi rtsol med rang babs kyi bde
NK095(ce)001:4064: ba de nyid blang dor rtsol sgrub la zhen pas
NK095(ce)001:4065: spong bar byed pa'i theg pa 'og ma pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:4066: la re dogs kyi bya ba gang la yang mi
NK095(ce)001:4067: rtsol bar byar med bde ba'i ngang la gnas par
NK095(ce)001:4068: byed pa'i lung theg mchog rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs
NK095(ce)001:4069: don 'di mngon du bstan nas lhun grub gdod ma'i
NK095(ce)001:4073: de yang mtshan nyid theg pa'i lam nas bskal pa
NK095(ce)001:4074: grangs med gsum dang phyi rgyud pas mi tshe bdun
NK095(ce)001:4075: sogs dang nang rgyud gnyis kyis lam nas dbang po
NK095(ce)001:4076: rab kyi zla ba drug dang 'bring gis lo gcig
NK095(ce)001:4077: dang zla ba bzhi tha mas zla ba bcu drug
NK095(ce)001:4078: gi yun la rtsol bar byed pa'i rtsol bcas kyi
NK095(ce)001:4079: theg pa can rnams la byar med rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:4080: po'i gnas lugs ma bcos pa'i ngo bo sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:4081: rang byung gi ye shes 'di bstan par byas pas
NK095(ce)001:4082: / 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad gdod nas
NK095(ce)001:4083: ye grol chen po'i ngo bor sangs rgyas zin pa
NK095(ce)001:4084: la blang dor rtsol sgrub kyis bcos su med par
NK095(ce)001:4085: rtogs nas mi rtsol lhun gyis grub pa'i bde ba
NK095(ce)001:4086: la gnas par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa'am phan yon yod
NK095(ce)001:4087: / par gsungs pa'o // lnga pa thams cad kun
NK095(ce)001:4088: 'dus rdzogs pa chen por gtan la phab pa ni
NK095(ce)001:4089: / par gsungs pa'o // / de lta bu'i theg
NK095(ce)001:4090: pa kun gyi yang rtse chos nyid rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:4091: po gnas lugs rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'di
NK095(ce)001:4092: yi klong la 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:4093: thams cad ma rdzogs pa gang yanga med pas rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:4094: pa chen po zhes gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:4096: rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:4097: sangs rgyas rdzogs la sems can rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:4099: bde dang sdug bsngal gnyis med rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:4100: theg pa rdzogs la chos nyid rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:4101: yod pa'i mtha' rdzogs med mtha' rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:4102: gcig rdzogs kun rdzogs thams cad rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:4103: ces gsungs pa ltar gcig rdzogs chos thams cad rig
NK095(ce)001:4104: pa'i ngang du tha dad med par rdzogs pa dang
NK095(ce)001:4105: / gnyis rdzogs sems kyis byas pa 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ba thams cad rdzogs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4106: kun rdzogs phun sum tshogs pa'i chos thams cad ma
NK095(ce)001:4107: rdzogs pa med pas na theg pa 'og ma'i lam
NK095(ce)001:4108: nas 'bad rtsol gyis bsgrubs pa'i lam 'bras kyis yon
NK095(ce)001:4109: tan thams cad bya byed kyi rtsol ba gang la
NK095(ce)001:4110: yang ma ltos par da lta nyid nas snying po
NK095(ce)001:4111: rig pa'i klong du phun sum tshogs par rdzogs pas
NK095(ce)001:4112: rtsol med bde ba chen po'i ngang du gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:4113: ste / de yang snang srid 'khor 'das su snang
NK095(ce)001:4114: ba'i chos dag pa dang ma dag pa'i rnam par
NK095(ce)001:4115: shar ba thams cad don la rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:4116: shes gcig gi ngang du rdzogs pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:4117: ci'i phyir na chos de dag thams cad byung yang
NK095(ce)001:4118: rig pa byang chub sems kyi rtsal las byung ba
NK095(ce)001:4119: dang gnas kyang byang chub sems kyi ngang du gnas
NK095(ce)001:4120: pa dang grol yang byang chub sems kyi ngang la
NK095(ce)001:4121: grol zhing de las 'da' ba med pas na snying
NK095(ce)001:4122: po byang chub kyi sems su rdzogs pa yin la
NK095(ce)001:4123: / gnyis rdzogs sems kyi byas pa ni 'jig rten
NK095(ce)001:4124: pa 'khor ba'i chos su snang ba snang srid snod
NK095(ce)001:4125: bcud phung khams skye mched kyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams
NK095(ce)001:4126: / dang / 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos theg pa'i rnam grangs dang /
NK095(ce)001:4127: de dag gi brjod bya gzhi lam 'bras bu'i bsdus
NK095(ce)001:4128: so cog thams cad gzhan du ci yang med par
NK095(ce)001:4129: sems kyis byas shing sems la snang ba sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:4130: bag chags las byung ba yin kyang don la rig
NK095(ce)001:4131: pa byang chub sems kyi klong na med snang stong
NK095(ce)001:4132: gzugs kyi rol pa tsam las yod ma myong pas
NK095(ce)001:4133: des ngang du rdzogsa pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4134: kun rdzogs pa ni rgyal ba sku gsum gyis bsdus
NK095(ce)001:4135: pa'i ston pa la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa
NK095(ce)001:4136: thams cad ye nas rig pa'i rang bzhin stong pa
NK095(ce)001:4137: chos sku gsal ba longs sku thugs rje 'gags pa
NK095(ce)001:4138: med pa sprul pa'i sku ste sku gsum du gnas
NK095(ce)001:4139: pa'i rang rtsal 'gags pa med par shar zhing de'i
NK095(ce)001:4140: ngang la rdzogs pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:4141: des na spros pa med pa'i gang zag chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:4142: nyag gcig gi don la dga' ba'i dbang po yang
NK095(ce)001:4143: rab rnams la rang byung gi ye shes gcig gi
NK095(ce)001:4144: ngang la chos thams cad kun yongs su 'dus shing
NK095(ce)001:4145: rdzogsa pa'i lung byar med lhun gyis grub pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:4146: 'di bstan pa yis rtsol sgrub kyi gdung ba med
NK095(ce)001:4147: par sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mthar thug pa 'di
NK095(ce)001:4148: la da lta nyid nas gnas pa'i dgos pa yod
NK095(ce)001:4149: la / kun rdzogs pa yi lung theg pa'i rnam
NK095(ce)001:4150: grangs sna tshogs pa yi don 'di theg pa thun
NK095(ce)001:4151: mong pa'i rigs can rnams la bstan pa yis 'gro
NK095(ce)001:4152: ba thams cad a ti yo ga la rim gyis
NK095(ce)001:4153: dkri ba'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i don thams cad phun
NK095(ce)001:4156: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mdo 'di ni /
NK095(ce)001:4157: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK095(ce)001:4158: sngar grub dgongs pa 'di yis grub //
NK095(ce)001:4159: da ltar bzhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK095(ce)001:4160: mi yengs dgongs lam 'di la gnas //
NK095(ce)001:4162: dgongs pa'i lung bstan 'di yis mdzad //
NK095(ce)001:4164: drug pa de rtogs pa'i gang zag la basngagasa pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:4165: de lta bu'i chos nyid rdzogs pa chen po blang
NK095(ce)001:4166: dor bya rtsol med pa'i don 'di la gang zag
NK095(ce)001:4167: gang zhig gnas pa yi rnal 'byor pa de yi
NK095(ce)001:4168: lus 'di gang zag lha dang mi yi rig sa
NK095(ce)001:4169: gang du gtogs pa de nyid du snang ba yin
NK095(ce)001:4170: yang rung thugs sam dgongs pa ni chos nyid 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:4171: ba med pa rig pa byang chub sems kyi gnas
NK095(ce)001:4172: lugs mngon du gyur pa'i sangs rgyas dngos yin pas
NK095(ce)001:4173: gang zag dam pa 'di yis gdul bya sems can
NK095(ce)001:4174: rnams kyis don mdzad par byas na gdul bya de
NK095(ce)001:4175: dag rtsol bcas theg pa'i lam gyis gdung ba dang
NK095(ce)001:4176: bral nas blang dor rtsol sgrub mi byed par rtsol
NK095(ce)001:4177: med bde ba chen po 'bras bu ye shes bla
NK095(ce)001:4178: ma'i sa la da lta nyid nas gnas par 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:4181: gang su 'di la gnas pa yi //
NK095(ce)001:4182: de ni rnal 'byor chen po yin //
NK095(ce)001:4183: lus ni gang zag 'jig rten yang //
NK095(ce)001:4184: sems dgongs rdzogs chen sangs rgyas yin //
NK095(ce)001:4185: 'di yis sems can don byas kyang //
NK095(ce)001:4186: don la nor ba nges mi 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:4187: yin pa dag la nor ba med //
NK095(ce)001:4188: nges pa dag la the tshom med //
NK095(ce)001:4189: rdzogs pa chen po'i lung 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:4190: yod med tshig dang ma nges pa'i //
NK095(ce)001:4191: don la 'da' ba mi mnga' bas //
NK095(ce)001:4192: brjod pa'i tshig las 'da' mi mnga' //zhes gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:4194: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las rnam
NK095(ce)001:4195: grangs bsdus pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'i 'grel ba'o ////lnga
NK095(ce)001:4196: pa sems nyid las gzhan pa'i sangs rgyas logs su
NK095(ce)001:4197: ma grub pa'i gtan tshig don gyi le'u brgyad pa
NK095(ce)001:4198: la gnyis te / mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4201: de ltar byang chub sems las mngon du phyung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:4202: chos rnam par dbye ba bstan pa de nas byang
NK095(ce)001:4203: chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal pos byas pa'i 'khor
NK095(ce)001:4204: 'das kyi chos thams cad chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:4205: du gcig pa las de bzhin nyid la ston 'khor
NK095(ce)001:4206: bstan pa yi rang bzhin gsum du snang bar 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:4207: ba yi 'char gzhi'i rang bzhin ngo bo thugs rje
NK095(ce)001:4208: gsum du yod pa las phun sum tshogs pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:4209: po de so sora dngos su snang ba yi tshul
NK095(ce)001:4211: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:4212: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes las chos thams cad bkod pa'i tshul dang /
NK095(ce)001:4213: rnal 'byor bzhi'i dbye ba snang tshul /
NK095(ce)001:4214: rnal 'byor gong 'og gi khyad par bstan tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:4216: sku gsum du bkod pa'i tshul /
NK095(ce)001:4217: des bstan pa rgyu 'bras so sor dbye ba /
NK095(ce)001:4218: de dag kyang dbyings de bzhin nyid du bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:4219: de bzhin nyid kyi dbye ba /
NK095(ce)001:4220: ngo bo gcig gi rang bzhin las rnal 'byor bzhi ji ltar snang tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:4222: sems nyid de bzhin nyid phun sum tshogs par ye nas bkod tshul /
NK095(ce)001:4223: sku gsum rnam par dbye ba /
NK095(ce)001:4224: thugs rje rang byung gi ye shes 'khor 'das gnyis su snang tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:4226: kye sems dpa' chen po ston pa kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:4227: yi sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:4228: de bzhina nyid las ni ston 'khor bstan pa ste
NK095(ce)001:4229: phuna sum tshogs pa gsum du snang ba yin te
NK095(ce)001:4230: / de la snying po byang chub sems kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:4231: bzhin de nyid gdod nas ji ltar gnas pa de
NK095(ce)001:4232: bzhin tu ma skyes ma 'gags pa chos nyid 'dus
NK095(ce)001:4233: ma byas pa'i rang bzhina du gnas pa la ni
NK095(ce)001:4234: chos nyid de bzhin nyid du brjod pa yin la
NK095(ce)001:4235: de nyid rtogs bya'i yul du snang ba'i cha nas
NK095(ce)001:4236: bstan pa phun sum tshogs par bzhag pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:4237: de lta bu'i yu la de 'khor 'das kun gyi
NK095(ce)001:4238: gnas lugs sam chos nyid de bzhina nyid kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:4239: bzhin spros bral blo las 'das pa yin pas de'i
NK095(ce)001:4240: ngo bo ji bzhin pa ni gzhan gyis tshig dang
NK095(ce)001:4241: yi ges mtshon te bstan du med pa'i phyir na
NK095(ce)001:4242: / ma nor nges pa'i slob dpon rig pa rang
NK095(ce)001:4243: byung gi ye shes kyis rang gi rang la ngo
NK095(ce)001:4244: bo de bstan pas rtogs pa yin par gsungs te
NK095(ce)001:4246: dus gsum ston pa gang gis kyang //
NK095(ce)001:4247: bstan pa'i rang bzhin 'di yin zhes //
NK095(ce)001:4248: tshig dang yi ges brjod pa med //
NK095(ce)001:4249: ma gsungs mi gsung gsung mi 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:4250: khyed kyi rang bzhin bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4251: ye shes thugs kyi rig pa yis //
NK095(ce)001:4252: rang gi rang bzhin ngo bstan te //
NK095(ce)001:4253: de mthong bstan pas de 'dus pas //
NK095(ce)001:4254: de la de bstan de yang mthong //
NK095(ce)001:4255: de ni bstan pa zhes su bshad //
NK095(ce)001:4258: de lta bu'i bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:4259: bzhin byang chub kyi sems de bzhin nyid du gnas
NK095(ce)001:4260: pa de la rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa ba kun
NK095(ce)001:4261: kyang brtags par byas nas yul chos kyi dbyings de
NK095(ce)001:4262: bzhin nyid de la lta bar byed pa la /
NK095(ce)001:4263: de nyid ston pa po'am rtogs byed kyi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:4264: mtha' thug pa sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:4265: las dang nyon mongs la sogs pa gang gis kyang
NK095(ce)001:4266: ma bsgribs pa'i rang byung gi ye shes nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:4267: rtsal las ni rgyu 'bras kyi ston pa sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:4269: rang rig ye shes rig pa'i rgyal //
NK095(ce)001:4270: rang bzhin rnam pa gsum snang ste //
NK095(ce)001:4271: mi gnas sems kyi rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:4272: rang byung ye shes rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:4273: thugs rje sprul pa'i rang bzhin no //
