NK095(ce)001:4274: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:4275: mi gnas chos kyi sku ru bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:4276: rang byung ye shes rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:4277: rdzogs pa'i longs spyod sku ru bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:4278: thugs rje sprul pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:4279: rnam pa cir yang sprul te bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:4281: de yang ji ltar snang ba'i tshul ni la la
NK095(ce)001:4282: ste so so'i skye bo las dag pa ba rnams
NK095(ce)001:4283: la mtshan nyid rgyu yi chos ston pa sprul sku'i
NK095(ce)001:4285: gdul bya la la ste sa thob kyi 'phags pa
NK095(ce)001:4286: rnams la gzhi 'bras dbyer med dam rgyu 'bras 'brel
NK095(ce)001:4287: ba'i chos kyi ston pa longs sku'i rnam par snang
NK095(ce)001:4288: ba dang / sa thob kyi sems dpa' la la
NK095(ce)001:4289: zhes rgyun mtha' ba rnams dang khyad par sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:4290: rang snang gi 'khor rnams la sems nyid ye nas
NK095(ce)001:4291: sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin 'bras bu'i ngo bor ston
NK095(ce)001:4292: pa chos sku'i rnam par snang ba yin te /
NK095(ce)001:4294: mi gnas chos skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:4295: 'khor yang byang chub sems su bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:4296: byang chub sems kyi 'khor rnams la //
NK095(ce)001:4297: spros pa med pa'i don yang ston //
NK095(ce)001:4298: longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:4300: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK095(ce)001:4301: sku dang ye shes rdzogs par ston //
NK095(ce)001:4302: sna tshogs sprul skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:4304: rgyud drug sems can 'khor rnams la //
NK095(ce)001:4305: yid bzhin dbang po gang 'thad ston //
NK095(ce)001:4308: de bzhin nyid rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:4309: de yi thugs rje yi rol rtsal 'gags pa med
NK095(ce)001:4310: pa'i cha mngon du phyung ba yi stong gsal 'gags
NK095(ce)001:4311: pa med pa'i rang byung gi ye shes rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:4312: lnga las byung ba'i rigs lngas bsdus pa'i sangsa rgyas
NK095(ce)001:4313: rnams dang rgyud lngas bsdus pa'i sems can rnams ni
NK095(ce)001:4314: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa rnams bstan pa'i yul dang
NK095(ce)001:4315: / sku gsum gyi ston pa'i 'khor du snang ba yin te /
NK095(ce)001:4317: ston pa chos kyi sku 'khor ni //
NK095(ce)001:4318: dus gsum sangs rgyas bzhugs pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:4319: khams gsum rgyud drug sems can de //
NK095(ce)001:4320: 'phags pa'i thugs rje'i sems can la //
NK095(ce)001:4321: 'brel ba phun sum tshogs par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:4322: ston pa longs spyod sku'i 'khor ni //
NK095(ce)001:4323: mi rtog ting 'dzin bcu sbyangs pa'i //
NK095(ce)001:4324: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sa //
NK095(ce)001:4325: nyon mongs mi gnas shes bya sbyang //
NK095(ce)001:4326: ye shes tshogs dang thugs rje 'brel //
NK095(ce)001:4327: des na phun sum tshogs ces bya //
NK095(ce)001:4328: ston pa sprul ba'i sku 'khor ni //
NK095(ce)001:4329: sku sprul thugs rje drug snang bas //
NK095(ce)001:4330: 'khor yang rgyud drug sems can no //
NK095(ce)001:4331: las dang thugs rje 'brel ba ni //
NK095(ce)001:4332: 'khor ni phun sum tshogs ces bya //
NK095(ce)001:4335: gong du bshad pa de lta bu yi 'khor gyi
NK095(ce)001:4336: tshogs rnams la rgyu dang 'bras bu'i chos rnams gsal
NK095(ce)001:4337: bar mdzad pa'i ston pa sku gsum gyis chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:4338: de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo yul gcig gi rang
NK095(ce)001:4339: bzhin la 'khor gyi gdul bya rnams kyi khams dbang
NK095(ce)001:4340: gis lta ba mtho dman so sor mi 'dra bas
NK095(ce)001:4341: de dag rjes su 'dzin phyir gdul bya la la
NK095(ce)001:4342: nyan thos kyi rigs can rnams kun 'byung las nyon
NK095(ce)001:4343: gyi cha rnams spong bar bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4344: rang sangs rgyas kyi rigs can rnams la las dang
NK095(ce)001:4345: nyon mongs thams cad rten 'brel lug ldog gi tshul
NK095(ce)001:4346: gyis 'gegs par byed pa'i yul du bstan pa dang
NK095(ce)001:4347: / gdul bya la lara ste byang chub sems dpa'i
NK095(ce)001:4348: rigs can rnams la ma dag kun rdzob kyi snang
NK095(ce)001:4349: ba 'khrul ba'i cha thams cad chos dbyings skye ba
NK095(ce)001:4350: med pa'i ngang du sbyong zhing dag pa'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:4351: lam rim gyis bsgrod de sangs rgyas par bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:4352: / dang / gsang sngags kyi rigs can la lara
NK095(ce)001:4353: ste byed rgyud kyi theg pa ba rnams la ma
NK095(ce)001:4354: dag sgo gsum gyi cha thams cad dag pa lha'i
NK095(ce)001:4355: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlabs pas dag pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4356: ngo bor sgrub par bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4357: la lara ste rnal 'byor gyi theg pa ba rnams
NK095(ce)001:4358: la lta spyod yang dag pa blang zhing de'i mi
NK095(ce)001:4359: mthun phyogs thams cad dor bar bya ba'i lam gyis
NK095(ce)001:4360: 'bras bu grub pa bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4361: la lara ste gsang sngags bla med kyi snod du
NK095(ce)001:4362: gyur pa rnams la rang rgyud gdod nas dag pa
NK095(ce)001:4363: lha'i rang bzhin du gnas pa nyid lam bskyed rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:4364: zab mos mngon du bsgrub par bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:4365: mdor na lam de dag kun kyang rgyu lam la
NK095(ce)001:4366: brtsal zhing 'bras bu bsgrub tu yod par bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:4367: yin pas rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i theg
NK095(ce)001:4368: pa las gzhan du gyur pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:4370: de ltar kun byed byang chub kyis sems las mngon
NK095(ce)001:4371: du phyung ba'i ston pa sku gsum gyi rgyu mtshan
NK095(ce)001:4372: nyid kyi theg pa dang 'bras bu sngags kyi rigs
NK095(ce)001:4373: can rnams la dgongsa nas de dag gi blo dang
NK095(ce)001:4374: 'tshams par rgyu 'bras kyi chos rnams so sor bstan
NK095(ce)001:4375: na yang don la rgyu dang 'bras bu rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:4376: gnyis ka nyid kyang gang las snang ba'i gzhi chos
NK095(ce)001:4377: nyid de bzhin nyid las g.yos pa rdul tsam yang
NK095(ce)001:4378: med par ston pa kun byed nga yi lung bstan
NK095(ce)001:4381: de lta bu'i phun sum tshogs pa kun gyi rang
NK095(ce)001:4382: bzhin chos nyid de bzhin nyid de rang gi ngo
NK095(ce)001:4383: bo ni spros pa thams cad dang bral zhing dmigs
NK095(ce)001:4384: pa'i yul las 'das pas dbye ba med na yang
NK095(ce)001:4386: chos kyi dbyings la dbyer med pas //
NK095(ce)001:4387: rigs ni tha dad rung ma yin //
NK095(ce)001:4388: brten pa'i chos kyi bye brag gis //
NK095(ce)001:4389: de yi dbye ba yongs su bya //
NK095(ce)001:4391: tshul mthun par chos can snang ba'i ngos nas dbye
NK095(ce)001:4392: na 'di lta ste rgyal ba sku gsum gyi ston
NK095(ce)001:4393: par snang ba chos sku kun byed rgyal po nga
NK095(ce)001:4394: yang chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin rig
NK095(ce)001:4395: pa byang chub kyi sems sku gsum 'du 'bral med
NK095(ce)001:4397: ngas byas 'khor 'das kyi chos kun kyang dbyings spros
NK095(ce)001:4398: pa dang bral ba de bzhin nyid kyi ngang las
NK095(ce)001:4399: rtsal snang 'gag pa med pa stong gzugs sgyu ma'i
NK095(ce)001:4400: cho 'phrul du shar ba tsam yin pas de las
NK095(ce)001:4402: de la kun byed nyid kyis byas pa'i chos de
NK095(ce)001:4403: so sor dbye na gang dang gang yin zhe na
NK095(ce)001:4404: / phyi yul gyi rnam par snang ba gzugs sgra
NK095(ce)001:4405: la sogs pa drug po rnams kyang kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:4406: yis byas pa yin no zhes 'di dag thams cad
NK095(ce)001:4407: kun byed byang chub sems kyi rtsal las rol bar
NK095(ce)001:4408: shar ba tsam yin pas de ltar gsungs pa'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:4409: 'di 'og ma rnams la yang 'dre bar byas nas
NK095(ce)001:4410: / / de bzhin du mig la sogs pa'i dbang
NK095(ce)001:4411: po drug tu snang ba 'di ni nga yi rang
NK095(ce)001:4412: snang ma 'gag par chos rnams sgrib med mngon sum
NK095(ce)001:4413: du rig cing shes pa yi ngo bo yin pa
NK095(ce)001:4414: / / dang / mig gi rnam para shes pa
NK095(ce)001:4415: sogs rnam par shes pa'i tshogs rnams ni kun byed
NK095(ce)001:4416: nga yi rang byung gi ye shes kyi bdag nyid
NK095(ce)001:4418: chen po lnga yang snod bcud kun gyi brten pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4419: gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rgyu ru gyur pa'i phyir snod
NK095(ce)001:4420: bcud thams cad 'di lnga yi rang bzhin las ma
NK095(ce)001:4421: 'das pa ste de ltar snod bcud kun gyi rgyu
NK095(ce)001:4422: 'byung ba lnga yin na yang 'byung ba de dag
NK095(ce)001:4423: kyang byang chub kyi sems de bzhin nyid las gzhan
NK095(ce)001:4425: thugs rje 'gag pa med pa rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:4426: shes lnga yi rtsal las khams gsum rgyud drug gi
NK095(ce)001:4427: sems can rnams byung ba yang de bzhin nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:4428: ngo bor bshad pa ma gtogs gzhan du rdul tsam
NK095(ce)001:4429: yang med de / klong chen las /
NK095(ce)001:4430: klong chen gcig po kun yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:4431: thams cad kun gyi dngos gzhir shar //
NK095(ce)001:4432: phyogs 'dzin gang yang ma spangs pas //
NK095(ce)001:4433: phyogs med kun tu shar ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:4434: zang thal yin pas kun tu shar //
NK095(ce)001:4435: mu mtha' med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:4438: 'o na chos thams cad chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:4439: gcig gi rang bzhin las med na de la rnal
NK095(ce)001:4440: 'byor rnam pa bzhi yis so so'i rtogs tshul mi
NK095(ce)001:4441: 'dra ba tha dad pa rnams ji ltar byung snyam
NK095(ce)001:4442: na / de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings
NK095(ce)001:4443: spros pa dang bral ba nyid de ngo bo gnyis
NK095(ce)001:4444: su grub pa med pa nyid ni dmigs mtshan blo
NK095(ce)001:4445: yi spyod yul kun las 'das pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:4446: des na rnam pa'i dbye ba tha dad kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:4447: su grub pa gang yang med par rang gi rang
NK095(ce)001:4448: bzhin ni chos nyid rang byung ye shes gcig tu
NK095(ce)001:4449: gnas pa yin kyang de la rnal 'byor gyi lam
NK095(ce)001:4450: rnam par bzhag pa bzhi phyung ba ni rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:4451: rnam pa bzhi yi rigs can gyi gdul bya rnams
NK095(ce)001:4452: kyi bsam pa'i dbang las de ltar byung ba yin
NK095(ce)001:4453: no // gnyis pa rnal 'byor bzhi'i dbye ba la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:4454: rnal 'byor bzhi sems nyid gcig la dbye ba /
NK095(ce)001:4455: dbye ba bzhi'i rang bzhin nges par bya ba /
NK095(ce)001:4456: de don dbye ba bzhi bzhis rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4458: kye sems dpa' chen po rnal 'byor rnam pa bzhi
NK095(ce)001:4459: yi dbye ba la nyon cig de la chos thams
NK095(ce)001:4460: cad kun gyi 'byung gnas snying po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:4461: sems ye ji bzhin par gnas pa 'di ni chos
NK095(ce)001:4462: rnams kun gyi chos nyid de bzhin nyid ma bcos
NK095(ce)001:4463: rnal ma'i ngo bo ste gnas lugs ji bzhin pa
NK095(ce)001:4464: yin la / de nyid sangs rgyas sgam pos bzang
NK095(ce)001:4465: du ma bcos sems can bsgrim pos ngan du ma
NK095(ce)001:4466: bcos par rang gi ngo bo ji lta ba de
NK095(ce)001:4467: bzhin nyid du ye nas gnas pa yin kyang /
NK095(ce)001:4468: gdul bya gang zag rnams kyi blo'i rtsal 'phang mi
NK095(ce)001:4469: 'dra ba'i dbang gis shin tu rnal 'byor a ti
NK095(ce)001:4470: yo ga dang yongs su rnal 'byor a nu yo
NK095(ce)001:4471: ga dang rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga
NK095(ce)001:4472: dang sems dpa'i rnal 'byor phyi rgyud sde gsum ste
NK095(ce)001:4473: / de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa rnam pa bzhis
NK095(ce)001:4474: chos kun gyi snying po don gyi gnas tshul rnal
NK095(ce)001:4475: ma bya bral lhun rdzogs chen po spros pa med
NK095(ce)001:4476: pa'i dbyings la bltas shing brtags pas mthong tshul mi
NK095(ce)001:4477: 'dra ba'i yul ni rnam pa bzhi ru byung ba
NK095(ce)001:4478: / yin no // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:4479: yo ga ma h+aa a nu gsum gyis rnal ma'i don mi rtogs par bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4480: a ti sa ma bcos rnal du 'byor ba'i ngo bor bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4482: de la sems dpa'i rnal 'byor sngags phyi pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:4483: gyis ni chos nyid don dam pa'i gnas lugs la
NK095(ce)001:4484: phyi nang snod bcud kyi snang ba 'di thams cad
NK095(ce)001:4485: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i byin rlabs las snang
NK095(ce)001:4486: ba yin pas rigs gsum lha'i ngo bo'am 'og min
NK095(ce)001:4487: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du lta ba yin
NK095(ce)001:4489: yo ga'i theg par gnas 'dod pas //
NK095(ce)001:4490: 'og min rdo rje dbyings su lta //
NK095(ce)001:4491: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'dod pa yin mod /
NK095(ce)001:4492: 'on kyang snang tshul 'khrul ba'i ngos nas phyi yul
NK095(ce)001:4493: dang nang dbang por 'brel ba'i gzung 'dzin ma dag
NK095(ce)001:4494: pa'i chos su mthong nas mngon par byang chub pa
NK095(ce)001:4495: lnga dang cho 'phrul rnam pa bzhis snod bcud thams
NK095(ce)001:4496: cad dag pa lha'i sku gsung thugs su bsgoms zhing
NK095(ce)001:4497: byin gyis brlabs nas bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i ngo
NK095(ce)001:4498: bor gnas pa dang lha ye shes pa gnyis bzang
NK095(ce)001:4499: ngan can du lta bar byed pa des ni snying
NK095(ce)001:4500: po don gyi gnas lugs rnal ma bzang ngan blang
NK095(ce)001:4501: dor med pa'i tshul mthong ba med pas /
NK095(ce)001:4502: de 'dre'i bzang ngan blang dor du lta ba de
NK095(ce)001:4503: bor la gnas lugs ma bcos pa chos nyid de
NK095(ce)001:4504: bzhin nyid kyi ngang du sems dpa' yi rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:4505: rnams kyis zhog cig ces gdams so //
NK095(ce)001:4506: yang don gyi snying po rnal ma bya rtsol med
NK095(ce)001:4507: pa la rnal 'a byor chen po ma h+aa yo
NK095(ce)001:4508: ga ba rnams kyis mthong ba ni ye nas rang
NK095(ce)001:4509: rgyud dag pa'i ngo bo gdan gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK095(ce)001:4511: de nyid mngon du byed pa'i thabs su rgyu ting
NK095(ce)001:4512: nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum las 'bras bu lha yi
NK095(ce)001:4513: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bsgoms par byas te bsgrub pa
NK095(ce)001:4514: la bsnyen pa dang nye bsnyen sgrub pa dang sgrub
NK095(ce)001:4515: chen bzhi yi yan lag rdzogs par byas nas 'od
NK095(ce)001:4516: zer 'phro 'du sogs kyis bdag nyid ye nas gzhi
NK095(ce)001:4517: rgyud rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du
NK095(ce)001:4518: bzhugs pa nyid mngon du 'grub par lta ba des
NK095(ce)001:4519: kyang chos nyid don gyi snying po rnal ma rtsol
NK095(ce)001:4520: sgrub las 'das pa'i don ni mthong ba med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4521: phyir na / ma bcosa de bzhina nyid kyi ngang
NK095(ce)001:4522: du rnal 'byor chen po yi dgongs pa de nyid
NK095(ce)001:4523: zhog cig /de bzhin du gnas lugs don gyi snying
NK095(ce)001:4524: po ma bcos de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin rnal
NK095(ce)001:4525: ma rgyu 'bras bya rtsol med pa nyid la yongs
NK095(ce)001:4526: su rnal 'byor a nu yo ga ba rnams kyis
NK095(ce)001:4527: phyir na / mthong ba ni / dbyings skye med
NK095(ce)001:4528: spros pa dang bral ba kun tu bzang mo ye
NK095(ce)001:4529: ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor ni gnas lugs snying po
NK095(ce)001:4530: ma bcos pa'i rnal ma ngo bo rtogs bya'i yul
NK095(ce)001:4532: des snang cha ye shes chen po kun tu bzang
NK095(ce)001:4533: po rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ni
NK095(ce)001:4534: yul ji bzhin pa rtogs pa'i rnal ma'i 'bras bur
NK095(ce)001:4535: mthong ba ste de ltar snying po rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:4536: ye shes de bzhin nyid gcig la rgyu 'bras gnyis
NK095(ce)001:4537: su mthong ba la a nu yo ga bas kyang
NK095(ce)001:4538: rgyu 'bras gnyis las 'das pa'i chos nyid rnal ma
NK095(ce)001:4539: ma bcos pa'i don ni mthong ba med pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:4540: na / rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das pa ma
NK095(ce)001:4541: bcos de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du yongs su rnal
NK095(ce)001:4542: 'byora pa rnams kyis zhog cig ces so //
NK095(ce)001:4544: gnas lugs don dam gyi bden pa chos rnams kun
NK095(ce)001:4545: gyi snying po rnal ma bya rtsol gyis bcos su
NK095(ce)001:4546: med pa la shin tu rnal 'byor a ti yo
NK095(ce)001:4547: ga ba rnams ni rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4548: ye shes sku gsum ye nas lhun rdzogs chen po
NK095(ce)001:4549: la spang blang bcos bsgyur spu tsam mi dgos par
NK095(ce)001:4550: ye grol bsal bzhag med pa'i lta ba blo 'das
NK095(ce)001:4551: rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin du mthong ba des
NK095(ce)001:4552: byang chub kyi sems ni chos kun gyi chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:4554: snying po de nyid blang dor rtsol sgrub la sogs
NK095(ce)001:4555: pa gnyen po gang gis kyang ma bcos pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:4556: gyi gnas lugs rnal mara mthong bas na /
NK095(ce)001:4557: de nas gzhan du lta ba zhig ye nas bsgom
NK095(ce)001:4558: du med par thag chod pas lhun 'byams yangs pa
NK095(ce)001:4559: chen por rang babs su bzhag pa las gzhan pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4560: sgom bya ci yang med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4561: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don la dam tshiga
NK095(ce)001:4562: bsrung mtshams las 'das pas ye nasa bsrung du meda
NK095(ce)001:4564: thams cad ye nas rang byung ye shes chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:4565: ngo bor sangs rgyas pa la bya byed kyi rtsol
NK095(ce)001:4566: ba mi mnga' bas phrin las ye nas btsal du
NK095(ce)001:4567: med par shes pas ma bcos rang babs su bzhag
NK095(ce)001:4568: pas mtshon rang bzhin bcu po kun la rtsol zhing
NK095(ce)001:4569: bsgrub tu med par rtogs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:4570: de ltar sgom sgrub spang blang gi rtsol ba spu
NK095(ce)001:4571: tsam med par rang babs rang gnas su bzhag pas
NK095(ce)001:4572: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi gnas lugs la ji
NK095(ce)001:4573: lta ba bzhin du rnal du 'byor ba yin pas
NK095(ce)001:4574: 'di ni rnal 'byor kun gyi nang nas rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:4575: gyi dbang phyug chen po bla na med pa ste
NK095(ce)001:4577: rnal 'byor chen po bsgom las 'das par rtogs //
NK095(ce)001:4578: rtogs pa'i don la bya rtsol mi mnga' bar //
NK095(ce)001:4579: rang gdangs chen po'i ngang la gnas pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:4580: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po bya rtsol 'das pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:4582: gsum pa de don dbye ba bzhi bzhis rgya cher bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:4585: yongs su rnal 'byor shin tu rnal 'byor gyi don rnal 'byor bzhi ldan du rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4587: de la rnal 'byor rnam pa bzhi po'i lta ba'i
NK095(ce)001:4588: bye brag so sor dbye ba ni yul sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:4589: rang byung gi ye shes de bzhin nyid gcig yin
NK095(ce)001:4590: pa la blo rnal du 'byor tshul gyi sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:4591: rnam pa bzhi yod pa de re re la yanga
NK095(ce)001:4592: nang gses su bzhi bzhir dbye ba yi tshul ni
NK095(ce)001:4593: 'di ltar / dang po sems dpa'i rnal 'byor la
NK095(ce)001:4594: nang gi bye brag tu rnal 'byor rnam pa bzhir
NK095(ce)001:4595: 'di ltar / dbye ba ni / phyi yul dang
NK095(ce)001:4596: nang dbang po sogs chos thams cad stong nyid spros
NK095(ce)001:4597: pa dang bral ba don dam mtshan ma med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4598: rang bzhin du gtan la phabs nas chos nyid rnam
NK095(ce)001:4599: par mi rtog pa'i don la gcig tu sems par
NK095(ce)001:4600: byed pa'i rgyu mtshan nges na sems dpa'i rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:4601: nyid du bshad pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:4602: de lta bu'i don dam mtshan ma med pa'i snang
NK095(ce)001:4603: cha kun rdzob kyi snang ba thams cad mngon par
NK095(ce)001:4604: byang chub pa lnga yi sgo nas 'og min rdo
NK095(ce)001:4605: rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du bsgoms pa la gnas
NK095(ce)001:4606: gsum byin gyis brlabs pa dang ting 'dzin byin rlabs
NK095(ce)001:4607: dbang bskur mchod pa ste cho 'phrul bzhi mngon du
NK095(ce)001:4608: 'byin cing bsgom pa rnams ni bskyed pa'i char gyur
NK095(ce)001:4609: pa yin pas de yi cha nas ni rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:4610: chen po zhes su bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4611: sku gsung thugs phrin las te phyag rgya chen po
NK095(ce)001:4612: bzhi dang ldan pas sgo gsum bya ba dang bcas
NK095(ce)001:4613: pa lha'i sku gsung thugs phrin las dang bcas par
NK095(ce)001:4614: yongs su bsgyur bar byed pa la ni yongsa su
NK095(ce)001:4615: rnal 'byor zhes su bshad pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:4616: mthar ril 'dzin dang rjes gzhig gang rung gi lha
NK095(ce)001:4617: ye shes pa dang bdag dam tshig pa gnyis ka
NK095(ce)001:4618: rang bzhin med pa mi dmigs spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:4619: ba'i lta ba yi ngang la 'jog pa ni shin
NK095(ce)001:4620: tu rnal 'byor gyi dgongs pa yin par sems dpa'
NK095(ce)001:4622: de lta bu'i sems dpa'i rnal 'byor ba de nyid
NK095(ce)001:4623: 'khor 'das dang gtsang rme la sogs pa'i blang dor
NK095(ce)001:4624: gnyis su lta ba yin pas na blang dor med
NK095(ce)001:4625: pa'i rnal 'byor chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i don de
NK095(ce)001:4628: de bzhin du rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo
NK095(ce)001:4629: ga la nang gses kyi bye brag bzhir dbye ba
NK095(ce)001:4631: dang por stong chen de bzhin nyid dang kun snang
NK095(ce)001:4632: snying rje chen po dang rgyu yi yi ge bsgom
NK095(ce)001:4633: pa ste ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum gyi don la
NK095(ce)001:4634: sems par byed pa la ni sems dpa'i rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:4635: zhes su bshad pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:4636: rang rgyud kyi phung khams gshegs pa gshegs ma /
NK095(ce)001:4637: dbang yul sems dpa' sems ma /
NK095(ce)001:4638: yan lag khro bo khro mo'i rang bzhin du dag
NK095(ce)001:4639: pasa ye shes kyi lha'i ngo bo ra lta bar
NK095(ce)001:4640: byed pa yi cha nas rnal 'byor chen po zhes
NK095(ce)001:4642: de nas bsnyen sgrub rnam pa bzhi yi yan lag
NK095(ce)001:4643: yongas su rdzogsa par byed pa ni yongsa su rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:4644: pa'i rnal 'byor zhes su bashada pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:4645: chos thamsa cada bdag nyid chen por gtan la 'beb
NK095(ce)001:4646: pa'i gtan tshigs lta bu'i rang byung ye shes gcig
NK095(ce)001:4647: gi rang bzhin du lta ba la ni shin tu
NK095(ce)001:4648: rnal 'byor zhes su bshad pa yin mod /
NK095(ce)001:4649: 'on kyang gnas tshul la de ltar 'dod pa las
NK095(ce)001:4650: snang tshul la ma dag dri ma'i cha tshogs brgyad
NK095(ce)001:4651: yul dang bcas pa sbyangs byar bltas te /
NK095(ce)001:4652: de nyid sbyongs pa'i rtsol sgrub la gnas pas rgyu
NK095(ce)001:4653: 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i chos nyid rnal ma
NK095(ce)001:4654: ji bzhin du mthong ba min no //
NK095(ce)001:4656: yongs su rnal 'byor a nu yo ga la yang bye brag bzhir lta ba gang zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:4657: 'di ltar ma h+aa yo ga ltar du ting 'dzin
NK095(ce)001:4658: rnam gsum sogs kyi rim pas bdag nyid lha'i skur
NK095(ce)001:4659: mi bskyed para chos nyid byang chub sems kyi klong
NK095(ce)001:4660: na ranga rgyud ma dag pa rdul tsam yang med
NK095(ce)001:4661: par chos thams cad dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:4662: du dag par bzhugs pa'i tshul la semsa par byed
NK095(ce)001:4663: pa'i phyir na de tsam gyi sgo dang bstun nas
NK095(ce)001:4664: semsa dpa'i rnal 'byor zhes su bashada pa yin la
NK095(ce)001:4665: / gong du bshad pa'i ting 'dzin rnam gsum sogs
NK095(ce)001:4666: kyis dang por gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa dang
NK095(ce)001:4667: / / de nas yab yum gnyis thabs dang shes
NK095(ce)001:4668: rab mnyam par sbyor ba'i sgo nas 'khor gyi lha
NK095(ce)001:4669: tshogs bskrun pa lta bu'i rtsol ba chen po la
NK095(ce)001:4670: / / mi ltos para / lha'i snyinga po rtsa
NK095(ce)001:4671: sngags brjod pa tsam gyis dkyil 'khora yongs su rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:4673: rnal 'byor chen po'i dgongs pa dang mthun para bshad pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:4674: rtsa rlung gi byed pa sogs la brten nas ma
NK095(ce)001:4675: dag tha mal gyi snang ba thams cad gdod nas
NK095(ce)001:4676: rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid bde ba chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:4677: klong du sbyongs zhing dag pa'i rang bzhin du spyod
NK095(ce)001:4678: pas yongsa su rnal 'byor nyid du bshad pa dang
NK095(ce)001:4679: / ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun
NK095(ce)001:4680: rgyu dbyings dang 'bras bu ye shes gnyis dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:4681: pa sras bde ba chen po byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:4682: dkyil 'khor du lta ba'i phyir na shin tu rnal
NK095(ce)001:4683: 'byor zhes su bshad pa yin mod /
NK095(ce)001:4684: des kyang rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i don rnal ma
NK095(ce)001:4685: ji bzhin pa mthong ba min te rgyu 'bras gnyis
NK095(ce)001:4686: su lta ba dang bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:4688: theg pa'i yang rtse shin tu rnal 'byor a ti
NK095(ce)001:4689: yo ga la bye brag tu rnal 'byor rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:4690: bzhi ru dbye ba ni rig pa byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:4691: sems gcig la ldog chas dbye ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:4692: de yang sems pa'i rnal 'byor gyi skabs su dag
NK095(ce)001:4693: pa lha'i sku gsung thugs gsum dang ma dag tha
NK095(ce)001:4694: mal gyi sgo gsum la blang dor gnyis su lta
NK095(ce)001:4695: ba de don blang dor med pa'i gnas lugs byang
NK095(ce)001:4696: chub kyi sems gcig gi bdag nyid yin pa de
NK095(ce)001:4697: yi cha nas ni sems dpa'i rnal 'byor zhes su
NK095(ce)001:4699: rnal 'byor chen pos bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi sogs kyi
NK095(ce)001:4700: lam la rtsol sgrub byed pa de yang a ti'i
NK095(ce)001:4701: rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i byang chub sems kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:4702: bzhin du bstan pa de la ni rnal 'byor chen
NK095(ce)001:4703: po zhes su bshad pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:4704: a nus rgyu dbyings dang 'bras bu ye shes gnyis
NK095(ce)001:4705: su lta ba de yang 'dir rgyu 'bras gnyis las
NK095(ce)001:4706: 'das pa'i byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin spros bral
NK095(ce)001:4707: thig le nyag gcig tu rtogs pa de yi cha
NK095(ce)001:4708: nas ni yongs su rnal 'byor zhes su bshad pa
NK095(ce)001:4709: yin no // chos thams cad gdod nas ye grol
NK095(ce)001:4710: ka dag chen po yin min gang gi phyogs su
NK095(ce)001:4711: sgro dang skur ba 'debs pa sogs mtshan 'dzin rtogs
NK095(ce)001:4712: pa kun las 'das pa'i dbyings su la bzla ba'i
NK095(ce)001:4713: phyir na shin tu rnal 'byor zhes su kun byed
NK095(ce)001:4714: rgyal po nga yis bshad pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:4715: de lta bu'i yo ga bzhi po de dag che
NK095(ce)001:4716: ba lnga dang sbyar na che ba nyi shur dbye
NK095(ce)001:4717: bar gsungs te / de yang sangs rgyas med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4718: che ba bzhi ni yo ga bzhi yi la bzla
NK095(ce)001:4719: bar gsungs te / bzhi dang / mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba bzhi ni /
NK095(ce)001:4720: yo ga bzhi yi a ti bzhi dang /
NK095(ce)001:4721: chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba bzhi ni /
NK095(ce)001:4722: yo ga bzhi yi a nu bzhi dang /
NK095(ce)001:4723: bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che ba bzhi ni yo ga bzhi yi ma h+aa bzhi dang /
NK095(ce)001:4724: de yin par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba bzhi ni
NK095(ce)001:4725: yo ga bzhi yi yo ga bzhi ru gsungs te
NK095(ce)001:4727: sangs rgyas med pa'i che bzhi ni //
NK095(ce)001:4728: yo ga bzhi yi la bazla'o //
NK095(ce)001:4729: mngon par sangs rgyas che bzhi ni //
NK095(ce)001:4730: yo ga bzhi yi a ti bzhi //
NK095(ce)001:4731: chos dbyings sangs rgyas che bzhi ni //
NK095(ce)001:4732: yo ga bzhi yi a nu bzhi //
NK095(ce)001:4733: bdag nyid sangs rgyas che bzhi ni //
NK095(ce)001:4734: yo ga bzhi yi ma h+aa bzhi //
NK095(ce)001:4735: de yin sangs rgyas che bzhi ni //
NK095(ce)001:4736: yo ga bzhi yi yo ga bzhi'o //
NK095(ce)001:4738: de yang che ba lnga la gnas skabs 'gyur ba'i che ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:4739: mthar thug nges pa'i che ba gnyis su yod pa
NK095(ce)001:4740: las 'dir yo ga bzhi la so sor sbyar ba
NK095(ce)001:4741: ni gnas skabs 'gyur ba'i che ba dang rdzogs pa
NK095(ce)001:4742: chen po'i thun min gyi che ba lnga ni mthar
NK095(ce)001:4743: thug gi che ba yin par shes par bya ste
NK095(ce)001:4745: gnas skabs 'gyur ba'i che ba rnams //
NK095(ce)001:4746: theg pa so so'i che ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:4747: mthar thug che ba rnam pa lnga //
NK095(ce)001:4750: gsum pa rnal 'byor gong 'og gi khyad par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:4751: rnal 'byor gong ma gsum gyis sems nyid rnal ma'i don cig char du mi rtogs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4752: a tis rtogs pa'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4753: dang po ni de lta bu'i rnal 'byor rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:4754: bzhi las yongsa su rnal 'byor la sogs pa 'og
NK095(ce)001:4755: ma gsum po la ye nas 'khrul ma myong ba'i
NK095(ce)001:4756: rang byung ye shes che ba'am chena po bcos bsgyur
NK095(ce)001:4757: spu tsam mi dgos par bzhugs pa'i tshul da lta
NK095(ce)001:4758: thad kar du ngo sprod par byed pa'i man ngag
NK095(ce)001:4759: dang mi ldan pas lam lnga la rim gyis bsgrod
NK095(ce)001:4760: par byed cing 'gyur ba ma nges pa'i sa la
NK095(ce)001:4761: sogs pa so so'i gzhung nas gsungs pa'i sa rnams
NK095(ce)001:4762: la rang rang gi ngo skal gyi sgrib pa sbyong
NK095(ce)001:4764: lam gyi grogs su dam tshig gi rim pa rnams mi nyams par tshul bzhin du bsrung ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:4765: rang rang gis ji ltar gtan la phab pa'i lta
NK095(ce)001:4766: ba de'i ngang du sems gnas thabs dgu la sogs
NK095(ce)001:4767: pas sgom par byed pa yin pas na /
NK095(ce)001:4768: 'di ltar a ti yo ga'i lam gyi gom pa
NK095(ce)001:4769: drag dal zhes pa cig char gyi don yin pas
NK095(ce)001:4770: skad cig gcig gis bye brag byed pas shugs drag
NK095(ce)001:4771: cing rlabs che ba dang rtsol sgrub kyi ngal ba
NK095(ce)001:4772: med par byar med bag yongs su gnas pas dal
NK095(ce)001:4773: ba'i rang bzhin gyi lta spyod khyad par can de
NK095(ce)001:4774: 'dra ba yod pa ma yin par gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:4776: rnal 'byor 'og ma gsum gyis sems nyid rnal ma'i
NK095(ce)001:4777: don cig char du rtogs pa med pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK095(ce)001:4778: de bas na shin tu rnal 'byor a ti yo
NK095(ce)001:4779: ga'i lta spyod ni de lta bu ma yin par
NK095(ce)001:4780: chos thams cad ye nas rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:4781: kun byed byang chub kyi sems nyid kyis byas shing
NK095(ce)001:4782: de'i ngang du gdod nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:4783: yin pa'i phyir re dogs dang rtsol sgrub kyi blo
NK095(ce)001:4784: med la / de med pas lam la mi bsgrod
NK095(ce)001:4785: cing sa la sbyong bar mi byed de rdzogs pa
NK095(ce)001:4786: spyir chub kyi sa'am chos nyid dbye ba med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4787: sa la ye nas phyin zin pa'i phyir dang /
NK095(ce)001:4788: de bzhin du dam tshig mi bsrung zhing lta ba sgom par mi byed de /
NK095(ce)001:4789: cis phyir gong du smos pa ltar rang byung ye
NK095(ce)001:4790: shes byang chub chen po'i lam nas 'khor 'das lam
NK095(ce)001:4791: gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos kun 'byung zhing de nyid
NK095(ce)001:4792: kyi ngo bo las gzhan du med pa'i phyir na
NK095(ce)001:4793: byang chub kyi sems nyid kyi rang bzhin la byang
NK095(ce)001:4794: chub nyid kyis mi bgrod pa'am bgrod mi dgos te
NK095(ce)001:4795: gang du bgrod pa'i yul du gyur pa'i sa dang
NK095(ce)001:4796: bgrod par byed pa po gnyis ka byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:4797: sems nyid las gzhan du med pa'i phyir dang /
NK095(ce)001:4798: byang chub nyid kyi ngo bor gyur pa'i sa la
NK095(ce)001:4799: byang chub nyid kyis sgrib pa mi sbyong ste thams
NK095(ce)001:4800: cad byang chub kyi sems gcig gi rang bzhin yin
NK095(ce)001:4801: pa la sbyang bya sbyong byed tha dad du med
NK095(ce)001:4802: pa'i phyir dang / dam tshig gi rang bzhin yang
NK095(ce)001:4803: ye nas bsrung mtshams las 'das pa byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:4804: kyi rang bzhin nyid las yod pa ma yin pas
NK095(ce)001:4805: na byang chub nyid la byang chub nyid kyis de
NK095(ce)001:4806: yang mi bsrung ste bsrung bya bsrung byed gnyis su
NK095(ce)001:4808: bsgom par bya ba'i yul dang sgom pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:4809: yang byang chub kyi sems nyid yin gyis de las
NK095(ce)001:4810: gzhan du yod pa ma yin pas byang chub nyid
NK095(ce)001:4811: kyis byang chub nyid la bsgom du med de bsgom
NK095(ce)001:4812: bya sgom byed tha dad du med pa dang rang
NK095(ce)001:4813: gis rang nyid bsgom mi dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK095(ce)001:4814: lta ba'i yul gtan la dbab par bya ba dang
NK095(ce)001:4815: ni gtan la 'beb byed yul can gyi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:4816: gnyis ka byang chub kyi sems nyid yin zhing de
NK095(ce)001:4817: las gzhan du med pas na byang chub nyid kyis
NK095(ce)001:4818: nyid la blta bar byar med pa ste rgyu mtshan
NK095(ce)001:4819: de nyid kyi phyir na shin tu rnal 'byor a
NK095(ce)001:4820: ti yo ga'i lta spyod thams cad bya rtsol med
NK095(ce)001:4821: par ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin can
NK095(ce)001:4822: 'di ni rang byung rig pa'i ye shes ma bcos
NK095(ce)001:4823: thad kar ngo 'phrod pa'i gom pa drag dal can
NK095(ce)001:4824: de ni kun byed rgyal po nga yi gom pa'am
NK095(ce)001:4825: bsgom pa re dogs rtsol sgrub las 'das pa kho
NK095(ce)001:4826: na yin gyis rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub la zhen pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4827: theg pa can gyi gang zag rnams kyi spyod yul
NK095(ce)001:4831: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las chos
NK095(ce)001:4832: nyid kyi rang bzhin gcig las chos nyid kyi yul
NK095(ce)001:4833: kun la bkod pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'i 'grel ba'o
NK095(ce)001:4834: ////drug pa sems nyid skyon yon las 'das pas gol
NK095(ce)001:4835: sgrib gzhi nas dag pa'i le'u dgu pa la gnyis
NK095(ce)001:4839: de ltar chos nyid de bzhin nyid gcig las rang
NK095(ce)001:4840: bzhin gsum du so sor snang ba'i tshul bstan pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4841: rjes de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:4842: po des rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa 'og ma pa
NK095(ce)001:4843: rnams kyis rang rang gis bgrod par bya ba'i lam
NK095(ce)001:4844: de dag sems nyid ma bcos rnal ma'i don ji
NK095(ce)001:4845: bzhin ma rtogs par nor ba yin pas rdzogs pa
NK095(ce)001:4846: chen po'i lam lasa gol sa dang sgrib par gyur
NK095(ce)001:4847: pa las sems nyid rang gi ngo bo la gol
NK095(ce)001:4848: sgrib gzhi nas mi srid pa'i tshul 'di gsungsa so
NK095(ce)001:4849: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bdun te /
NK095(ce)001:4850: gshis sems nyid kun byed nyid sbyangs bsgrod spang gnyen
NK095(ce)001:4851: las 'das pas gol sgrib gdod nas dag pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:4852: bzhin bstan pa / de nyid ma rtogs pa'i rtsol sgrub can la gol sgrib byung tshul /
NK095(ce)001:4853: rnal ma'i don la gol sgrib med pa'i 'thad pa /
NK095(ce)001:4854: rtsol sgrub can la gol sgrib byung ba'i rgyu mtshan /
NK095(ce)001:4855: byang chub kyi sems rtsol sgrub kun las 'das tshul /
NK095(ce)001:4856: rang bzhin bcus rtsol ba'i nyes pa /
NK095(ce)001:4857: rtsol sgrub kun las 'das pa'i rang bzhin bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4859: kye sems dpa' chen po zhes bos nas 'di ltar
NK095(ce)001:4860: rig pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin skyon thams
NK095(ce)001:4861: cad ye dag dang yon tan thams cad ldan gyi
NK095(ce)001:4862: rang bzhin can 'di nyid ni 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:4863: thams cad kun gyi 'byung gnas yin pa dang thams
NK095(ce)001:4864: cad la chos nyid kyi tshul du khyab cing gnas
NK095(ce)001:4865: pas chos rnams ma lus pa yi snying po'am ngo
NK095(ce)001:4866: bo ste / de yi rang bzhin ni ye gdod
NK095(ce)001:4867: ma nyid nas ma skyes pa'i chos nyid spros bral
NK095(ce)001:4868: ka dag gi ngo bo rnam para dag pa yin
NK095(ce)001:4869: pas nyon shes kyi sgrib pa gnyis kyi dri ma
NK095(ce)001:4870: med cing blang dor rtsol sgrub thams cad las 'das
NK095(ce)001:4871: pa yin phyir da gsar du tshogs gnyis bsags pa
NK095(ce)001:4872: dang sgrib pa sbyang ba la sogs pa'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:4873: bgroda par byed pa'i sa lam thams cad dang brala
NK095(ce)001:4874: bo ste / ba yin la / de ltar sa
NK095(ce)001:4875: lam bgrod du med pa'i rgyu mtshan de bas na
NK095(ce)001:4876: de'i ldogs phyogs su gyur pa'i gol sa yang med
NK095(ce)001:4877: bo ste / ba yin la / cing / sku
NK095(ce)001:4878: bzhi ye shes lnga yi bdag nyid chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:4879: kyi 'byung gnas rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:4880: 'di ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bor lhun gyis
NK095(ce)001:4881: grub zin pas gzhan nas btsal du med par gsungs
NK095(ce)001:4882: bo ste / ba yin la / cing / so // de ltar yang gting rdzogs las /
NK095(ce)001:4883: gzhan las ma btsal rang las rnyed pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:4884: gnyen pos ma bskyed rang bzhin yin pas na //
NK095(ce)001:4885: lus ngag ched du btsal du med pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:4886: ma btsal lhun gyis grub par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:4888: gnyis pa de nyid ma rtogs pa'i rtsol sgrub can la gol sgrib byung tshul la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:4893: 'di ltar snang srid 'khor 'das kyi bsdus pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:4894: kun snying po byang chub kyi sems las logs su
NK095(ce)001:4895: grub pa rdul tsam yang med par de nyid gcig
NK095(ce)001:4897: theg pa 'og ma'i blo can gyi gang zag rnams
NK095(ce)001:4898: kyis de ltar ma shes pas byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:4899: gcig pu la dbye ba'i sgo rang bzhin bcu ru
NK095(ce)001:4900: rnam par bgrang bas chos nyid byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:4901: don las gzhan du gol zhing snying po rnal ma'i
NK095(ce)001:4902: don nyid mi mthong ba'i sgrib pa byung ba yin
NK095(ce)001:4904: rang bzhin bcu ru bgrangs ba ni //
NK095(ce)001:4905: sems kyi cha yi bye brag ste //
NK095(ce)001:4906: sems can blo la snang bas bgrangs //
NK095(ce)001:4907: sems la bgrangs bas gol sgrib byung //
NK095(ce)001:4908: bgrangs du med la gol sgrib med //
NK095(ce)001:4909: bgrangs te ma shes gol sgrib yin //
NK095(ce)001:4910: bgrangs yod mthong bas gol sgrib yin //
NK095(ce)001:4911: sems gcig byang chub snying po la //
NK095(ce)001:4912: lta ba'i khyad par dgu bgrangs nor //
NK095(ce)001:4913: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar la /
NK095(ce)001:4914: 'o na a ti yo ga rang gi skabs na
NK095(ce)001:4915: yang rang bzhin bcu ru bgrangs du med dam de
NK095(ce)001:4916: gol sgrib ji ltar yin snyam na /
NK095(ce)001:4917: 'dir a ti yo ga'i gzhung nas rang bzhin bcu
NK095(ce)001:4918: ru bgrangs ba ni snying po byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:4919: gcig la ma bcos lhun grub kyi tshul du yon
NK095(ce)001:4920: tan gyi che ba bcu ru snang ba'i tshul bstan
NK095(ce)001:4921: pa tsam las / dngos po tha dad pa bcu bgrang ba ma yin te /
NK095(ce)001:4923: rang bzhin ma bcos bcu bgrangs ba //
NK095(ce)001:4924: bgrangs pa ma yin ngo bo gcig /ngo bo gcig la rang bzhin bcu //
NK095(ce)001:4925: byang chub sems kyi che bar bgrangs //
NK095(ce)001:4926: yon tan bcu ru snang mod kyi //
NK095(ce)001:4927: snying po byang chub sems 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:4928: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK095(ce)001:4929: snga rabs 'das pas sngar ma bgrangs //
NK095(ce)001:4930: da ltar bzhugs pas bgrangs mi bya //
NK095(ce)001:4931: slad kyis byon pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK095(ce)001:4932: sems nyid 'di la bgrangs mi byed //
NK095(ce)001:4933: bgrangs med sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK095(ce)001:4934: gcig ste rnam pa bgrangs du med //
NK095(ce)001:4935: bgrangs du med pa'i snying po la //
NK095(ce)001:4936: gol sa sgrib pa gnyis med de //
NK095(ce)001:4937: sems la bgrangs du med pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4939: de bzhin du chos thams cad ye nas rig pa'i
NK095(ce)001:4940: ngang du rdzogs zhing rig pa sku gsum gyi bdag
NK095(ce)001:4941: nyid du sangs rgyas zin pa de las gzhan sa
NK095(ce)001:4942: lam la rtsol sgrub kyis bgrod du med pa la
NK095(ce)001:4943: bgrod par 'dod pas thegs pa 'og ma'i lam du
NK095(ce)001:4945: rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs dmigs med khyab brdal
NK095(ce)001:4946: chen po'i rang bzhin yin pa la theg pa rang
NK095(ce)001:4947: rang gi lta ba'i don ltar bltas pas chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:4948: byang chub sems kyi rang zhal ma mthonga bar sgrib
NK095(ce)001:4949: pa yi dri ma byung ba yin no //
NK095(ce)001:4950: de yang gol sgrib gnyis po 'dis khyad par ni
NK095(ce)001:4951: theg pa gong ma'i don ma shes pa sgrib pa
NK095(ce)001:4952: dang 'og ma'i lam du nor ba gol sa yin
NK095(ce)001:4954: gong ma ma shes sgrib par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:4955: 'og ma'i lam nor gol sa ste //
NK095(ce)001:4957: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:4960: yo ga bzhi'i sgrib pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4961: ma h+aa a nu gnyis kyi gol ba rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:4963: 'di ltar chos thams cad chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:4964: du bzang ngan dang dbye ba med par thamsa cad
NK095(ce)001:4965: mnyam nyid gcig gi rang bzhin yin pa la rgyu
NK095(ce)001:4966: pha rol du phyin pa bcu la spyad pas de'i
NK095(ce)001:4967: 'bras bu rnams phyi mar ram ma 'ong pa na
NK095(ce)001:4968: 'byung bar 'dod pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa
NK095(ce)001:4969: ba rnams ni bsam pa smon 'jug gi sems rnam
NK095(ce)001:4970: pa gnyis bskyed cing sbyor ba pha rol du phyin
NK095(ce)001:4971: pa drug gam bcu yis bsdus pa'i tshogs gnyis rgya
NK095(ce)001:4972: mtsho lta bu la bslabs pa'i sgo nas sa bcu
NK095(ce)001:4973: rim gyis bgrod te 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa
NK095(ce)001:4974: thob par 'dod pa de yis bskal pa grangs med
NK095(ce)001:4975: gsum gyi bar du a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:4976: don las gzhan du gol nas chos nyid snying po'i
NK095(ce)001:4977: don sgrib par byed pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:4978: de bzhin kri ya ste bya ba'i rgyud kyis phyi
NK095(ce)001:4979: nang rtog pa gsum po lha dang dkyil 'khor dag
NK095(ce)001:4980: pa / rdzas dang yo byad dag pa sngags dang
NK095(ce)001:4981: ting 'dzin dag pa ste dag pa rnam pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:4982: gyi tshul gyis lam sgrub par byed cing /
NK095(ce)001:4983: de yang mtshan bcas lha'i rnal 'byor la dbang thob
NK095(ce)001:4984: cing sems bskyed dang ldan pas mngon par byang chub
NK095(ce)001:4985: pa lnga dang cho 'phrul rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:4986: sam stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:4987: kri ya lha drug gi tshul gyis rigs gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:4988: lha bsgom pa dang mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor lha
NK095(ce)001:4989: snang mi dmigs par bsdus nas don dam stong pa
NK095(ce)001:4990: nyid dag pa mtha' bzhi bral ba'i ngang la 'jog
NK095(ce)001:4991: pa dang / rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam
NK095(ce)001:4992: tshig dang sdom pa thams cad mi nyams pa tshul
NK095(ce)001:4993: bzhin du bsrung zhing dag par byed pa yin na
NK095(ce)001:4994: pa dang / yang / 'bad rtsol blang dor la
NK095(ce)001:4995: zhen pa dang bcas pa yin pas mi tshe bduna
NK095(ce)001:4996: gyi bar du rdzogs pa chen po'i lam las gol
NK095(ce)001:4998: u pa ya ste spyod pa'i rgyud du dbang dang
NK095(ce)001:4999: dam tshig dang ldan pas mtshan bcas dang mtshan med
NK095(ce)001:5000: gyi rnal 'byor la brtson pa sogs rgyu lam la
NK095(ce)001:5001: spyod kyang 'bras bu rdo rje 'chang gi sa thob
NK095(ce)001:5003: lta ba yo ga dang spyod pa kri ya ltar
NK095(ce)001:5004: so so tha dad du bzung zhing gnyis su bltas
NK095(ce)001:5005: pa yis chos gnyis su med pa byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:5006: kyi gnas lugs mthong ba la mi tshe gsum du
NK095(ce)001:5008: yo ga ste rnal 'byor rgyud kyis chos rnams thams
NK095(ce)001:5009: cad snying po byang chub kyi sems gcig gi rang
NK095(ce)001:5010: bzhin yin pa la rang lam gyi dbang dang lta
NK095(ce)001:5011: spyod dam tshig la sogs pa la brten nas chos
NK095(ce)001:5012: la bzang ngan du lta zhing blang dor byed pa
NK095(ce)001:5013: de yis chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems thig
NK095(ce)001:5014: le nyag gcig tu ma mthong zhing bdag dang lha
NK095(ce)001:5016: de lta bu'i bzang ngan blang dor gyi zhen pa
NK095(ce)001:5017: dang ma bral bar du snying po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:5018: lam las gol zhing bsgribs pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:5019: gnyis pa ma h+aa a nu gnyis kyi gol sa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:5020: de yang ma h+aa yo ga bas kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:5021: po rang byung gi ye shes gcig la snod 'byung
NK095(ce)001:5023: bcud phung po lnga yab lnga /
NK095(ce)001:5024: rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5025: yin pa gsum bsgom pas blang dor rtsol sgrub kun
NK095(ce)001:5026: dang bral ba rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lung
NK095(ce)001:5027: las gzhan du gol bar gyur pa yin no zhes
NK095(ce)001:5028: sems dpa' chen po khyod kyis 'khor gyi tshogs la
NK095(ce)001:5029: lung ston cig ces pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5030: a nu yo ga bas ji ltar snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams la /
NK095(ce)001:5031: snying po de bzhin nyid byang chub sems kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:5032: bzhin du ma rtogs par dbyings stong pa nyid dang
NK095(ce)001:5033: ye shes gsal ba'i cha gnyis kyi snga ma rgyu
NK095(ce)001:5034: dang phyi ma 'bras bu ste rgyu 'bras gnyis su
NK095(ce)001:5036: rgyu yi cha la 'bras bu bskyed par sgros 'dogs
NK095(ce)001:5037: pa dang 'bras bu'i cha la rgyu la ltos dgos
NK095(ce)001:5038: par skur ba 'debs pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:5039: rgyu 'bras blang dor las 'das par chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:5040: gdod nas skye 'gag dang bral bar rang byung ye
NK095(ce)001:5041: shes kyi ngo bor ma rtogs pas sgro skur gnyis
NK095(ce)001:5042: dang bral ba rdzogs chen a ti'i dgongs don la
NK095(ce)001:5043: yid ches tshul bzhin ma 'drong gi bar du chos
NK095(ce)001:5044: nyid ji bzhin pa'i don mi rtogs par sgrib par
NK095(ce)001:5045: gsungs so // gsum pa don bsdu la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:5046: so so'i theg pa drug gol sgrib yin pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK095(ce)001:5047: mthar 'dzin byed pa'i gnyis bcas thams cad gol sgrib nyid du bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5049: chos thams cad ye sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin las
NK095(ce)001:5050: gzhan pa'i 'bras bu zhig thob tu med pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:5051: bzhin yin pa la de ltar ma rtogs par lam
NK095(ce)001:5052: gyi 'bad rtsol la brten nas rang rang gi lam
NK095(ce)001:5053: gyi 'bras bu nges par thob tu yod par 'dod
NK095(ce)001:5055: 'bras bu mngon du thob par byed pa'i rgyu la
NK095(ce)001:5056: gzhi kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa gnyis
NK095(ce)001:5057: su gtan la phab nas lam tshogs gnyis zung 'jug
NK095(ce)001:5058: nyid du bsgrub pa'i tshul nyid kyis 'bras bu sangs
NK095(ce)001:5059: rgyas nyid thob par byed pa mtshan nyid theg pa
NK095(ce)001:5060: dang / dag pa rnam pa gsum gyi sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:5061: lam la spyad pas 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa
NK095(ce)001:5063: lta spyod so sosa te mi mthun pa cha gnyis
NK095(ce)001:5064: su nyams su blang bas 'bras bu thob par 'dod
NK095(ce)001:5066: lha dang rtog pa gtsang dang rme ba la sogs
NK095(ce)001:5067: bzang ngan blang dor du spyad pas 'bras bu thob
NK095(ce)001:5068: par 'dod pa yo ga ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:5069: snod bcud rgyud rnams lha'i rang bzhin du rig cing
NK095(ce)001:5070: rtogs pa de nyid ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:5071: gyi sgo nas bsgoms pas 'bras bu thob para 'dod
NK095(ce)001:5072: pa ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK095(ce)001:5073: rgyu 'bras gnyis kyi rang bzhin dbyings nyid dang ye
NK095(ce)001:5074: shes su so sor bltas nas lam sgrub pa yis
NK095(ce)001:5075: 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa'i theg pa a nu
NK095(ce)001:5076: ste nges pa thob pa'i theg pa rnam pa drug
NK095(ce)001:5077: po de ni rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi gol
NK095(ce)001:5078: sa drug dang / sgrib pa drug drug ste /
NK095(ce)001:5079: snying po byang chub kyi sems las gzhan du gol zhing sgrib pa'i skyon dang bcas pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:5080: rang 'bras nges pa re thob tu yod par 'dod
NK095(ce)001:5081: pa'i theg pa drug gi gong ma la ltos nas
NK095(ce)001:5082: 'og ma gol sgrib tu gyur pa'i skyon dang 'og
NK095(ce)001:5083: ma 'og ma la ltos nas gong ma gong ma
NK095(ce)001:5084: yon tan du gyur tshul gsal bar gsungs pa yin
NK095(ce)001:5085: no // gnyis pa mthar 'dzin byed pa'i gnyis bcas gol sgrib nyid du bshad pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:5086: 'di ltar byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa bas rtog
NK095(ce)001:5087: dpyod kyi yul las 'das pa'i chos nyid byang chub
NK095(ce)001:5088: kyi sems la bden pa gnyis kyi rtog dpyod kyis
NK095(ce)001:5089: bsgom par byed pa nyid kyang rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:5090: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi gol sa dang sgrib
NK095(ce)001:5091: pa yin la / de bzhin du kri y+aa bas
NK095(ce)001:5092: chos nyid ye nas gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5093: yin pa la da gdod gzung 'dzin gnyis dag pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5094: thabs la brtson cing sgom par 'dod pa de nyid
NK095(ce)001:5095: kyang gshis kyi gol sa dang sgrib par bshad pa
NK095(ce)001:5096: pa yin la / dang / u pa yas byang
NK095(ce)001:5097: chub sems kyi ngo bo spros med thig le nyag
NK095(ce)001:5098: gcig gi don yin pa la lta ba dang spyod
NK095(ce)001:5099: pa gnyis cha mnyam du 'brel ba can du bsgom
NK095(ce)001:5100: par 'dod pa de nyid kyang gol sa dang sgrib
NK095(ce)001:5101: pa'i skyon yin par bshad do //
NK095(ce)001:5102: gzhan yang yo ga bas lta spyod blang dor can du lta ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:5103: ma h+aa yo gas rtsol sgrub kyi sgo nas lam bsgom pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5104: a nu yo gas dbyings dang ye shes rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:5105: gnyis su lta zhing lam bsgom pa kun las chos
NK095(ce)001:5106: nyid byang chub kyi sems 'di 'das pa yin pas
NK095(ce)001:5107: de dag kun kyang gol sgrib tu bshad pa yin
NK095(ce)001:5109: mdo sde byang chub sems dpa' ni //
NK095(ce)001:5111: bden pa gnyis kyi rtog dpyod pas //
NK095(ce)001:5112: chos nyid stong pa nam mkhar rtogs //
NK095(ce)001:5113: a ti yo ga'i bde chen ni //
NK095(ce)001:5114: rtog dpyod 'das pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:5115: rtog dpyod 'das la mdo sdes bsgribs //
NK095(ce)001:5116: rdzogs chen rtog dang dpyod pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:5117: mdo sde dag tu gol bar bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5119: dag pa rnam gsum sgor zhugs nas //
NK095(ce)001:5120: chos nyid dag pa 'dzin pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:5121: gzung 'dzin dag pa'i yul la gnas //
NK095(ce)001:5122: a ti yo ga'i bde chen ni //
NK095(ce)001:5125: rdzogs chen gzung dang 'dzin byed pa //
NK095(ce)001:5126: kri y+aa dag tu gol bar bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5127: u pa ya yi lta spyod ni //
NK095(ce)001:5128: kri y+aa spyod cing yo ga bsgribs //
NK095(ce)001:5129: lta spyod 'brel ba'i don med pas //
NK095(ce)001:5130: gnyis su med pa'i don ma rtogs //
NK095(ce)001:5131: a ti yo ga'i bde chen ni //
NK095(ce)001:5132: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:5133: gnyis su med la u pas bsgribs //
NK095(ce)001:5134: rdzogs chen gnyis su 'byed pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:5135: u pa ya ru gol bar bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5136: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pas //
NK095(ce)001:5137: mtshan ma yod med sgor zhugs nas //
NK095(ce)001:5138: phyag rgya bzhi la gtsor byed pa //
NK095(ce)001:5139: blang dor med la 'jug ma nus //
NK095(ce)001:5140: a ti yo ga'i bde chen ni //
NK095(ce)001:5141: blang dor med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:5142: blang dor med la yo gas bsgribs //
NK095(ce)001:5143: rdzogs chen blang dang dor byed pa //
NK095(ce)001:5144: yo ga dag tu gol bar bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5146: ting 'dzin rnam gsum sgor zhugs nas //
NK095(ce)001:5147: rang rgyud dag pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK095(ce)001:5148: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi'i sgrub par byed //
NK095(ce)001:5149: a ti yo ga'i bde chen ni //
NK095(ce)001:5150: rtsol sgrub 'das pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:5151: rtsol sgrub 'das la ma h+aas bsgribs //
NK095(ce)001:5152: rdzogs chen rtsol sgrub byed pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:5153: ma h+aa yo gar gol bar bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5154: a nu dbyer med pa 'dod pas //
NK095(ce)001:5155: dbyings dang ye shes sgor zhugs nas //
NK095(ce)001:5156: rgyu ni dag pa'i dbyings su blta //
NK095(ce)001:5158: a ti yo ga'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:5159: rgyu 'bras dag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:5161: rdzogs chen rgyu 'bras gnyis blta na //
NK095(ce)001:5162: a nu yo gar gol bar bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5163: theg pa dag gi gol sgribs so //
NK095(ce)001:5165: des na kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5166: ni dmigs mtshan spros pa thams cad dang bral zhing
NK095(ce)001:5167: zhen 'dzin gyi rtsol ba gang yang mi mnga' bas
NK095(ce)001:5168: mi rtsol mi bsgrub pa'i rang bzhin can yin kyang
NK095(ce)001:5169: / de lta bu'i gnas lugs 'gyur med bde ba
NK095(ce)001:5170: che ba'am chen po'i gnas lugs gdod nas bsal bzhag
NK095(ce)001:5171: bral ba'i rang bzhin 'di la theg pa 'og ma
NK095(ce)001:5172: kun gyis blang dor rtsol sgrub byas pa'i dbang gis
NK095(ce)001:5173: gol zhing sgrib pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:5174: gsum pa rnal ma'i don la rtsol sgrub med par bstan pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:5175: 'di ltar chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs kun byed
NK095(ce)001:5176: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni chos nyid yangs
NK095(ce)001:5177: pa chen po dpe nam mkha' lta bu ste /
NK095(ce)001:5178: de ltar nam mkha' lta bu yi sems nyid skye
NK095(ce)001:5179: ba med pa chos nyid spros pa thams cad dang
NK095(ce)001:5180: bral ba'i rang bzhin gdod nas ye sangs rgyas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5181: bdag nyid de la lta bas gtan la phab nas
NK095(ce)001:5182: bsgom du med de dmigs med blo las 'das pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5183: phyir dang dam tshig bsrung du med de ye nas
NK095(ce)001:5184: 'da' nyams dang bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK095(ce)001:5185: don gnyis lhun gyis grub pas phrin las btsal du
NK095(ce)001:5186: med pa dang sgrib gnyis gzhi nas grol bas ye
NK095(ce)001:5187: shes sgrib pa med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5188: ma bgrod ye nas non pas sa la sbyang du med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5189: 'bras bu gzhi la rdzogs pas bgrod pa'i lam lnga yang med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5190: gzung 'dzin gdod nas dag pas phra ba chos nyid tsam yang med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5191: sems nyid gcig gi rang bzhin la tha dad gnyisa
NK095(ce)001:5192: su grub pa med pas rgyud kyi 'brel ba med
NK095(ce)001:5193: pa dang / byang chub sems las gzhan pa'i nges
NK095(ce)001:5194: pa'i lung gis gtan la 'bebs pa med pa dang
NK095(ce)001:5195: pa dang / / sems nyid ye na sgro skur
NK095(ce)001:5196: las 'das pas man ngag gis la bzlar te la
NK095(ce)001:5197: bzla bar bya ba tsam yang med pa de ni
NK095(ce)001:5198: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i rig pa byang chub
NK095(ce)001:5199: sems kyi lta ba rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub thams cad
NK095(ce)001:5200: dang bral ba yin par gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5201: de ltar rdzogs chen byang chub sems kyi gnas lugs
NK095(ce)001:5202: la rang bzhin bcu'i rtsol zhing bsgrub tu med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5204: rdzogs chen shin tu rnal 'byor gyi //
NK095(ce)001:5205: lta ba bsgom du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5206: dam tshig bsrung du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5207: phrin las btsal du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5208: ye shes sgrib pa med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5209: sa la sbyang du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5210: lam la bsgrod du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5211: phra ba gzung 'dzin bral ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:5212: rgyud kyi rang bzhin 'brel ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:5213: lung gi rang bzhin thob tu 'bebs //
NK095(ce)001:5214: man ngag dag gis la yang bzla //
NK095(ce)001:5215: rdzogs chen shin tu rnal 'byor gyi //
NK095(ce)001:5216: rang bzhin bcu ni de ltar ro //
NK095(ce)001:5217: zhes gsungs pa ni byang chub kyi sems gcig pu
NK095(ce)001:5218: la ldog pas phye ba tsam las med par bstan
NK095(ce)001:5219: pa'o // bzhi pa rtsol sgrub can la gol sgrib byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK095(ce)001:5220: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pas lta bas bltar med
NK095(ce)001:5221: pa'i chos nyid byang chub kyi sems gcig la byis
NK095(ce)001:5222: pa'i blo can rnams kyis btags pa'i theg pa drug
NK095(ce)001:5223: gi sgom byed kyi blo drug du byung bas /
NK095(ce)001:5224: a ti ye grol chen po'i lam las gzhan du
NK095(ce)001:5225: theg pa 'og ma'i lam la gol sa dang gnas
NK095(ce)001:5226: lugs kyi rang zhal la bsgribs pa'i lta ba'i gol
NK095(ce)001:5228: de bzhin du bsrung bya bsrung byed las 'das pas
NK095(ce)001:5229: dam tshig bsrung du med pa'i rang bzhin chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:5230: thig le nyag gcig la 'og ma'i theg pa drug
NK095(ce)001:5231: gis rang rang gi sdom pa mi 'dra ba drug
NK095(ce)001:5232: bsrung bas rdzogs chen bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig
NK095(ce)001:5233: las 'og ma'i lam la gol sa dang ye bsrung
NK095(ce)001:5234: chen po'i don la sgrib pa'i dam tshig gi gol
NK095(ce)001:5236: don gnyis bsgrub pa'i phrin las btsal du med par
NK095(ce)001:5237: chos nyid gcig gi rang bzhin yin pa la theg
NK095(ce)001:5238: pa 'og ma rnams kyis so so'i lam gyi phrin
NK095(ce)001:5239: las kyi mdzad pa drug la brtsol sgrub byas pas
NK095(ce)001:5240: byar med kyi lam la gol sa dang de la
NK095(ce)001:5241: bsgribs par gyur pa'i phrin las kyi gol sgrib byung
NK095(ce)001:5242: ba dang / gdod nas rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal
NK095(ce)001:5243: zhing gzung 'dzin gyi bsgribs pa med pa'i rang byung
NK095(ce)001:5244: gi ye shes gcig la theg pa 'og ma'i blos
NK095(ce)001:5245: btags kyi ye shes drug gi 'dzin pa byung bas
NK095(ce)001:5246: 'og ma'i lam la gol sa dang rig pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:5247: zhal la bsgrib pa'i ye shes kyi gol sgrib byung
NK095(ce)001:5248: ba dang / ba dang / bsgrib pa ye nas
NK095(ce)001:5249: med pas sbyangs bar byar med pa'i ma bcos ye
NK095(ce)001:5250: shes bla ma'i sa gcig gi bdag nyid yin pa
NK095(ce)001:5251: la bsgribs pa sbyangs ba'i sgo nas sa bcu rim
NK095(ce)001:5252: gyis thob par zhen pa drug tu byung bas 'og
NK095(ce)001:5253: ma'i lam la gol ba dang rdzogs chen don la
NK095(ce)001:5254: bsgribs pa'i sa yi gol sgrib byung ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:5255: lam la bsgrod du med par gzhi 'bras dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:5256: chen po gcig gi rang bzhin yin pa la lam
NK095(ce)001:5257: bgrod par 'dod pa'i 'og ma'i theg pa drug tu
NK095(ce)001:5258: byung bas 'og ma'i lam la gol zhing gong ma'i
NK095(ce)001:5259: rang bzhin la sgrib pa'i lam gyi gol sgrib byung
NK095(ce)001:5260: ba dang / dngos po'i chos nyid gang du yang
NK095(ce)001:5261: ma grub pas gzung ba'i yul du med pa chos
NK095(ce)001:5262: dbyings gcig gi rang bzhin yin pa la 'dzin byed
NK095(ce)001:5263: yul can gyi dbye ba drug tu byung bas la
NK095(ce)001:5264: gol la bsgribs phra ba chos nyid kyi gol sgrib
NK095(ce)001:5265: ba dang / byung ba dang / chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:5266: la 'brel bya 'brel byed tha dad du ma grub
NK095(ce)001:5267: par gnyis med blo 'das chen po gcig gi rang
NK095(ce)001:5268: bzhin la chos dang chos can 'khor ba dang myang
NK095(ce)001:5269: 'das gzhi lam 'bras bu sogs gnyis bcas 'brel ba
NK095(ce)001:5270: can du 'dzin pa drug tu byung bas la gol
NK095(ce)001:5271: la bsgribs 'brel ba'i don can rgyud kyi gol sgrib
NK095(ce)001:5272: ba dang / byung ba dang / byung ba dang
NK095(ce)001:5273: / rang byung ye shes chen po bden pa dbyer
NK095(ce)001:5274: med gcig las med pa la theg pa so so'i
NK095(ce)001:5275: rtogs tshul gyis gtan la dbab bya'i nges pa'i bden
NK095(ce)001:5276: pa drug tu byung bas la gol la bsgribsa lung
NK095(ce)001:5277: gi gol sgrib byung ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:5278: ngag tshig gis brjod du med pa'i chos nyid gcig
NK095(ce)001:5279: gi rang bzhin pa la brjod byed kyi theg pa
NK095(ce)001:5280: drug tu byung bas 'og ma'i sgra tshig mtshan ma'i
NK095(ce)001:5281: yul du zhen pa'i lam la gol ba dang rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:5282: chen brjod med kyi don la bsgribs pa'i man ngag
NK095(ce)001:5283: gi gol sgriba byung ba yin no zhes pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5284: lnga pa byang chub kyi sems rtsol sgrub kun las 'das pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:5285: 'di ltar chos rnams ma lus pa kun gyi snying
NK095(ce)001:5286: po kun byed byang chub kyi sems 'di ni ye
NK095(ce)001:5287: gdod nas rang gi rang bzhin 'bad rtsol la ma
NK095(ce)001:5288: ltos par lhun gyis grub zin pa yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:5289: / phyi nas lta ba dang dam tshig la sogs
NK095(ce)001:5290: pa rang bzhin bcu yis gzhan nas btsal zhing sgrub
NK095(ce)001:5291: par byed mi dgos par kun byed byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:5292: sems nga yi rang bzhin ni dus dang rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:5293: kun tu rgyu rkyen rtsol sgrub gang la'ang mi ltos
NK095(ce)001:5294: pa dpe nam mkha' ji 'dra ba de bzhin mthong
NK095(ce)001:5295: thos la sogs pa'i dmigs pa'i spyod yul kun dang
NK095(ce)001:5296: bral ba yin la des na nam mkha' dag la
NK095(ce)001:5297: mkhas blun kun gyis kyang bya ba gang yang rtsol
NK095(ce)001:5298: bar mi byed kyang nam mkha' dag la su kun
NK095(ce)001:5299: gyis kyang rtsol bar bya ru ma dmigs la /
NK095(ce)001:5300: de ltar nam mkha' rang nyid ma grub cing gzhi
NK095(ce)001:5301: med rtsa bral gyi rang bzhin yin pas su kun
NK095(ce)001:5302: gyis byas shing rtsol sgrub byed pa'i yul kun las
NK095(ce)001:5303: 'das pa de bzhin du kun byed snying po byang
NK095(ce)001:5304: chub kyi sems nga nyid tshul mthong gi shes pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5305: spyod yul kun las 'das shing ma grub pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:5306: na / kun byed gdod ma'i gshis lugs rig pa
NK095(ce)001:5307: rang byung gi ye shes nga la lta bas bltar
NK095(ce)001:5308: med la yid kyis bsgom du ye nas med de
NK095(ce)001:5309: bsgam bya yul dang sgom byed kyi blo gnyis dang
NK095(ce)001:5311: de bzhin du gong du bstan pa'i rang bzhin bcu
NK095(ce)001:5312: po des kyang ni blo 'das gnyug ma'i ye shes
NK095(ce)001:5313: kun byed byang chub kyi sems spros pa thams cad
NK095(ce)001:5314: dang bral ba nga la 'bad rtsol gyi bya ba
NK095(ce)001:5315: ci yang bya ru yod pa ma yin no //
NK095(ce)001:5317: drug pa rang bzhin bcu'i rtsol ba'i nyes pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:5318: de ltar snying po byang chub kyi rang bzhin ye
NK095(ce)001:5319: nas bya rtsol gyi yul las 'das pa la rgyu
NK095(ce)001:5320: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang 'bras bu'i theg pa
NK095(ce)001:5321: can sngags 'og ma ba rnams kyi rang bzhin bcu
NK095(ce)001:5322: po de yis rang byung rig pa byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:5323: sems nga la rtsol sgrub chen pos btsal bar byas
NK095(ce)001:5324: pa'i sgo nas kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga
NK095(ce)001:5325: dang nga yi rang bzhina chos dbyings dmigs mtha' dang
NK095(ce)001:5326: bral ba mthong bar 'doda pas a ti ye grub
NK095(ce)001:5327: chen po'i don las nyams par gyur pa dper na
NK095(ce)001:5328: nam 'kha' la gom pa bor zhing 'gro bar 'dod
NK095(ce)001:5329: pa'i gang zag de sa la ltung ba ma gtogs
NK095(ce)001:5330: mkha' la 'gro ba'i yul med pa bzhin du rang
NK095(ce)001:5331: bzhin bcu pos sa lam bgrod par 'dod pas theg
NK095(ce)001:5332: pa 'og ma'i lam du ltung zhing gol bar 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:5334: bdun pa rtsol sgrub kun las 'das pa'i rang bzhin bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:5335: ye nas gang du'ang dmigs pa thams cad las 'das pa /
NK095(ce)001:5336: gzung 'dzin gnyis bcas las 'das pas ye nas bya
NK095(ce)001:5337: ba rtsal med par la bzla ba gol sgrub kyi
NK095(ce)001:5339: thams cad byang chub kyi sems su bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5341: sems nyid lta sgom las 'das pa //
NK095(ce)001:5342: bsrung sdom rtsol sgrub las 'das pa //
NK095(ce)001:5343: sgrib med sbyangs bsgrod las 'das pa //
NK095(ce)001:5344: gzhi bral ngos bzung las 'das pa //
NK095(ce)001:5345: mchog gsang spros pa las 'das pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5347: de la kun byed rgyal po nga yi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5348: ji ltar gnas pa'i tshul ma nor nges par byed
NK095(ce)001:5349: pa'i thabs su man ngag don gyi khungs sam lung
NK095(ce)001:5350: zab mo bstan pa ni nga ni rang bzhin bcu
NK095(ce)001:5351: pos rtsol zhing sgrub pa'i spyod yul kun las 'das
NK095(ce)001:5352: pa'i phyir na blta bya lta byed kyi tshul du
NK095(ce)001:5353: mtshan 'dzin dmigs pa'i blo yis lta ba bsgom du
NK095(ce)001:5355: de bzhina tu dam tshig phrin las la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:5356: rang bzhin bcu ga la rtsol bar 'dod pa thams
NK095(ce)001:5357: cad lta ba bsgom du med pa de bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:5358: ngal ba tshi chad kyi rgyu tsam las don 'bras
NK095(ce)001:5359: thob tu med pa'i rgyu mtshan de nyid kyis na
NK095(ce)001:5360: rang bzhin bcu la rtsol sgrub byas pas don yod
NK095(ce)001:5361: par ma rtogs shig /rgyu mtshan des na sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:5362: nam mkha' lta bu chos sku kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:5363: nga la ni yod med dang snang stong sogs gang
NK095(ce)001:5364: du bltas pas kyang mthong ba'i yul du grub pa
NK095(ce)001:5365: med pas / dmigs mtshan spros pa'i spyod yul gang
NK095(ce)001:5366: du'ang lta bar ma byed par gshis lugs bcos bsgyur
NK095(ce)001:5367: dang bral ba chos nyid de bzhina nyida kyi ngang
NK095(ce)001:5368: du rang babs su zhoga cig ces lta ba sgom
NK095(ce)001:5371: byang chub sems la btsal du ye nas med //
NK095(ce)001:5372: ji bzhin ngang la ma bcos gang dgar thong //
NK095(ce)001:5373: bdag gzhan yul can ye nas med pas na //
NK095(ce)001:5374: mnyam pa ris med rig pa gang dgar thong //
NK095(ce)001:5375: rtag tu de dang 'du 'bral med pas na //
NK095(ce)001:5376: gnyis su yul med ris med gang dgar thong //
NK095(ce)001:5379: snying po byang chub rang bzhin la //
NK095(ce)001:5380: gzhan du blta ba'i yul med pas //
NK095(ce)001:5381: lta ba bsgom du med pa yin /
NK095(ce)001:5384: rig pa byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ni gdod
NK095(ce)001:5385: nas gzung 'dzin gyi spros pa thams cad dang bral
NK095(ce)001:5386: ba ma skyes ka nas dag pa yin pas las
NK095(ce)001:5387: nyon gyi zag pa dang bral bar bya ba'i rgyu
NK095(ce)001:5388: sdom pa dang dam tshig bsrung bar bya ba gang
NK095(ce)001:5389: yang med pas theg pa 'og ma ltar du sdom
NK095(ce)001:5390: pa dang ni tshul khrims bsrung mi dgos zhes dam
NK095(ce)001:5391: tshig bsrung du med par bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5393: gcig la kun rdzogs ma spangs rang sar grol //
NK095(ce)001:5394: sangs rgyas sku dang sems can nyon mongs lus //
NK095(ce)001:5395: ji ltar snang ba thams cad rig pa'i rgyan //
NK095(ce)001:5396: nyon mongs dug lnga ye shes bdud rtsi ste //
NK095(ce)001:5397: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa byang chub lam du drangs //
NK095(ce)001:5398: dug gsum sku gsum klong du gtan sprugs te //
NK095(ce)001:5399: skye shi rtsad gcod khams gsum yongs su grol //
NK095(ce)001:5400: zhes gsungs pa ltar khams gsum rgyud drug gi 'gro
NK095(ce)001:5401: ba thams cad rig pa byang chub kyi snying por
NK095(ce)001:5402: ye nas lhun gyis grub cing sangs rgyas zin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5403: phyir na de las gzhan du phrin las zhig rtsol
NK095(ce)001:5404: bar dang ni 'bad pas bsgrub pa bya mi dgosa
NK095(ce)001:5405: so zhes phrin las bsgrub tu med par bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:5407: snying po byang chub sems de la //
NK095(ce)001:5408: gzung 'dzin med pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:5409: dam tshig bsrung du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5410: snying po byang chub sems de la //
NK095(ce)001:5411: lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:5412: phrin las btsal du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5415: snying po rang byunga gi ye shes la ma rig
NK095(ce)001:5416: pa'i mun pas sgrib pa gdod nas med pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:5418: 'di ni nyi ma'i snying po de nyid don //
NK095(ce)001:5419: rang bzhag 'od gsal mi g.yo gnas par 'dod //
NK095(ce)001:5420: gzhan ni sprin dang mun sel rtsol sgrub kyis //
NK095(ce)001:5421: nyi ma gdod sgrub byed dang mtshungs par bstan //
NK095(ce)001:5422: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du dper na nyi ma'i ngos
NK095(ce)001:5423: la sprin gyis sgrib pa yod ma myong pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:5424: sprin bsal nas nyi ma gsal bar bskyed du med
NK095(ce)001:5425: pa ltar rang byung rig pa'i ye shes ye nas
NK095(ce)001:5426: 'od gsal ba'i rang bzhin du gnas pa de la
NK095(ce)001:5427: ni gsar du blang dor rtsol sgrub kyi sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:5428: las nyon gzung 'dzin gyi sgrib pa bsal zhing ye
NK095(ce)001:5429: shes kyi rang bzhin gsal bar bskyed du med do
NK095(ce)001:5430: zhes ye shes bskyed du med par bstan pa dang
NK095(ce)001:5431: / srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba thamsa
NK095(ce)001:5432: cad chos sku kun byed rgyal po nga yi sa
NK095(ce)001:5433: ru ye thog ma'i dus nas gnas shing de las
NK095(ce)001:5434: skad cig kyang g.yo ba med pa'i phyir na sgrib
NK095(ce)001:5435: pa sbyangs ba sogs 'bad rtsol gyi sgo nas bsgrod
NK095(ce)001:5436: par byed pa'i sa yi go rim kyang ni yod
NK095(ce)001:5438: zhes sa la sbyang du med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5439: kun byed nga yis 'khor 'das kun la ye nas
NK095(ce)001:5440: khyab cing dbyer med par gnas pa'i phyir na chos
NK095(ce)001:5441: rnams kun gyi gnas lugs 'gyur ba med pa'i ye
NK095(ce)001:5442: shes srid zhi kun khyab chen po nga la gzhan
NK095(ce)001:5443: du bgrod par bya ba'i lam lnga yang yod pa
NK095(ce)001:5444: min pa'i tshul shes par bya'o zhes sa lam la
NK095(ce)001:5445: bgrod du med par bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:5447: snying po byang chub sems 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:5448: sgrib pa med pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:5449: ye nas rang byung ye shes yin //
NK095(ce)001:5450: snying po byang chub sems 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:5451: thams cad 'di la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:5452: sa zhes bya ba sbyang du med //
NK095(ce)001:5453: snying po byang chub sems 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:5454: gzhan du bgrod du med pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:5455: lam la bgrod du med pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5458: chos nyid snying po rang byung gi ye shes nga ni ye nas phyir bzung ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:5459: nang 'dzin pa'i sems gnyis dang bral ba'i gzhi grol
NK095(ce)001:5460: blo las 'das pa yin pa'i phyir na phra ba
NK095(ce)001:5461: chos nyid kyi rang bzhin zhes pa tsam du yang
NK095(ce)001:5462: ni ming du gdags pa dang sems kyi dmigs gtad
NK095(ce)001:5463: sogs su bya ba'i yul du'ang grub pa med do
NK095(ce)001:5464: ces phra ba chos nyid med pa bstan pa dang
NK095(ce)001:5465: / gang snang ji shar thams cad kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:5466: po'i sku yi bkod pa yin pas snying po nga
NK095(ce)001:5467: yi gzugs kyis 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5468: chos kun la ma khyab pa med par khyab cing
NK095(ce)001:5469: dbyer med pa'i phyir na 'khor 'das gnyis shes bya
NK095(ce)001:5470: ba sogs gnyis chos thams cad ye nas yod pa
NK095(ce)001:5471: ma yin pas 'brel bya dang 'brel yul med pa'o
NK095(ce)001:5472: zhes 'brel ba rgyud kyi rang bzhin med par bstan
NK095(ce)001:5474: snying po byang chub sems 'di ni //
NK095(ce)001:5475: ye nas chos nyid yin pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:5476: phra ba dag gi rang bzhin yin //
NK095(ce)001:5477: snying po byang chub sems 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:5478: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis snang ba //
NK095(ce)001:5479: 'brel ba rgyud kyi rang bzhin yin //
NK095(ce)001:5480: ces pa'i lung 'di nyid kyis sgrub pa'i tshul du
NK095(ce)001:5481: bstan pa ni byang chub sems la ldog pa'i cha
NK095(ce)001:5482: nas dbye na yon tan de dag tshang tshul bstan
NK095(ce)001:5483: pa dang / 'dir gzhung las dgag pa'i tshul gyis
NK095(ce)001:5484: bstan pa ni theg pa 'og mas brtags pa lta
NK095(ce)001:5485: bu'i rang rgyud pa med par bstan pa gnyis 'gal
NK095(ce)001:5488: kun byed nga ni ye gdod nas ranga byung ye
NK095(ce)001:5489: shes chen po rgyu rkyen gang la mi ltos par
NK095(ce)001:5490: 'gyur med 'dus ma byas pa'i rang bzhin yin zhing
NK095(ce)001:5491: ji ltar snang ba'i chos kun kyang de'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5492: du gtan la phebs zin pa yin pa'i phyir na
NK095(ce)001:5493: nga la zab mo'i lung gzhan gyis gtan la dbab
NK095(ce)001:5494: tu med do zhes nges pa'i lung med par bstan
NK095(ce)001:5495: pa dang / nga ni 'khor 'das kun gyis snying
NK095(ce)001:5496: po gnas lugs byang chub kyi sems rang bzhin rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:5497: pa chen po ye babs spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:5498: bdag nyid du la bzlas zin pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:5499: de bas lhag par gyur pa'i gsang ba'i man ngag
NK095(ce)001:5500: ches zab pa zhig gzhan na btsal du yod pa
NK095(ce)001:5502: man ngag btsal du med par bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:5504: rang byung ye shes snying po 'dis //
NK095(ce)001:5505: chos kun gtan la 'bebs pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:5506: lung gi thog tu 'bebs pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5507: rang byung ye shes snying po 'di //
NK095(ce)001:5508: sgro skur kun dang bral ba'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:5509: la zlo ba yi man ngag yin //
NK095(ce)001:5511: de ltar sa bcad lnga po des snying po byang
NK095(ce)001:5512: chub sems kyi gnas lugs la rang bzhin bcu yis
NK095(ce)001:5513: dmigs su med par bstan pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:5514: gnyis pa gzung 'dzin gnyis bcas las 'das pas ye nas bya btsal med par la bzla ba ni /
NK095(ce)001:5515: de ltar na chos sku kun byed rgyal po nga
NK095(ce)001:5516: ni ngo bos mi stong ba rtag pa ther zugs
NK095(ce)001:5517: su yod par sgro 'dogs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5518: sku dang ye shes thams cad ye nas lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:5519: rdzogs pa chen por grub zin pa la med par
NK095(ce)001:5520: skur ba 'debs pa sogs gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i spros
NK095(ce)001:5522: byar med ye sangs rgyas pa'i ngang du chos rnams
NK095(ce)001:5523: kun gyi la ni nga yis bzlas pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:5525: bye brag tu 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa kun
NK095(ce)001:5526: khyab nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin chos sku kun
NK095(ce)001:5527: byed rgyal po nga med pa yi yul lam nga
NK095(ce)001:5528: yi rang bzhin du ma gyur pa'i chos ni gzhan
NK095(ce)001:5529: gang yang med pas de las gzhan du lta ba
NK095(ce)001:5530: rang byung gi ye shes la bsgom pas bzang du
NK095(ce)001:5531: 'gro ba med par ye grol byar med chen por
NK095(ce)001:5532: la yang bzlas zin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5533: de bzhin du ye med stong pa ka dag chen
NK095(ce)001:5534: po gcig pu'i bdag nyid rang gnas phyal ba'i ye
NK095(ce)001:5535: shes 'od gsal lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin nga
NK095(ce)001:5536: nyid las gzhan du bsrung bya'i chos dang srung byed
NK095(ce)001:5537: kyi blo yang ma grub pas bsrung du med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5538: phyir dam tshig dang sdom pa bsrung du med par
NK095(ce)001:5539: la yang bzlas zin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5540: snang spyod thams cad nga yi phrin las rtsol med
NK095(ce)001:5541: lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin yin pa de las
NK095(ce)001:5542: gzhan du gdul bya 'dul ba'i phrin las zhig btsal
NK095(ce)001:5543: du med pa'i phyir na phrin las btsal du med
NK095(ce)001:5544: par la yang bzlas zin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5545: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kun byed
NK095(ce)001:5546: nga yi ngo bo ye shes bla ma'i sa la
NK095(ce)001:5547: da lta nyid nas gnas yod pa 'di las gzhan
NK095(ce)001:5548: du gnas pa gcig kyang med pa'i phyir na da
NK095(ce)001:5549: gsar du sa rnams rim gyis thob pa la ltos
NK095(ce)001:5550: pa med pas sa la sbyang du med par la
NK095(ce)001:5552: ye grol ka dag chen po 'od gsal 'pho 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:5553: med pa'i sems nyid kun byed rgyal po nga la
NK095(ce)001:5554: las nyon gzung 'dzin gyi mun pas sgrib pa ye
NK095(ce)001:5555: nas med pa'i phyir na rang byung 'dus ma byas
NK095(ce)001:5556: pa'i ye shes rgyu rkyen kun las 'das pa yin
NK095(ce)001:5557: par la yang bzlas zin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5558: nga yi ngo bo dang rtsal dang rol pas bsdus
NK095(ce)001:5559: pa'i chos thams cad ni rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed pa
NK095(ce)001:5560: ltar snang dus nyid nas ma skyes shing 'gag pa
NK095(ce)001:5561: med pa'i chos nyid yin pa'i phyir na phra ba
NK095(ce)001:5562: chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba yang nga nyid
NK095(ce)001:5563: yin par la yang bzlas zin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5564: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:5565: yi ngo bo zung 'jug mi slob pa'i lam la
NK095(ce)001:5566: gnas zin pa las gzhan du lam je bzang du
NK095(ce)001:5567: 'gro ba'i sgo nas gong nas gong mar bgrod du
NK095(ce)001:5568: med pa'i phyir lam la bgrod du med par la
NK095(ce)001:5570: dag pa sangs rgyas ltar snang ba dang ma dag
NK095(ce)001:5571: sems can ltar snang ba dang snang zhing srid pas
NK095(ce)001:5572: bsdus pa'i snod bcud kyi chos kun snying po byang
NK095(ce)001:5573: chub kyi sems gdod nas ye sangs rgyas pa nga
NK095(ce)001:5574: yi rtsal las byung ba'i rang bzhin yin pa la
NK095(ce)001:5575: khyad par med pa'i phyir na sangs rgyas dang sems
NK095(ce)001:5576: can ye nas bzang ngan gnyis su med par 'khor
NK095(ce)001:5577: 'das dbyer med chen po la yang bzlas zin pa
NK095(ce)001:5578: dang / snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:5579: rang byung ye shes chen po gcig pu'i bdag nyid
NK095(ce)001:5580: du gtan la 'bebs shing snang srid kyi spros pa
NK095(ce)001:5581: thams cad cig char du gcod pa'i phyir na a
NK095(ce)001:5582: ti gsang chen snying po kun byed byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:5583: sems 'di nyid lung thams cad kyi nang nas chen
NK095(ce)001:5584: po'am rgyal po yin lung ji bzhin pa'i thog tu
NK095(ce)001:5585: 'bebs par byed pa yin par la yang bzlas pa
NK095(ce)001:5586: dang / dang / phyi nang snod bcud kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:5587: rnams thamsa cada snying po nga yi rang bzhin skye
NK095(ce)001:5588: med ye stong chen po ma bcos de bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:5589: las gzhan du med pa'i phyir na kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:5590: po byang chub kyi sems nga nyid kyi klong chos
NK095(ce)001:5591: dbyings yangs pa chen po'i ngang du 'khor 'das su
NK095(ce)001:5592: snang ba'i chos thams cad bzang ngan dang dbye bsal
NK095(ce)001:5594: 'khor 'das dang bde sdug /dgag sgrub dang spang blang
NK095(ce)001:5595: med par ye nas grol zin pa yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:5596: ston pa kun byed nga ni chos rnams ma lus
NK095(ce)001:5597: pa kun gyi la bzla yin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:5599: dbyings la dbyings shar dbyings kyi klong du grol //
NK095(ce)001:5600: mkha' la grol lo mnyam pa nyid du grol //
NK095(ce)001:5601: dbyings su grol lo bzang ngan med par grol //
NK095(ce)001:5602: klong du grol lo mtho dman med par grol //
NK095(ce)001:5603: gcig tu grol lo skye shi med pas grol //
NK095(ce)001:5604: gcig gi dbyings su 'bad med rtsol med grol //
NK095(ce)001:5605: mi gnas rang dag ma spangs rang sar grol //
NK095(ce)001:5606: mi mnyam grol yang mnyam pa'i dbyings su grol //
NK095(ce)001:5607: grol ba'i dus na rang grol rang sa zin //
NK095(ce)001:5608: grol dang ma grol dbyings la ye med pas //
NK095(ce)001:5609: ji ltar grol yang rang sar rang la grol //
NK095(ce)001:5610: kun kyang ro gcig mnyam pa'i dbyings su grol //
NK095(ce)001:5611: lugs zlog med par dbyings su grol ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:5612: chos nyid klong du grol lo dbye bsal med //
NK095(ce)001:5613: rtsol ba med par grol lo sgrub tu med //
NK095(ce)001:5614: nges pa med par grol lo gza' gtad med //
NK095(ce)001:5615: lhun gyis grub par grol lo phyogs ris med //
NK095(ce)001:5616: mtshan ma thams cad rang sar grol ba'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:5617: byang chub sems la grol dang ma grol med //
NK095(ce)001:5618: nam mkha'i klong na ji ltar byas kyang grol //
NK095(ce)001:5619: lhun grub klong la gang ltar byas kyang grol //
NK095(ce)001:5620: kun kyang 'dra'o gzhan med ye nas grol //
NK095(ce)001:5621: spang blang med par rang sar rang shar grol //
NK095(ce)001:5622: zhes gsungs pa ltar chos thams cad rig pa byang
NK095(ce)001:5623: chub sems kyi dbyings su ye grol bskyar gzhi med
NK095(ce)001:5624: par la bzla bar gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5625: gsum pa gol sgrib kyi nges tshig bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:5628: don bsdu ba de nyid spang bar gdams pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5630: de la gol sa dang sgrib pa zhes bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:5631: rgyu mtshan nam nges tshig ni 'di ltar khams gsum
NK095(ce)001:5632: na gnas pa'i sems can yin no cog gi rgyud
NK095(ce)001:5633: na chos sku kun byed rgyal po rig pa rang
NK095(ce)001:5634: byung gi ye shes nga nyid bri gang 'pho 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:5635: dang bral bar lhun grub ye sangs rgyas pa'i bdag
NK095(ce)001:5636: nyid du bzhugs pa yin kyang rang ngo rang gis
NK095(ce)001:5637: ma shes pas 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang du ma la
NK095(ce)001:5638: spyod cing 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang zhig
NK095(ce)001:5639: blang dor bya rtsol la brten nas gzhan du tshol
NK095(ce)001:5640: bar byed pa ni 'od gsal snying po'i don la
NK095(ce)001:5641: sgrib pa'i ngo bor bshad pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:5643: ji ltar mi dbul khyim nang rin chen gter //
NK095(ce)001:5644: mi zad pa yi gter ni yod gyur la //
NK095(ce)001:5645: mi des de ma shes shing gter des yang //
NK095(ce)001:5646: de la nga 'dir yod ces mi smra ltar //
NK095(ce)001:5647: de bzhin yid kyi nang chud rin chen gter //
NK095(ce)001:5648: dri med bsal dang bzhag med chos nyid kyang //
NK095(ce)001:5649: ma rtogs pas na dbul ba'i sdug bsngal ni //
NK095(ce)001:5650: rnam mang rgyun du skye dgu 'dis myong ngo //
NK095(ce)001:5652: de ltar rang byung gi ye shes de nyid rang
NK095(ce)001:5653: ngo ma shes pa'i dbang gis sems nyid rang byung
NK095(ce)001:5654: gi ye shes chos sku kun byed rgyal po nga
NK095(ce)001:5655: nyid ye nas 'bral med lhun grub tu yod pa
NK095(ce)001:5656: la yid ma ches par de las gzhan du rgyu
NK095(ce)001:5657: rkyen rtsol sgrub kyi sgo nas 'bras bu sngon med
NK095(ce)001:5658: gsar byung zhig thob par re zhing btsal bas theg
NK095(ce)001:5659: pa 'og ma'i lam du gol sa byung ba yin
NK095(ce)001:5661: sgrib pa sgrib pa zhes bya ba //
NK095(ce)001:5662: rig shes bya ba'i yul de la //
NK095(ce)001:5663: ma rig ma shes ma rtogs pa //
NK095(ce)001:5664: sgrib pa sgrib pa zhes su bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5665: gol sa gol sa zhes bya ba //
NK095(ce)001:5666: dper na don yod lam zhugs pas //
NK095(ce)001:5667: shar gyi don yod nub lam phyin //
NK095(ce)001:5668: nub phyin shar gyi don mi 'grub //
NK095(ce)001:5669: spros pa med pa'i don bshor bas //
NK095(ce)001:5670: mtshan ma dag gi lam la bsgrod //
NK095(ce)001:5671: sgro skur bral ba'i chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:5672: tshig dang yi ge brjod pas gol //
NK095(ce)001:5673: brjod yod rtog pa sgrib pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:5675: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:5676: de lta bu'i sgrib pa de la dbye na las
NK095(ce)001:5677: kyi sgrib pa dang shes bya yi sgrib pa rnam
NK095(ce)001:5679: de yang rang byung rig pa'i ye shes kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:5680: zhal mngon sum du ma mthong ba'am ma rig pa
NK095(ce)001:5681: ni las kyi sgrib pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:5682: ji ltar na mtshan nyid theg pa'i lam gyis bden
NK095(ce)001:5683: pa gnyis kyi don la rtog cing dpyod pa'i las
