NK095(ce)001:5684: la rtsol bas sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:5685: kyi don ji bzhin mi mthong bar sgrib par byed
NK095(ce)001:5686: pa dang / de bzhin du kri ya bas dag
NK095(ce)001:5687: pa rnam pa gsum gyi las la rtsol bas dang
NK095(ce)001:5688: pa dang / / u pa yas lta spyod zung 'brel gyi las la rtsol ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:5689: yo ga bas blang dor gnyis kyi las la rtsol ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:5690: ma h+aas bsnyen sgrub bzhi yi las la rtsol ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:5691: a nus dbyings dang ye shes kyi sgor zhugs nas
NK095(ce)001:5692: bde stong lhan gcig skyes pa'i ye shes bskyed pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5694: theg pa rang rang gi las de la zhen pas
NK095(ce)001:5695: btsal med rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs ji bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5696: mi mthong bar sgrib par byed pa'i cha nas las
NK095(ce)001:5697: kyi bsgrib par bshad pa yin la de'i dbang gis
NK095(ce)001:5698: rig pa'i rtsal las shar ba'i snang srid kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:5699: thams cad ye grol ka dag chen po yin par
NK095(ce)001:5700: ma shes par gzung 'dzin tha dad du bltas pa
NK095(ce)001:5701: ni shes bya'i sgrib pa yina pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:5702: de bas na ji ltar snang zhing srid pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:5703: thams cad kun snying po byang chub sems kyi ngo
NK095(ce)001:5704: bo las gzhan du blang dor gyi yul gang yang
NK095(ce)001:5705: med par bas kyang tshul de ltar du ma rig
NK095(ce)001:5706: pa dang ma shes pa ni sgrib pa gnyis kyi
NK095(ce)001:5708: de ltar chos thams cad snying po rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:5709: ye shes sgrib med bsal bzhag bral ba'i chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:5710: rtsol sgrub bral ba yin par ma shes pas rang
NK095(ce)001:5711: bzhin bcu la so sor zhen nas btsal zhing bsgrub
NK095(ce)001:5712: par byed pa de ni theg pa 'og ma'i lam
NK095(ce)001:5713: du ltung ba'i cha nas rdzogs pa chen po'i gol
NK095(ce)001:5714: sar gyur ba yin par ston pa kun byed ngas
NK095(ce)001:5715: bshad do zhes pa ste de nyid las /
NK095(ce)001:5716: rang bzhin bcu po'i ngo bo ni //
NK095(ce)001:5717: snying po byang chub sems yin te //
NK095(ce)001:5718: ya na 'dun gyi go skabs su //
NK095(ce)001:5719: rang gi rang bzhin ma shes na //
NK095(ce)001:5720: sgrib pa sgrib pa zhes su bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5721: rang gi rang bzhin ma shes nas //
NK095(ce)001:5723: gol sa gol sa zhes su bshad //
NK095(ce)001:5726: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /ji ltar snang
NK095(ce)001:5727: ba'i 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams thams cad ni snying
NK095(ce)001:5728: po byang chub sems kyi rang gi rang rtsal yin
NK095(ce)001:5729: gyis gzhan du grub pa rdul tsam yang yod pa
NK095(ce)001:5730: min mod / 'on kyang de la bzang ngan dang
NK095(ce)001:5731: rang gzhan sogs su zhen nas rtog par byed na
NK095(ce)001:5732: min mod / / de ltar rtog cing zhen pa
NK095(ce)001:5733: de yis ni rang gi rang zhal la rang gis
NK095(ce)001:5734: min mod / / sgribs pa ste / rang gi
NK095(ce)001:5735: rang bzhin snying po byang chub sems kyi gshis lugs
NK095(ce)001:5736: ji lta ba nyid gang zag de yis shes pa
NK095(ce)001:5737: min la des dbang gis gzhan du btsal bas gol
NK095(ce)001:5738: sa yang 'byung ba yin no zhes so //
NK095(ce)001:5739: bzhi pa de nyid spang bar gdams pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:5740: ngo bo rang sems yin pas ye bde gol sgrib las 'das pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5741: de nyid bya btsal las 'das par bzhag pas gol sgrib gang yang med par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5743: gong du bshad pa'i rgyu mtshan des na ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:5744: snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun sems dpa' rdo
NK095(ce)001:5745: rje nyid ces zhu ba pos mtshon nas sems can
NK095(ce)001:5746: thams cad kyis rang gi sems nyid kyi rtsal 'gags
NK095(ce)001:5747: med du rang la snang ba yin pa ma gtogs
NK095(ce)001:5748: rang nyid las gzhan pa'i chos zhig yod pa min
NK095(ce)001:5749: par shes par gyis la 'khor 'das kyi chos 'di
NK095(ce)001:5750: rnams la tshur mthong gi blos mi rtog cing rang
NK095(ce)001:5751: bzhin bcu yis rtsol bar mi byed par rtog med
NK095(ce)001:5752: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du ma bcos rang babs
NK095(ce)001:5753: su gnas pas bya byed kyi gdung ba med par
NK095(ce)001:5754: bde bar mnos shig dang gol sgrib thams cad las
NK095(ce)001:5755: 'das pa yin no zhes gdams pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:5757: e ma sangs rgyas sems dpa'i rigs //
NK095(ce)001:5758: don gyi dgongs pa nges bstan gyis //
NK095(ce)001:5759: legs par zung zhig rdo rje 'chang //
NK095(ce)001:5760: yul la rtogs byed mi snang bas //
NK095(ce)001:5761: sems kyi 'dzin pas nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5762: ye shes chos las 'das pas na //
NK095(ce)001:5763: sna tshogs blo yis nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5764: snang yul gnyis su mi 'dzin pas //
NK095(ce)001:5765: rnam shes brgyad kyis nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5766: sangs rgyas sems can mi 'byed pas //
NK095(ce)001:5767: bzang ngan gnyis kyi nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5768: stong gsal gnyis su mi 'byed pas //
NK095(ce)001:5769: bying rgod gnyis kyi nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5770: bya byed gnyis su mi 'dzin pas //
NK095(ce)001:5771: theg pa'i rtsol bas nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5772: rtogs dang ma rtogs gnyis med pas //
NK095(ce)001:5773: yin min gnyis kyis nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5774: shes dang ma shes gnyis med pas //
NK095(ce)001:5775: blo dngos gnyis kyis nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5776: phyogs dang ris su mi 'dzin pas //
NK095(ce)001:5777: dgra gnyen gnyis kyis nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5778: mtha' dang dbus su mi 'byed pas //
NK095(ce)001:5779: gol sgrib gnyis kyis nga mi bsgrib //
NK095(ce)001:5780: ces pa la sogs pas bstan pa bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:5782: 'o na bde bar mnos shig ces gdams par mdzad
NK095(ce)001:5783: na de la bde ba'i don la gnas pas gol
NK095(ce)001:5784: sgrib thams cad las 'das pa'i tshul ni ji lta
NK095(ce)001:5786: de ni 'di lta ste ye grol phyogs yan chen
NK095(ce)001:5787: po'i dgongs pa 'di la lta ba dang dam tshig
NK095(ce)001:5788: la sogs pas lam gyi rang bzhina theg pa kun
NK095(ce)001:5789: la khyab pas chen po bcu zhes gsungs pa de
NK095(ce)001:5790: yis 'bad rtsol gang yang mi dgos pas na lus
NK095(ce)001:5791: ngag gi bya byed gang yang med par snang ba
NK095(ce)001:5792: rgya yan / shes pa rang grol rig pa gtad
NK095(ce)001:5793: med du btang nas rang bzhin chen po bcu la
NK095(ce)001:5794: blang dor re dogs kyis ma btsal bas gol sa
NK095(ce)001:5795: dang sgrib pa drug drug bcu po yi zhes nges
NK095(ce)001:5796: thob kyi theg pa drug po re re bzhin lta
NK095(ce)001:5797: rgya yan / ba dang / dam tshig dang /
NK095(ce)001:5805: man ngag gi gol sgrib bcu rer phye bas a
NK095(ce)001:5806: nu la gol sa ma h+aa la sogs pa 'og
NK095(ce)001:5807: ma lnga po'i rang bzhin bcur gol ba'i chas dbye
NK095(ce)001:5809: sgrib pa gol ma a ti'i rang bzhin bcu la bsgrib pa'i cha bcu yod pas drug cu dang /
NK095(ce)001:5810: de'i 'gros kyis ma h+aa yo gar gol sa bzhi
NK095(ce)001:5811: bcu dang sgrib pa nyi shu ste drug cu dang
NK095(ce)001:5812: / yo ga la gol sgrib gnyis ka sum cu re ste drug cu dang /
NK095(ce)001:5813: u pa la gol sa nyi shu dang sgrib pa bzhi bcu ste drug cu dang /
NK095(ce)001:5814: kri ya la gol sa bcu dang sgrib pa lnga bcu ste drug cu dang /
NK095(ce)001:5815: mdo sde la sgrib pa drug cu yod pas de
NK095(ce)001:5816: ltar drug cu tshan drug sdom pas sum brgya drug
NK095(ce)001:5817: cu yi gol sgrib mtha' yas pa kun 'byung ba
NK095(ce)001:5818: med par ma zad lta ba ye 'byams chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:5819: dgongs pa rang byung ye shes kyi rang bzhin mngon
NK095(ce)001:5820: du 'gyur bas rtsol grub kun las 'das te bde
NK095(ce)001:5821: bar gnas pa yin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:5823: mtshan nyid ma 'gags sna tshogs cir yang 'char //
NK095(ce)001:5824: dbang po gcer mthong cir snang chos nyid gsal //
NK095(ce)001:5825: snang ba rgya yan rig pa gang dgar bde //
NK095(ce)001:5826: ma bcos rnal 'dug rig pa khong klod bde //
NK095(ce)001:5827: shes pa bag yang byar med skyes bu bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:5828: grim lhod med par lus sems gang dgar bzhag /sus kyang ma bcos rang gis rang nyid gsal //
NK095(ce)001:5829: rtsol sgrub med par chos nyid bde gdal bas //
NK095(ce)001:5830: ye nas yin pas bcos su ga la yod //
NK095(ce)001:5831: gcig pur ma bcos glod na rang grol bde //
NK095(ce)001:5833: bzhi pa thams cad byang chub sems su bstan pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:5834: kye sems dpa' chen po ji ltar snang zhing srid
NK095(ce)001:5835: pa'i chos rnams thams cad kun rang gi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5836: snying po byang chub sems kyi rang rtsal 'ba' zhig
NK095(ce)001:5837: mngon du phyung gis te mngon du byung ba tsam
NK095(ce)001:5838: las kun byed byang chub kyi sems 'di ma yin
NK095(ce)001:5839: par nyid kyi rang bzhin las gzhan pa'i rang mtshan
NK095(ce)001:5840: gyi chos su grub pa ni gzhan zhig na yod
NK095(ce)001:5841: par ma bshad pas 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams
NK095(ce)001:5842: la gzhan du ma rtogs shig par kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:5843: nyid kyis lung ston pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:5844: sems dpa' chen po khyod kyis yang rab a ti'i
NK095(ce)001:5845: skal ba dang ldan pa'i 'khor gyi tshogs dngos su
NK095(ce)001:5846: 'dus pa rnams la ngas ji ltar lung bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:5847: bzhin du lung ston pa dang phyi rabs rjes 'jug
NK095(ce)001:5848: gi tshogs rnams la yang de bzhin du lung ston
NK095(ce)001:5851: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las gol
NK095(ce)001:5852: sgrib skyon sel gyi le'u ste dgu pa'i 'grel pa'o
NK095(ce)001:5853: ////bdun pa thams cad byang chub sems su 'dus shing
NK095(ce)001:5854: sems la snang ba'i le'u bcu pa la gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:5858: de ltar gol sgrib spang tshul dang bcas pa bstan
NK095(ce)001:5859: pa'i rjes de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed
NK095(ce)001:5860: rgyal pos nyid kyi rang bzhin stong gsal thugs rje
NK095(ce)001:5861: gsum gyi rtsal las ston 'khor bstan pa ste phun
NK095(ce)001:5862: sum tshogs pa gsum du snang ba'i tshul 'di gsungs
NK095(ce)001:5863: so // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:5864: phun sum tshogs pa'i rang bzhin spyir bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5867: kye sems dpa' chen po kun byed nga yi rang
NK095(ce)001:5868: bzhin las sku gsum gyi phun sum tshogs pa thams
NK095(ce)001:5869: cad byung ba'i tshul 'di nyon cig /de yang ji
NK095(ce)001:5870: ltar zhe na kun byed nga la ston pa dang
NK095(ce)001:5871: bstan pa la sogs pa thams cad 'dus shing tshogs
NK095(ce)001:5872: pa'i phyir na de phyir ston 'khor la sogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5873: chos rnams la phun sum tshogs pa zhes bya bar
NK095(ce)001:5874: bshad la / kun byed nga yi rang bzhin stong
NK095(ce)001:5875: pa dang gsal ba dang thugs rje rig pa'i cha
NK095(ce)001:5876: rnam pa gsum las sku gsum gyi ston pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:5877: dang de dag gi bstan pa dang so so'i 'khor
NK095(ce)001:5878: rnams byung ba'i phyir na 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams
NK095(ce)001:5879: kun byed pa'i rgyal po nyid ces ni rgyu mtshan
NK095(ce)001:5880: de la brten nas btags pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:5881: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:5882: kun byed kyi rang bzhin las phun sum tshogs pa byung bar bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5883: kun byed nyid la phun sum tshogs pa thams cad tshang bar bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5891: bshad lugs phun sum tshogs pa rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5896: de la snying po byang chub kyi sems las phun
NK095(ce)001:5897: sum tshogs pa rnams ji ltar byung ba'i tshul las
NK095(ce)001:5898: dang por ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:5899: snang ba'i tshul ni ston pa kun byed nga yi
NK095(ce)001:5900: snying po rang byung gi ye shes 'gyur ba med
NK095(ce)001:5901: pa lhun grub rtsal gyi klong las 'gags pa med
NK095(ce)001:5902: pa'i rang bzhin rnam pa gsum du byung ba de
NK095(ce)001:5903: ni sku gsum gyi ston pa rnam pa gsum du
NK095(ce)001:5905: de yang sangs rgyas chos kyi sku spros bral rang
NK095(ce)001:5906: byung gi ye shes 'pho 'gyur dang bral ba dang
NK095(ce)001:5907: / rig rtsal 'dzin med rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:5908: 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa'i ngo bo longs spyod
NK095(ce)001:5910: rtog bral blo las 'das pa'i ye shes thugs rje
NK095(ce)001:5911: kun khyab ye rdzogs chen po sprul pa'i sku dang
NK095(ce)001:5912: rnam pa gsum du bstan pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:5914: de lta bu'i sku gsum po de yi rang bzhin nam mtshan nyid bstan pa ni 'di ltar /
NK095(ce)001:5915: dang po chos kyi sku yi rang bzhin ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:5916: yin pa bstan pa ni chos dbyings byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:5917: kyi rang bzhin gdod nas ma skyes shing 'gags pa
NK095(ce)001:5918: med pas skye med spros pa dang bral ba gzung
NK095(ce)001:5919: 'dzin gyi mtshan ma kun dang bral ba'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5920: mi rtog mnyam pa chen po ka dag gi ngo
NK095(ce)001:5922: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi rang bzhin bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:5923: ni ji ltar na byang chub sems kyi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:5924: gsal ba'i cha gnyis snang 'dzin bral gyi klong nas
NK095(ce)001:5925: rang gdang 'gag med kyi rang rtsal gzugs sgra dri
NK095(ce)001:5926: ro la sogs pa 'doda pa'i longs spyod thams cad
NK095(ce)001:5927: ma btsal lhun gyis grub par 'gags med rang rtsal
NK095(ce)001:5928: du rdzogs shing rang snang rgyan du shar ba'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:5929: gyis longs spyod par bzhugs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5930: gang 'dul sprul pa'i sku yi rang bzhin ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:5931: bstan pa ni thugs rje'i rig rtsal go ma 'gags
NK095(ce)001:5932: pa'i cha las gdul bya gang la thabs gang gis
NK095(ce)001:5933: tshul ji ltar 'dul ba'i sgyu 'phrul gyi rol pa
NK095(ce)001:5934: tshad med pa'i sku ru sprul nas bzhugs pa ste
NK095(ce)001:5935: / bang mdzod 'phrul gyi lde'u mig las /
NK095(ce)001:5936: chos kyi sku ru bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:5937: mi rtog mnyam pa'i ngo bor bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:5938: longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:5939: sna tshogs chos la longs spyod cing //
NK095(ce)001:5940: ma spangs ye shes rgyan du bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:5941: sprul pa'i sku ru bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:5942: gang la gang dgos der sprul nas //
NK095(ce)001:5943: dgos pa phun sum tshogs par bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:5945: gnyis pa bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:5949: de lta bu'i sku gsum gyi ston pa gsum po
NK095(ce)001:5950: de yi bstan pa ni ji ltar zhe na de
NK095(ce)001:5951: la sprul sku'i bstan pa ni phyi mtshan nyid sde
NK095(ce)001:5952: gsum dang / longs sku'i bstan pa ni nang kri yog sde gsum dang /
NK095(ce)001:5953: chos sku'i bstan pa ni gsang ba nang rgyud sde
NK095(ce)001:5954: gsum ste rnam pa gsum du bstan pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:5955: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:5956: chos sku longs sku sprul sku'i bstan pa rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5958: gsang ba gsum spyir bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5961: a ti gsum bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:5963: de la ston pa chos sku'i bstan pa rnam pa gsum ni gang yin zhe na 'di lta ste /
NK095(ce)001:5964: 'og ma'i theg pa ba rnams kyis shin tu rtogs
NK095(ce)001:5965: par dka' zhing blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas
NK095(ce)001:5966: gsang ba gsum gyi rang bzhin du bstan pa ste
NK095(ce)001:5967: / de yang chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs gzhi
NK095(ce)001:5968: yi rang bzhin gnyug ma don gyi ye shes sam
NK095(ce)001:5969: chos nyid rnam dag gi rang bzhin de ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:5970: rtogs pa'i tshul ni ma h+aa yo ga bas chos
NK095(ce)001:5971: thams cad kyi rang bzhin gnas lugs don dam pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5972: bden pa dkor bdun ngo bo nyid med par lhun
NK095(ce)001:5974: de'i snang cha kun rdzob kyi chos thams cad dag
NK095(ce)001:5975: pa lha'i rang bzhin du gnas pa gnyis ye nas
NK095(ce)001:5976: gnyis su med pas bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod
NK095(ce)001:5977: yul dang bral bar rtogs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5978: a nu yo ga bas 'khor 'das su snang ba'i
NK095(ce)001:5979: chos thams cad gdod nas skye ba med pa dbyings
NK095(ce)001:5980: spros pa dang bral ba'i ngo bor gnas pa kun
NK095(ce)001:5981: tu bzang mo ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor dang
NK095(ce)001:5982: / de'i snang cha rig rtsal 'gag pa med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:5983: rol pa ris med mnyam pa chen por khyab gdal
NK095(ce)001:5984: du shar ba ni kun tu bzang po rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5985: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK095(ce)001:5986: dbyings dang ye shes de gnyis ye nas dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:5987: pa sras bde ba chen po byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:5988: dkyil 'khor te / de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin du rtogs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:5989: a ti yo ga bas sems nyid rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:5990: ye shes ngo bo ye stong spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:5991: ba ka dag skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin 'od
NK095(ce)001:5992: gsal ba'i snang cha thams cad lhun grub 'dus ma
NK095(ce)001:5993: byas pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pa gnyis dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:5994: pa'i rtsal snang 'khor 'das kyi rol pa sna tshogs
NK095(ce)001:5995: su 'char bas thugs rje kun khyab kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:5996: can te / de lta bu'i rig pa sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:5997: gyi ngo bor chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:5998: pa'i bdag nyid du rtogs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:5999: de ltar rtogs tshul gyi rim pa gsum du yod
NK095(ce)001:6000: pa las gsang ba bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor
NK095(ce)001:6001: ston pa ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK095(ce)001:6002: rab tu gsang ba mtshan bcas rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa a nu yo ga dang /
NK095(ce)001:6003: shin tu gsang ba yang gsang bla na med pa
NK095(ce)001:6004: mtshan med rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin ma nor
NK095(ce)001:6005: bar rtogs pa a ti yo ga dang gsum po
NK095(ce)001:6006: de gang zag dbang po rnon po'i rigs can rnams
NK095(ce)001:6007: las kun gyi spyod yul du gyur ba ma yin
NK095(ce)001:6008: pas na gsang bar bshad pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:6012: a ti gsum bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6013: dang po ma h+aa yo ga'i 'jug sgo ni dbang bzhis rang rgyud smin par byed pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6015: slob dpon gsang ba shes ra ba dang //
NK095(ce)001:6016: de ma thag pa bzhin pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:6018: de yang rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po gsang ba sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ltar na /
NK095(ce)001:6020: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK095(ce)001:6021: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK095(ce)001:6022: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK095(ce)001:6023: zhes pa ltar rang don nus pa'i dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu dang /
NK095(ce)001:6024: gzhan don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga /
NK095(ce)001:6025: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la gsang ba
NK095(ce)001:6026: zab mo'i dbang gsum ste dbang mchog bco brgyad du
NK095(ce)001:6027: gsungs pa sogs rgyud sde so so'i dbang bzhi la
NK095(ce)001:6028: dbye bsdu'i khyad par mang du yod la /
NK095(ce)001:6029: sgrub sde thams cad kyi spyi bka' bka' brgyad bde
NK095(ce)001:6030: gshegs 'dus pa ltar na gdul bya zhe sdang can
NK095(ce)001:6031: sgrol ba lam du khyer ba'i phyir phyi dbang rdzas
NK095(ce)001:6033: nga rgyal can lha lam du khyer ba'i phyir nang dbang lus la brten nas bskur ba /
NK095(ce)001:6034: 'dod chags can sbyor ba lam du khyer ba'i phyir gsang dbang yun la brten nas bskur ba /
NK095(ce)001:6035: gti mug can rnam rtog lam du khyer ba'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:6036: de kho na nyid kyi dbang sems la brten nas
NK095(ce)001:6038: sgrub sde'i dgos bka' yang phur ma gshin sogs la
NK095(ce)001:6039: so so'i zab khyad sgrub dbang gi lugs su bskur
NK095(ce)001:6040: ba mang du yod kyang spyi rigs nas bsdu na
NK095(ce)001:6041: bla med kyi dbang thams cad dbang bzhi'i khungs su
NK095(ce)001:6043: 'di dag gi bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni le'u so brgyad pa nas ston la /
NK095(ce)001:6044: tshul khrims ni le'u zhe drug par ston pas 'dir ma spros so //
NK095(ce)001:6045: lta ba ni gong du bstan pa ltar chos thams
NK095(ce)001:6046: cad dag mnyam bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod yul
NK095(ce)001:6047: dang bral par gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6049: don dam par chos thams cad ye stong skye ba
NK095(ce)001:6050: med pa'i ngo bor gnas pas bskyed bya skyed byed
NK095(ce)001:6051: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin yin pa la kun
NK095(ce)001:6054: phyag rgya phra rags te ting nge 'dzin gyi rim
NK095(ce)001:6055: pa gsum dang bsnyen sgrub yan lag dang bcas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6056: tshul gyis snod bcud dag pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK095(ce)001:6057: bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston cing rdzogs rim
NK095(ce)001:6058: kyang rtsa thig rlung gsum la gnad du bsnun pas
NK095(ce)001:6059: gsal stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes bskyed
NK095(ce)001:6060: pa sogs la brten nas lam bsgrub pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6061: spyod pa ni chos thams cad la blang dor med
NK095(ce)001:6062: pa'i ngang nas sbyor sgrol la sogs pa'i spyod pa
NK095(ce)001:6063: rlabs po che la bsten nas /
NK095(ce)001:6064: 'bras bu ni gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK095(ce)001:6065: mthar thug gi 'bras bu yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob par 'dod pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6066: de lta bu'i gsang ba mchog gi don ston par
NK095(ce)001:6067: byed pa de ni bskyed rim gtso bor ston pas
NK095(ce)001:6068: gsang ba bskyed pa'i rim pa zhes su bshad pa'o
NK095(ce)001:6069: // gnyis pa a nu yo ga la /
NK095(ce)001:6072: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK095(ce)001:6073: sgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK095(ce)001:6074: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK095(ce)001:6075: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:6077: a nu yo ga'i dkyil 'khor du phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo bcu /
NK095(ce)001:6078: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bcu gcig /sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bcu gsum /
NK095(ce)001:6079: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo gnyis bcas dbang mchog
NK095(ce)001:6080: sum cu rtsa drug gis smin par byed pa yin
NK095(ce)001:6081: no // lta ba ni thun mong gi spyod yul
NK095(ce)001:6082: du ma gyur pas gsang ba mtshan bcas rdzogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6083: rim pa gtso bor ston pas sam bskyed sngags brjod
NK095(ce)001:6084: pa tsam gyis snod bcud lha'i dkyil 'khor du rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:6085: par bsgom pas rdzogs pa a nu yo ga zhes
NK095(ce)001:6086: su bstan pa yis chos thams cad rig stong gnyis
NK095(ce)001:6087: su med pa bde chen byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK095(ce)001:6088: 'khor du gtan la phab pa ni gong du bstan
NK095(ce)001:6090: sgom pa ni snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK095(ce)001:6091: cad thog mar gang las snang ba'i gzhi nang gi
NK095(ce)001:6092: lus kyi rtsa rlung thig le sems dang bcas pa
NK095(ce)001:6093: rdo rje bzhi'i rang bzhin du rtogs pa'i shes rab
NK095(ce)001:6094: la brten nas ma h+aa yo ga ltar ting nge
NK095(ce)001:6095: 'dzin gsum gyis lha bskyed pa'i spros pa la mi
NK095(ce)001:6096: rtog cing / ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams
NK095(ce)001:6097: cad la so sor rtog mi dgos par nang gi
NK095(ce)001:6098: rtsa rlung thig le rnams lam du slong na thams
NK095(ce)001:6099: cad dag pa ye shes su 'char ba dang ma
NK095(ce)001:6100: slong na ma dag 'khor ba'i snang ba dbang med
NK095(ce)001:6101: du 'byung bar shes nas rtsa rlung thig le la
NK095(ce)001:6102: brten pa'i rdo rje'i bzlas pa dang lus kyi 'khrul
NK095(ce)001:6103: 'khor dang sbyor ba bzhi ldan gyi rlung bum pa
NK095(ce)001:6105: khyad par du rang lus dang gzhan lus kyi thabs
NK095(ce)001:6106: la brten nas bde stong lhan gcig skyes pa'i ye
NK095(ce)001:6107: shes mngon du byed pa'i mtshan bcas kyi rdzogs rim
NK095(ce)001:6109: lha sgom pa'i tshul kyang ting nge 'dzin dang shes
NK095(ce)001:6110: rab zab mo dang ldan pas lha'i sa bon nam
NK095(ce)001:6111: snying po bskyed sngags brjod pa tsam gyis rang rgyud
NK095(ce)001:6112: kyi phung khams skye mched thams cad rnam par dag
NK095(ce)001:6113: pa ye nas lhar bzhugs pa nyid chu las nya
NK095(ce)001:6114: 'phar ba ltar skad cig gis gsal bar byas nas
NK095(ce)001:6115: rang gi lus kyi gnas lugs rdo rje phung po'i
NK095(ce)001:6116: grong khyer yin pas skye mched rnams dag pa lha'i
NK095(ce)001:6120: byin gyis rlabs kyi spyod pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:6121: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi spyod pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:6122: dper na nam mkha' rgyal po'am //
NK095(ce)001:6123: ji ltar me dpung chu bo 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:6124: zhes gsung pa ltar dbyings ye gnyis med du rtogs
NK095(ce)001:6125: pa'i byin rlabs kyi spyod pa nam mkha' lta bu
NK095(ce)001:6126: / dug lnga ye shes su dbang bsgyur ba'i spyod
NK095(ce)001:6127: pa rgyal pos mnga' ris la dbang bsgyur ba lta
NK095(ce)001:6128: bu'am me dpung gis bud shing bsreg pa lta bu
NK095(ce)001:6129: / / srid zhi mnyam nyid du rtogs pa'i lta
NK095(ce)001:6130: ba dang ldan pas spyod pa blang dor gnyis su
NK095(ce)001:6131: med pa'i thabs kyi spyod pa rgyun mi chad pa
NK095(ce)001:6132: chu bo'i rgyun lta bu rnams so //
NK095(ce)001:6134: de lta bu rnal 'byor zab mo la brten nas
NK095(ce)001:6135: 'dun pa sems pa'i rnal 'byor la sogs pa'i lam
NK095(ce)001:6136: lnga dang 'gyur dbang ma nges pa'i sa la sogs
NK095(ce)001:6137: pa sa bcu gcig po myur du bgrod nas sku
NK095(ce)001:6138: bzhi ye shes lnga yi bdag nyid bde ba chen
NK095(ce)001:6139: po sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang gi sku mngon du
NK095(ce)001:6140: thob par 'dod pa de ni nang gi shes rab
NK095(ce)001:6141: dang ting 'dzin la brten pa'i lam gsang ba yongs
NK095(ce)001:6142: su rdzogs pa yin par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6143: gsum pa a ti yo ga ni /
NK095(ce)001:6144: shin tu gsang ba theg pa'i rtse rgyal rdzogs pa chen po ji ltar bstan pa yi tshul la /
NK095(ce)001:6146: dbang rdzogs pa rang byung las /
NK095(ce)001:6147: spros bcas spros pa med pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:6148: shin tu spros med rab spros med //
NK095(ce)001:6149: dbang ni rnam pa bzhi yis kyang //
NK095(ce)001:6150: skal pa ldan la smin par bya //
NK095(ce)001:6151: zhes gsungs pa ltar dbang bzhi pa la nang gses su phye ba'i spros bcas bum pa'i dbang dang /
NK095(ce)001:6153: shin tu spros med shes rab ye shes kyi dbang /
NK095(ce)001:6154: rab tu spros med don dam tshig gi dbang bzhi'am
NK095(ce)001:6155: rig pa'i rtsal dbang la rten nas smin par byed
NK095(ce)001:6156: pa'o // lta ba ni ji ltar snang ba'i chos
NK095(ce)001:6157: rnams thams cad ni rtsa ba rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:6158: shes snying po byang chub sems su 'dus shing byang
NK095(ce)001:6159: chub kyi sems sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag
NK095(ce)001:6160: nyid du gnas pa ni spang blang bsal bzhag thams
NK095(ce)001:6161: cad dang bral ba yin pas ma h+aa yo ga
NK095(ce)001:6162: ltar ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum gyis byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:6163: sems gsar du ma bskyed la /
NK095(ce)001:6164: a nu yo ga ltar snying po yig 'bru brjod
NK095(ce)001:6165: pa'i sgo nas lha'i dkyil 'khor du rdzogs par ma
NK095(ce)001:6166: byas par kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga ni
NK095(ce)001:6167: ye nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:6168: bzhin ma btsal lhun gyis grub pas rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:6169: po ste / de lta bu'i snying po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:6170: kyi sems nga la ma rdzogs pa yi 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:6171: kyi chos de ni gang yang med la /
NK095(ce)001:6172: nga yi rang bzhin sku gsum gyi ldog pas rnam
NK095(ce)001:6173: pa gsum du bstan pa ni don la rdzogs chen
NK095(ce)001:6174: byang chub kyi sems su ngo bor dbyer med pa
NK095(ce)001:6175: gcig pu'i rang bzhin la ldog pa tsam du de
NK095(ce)001:6176: ltar gsum du bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6177: des na chos thams cad rig pa byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:6178: kyi rang bzhin du ye nas sangs rgyas par lta
NK095(ce)001:6179: ba yin no // sgom pa ni de lta bu'i
NK095(ce)001:6180: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs mthar thug pa rig
NK095(ce)001:6181: par byang chub kyi sems de la rtsol bas sgom
NK095(ce)001:6182: du med cing yengs su ye nas med pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:6183: bzhin bab kyi bsam gtan ngang bzhag chu bo'i rgyun
NK095(ce)001:6184: gyi ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6185: spyod pa ni cir snang thams cad chos nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:6186: rol pa nyag gcig tu shar bas ched du rtsol
NK095(ce)001:6187: ba'i blang dor gang yang med par lhun 'byams byar
NK095(ce)001:6188: med chen po gang shar shugs 'byung gi tshul kyis
NK095(ce)001:6190: a ti yo ga'i spyod pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:6191: lta sgom srog dang ldan pa yis //
NK095(ce)001:6192: shugs las byung ba'i spyod pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:6193: ji ltar smyon pa'i spyod pa bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:6194: gang la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK095(ce)001:6196: 'bras bu ni ye nas sku gsum gyi yon tan
NK095(ce)001:6197: thams cad ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul du
NK095(ce)001:6198: gnas pa nyid ji lta ba bzhin du mngon du
NK095(ce)001:6199: thob par 'dod pa de ni shin tu gsang ba
NK095(ce)001:6200: rdzogs pa chen por bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6201: de lta bu'i shin tu gsang ba las kyang yang
NK095(ce)001:6202: gsang bla na med pa ma h+aa a nu a
NK095(ce)001:6203: ti gsum po de ni ston pa chos kyi sku'i
NK095(ce)001:6204: bstan pa yin par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6205: gnyis pa longs sku'i bstan pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:6206: nang pa gsum spyir bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6209: yo ga gsum bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6211: de la ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi
NK095(ce)001:6212: bstan pa ni phyi nang gi chos rnams la blang
NK095(ce)001:6213: dor gyi bya ba byed pa'i phyir na phyi bya
NK095(ce)001:6214: ba dang phyi'i dka' thub la brten nas nang gi
NK095(ce)001:6215: don rig par byed pas dka' thub rig byed kyi
NK095(ce)001:6216: theg pa zhes grags pa kri ya u pa yo
NK095(ce)001:6217: ga yi sde gsum du bstan pa ste de dag
NK095(ce)001:6218: ni ston pa longs sku'i bstan pa yin no zhes
NK095(ce)001:6219: spyir bstan pa'o // gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum las /
NK095(ce)001:6221: 'di ltar lus ngag gi bya ba khrus dang gtsang
NK095(ce)001:6222: sbra la sogs pa byed pa'i rtog pa can gyi
NK095(ce)001:6223: sde ba bya ba'i rgyud kyi thog ma'i 'jug sgo
NK095(ce)001:6224: ni / ye shes thig le las /
NK095(ce)001:6225: chu yi dbang bskur dbu rgyan dag /bya ba'i rgyud la rab tu grags //
NK095(ce)001:6226: zhes gsungs pa ltar bum pa'i dbang gis chos sku
NK095(ce)001:6227: dang cod pan dbang gis gzugs sku'i nus pa 'jog
NK095(ce)001:6229: de'i 'khor du me tog gang la phog pa'i lha
NK095(ce)001:6230: yi bzlas lung sbyin pa rdo rje slob ma'i dbang
NK095(ce)001:6231: dang / bar chad zhi zhing bgegs gzhom pa bya ba bkru bsrung ba'i dbang dang /
NK095(ce)001:6232: 'byor pa rgyas byed bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang rnams bskur ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:6233: lta ba ni don dam par chos thams cad rang
NK095(ce)001:6234: bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa yod med snang stong
NK095(ce)001:6235: gi spros pa'i mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i snang cha
NK095(ce)001:6236: kun rdzob rigs gsum lha'i rang bzhin du bltas te
NK095(ce)001:6237: bsgom na mthar thug rang nyid lha de dang de'i
NK095(ce)001:6238: ngo bor 'gyur du rung ba'i nges shes khyad par
NK095(ce)001:6239: can dang ldan pa'i sgo nas sgom pa ni mtshan
NK095(ce)001:6240: bcas dang mtshan med gnyis las /
NK095(ce)001:6241: dang por rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK095(ce)001:6242: gyis te ting 'dzin gyi ngang nas mtshan bcas lha'i
NK095(ce)001:6243: ting 'dzin ji ltar bsgom par bya ba'i tshul ni
NK095(ce)001:6244: sha chang sgog tsong la sogs pa spang zhing khrus
NK095(ce)001:6245: dang gtsang sbra la gnas pa phyi rdzas dang yo
NK095(ce)001:6246: byad dag pa / bzlas brjod dang bsam gtan gyi
NK095(ce)001:6247: de kho na nyid ni nang sngags dang ting 'dzin
NK095(ce)001:6248: byad dag pa / dag pa dang / bdag dang
NK095(ce)001:6249: lha'i de kho na nyid ni gsang ba rtog tshogs
NK095(ce)001:6250: lha dang dkyil 'khor du da ga pa ste dag
NK095(ce)001:6251: pa gsum dang ldan par sgom dgos pas /
NK095(ce)001:6252: de tshul la 'jug pa na blang dor la rnam
NK095(ce)001:6253: par rtog pa'i sgo nas phur bu dang pa sangs
NK095(ce)001:6254: sogs gza' skar bzang ba dang mgo dang rgyal la
NK095(ce)001:6255: sogs pa rgyu skar bzang ba dang yar gyi tshes
NK095(ce)001:6256: brgyad la sogs pa dus tshod bzang po'i 'phrod sbyor
NK095(ce)001:6257: dang bstun pa'i sgo nas 'jug cing /
NK095(ce)001:6258: de yang de kho na nyid bzhi'i sgo nas bsgom par gsungs pa las /
NK095(ce)001:6259: dang po bdag gi de kho na nyid ni lta
NK095(ce)001:6260: ba'i ngang du 'jog pa ste gong du bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:6261: ltar la / gnyis pa lha'i de kho na nyid ni spyir kri ya lha drug tu grags pa /
NK095(ce)001:6263: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang //
NK095(ce)001:6264: phyag rgya mtshan ma lha drug go //
NK095(ce)001:6265: zhes pas stong pa'i lha bdag gi de kho na nyid lta ba' ngang la 'jog pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6266: yi ge'i lha kun rdzob zla dkyil gyi rnam par bsgom pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6267: sgra'i lha ni de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags rang sgra sgrog par bsgom pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6268: gzugs kyi lha zla dkyil sngags phreng dang bcas pa
NK095(ce)001:6269: las 'od zer spro bsdus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa
NK095(ce)001:6270: bsgrub ste sngags phreng zla dkyil dang bcas pa yongs
NK095(ce)001:6271: su gyur pa las rigs gsum gyi lha gang yin
NK095(ce)001:6273: phyag rgya'i lha de la rigs gang yin gyi lhas dam rgyas 'debs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6274: mtshan ma'i lha ni spyod lam kun tu lha de'i
NK095(ce)001:6275: snang ba dang mi 'bral ba ste de ltar du
NK095(ce)001:6277: skabs 'dir mngon par byang chub pa lnga'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:6278: bsgom par gsungs pa gang ltar yang dbye bsdu tsam
NK095(ce)001:6279: las don gnad mthun pa 'dra la /
NK095(ce)001:6280: de la mngon byang lnga ni /
NK095(ce)001:6285: sku yongs rdzogs las mngon par byang chub pa lnga dang ni /
NK095(ce)001:6286: lha gtso 'khor yongs rdzogs su bsgom pa ni ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK095(ce)001:6287: lha de dag la rang rang gi rigs kyis byin
NK095(ce)001:6288: gyis brlab pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang
NK095(ce)001:6289: / rang rigs kyi sku dang ye shes dang gzung
NK095(ce)001:6290: dang ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pas dbang bskur ba
NK095(ce)001:6291: ni dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK095(ce)001:6292: phyag mchod bstod pa bya ba ni mchod pa'i cho 'phrul ste /
NK095(ce)001:6293: de lta bu'i cho 'phrul bzhi la sogs pa'i thabs
NK095(ce)001:6294: sna tshogs kyis bdag dam tshig pa dang ye shes
NK095(ce)001:6295: kyi lha gnyis ni rje bo dang khol po'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:6296: du bsgom zhing / lha mnyes pa'i ched du phyag
NK095(ce)001:6297: 'tshal ba dang dag pa gsum ldan gyis mchod pa
NK095(ce)001:6298: 'bul ba sogs yan lag bdun pa dang bstod pa
NK095(ce)001:6299: du bsgom zhing / rnams bya ba'o // gsum pa bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK095(ce)001:6300: bsam gtan phyi ma'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:6301: sgra dang sems dang gzhi la gzhol //
NK095(ce)001:6302: gsang sngags mi 'gyur gzhi la gnas //
NK095(ce)001:6303: yan lag ma nyams gsang sngags bzlas //
NK095(ce)001:6305: gzhi dang po ni lha ye shes pa mdun du bsgom pa /
NK095(ce)001:6306: phyi ma ni bdag nyid lhar gsal ba /
NK095(ce)001:6307: sems ni de dag gi thugs kar zla dkyil bsam pa /
NK095(ce)001:6308: sgra ni de'i steng du sngags phreng rang sgra sgrogs par bsam pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6309: de ltar yan lag bzhi po ma nyams par bzlas pa bya ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:6310: bzhi pa bsam gtan gyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK095(ce)001:6312: gsang sngags mer gnas dngos grub ster //
NK095(ce)001:6313: sgrar gnas rnal 'byor ster bar dran //
NK095(ce)001:6314: sgra mthas thar ba ster bar byed //
NK095(ce)001:6315: 'di dag de nyid gsum po yin //
NK095(ce)001:6316: zhes pas de nyid gsum las dang po mer gnas
NK095(ce)001:6317: ni bdag mdun gyi thugs kar me 'bar ba'i dbus
NK095(ce)001:6318: su zla ba la sngags phreng bkod nas srog sdom
NK095(ce)001:6319: pa'i sbyor bas bsgom pa ste des ni las gzhi'i
NK095(ce)001:6321: de nyid gnyis pa sgra gnas ni sngags kyi yi
NK095(ce)001:6322: ge rnams las rang sgra dril bu'i sgra ltar bsam
NK095(ce)001:6323: pa'o // des ni rnal 'byor ste zhi gnas skye ba'i rten byed pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6324: de nyid gsum pa sgra mtha' ni sgra yi rgyun
NK095(ce)001:6325: je phrar song nas mthar mi dmigs par 'jog pa
NK095(ce)001:6326: ste des ni thar pa ste lhag mthong skye ba'i
NK095(ce)001:6327: rten byed pa'o // gnyis pa mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK095(ce)001:6328: de ltar bzlas sgom gyi rjes su gtang rag gi
NK095(ce)001:6329: mchod bstod dang bzod gsol dge bsngo rnams byas mthar
NK095(ce)001:6330: lha snang mi dmigs par bsdus nas stong pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:6331: mtshan ma med par bsgom pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6332: spyod pa ni khrus gsum byed pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6333: gos gsum barje ba la sogs pa gtsang sbra spyod
NK095(ce)001:6334: cing sbyin sreg dang mchod pa sogs sngags 'grub byed
NK095(ce)001:6335: kyi cho ga'i yan lag rnams la brtson par byed
NK095(ce)001:6336: pa'o // 'bras bu ni de lta bu'i mtshan bcas
NK095(ce)001:6337: dang mtshan med kyi lam la brten nas 'brar bu
NK095(ce)001:6338: gzhan nas thob tu med kyang yod par lta ba'i
NK095(ce)001:6341: thugs rigs mi bskyod pa ste rigs gsum rdo rje
NK095(ce)001:6342: 'dzin pa'i sa'am sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:6343: ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can gyi dngos grub 'dod
NK095(ce)001:6344: pa ste / 'di bas kun rdzob dang don dam gnyis ka sgyu mar bshad ces pa'i don ni /
NK095(ce)001:6345: dam pa rin po che'i theg spyi'i 'grel bar /
NK095(ce)001:6346: lta ba ni phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang nang
NK095(ce)001:6347: bcud kyi sems can sgyu ma rmi lam tsam du
NK095(ce)001:6348: chos can dang dngos por snang ba 'di rnams don
NK095(ce)001:6349: la sems yin cing sems nyid kyang gdod ma nas
NK095(ce)001:6350: stong zhing skye ba med pa don dam par spros
NK095(ce)001:6351: pa'i mtha' yod med rtag chad bzhi dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:6352: las kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid du snang ba'o
NK095(ce)001:6353: zhes dang / kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid ni
NK095(ce)001:6354: 'khrul ba'i ngo la ji ltar snang yang de nyid
NK095(ce)001:6355: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs gsum mgon po'i ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:6356: zhes dang / nyid yin te / zhes sogs gsungs
NK095(ce)001:6357: pa ltar don dam du chos thams cad spros pa
NK095(ce)001:6358: dang bral bzhin du sgyu ma lta bu'i snang ba
NK095(ce)001:6359: mi 'gag pas sgyu ma lta bu dang /
NK095(ce)001:6360: kun rdzob rigs gsum lha'i rnam par snang ba yang sgyu ma lta bur bshad pa'am /
NK095(ce)001:6361: yang na kun rdzob la yang log gnyis su phye
NK095(ce)001:6362: ba'i snga ma mtho 'jam rtsub pa'i dngos po rnams
NK095(ce)001:6363: rigs gsum mgon po'i rang bzhin du 'dod pa yang
NK095(ce)001:6364: dag kun rdzob bam don dam pa dang phyi ma
NK095(ce)001:6365: dbu ma man chad kyi yang log gi kun rdzob
NK095(ce)001:6366: tu bzhag pa rnams te de gnyis ka sgyu ma
NK095(ce)001:6367: lta bu'i rang bzhin du bshad pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6369: gnyis pa u pa ya ni /
NK095(ce)001:6370: lta ba yo ga dang spyod pa kri ya ltar
NK095(ce)001:6371: gnyis su 'byed par byed pas gnyis ka'i rgyud ces
NK095(ce)001:6372: bya bar grags pa de yi 'jug sgo ni /
NK095(ce)001:6374: rdo rje dril bu de bzhin ming //
NK095(ce)001:6375: spyod pa'i rgyud du rab tu gsal //
NK095(ce)001:6376: zhes gsungs pa ltar chu dang cod pan gyi steng du spyod rgyud rang gi dgos dbang /
NK095(ce)001:6377: rdo rje dril bu ming dbang rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:6378: me long mig thur chos bshad rjes gnang sogs mtha' brten dang bcas par bskur ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:6380: dka' ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim las /
NK095(ce)001:6381: gnyis ka'i rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:6382: lta spyod gong 'og rjes su mthun //
NK095(ce)001:6383: zhes gsungs pa lta bu las bye brag chos kyi
NK095(ce)001:6384: dbyings mtha' thams cad dang bral ba dang gnyis su
NK095(ce)001:6385: med pa rig pa ye shes kyi byin rlabs rigs
NK095(ce)001:6386: bzhi'i lhar shar ba nyid spun grogs kyi tshul du
NK095(ce)001:6387: bsgom na mthar thug rang nyid lha de dang de'i
NK095(ce)001:6388: ngo bor 'grub tu rung ba'i tshul la yid ches
NK095(ce)001:6389: kyi lta ba dang ldan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6390: sgom pa la mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis las /
NK095(ce)001:6391: dang po ni rnam snang mngon byang las /
NK095(ce)001:6392: yi ge dang ni yi ge sbyar //
NK095(ce)001:6393: de bzhin gzhi las gzhir gyur nyid //
NK095(ce)001:6394: shin tu bsdams pa'i yid las ni //
NK095(ce)001:6396: zhes gsungs pa ltar bdag gnas rnal 'byor rnams sngon du 'gro bas /
NK095(ce)001:6397: yi ge dang po don dam byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:6398: nyid kyi ngang las de'i snang cha kun rdzob zla
NK095(ce)001:6399: dkyil gyi rnam par bsgom pa /
NK095(ce)001:6400: yi ge gnyis pa de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags rang sgra sgrog par bsam pa /
NK095(ce)001:6401: gzhi dang po sngags phreng zla dkyil bcas pa yongs
NK095(ce)001:6402: su gyur pa las rang nyid lhar bsgom nas sngags
NK095(ce)001:6403: rgya sogs kyis byin gyis rlob pa /
NK095(ce)001:6404: gzhi gnyis pa ye shes pa mdun du gsal ba'i
NK095(ce)001:6405: thugs kar zla dkyil la sngags phreng bkod nas srog
NK095(ce)001:6406: bsdam zhing dmigs pa rtse gcig pas bzlas pa byed
NK095(ce)001:6407: pa'o // mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor ni phung sogs
NK095(ce)001:6408: skye med du dpyad pas rtogs pa 'jug pa'i sems
NK095(ce)001:6409: pa'o // / de mi rtog pa'i ngo bor mngon sum du rtogs pa gnas pa'i sems /
NK095(ce)001:6410: de ltar ma rtogs pa la snying rje chen pos rjes su 'jug pa ldang ba'i sems te /
NK095(ce)001:6411: de ltar 'jug gnas ldang gsum dang sbyar ba'i byang chub kyi sems bsgom pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6412: spyod pa ni spyod rgyud dang mthun par khrus dang gtsang sbra sogs grogs tsam du bsten pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6413: 'bras bu ni gnas skabs su mngon shes la sogs
NK095(ce)001:6414: pa thun mong gi grub pa dang mthar thug rigs
NK095(ce)001:6415: bzhi'i sangs rgyas su 'grub par 'dod pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6416: 'on kyang rdzogs pa chen pos yas nas gzhal na
NK095(ce)001:6417: lta spyod gong 'og gi tshul gnyis la brten nas
NK095(ce)001:6418: 'dod pa'i don rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:6419: gcig bsgrub par byed pa de yang rgyu lta spyod
NK095(ce)001:6420: gnyis su yod par zhen pa'i spyod pas 'bras bu
NK095(ce)001:6421: sngon med pa'am gzhi la ma grub pa'i don zhig
NK095(ce)001:6422: sgrub par byed pas na dper na rten med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6423: nam mkha' stong pa la gcan gzan spyang mo nyung
NK095(ce)001:6424: bar byas kyang bza' ba'i dngos po ci yang thob
NK095(ce)001:6425: tu med pa dang 'dra ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:6426: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:6427: gnyis med rang gsal nyag gcig la //
NK095(ce)001:6428: nges med gnyis kyi cha 'dzin cing //
NK095(ce)001:6429: don la nges pa'i 'bras bu gcig /
NK095(ce)001:6431: gnyis kyis gnyis med ji ltar snyed //
NK095(ce)001:6434: lta spyod la blang dor gyi sgo nas 'jug par
NK095(ce)001:6435: byed pa'i theg pa phyi rgyud sde gsum zhes bya
NK095(ce)001:6436: ba'i nang nas sems kyi sgom pa gtso bor 'dod
NK095(ce)001:6437: pas gsang ba rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kyi thog ma'i
NK095(ce)001:6438: 'jug sgo ni / ye shes thig le las /
NK095(ce)001:6439: phyir mi ldog pa bum pa'i dbang //
NK095(ce)001:6440: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsal bar byas //
NK095(ce)001:6441: de ni slob dpon dbang zhes bya //
NK095(ce)001:6442: zhes gsungs pa ltar rig pa'i dbang lnga'i steng du slob dpon gyi dbang drug bskur ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:6443: de yang rig dbang ngam slob ma'i dbang lnga ni /
NK095(ce)001:6444: dkyil 'khor du zhugs shing dam tshig dang sdom pa bzung /
NK095(ce)001:6445: ye shes pa dbab cing me tog dor bas lhag pa'i lha nges par byas te /
NK095(ce)001:6446: las bum gyi khrus sngon du 'gro bas lha bum gyi dbang dang /
NK095(ce)001:6447: rigs gang yin gyi cod pan dang /
NK095(ce)001:6448: de'i rig kyi rdo rje dang /
NK095(ce)001:6449: de'i yu ba byas pa'i dril bu dang /
NK095(ce)001:6450: rang rigs dang mthun pa'i ming dbang rnams so //
NK095(ce)001:6451: dpon slob kyi dbang drug ni /
NK095(ce)001:6452: phyir mi ldog pa'i dbang dam tshig gsum bzung ba /
NK095(ce)001:6457: gzeng bstod rnams te sdom pas dbang bcu gcig po rnams bskur ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:6458: 'dir gsang ba'i dbang yang bla med kyi gsang dbang
NK095(ce)001:6459: dang mi mtshungs par dkyil 'khor du gsang ba'i 'jug
NK095(ce)001:6460: pas zhugs shing mthong ba la dkyil 'khor dang lha'i
NK095(ce)001:6462: dkyil 'khor gyi de nyid bcu dang las kyi rim
NK095(ce)001:6463: pa bstan par bya ba la gsang dbang du gsungs
NK095(ce)001:6464: so // lta ba ni don dam par chos thams
NK095(ce)001:6465: cad spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:6466: 'od gsal stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin du 'dod
NK095(ce)001:6467: so // la / kun rdzob tu snang ba'i dngos
NK095(ce)001:6468: po thams cad chos nyid rtogs pa'i byin rlabs las
NK095(ce)001:6469: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil
NK095(ce)001:6471: skye bos brtags pa'i snang ba rang rgyud pa thams cad don la ma grub par 'dod de /
NK095(ce)001:6473: yo ga don dam rnam dag pa'i //
NK095(ce)001:6474: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su //
NK095(ce)001:6475: rtogs pa'i byin brlabs lhar snang ba //
NK095(ce)001:6476: de phyir skye bo ltar snang 'khrul //
NK095(ce)001:6478: khyad par ba'i dbang du na /
NK095(ce)001:6479: kun gzigs mi pham pa'i zhal nas /
NK095(ce)001:6480: mnyam nyid kyi lta ba gong ma gnyis las khyad
NK095(ce)001:6481: par 'phags pa'i dbang gis bdag dang lha don la
NK095(ce)001:6482: mnyam par mthong ba'i nges shes kyis kun rdzob tu
NK095(ce)001:6483: yang chu la chu bzhin mnyam par byas te bsgoms
NK095(ce)001:6484: na / chos thams cad rang sems kyi snang ba
NK095(ce)001:6485: tsam yin pas ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang bsgyur na
NK095(ce)001:6486: ji ltar dmigs pa'i lha mngon du grub pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:6487: lha'i sku gsung thugs dang phrin las kyi bdag nyid
NK095(ce)001:6488: phyag rgya bzhi yi ngo bor 'bad pas bsgrub pas
NK095(ce)001:6489: de yi ngo bor 'grub pa'i nges pa khyad par
NK095(ce)001:6490: can gyi lta ba dang ldan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6491: zhes gsungs pa ltar gong ma gnyis las bden pa
NK095(ce)001:6492: gnyis ka khyad par du 'phags par shes par bya'o
NK095(ce)001:6493: // sgom pa la mtshan bcas dang mtshan med gnyis las dang po ni /
NK095(ce)001:6495: byang chub sems ni ma bskyed dang //
NK095(ce)001:6496: the tshom ldan pa nyid dang ni //
NK095(ce)001:6497: bka' bzhin du ni mi byed dang //
NK095(ce)001:6499: zhes gsungs pa'i skyon bzhi dang bral ba'i ldog phyogs
NK095(ce)001:6500: yon tan bzhi ldan gyi gang zag gis skyabs sems
NK095(ce)001:6502: chos thams cad la rnam par mi rtog pa stong
NK095(ce)001:6503: pa nyid kyi ngang las mngon byang lnga yi sgo
NK095(ce)001:6504: nas kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom pa ting
NK095(ce)001:6505: nge 'dzin dang gnas gsum byin gyis brlabs pa dang
NK095(ce)001:6506: / dbang bskur ba dang mchod pa'i cho 'phrul gyis
NK095(ce)001:6507: dkyil 'khor thams cad byin gyis brlabs te bdag dang
NK095(ce)001:6508: lha ye shes sems dpar te sems dpa' gnyis dbyer
NK095(ce)001:6509: med du bsgom par byas nas /
NK095(ce)001:6510: mchod pa'i bye brag me tog la sogs pa phyir yi mchod pa /
NK095(ce)001:6511: sgegs sogs nang gi mchod pa rig ma bcu drug gsang ba yi mchod pa gsum gyis mchod nas /
NK095(ce)001:6512: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po /
NK095(ce)001:6514: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK095(ce)001:6515: phrin las las kyi phyag rgya ste bzhi yis rang
NK095(ce)001:6516: gi sgo gsum bya ba dang bcas pa la lha'i
NK095(ce)001:6517: sku gsung thugs mdzad pa dang bcas pas rgyas btab
NK095(ce)001:6518: ste dam ye gnyis med kyi ngang nas bzlas pa
NK095(ce)001:6520: 'di la gtso bo tsam skyed pa dang po'i sbyor ba /
NK095(ce)001:6521: gtso 'khor yongs rdzogs bskyed pa dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog dang /
NK095(ce)001:6522: ye shes pa gzhugs pa sogs las rgyal mchog ste
NK095(ce)001:6523: de lta bu'i sgo nas ting nge 'dzin la brtson
NK095(ce)001:6524: pa ni rags pa lha la dmigs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6525: rdo rje la sogs pa'i phyag mtshan shin tu phra
NK095(ce)001:6526: ba sna rtse sogs su bsgoms nas mthar mi rtog
NK095(ce)001:6527: par 'jog pa ni phra ba phyag mtshan la dmigs
NK095(ce)001:6528: pa rnam pa gnyis su gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:6529: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK095(ce)001:6530: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i gnas lugs dang kun
NK095(ce)001:6531: rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi lha snang gnyis ka gnyis
NK095(ce)001:6532: su med pa'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6533: spyod pa ni gtsang sbra la sogs pa phyi'i kun
NK095(ce)001:6534: spyod grogs tsam du byas nas gtso bor nang gi
NK095(ce)001:6535: ting nge 'dzin zab mo dang ldan pa'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:6537: 'bras bu ni ji ltar 'dod pa'i don gnas skabs
NK095(ce)001:6538: su thun mong gi dngos grub dang mthar thug mchog
NK095(ce)001:6539: gi dngos grub rigs lnga stug po bkod pa'i sa
NK095(ce)001:6540: la mngon par sangs rgyas pa thob tu re ba
NK095(ce)001:6541: dang ldan pas / chags thogs med pa'i 'bras bu
NK095(ce)001:6542: ye nas grub zin pa de la rtsol ba'i re
NK095(ce)001:6543: ba 'jog pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'di yis kyang lta
NK095(ce)001:6544: spyod blang dor byed pas blang dor med pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:6547: dus dang grangs la ltos pa'i theg dman rnams //
NK095(ce)001:6548: mkha' la shar ba'i 'ja' tshon 'dzin pa ltar //
NK095(ce)001:6549: thug pa'i mtha' med zin pa'i dus med pas //
NK095(ce)001:6550: nan gyis rang sems byar med rtsol bas bcing //
NK095(ce)001:6552: de ltar bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kyi rgyud
NK095(ce)001:6553: sde gsum po de ni rgyal ba longs spyod rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:6554: pa'i sku yi bstan pa yin par bshad do //
NK095(ce)001:6555: gsum pa sprul sku'i bstan pa bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:6556: phyi pa gsum sbyir bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:6557: gang gi don du gsungs pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK095(ce)001:6558: 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa gsum gyi dbye ba don bsdu ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:6560: de la ston pa sprul pa'i sku yi bstan pa ni gang zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:6561: rang gi yongs 'dzin rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sogs la
NK095(ce)001:6562: ji ltar nyan cing thos pa'i don gzhan la ston
NK095(ce)001:6563: cing sgrogs par byed pas na thos sgrogs sam nyan
NK095(ce)001:6564: thos dang / srid pa tha ma'i tshe dge ba'i
NK095(ce)001:6565: bshes gnyen gzhan la mi brten par rang gi byang
NK095(ce)001:6566: chub rang gis thob par byed pas rang rgyal dang
NK095(ce)001:6567: thos dang / / theg pa dman pa las dmigs
NK095(ce)001:6568: pa chen po la sogs pa chen po bdun gyis
NK095(ce)001:6569: 'phags pa theg pa chen po byang chub bsgrub pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6570: ched du bya dka' ba'i spyod pa la sems mi
NK095(ce)001:6571: zhum par dpa' bas byang chub sems dpa'i mdo sde
NK095(ce)001:6572: gsum la phyi mtshan nyid theg pa zhes bzhag pa
NK095(ce)001:6573: thos dang / / ste / de yang so so'i
NK095(ce)001:6574: lam des rang 'bras mtshon par byed pas mtshan nyid
NK095(ce)001:6575: theg pa'am phyi'i kun spyod gtso bor ston pas phyi
NK095(ce)001:6576: pa zhes su bshad pa ste gsum du yod pa
NK095(ce)001:6577: thos dang / / ste / las / dang po nyan thos kyi theg pa'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK095(ce)001:6579: nyan thos bden bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug /zhes gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:6580: ltar 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi la blang dor 'jug
NK095(ce)001:6582: lta ba ni spyir nyan thos la nang gi dbye
NK095(ce)001:6583: ba bye brag smra ba dang mdo sde ba gnyis
NK095(ce)001:6584: su yod kyang thun mong du gzung 'dzin du snang
NK095(ce)001:6585: ba'i dngos po 'di thams cad la gnyen pos bcom
NK095(ce)001:6586: pa dang blos gzhig cing dpyad par byas na rags
NK095(ce)001:6587: pa'i snang ba thams cad don la ma grub par
NK095(ce)001:6588: du ma dang skad cig ma'i rang bzhin yin pas
NK095(ce)001:6589: gang zag gi bdag dang mtshan nyid mi mthun pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6590: phyir phung po bdag min la de las gzhan du
NK095(ce)001:6591: yang bdag yod par mi dmigs pas na gang zag
NK095(ce)001:6592: gi bdag med par rtogs kyang /
NK095(ce)001:6593: gzung 'dzin rags pa'i rtsom gzhi cha med gnyis don
NK095(ce)001:6594: dam du yod par 'dod cing kun byang gi chos
NK095(ce)001:6595: thams cad gzhi med du ma rtogs pas chos kyi
NK095(ce)001:6596: bdag yod par lta ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:6598: gang zag bdag med rtog kyang chos nyid bdag ma spangs //
NK095(ce)001:6599: chos kyi bdag ni gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang //
NK095(ce)001:6601: rtag chad gnyis las 'das pa ltar //
NK095(ce)001:6602: dper na chu bo gang g+aa bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:6603: gzung bya kun rdzob phar bsal nas //
NK095(ce)001:6604: don dam rngul phran rdzas su 'dod //
NK095(ce)001:6605: dper na g.yag rnga ne seng bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:6606: mdo sde bye brag rnam gnyis 'dod //
NK095(ce)001:6608: sgom pa ni 'dod chags kyi gnyen por mi sdug pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6609: zhe sdang gi gnyen por byams pa la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:6610: dug gsum gyi gnyen po so sor dang thun mong
NK095(ce)001:6611: du bsam gtan dang rnam thar sogs zhi gnas dang
NK095(ce)001:6612: bden bzhi rnam pa bcu drug bsgom pa lhag mthong
NK095(ce)001:6613: rnams so // spyod pa ni so sor thar pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6614: tshul khrims yongs su dag par bsrung ba dang sbyang
NK095(ce)001:6615: ba'i yon tan bcu gnyis la gnas par byed pa'o
NK095(ce)001:6616: rnams so // // 'bras bu ni gnas skabs kyi
NK095(ce)001:6617: 'bras bu rgyun zhugs la sogs pa bdun dang mthar
NK095(ce)001:6618: thug gi 'bras bu dgra bcom pa nyid thob pa'o
NK095(ce)001:6619: rnams so // // // gnyis pa rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK095(ce)001:6621: rang rgyal rten 'brel sgo nas 'jug /ces gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:6622: ltar rten 'brel bcu gnyis la lugs 'byung ldog tu
NK095(ce)001:6623: rtog cing dpyod pa'i sgo nas 'jug pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6624: lta ba ni gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa nyan thos dang 'dra ba la /
NK095(ce)001:6625: chos kyi bdag las nang gi shes pa skad cig
NK095(ce)001:6626: mar skyes pa'i rten 'brel gyi dbang gis phyi rol
NK095(ce)001:6627: gyi snang ba rmi lam gyi rol pa ltar snang
NK095(ce)001:6628: ba tsam las rdul phran cha med kyang ma grub
NK095(ce)001:6629: par rtogs kyang gzung ba'i dngos po de dag gi
NK095(ce)001:6630: snang gzhi shes pa skad cig cha med bden grub
NK095(ce)001:6631: tu 'dod pas bdag med phyed gnyis tsam rtogs pa
NK095(ce)001:6633: gang zag bdag med gong mthun des rtogs nas //
NK095(ce)001:6634: chos kyi khams la phyogs gcig bdag med pa //
NK095(ce)001:6635: de nyid mtshan mar ngos 'dzin pa //
NK095(ce)001:6636: rang rgyal zhes 'dod lta ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:6638: sgom pa ni bden pa bzhi dang rten 'brel lugs
NK095(ce)001:6639: 'byung bkag nas lugs ldog gi gnad la nges pa
NK095(ce)001:6641: spyod pa ni ngag gi chos mi gsung par lus
NK095(ce)001:6642: kyi brdas chos ston cing rju 'phrul ya ma zung
NK095(ce)001:6643: gi sems can la phan 'dogs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6645: gang gang don ni gang gang la //
NK095(ce)001:6646: ji lta ji ltar nyan 'dod pa //
NK095(ce)001:6647: de de la don de dang de //
NK095(ce)001:6648: sgra med kyang ni de ltar snang //
NK095(ce)001:6650: 'bras bu ni yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa'am rang rgyal dgra bcom pa'i go 'phang thob pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6651: gsum pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK095(ce)001:6653: mdo sde bden gnyis sgo nas 'jug /ces gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:6654: ltar kun rdzob tu sems can rnams kyi don du
NK095(ce)001:6655: smon 'jug byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis la
NK095(ce)001:6656: brten nas byang chub chen po'i lam la 'jug pa
NK095(ce)001:6657: dang / don dam par chos thams cad skye ba
NK095(ce)001:6658: med pa spros bral stong pa nyid du shes pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6661: chos dang gang zag gi bdag med gnyis ka rtogs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6662: de yang theg pa chen po'i mdo sde zab pa
NK095(ce)001:6663: dang rgya che ba'i phyogs so sor bkral tshul gyi
NK095(ce)001:6664: dbang gis dbu ma dang sems tsam pa gnyis su
NK095(ce)001:6665: yod pa las / dang po sems tsam pa ni
NK095(ce)001:6666: 'di ltar gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba'i chos 'di
NK095(ce)001:6667: dag thams cad ni don la grub pa med pa
NK095(ce)001:6668: kun tu brtags pa tsam gyis rang bzhin yin pas
NK095(ce)001:6669: kun rdzob kyi bden pa yin par 'dod la /
NK095(ce)001:6670: de dag gang las snang ba'i gzhi gzhan dbang gi
NK095(ce)001:6671: shes pa mthar thug pa rang rig rang gsal tsam
NK095(ce)001:6672: don dam par grub par 'dod pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6673: de'i steng na gzung 'dzin kun brtags kyi cha bdag
NK095(ce)001:6674: gnyis kyis stong pa'i chos dbyings de bzhin nyid chos
NK095(ce)001:6675: nyid kyi tshul tu yod pa ni yongs grub ste
NK095(ce)001:6676: de gnyis ni chos can dang chos nyid don dam
NK095(ce)001:6678: de la yang yul gyi rnam pa sna tshogs su
NK095(ce)001:6679: snang ba 'di rnams tha snyad du shes pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:6680: bzhin du bden par 'dod pa rnam bden pa dang
NK095(ce)001:6681: / mi bden pa rdzun snang tsam du 'dod pa
NK095(ce)001:6682: rnam rdzun pa gnyis dang rnam bden pa la'ang shes
NK095(ce)001:6683: pas yul shes tshul gyi sgo nas nang gses kyi
NK095(ce)001:6684: dbye ba gsum du yod do //
NK095(ce)001:6685: gnyis pa dbu ma pas ni gzung 'dzin gnyis stong
NK095(ce)001:6686: gi shes pa tsam yang bden grub tu mi 'dod
NK095(ce)001:6687: par chos thams cad stong bzhin du snang ba'i rten
NK095(ce)001:6688: 'byung zab mo'i don la yid ches pa'i lta ba
NK095(ce)001:6690: de la yang bden gnyis dbyer med du rtogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6691: blo'i rtsal 'phang gis thal rang gnyis su yod pa
NK095(ce)001:6692: las / dang po rang rgyud pas ni gnas skabs
NK095(ce)001:6693: su bden gnyis so sor phye ba'i sgo nas don
NK095(ce)001:6694: dam par chos thams cad spros pa thams cad dang
NK095(ce)001:6695: bral ba'i stong pa nyid yin kyang /
NK095(ce)001:6696: kun rdzob tu tha snyad kyi dngos po rnams kyis
NK095(ce)001:6697: rang rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin cing mi bslu ba
NK095(ce)001:6698: don byed nus pa'i ngo bor yod par 'dod pa
NK095(ce)001:6699: dang / mthar thug bden gnyis so so'i 'dzin pa
NK095(ce)001:6700: dang bral nas bden gnyis dbyer med chen por la
NK095(ce)001:6702: lam rim gyis pa lta bu yin par gsungs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6703: de la'ang rang rgyud gong 'og sogs nang gi dbye ba du ma yod do //
NK095(ce)001:6704: gnyis pa thal 'gyur pas ni dang po nyid nas
NK095(ce)001:6705: chos thams cad yod med yin min la sogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6706: spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i rnam grangs
NK095(ce)001:6707: min pa'i don dam bden gnyis dbyer med chen por
NK095(ce)001:6708: gtan la 'beb par byed pas na lam cig char
NK095(ce)001:6709: ba lta bu yin par gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:6710: de lta bu'i dbu sems gnyis ka'i sgom pa ni
NK095(ce)001:6711: theg chen gyi sa bcu lam lnga dang 'brel ba'i
NK095(ce)001:6712: byang chub phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun bsgom
NK095(ce)001:6713: pa dang / spyod pa ni pha rol du phyin
NK095(ce)001:6714: pa drug gis bsdus pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i spyod
NK095(ce)001:6715: pa rgya mtsho lta bu la bskal pa grangs med
NK095(ce)001:6716: gsum la sogs par spyod pas 'bras bu ni bcu
NK095(ce)001:6717: gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa la mngon par rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:6718: par sangs rgyas par 'dod pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6719: de lta bu'i mtshan nyid sde gsum po de ni
NK095(ce)001:6720: stong pa sprul pa'i sku yi bstan pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:6722: de yang mtshan nyid sde gsum po de nyid don
NK095(ce)001:6723: gang gi ched du gsungs pa yin zhe na 'di
NK095(ce)001:6724: ltar ston pa kun byed nga yi ngo bo gcig
NK095(ce)001:6725: gi rtsal snang las phyi 'dod yon lnga dang nang
NK095(ce)001:6726: ye shes lnga yi ngo bora rang shar du phyung
NK095(ce)001:6727: ba la / rang snang du ma shes par gzung
NK095(ce)001:6728: 'dzin rgyang chad du bltas pa'i dbang gis 'dod chags
NK095(ce)001:6729: zhe sdang gti mug ste dug gsum rang rgyud pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6730: rnam par byung ste de'i sgo nas dge sdig gi
NK095(ce)001:6731: las sna tshogs bsags pa'i 'bras bu 'gro drug gi
NK095(ce)001:6732: 'khrul snang tshad med pa mched pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:6733: de dag gi rgyu nyon mongs pa dug gsum po
NK095(ce)001:6734: de 'dul ba yi gnyen por gsungs pa yi ni
NK095(ce)001:6735: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gi grangs
NK095(ce)001:6737: de la 'dod pa'i yon tan rnam pa lnga ru
NK095(ce)001:6738: byung ba ni gang zhe na gzugs dang sgra dang
NK095(ce)001:6739: dri dang ro dang reg bya ste rnam pa lnga
NK095(ce)001:6740: yin la / de lnga po kun byed byang chub
NK095(ce)001:6741: kyi sems gnyis med ye shes chen po'i rang mdangs
NK095(ce)001:6742: su ma shes par phyi rol du zhen cing chags
NK095(ce)001:6743: pa las yul lnga po yid du 'ong ba la
NK095(ce)001:6744: brten nas 'dod chags dang yid du mi 'ong ba
NK095(ce)001:6745: la brten nas zhe sdang dang bar ma la brten
NK095(ce)001:6746: nas gti mug rnam pa gsum byung ba la /
NK095(ce)001:6747: de dag 'dul ba'i gnyen por ston pa sprul pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6748: sku nyid tshangs spyod chags bral gyi rnam par snang
NK095(ce)001:6749: nas chos kyi rnam grangs bsdu na sde snod rnam
NK095(ce)001:6750: pa gsum du bstan pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:6752: de la sde snod gsum ni gang yin zhe na
NK095(ce)001:6753: 'di ltar nyon mongs pa 'dod chags kyi rtog pa
NK095(ce)001:6754: nyi khri chig stong 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:6755: ni lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa gtso bor
NK095(ce)001:6756: ston pa 'dul ba yi sde snod nyi khri chig
NK095(ce)001:6758: nyon mongs pa gti mug gi rtog pa nyi khri
NK095(ce)001:6759: chig stong 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni lhag
NK095(ce)001:6760: pa ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa gtso bor ston
NK095(ce)001:6761: pa mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs
NK095(ce)001:6762: pa dang / nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi rtog
NK095(ce)001:6763: pa nyi khri chig stong 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs
NK095(ce)001:6764: pa ni lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa gtso
NK095(ce)001:6765: bor ston pa mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig
NK095(ce)001:6767: dug gsum cha mnyam gyi rtog pa nyi khri chig
NK095(ce)001:6768: stong 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru sde snod gsum las
NK095(ce)001:6769: brjod bya gtso che chung med par cha mnyam pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6770: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:6771: ste / de ltar na nyon mongs pa'i kun rtog
NK095(ce)001:6772: brgyad khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por chos sgo brgyad
NK095(ce)001:6773: khri bzhi stong du gsungs pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:6774: tshul 'di ltar klong chen rab 'byams kyi rgyud las kyang /
NK095(ce)001:6775: ma rig lus can 'khrul pa'i sems can la //
NK095(ce)001:6776: nyon mongs brgyad khri bzhi stong gnas pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:6777: gnyen po brgyad khri bzhi stong chos kyang bshad //
NK095(ce)001:6778: chos sgo bsam 'das de snyed kyang //
NK095(ce)001:6779: sde snod gsum gyis 'dul ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:6781: gti mug gnyen por mdo sde dang //
NK095(ce)001:6782: zhe sdang gnyen por mngon pa rnams //
NK095(ce)001:6783: kun kyang nyi khri chig stong ste //
NK095(ce)001:6784: dug gsum cha snyoms sde snod gsum //
NK095(ce)001:6785: cha snyom nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK095(ce)001:6787: bzhi pa don bsdu la lnga ste /
NK095(ce)001:6792: gang gis gsungs pa'i don bsdu pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6794: de ltar mdor na gong du bstan pa ltar sde
NK095(ce)001:6795: snod gsum la nyi khri chig stong tshan bzhi gsungs
NK095(ce)001:6796: pa rnams sdom pas spyi ru chos sgo brgyad khri
NK095(ce)001:6797: bzhi stong gi grangs su gsungs pa de ma lus
NK095(ce)001:6798: pa yang don du dug gsum gyi rang bzhin can
NK095(ce)001:6799: gyi nyon mongs pa'i rtog pa de rnams gnyen pos
NK095(ce)001:6800: 'dul ba kho na'i phyir du gsungs pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:6802: de lta bu'i chos sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong po
NK095(ce)001:6803: de dag thams cad tshur bsdu na nyan thos rang
NK095(ce)001:6804: rgyal byang chub sems dpa' ste mtshan nyid rgyu yi
NK095(ce)001:6805: theg pa rnam pa gsum du 'du ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:6807: dbang po tha ma'i don du ni //
NK095(ce)001:6808: sde snod gsum gyi theg pa bstan //
NK095(ce)001:6810: de ltar na theg pa gsum po de rnams chos
NK095(ce)001:6811: kyi sgo ni mdo sde dang 'dul ba mngon pa
NK095(ce)001:6812: gsum du bstan pa de ni bsdus pa'i don no
NK095(ce)001:6815: de lta bu'i mtshan nyid mdo sde yi theg pa
NK095(ce)001:6816: de la yang phar dbye ba'i dbang du na gsung
NK095(ce)001:6817: rab rnams bshad lugs mi 'dra ba'i sgo nas yan
NK095(ce)001:6818: lag bcu dang gnyis su yod de /
NK095(ce)001:6819: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyis bshad rgyud rin po che'i phreng ba las /
NK095(ce)001:6820: 'bring ni rnam pa bcu gnyis te //
NK095(ce)001:6821: mdo dang dbyangs dang lung du bstan //
NK095(ce)001:6822: tshig bcad ched brjod gleng gzhi'i sde //
NK095(ce)001:6823: rtogs brjod de byung skyes pa'i rabs //
NK095(ce)001:6824: rgyas dang rmad byung gtan la phab //
NK095(ce)001:6825: yan lag bcu gnyis srid rtsa bton //
NK095(ce)001:6826: zhes gsungs pa ltar tshig mdor bsdus shing don sde
NK095(ce)001:6827: tshan du bcad de bshad pa mdo yi sde dang
NK095(ce)001:6828: / tshig lhug pa'i sgo nas rgyas par gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:6829: de dag slar yang tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs kyi
NK095(ce)001:6830: bsnyad de bshad pa ni dbyangs bsnyad dang /
NK095(ce)001:6831: ma 'ongs pa na 'byung 'gyur gyi chos gang zhig
NK095(ce)001:6832: lung bstan pa rnams ni lung du bstan pa dang
NK095(ce)001:6833: / dang po nas tshigs su bcad pa kho nas gsungs pa ni tshig bcad dang /
NK095(ce)001:6834: gzhan gyis ma bskul bar ston pa nyid kyis ched du bka' rtsal ba ni ched brjod dang /
NK095(ce)001:6835: gleng gzhi la brten nas rgya cher gsungs pa ni gleng bzhi dang /
NK095(ce)001:6836: gang zag da lta ba 'ga' zhig gi ngo mtshar gyi lo rgyus bshad pa ni rtogs brjod dang /
NK095(ce)001:6837: sngon byung gi chos rnams kyi lo rgyus gsungs pa ni de lta bu byung ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:6838: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi skye ba'i phreng ba bshad pa ni skyes rabs dang /
NK095(ce)001:6839: zab cing rgya che ba'i chos gang zhig shin tu
NK095(ce)001:6840: rgyas pa'i sgo nas tshad med par gsungs pa ni
NK095(ce)001:6842: shin tu ngo mtshar ba'i chos sngar ma grags pa
NK095(ce)001:6843: lta bu gsungs pa ni rmad du byung ba dang
NK095(ce)001:6844: / brjod bya gang zhig phra zhib nas so sor gtan la phabs te /
NK095(ce)001:6845: bshad pa ni gtan la dbab pa'i sde ste /
NK095(ce)001:6846: de ltar bcu gnyis su bstan pa ni 'bring du bstan pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:6847: de dag bsdu na sde snod gsum du 'du ba'i tshul kyang /
NK095(ce)001:6849: bsdus pa sde snod gsum dag ste //
NK095(ce)001:6850: mdo sde 'dul ba chos mngon no //
NK095(ce)001:6851: de yang rnam pa bzhi yin te //
NK095(ce)001:6852: gang gsungs gang du gang gi phyir //
NK095(ce)001:6853: tshul ni ji ltar bsdus pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6854: gang ni bcu dang gnyis bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6855: gang du sde snod gsum du'o //
NK095(ce)001:6856: gang phyir rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK095(ce)001:6857: gnyen po'i don phyir gsum nyid dang //
NK095(ce)001:6858: bslab gsum rgyud la skye phyir gsum //
NK095(ce)001:6859: chos dang chos phyir bsdu ba gsum //
NK095(ce)001:6860: zhes gsungs pa ltar gang zhig bsdu ba ni gsungs rabs yan lag bcu gnyis so //
NK095(ce)001:6861: gang du bsdu na sde snod rnam pa gsum du bsdu ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:6862: rgyu mtshan nam dgos pa gang gi phyir bsdu na /
NK095(ce)001:6863: the tshom dang spyod pa dang lta ba phyin ci
NK095(ce)001:6864: log gsum mam dug gsum gyi gnyen po'i don gyi
NK095(ce)001:6865: phyir sogs rnam pa gsum gyi phyir du bsdu ba
NK095(ce)001:6866: yin zhing / ji ltar bsdu ba'i tshul la rnam
NK095(ce)001:6867: pa gnyis su gsungs te brjod bya'i don gyi sgo
NK095(ce)001:6869: brjod byed tshig gi sgo nas bsdu ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:6870: dang po don gyi sgo nas bsdu ba ni gang zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:6871: bsgom pa gtso bor ston pa mdo sde dang /
NK095(ce)001:6872: bsrung sdom gtso bor ston pa 'dul ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:6873: lta ba gtso bor ston pa mngon pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6875: bsdu tshul la ni rnam gnyis te //
NK095(ce)001:6876: don dang tshig gi sgo nas so //
NK095(ce)001:6877: don la rnam pa gsum bshad de //
NK095(ce)001:6878: sgom pa gtsor ston mdo yi sde //
NK095(ce)001:6879: bsrung sdom gtsor ston 'dul ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:6880: lta ba gtsor ston mngon pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:6882: tshig gi sgo nas bsdu ba la theg pa chung ngu'i bsdu tshul dang /
NK095(ce)001:6883: theg pa chen po'i bsdu tshul dang /
NK095(ce)001:6884: gnyis ga'i thun mong gi bsdu tshul gsum las /
NK095(ce)001:6886: snga ma lnga mdo sde dang /
NK095(ce)001:6887: de rjes gleng gzhi la sogs pa rnam pa bzhi 'dul ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:6888: rgyas pa dang rmad byung gtan dbab gsum mngon pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6889: gnyis pa theg chen ltar na /
NK095(ce)001:6890: rgyas pa dang rmad byung gnyis mdo sde dang /
NK095(ce)001:6891: mdo sde nas skyes rabs kyi bar dgu ni 'dul ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:6892: gtan la phab pa mngon pa yin par gsungs la /
NK095(ce)001:6893: thun mong ba ltar na dang po lnga ni mdo sde dang /
NK095(ce)001:6894: de rjes gleng gzhi la sogs pa drug ni 'dul ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:6895: gtan dbab ni mngon pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:6897: tshig bsdu rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK095(ce)001:6898: theg pa che chung thun mong gsum //
NK095(ce)001:6899: mdo sogs rim lnga mdo yi sde //
NK095(ce)001:6900: de rjes rnam bzhi 'dul ba ste //
NK095(ce)001:6901: tha ma gsum ni mngon pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6902: de ni theg pa chung ngu yin //
NK095(ce)001:6903: rgyas dang rmad byung mdo yi sde //
NK095(ce)001:6904: mdo sogs dgu ni 'dul ba la //
NK095(ce)001:6905: gtan la phab pa mngon pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:6906: de ni theg pa chen po'i gzhung //
NK095(ce)001:6907: dang po lnga ni mdo yi sde //
NK095(ce)001:6908: de rjes drug ni 'dul ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:6909: tha ma mngon pa thun mong gzhung //
NK095(ce)001:6911: de ltar na gsung rabs yan lag bcu gnyis su
NK095(ce)001:6912: gsungs pa de ni sde snod gsum po de las
NK095(ce)001:6913: 'bring du so sor dabye ba'i don du bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:6914: yin la / rgyas par ni gong du bshad pa
NK095(ce)001:6915: ltar chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong du
NK095(ce)001:6918: de las rgyas par gsungs pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:6919: dug gsum nyon mongs cha mnyam pa'i //
NK095(ce)001:6920: gnyen po brgyad khri bzhi stong ngo //
NK095(ce)001:6921: theg pa sna tshogs thabs tshul gyis //
NK095(ce)001:6925: de lta bu'i sangs rgyas sprul pa'i skus gsungs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6926: mtshan nyid theg pa gsum gyis bstan bya'i gtso bo
NK095(ce)001:6927: ni / dug gsum gyi rgyu la spyad pa las 'bras bu zhe sdang gis dmyal ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:6929: gti mug gis 'bras bu dud 'gro ste ngan song
NK095(ce)001:6930: gsum du skye ba yin pas de dag spang bya'o
NK095(ce)001:6931: zhes spang thabs dang bcas pa bstan pa'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:6932: / sems can rnams rgyu dug gsum po de las
NK095(ce)001:6933: bzlog te yang dag pa'i lam la dkri ba'i ched
NK095(ce)001:6934: du las dkar nag la spyod pa'i dbang gis dge
NK095(ce)001:6935: sdig gnyis kyi 'bras bu rim pa ltar mtho ris
NK095(ce)001:6936: dang ngan song rnam pa gnyis po zhes dge sdig
NK095(ce)001:6937: de dag la blang dor byed pa'i tshul ni mtshan
NK095(ce)001:6938: nyid rgyu yi theg pa gsum po de las rab
NK095(ce)001:6939: tu bsgrags pa yin no zhes 'dis rgyu yi theg
NK095(ce)001:6940: pa zhes pa'i rgyu mtshan kyang bstan pa yin te
NK095(ce)001:6942: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:6943: dge sdig las kyi rgyu byas pas //
NK095(ce)001:6945: chos spyod dge bas rgyu byas nas //
NK095(ce)001:6946: de nyid lam du khyer ba'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:6947: rgyu yi theg pa bstan pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:6950: de ltar rgyu 'bras la blang dor gyis brtson par
NK095(ce)001:6951: byed pa'i theg pa 'di ni ston pa sprul pa'i
NK095(ce)001:6952: sku rnams kyis sngar yang gsungs pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:6953: da ltar phyogs bcu'i zhing na sku 'tsho zhing mngon
NK095(ce)001:6954: sum du bzhugs pa rnams kyis gsung bzhin pa dang
NK095(ce)001:6955: / phyis su 'byon par 'gyur ba rnams kyis kyang gsung bar 'gyur la /
NK095(ce)001:6956: dge sdig blang dor byed pa 'di lta bu yi
NK095(ce)001:6957: don thams cad smra bsam brjod du med pa kun
NK095(ce)001:6958: byed byang chub sems kyi klong du la bzla bar
NK095(ce)001:6959: byed pa'i don du gsungs pa kun byed chos sku'i
NK095(ce)001:6960: bstan pa 'di ni sprul sku'i ston pa rnams kyi
NK095(ce)001:6961: snga ma 'das pa'i dus su ma gsungs la /
NK095(ce)001:6963: de bzhin du ston pa sprul pa'i sku yis phyis
NK095(ce)001:6964: kyang gsung par mi 'gyur ba de bas na sprul
NK095(ce)001:6965: pa'i sku yi bstan pa ni mtshan nyid rgyu yi
NK095(ce)001:6966: theg pa gsum po 'di nyid yin par bshad do
NK095(ce)001:6967: // gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rgya cher bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:6971: sprul sku gsum gyi 'khor rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:6973: kye sems dpa' chen po ston pa kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:6974: yi rang bzhin stong gsal thugs rje ste rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:6975: gsum gyi rtsal la 'khor gyi dang po ston pa
NK095(ce)001:6976: sku gsum du shar zhing byung ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:6977: de lta bu'i sku gsum ston pa gsum gyi 'khora
NK095(ce)001:6978: rnams rim pa bzhin du bstan pa ni 'di ltar
NK095(ce)001:6981: chos sku longs sku sprul sku'i 'khor gsum las /
NK095(ce)001:6983: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig kun byed byang
NK095(ce)001:6984: chub sems kyi rang bzhin ston pa chos kyi sku
NK095(ce)001:6985: yi 'khor rnams bstan pa ni gang zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:6986: kun byed rgyal po nga yis byas shing rang rtsal
NK095(ce)001:6987: las sprul pa'i 'khor ni srid zhi gnyis kyis bsdus
NK095(ce)001:6988: pa'i chos thams cad kun rang byung snying po byang
NK095(ce)001:6989: chub kyi sems nga yi rang bzhin gdod ma'i mgon
NK095(ce)001:6990: po chos kyi sku yi 'khor yin pas na /
NK095(ce)001:6991: rig pa byang chub kyi sems rang ngo shes pa'i sangsa rgyas dang /
NK095(ce)001:6992: rang ngo ma shes pas 'khrul pa ltar snang ba'i
NK095(ce)001:6993: sems cana gyi khams snang srid snod bcud kyis bsdus
NK095(ce)001:6994: pa 'di thams cad kun ston pa chos kyi sku
NK095(ce)001:6995: yi 'khor du ma 'dus pa gcig kyang med pas
NK095(ce)001:6996: thams cad chos kyi sku yi 'khor du bshad do
NK095(ce)001:6997: ces gsungs so // gnyis pa longs sku'i 'khor ni /
NK095(ce)001:6998: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:6999: kyi ngo bo ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK095(ce)001:7001: mos pas spyod pa drod rtse mo bzod pa chos
NK095(ce)001:7002: mchog bzhi yi sa la brten nas 'jig rten las
NK095(ce)001:7003: 'das pa yi sa dang po rab tu dga' ba'i
NK095(ce)001:7004: sa mnan pa nasa bzung ste sa bcu pa chos
NK095(ce)001:7005: kyi sprin gyi bar gyi sa pa yi byang chub
NK095(ce)001:7007: de ni ston pa longs spyod rdzogsa pa'i sku yi 'khor du bstan pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:7009: kun byed byang chub sems kyi thugs rje'i rol rtsal
NK095(ce)001:7010: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yi 'khora rnams bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:7011: ni / 'di ltar dngos po'i gnas tshul la phyin
NK095(ce)001:7012: ci log par rtogs pa la phya dang dbang phyug
NK095(ce)001:7013: gtso bdag la sogs pa rtag par lta ba mu
NK095(ce)001:7014: ni / stegs pa dang / tshe snga phyi dang
NK095(ce)001:7015: las 'bras sogs med par lta bas chad lta mur
NK095(ce)001:7017: grub mthas blo ma bsgyur zhing las 'bras yod med sogs ci yang ma rtogs pa la /
NK095(ce)001:7018: phyi ma rgyang du 'phen zhing tshe 'di gang la
NK095(ce)001:7019: btsan phyug la sogs pa bsgrub pa'i ched du mchod
NK095(ce)001:7020: sbyin phra mo byed pa dang pha mes kyi mtshun
NK095(ce)001:7021: gsol ba dang mo bon g.yang blan la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:7022: tshe 'dir phan pa 'ba' zhig bsgrub par byed pa
NK095(ce)001:7023: rgyang 'phen dang / 'jig rten tha mal pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:7024: las kyang shin tu glen zhing rmongs pa phyug lta
NK095(ce)001:7025: bu rgyu 'bras dang spang blang ci yang mi shes
NK095(ce)001:7026: pas lta ba dang grub mtha' 'di yin gyi nges
NK095(ce)001:7027: pa med pa phyal ba ste rnam pa bzhi po
NK095(ce)001:7028: 'di nyid bla med byang chub kyi lam la ma
NK095(ce)001:7029: zhugs shing phyin ci log pa'i lam la gtan du
NK095(ce)001:7031: de dag gi khams dang dbang po sems kyi bye
NK095(ce)001:7032: brag rnams yang dag pa'i lam du bsgyur bar byed
NK095(ce)001:7033: cing zag med rang byung gi thugs rje yis byin
NK095(ce)001:7034: gyis brlabs nas las la rim gyis drangs bar mdzad
NK095(ce)001:7035: pa'i 'khor dge slong pho mo gnyis dang dge bsnyen
NK095(ce)001:7036: pho mo gnyis te rnam pa bzhi po de ni
NK095(ce)001:7037: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yi 'khor du bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:7039: bzhi pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:7041: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum gyi gnas rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:7043: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:7044: las byung ba'i ston pa sku gsum gyi bzhugs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7045: gnas gang zhig sku gsum po so sor nga re
NK095(ce)001:7046: yi zhes rang rang gi gnas kyi khyad par bstan
NK095(ce)001:7047: pa ni 'chad 'gyur 'di nyid do zhes mdor bstan
NK095(ce)001:7048: pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum las /
NK095(ce)001:7049: dang po chos sku'i gnas ni /
NK095(ce)001:7050: de la ston pa chos kyi sku'i gnas kyi mtshan nyid ni 'di lta ste /
NK095(ce)001:7051: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa gang gi yang 'og tu
NK095(ce)001:7052: ma gyur pa'i phyir na 'og min gyi gnas chos
NK095(ce)001:7053: thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas chos kyi
NK095(ce)001:7055: de ni rtog pa'i grwa zur shin tu phra ba
NK095(ce)001:7056: las kyang 'das shing chos rnams kyi gnas lugs mthar
NK095(ce)001:7057: thug pa yin pas yang dag don gyi 'og min
NK095(ce)001:7058: zhes bshad pa'i rgya chad phyogs lhung dang bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:7059: rang bzhin de ru ston pa chos kyi sku nyid
NK095(ce)001:7060: dus gsum 'pho 'gyur bral ba'i ngo bor bzhugs pas
NK095(ce)001:7061: na de lta bu'i gnas de ni ston pa chos
NK095(ce)001:7062: kyi sku'i bzhugs gnas su bshad do //
NK095(ce)001:7063: gnyis pa longs sku'i gnas ni /
NK095(ce)001:7064: 'di ltar ston pa longsa spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi gnas bstan pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:7065: 'jig rten gyi gnas gzugs su snang ba'i mtshan ma
NK095(ce)001:7066: kun gyi steng du gyur pa 'am mtshan ma'i spyod
NK095(ce)001:7067: yul kun las 'das pa 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og
NK095(ce)001:7068: min khanga bu brtsegs pa yi gzhal yas khang chen
NK095(ce)001:7069: po ste / sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK095(ce)001:7070: gtsang ma'i rigs dag rab spang ba'i //
NK095(ce)001:7071: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK095(ce)001:7072: rigs bdag phyag rgya lhun grub sku //
NK095(ce)001:7073: gcig dang du ma rnam spangs pa //
NK095(ce)001:7074: sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi gzugs te //
NK095(ce)001:7075: gdod nas theg chen mdzod nyid phyir //
NK095(ce)001:7076: sgrib pa mtha' spangs gdul bya la //
NK095(ce)001:7077: skad cig gcig gis snang bar mdzad //
NK095(ce)001:7079: yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las //
NK095(ce)001:7080: de dag gong na srid pa tha ma'i gnas //
NK095(ce)001:7081: 'og min rnam mdzes sa bcu thob pa'i gnas //
NK095(ce)001:7082: dwangs shing gsal la yongs su rdzogs pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:7083: ces gsungs pa de ni ston pa longs spyod rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:7084: pa'i sku'i bzhugs gnas kyi 'og min tu bshad pa'o
NK095(ce)001:7085: // gsum pa sprul sku'i gnas ni /
NK095(ce)001:7086: de la ston pa sprul pa'i sku yi gnas bstan pa ni gang yin zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:7087: 'di ltar mchog gi sprul pa'i sku ni sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:7088: rabas bdun nam dpa' bo bdun zhes sh+aakya thub pa
NK095(ce)001:7089: dang rnam gzigs gtsug tor can la sogs pa ste
NK095(ce)001:7090: / de dag gi gnas ni rgya gar bya rgod
NK095(ce)001:7091: phung po'i ri dang ma ga d+h+aa yi gnas la
NK095(ce)001:7092: sogs pa yin par bstan te /
NK095(ce)001:7093: mdor na mi mthun phyogs kyi dri mas shin tu
NK095(ce)001:7094: dben pa'i yang dag pa'i thugs rje yi rol par
NK095(ce)001:7095: sprul pa sna tshogs tshad med par snang ba rnams
NK095(ce)001:7096: ni gnas 'di na bzhugs dang 'dir mi bzhugs zhes
NK095(ce)001:7097: pa'i nges pa med par gdul bya gang zhig gnas
NK095(ce)001:7098: gang du thabs ci lta bu'i 'dul ba'i dus la
NK095(ce)001:7099: bab pa na gnas de dang de nyid du gang
NK095(ce)001:7100: 'dul gyi rol pa sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul ltar snang
NK095(ce)001:7101: ba yin no // zhes gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:7102: lnga pa zhing khams phun sum tshogs pa rgya cher bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:7104: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum gyi zhing khams rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:7106: kye sems dpa' rdo rje chen po nyon cig snying
NK095(ce)001:7107: po byang chub kyi sems kun byeed nga las byung
NK095(ce)001:7108: ba'i sku gsum gyi ston pa gsum po de yi
NK095(ce)001:7109: gdul bar bya ba'i zhing khams kyi khyad par bstan
NK095(ce)001:7112: gnyis pa sku gsum gyi zhing khams rgyas par bshad pa la gsum las /
NK095(ce)001:7114: 'di ltar kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7115: las byung ba chos sku yi ston pa gang gi
NK095(ce)001:7116: 'dula bya'i zhing khams ni rgya chad phyogs lhung dang
