NK095(ce)001:7117: bral ba spros bral chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha'a yis
NK095(ce)001:7118: klas pa dang nam mkha' khams kyis phyogs bcu'i 'jig
NK095(ce)001:7119: rten thams cad la ji ltar khyab pa de thams
NK095(ce)001:7120: cad sangs rgyas chos kyi sku yi 'dul ba'i gnas
NK095(ce)001:7121: su gyur pa 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i zhing
NK095(ce)001:7122: khams zhes bya ba yin no //
NK095(ce)001:7123: de yang klong chen rab 'byams las /
NK095(ce)001:7124: chos sku'i ston pa rig stong dang //
NK095(ce)001:7125: chos sku'i gnas ni 'og min nyid //
NK095(ce)001:7126: chos sku'i 'dul zhing nam mkha'i khams //
NK095(ce)001:7127: chos sku'i 'khor ni rig pa'i mdangs //
NK095(ce)001:7128: chos sku'i bstan pa rnam pa bzhi //
NK095(ce)001:7129: ma h+aa a nu a ti dang //
NK095(ce)001:7130: a ti chen po rnam pa bzhi //
NK095(ce)001:7132: 'dir a ti chen po ni thod rgal la gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:7134: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i 'dul ba'i zhing
NK095(ce)001:7135: khams ni gang zhe na ston pa kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:7136: las byung ba'i rang mdangs 'gag pa med pa'i rol
NK095(ce)001:7137: pa yul snang gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga
NK095(ce)001:7138: po ji ltar 'dod pa'i yon tan gyis brgyan pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7139: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad ni ston pa longs
NK095(ce)001:7140: spyod rdzogs pas gdul ba'i zhing khams te /
NK095(ce)001:7141: de la nang gses su rnam snang gang chen mtsho
NK095(ce)001:7142: gcig gi sku lus kyi cha la brten pa'i zhing
NK095(ce)001:7143: gi bkod pa thams cad sdom pa la gzhi dang
NK095(ce)001:7144: snying po me tog gis brgyan pa'i zhing khams zhes
NK095(ce)001:7145: gsungs pa dang / de 'dra rigs lnga ka la
NK095(ce)001:7146: tshangs pa lnga sgra'i zhing khams zhes pa ste de
NK095(ce)001:7147: lta bu'i nam mkha'i dbyings thams cad ma khyab pa
NK095(ce)001:7148: med pa rnams ni longs sku'i bstan pa'i zhing khams
NK095(ce)001:7149: gsungs pa dang / te / de nyid las /
NK095(ce)001:7150: longs sku'i ston pa gangs chen mtsho //
NK095(ce)001:7151: longs sku'i gnas ni khang bu brtsegs //
NK095(ce)001:7152: longs sku'i 'dul zhing snang ba rnams //
NK095(ce)001:7153: 'dod pa'i longs spyod khyab tshad yin //
NK095(ce)001:7154: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i 'khor ni 'di lta ste //
NK095(ce)001:7155: mos spyod bzhi yi sa las rab 'das nas //
NK095(ce)001:7156: dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa gnon te //
NK095(ce)001:7157: sa bcu chos kyi sprin la gnas rnams yin //
NK095(ce)001:7158: 'dul zhing snang ba gsal bas khyab tshad te //
NK095(ce)001:7159: bstan pa kri ya u pa yo ga'o //
NK095(ce)001:7162: de bzhin du ston pa sprul pa'i sku yi 'dul bar bya ba'i zhing khams ni /
NK095(ce)001:7164: gling bzhi dang ni nyi zla dang //
NK095(ce)001:7165: ri rab dang ni 'dod lha dang //
NK095(ce)001:7166: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten stong la ni //
NK095(ce)001:7167: stong ni spyi phud yin par 'dod //
NK095(ce)001:7168: de stong la ni stong gnyis pa //
NK095(ce)001:7169: bar ma'i 'jig rten khams yin no //
NK095(ce)001:7170: de stong la ni stong gsum mo //
NK095(ce)001:7171: zhes gsungs pa lta bu'i stong gsum gyi stong chen
NK095(ce)001:7172: po gcig na gling bzhi ri rab la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:7173: bye ba phrag brgya re yod pa de sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:7174: sprul pa'i sku gcig gi 'dul zhing yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:7175: lho phyogs 'dzam bu'i gling ni bye ba phrag brgya
NK095(ce)001:7176: zhes mchog gi sprul sku rnams kyi bzhugs gnas dngos
NK095(ce)001:7177: kyis mtshon pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig
NK095(ce)001:7178: rten gyi khams thams cad du gdul bya rang rang
NK095(ce)001:7179: gi las dang skal ba dang mtshams par rang byung
NK095(ce)001:7180: ye shes kyi rtsal dmigs pa med pa'i thugsa rje
NK095(ce)001:7181: chen pos rgyud drug gam 'gro ba drug gi sems
NK095(ce)001:7182: can rnams 'dul bar byed pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:7183: de lta bu'i stong gsum po de ni sprul sku'i
NK095(ce)001:7184: ston pa gcig gi 'dul zhing yin pa de bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7185: du / gzhan yang de dang mthun pa'i phyogs bcu'i
NK095(ce)001:7186: zhing gi byed brag 'jig rten gyi khams tshad med
NK095(ce)001:7187: bsam gyis mi khyab pa ji snyed yod pa thams
NK095(ce)001:7188: cad kyang ston pa sprul pa'i sku'i 'dul zhing du
NK095(ce)001:7191: sprul sku'i gnas ni nges med bya rgod ri //
NK095(ce)001:7192: ston pa rab bdun sh+aaka thub la sogs pa //
NK095(ce)001:7193: 'dul zhing bye ba phyag brgya'i 'dzam gling ste //
NK095(ce)001:7194: 'khor ni lha mi mu stegs bstan gso rnams //
NK095(ce)001:7195: dbang po sems bsgyur thugs rje'i byin rlabs nas //
NK095(ce)001:7196: dge slong pho mo dge bsnyen pho mo bzhi //
NK095(ce)001:7197: ma nges sna tshogs sprul sku'i 'khor yin te //
NK095(ce)001:7198: bstan pa nyan thos rang rgyal byang sems gsum //
NK095(ce)001:7199: sku gsum ston gnas 'khor bstan bshad pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:7201: drug pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:7202: gong du bstan pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:7203: nga las byung ba'i ston pa chos longs sprul pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7204: sku ste sku gsum po de ni gang las byung
NK095(ce)001:7205: ba'i rgyu yang tha dad med par gcig tu mthun
NK095(ce)001:7206: cing 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo la yang bzang
NK095(ce)001:7207: ngan med par mthun la rang bzhin yang tha dad
NK095(ce)001:7209: de yang rgyu ni kun byed byang chub kyi sems su sku gsum po kun mthun la /
NK095(ce)001:7210: rgyu de nyid kyi rtsal las shar ba'i 'bras bu
NK095(ce)001:7211: sangs rgyas yin par yang sku gsum po kun kyang
NK095(ce)001:7212: mthun pa dang / de gsum gyi rang bzhin chos
NK095(ce)001:7213: nyid dbyings kyi ngo bo chos sku 'dus ma byas
NK095(ce)001:7214: pa'i bdag nyid yang gcig las tha dad med par
NK095(ce)001:7215: bstan pa de nyid kyi phyir na sku gsum po
NK095(ce)001:7216: des gdul bya rnams 'dul ba'i dus la snga phyi
NK095(ce)001:7217: so sor phye ba med par gcig tu bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:7218: mthun pa dang / yin no // zhes gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:7219: de ltar yang bang mdzod 'phrul sde las /
NK095(ce)001:7220: ston pa sku gsum tshur bsdu na //
NK095(ce)001:7221: rgyu yi dus na byang chub sems su kun kyang gcig /
NK095(ce)001:7222: 'bras bu'i dus na sangs rgyas yin par kun kyang gcig /
NK095(ce)001:7223: 'dus pa'i dus na snga phyi med par kun kyang
NK095(ce)001:7224: gcig /chos sku'i rang bzhin ngo bor rang bzhin med
NK095(ce)001:7226: bdun pa bshad lugs phun sum tshogs pa rgya cher bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:7228: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum gyis rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:7230: ston pa rang byung gi ye shes chos sku kun
NK095(ce)001:7231: byed rgyal pos rang gi rig rtsal las shar ba'i
NK095(ce)001:7232: 'khor la / kye sems dpa' chen po yang nyon
NK095(ce)001:7233: cig ces bos nas kun byed rgyal po nga las
NK095(ce)001:7234: byung ba yi sku gsum gyi ston pa gsum po
NK095(ce)001:7235: de yis rang rang gi 'khor rnams la snying po'i
NK095(ce)001:7236: chos kyi rang bzhin tshul ji lta bu yi sgo
NK095(ce)001:7237: nas bshad pa'i lugs sam gsungs pa'i tshul ni gang
NK095(ce)001:7238: 'khor la / zhe na / 'di ltar ston pa
NK095(ce)001:7239: chos kyi skus ni nyid kyi thugs rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:7240: ye shes kyi rtsal las skye ba'o cho 'phrul du
NK095(ce)001:7241: shar ba'i snang ba thams cad sgra tshig gis brjod
NK095(ce)001:7242: pa la mi ltos par skye med ye stong chen
NK095(ce)001:7243: po'i dgongs pa'i byin gyisa ye nas brlabs pa'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:7245: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yis ni 'di ltar snang
NK095(ce)001:7246: ba'i chos thams cad 'dod yon lnga'i rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:7247: ma spangs rgyan du rol ba'i tshul gyis ye nas
NK095(ce)001:7248: rang rtsal du rdzogs par rang gi ngo bos mtshon
NK095(ce)001:7249: te bshad pa'am ston par byed pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7250: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yis ni yan lag drug
NK095(ce)001:7251: cu dang ldan pa'i gsung gis brjod byed kyi tshig
NK095(ce)001:7252: dang brjod bya'i don rnams bsdebs sbyor legs pa'i sgo
NK095(ce)001:7253: nas gdul bya'i gang zag rnams kyi rna ba'i dbang
NK095(ce)001:7254: por tshig gi don rnams nor 'khrul med par ston
NK095(ce)001:7255: pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum las /
NK095(ce)001:7257: de la ston pa chos kyi sku yis byin gyis brlabs kyis ji ltar bshad pa yi tshul ni /
NK095(ce)001:7258: kun byed nga yi rang bzhin gdod nas skye ba
NK095(ce)001:7259: med pa mtha' grol blo 'das chen po'i don ston
NK095(ce)001:7260: 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med kyi ngang nas bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:7262: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK095(ce)001:7263: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK095(ce)001:7264: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK095(ce)001:7265: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK095(ce)001:7266: ces gsungs ba ltar chos thams cad gdod nas skye
NK095(ce)001:7267: ba med pa las skye ba'i cho 'phrul du ji
NK095(ce)001:7268: ltar snang srid snod bcud du shar ba thamsa cad
NK095(ce)001:7269: kun chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba de nyid
NK095(ce)001:7270: kyi ngo bo rtsal snang 'gag pa med pa'i thugs
NK095(ce)001:7271: rje yi cho 'phrul du phyung ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:7272: de yang snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin stong pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7273: dbyings chos sku skye ba med pa'i dgongs pa las
NK095(ce)001:7274: skad cig kyang g.yo ba med pa de bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:7275: 'khor rnams kyi blo la rang gsal ba la chos
NK095(ce)001:7276: skus byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad ces bya'o //
NK095(ce)001:7277: tshul de ltar don gsal las kyang /
NK095(ce)001:7278: chos sku'i phun sum tshogs pa lnga //
NK095(ce)001:7279: ston pa 'gyur med chos kyi sku //
NK095(ce)001:7280: bstan pa mi nub rgyal mtshan ni //
NK095(ce)001:7281: gsang ba rig pa'i rgyud chen lnga //
NK095(ce)001:7282: 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs nyid las mi gzhan pa //
NK095(ce)001:7283: rigs lnga bde gshegs 'od du 'bar ba lnga //
NK095(ce)001:7284: bzhugs gnas skye med chos kyi dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:7285: dus ni 'das dus ma byon sngon rol nas //
NK095(ce)001:7286: rtog med ston pas byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad //
NK095(ce)001:7287: nyid las mi gzhan sku lnga rang rang gis //
NK095(ce)001:7288: rgyud chen byin gyis rlabs kyis so //
NK095(ce)001:7291: ston pa longsa spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yis ni tshig
NK095(ce)001:7292: dang yi ge'i sgo nas mi 'chad par longs sku
NK095(ce)001:7293: rang gi sku yi cha byad dam ngo bo ston
NK095(ce)001:7295: de yang ji ltar na gang zhig snang ba'i chos
NK095(ce)001:7296: rnams thamsa cad kun ste gzugs sgra dri ro reg
NK095(ce)001:7297: bya la sogsa pa yi 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i
NK095(ce)001:7298: longs spyod thamsa cad ye shes rang gsal chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:7299: ngo bo ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul du
NK095(ce)001:7300: rdzogs pa 'di las gzhan na rgyal ba longs sku'i
NK095(ce)001:7301: dgongs pa gang yang med par ston pa na longs
NK095(ce)001:7302: sku rang gi sku yi ngo bos bshad ces kun
NK095(ce)001:7303: byed nga yis bshad pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:7306: ston pas longs sku'i phun sum tshogs pa lnga gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:7307: ston pa rigs lnga bde bar gshegs pa lnga bstan pa gsang ba'i rgyud chen lnga /
NK095(ce)001:7308: 'dus pa'i 'khor ni sems dpa' sems ma'i tshogs //
NK095(ce)001:7309: bzhugs pa'i gnas ni ye shes gzhal med 'od kyi klong //
NK095(ce)001:7310: dus ni de rnams rig pa yul du shar ba'i tshe //
NK095(ce)001:7311: tshig dang yi ge'i sgo nas mi 'chad par //
NK095(ce)001:7312: sku yi cha byad sgo nas ston //
NK095(ce)001:7315: ston pa sprul pa'i sku yis tshig dang yi ge'i
NK095(ce)001:7316: sdeb sbyor legs pa la brten nas ji ltar bshad
NK095(ce)001:7317: pa yi tshul ni gang zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:7318: ji ltar snang ba'i chos phyi nang snod bcud kyi
NK095(ce)001:7319: bsdus pa 'di rnams thams cad kun ye nas ston
NK095(ce)001:7320: pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi ngo bora gyur
NK095(ce)001:7321: pa rang byung ye shes kyi rtsal mdangs 'gags med
NK095(ce)001:7322: du shar ba las gzhan du med kyang /
NK095(ce)001:7323: de thad drang du ston par mdzad pas gdul bya
NK095(ce)001:7324: rnams kyi ma rig ste rtogs par mi nus pa
NK095(ce)001:7325: des na ston pa thabs la mkhas pas bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:7326: dam pa'i chos zhes bya ba'i theg pa'i khyad par
NK095(ce)001:7327: mi 'dra ba gdul bya rang rang gi ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:7328: 'dod pa'i blo dang 'tshams par sde snod gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:7329: chos rnams sprul pas brjod bya'i don rnams tshig dang
NK095(ce)001:7331: sgra yi ngo bor tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis brjod pas /
NK095(ce)001:7332: rjod byed tshig gi sgra des brjod bya zab cing
NK095(ce)001:7333: rgya che ba'i don de dang de go bar byas
NK095(ce)001:7334: nas bstan pa yin pas gang zhig bstan par bya
NK095(ce)001:7335: ba'i don de thams cad ston pa sprul pa'i skus
NK095(ce)001:7336: tshig gi sgra sdebs sbyor legs pa de yis bshad
NK095(ce)001:7337: pa yin la / de las bye brag tu kun
NK095(ce)001:7338: tu bzang po chos sku'i ston pa de nyid mtshan
NK095(ce)001:7339: rdzogs sprul pa'i sku rdo rje 'chang gi rnam par
NK095(ce)001:7340: bzhengs nas rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud rnams
NK095(ce)001:7341: ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul ni /
NK095(ce)001:7342: ston pa sprul sku'i phun sum tshogs pa lnga gsungs pa /
NK095(ce)001:7343: ston pa rdo rje 'chang chen ngas /
NK095(ce)001:7344: bstan pa'i snying po gsang ba'i rgyud chen lnga //
NK095(ce)001:7345: de sogs phyi nang gsang bas bsdus pa rnams //
NK095(ce)001:7346: thugs kyi klong du shes rab chen pos bkrol //
NK095(ce)001:7347: mgul gyi bum par ye shes rlung gis dril //
NK095(ce)001:7348: zhal gyi ljags la ma 'dres gsal bar bkram //
NK095(ce)001:7349: tshems kyi bar nas tshig don so sor bshad //
NK095(ce)001:7350: yan lag drug cu sdebs sbyor legs par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:7351: khyung chen lding thabs don gyi spyi khog phub //
NK095(ce)001:7352: stag mo'i mchong stabs dkyus kyi sa chen bcad //
NK095(ce)001:7353: ru sbal 'gros kyis tshig gi 'bru rnams bcom //
NK095(ce)001:7354: seng ge'i gdangs skad lta bas theg brgyad zil gyis mnan //
NK095(ce)001:7355: glag mo gzan 'jug lta bus man ngag 'dril //
NK095(ce)001:7356: 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs sangs rgyas rab bdun la //
NK095(ce)001:7357: lha gnas gsum du bdud rtsi'i char chen phab //
NK095(ce)001:7358: pad+ma brtsegs pa'i gnas mchog rnam gsum mo //
NK095(ce)001:7360: gnyis pa kun byed nyid la phun sum tshogs pa tshang bar bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:7361: phun sum tshogs pa'i tshang tshul rgyu mtshan dang bcas pas mdor bstan /
NK095(ce)001:7362: snang tshul dbye ba dang bcas pas rgyas par bshad /
NK095(ce)001:7363: bkod tshul rang bzhin dang bcas pas don bsdu ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:7365: phun sum tshogs pa gsum gyi tshang tshul /
NK095(ce)001:7366: tha dad du smos kyang gcig tu 'du ba'i rgyu mtshan /
NK095(ce)001:7367: de dag gi don bsdu ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:7370: ston pa bstan pa 'khor gyi rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:7372: kye bka' yi sdud pa po sems dpa' chen po
NK095(ce)001:7373: khyod nyon cig dang kun byed rgyal po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:7374: kyi sems nga ni ston pa sku gsum gyi phun
NK095(ce)001:7375: sum tshogs pa ma lus pa'i ngo bo dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:7376: gcig gi bdag nyid yin pa'i tshul 'di lta bu
NK095(ce)001:7377: ste zhes sems can rnams kyi da lta'i sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:7378: rang byung gi ye shes 'di las gzhan na ston
NK095(ce)001:7379: pa sku gsum zhig btsal du med par mdor bstan
NK095(ce)001:7380: pa'o // gnyis pa la ston 1 'khor 3bstan 2 pa gsum las /
NK095(ce)001:7381: dang po ston pa'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:7382: de la ston pa sku gsum po thams cad kun
NK095(ce)001:7383: byed byang chub kyi sems gcig gi ngo bo yin
NK095(ce)001:7385: 'di ltar gnas lugs don gyi ye shes mi rtog
NK095(ce)001:7386: mnyam pa chen po brjod med blo 'das bya rtsol
NK095(ce)001:7387: las 'das pa'i rang bzhin nyid du gnas pa de
NK095(ce)001:7388: ni chos dbyings spros pa thams cad dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:7389: chos kyi sku yi ngo bo yina la /
NK095(ce)001:7390: de'i rang bzhina 'od gsal ba'i ye shes kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:7391: rtsal rtsol med shugs 'byung gi tshul du rang snang
NK095(ce)001:7392: zhing byung ba'i skye ba'i cho 'phrul du shar ba'i
NK095(ce)001:7393: gzugs sgra dri ro la sogs pa ji snyed pa
NK095(ce)001:7394: de thams cad ni ma spangs rig pa'i rgyan du
NK095(ce)001:7395: shar ba yin pa'i phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:7396: de ni 'dod pa yi yon tan rnam pa lnga
NK095(ce)001:7397: po 'bad med du 'byung ba'i rang bzhin can longs
NK095(ce)001:7398: spyod rdzogsa pa'i sku yina la /
NK095(ce)001:7399: dmigs med thugsa rje chen po'i rang rtsal 'gags pa
NK095(ce)001:7400: med pasa gdul bya rnams ji ltar 'dul ba'i skal
NK095(ce)001:7401: ba dang mtshams par sems can gyi don mdzad pa
NK095(ce)001:7402: de ni sprul pa'i sku yi ngo bo yin pa
NK095(ce)001:7403: ste / de ltar na ston pa kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:7404: po'i rang bzhin stong gsal thugs rje rnam pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:7405: gyis gdul bya gang la ston pa gang gis 'dul
NK095(ce)001:7406: ba'i skur ston par mdzad pa de las gzhan na
NK095(ce)001:7407: ston pa sku gsum zhes bya ba gang yang yod
NK095(ce)001:7410: de bzhin du bstan pa dam pa'i chos kyang gzhan
NK095(ce)001:7411: du med par kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:7412: bzhin brjod du med pa'i gnas lugs 'od gsal spros
NK095(ce)001:7413: pa dang bral ba'i don de ni brjod med chos
NK095(ce)001:7415: de lta bu'i brjod med blo las 'das pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:7416: de gzugs sku'i ston pa gnyis kyis gdul bya so
NK095(ce)001:7417: so rang rang gang la gang 'tshams par bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:7418: de yis sems can rnams kyi don 'bad med du
NK095(ce)001:7419: mdzad pa de ni longs sku dang sprul sku'i bstan
NK095(ce)001:7420: pa phun sum tshogs par gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:7422: sku gsum gyi ston pa de yi 'khor gyi rang bzhin bstan pa ni gang yin snyam na /
NK095(ce)001:7423: de la chos sku'i 'khor ni gang zhig byang chub
NK095(ce)001:7424: sems kyi rtsal 'gag pa med pa la rang snang
NK095(ce)001:7425: ba'i chos rnams thams cad dang /
NK095(ce)001:7426: longs sku'i 'khor ni sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK095(ce)001:7427: gang zhig 'og min chen por 'dus nas theg pa
NK095(ce)001:7428: chen po'i chos la longs spyod pa rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:7429: sprul sku'i 'khor ni ston pa sprul pa'i sku nyid
NK095(ce)001:7430: gang du snang ba'i gnas bya rgod spung ri la
NK095(ce)001:7431: sogs pa de la 'dus nas dam pa'i chos la
NK095(ce)001:7432: longs spyod cing ston pa de yi gdung 'tsho ba
NK095(ce)001:7433: pa dang brgyud pa 'dzin pa de la phun sum
NK095(ce)001:7434: tshogs pa'i 'khor zhes su brjod par bya ba yin
NK095(ce)001:7436: snying po rang byung gi ye shes nga yi rang
NK095(ce)001:7437: bzhin ni sku gsum gyi rgyal ba ma lus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7438: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa'i chos kun byed pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7439: rgyal po byang chub kyi sems te /
NK095(ce)001:7440: de lta bu'i kun byed byang chub kyi sems gcig
NK095(ce)001:7441: gi rang bzhin la dbye ba rnam pa gsum du
NK095(ce)001:7443: gang zhe na ston pa kun byed rgyal po nga nyid rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK095(ce)001:7445: nga yi byas pa'i chos dang rnam pa gsum mo //
NK095(ce)001:7446: de la nga nyid kyi ngo bo ni sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:7447: gyi ston pa kun byed pa'i rgyal po ste dus
NK095(ce)001:7448: gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi mes po yin la /
NK095(ce)001:7449: nga yi rang bzhin ni 'jug sgo dang lta ba
NK095(ce)001:7450: dang dam tshig dang spyod pa la sogs pa rnam
NK095(ce)001:7451: pa bcur bstan pa de ni rgyal ba'i bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:7452: kun gyi snying por bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7453: kun byed nga yi byas pa'i chos rnams ni gang
NK095(ce)001:7454: zhe na dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad don
NK095(ce)001:7455: la snga phyi med par 'dus ma byas ye 'byams
NK095(ce)001:7456: mnyam pa chen po gcig na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:7457: dang / 'dod gzugs med kyi khams gsum na gnas
NK095(ce)001:7458: pa'i 'gro ba rigsa drug gi sems can gang ji
NK095(ce)001:7459: snyed pa thams cad kun bzang ngan gyi dbye ba
NK095(ce)001:7460: med par rang snang nyag gcig yin pas 'khor gyi
NK095(ce)001:7462: de ltar kun byed byang chub kyi sems gcig gis
NK095(ce)001:7463: phun sum tshogs pa thams cad tshang bar byas pa
NK095(ce)001:7464: yin pas na 'khor gyi gdul bya rnams la bstan
NK095(ce)001:7465: pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ston par mdzad
NK095(ce)001:7466: pa la gang zhig tshang dgos pa ston 'khor bstan
NK095(ce)001:7467: pa gsum po kun byas shing phun sum tshogs par
NK095(ce)001:7469: de ltar byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin brjod med
NK095(ce)001:7470: don gyi gnas lugs gang zhig ston par byed pa
NK095(ce)001:7471: la gang dag med na mi 'byung bas tshang dgos
NK095(ce)001:7472: pa ni ston par bya ba'i chos dang /
NK095(ce)001:7473: de nyid gang gis ston pa po dang /
NK095(ce)001:7474: des gang la ston pa'i yul 'khor gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:7475: de lta bu'i dgos pa kun ma tshang ba med
NK095(ce)001:7476: par tshogs pa la kun byed nga yi phun sum
NK095(ce)001:7478: ston pa'i rang bzhin rnam pa gsum du bstan to //
NK095(ce)001:7479: 'di ltar skye med 'pho 'gyur dang bral ba chos kyi sku dang /
NK095(ce)001:7480: ye shes gsal ba'i snang cha longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK095(ce)001:7481: thugs rje'i rol rtsal 'gags med du shar ba sprul pa'i sku ste /
NK095(ce)001:7482: de lta bu'i sku gsum po gang gis 'dul bar
NK095(ce)001:7483: bya ba'i gdul bya rnams kyi ngor ston pa sku
NK095(ce)001:7484: gsum du snang ba de la sku gsum po rang
NK095(ce)001:7485: rang nyid dang mthun pa'i gnas dang dus dang 'khor
NK095(ce)001:7486: dang bstan pa thams cad ma tshang ba med pas
NK095(ce)001:7487: phun sum tshogs par snang ba yin no zhes pa
NK095(ce)001:7489: ston pa byang chub snying po ni //
NK095(ce)001:7490: chos nyid dbyings kyi gnas chen du //
NK095(ce)001:7491: sangs rgyas sems can 'khor tshogs nas //
NK095(ce)001:7492: snga phyi med pa'i bstan pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:7493: rang rig ye shes rig pa'i rgyal //
NK095(ce)001:7494: rang bzhin rnam pa gsum snang ste //
NK095(ce)001:7495: mi gnas sems kyi rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:7496: rang byung ye shes rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:7497: thugs rje sprul pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:7498: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:7499: mi gnas chos kyi sku ru bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:7500: rang byung ye shes rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:7501: rdzogs pa'i longs spyod sku ru bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:7502: thugs rje sprul pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK095(ce)001:7503: rnam pa cir yang sprul te bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:7505: gnyis pa snang tshul dbye ba dang bcas pas rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:7506: ston pa gsum gyi snang tshul //
NK095(ce)001:7508: dkon mchog gsum gyi tshang tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:7511: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum du snang bas rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:7513: sku gsum gyi ston pa'i yang ston par gyur pa
NK095(ce)001:7514: chos sku kun byed rgyal po ngas nga yi rang
NK095(ce)001:7515: bzhin gcig la dbye ba rnam pa gsum du bstan
NK095(ce)001:7516: pa de gang yin zhen kun byed byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:7517: kyi 'khor gyi dang po ston pa sku gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:7518: rnam par shar ba 'di rnams yin no //
NK095(ce)001:7520: 'o na ston pa sku gsum po de ni ji lta bu zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:7521: 'di ltar rig pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7522: gdod nas ma skyes shing yul sems gzung 'dzin dang
NK095(ce)001:7523: bral ba'i rang bzhin spros bral 'dus ma byas pa
NK095(ce)001:7524: ka dag rang byung gi ye shes skye med bsam
NK095(ce)001:7525: brjod las 'das pa de ni 'khora gyi dang po
NK095(ce)001:7526: ston pa chos skur shar ba yin la de lta
NK095(ce)001:7527: bu'i chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK095(ce)001:7528: pa skye ba med pa'i klong las skye ba'ii cho
NK095(ce)001:7529: 'phrul 'od gsal lhun gyis grub pa ye shes rang
NK095(ce)001:7530: byung kun tu bzang po'i rol par shar ba de
NK095(ce)001:7531: ni 'dod yon lnga'i rang bzhin zag med bde ba
NK095(ce)001:7532: chen por longs spyod pas ston pa longs spyod rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:7533: pa'i sku ru shar ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:7534: gdul bya'i mos pa sna tshogs dang mthun par ji
NK095(ce)001:7535: ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sprul pa'i rol pa tshad
NK095(ce)001:7537: gdul bya de yi rang rang so so'i skal ba
NK095(ce)001:7538: dang mthun par sems can kun kyang tshom par byed
NK095(ce)001:7539: pa de ni sna tshogs sprul pa'i sku zhes su
NK095(ce)001:7542: 'khor gyi snang ba dang mthun par ston pa'i snang tshul /
NK095(ce)001:7543: de'i blo dang mthun par bstan pa'i snang tshul /
NK095(ce)001:7544: sku gsum gang la snang ba'i rang bzhin /
NK095(ce)001:7545: phrin las gang du 'jug pa'i dus tshigs so //
NK095(ce)001:7547: de lta bu'i rgyal ba sku gsuma gyi ston pa
NK095(ce)001:7548: zhes yongs su grags pa de rnams 'khor gyi phyogs
NK095(ce)001:7549: gang du mthong zhing snang bar mdzad pa yi tshul
NK095(ce)001:7550: ni 'di ltar chos sku'i 'khor ni dus gsum gyis
NK095(ce)001:7552: longs sku'i 'khor ni 'phags pa'i sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:7553: sprul sku'i 'khor ni sbyor lam bzod pa thob pa
NK095(ce)001:7554: la sogs pa nas khams gsum rgyud drug gi 'gro
NK095(ce)001:7555: ba rnams te / de lta bu'i 'khor gsum po'i
NK095(ce)001:7556: snang ba dang mthun par sku gsum du snang zhing
NK095(ce)001:7557: gdul bya rang rang gi blo dang gang zhig 'thad
NK095(ce)001:7558: pa'am 'tshams par snang ba'i ston pa so so'i sku
NK095(ce)001:7559: la 'khor gyi tshul du de rnams 'dus nas /
NK095(ce)001:7560: ston 'khor de rnams rang rang dang mthun pa'i gnas
NK095(ce)001:7561: su bstan pa dam pa'i chos kyi don rnams ston
NK095(ce)001:7562: par mdzad cing bzhugs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:7564: mi gnas chos skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:7565: 'khor yang byang chub sems su bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:7566: byang chub sems kyi 'khor rnams la //
NK095(ce)001:7567: spros pa med pa'i don yang ston //
NK095(ce)001:7568: longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:7570: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK095(ce)001:7571: sku dang ye shes rdzogs par ston //
NK095(ce)001:7572: sna tshogs sprul skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:7574: rgyud drug sems can 'khor rnams la //
NK095(ce)001:7575: yid bzhin dbang po gang 'thad ston //
NK095(ce)001:7578: ston pa gsum po de yi bstan pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7579: yang ni sku gsum gyi ston pa rnams gdul bya
NK095(ce)001:7580: dang 'tshams par snang ba'i tshul de dang 'dra ba
NK095(ce)001:7581: ste / 'di ltar sku gsum po gang gis rang
NK095(ce)001:7582: rang gi 'khor rnams la chos gang zhig ston pa
NK095(ce)001:7583: yi tshul ni gdul bya gang la thabs gang gis
NK095(ce)001:7584: 'dul ba'i don rnams kyis zhes bstan bya chos kyi
NK095(ce)001:7585: don ci lta bus 'dul bar nus pa de bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7586: du 'khor gyi thog ma dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:7587: nas 'gro ba lha mi yi bar gyi 'jig rten
NK095(ce)001:7588: las dag pa rnams la de dang mthun par 'jig
NK095(ce)001:7589: rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa'i rnam
NK095(ce)001:7590: grangs tshad med par bstan pas gdul bya rnams 'dul
NK095(ce)001:7591: ba'i phyir na gang 'dul gyi chos kyi rnam grangs
NK095(ce)001:7592: tshad med pas bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa zhes
NK095(ce)001:7595: de yang 'di ltar spros pa'i mtha' gang la'ang mi
NK095(ce)001:7596: gnas pa'i chos sku bya btsal dang bral ba'i dbyings
NK095(ce)001:7597: sgrib med 'od gsal zang ma thal byung gi klong
NK095(ce)001:7599: 'khor dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams dang khams gsum
NK095(ce)001:7600: gyi sems cana thams cad dgongs pa la bzang ngan
NK095(ce)001:7601: med par khyab gdal lhun 'byams chen por 'byams klas
NK095(ce)001:7603: chos smra brjod bsam yul las 'das pa spros med
NK095(ce)001:7604: rang byung gi ye shes byang chub kyi sems ni
NK095(ce)001:7605: ston pa chos kyi skus skye med dgongs pa'i dbyings
NK095(ce)001:7607: chos dbyings 'od gsal ba'i ye shes 'gags pa med
NK095(ce)001:7608: pa'i ngo bo longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dbang phyug
NK095(ce)001:7609: chen po'i 'og min na bzhugs pa yis /
NK095(ce)001:7610: 'khor sa bcu na bzhugs pa yi byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:7611: dpa' sgrib med rang byung gi chos kyi sprin gyis
NK095(ce)001:7613: chos rang byung dbyings kyi ngo bo byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:7614: kyi rang bzhin de la sku dang ye shes thams
NK095(ce)001:7615: cad gdod nas 'bral ba med par dbyer med mnyam
NK095(ce)001:7616: pa chen po'i bdag nyid du dgongs pa brda'i gsung
NK095(ce)001:7618: rang gdangs 'gag pa med pa'i thugs rje 'pho 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:7619: dang bral ba'i ye shes cir yang 'char du rung
NK095(ce)001:7620: bas sna tshogs nges pa med pa'i sprul pa yi
NK095(ce)001:7621: sku yis / 'khor bzod pa thob pa la sogs
NK095(ce)001:7622: pa gnas gang na lhan du 'dus pa'i 'khor de
NK095(ce)001:7623: rnams la chos 'od gsal dbyings kyi sgrom bu las
NK095(ce)001:7624: byung ba'i theg pa'i rnam grangs ma nges pa gang
NK095(ce)001:7625: la gang gis 'dul ba'i don yang gdul bya rang
NK095(ce)001:7626: rang gi blo dang 'tshams par bstan to //
NK095(ce)001:7628: de la ston pa kun byed nyid kyi phun sum
NK095(ce)001:7629: tshogs pa thams cad lhan du rdzogs nas phrin las
NK095(ce)001:7630: rtsol med du 'jug pa'i dus sngon gyi smon lam
NK095(ce)001:7631: rnam dag btab pa sogs las 'phro bzang po'i rkyen
NK095(ce)001:7632: gyis dus gzhan gyis bar ma chod par ston pa
NK095(ce)001:7633: phun sum tshogs pa kun byed rgyal po nga dang
NK095(ce)001:7634: / nga yi thugs rje 'gag pa med pa'i rtsal
NK095(ce)001:7635: gyi rol pa phrin las kyi byed pa po sems
NK095(ce)001:7636: dpa' rdo rje'i rnam par snang ba'i dus la bab
NK095(ce)001:7637: pa ltar kun byed des bstan pa'i chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:7638: 'khor gyi nang nas sems dpa' rdo rje khyod bka'
NK095(ce)001:7639: yi sdud pa po'i tshul du snang ba 'khor phun
NK095(ce)001:7641: bsam brjod kun las 'das pa 'od gsal spros pa
NK095(ce)001:7642: dang bral ba'i ye shes gnyis su med pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:7643: nyid ston pa kun byed nga yis ji ltar bstan
NK095(ce)001:7644: pa ni chos phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:7645: de ltar ston 'khor bstan pa gsum po tshogs pas
NK095(ce)001:7646: dus dang gnas kyi rang bzhin yang de la ngang
NK095(ce)001:7647: gis tshang ba'i phyir na de'i rtsal las gdul bya
NK095(ce)001:7648: rang rang gi skal ba dang 'tshams par sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:7649: gyi bstan pa rnams snang ba yin pas de ni
NK095(ce)001:7650: phrin las 'jug pa'i dus tshigs su bstan pa yin
NK095(ce)001:7652: kun gyi ston pa byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:7653: ston pas bstan pa'i 'khor tshogs pas //
NK095(ce)001:7654: dus dang gnas ni rang bzhin 'dus //
NK095(ce)001:7657: gong du bstan pa de lta bu'i ston pa dang
NK095(ce)001:7658: bstan pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:7659: po de ni dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK095(ce)001:7660: rin po che ltar du ye nas 'byung bar dkon
NK095(ce)001:7661: pa'i dkon mchog rin po che rnam pa gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:7662: ngo bo nyid du bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7663: kun byed rgyal po nga yi gsang gsum 'gyur ba
NK095(ce)001:7664: med pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin dang gnyis
NK095(ce)001:7665: su med par bshad pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:7666: de la ston pa kun gyi nang nas bla na
NK095(ce)001:7667: med cing 'byung bar dkon pa'i sangsa rgyas dkon mchog
NK095(ce)001:7668: ni chos kyi sku dang longs spyod rdzogs sku dang
NK095(ce)001:7669: sprul pa'i sku ste rnam pa gsum yin la /
NK095(ce)001:7670: bstan pa dam pa'i chos rnams kyi nang nas shin
NK095(ce)001:7671: tu 'byung bar dkon pa'i gsung mchog ni bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:7672: kun gyi snying po 'od gsal byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:7673: rang bzhin brda' tshig gis brjod du med pa'i kun
NK095(ce)001:7674: byed byang chub sems kyi gsung mchog gang zhig sku
NK095(ce)001:7675: gsum gyi gsung gi rang bzhin can du snang ba'o
NK095(ce)001:7676: // 'khor gyi dge 'duna dkon pa'i ngo bo ni sku gsum gyi 'khor du 'dus pa rnams te /
NK095(ce)001:7677: de ni ston pa kun byed rgyal po'i thugs mchog
NK095(ce)001:7678: zab gsal gnyis su med pa kun khyab mnyam brdal
NK095(ce)001:7679: chen po spro bsdu dang bral ba'i rang bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:7680: de / de lta bu'i 'khor gyi ngo bo dge
NK095(ce)001:7681: 'dun dkon mchog de la ni rang rang gang la
NK095(ce)001:7682: gang dgos pa'i chos rnams so so'i blo dang gang
NK095(ce)001:7683: 'tshamsa pa de bzhin du ston par byed pa yin
NK095(ce)001:7684: de / par gsungs pa'o // gsum pa bkod tshul
NK095(ce)001:7685: rang bzhin dang bcas pas mjug bsdu ba la gnyis
NK095(ce)001:7686: de / par gsungs pa'o // te / ston pa
NK095(ce)001:7687: bstan pa 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin bkod tshul dang
NK095(ce)001:7688: de / par gsungs pa'o // te / / kun byed nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:7690: de la phun sum tshogs pa gsum po de nyid
NK095(ce)001:7691: gang gis ji ltar bkod pa'i tshul ni 'di ltar
NK095(ce)001:7692: gsungs te / nga ni ston pa kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:7693: po byang chub kyi sems te spros bral thig le
NK095(ce)001:7694: chen po gcig gi rang bzhin yin pa la /
NK095(ce)001:7695: gdul bya rnams kyi ngor ston pa sku gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:7696: rnam par snang ba yang chos thams cad kun byed
NK095(ce)001:7697: pa'i rgyal po ston pa ngas byas nas mngon du
NK095(ce)001:7699: zhes 'khor gyi dang po ston pa sku gsum po bstan nas /
NK095(ce)001:7700: des bstan pa dam pa'i chos sku gsum ston pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7701: gsung gsum du bkod pa ni phyi mtshan nyid sde
NK095(ce)001:7702: gsum dang nang kri yog sde gsum dang gsang ba
NK095(ce)001:7703: nang rgyud sde gsum du bkod pa de la nang
NK095(ce)001:7704: gses su rnam pa gsum gsum du phye bas theg
NK095(ce)001:7705: pa'i rim pa dgur grags pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:7706: de yang sprul pa'i sku rnams kyi thugs rjesa gdul
NK095(ce)001:7707: bya rnams ji ltar 'dus par byed pa'i chos nyan
NK095(ce)001:7708: rang byang sems te mtshan nyid sde gsum du bsgrags
NK095(ce)001:7709: pa dang / longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus bya ba
NK095(ce)001:7710: byed pa'i phyi rgyud la nang gses su phyi kri
NK095(ce)001:7711: ya nang u pa gsang ba yo ga yi theg
NK095(ce)001:7712: pa gsum du sgrogs cing ston pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7713: ston pa chos kyi sku yi thugs kyi gsang ba
NK095(ce)001:7714: zam mo shin tu rtogs par dka' ba'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7715: can mngon du ston par byed pa'am /
NK095(ce)001:7716: sde snod gsum gyi nang nas mngon par gtogs pa
NK095(ce)001:7717: ma h+aa a nu a ti ste nang rgyud sde
NK095(ce)001:7718: gsum po sgrogs cing ston pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:7719: de lta bu'i sku gsum gyi bstan pa'i ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:7720: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba gsum po de ni
NK095(ce)001:7721: gdul bya'i sems can rnams kyi lus dang ngag dang
NK095(ce)001:7722: yid gsum dang / ston pa kun byed nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:7723: sku gsung thugs gsum ye nas dbyer mi phyed pa
NK095(ce)001:7724: de yi rtsal las 'phros pas rnam pa dgur byung
NK095(ce)001:7725: yid gsum dang / ba yin te / gsang ba spyi rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:7726: sku gsum byin brlabs theg pa dgu //
NK095(ce)001:7727: sems nyid sku gsung thugs yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:7728: sku gcig sku gsung thugs yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:7729: sprul pa sku yi rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:7730: sprul pa gsung gi rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:7731: sprul pa thugs kyi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:7732: longs spyod sku yi rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:7733: longs spyod gsung gi rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:7734: longs spyod thugs kyi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:7735: chos nyid sku yi rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:7736: chos nyid gsung gi rang bzhin dang //
NK095(ce)001:7737: chos nyid thugs kyi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:7739: de lta bu'i theg pa dgu po de la brten
NK095(ce)001:7740: nas theg pa dgu po so so'i lta ba'i la
NK095(ce)001:7741: bzla dgu dang yid ches kyi lung don dgu dang
NK095(ce)001:7742: bgrod bya'i sa lam dgu po de rnams bgrod pa
NK095(ce)001:7743: yisa / mthar 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa spros
NK095(ce)001:7744: bral rang byung gi ye shes bsam brjod las 'das
NK095(ce)001:7745: pa ji bzhin du ston par byed pa'i theg gcig
NK095(ce)001:7746: a ti yo ga kun byed byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:7747: sa la bgrod par byed pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:7748: zhes theg pa de dag thams cad kun byed byang
NK095(ce)001:7749: chub sems su bgrod pa'i lam stegs su bshad pa
NK095(ce)001:7751: yod ni gcig las med pa la //
NK095(ce)001:7752: byung ni theg pa dgu ru byung //
NK095(ce)001:7753: mthong ni snang ba dgu ru mthong //
NK095(ce)001:7754: de yis gang byas las 'bras kun //
NK095(ce)001:7755: rdzogs chen nga yi so nam yin //
NK095(ce)001:7757: 'o na sngar rtsol bcas kyi the ga pa brgyad
NK095(ce)001:7758: po rdzogs pa chen po'i gol sar gsungs pa dang
NK095(ce)001:7759: 'dir lam stegs su bshad pa gnyis mi 'gal lam
NK095(ce)001:7760: snyam na / mi 'gal te sngar gol sar gsungs
NK095(ce)001:7761: pa ni rdzogs pa chen po'i lam du zhugs nas
NK095(ce)001:7762: de'i lta spyod ma rtogs par 'og ma'i lta spyod
NK095(ce)001:7763: ltar spyad na gol sar 'gyur bar gsungs la /
NK095(ce)001:7764: 'dir lam stegs su bshad pa ni 'og ma'i theg
NK095(ce)001:7765: pa rang rang gi lam du zhugs nas de'i lta
NK095(ce)001:7766: spyod bzhin spyad de rim gyis rdzogs la 'jug na
NK095(ce)001:7767: lam stegs su bshad pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:7769: de lta bu'i phun sum tshogs pa'i chos ma lus
NK095(ce)001:7770: pa kun gyi snying po kun byed byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:7771: sems rang gi rang bzhin ni dgag sgrub spang blang
NK095(ce)001:7772: la sogs pa'i bya byed gang yang med par khyab
NK095(ce)001:7773: gdal nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin du bzhugs pa
NK095(ce)001:7774: bsam brjod dang rtsol sgrub kun gyi yul las 'das
NK095(ce)001:7775: pa gnyug ma rang byung gi ye shes chags thogs
NK095(ce)001:7776: dang bral ba yin pas sa lam bgrod pa la
NK095(ce)001:7777: ltos pa med par snying po byang chub kyi sa
NK095(ce)001:7778: la ye nas phyin pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:7781: ye nas rang byung ye shes la //
NK095(ce)001:7782: chos kun dus gsum sgrib med pas //
NK095(ce)001:7783: spong dang len pa mi mnga' ste //
NK095(ce)001:7784: rang byung ye shes 'gyur med gnas //
NK095(ce)001:7786: snying po don gyi rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:7787: dus gsum rnam dag rig pa dbyer med pas //
NK095(ce)001:7788: rig pa dbyer med gcig tu lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:7789: ma bsags ma sbyangs ye sangs rgyas pa'i klong //
NK095(ce)001:7790: mtha' bral rig pa'i klong la bsam zhing brjod du med //
NK095(ce)001:7791: ye nas kun rdzogs bdag nyid lhun rdzogs dang //
NK095(ce)001:7792: sa la mi bgrod lam la mi sbyong ste //
NK095(ce)001:7793: mi rtog ting 'dzin sbyong ba sgyu ma'i nang //
NK095(ce)001:7794: ma btsal rang bzhin bzhag pas grub pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:7796: de ltar mngon du phyung ba'i mdo lung bcu dgos
NK095(ce)001:7797: pa dang bcas pas chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7798: ngo bo thugs rje gsum gnas lugs ji lta ba
NK095(ce)001:7799: nyid gsal bar ston pas dmus long mig phye ba
NK095(ce)001:7802: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las phun
NK095(ce)001:7803: sum tshogs pa shin tu dkon pa'i le'u ste bcu
NK095(ce)001:7804: pa'i 'grel pa'o ////don gnyis pa chos nyid sgrub bsal
NK095(ce)001:7806: kun 'dus rin po che'i le'u sum cu'i bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:7807: de nyid nges pa'i le'u bcu /
NK095(ce)001:7809: ma btsal rdzogs pa'i le'u bcu'o //
NK095(ce)001:7811: dang po chos thams cad kun byed nyid du nges pa'i le'u bcu gcig pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:7815: de ltar kun byed rgyal pos chos thams cad phun
NK095(ce)001:7816: sum tshogs pa lnga'i rang bzhin du bkod par gsungs
NK095(ce)001:7817: pa'i rjes de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed
NK095(ce)001:7818: rgyal pos snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:7819: sems kyis byas shing sems la snang ba sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:7820: rang bzhin las gzhan du med la /
NK095(ce)001:7821: sems kyang gzung 'dzin rnam rtog gi chos su grub
NK095(ce)001:7822: pa med par ye nas rang byung ye shes chen
NK095(ce)001:7823: po'i ngang tshul las 'da' ma myong ba'i phyir na
NK095(ce)001:7824: chos kun gyi rtsa ba rig pa byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:7827: thams cad kun byed nyid du 'du tshul mdor bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:7828: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa //
NK095(ce)001:7831: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon ciga 'di ltar 'khor
NK095(ce)001:7832: 'das lam gsum gyi chos thamsa cad kyi gshis lugs
NK095(ce)001:7833: 'gyur ba med pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK095(ce)001:7834: de dag gang las byung ba'i rtsa ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK095(ce)001:7835: gang zhe na kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga
NK095(ce)001:7836: ni chosa kun gyi ranga bzhina chos nyid 'pho 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:7837: dang bral ba'i bdag nyid yin pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:7838: ston pa nga yi rang bzhin ye grol blo las
NK095(ce)001:7839: 'das pa 'di las ni tha dad du gyur pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7840: chos gzhan du grub pa rdul tsam med pa des
NK095(ce)001:7841: na / chos sku la sogs pa'i ston pa sku gsum po nga yi rang bzhin yin la /
NK095(ce)001:7842: de bzhin du dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyang nga yi rang bzhin yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7843: lam la slob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyang nga yi rang bzhin yina pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7844: sems dpa'i rnal 'byor la sogs pa'i rnal 'byor rnam
NK095(ce)001:7845: pa bzhi po yang nga yi rang bzhin yin la
NK095(ce)001:7846: / 'dod khams dang gzugsa khams dang gzugs med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7847: khams gsum po yang kun byed rgyal po nga yi
NK095(ce)001:7848: rang bzhina du bstan pa yina la /
NK095(ce)001:7849: sa sogs 'byung ba chen po lnga yanga ston pa nga yi ranga bzhina yina pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7850: 'gro ba rgyud drug gi sems can rnams kyang nga yi rang bzhin yin la /
NK095(ce)001:7851: ri gling la sogs pa 'di ltar phyi snang ba
NK095(ce)001:7852: snod kyi 'jig rten ltar snang ba thams cad kyang
NK095(ce)001:7853: nga yi rang bzhin yin la /
NK095(ce)001:7854: de la brten pa na srid pa bcud kyi 'gro
NK095(ce)001:7855: ba thams cada kyang nga yi rang bzhin yin pa
NK095(ce)001:7856: dang / mdor na phyi nang snod bcud gnyis kyis
NK095(ce)001:7857: bsdus pa 'di thams cad ston pa byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:7858: sems nga yi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:7859: kun byed nga yi rang bzhin rig pa byang chub
NK095(ce)001:7860: kyi sems ye stong spros pa dang bral ba 'di
NK095(ce)001:7861: las ni gzhan du gyur pa'i chos gang yang med
NK095(ce)001:7862: pas chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:7863: la 'dus shing / nga yi rtsal las ma byung
NK095(ce)001:7864: ba'am ma 'dus pa yi chos ni gcig kyang med
NK095(ce)001:7865: do zhes mdor bstan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:7866: tshul de ltar rin chen spungs pa las kyang /
NK095(ce)001:7867: 'byung ba sa chu me rlung kyang //
NK095(ce)001:7868: bdag nyid chen po'i de bzhin nyid //
NK095(ce)001:7869: 'gro ba'i rgyud drug snang ba yang //
NK095(ce)001:7870: dag pa'i ye shes rgyu yi dang //
NK095(ce)001:7871: phyi nang snod bcud ma lus kun //
NK095(ce)001:7872: dang po rgyu med dbyings las byung //
NK095(ce)001:7873: tha ma rgyu med dbyings su thim //
NK095(ce)001:7876: ston pa dus dang chos nyid kun byed nyid du bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:7877: rnal 'byor khams gsum rgyud drug kun byed nyid du bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:7878: sku gsum dang dus gsum sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' kun byed nyid du bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:7880: de la dang po ston pa sku gsum nyid kun
NK095(ce)001:7881: byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ji ltar yin
NK095(ce)001:7882: na / kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7883: stong pa'i cha chos sku zag med ye shes kyi
NK095(ce)001:7884: ngoo bo gdod nas ma skyes shing ka dag spros
NK095(ce)001:7885: pa dang bral ba'i rang bzhin dang /
NK095(ce)001:7886: de'i snang cha rang byung 'od gsal ba'i ye shes
NK095(ce)001:7887: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rtag brtan 'pho 'gyur dang
NK095(ce)001:7888: bral ba las skye ba'i rol pa 'gags med rang
NK095(ce)001:7889: byung gi cho 'phrul du shar ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:7890: de'i rtsal snang sprul sku thugsa rje'i rang bzhin 'bad
NK095(ce)001:7891: med shugs 'byung gi rol pa 'gags pa med pa
NK095(ce)001:7892: rnam pa gsum du byung ba de ni sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:7893: gyi ston pa gsum gyi rang bzhin yin la /
NK095(ce)001:7894: de bzhin du sngar 'das pa'i dus dang bar pa
NK095(ce)001:7895: da lta yi dus dang phyi pa ma 'ong ba'i
NK095(ce)001:7897: ston pa kun byed rgyal po nga nyid ye nas
NK095(ce)001:7898: dus gsum 'pho 'gyur dang bral bas kun bzang yangs
NK095(ce)001:7899: pa chen po'i klong na dus bzhi mnyam nyid gcig
NK095(ce)001:7900: tu gnas pa'i rang bzhin las gzhan du med de
NK095(ce)001:7902: nga ni dus gsum rtag par bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:7903: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK095(ce)001:7904: dri med rang byung 'od gsal ba //
NK095(ce)001:7905: dus gsum gcig ste rtag par bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:7906: zhes gsungs pa ltar dus gsum du byon pa'i sangsa
NK095(ce)001:7907: rgyas thamsa cad kyang snying po byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:7908: dus bzhi mnyam pa chen po gcig tu gnas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7909: phyir na / de lta bu'i dus gsum po de
NK095(ce)001:7910: yang kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga yi rang
NK095(ce)001:7911: bzhina du bstan pa yina pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7912: nga nyid gzung 'dzin ye bral chen po'i dgongs par rang shar pasa byang ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:7913: nam mkha' bzhin du 'khor 'das kun la mnyam brdal
NK095(ce)001:7914: du khyab cing rig pa'i klong du rdzogs pas chub
NK095(ce)001:7915: pa dang / gzhi klong rnam par dag pa'i rtsal
NK095(ce)001:7916: 'gags med rang byung du shar ba'i snang srid kyi
NK095(ce)001:7917: chos rnams kun gyi snying po byed pa'i phyir na
NK095(ce)001:7918: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid byang chub kyi semsa
NK095(ce)001:7919: kyang kun byed nga yi rang bzhin yin no zhes
NK095(ce)001:7920: pa dang / gsungs so // gnyis pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:7921: gzhan yang kun byed nga ni rgyu rkyen gang la
NK095(ce)001:7922: ma ltos par rang byung 'dus ma byas pa spros
NK095(ce)001:7923: bral thig le nyag cig tu gnas pa yin la
NK095(ce)001:7924: / nga yi rang bzhin mkha' khyab dbyings kyi rdo
NK095(ce)001:7925: rje chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi don rnal ma
NK095(ce)001:7926: la sems dpa'i rnal 'byor la sogs pa rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:7927: bzhi po'i rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi blo yang
NK095(ce)001:7928: dag par 'byor pa yi sgo nas bzhir dbyes kyang
NK095(ce)001:7929: don la kun byed byang chub sems kyi don rnal
NK095(ce)001:7930: ma gcig tu 'byor ba las tha dad med pa
NK095(ce)001:7931: des na rnal 'byor bzhi yang kun byed nga yi
NK095(ce)001:7932: rang bzhin yin par bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7933: kun byed nga yi lus snang ba 'dod pa'i srid
NK095(ce)001:7934: pa ngag phyed snang gzugs kyi srid pa yid mi
NK095(ce)001:7935: snang ba gzugs med pa'i srid pa gsum yin pa
NK095(ce)001:7936: las gzhan gang yang med pas khams gsum po dang
NK095(ce)001:7937: po byung yang nga yi rang bzhin de las byung
NK095(ce)001:7938: ba dang / 'dus kyang nga yi rang bzhin sgo gsum po de la 'dus pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:7939: yin yang nga yi ngo bo stong gsal thugs rje
NK095(ce)001:7940: gsum po de nyid yin pas na khams gsum po
NK095(ce)001:7941: thams cad nga yi rang bzhin yin par bshad de
NK095(ce)001:7943: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid ni //
NK095(ce)001:7944: ma skyes stong pa skye ba med //
NK095(ce)001:7945: de ni gzugs med khams yin no //
NK095(ce)001:7946: skye ba'i cho 'phrul gzugs snang ba //
NK095(ce)001:7947: de ni gzugs kyi khams yin te //
NK095(ce)001:7949: de ni 'dod pa'i khams su yin //
NK095(ce)001:7951: de bzhin du kun byed nga yi rang bzhin stong
NK095(ce)001:7952: gsal 'gag pa med pa'i rang mdangs su shar pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7953: 'byung ba chen po rnam pa lnga ni nga yi
NK095(ce)001:7954: ngo bo ye shes rnam pa lnga yi rang mdangs
NK095(ce)001:7957: rang las byung ba'i ye shes lnga //
NK095(ce)001:7958: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor thugs kyi mtshon //
NK095(ce)001:7959: mtshan nyid me chu sa rlung lnga //
NK095(ce)001:7960: rang las byung ba'i chos nyid de //
NK095(ce)001:7961: zhes gsungs pa ltar te des na gsal la go
NK095(ce)001:7962: phye ba'i rang bzhin nam mkha' dang yang zhing g.yo
NK095(ce)001:7963: ba'i mtshan nyid rlung dang rlan zhing sdud pa'i rang
NK095(ce)001:7964: bzhin chu dang sra zhing rten pa'i mtshan nyid sa
NK095(ce)001:7965: dang smin cing dro ba'i mtshan nyid can me yi
NK095(ce)001:7966: rnam par snang ba lnga yang kun byed nga yi
NK095(ce)001:7967: rang bzhin mngon du phyung ste bstan pa yin la
NK095(ce)001:7968: / kun byed nga yi rig rtsal 'gag med kyi
NK095(ce)001:7969: thugsa rjes mngon du phyung nas rang byung 'dus ma
NK095(ce)001:7970: byas pa'i ye shes rnam pa lnga bstan pa ni
NK095(ce)001:7971: / / ngo ma shes pa'i dbang gis 'gro ba
NK095(ce)001:7972: rigs drug gi sems can du snang ba ma lus
NK095(ce)001:7973: pa yang don la kun byed nga yi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:7974: gdod nas skye ba med pa las skye ba'i cho
NK095(ce)001:7975: 'phrul 'gags med kyi rol bar bstan pa yin pa
NK095(ce)001:7976: / / ste / mdor na kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:7977: nga yi rang bzhin las logs su ma gyur pa'i
NK095(ce)001:7978: snang srid snod bcud kyis bsdus pa yi chos 'di
NK095(ce)001:7979: thams cad kun rgyu rkyen gyi byed pa gzhan med
NK095(ce)001:7980: par rig pa byang chub sems kyi rtsal las chos
NK095(ce)001:7981: thams cad rang byung du shar ba yin pas kun
NK095(ce)001:7982: byed ngasa byas pa yin pa dang nga las byung
NK095(ce)001:7983: ba'i snang ba yin pa'i phyir na snying po rang
NK095(ce)001:7984: byung gi ye shes ngor ma 'dus pa'i chos ni
NK095(ce)001:7985: gcig kyang meda de mdo bcu las /
NK095(ce)001:7986: sangs rgyas sku dang ye shes dang //
NK095(ce)001:7987: sems can lus dang bag chags dang //
NK095(ce)001:7988: snang dang srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:7989: byang chub sems dang dbyings su 'dus //
NK095(ce)001:7992: ston pa byang chub kyi sems nga las byung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:7993: ston pa sku gsum yang kun byed byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:7994: sems nga yi rang bzhin lhun grub rnam pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:7995: las gzhan du med pas ston pa sku gsum yang
NK095(ce)001:7996: rang byung gi ye shes nyid du bstan te /
NK095(ce)001:7998: mi g.yo rang bzhin gnas pa chos sku yin //
NK095(ce)001:7999: gsal la rtog pa med pas longs sku yin //
NK095(ce)001:8000: sems la dbang thob cir yang bsgyur nus pas //
NK095(ce)001:8001: de ni thugs rje sprul pa'i sku //
NK095(ce)001:8003: snga ba 'das pa'i dus dang bar ma da lta
NK095(ce)001:8004: yi dus dang phyi ba ma 'ong pa'i dus te
NK095(ce)001:8005: dus gsum gyi dbye ba rnam pa gsum po gcig
NK095(ce)001:8006: tu 'dres pa'i dus bzhi chos nyid kyi dbyings na
NK095(ce)001:8007: dgongs klong dbyer med gcig tu gnas pa'i sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:8008: thams cad kyang snga phyi dus kyi dbye ba med
NK095(ce)001:8009: par kun byed rgyal po'i rang bzhin du gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:8010: dang / gzung 'dzin rtog pa'i dra ba ci rigs
NK095(ce)001:8011: pa dang bral ba'i sar gnas kyi byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:8012: dpa' ma lus pa yang kun byed nga yi rang
NK095(ce)001:8013: bzhin bsal bzhag bral ba'i chos nyid mngon du bsgrub
NK095(ce)001:8014: par byed pa la semsa mi skrag cing dapa'a bar
NK095(ce)001:8015: byed pa las gzhan du med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:8016: sems dpa'i rnal 'byor la sogs pa rnal 'byor rnam
NK095(ce)001:8017: pa bzhi yis chos nyid rnal ma'i don la blo
NK095(ce)001:8018: ji bzhin du rnal mar 'jog pa yang kun byed
NK095(ce)001:8019: nga yi rang bzhin byang chub sems kyi ngang la
NK095(ce)001:8020: rnal du 'jog para byed pa yin pas na de
NK095(ce)001:8021: dag thams cad kun byed nyid du 'dus pa yin
NK095(ce)001:8022: tee / nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa las //
NK095(ce)001:8023: sangs rgyas kun dang de yi sras //
NK095(ce)001:8024: kun kyang rtsa ba byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:8025: bcos med rig pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK095(ce)001:8026: rang gsal ye shes 'od la bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:8029: de ltar mdor na ston pa kun byed rgyal posa
NK095(ce)001:8030: 'khor 'das kyi chos thamsa cad kun byas pa bzhina
NK095(ce)001:8031: du ji ltar snang ba'i chos thamsa cad sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:8032: rang byung gi ye shes kun byeda rgyal po nyid
NK095(ce)001:8033: la lhun grub rdzogs pa chen po'i tshul du 'dus
NK095(ce)001:8034: shing gnas pa yin no zhes gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:8035: rin po che rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:8036: thams cad byang chub sems las byung ba'i snang ba ste //
NK095(ce)001:8037: de las ma gtogs dngos po gang yang med //
NK095(ce)001:8040: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las chos
NK095(ce)001:8041: thams cad kyi rtsa ba byang chub kyi semsa kun
NK095(ce)001:8042: byed rgyal po nyid kho nar 'dus pa'i le'u ste
NK095(ce)001:8043: bcu gcig pa'i 'grel ba'o ////don gnyis pa sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:8044: kun byed rgyal po rgyud lung kun gyi rtsa ba
NK095(ce)001:8045: yin pa'i le'u bcu gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:8049: de ltar chos thams cad rang byung ye shes chen
NK095(ce)001:8050: po rtsa ba byang chub sems su 'dus par bstan
NK095(ce)001:8051: pa de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:8052: po nga yis 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK095(ce)001:8053: cad gang las byung zhing snang ba kun byed nyid
NK095(ce)001:8054: kyi rang bzhin yin par ston pa'i khungsa kyi mdo
NK095(ce)001:8055: 'di gsungs so // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:8056: kun gyi lung khungs kun byed nyid du phyir bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:8057: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:8058: kun byed nyid du 'du bas don bsdu ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:8060: kye sems dpa' chen po kun byed nga ni chos
NK095(ce)001:8061: kun gyi rang bzhin gtan la 'beb par byed pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8063: des na ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thamsa cad
NK095(ce)001:8064: kun dus dang rnam pa thams cad du ston pa
NK095(ce)001:8065: kun byed nga las byung ba yin par shes par
NK095(ce)001:8066: gyis shig /de ltar sems dpa' rdo rje rang gis
NK095(ce)001:8067: ji ltar shes shing rtogs pa bzhin du srid dang
NK095(ce)001:8068: zhi bas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas
NK095(ce)001:8069: su gyur cing thams cad gtan la 'beb par byed
NK095(ce)001:8070: pas spyi khungs chen po yin pa'i tshul 'di nyon
NK095(ce)001:8071: la gdul bya gzhan rnams la yang chos rnams thamsa
NK095(ce)001:8072: cad 'di ltar du lung ston par mdzod cig ces
NK095(ce)001:8073: so // gnyis pa la bdun te /
NK095(ce)001:8074: lung chen kun gyi rgyal por bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:8075: man ngag kun gyi rtsa bar bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:8076: mdo rgyud kun gyi spyi 'grel yin pa /
NK095(ce)001:8077: bstan pa kun gyi yang rtser brjod pa /
NK095(ce)001:8078: theg pa kun gyi nying khur gsungs pa /
NK095(ce)001:8079: ye shes chen po'i snang ba mched pa /
NK095(ce)001:8080: kun rtog nyon mongs d+r+wa ba gcod pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:8082: 'di ltar theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyi lugs
NK095(ce)001:8083: ltar spong 'gog sbyangs bgrod sogs kyi rtsol sgrub la
NK095(ce)001:8084: mi ltos par chos thams cad gdod nas gnyis med
NK095(ce)001:8085: ye shes chen po gcig gi rang bzhin yin pas
NK095(ce)001:8086: dgag sgrub spang blang gang yang mi dgos pa'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:8087: drang thad du ston par byed pa kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:8088: po byang chub kyi sems nga ni sku gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:8089: rgyal ba rnams kyis lung chen po gsungs pa kun
NK095(ce)001:8090: gyi nang nas rgyal po lta bu nga yin pas
NK095(ce)001:8091: / kun byed byang chub sems kyi nges pa'i lung
NK095(ce)001:8092: 'di la brten nas ston pa sku gsum po yang
NK095(ce)001:8093: dang po kun bzang gdod ma'i mgon po'am dang po'i
NK095(ce)001:8094: sangs rgyas nga las byung ba yin la /
NK095(ce)001:8095: de la lung zhes bya ba de gang zhe na
NK095(ce)001:8096: lung zhes pa ni sku gsum gyi ston pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:8097: kyis gsungs pa'i bka' la gdags zhing de thams cad
NK095(ce)001:8098: gang las 'byung ba'i khungs dang kun gyi nang nas
NK095(ce)001:8099: rtsol med ye sangs rgyas pa'i dgongs pa ston pas
NK095(ce)001:8100: rgyal po lta bu ni kun byed nga nyid yin
NK095(ce)001:8101: par shes par gyis shig /ces pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:8103: de bzhin du man ngaga kun gyi rtsa ba'am bstan
NK095(ce)001:8104: don mthar thug pa yang chos rnams kun gyi gnas
NK095(ce)001:8105: lugs sku gsum lhun grub chen po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:8106: sems nga nyid yin pas na sems nyid skye ba
NK095(ce)001:8107: med pa'i gnas lugs 'di las ma gtogs pa yi
NK095(ce)001:8108: chos nyid spros bral rang byung gi ye shes rang
NK095(ce)001:8109: byung kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa ni dus gsum
NK095(ce)001:8110: gyi sangs rgyas rnams dang khams gsum gyi sems can
NK095(ce)001:8111: rnams la kun byed nga yis yang dag par bstan
NK095(ce)001:8112: pa med do // gsum pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:8113: gsang sngags kyi rgyud dang zab rgyas kyi mdo sde
NK095(ce)001:8114: kun gyi brjod bya mthar thug gtan la 'beb par
NK095(ce)001:8115: byed pa'i kun gyi spyi 'grel chen po yang kun
NK095(ce)001:8116: byed rgyal po 'di nyid yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:8117: rgyud sde phyi nang dang mdo sde mtshan nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:8118: theg pa rnams ston pa'i sku gsum gyi ston pa
NK095(ce)001:8119: gsum yang kun byed nga yi rang bzhin mngon du
NK095(ce)001:8120: phyung ba yin pa des na ston pa dang ni
NK095(ce)001:8121: bstan pa dam pa'i chos gnyis ka yi spyi 'grel
NK095(ce)001:8122: yin no zhes de dag thams cad kun byed byang
NK095(ce)001:8123: chub semsa kyi rtsal 'gag pa med pa las snang
NK095(ce)001:8124: bar byas pas kun gyi 'byung gnas yin pa dang
NK095(ce)001:8125: mdo rgyud de dag gi brjod bya mthar thug pa
NK095(ce)001:8126: yang kun byed nyid yin pa'i phyir te /
NK095(ce)001:8128: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK095(ce)001:8129: 'byung ga nas gtan la 'bebs pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:8130: kun gyi spyi 'grel yin par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:8133: kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi sems nga ni
NK095(ce)001:8134: bstan pa dam pa'i chos ma lus pa kun gyi
NK095(ce)001:8135: yang rtse yin par yang bshad de /
NK095(ce)001:8136: des tshul ji ltar zhe na kun byed nga las
NK095(ce)001:8137: byung ba'i ston pa sku gsum gyis bstan pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:8138: 'dul ba mado sde mngon pa gsum dang sngags kyi
NK095(ce)001:8139: tan tra chen po so so'i sde ni 'bum sde
NK095(ce)001:8140: dang de dag gi brjod bya shin tu zab pa
NK095(ce)001:8141: spros bcas bskyed pa'i rim pa dang spros med rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:8142: pa'i rim pa ston par byed pa'i gsang ba bla
NK095(ce)001:8143: na med pa la sogs pa mdor na rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:8144: can gyi theg pa kun kyang 'dir rtsol sgrub las
NK095(ce)001:8145: 'adsa pa spros bral blo 'das ye 'byams chen po
NK095(ce)001:8146: nga yi sa la bgrod dgos shing /
NK095(ce)001:8147: dper na dma' ba'i lung nas lhun po'i rtse mo
NK095(ce)001:8148: mthong bar mi nus pa ltar rtsol sgrub can gyi
NK095(ce)001:8149: theg pa de nyid kyis rtsol sgrub kun las 'das
NK095(ce)001:8150: pa stong gsal thugs rje kun khyab kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:8151: can kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga nyid mi
NK095(ce)001:8152: mthong ba des na bstan pa kun gyi yang rtse
NK095(ce)001:8155: rgyu 'bras theg pa kun las khyad 'phags pas //
NK095(ce)001:8156: theg pa'i yang rtse yin par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:8159: theg pa kun gyi rtse mo gsang sngags kyi theg
NK095(ce)001:8160: pa yin la de'i kyang rtse mo rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:8161: po yin pas theg pa'i yang rtse yin par gsungs
NK095(ce)001:8163: kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi sems nga ni
NK095(ce)001:8164: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa kun gyi nying khu'am yang
NK095(ce)001:8165: zhun lta bu yin par yang bshad de /
NK095(ce)001:8166: 'di ltar ston pa gsum gyi chos lam stegs tsam la gnas pa'i kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa /
NK095(ce)001:8167: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa /
NK095(ce)001:8168: ma h+aa a nu gnyis dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:8169: de lta bu'i theg pa gsum po thams cad nges
NK095(ce)001:8170: pa don gyi snying po zab gsal gnyis su med
NK095(ce)001:8171: pa'i ye shes mthar thug par gnas par byed pa
NK095(ce)001:8172: yi theg pa gcig las med la nges pa'i theg
NK095(ce)001:8173: pa gcig po de ni rgyal ba kun gyis bgrod
NK095(ce)001:8174: pa gcig pu pa theg gcig byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:8175: sa 'di nyid yin pa'i phyir na de ni theg
NK095(ce)001:8176: pa kun gyi nying khur gyur pas dus gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:8177: sangs rgyas thams cad gang nas gshegs pa'i shul lam
NK095(ce)001:8178: chen po yin par bshad de /
NK095(ce)001:8180: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi lam yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:8181: rnam dag lam chen yin par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:8184: kye kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga ni nam
NK095(ce)001:8185: mkha'i dbyings ma lus pa khyab cing mtha' yas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8186: 'gro ba kun gyi rgyu lhan skyes dang rkyen kun
NK095(ce)001:8187: brtags kyi ma rig pa yi mun pa'i sprin tshogs
NK095(ce)001:8188: shin tu stug cing spang dka' ba ma lus pa
NK095(ce)001:8189: kun bsal bar byas nas mkhyen pa'i ye shes 'od
NK095(ce)001:8190: gsal chen po'i snang ba phyogs med du mched par
NK095(ce)001:8192: de yang tshul ji lta bu yi sgo nas ma
NK095(ce)001:8193: rig pa'i mun pa sel zhing ye shes kyi snang
NK095(ce)001:8194: ba mched par byed pa lags zhes bstan pa yin
NK095(ce)001:8195: zhe na / ji ltar snang srid snod bcud du
NK095(ce)001:8196: snang ba'i chos rnams thamsa cada kun gzhan du ci
NK095(ce)001:8197: yang med par rig pa byang chub sems kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:8198: nyid stong chen de bzhin nyid kyi rtsal ma 'gags
NK095(ce)001:8199: par shar ba'i snang ba yin pa la sems can
NK095(ce)001:8200: rnams kyis de ltar du ma rig ste /
NK095(ce)001:8201: chos can so so'i mtshan mar zhen cing chags pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8202: ma rig gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa'i mun par 'thib
NK095(ce)001:8203: pa yi dbang gis khams gsum 'khor ba'i duhkhasa rtag
NK095(ce)001:8205: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cada kun byed
NK095(ce)001:8206: byang chub sems kyis byas pa'am thog ma'i 'od gsal
NK095(ce)001:8207: gzhi dbyings chen po'i gdangs 'gags pa med pa'i rtsal
NK095(ce)001:8208: gzhi snang phyir gsal gyi rnam par shar ba yin
NK095(ce)001:8209: pa'i phyir na kun byed byang chub sems kyi rtsal
NK095(ce)001:8210: snang du chos thams cad shar zhing /
NK095(ce)001:8211: de ltar shar ba'i dus nyid nas gzhi med rtsa
NK095(ce)001:8212: bral chen po'i rang bzhin chos dbyings skye ba med
NK095(ce)001:8213: pa'i dbyings su ye grol du song ba'i tshul rig
NK095(ce)001:8215: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun la
NK095(ce)001:8216: bdag gzhan dang yul yul can la sogs par so
NK095(ce)001:8217: sora rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi mun pa de nyid
NK095(ce)001:8219: spros bral rang byung gi ye shes lhun grub 'od
NK095(ce)001:8220: gsal chen po gzhi rdzogs 'pho 'gyur dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:8221: nam mkha' lta bu'i snang ba mched par byed pa
NK095(ce)001:8222: des na ma rig pa'i mun pa thams cad sgrib
NK095(ce)001:8223: bral zang thal chen por sel ba'am dngas shing rang
NK095(ce)001:8224: byung ye shes kyi snang ba mched cing rgyas par
NK095(ce)001:8225: byed do ces bya bar bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:8227: kye sems dapa'a chen po kun byed byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:8228: sems ngas ni 'gro ba rnams kyi rgyud kyi blang
NK095(ce)001:8229: dor rtsol sgrub la zhen pa la sogs pa'i rnam
NK095(ce)001:8230: par rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba ma lus pa dral bar
NK095(ce)001:8231: byas nas ni dug lnga'i nyon mongsa pa yi 'dzin
NK095(ce)001:8232: zhen gyi srid pa'i phreng thag ma lus pa rtsa
NK095(ce)001:8233: ba nas gcod par byed pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:8234: de yang tshul ji ltar zhe na phyi nang snod
NK095(ce)001:8235: bcud du snang ba'i chos 'di dag thams cad la
NK095(ce)001:8236: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa can rnams kyis rang
NK095(ce)001:8237: sems las gzhan du rtog pa'i dbang gis dgag sgrub
NK095(ce)001:8238: dang blang dor sna tshogs su byed de /
NK095(ce)001:8239: de yang blo dman nyan rang gi rigs can la
NK095(ce)001:8240: las 'dod yon dang nyon mongs pa sogs la thar
NK095(ce)001:8241: ba'i srog la rgol pa'i dug tu mthong nas de
NK095(ce)001:8242: nyid gnyen pos spong ba dang 'gog par bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:8243: yul du rtog cing 'dzin la gnas par byed pa
NK095(ce)001:8244: dang / byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ba la
NK095(ce)001:8245: las sems chags zhing zhen pa yi yul du mthong
NK095(ce)001:8246: nas de las bzlog pa'i phyir du kun rdzob sgyu
NK095(ce)001:8247: ma lta bu dang don dam stong pa nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:8248: rang bzhin du bden pa gnyis kyi tshul du gtan
NK095(ce)001:8249: la phab te gang la'ang ma chags pa yi thabs
NK095(ce)001:8250: la rtog cing dpyod pa yi lam la gnas par
NK095(ce)001:8251: dang / byed pa dang / la las te kri
NK095(ce)001:8252: yog sde gsum gyi theg pa ba rnams kyis gzung
NK095(ce)001:8253: 'dzin gyi dri ma rnam par dag par bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:8254: yul du mthong nas dag pa gsum dang bdag gnas
NK095(ce)001:8255: yo byad thams cad byin gyis rlabs pa dang cho
NK095(ce)001:8256: 'phrul gyis te cho 'phrul bzhi la sogs pa'i thabs
NK095(ce)001:8257: kyi lha dang bdag gnyis rje dang khol gyi tshul
NK095(ce)001:8258: lam spun nam grogs kyi tshul du rtog cing sgom
NK095(ce)001:8260: la las te ma h+aa dang a nu'i lam du
NK095(ce)001:8261: zhugs pa rnams kyis chos thams cad rang gi ngo
NK095(ce)001:8262: bos dag pa chen po yi ranga bzhin yin pa
NK095(ce)001:8263: la 'on kyang gzung 'dzin gyi dri mas bsgrib pa
NK095(ce)001:8264: yod pa'i phyir de nyid bsal nas dag pa mngon
NK095(ce)001:8265: du 'gyur ba' phyir du bsnyen sgrub rnam pa bzhis
NK095(ce)001:8266: sgrub par 'doda pa'i rtog pa yid la byed pa
NK095(ce)001:8267: ste / des na 'og ma'i theg pa brgyad po
NK095(ce)001:8268: de dag thamsa cad rtog pa'i d+r+wa bar tshud pa
NK095(ce)001:8269: la kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga yis snang
NK095(ce)001:8270: srid 'khor 'das thams cad rang byung ye shes kyi
NK095(ce)001:8271: rtsal snang mnyam nyid gcig gi ngo bor gdod nas
NK095(ce)001:8272: ye sangs rgyas par ston pa'i sgo nas sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:8273: rang rig pa'i ye shes las gzhan ma zhig yin
NK095(ce)001:8274: par rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba thams cad rig stong ye
NK095(ce)001:8275: shes chen po'i mtshon gyis dral bar byas nas ni
NK095(ce)001:8276: ste / / 'di ltar snang ba'i yul la nga
NK095(ce)001:8277: bdag so sor rtog pa'i zhen 'dzin nyon mongs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8278: phreng thag ma lus pa gcoda par byed ces gsungsa
NK095(ce)001:8279: ste / / so // de ltar yang mdo bcu las /
NK095(ce)001:8280: spang 'geg sbyang zhing bgrod pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:8281: gzung 'dzin blang dor bya ba dang //
NK095(ce)001:8282: lta sgom rtsol sgrub byar med de //
NK095(ce)001:8283: lam dang gnyen pos bcos med par //
NK095(ce)001:8284: byang sems kun bzang rang bzhin du //
NK095(ce)001:8285: nga yis bstan pa'i don 'di ni //
NK095(ce)001:8286: byang chub sems kyi lung chen yin //
NK095(ce)001:8287: rgyud dang mdo sde'i spyi 'grel yin //
NK095(ce)001:8288: man ngag kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:8289: gsung rab kun gyi snying po yi //
NK095(ce)001:8290: bstan pa kun gyi yang rtse yin //
NK095(ce)001:8291: theg pa kun gyi nying khu yin //
NK095(ce)001:8292: ma rig pa yi mun sel yin //
NK095(ce)001:8293: rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba 'di yis sel //
NK095(ce)001:8296: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK095(ce)001:8298: kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi sems nga ni
NK095(ce)001:8299: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs bya rtsol bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:8300: rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:8301: sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis nga yi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:8302: chos dbyings spros bral chen po'i ngo bo brjod bral
NK095(ce)001:8303: 'dus ma byas pa'i gnas lugs 'di tshul bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:8305: ji ltar snang ba'i chos 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis
NK095(ce)001:8306: bsdus pa 'di rnams thams cad kun kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:8307: las gzhan du med par chos dbyings byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:8308: kyi rang bzhin blo 'das mnyam pa chen po ru
NK095(ce)001:8309: lung ston par mdzod cig dang /
NK095(ce)001:8310: sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyi nga yi nges pa
NK095(ce)001:8311: don gyi lung rtsol sgrub bral ba'i rang bzhin 'di
NK095(ce)001:8312: 'khor gyi tshogs la bstan par gyur na khyod la
NK095(ce)001:8313: dad pas 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogsa thams cad kyis chos
NK095(ce)001:8314: nyid rtsol sgrub dang bral ba kun byed nga yi
NK095(ce)001:8315: rang bzhin ji bzhin rtogs par gyur nas 'dus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8316: 'khor tshogs kun kyang ston pa nga yi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:8317: dang dbyer med pa nyid du 'gyur ba yin la
NK095(ce)001:8318: / de ltar kun kyang rang byung ye shes chen
NK095(ce)001:8319: po kun byed nga yi rang bzhina du gyur pa
NK095(ce)001:8320: de'i tshe na ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thamsa
NK095(ce)001:8321: / cad la / 'gro ba kun kyang nyan rang
NK095(ce)001:8322: ltar sdug kun gyi ngo bor bltas nas spong zhing
NK095(ce)001:8324: byang sems ltar bden pa gnyis su lta bas chos nyid du sbyong bar mi byed la /
NK095(ce)001:8325: phyi rgyud ltar gtsang sbras lha rnams mnyes par byed
NK095(ce)001:8326: pa dang dag pa gsum dang byin gyis rlob pa
NK095(ce)001:8327: sogs kyi blang dor mi byed cing /
NK095(ce)001:8328: nang rgyud 'og ma gnyis ltar tinga nge 'dzin gyis
NK095(ce)001:8329: sems rtog tshogs thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed
NK095(ce)001:8330: pa sogs kyis rtsol ba dang sgrub par mi byed
NK095(ce)001:8331: par rtsol med bde ba chen po'i sa la gnas
NK095(ce)001:8332: par 'gyur la / de ltar kun byed rgyal po'i
NK095(ce)001:8333: rang bzhin 'di rtogs par gyur tshe rtsol sgrub mi
NK095(ce)001:8334: dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:8335: 'di ltar chos thams cad kun byed nga yi rang
NK095(ce)001:8336: bzhin gdod nas ye grol byar med chen po ru
NK095(ce)001:8337: byas zin pas kun byed nga ru 'khor 'das kyi
NK095(ce)001:8338: chos thams cada chos nyid ye klong chen por snang
NK095(ce)001:8339: ba a 'thas kyi gol sgrib med par phyams brdal
NK095(ce)001:8340: du dengs shing / de yang stong pa phyang chad
NK095(ce)001:8341: lta bu ma yin par ka dag dang lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:8342: dbyer med pa'i gshis lugs blo 'das spros pa dang
NK095(ce)001:8343: bral ba ye grol mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:8344: du grub zin pas ye nas mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:8345: rang bzhin du bzhugs pa nga yis da gzod spang
NK095(ce)001:8346: blang bya rtsol la brten nas mnyam pa nyid du
NK095(ce)001:8347: sgrub par bya mi dgos te /
NK095(ce)001:8349: thams cad ye nas dbyings su grol zin pas //
NK095(ce)001:8350: da gzod 'bad pas sus kyang grol mi dgos //
NK095(ce)001:8351: de la 'bad rtsol byas kyang don med pas //
NK095(ce)001:8352: ma byed ma byed rtsol zhing sgrub ma byed //
NK095(ce)001:8353: ces gsungs pa ltar rtsol sgrub kyi sgo nas mnyam
NK095(ce)001:8354: nyid chos sku'i dgongs pa zhig da gsar du sgrub
NK095(ce)001:8355: par bya mi dgos par kun tu bzang po'am kun
NK095(ce)001:8356: byed chos sku'i ston pa nga yis sngar nas lung
NK095(ce)001:8360: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las nges
NK095(ce)001:8361: par lung khungs bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8362: 'grel ba'o ////don gsum pa sems nyid kun byed nges
NK095(ce)001:8363: par bshad pa'i le'u bcu gsum pa la gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:8367: de ltar sems nyid kun byed rgyal po rgyud lung
NK095(ce)001:8368: kun gyi rtsa ba yin par bstan pa de nas
NK095(ce)001:8369: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po des rang
NK095(ce)001:8370: nyid sku gsum gyi rgyal ba'i bka' lung thams cad
NK095(ce)001:8371: kyi rgyal po yin pa'i phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:8372: theg pa gong 'og gi chos thams cad kyi spyi
NK095(ce)001:8373: yi lung chen po kun byed byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:8374: theg pa 'di nyid tshul ji ltar bshad pa'i bshad
NK095(ce)001:8376: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:8377: 'chad tshul lnga yi rnam grangs bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:8382: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /snying po byang
NK095(ce)001:8383: chub kyi sems pa ni rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams
NK095(ce)001:8384: cad kyi spyi yi lung chen po yin pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:8385: na the tshom gyi sgro 'dogs sel bar byed pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8386: gtan tshigsa don gyi bshad lugs rnam pa lnga ni
NK095(ce)001:8387: 'og nas 'byung ba 'di ltar spyi don rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:8389: gang zhe na khungs la yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:8390: du lo rgyus don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa dang
NK095(ce)001:8391: / chos kun sems su rtogs pa'i phyir du rtsa ba don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:8392: theg pa'i shan thang 'byed pa'i phyir du yo ga don gyi bshad lugsa bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:8393: rtsol sgrub bya mi dgos pa'i phyir du dgos pa don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:8394: don nyid ji bzhin rtogs par bya ba'i phyir du
NK095(ce)001:8395: tshig gi don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa dang rnam
NK095(ce)001:8397: de la man ngag zab mo 'di nyid 'chad pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8398: tshe na chos zab mo ji ltar byung ba'i lo
NK095(ce)001:8399: rgyus bsnyad par ma byas na gdul bya rnams yid
NK095(ce)001:8400: mi ches pa'i skyon du 'gyur bar gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:8402: lo rgyus don gyis ma bshad na //
NK095(ce)001:8403: yid mi ches pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:8404: zhes gsungs pa de ltar bu'i phyir na dang po
NK095(ce)001:8405: gdul bya rnams la yid ches pa yi khungs bstan
NK095(ce)001:8406: pa'i phyir du bstan pa'i snying po 'di nyid ji
NK095(ce)001:8407: ltar byung ba'i lo rgyus kyi don gyi bshad lugs
NK095(ce)001:8409: de'i rjes su snang srid kyi chos kun rtsa ba
NK095(ce)001:8410: chos nyid byang chub sems su 'dus par rtogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8411: dgos pa yod pa'i phyir na des na rtsa ba'i
NK095(ce)001:8412: don de bstan par bya ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:8413: de nas rtsa ba de las 'phros pa'i theg pa'i
NK095(ce)001:8414: khyad par so sor 'byed pa'i phyir du yo ga
NK095(ce)001:8415: don gyi rtsa ba bstan para bya la /
NK095(ce)001:8416: 'on kyang gdul bya'i blo rim la ltos nas theg
NK095(ce)001:8417: pa'i rnam grangs de ltar bstan kyang dngos don la
NK095(ce)001:8418: rtsol sgrub gang yang bya mi dgos par rtsol med
NK095(ce)001:8419: ye sangs rgyas par bstan pa'i phyir du dgos ched
NK095(ce)001:8420: don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa'i dgos pa de ru
NK095(ce)001:8422: de nas de lta bu'i rtsol sgrub kun las 'das
NK095(ce)001:8423: pa mi rtog mnyam pa nyid kyi don de mtshon
NK095(ce)001:8424: byed tshig la brten nas rtogs par bya ba'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:8425: du de'i rjes su tshig gi don de ji lta
NK095(ce)001:8426: ba bzhin tu sgra ru brjod par bya ba yin
NK095(ce)001:8427: no // de ltar yang lung snga ma'i 'phros las /
NK095(ce)001:8428: rtsa ba'i don gyis ma bshad na //
NK095(ce)001:8429: chos rnams sems su mi 'dus pas //
NK095(ce)001:8430: mtha' yas pa yi skyon du 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:8431: yo ga'i don gyis ma bshad na //
NK095(ce)001:8432: theg pa'i shan thang mi phyed pas //
NK095(ce)001:8433: khyad mi phyed pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:8434: dgos ched don gyis ma bshad na //
NK095(ce)001:8435: rtsol sgrub bya btsal ma byas par //
NK095(ce)001:8436: sangs rgyas sa la don med 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:8437: tshig gi don gyis ma bshad na //
NK095(ce)001:8438: tshig dang don du mi bsdeb pas //
NK095(ce)001:8440: de bzlog bshad pa'i yon tan yin //
NK095(ce)001:8443: lo rgyus don gyi dgos ched bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:8444: rtsa ba'i don gyi dgos ched bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:8445: yo ga don gyi dgos ched bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:8446: dgos ched don gyi dgos ched bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:8447: tshig gi don gyi dgos ched bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:8449: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /lo rgyus don gyi bshad lugs kyi dgos pa bstan pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:8450: dang por 'dus pa'i 'khor rnams yid ches pa yi
NK095(ce)001:8451: sgo nas 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod pas bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:8452: 'di nyid gang las byung ba'i khungsa bstan pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:8453: du lo rgyus don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa ni
NK095(ce)001:8454: ji ltar zhe na rgyal ba dgongs brgyud /
NK095(ce)001:8456: gang zag snyan brgyud gsum gyi sgo nas bshad pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:8457: de yang chos kyi dbyings spros pa thams cad dang
NK095(ce)001:8458: bral ba'i klong yang dag don gyi 'og min chen
NK095(ce)001:8459: po ru / ston pa ye sangs rgyas pa'i bdag
NK095(ce)001:8460: nyid bcom ldan 'das kun byed rgyal po de nyid
NK095(ce)001:8461: dgongs pa don gyi chos nyid las bzhengs te /
NK095(ce)001:8462: 'og min khang bu brtsegs pa'i gzhal med khang chen por /
NK095(ce)001:8463: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:8464: dang rgyal sras sems dpa' la sogs pa spyi dang
NK095(ce)001:8465: / khyad par du nyid kyi thugs rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:8466: ye shes las rang shar ba'i bka' yi sdud pa
NK095(ce)001:8467: po sems dpa' rdo rje la brjod med don gyi
NK095(ce)001:8468: gsung gis dgongs pa dbyer med kyi ngang nas bshad
NK095(ce)001:8469: pa ni ston pa chos kyi skus rang bzhin byin
NK095(ce)001:8470: gyis brlabs kyis bshad lugs te /
NK095(ce)001:8472: byin rlabs chos sku don gyis gsung //
NK095(ce)001:8473: brjod med don gyis byin gyis brlabs //
NK095(ce)001:8474: don gyi mi gnyis brgyud pa can //
NK095(ce)001:8475: tha snyad bral ba'i don mtshon pa //
NK095(ce)001:8476: man ngag tshad mas rang mtshan ston //
NK095(ce)001:8477: ces gsungs pa dang de nas ston pa sems dpa'
NK095(ce)001:8478: rdo rje longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur bzhengs nas sprul
NK095(ce)001:8479: pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rje la sogs pa la
NK095(ce)001:8480: thugs kyi dgongs pa dang sku yi brda' thabs la
NK095(ce)001:8481: brten pa'i dgongs pa brda yi gsung rang gi ngo
NK095(ce)001:8482: bos mtshon te brda bral rang grol gyi man ngag
NK095(ce)001:8483: rang mtshan yul med du rtogs par mdzad pa ni
NK095(ce)001:8484: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus rang gi ngo bo bstan
NK095(ce)001:8487: longs skus dgongs pa brda sgo nas //
NK095(ce)001:8488: rang gi ngo bos rang shar mtshon //
NK095(ce)001:8489: ngo bos mi gnyis ma nor nges //
NK095(ce)001:8490: brda bral rang grol rang rig nyams //
NK095(ce)001:8491: rang mtshan yul med rang shar pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:8493: sprul pa'i sku rig 'dzin dga' rab rdo rjes slob
NK095(ce)001:8494: dpon chen po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la sgra tshig
NK095(ce)001:8495: sdeb sbyor legs pas bshad pa ni sprul pa'i skus
NK095(ce)001:8496: don gyi sgra tshig sdeb pa'i sgo nas bshad lugsa
NK095(ce)001:8498: sprul pa'i dbang pos tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK095(ce)001:8499: tshig tu sdeb legs don kun mtshon //
NK095(ce)001:8500: brgyud pas brda sprod yi ger bkod //
NK095(ce)001:8501: spyi tsam yid ches rdzogs lung yin //
NK095(ce)001:8502: lo rgyus don gyi bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:8504: de ltar lo rgyus don gyis bshad pa'i dgos pa yang /
NK095(ce)001:8506: lo rgyus don la rnam gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:8507: gang zag dag gis 'phral la byas pa ma yin par //
NK095(ce)001:8508: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa brgyud las bshad //
NK095(ce)001:8509: sangs rgyas zhal nas gsungs pas yid ches 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:8510: nges pa don gyi 'khor yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:8511: rig 'dzin brda yi brgyud pas bshad //
NK095(ce)001:8512: ldem po'i don la dgongs pa ma yin par //
NK095(ce)001:8513: nges pa'i don du gsungs pas yid ches 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:8514: de bzhin bshad pa'i dus su gang zag rna bar brgyud nas bshad //
NK095(ce)001:8515: brgyud pa 'brel ma chad pas nges par yid ches 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:8517: ston pa kun byed nga yi rang bzhin rnam pa gsum gyi rtsal las rang shar ba'am /
NK095(ce)001:8518: nga las byung ba'i ston pa sku gsum gyis rim
NK095(ce)001:8519: pa ltar rang bzhin byin gyis rlabs dang ni rang
NK095(ce)001:8520: gi ngo bo dang sgra tshig legs pa dag gis
NK095(ce)001:8521: ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul gyis bstan pa gang las
NK095(ce)001:8522: byung ba'i khungs bshad pa des ni gdul bya rnams
NK095(ce)001:8523: yid kyang ches par 'gyur bas man ngag gi snod
NK095(ce)001:8524: du rung ba'i dgos pa yod par gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:8526: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:8527: kyi rtsa ba don gyi bshad lugs kyi dgos pa
NK095(ce)001:8528: bstan pa ni / 'di ltar snang srid snod bcud
NK095(ce)001:8529: kyis bsdus pa yi chos thams cad dang dag pa
NK095(ce)001:8530: sangs rgyas dang ma dag sems can gyis bsdus pa
NK095(ce)001:8531: 'di thams cad kun kyang kun byed byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:8532: sems nga yis byas pa yin pa'i phyir na chos
NK095(ce)001:8533: de rnams thams cad snying po rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:8534: shes byang chub kyi sems chos sku thig le nyag
NK095(ce)001:8535: gcig 'di las ma gtogs pa de las gzhan du
NK095(ce)001:8536: gyur pa'i chos ma dag pa zhes bya ba zhig
NK095(ce)001:8537: ye nas grub pa med pa'i tshul /
NK095(ce)001:8539: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid de //
NK095(ce)001:8540: yod ni gcig las med pa la //
NK095(ce)001:8541: byung ni snang srid kun tu byung //
NK095(ce)001:8542: khyab ni snod bcud kun la khyab //
NK095(ce)001:8543: bstan ni theg pa dgu ru bstan //
