NK095(ce)001:10025: 'jug par mi nus 'di yis skrag gyur nas //
NK095(ce)001:10026: chud par mi byed lhan gcig 'grogs mi byed //
NK095(ce)001:10029: gang zhig sangsa rgyas thob par 'doda pa'i rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:10030: ba mi rtog rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom
NK095(ce)001:10031: pa'i blo can de ni ting nge 'dzin sgom par
NK095(ce)001:10032: 'dod pa'i re dogs dang bcas pa'i phyir na ma
NK095(ce)001:10033: bcos gnyug mar gnas pa'i rnal 'byor dam pa'i lam
NK095(ce)001:10034: ni gang zag de yis mi thob pas spangs ba
NK095(ce)001:10035: yin la / sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:10036: bcos bsgyur spu tsam med pas ma bcos rnal ma
NK095(ce)001:10037: ru gnas pa 'di ni 'khor 'das kun gyi chos
NK095(ce)001:10038: nyid de bzhin nyid rig pa byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:10039: gnas lugs ma nor ba yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:10040: de lta bu'i chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:10041: rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes 'di las
NK095(ce)001:10042: ni sangs rgyas zhes pa zhig gud na med pas
NK095(ce)001:10043: sangsa rgyas zhes su minga du btagsa pa bla dwags
NK095(ce)001:10044: tsam yin no // chos nyid rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:10045: shes zhes bya ba de yang gazhana na med par
NK095(ce)001:10046: rang gi sems nyid gsal stong 'dzin med chen por
NK095(ce)001:10048: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:10049: rang byung gi ye shes 'di yi klong du gnyis
NK095(ce)001:10050: med du rdzogs shing ma spangs rang grol la song
NK095(ce)001:10051: bas khams gsum yongs grol chen por gnas pa yin
NK095(ce)001:10053: gcig la kun rdzogs ma spangs rang sar grol //
NK095(ce)001:10054: sangs rgyas sku dang sems can nyon mongs lus //
NK095(ce)001:10055: ji ltar snang ba thams cad rigs pa'i rgyan //
NK095(ce)001:10056: nyon mongs dug lnga ye shes bdud rtsi ste //
NK095(ce)001:10057: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa byang chub lam du drangs //
NK095(ce)001:10058: dus gsum sku gsum klong du gtan sprugs te //
NK095(ce)001:10059: skye shi rtsad gcod khams gsum yongs su grol //
NK095(ce)001:10060: gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bya byed kun snang kun //
NK095(ce)001:10061: nyid la nyid 'dzin nyid la nyid spyod pas //
NK095(ce)001:10062: rtsa ba byang chub rig pa'i klong du grol //
NK095(ce)001:10063: rang byung rig pa ye nas chos sku ste //
NK095(ce)001:10064: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyang de yi sku //
NK095(ce)001:10065: zhes gsungs pa des na rang sems ma bcos pa
NK095(ce)001:10066: 'di ka sangs rgyas chos kyi sku ru bshad pa
NK095(ce)001:10067: yin zhing ma bcos pa yi rang bzhin rig pa
NK095(ce)001:10068: byang chub kyi sems de la ye nas skye ba
NK095(ce)001:10069: med cing rgyu rkyen gang gis kyang bcos su med
NK095(ce)001:10070: pa rang byung 'dus ma byas pa yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:10071: / de lta bu skye med nam 'kha' lta bu'i
NK095(ce)001:10072: don de la btsal zhing bsgrub tu meda cing btsal
NK095(ce)001:10073: zhing bsgrubs pas bya rtsol med pa'i don de 'grub
NK095(ce)001:10074: par mi 'gyur bas na ma bcos mnyam pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:10076: des na de ltar bcos bsgyur blang dor spu tsam
NK095(ce)001:10077: mi dgos par chos thams cad ye grol chen por
NK095(ce)001:10078: sangs rgyas zin pas byar med bag yangs su gsungs
NK095(ce)001:10079: pa 'di theg dman rtsol ba can gyi gang zag
NK095(ce)001:10080: rnams kyis khong du mi chud pas na a ti
NK095(ce)001:10081: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor ba rnams kyi thun
NK095(ce)001:10082: min gyi khyad chos su gsungs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:10084: a ti ma sgrub dug lnga rgyun du mdzes //
NK095(ce)001:10085: yangs so che'i rig pa mkha' mnyam thugs //
NK095(ce)001:10086: spang thob med do thig le nyag cig klong //
NK095(ce)001:10087: rang sar grol lo rtogs dang ma rtogs med //
NK095(ce)001:10088: gnyis su med par grol ba'i chos nyid de //
NK095(ce)001:10089: theg 'og rnams la mi srid srid pa'i chos //
NK095(ce)001:10090: rna phrug brag la 'dzegs pa'i bde blag de //
NK095(ce)001:10091: srog chag gzhan la mi srid kho la srid //
NK095(ce)001:10092: rig pa byar med klong du grol ba de //
NK095(ce)001:10093: theg dman rtsol sgrub can la mi srid de //
NK095(ce)001:10094: rnal 'byor mkha' mnyam bya bral klong na bde //
NK095(ce)001:10095: ye sangs rgyas pa'i rig pa yul med de //
NK095(ce)001:10096: 'khor bar 'khyams par mi srid ye klong brdal //
NK095(ce)001:10098: gsum pa phun sum tshogs pa'i rang bzhin mngon du phyung tshul la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:10099: mngon du phyung tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10100: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum gyi phyung tshul rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:10101: dang po ni kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK095(ce)001:10102: 'di ltar ma skyes spros dang bral ba'i rang bzhin ston pa chos kyi sku dang /
NK095(ce)001:10103: 'gags med gsal dag chen po'i ngo bo longsa spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK095(ce)001:10104: nges med cir yang 'char ba'i thugs rje sprul pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10105: sku dang ston pa rnam pa gsum po de ni
NK095(ce)001:10106: / chos thams cad skye med spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:10107: ba chos sku thig le nyag gcig tu ston par
NK095(ce)001:10108: byed pa'i theg pa gcig dang /
NK095(ce)001:10109: lta spyod gnyis kyi rang bzhin ston par byed pa'i theg pa gnyis dang /
NK095(ce)001:10110: gdul bya dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi blo
NK095(ce)001:10111: dang 'tshams par bstan pa'i theg pa rnam pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:10112: gyi ston pa por kun byed rgyal po nga yis
NK095(ce)001:10113: mngon du phyung nas bstan pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10115: de yang kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga ni
NK095(ce)001:10116: rgyal ba sku gsum gyi ston pa kun gyi 'byung
NK095(ce)001:10117: gnas yin te / nga las ston pa sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:10118: po ji ltar phyung na ston pa kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10119: yi rang bzhin rnam pa gsum las sku gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:10120: ston pa rnams phyung ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:10121: 'di ltar chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs rang byung
NK095(ce)001:10122: gi ye shes spros pa thams cad dang bral zhing
NK095(ce)001:10123: gdod nas skye ba med pa ye babs sor bzhag
NK095(ce)001:10124: chen po'i don la dga' ba'i ston pa rang snang
NK095(ce)001:10125: gi 'khor rnams kyi ngo kha la kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10126: yi rang bzhin gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bral ba las
NK095(ce)001:10127: mi rtogs mnyam pa nyid kyi ngo bo chos kyi
NK095(ce)001:10129: chos sku'i 'khor gyi tshogs ni ston pa nyid las
NK095(ce)001:10130: tha dad du phye ba med pa ye shes rang
NK095(ce)001:10132: de la chos phun sum tshogs pa gdod nas ma
NK095(ce)001:10133: skyes mnyam pa nyid kyi klong du chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:10134: dbye bsal med par thig le nyag gcig tu gnas
NK095(ce)001:10135: pa'i don bstan pa de ni lhag ma med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10136: theg pa'am theg gcig rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:10138: nga yi rang bzhin ma skyes pa las tshogs drug
NK095(ce)001:10139: gi snang yul thams cad 'gags pa med par kun
NK095(ce)001:10140: tu snang ba la 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma
NK095(ce)001:10141: spangs rgyan du rol zhing longs spyod pa'i sa thob
NK095(ce)001:10142: dag pa'i 'khora gyi tshogs rnams la /
NK095(ce)001:10143: nga yi ngo bo gsal ba'i cha las ston pa
NK095(ce)001:10144: longs spyod rdzogs par phyung zhing ngo bo gang la
NK095(ce)001:10145: snang ba'i 'khor de la zab cing barlingasa pa'i lta
NK095(ce)001:10146: ba dang spyod pa gnyis yongs su rdzogs par byed
NK095(ce)001:10147: pa'i chos ston pa de ni kun gyi spyod yul
NK095(ce)001:10148: du ma gyur pas thun mong min pa'i theg pa
NK095(ce)001:10149: gnyis su bstan pa ste de ni kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10150: yi rol ba phyi gsal du rol pa'i ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:10151: mngon du phyung ba yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10152: nga yi rang bzhin skye ba med pa'i rtsal snang
NK095(ce)001:10153: 'gag pa med pa'i cha thugs rjer byung ba las
NK095(ce)001:10154: gdul bya'i 'gro ba rnams tshul ji ltar 'dul bar
NK095(ce)001:10155: 'gyur ba de bzhin du sprul nas 'gro don rtsol
NK095(ce)001:10156: med du madzada pa'i sprul pa'i sku ru snang ba
NK095(ce)001:10157: dang / des 'khor tshogs rnam pa bzhi la rgyu
NK095(ce)001:10158: 'bras blang dor dang 'tshams pa'am mthun pa'i chos dmigs
NK095(ce)001:10159: pa med pa'i thugs rje yis mngon du phyung ste
NK095(ce)001:10160: gsungs pa ni sprul sku'i theg pa gsum yin no
NK095(ce)001:10161: dang / // bzhi pa de'i 'thad pa rgya cher bshad pa la brgyad de /
NK095(ce)001:10162: rang bzhin gcig las chos thams cad snang ba nyid bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:10163: gnyis med las gzhan du rtog pa nyid theg pa 'og mar bzhag pa /
NK095(ce)001:10164: sems nyid kyi don la du mar spros shing brjod
NK095(ce)001:10165: kyang rang bzhin gcig las ma g.yos par bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:10166: / sems nyid sgrub rtsol med pa'i don bstan pas che ba lhun rdzogs su bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:10167: snying po rang sems su rdzogs pas sku gsum lhun grub tu gnas pa /
NK095(ce)001:10168: sems nyid chos dbyings bshad pas yon tan lhun rdzogs su bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:10169: dpe don rtags gsum tshang bas rang sems sangs rgyas su bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:10170: sems nyid de bzhin nyid du bstan pas yod med sgro skur las 'das pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:10172: kye sems dpa' chen po mdora na mngon du phyung
NK095(ce)001:10173: ba'i lung zhesa su bstan pa ni kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10174: yi rang bzhin byang chub kyi sems chos dbyings khyab
NK095(ce)001:10175: gdal chen po'i rtsal las 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK095(ce)001:10176: cad kyi snang ba 'di ltar bsten pa la mngon
NK095(ce)001:10177: du phyung ba'i lung zhes bya bar bstan pa yina
NK095(ce)001:10178: te / de yang kun byeda nga yi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:10179: spros bral chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo gcig pu
NK095(ce)001:10180: ru gnas pa la chos rnams thams cad gang las
NK095(ce)001:10181: snang ba'i yul lam gzhi ni stong gsal thugs rje
NK095(ce)001:10182: rnam pa gsum du snang ba yin la rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:10183: gsum po de yi rtsal las rang byung du shar
NK095(ce)001:10185: sangs rgyas dang sems can snang srid snod bcud kyi
NK095(ce)001:10186: bsdus pa'i chos 'di kun don la gnas lugs rang
NK095(ce)001:10187: byung gi ye shes kun byed byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:10188: nga yi rang bzhin las rtsal snang ma 'gags par
NK095(ce)001:10189: mngon du phyung ba yin no zhes pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:10190: de ltar yang rgya mtsho 'khyil ba'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:10191: snying pos gar khyab rtsal zer 'char //
NK095(ce)001:10192: de yang ji ltar 'char zhe na //
NK095(ce)001:10193: gzhi med ngang las kun gzhi shar //
NK095(ce)001:10194: dngos med ngang las dngos kun shar //
NK095(ce)001:10195: snang med ngang las sna tshogs shar //
NK095(ce)001:10197: gnyis med ngang las ma rig ye shes shar //
NK095(ce)001:10198: cir yang grub pa med pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK095(ce)001:10199: rang bzhin ngo bo thugs rje gsum du shar //
NK095(ce)001:10200: rig dang ma rig rnam gnyis las //
NK095(ce)001:10201: de las sku gsum dug gsum gnyis su shar //
NK095(ce)001:10202: de las zhing khams rnam gsum yid 'khor gsum du shar //
NK095(ce)001:10203: de las rang sar grol dang ma grol las //
NK095(ce)001:10204: 'char sgo 'khrul sgo gnyis su shar ba ste //
NK095(ce)001:10207: de las rtogs dang ma rtogs pas //
NK095(ce)001:10208: gzugs lnga sku lnga nyid du shar //
NK095(ce)001:10209: de las mngon du gyur dang ma gyur pas //
NK095(ce)001:10211: ci yang med las cir yang shar ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:10212: rtogs ma rtogs las sangs rgyas sems can gnyis //
NK095(ce)001:10213: gting yangs chos nyid nga yi rtsal du shar //
NK095(ce)001:10216: de ltar snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:10217: kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin yin pa
NK095(ce)001:10218: la / gal te rang gi sems nyid 'di las
NK095(ce)001:10219: gzhan ma dag 'khrul pa'i chos rang mtshan pa zhig
NK095(ce)001:10221: sangs rgyas zhes pa rang gi snang ba 'di las
NK095(ce)001:10222: gzhan pa ru yod par rtog cing tshol bar byed
NK095(ce)001:10223: pa des ni dper na rang nyid glang po la
NK095(ce)001:10224: zhon bzhin du glang po gzhan du tshol ba dang
NK095(ce)001:10225: 'dra bar kun byed rgyal po rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:10226: shes nga dang 'phrad pa'i skal ba med pasa /
NK095(ce)001:10227: kun byed rgyal po'i 'khor gyi dang po ston pa
NK095(ce)001:10228: sku gsum gyi bstan pa gang zhig gdul bya'i rgyud
NK095(ce)001:10229: rim pas sbyangsa ba'i ched du gsungs pa'i rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:10230: kyi theg pa 'og ma rnams bstan par bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:10231: 'khor tsam las theg mchog rdzogs pa chen po bstan
NK095(ce)001:10232: pa'i snod ma yin par gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:10234: kye sems dpa' chen po ston pa kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10235: yis rtsal snang 'gags pa med pa'i chos rnams mngon
NK095(ce)001:10236: du phyung ba 'di ni snang srid 'khor 'das kyi
NK095(ce)001:10237: chos rang las gzhan ma ltar mngon du phyung ba
NK095(ce)001:10238: yin na'ang don la gzhan min pa rang nyid rang
NK095(ce)001:10239: byung ye shes kyi ngo bo mngona du phyung ba
NK095(ce)001:10240: yin te / de yang ji ltar zhe na snang
NK095(ce)001:10241: srid kyi chos 'di thams cad chos nyid byang chub
NK095(ce)001:10242: sems su ye nas mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i ngo
NK095(ce)001:10243: bor mngon du phyung ba yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10244: de yang rang gi sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:10245: shes bdag nyid chen po'i ngo bor sangs rgyas par
NK095(ce)001:10246: mngon du phyung ba yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10247: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pas ma bslad pas don ma
NK095(ce)001:10248: nor ba chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas par mngon
NK095(ce)001:10249: du phyung ba yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10250: dpe don rtags gsum gyis nges pa la brten nas
NK095(ce)001:10251: ji ltar snang ba'i chos de nyid ye nas sangs
NK095(ce)001:10252: rgyas pa yin par mngon du phyung ba yina pa
NK095(ce)001:10253: dang / chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang na
NK095(ce)001:10254: sangs rgyas zhes pa ming gi bla dwags tsam las
NK095(ce)001:10255: don la grub pa med par mngon du phyung ba
NK095(ce)001:10256: dang / yin pa ste / de ltar chos thams
NK095(ce)001:10257: cad che ba lnga'i sangs rgyas su mngon du phyung
NK095(ce)001:10258: bar brjod kyang don la rang sems gcig pu 'di
NK095(ce)001:10259: nyid mngon du phyung nas bstan pa la che ba'i
NK095(ce)001:10260: yon tan gyi ldog pa nas dbye ba rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:10261: lngar phyes pa tsam las tha dad pa'i chos su
NK095(ce)001:10262: grub pa gang yang med do //
NK095(ce)001:10264: che ba lnga yi byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:10265: sems nyid che ba lngas 'phags te //
NK095(ce)001:10268: ma spangs mi gnas mi ltos rag ma lus //
NK095(ce)001:10269: tha snyad kun dang bral ba ste //
NK095(ce)001:10270: rang bzhin lhun grub 'dus ma byas pas na //
NK095(ce)001:10271: 'bras bu'i rgyal po khyad par dpag ste che //
NK095(ce)001:10274: kye sems dpa' chen po de ltar kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10275: yi rang bzhin mngon du phyung ba 'dis mdor na
NK095(ce)001:10276: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad ma spangs gar
NK095(ce)001:10277: yang ma spangs par mngon sum par sangs rgyas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10278: che ba dang / rag gar yang ma lus par
NK095(ce)001:10279: bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang
NK095(ce)001:10280: che ba dang / / gnas ci la yang mi
NK095(ce)001:10281: gnas par dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang
NK095(ce)001:10282: che ba dang / / / ltos ci la yang
NK095(ce)001:10283: mi ltos te de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10284: che ba dang / / / che ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:10285: thams cad nas thams cad du sangs rgyas pas sangs
NK095(ce)001:10286: rgyas las med pa'i che ba ste che ba lnga
NK095(ce)001:10287: yi ngo bor sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du mngon
NK095(ce)001:10289: de lta bu'i che ba lnga yi sangs rgyas te gang zhe na 'di lta ste /
NK095(ce)001:10290: kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga yi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:10291: mngon du phyung ba ni snang srid snod bcud du
NK095(ce)001:10292: snang ba'i chos 'di dag thams cad mtshan nyid theg
NK095(ce)001:10293: pa gsum gyis ma dag 'khor ba'i chos su mthong
NK095(ce)001:10294: nas tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa 'di rnams spang
NK095(ce)001:10295: 'gog sbyong ba'i chos su blta ba las /
NK095(ce)001:10296: don la kun byed nga yi chos nyid rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:10297: spros bral dang mtshan nyid rang rig dang rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:10298: sgyu mar snang ba ste lhun grub gsum gyi bdag
NK095(ce)001:10299: nyid 'di kun la snang bar gyur pa yin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10300: rgyu mtshan de bas na byang chub sems kyi ngo
NK095(ce)001:10301: bo mngon du phyung ba yin la /
NK095(ce)001:10302: des na gsar du 'bad rtsol gyi sgo nas mtshan
NK095(ce)001:10303: nyid theg pa ltar spong 'gog sbyong ba'i bya ba
NK095(ce)001:10304: la ltos mi dgos par chos nyid byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:10305: kyi rang bzhin la ma rig pa zhig gdod nas
NK095(ce)001:10306: yod ma myong bas sangs shing /
NK095(ce)001:10307: ye shes phyogs med du ye nas rgyas pa yin pas na ye nas sangsa rgyas pa yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:10308: de ltar rtsol sgrub med par ye nas sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:10309: pa yin pas nyan rang byang sems kyi theg pa
NK095(ce)001:10310: gsum zil gyis gnon par byed pa'i gnyen por ye
NK095(ce)001:10311: nas che bar bshad pa de ni mngon par sangsa
NK095(ce)001:10312: rgyas pa'i che ba zhes su bshad pa yin te
NK095(ce)001:10314: rdzogs chen rang gzhung mngon par sangs rgyas che //
NK095(ce)001:10315: spang 'gegs sbyong las tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas //
NK095(ce)001:10316: rang rig spros bral sgyu mar lhun grub pas //
NK095(ce)001:10317: der gnas bag chags rten grol dngos mtshan dang //
NK095(ce)001:10318: ma rig mun sangs ye shes phyogs med rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:10319: dman pa'i theg pa zil gnon gnyen po che //
NK095(ce)001:10322: de bzhin du kun byed nga yi rang sems snying
NK095(ce)001:10323: po rang byung gi ye shes mngon du phyung ba
NK095(ce)001:10324: 'di chos thams cad kyi snying por gyur pa'am ngo
NK095(ce)001:10325: bo yin pas kun gyi badga nyid yin la /
NK095(ce)001:10326: de ltar chos thams cad bdag nyid chen po'i rang
NK095(ce)001:10327: bzhin yin pa la ma h+aa yo ga bas bskyed
NK095(ce)001:10328: rdzogs 'bad rtsol gyi lam la brten nas mngon du
NK095(ce)001:10329: bya bar 'dod pa la rdzogs pa chen po'i rtsol
NK095(ce)001:10330: sgrub gang yang bya mi dgos par chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:10331: ye nas rang byung ye shes kyi bdag nyid chen
NK095(ce)001:10332: por dbang bsgyur zin pas 'og ma'i rtsol sgrub thams
NK095(ce)001:10333: cad ye nasa sam gzhi nas sangsa shing rang rig
NK095(ce)001:10334: pa'i ye shes phyogs med du rgyas pa yin phyir
NK095(ce)001:10335: rtsol sgrub gang yang med pas /
NK095(ce)001:10336: rtsol sgrub can gyi theg pa de'i gnyen por ye
NK095(ce)001:10337: nas che bar bshad pa ni bdag nyid chen po
NK095(ce)001:10338: ru sangs rgyas pa'i che bar bshad pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:10340: rnal 'byor chen po la sogs rtsol sgrub kyi //
NK095(ce)001:10341: gzhan dbang la ltos zil gnon gnyen por mang //
NK095(ce)001:10342: bdag nyid chen por rang nyid ye dbang pas //
NK095(ce)001:10343: tshul ngan rtsol sangs rang rig phyogs med rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:10346: 'di ltar chos thams cad gdod nas ma skyes shing
NK095(ce)001:10347: 'gags pa med pa spros bral rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:10348: shes mngon du phyung ba 'di nyid ye nas gzunga
NK095(ce)001:10349: 'dzina gyi rtog pa thams cad dang bral bas sangs
NK095(ce)001:10351: a nu yo ga bas chos kyi dbyings rgyu dang
NK095(ce)001:10352: rang byung gi ye shes 'bras bu'i chos su bltas
NK095(ce)001:10353: te rgyu 'bras dbyer med kyi ngo bor bsgom zhing
NK095(ce)001:10355: rdzogs pa chen pos rgyu rkyen 'bras bu'i chos thams
NK095(ce)001:10356: cad ye nas chos kyi dbyings su dbyer med ro
NK095(ce)001:10357: gcig du sangs rgyas pa'i phyir 'bad rtsol ci yang
NK095(ce)001:10358: bya mi dgos par 'dod pas rgyu 'bras kyi mtshan
NK095(ce)001:10359: mar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa ye nas ngang gis sangsa
NK095(ce)001:10360: shing / mtshan 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes phyogs med du rgyas pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:10361: de ltar rtsol sgrub gang yang mi dgos pas rgyu
NK095(ce)001:10362: 'bras rtsol sgrub la zhen pa'i theg pa'i gnyen por
NK095(ce)001:10363: gyur cing khyad par du 'phags pas ye nas che
NK095(ce)001:10364: bar bshad pa ni chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:10365: pa'i che ba yin par bshad de /
NK095(ce)001:10367: rjes 'jug la sogs rgyu 'bras gnyen por yang //
NK095(ce)001:10368: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu chos dbyings ro gcig pas //
NK095(ce)001:10369: ma bskyed mi gnas 'gag min de 'dod sangs //
NK095(ce)001:10370: kun mkhyen mtshan ma zil gnon ye shes rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:10373: chos thams cad kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga
NK095(ce)001:10374: yis rang gi ngo bo ngesa par mngon du phyung
NK095(ce)001:10375: nas snang ba 'gag med du bstan pa 'di la
NK095(ce)001:10376: rnal 'byor yo ga ba la sogs kyis blang dor
NK095(ce)001:10377: gnyis su bya ba'i yul du mthong zhing rtsol bar
NK095(ce)001:10378: byed pa de / a ti yo ga bas ye
NK095(ce)001:10379: nas blang dor med par sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid
NK095(ce)001:10380: du dpe don rtagsa ni rnam pa gsum gyis nges
NK095(ce)001:10383: chos rnams thams cad ma lus pa'i //
NK095(ce)001:10384: dpe ni nam 'kha' yin pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:10385: nam mkha' spyod yul kun las 'das //
NK095(ce)001:10386: mtshon du med pa'i khyad par gyis //
NK095(ce)001:10387: nam mkha'i dpe ni khyad par che //
NK095(ce)001:10388: don ni chos nyid yin pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:10389: chos nyid don ni skye med las //
NK095(ce)001:10390: skye ba'i cho 'phrul sangs rgyas kyi //
NK095(ce)001:10391: don ni chos nyid de yin te //
NK095(ce)001:10392: rtags ni sems nyid 'gag med yin //
NK095(ce)001:10393: 'gag pa med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:10394: mi 'gag pa yi khyad par gyis //
NK095(ce)001:10395: rtags ni che ba yin par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:10396: ces gsungs pa ltar chos nyid byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:10397: rang bzhin gdod nas skye ba med pa'i ngang las
NK095(ce)001:10398: skye ba'i cho 'phrul du shar ba'i snang srid kyi
NK095(ce)001:10399: chos 'di dag thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10400: rang bzhin yin pa ni sgrub bya'i don yin la
NK095(ce)001:10401: / de nyid mtshon par byed pa'i dpe ni chos
NK095(ce)001:10402: 'di dag thams cad snang ba'i dus nyid nas skye
NK095(ce)001:10403: med byang chub sems kyi ngo bor sangs rgyas pas
NK095(ce)001:10404: blo'i spyod yul las 'das par nam mkha'i dpe yis
NK095(ce)001:10405: mtshon nas bstan te byang chub sems kyi ngang las
NK095(ce)001:10406: 'gags med du shar ba'i rtsal snang thams cad ngo
NK095(ce)001:10407: bo ngos bzung dang bral ba'i rtags kyis nges pa
NK095(ce)001:10408: ru the tshom za ba rnams la chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:10409: la bzang ngan med pas blang dor du snang ba'i
NK095(ce)001:10410: chos de nyid mngon sum pa ru sangs rgyas par
NK095(ce)001:10411: bstan pas blang dor can gyi theg pa rnams zil
NK095(ce)001:10412: gyis gnon pa'i gnyen por che bas de las khyad
NK095(ce)001:10413: par du 'phags shing dpe nam mkhar nges pa don
NK095(ce)001:10414: chos nyid du nges pa rtags sems nyid du nges
NK095(ce)001:10415: pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs kyis rnal 'byor yo ga
NK095(ce)001:10416: ba la blang dor gnyis su snang bzhin pa de
NK095(ce)001:10417: nyid sangsa rgyas par bstan pas blang dor dang yin
NK095(ce)001:10418: min du 'dzin pa thams cad sangs shing mnyam pa
NK095(ce)001:10419: nyid kyi don rang gsal du rgyas pa ni nges
NK095(ce)001:10420: par sangs rgyas pa'am de nyid yin par sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:10423: sems dpa'i rnal 'byor la sogs blang dor can //
NK095(ce)001:10424: zil gnon gnyen por thams cad de yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:10425: yin min phyogs sangs mnyam nyid rang gsal rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:10428: gong du bshad pa de dag gi phyir na phyi
NK095(ce)001:10429: nang snod bcud du snang ba'i chos 'di dag thams
NK095(ce)001:10430: cad kun byed byang chub sems nga yi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:10431: ma nor ba de kho na nyid du mngon du
NK095(ce)001:10432: phyung zhing bstan pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:10433: de lta bu'i chos nyid 'di ni gzung 'dzin gyi blos bsam du med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10434: dmigs pa'i yul ma grub pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10435: mtshan ma'i spros pa med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10436: dpes mtshon du med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10437: gnyis bcas kyi chos su ma grub pa ste khyad
NK095(ce)001:10438: par lnga dang ldan pas theg pa 'og ma ba
NK095(ce)001:10439: su la mngon du phyung yang mi snang bas chos
NK095(ce)001:10440: nyid de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin kun las khyad
NK095(ce)001:10443: thams cad sangs rgyas che ba yang //
NK095(ce)001:10444: bsam med dmigs med spros pa med //
NK095(ce)001:10445: mtshon du med dang 'dus pa med //
NK095(ce)001:10446: rnam pa lnga ru shes par bya //
NK095(ce)001:10447: zhes gsungs pa ltar chos thams cad chos nyid de bzhin nyid du sangs rgyas pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:10448: 'di ltar de zhes bya ba ni gnas lugs rang
NK095(ce)001:10449: byung gi ye shes ma nor ba yi rang bzhina
NK095(ce)001:10450: yin la / bzhin ces bya ba ni de nyid
NK095(ce)001:10451: rgyu rkyen rtsol sgrub gang gis kyang bcos pa med
NK095(ce)001:10453: man ngag gi rtsa ba bsdus pa'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:10454: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ste //
NK095(ce)001:10455: rang bzhin gdod nas rnam par dag /sangs rgyas sgam pos 'di ma mdzad //
NK095(ce)001:10456: sems can sgrin pos 'di ma bcos //
NK095(ce)001:10458: nyid ces pa ni de lta bu'i gnas lugs ngo
NK095(ce)001:10459: bo nyid la ngos bzung gi ming gis btags pa
NK095(ce)001:10460: yin no // de lta bu'i gnas lugs de bzhin
NK095(ce)001:10461: nyid kyi rang bzhin de nyid la dngos po rang
NK095(ce)001:10462: mtshan du grub pa ci yang med pas dus gsum
NK095(ce)001:10463: gyi sangs rgyas yod pa'i sgros kyang mi 'dogs la
NK095(ce)001:10464: yin no // / cang med phyang chad pa lta
NK095(ce)001:10465: bu yang ma yin par 'gag med rang gsal chen
NK095(ce)001:10466: po'i ngo bo cir yang 'char du rung bas khamsa
NK095(ce)001:10467: gsuma sems can rnams med ces pa'i skur ba'ang mi
NK095(ce)001:10468: 'debs shing rtog dpyod kyi bsam pa cir yang ste
NK095(ce)001:10469: ci la yang dgongs pa med pas yod med rtag
NK095(ce)001:10470: chad kyi mtha' dang 'og ma'i theg pas rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:10471: rgyu 'bras blang dor du lta ba'i phyogs gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:10472: 'dzin pa de dag gzhi med du sangs shing rig
NK095(ce)001:10473: pa'i ngo bo ma bcos rang gsal du rgyas pa
NK095(ce)001:10474: de nyid ma mthong ba'i rmongs pa rnams la mtshon
NK095(ce)001:10475: pa'i phyir du chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:10476: yin no // / pa'o // zhes bla dwags su
NK095(ce)001:10477: btags pa tsam las don la dmigs mtshan spros pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10478: mtha' gang yang med par bstan pas brtags pa tsam
NK095(ce)001:10479: la nges pa'i don du zhen pa de zil gyis
NK095(ce)001:10480: gnon pa'i gnyen por che zhing zhen 'dzin thams cad
NK095(ce)001:10481: dang bral bar la bzla bar byed pas na sangsa
NK095(ce)001:10482: rgyas med pa'i che bar nga yis bashada do ces
NK095(ce)001:10483: yin no // / pa'o // gsungsa so // slob dpon dga' rab dpa' bo'i zhal nas /
NK095(ce)001:10484: lhun gnas bde chen don dam ye shes 'phags //
NK095(ce)001:10485: phyogs gsum la bzlas rang gsal ye sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:10486: dngos mtshan nyi tshe'i stong pa las grol zhing //
NK095(ce)001:10487: don nyid rmongs la mtshon phyir brda' sprad kyis //
NK095(ce)001:10488: de yang tshig tsam nges don zil gnon che'o //
NK095(ce)001:10490: de ltar na che ba lnga po de las dang
NK095(ce)001:10491: pos shes bya'i chos phyi nang snod bcud du snang
NK095(ce)001:10492: bzhin pa 'di nyid rgyu rkyen rtsol sgrub ci la
NK095(ce)001:10493: yang ma ltos par sangs rgyas par bstan pas shes
NK095(ce)001:10495: chos kyi dbyings dang bdag nyid chen po gnyis kyis
NK095(ce)001:10496: dang pos spros pa'i mu mtha' thams cad sangs pa
NK095(ce)001:10497: dang / gnyis pas de ltar mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK095(ce)001:10498: phyogs med du rgyas pa'i rang bzhin ston pas de
NK095(ce)001:10500: bzhi pas mngon sum du snang ba'i chos de nyid
NK095(ce)001:10501: sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo yin par mtshon pas nges
NK095(ce)001:10502: tshig dang / lnga pas de ltar sangs rgyas par
NK095(ce)001:10503: gsungs pa de yang dgos pa'i dbang gis btags pa
NK095(ce)001:10504: tsam las don gang du'ang ma grub par rgyas btab
NK095(ce)001:10505: te dmigs mtshan blo yi spros pa thams cad dang
NK095(ce)001:10506: bral bar la bzlas pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:10507: che ba lnga po des rtsol bcas kyi theg pa
NK095(ce)001:10508: kun las khyad par du 'phags pas na rdzogs pa
NK095(ce)001:10511: mngon sum snang ba'i rang bzhin ye sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:10512: de yi mtshan nyid chos dbyings mu mtha' grol //
NK095(ce)001:10513: de mkhyen ye shes mtha' dbus kun khyab rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:10514: de nyid de yin de mtshon nges pa'i tshig /dgos
NK095(ce)001:10515: pas sprad kyi sgra la don mi bzhag /dang pos
NK095(ce)001:10516: shes bya'i rang bzhin gnyis mtshan nyid //
NK095(ce)001:10517: gcig gis nges tshig tha mas rgyas btab pa //
NK095(ce)001:10518: che lngas khyad 'phags des na rdzogs pa che //
NK095(ce)001:10521: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po lasa rang
NK095(ce)001:10522: bzhin rnam pa gsum mngon du phyung ba'i le'u ste
NK095(ce)001:10523: bco lnga pa'i 'grel ba'o ////don drug pa phun sum
NK095(ce)001:10524: tshogs pa thams cad kun byed du ye nas grub
NK095(ce)001:10525: zin pas rtsol sgrub rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i le'u
NK095(ce)001:10526: bcu drug pa nyid bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:10530: de ltar ston 'khor bstan pa gsum po kun byed
NK095(ce)001:10531: rgyal po byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin las mngon
NK095(ce)001:10532: du phyung zhing che ba lngar ye nas sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:10533: par bstan pa de nas byang chub kyi sems kun
NK095(ce)001:10534: byed rgyal po des sems dapa'a rdo rje la chos
NK095(ce)001:10535: rnams thams cad ye nas byang chub sems kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:10536: bzhin du lhun gyis grub pas de nyid rtogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10537: rnal 'byor pa rnams dus rnams kun tu chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:10538: kyi 'khor lo las 'da' ba med phyir rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:10539: rtsol sgrub gang yang mi dgos par ma bcos rang
NK095(ce)001:10540: babs su 'jog pa'i gdams ngag gnad du phog pa
NK095(ce)001:10541: 'di gsungs so // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:10542: phun sum tshogs pa lnga sems nyid kun byed la
NK095(ce)001:10543: ye nas lhun grub tu rdzogs pas ji bzhin bzo
NK095(ce)001:10544: med du lhug par gzhag par gdams pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10545: sems nyid rang byung du grub pas rtsol sgrub rgyu 'bras kyis mi 'grub par lung bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10546: ji bzhin kun byed rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:10547: rang byung ye shes las mi 'da' bas kun tu
NK095(ce)001:10548: chos nyid kyi 'khor lor bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:10550: kye sems dpa' chen po byar med lhun gyis grub
NK095(ce)001:10551: pa'i gdams ngag 'di nyon cig dang bstan par bya'o
NK095(ce)001:10553: de yang ji ltar zhe na nga ni ye nas
NK095(ce)001:10554: phun sum tshogs pa kun byed pa'i rgyal po yin
NK095(ce)001:10555: te / 'di ltar sku gsum gyi ston pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:10556: dang de dag gis gsungs pa'i bstan pa rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:10558: de gang la bstan par bya ba'i yul du gyur pa'i 'khora rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:10559: de ltar ston pa'i dus dang gang du ston pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10560: gnas thams cad nga yis byas nas mngon du snang
NK095(ce)001:10561: ba yin pa'i phyir na sku gsum gyi ston pa
NK095(ce)001:10562: rnams la lam ston par byed pa'i stona pa yang
NK095(ce)001:10563: ni kun byed nga yis byed cing /
NK095(ce)001:10564: de dag la bstan bya'i don yang gzhan pa ci
NK095(ce)001:10565: yang med par kun byed nga yi rang bzhin rgyu
NK095(ce)001:10566: 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:10567: ngo bo de nyid ston par byed la /
NK095(ce)001:10568: 'khor yang nga yi ngo bo rtsal snang 'gag pa
NK095(ce)001:10569: pa med pa de mngon du phyung nas bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:10570: dang / de rnams 'dus pa'i dus dang gnas kyang
NK095(ce)001:10571: nga yi rang bzhin de ru ni ma 'dus pa
NK095(ce)001:10572: dang / med pas / ston pa kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10573: yi rang bzhin kho na bstan pa las nga nyid
NK095(ce)001:10574: min pa'i chos ni gcig kyang bstan pa med par
NK095(ce)001:10575: dang / med pas / gsungs pa ste / kun
NK095(ce)001:10576: tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud
NK095(ce)001:10577: dang / med pas / gsungs pa ste / las / phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas nga yi sems //
NK095(ce)001:10578: phyi nang snod bcud nga yi sems //
NK095(ce)001:10579: phyogs dang snang ba nga yi sems //
NK095(ce)001:10580: phyi dang nang yang nga yi sems //
NK095(ce)001:10581: mtho ris ngan song nga yi sems //
NK095(ce)001:10583: des na sems dpa' chen po rdo rje khyod nyid
NK095(ce)001:10584: kyang kun byed nga yi rang bzhin 'gag pa med
NK095(ce)001:10585: pa'i rol pa mngon du bstan pa yin pa'i phyira
NK095(ce)001:10586: na khyod kyang ston pa nga yi dbyings las nga
NK095(ce)001:10587: yi thugs rjes phyung ba yin pas kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10588: ni chos rnams thams cad kyi rang bzhin nam snying
NK095(ce)001:10589: por thag chod la blang dor rtsol sgrub kyi re
NK095(ce)001:10590: dogs gang yang mi byed par ma bcos rang bab
NK095(ce)001:10591: kyi ngang zhog cig ces gdams pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:10593: de ltar chos thams cad ni kun byed nga yi
NK095(ce)001:10594: rang bzhin las gzhan du med la kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10595: ni ye nas chos nyid rdzogs pa chen po ma
NK095(ce)001:10596: bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin du byas zin
NK095(ce)001:10597: pa yin gyis da gdod rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub la
NK095(ce)001:10598: brten nas bya dgosa par 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs kun
NK095(ce)001:10599: la sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis lung ma ston
NK095(ce)001:10600: cig /gal te da gdod bya dgos par 'dus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10601: 'khora tshogs rnams la lung bstan par gyur na 'dus
NK095(ce)001:10602: pa'i 'khora rnams rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa ba ltar
NK095(ce)001:10603: bya byed rtsol pa'i nad kyis zin para 'gyur ba
NK095(ce)001:10604: dang / 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang de
NK095(ce)001:10605: yang rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub kyis gsar du byas pa
NK095(ce)001:10606: zhig yin na rgyu rkyen la ltos pa med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10607: rang byung rig pa'i ye shes med pa'i skyon du
NK095(ce)001:10608: dang / 'gyur ba dang / byang chub kyi semsa
NK095(ce)001:10609: rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i rang bzhin la rtsol
NK095(ce)001:10610: sgrub kyis 'chos par byas pa'i skyon du 'gyur ba
NK095(ce)001:10611: dang / 'gyur ba dang / dang / gnas lugs
NK095(ce)001:10612: de bzhin nyid la de bzhin nyid du ma bzhag
NK095(ce)001:10613: par de las gzhan du bsgyur zhing 'chos pa'i skyon
NK095(ce)001:10615: zhing / de ltar na bya byed rtsol ba'i skyon
NK095(ce)001:10616: gyis ma bcos lhun rdzogs chen po'i yon tan rnams
NK095(ce)001:10617: med par gsar du bsgrub dgos par skur pa btab
NK095(ce)001:10618: nas khyad du gsoda par 'gyur ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:10619: dngos po'i don dang mi mthun pa'i drang don rdzun
NK095(ce)001:10620: pa'i lam gyis gnas lugs yang dag pa bden pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10621: don gzhan du log pa'i lam la khrid cing bslus
NK095(ce)001:10622: pas bslad par byas pas na /
NK095(ce)001:10623: de lta bu'i chos nyid kyi don dang mthun pa
NK095(ce)001:10624: min pa'i rtsol bas bsgrub par bya ba gang yang
NK095(ce)001:10625: med pa yin pas rgyu 'bras bya rtsol gyis ma
NK095(ce)001:10626: sgrub par rig pa rang 'gros bcos bslad med par
NK095(ce)001:10629: rang byung ye shes 'gyur med la //
NK095(ce)001:10630: spang dang 'geg pa yongs mi mnga' //sbyang zhing bgrod
NK095(ce)001:10631: pa yongs mi mnga' //gzung zhing 'dzin pa yongs mi
NK095(ce)001:10632: mnga' //blang zhing dor ba yongs mi mnga' //btsal zhing
NK095(ce)001:10633: bsgrub pa yongs mi mnga' //rgyu dang 'bras bu yongs
NK095(ce)001:10634: mi mnga' //des na rang byung ye shes la //
NK095(ce)001:10635: spang len med par bstan pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:10636: ya na rnam pa brgyad po la //
NK095(ce)001:10637: rang byung ye shes yod ma yin //
NK095(ce)001:10638: zhes ye shes spang len med pa'i man ngag gi skabs nas gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:10640: 'di ltar sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis kun byed
NK095(ce)001:10641: byang chub kyi sems nga yi rang bzhin ni dus
NK095(ce)001:10642: rtag tu gsal 'grib med par rig gis zhes da
NK095(ce)001:10643: lta rang babs tha mal du gnas pa'i dus kyi
NK095(ce)001:10644: shes rig 'gag pa med pa dus gsum gyi rtog
NK095(ce)001:10645: pas bslad ma zhugs pa'i stong gsal zang ma thal
NK095(ce)001:10646: byung 'di las gzhan na chos sku kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:10647: po zhig med pas de nyid rang la mngon sum
NK095(ce)001:10649: sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' tshig gsum pa'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:10650: rang gi shes rig gi ngo bo sang nge ba
NK095(ce)001:10651: 'di dngos po dang kha dog gi ngo bo ma
NK095(ce)001:10652: grub pa stong sang nge 'dug pa 'di sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:10653: kun tu bzang mo yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10654: rang gi shes rig gi ngo bo stong bdo tsam
NK095(ce)001:10655: na stong pa phyang chad du ma song bar shes
NK095(ce)001:10656: rig ma 'gag par wal le gsal ba 'di sangs
NK095(ce)001:10657: rgyas kun tu bzang po yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10658: rang gi rig pa dngos po cir yang ma grub
NK095(ce)001:10659: par ngo bo stong pa dang rang gi shes rig
NK095(ce)001:10660: wal le ba dbyer mi phyed par 'dug pa 'di
NK095(ce)001:10661: sangs rgyas chos kyi sku yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10663: rang gi shes rig wal le ba 'di ka sangs
NK095(ce)001:10664: rgyas yin pas sangs rgyas gzhan nas btsal du med
NK095(ce)001:10665: do // rang gi rig pa wal le /
NK095(ce)001:10666: khyug ge ba 'di rgyun du gsal bas sangs rgyas chos kyi sku la bsgrub par byar med do //
NK095(ce)001:10668: ye shes mar me'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:10669: kye gsang bdag lhun gyis grub pa ni rang gi
NK095(ce)001:10670: snying gi dkyil na rang gi rig pa 'od kyi
NK095(ce)001:10671: phung por bzhugs pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10672: thams cad 'char gzhi ma 'gags pa ni rang gi
NK095(ce)001:10673: rig pa mi gnas phar song bas gzugs mthong ba
NK095(ce)001:10675: rang gi mig mthong ba ma 'gags par gsal ba de ka chos sku'i ye shes yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10676: de bzhin du rna bas sgra thos mkhan gyi rig pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10677: snas dri tshor mkhan gyi rig pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10678: lces ro myong mkhan gyi rig pa 'di rnams rang gi chos sku'i ye shes yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10680: des na snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:10681: thams cad kun kyang chos nyid de bzhin nyid du
NK095(ce)001:10683: kun byed nga yis byasa pa'i chos rnams thamsa cada
NK095(ce)001:10684: kun ye gdod nas rang byung gi ye shes kun
NK095(ce)001:10685: byed byang chub sems kyi klong las skad cig tsam
NK095(ce)001:10686: yang g.yo ma myong pas chos nyid de bzhina nyid
NK095(ce)001:10688: de yang byas pa'i chos de gang dang gang zhe na phun sum tshogs pa lnga ste /
NK095(ce)001:10689: 'di ltar sku gsum gyi ston pa gsum yang nga
NK095(ce)001:10690: yi rang bzhin gsum las phyung ba'i rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:10692: de dag gi bstan pa'i theg pa gsum yanga nga
NK095(ce)001:10693: yi chos nyid de bzhin nyid las gzhan du yod
NK095(ce)001:10695: 'khor rnams kun kyang sems dapa'a rdo rje'i ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:10696: nga yi rtsal snang 'gags med du shar ba las
NK095(ce)001:10697: gzhan du med pa de yi tshul dang mthun par
NK095(ce)001:10698: ston pa nga yi rang bzhin yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10699: de bzhin du dus dang gnas phun sum tshogs pa
NK095(ce)001:10700: thams cad kun kyang gzhan du med par kun byed
NK095(ce)001:10701: rgyal po nga nyid mngon du phyung ba yin pa
NK095(ce)001:10702: des na gang snang ji shar thams cad byang chub
NK095(ce)001:10703: sems kyi ngo bo rtag tu sgrib med mngon sum
NK095(ce)001:10704: du gsal ba yin pa'i phyir tshul de ltar rtogs
NK095(ce)001:10705: pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dus rtag tu snang spyod
NK095(ce)001:10706: thams cad chos nyid kyi 'khor lo las mi 'da'
NK095(ce)001:10707: ba yin no // zhes gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:10709: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las sems
NK095(ce)001:10710: dpa' rdo rje la gdams ngag 'boga pa'i le'u ste
NK095(ce)001:10711: bcu drug pa'i 'grel pa'o ////don bdun pa sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:10712: bya btsal med pa'i don rgyal ba'i sku gdung yin
NK095(ce)001:10713: pas rtogs pa'i don las mi 'da' bar gom par
NK095(ce)001:10714: gyis shig pa'i le'u bcu bdun pa la gnyis te
NK095(ce)001:10717: de ltar rgyu 'bras rtsol grub la mi ltos par
NK095(ce)001:10718: ma bcos rang babs su bzhag na dus bzhi chos
NK095(ce)001:10719: nyid kyi 'khor lo las mi 'da' bar gdams pa
NK095(ce)001:10720: de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:10721: des nyid kyi sku gadung ring bsrel 'di dus rtag
NK095(ce)001:10722: tu mi 'bral bar zung shig par gdams pa 'di
NK095(ce)001:10723: gsungsa so // gnyis pa la lnga ste /
NK095(ce)001:10724: sems nyid sgrub bsal med pa'i sku gdung zungs shig par gdams pa /
NK095(ce)001:10725: de'i don ji ltar bzung zhus pa /
NK095(ce)001:10726: sku gdung gi rang bzhin bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:10727: ji ltar mchod cing yon tan dris pa /
NK095(ce)001:10728: rtog pa sems nyid kyi don las ma yengs par
NK095(ce)001:10729: mchod pas kun byed bya btsal med pa'i rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:10732: kye sems dpa' chen po dus gsum rgyal ba rnams
NK095(ce)001:10733: kyi sku gdung sems nyid bya btsal med pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:10734: 'di dang dus rtag tu mi 'bral bar zung zhig
NK095(ce)001:10735: dang / 'di lta bu'i sku gadung ring bsrel 'di
NK095(ce)001:10736: rtag tu mi 'bral bar 'chang bar byas na dus
NK095(ce)001:10737: gsum rgyal ba'i yang mes chos sku kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:10738: po nga dang skal pa mnyam par 'gyur ro zhes
NK095(ce)001:10739: dang / gsungs so // gnyis pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:10740: de nas 'khor gyi gtso bo sems dpa' rdo rjes
NK095(ce)001:10741: sku gdung ring bsrel de nyid ji ltar bzung bar
NK095(ce)001:10742: zhus pa ni / kye dus gsum du gshegs zhing
NK095(ce)001:10743: byon pa'i sangsa rgyas kun gyi yang mes chen po
NK095(ce)001:10744: ston pa sku gsum gyi yang ston par gyur pas
NK095(ce)001:10745: ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po lagsa /
NK095(ce)001:10746: sku gdung ring bsrel 'di nyid rtag tu mi 'bral
NK095(ce)001:10747: bar zungsa shig dang kun byed rgyal po khyod dang
NK095(ce)001:10748: skal pa mnyam par 'gyur ro zhes ston pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:10750: de la sku zhes pa ni rgyal ba gang dang gang gi sku yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10751: gdung zhes bya ba de ni sangsa rgyas gang dang gang gi gdung yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10752: ring bsrel zhes brjod pa ni don ji lta bu
NK095(ce)001:10753: la dgongs nas de ltar gdams par bgyi ba'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:10754: 'di ston pa nyid kyis gsungs bar mdzad du gsol
NK095(ce)001:10755: zhes zhus so // gsum pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:10756: de nas ston pas slar yang lan gsungs pa /
NK095(ce)001:10757: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK095(ce)001:10758: 'di ltar sku zhes bya ba ni kun byed nga
NK095(ce)001:10759: yi thugs sras rgyal ba sku gsum gyi sku yin
NK095(ce)001:10760: la / gdung zhes pa ni dus gsum gyi rgyal
NK095(ce)001:10761: ba kun gyi thugs rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngo
NK095(ce)001:10762: bo ston pa kun byed nga yi semsa sam byang
NK095(ce)001:10763: chub kyi sems 'di nyid yin la /
NK095(ce)001:10764: de nyid dus res 'ga' ba lta bu'i nges bzung
NK095(ce)001:10765: med par rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lo'i dus kun
NK095(ce)001:10766: tu semsa dapa'a rdo rjes 'di nyid mi 'bral bar
NK095(ce)001:10768: dus gsuma gyi sangsa rgyas ma lus pa rnams kyis
NK095(ce)001:10769: sku gdung ngam mchod pa'i rten yin pas na sku
NK095(ce)001:10770: gdung ring bsrel zhes bya ba'i don ni de lta
NK095(ce)001:10771: bu la 'dogs par bya'o zhes gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:10772: bang mdzod 'phrul gyi me long las /
NK095(ce)001:10773: sku ni ston pa sku gsum ste //
NK095(ce)001:10774: nga yi rang bzhin chos sku yin //
NK095(ce)001:10775: nga yi ngo bo longs spyod rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:10776: nga yi thugs rje sprul pa'i sku //
NK095(ce)001:10777: gdung ni sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs //
NK095(ce)001:10778: ma yengs gnas pa ring bsrel yin //
NK095(ce)001:10780: des na le'u 'di'i don ni rang gi sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:10781: rig pa sku gsum gyi bdag nyid can 'di ngo
NK095(ce)001:10782: shes pa'i don dang rtag tu ma bral na dus
NK095(ce)001:10783: gsum rgyal ba kun gyi thugs dang gnyis su med
NK095(ce)001:10784: pas dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku gdung khams gsum 'gro
NK095(ce)001:10785: ba kun gyis mchod pa'i rten du 'gyur bar bstan
NK095(ce)001:10786: pa yin no // bzhi pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:10787: kye stona pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po lags
NK095(ce)001:10788: sku gdunga ring bsrel zhes gsungs pa'i don ni nyid
NK095(ce)001:10789: kyis ji skad bstan pa de ltar lags na yang
NK095(ce)001:10790: / 'o na sku gdung ring bsrel de la dus
NK095(ce)001:10791: gsum gyi rgyal ba sangs rgyas rnams kyis tshul ji
NK095(ce)001:10793: de mchod pa la ni yon tan ji lta bu zhig mchis pa yin zhes zhus so //
NK095(ce)001:10795: kye sems dpa' chen po khyod nyon cig ston pa
NK095(ce)001:10796: kun byed nga yi sku gdung ring bsrel de la
NK095(ce)001:10797: ni tshul ji ltar mchod na dus gsum gyi sangs
NK095(ce)001:10798: rgyas kun gyis dus rtag tu rang gi sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:10799: rang byung gi ye shes de la bltas nas zhes
NK095(ce)001:10800: rang ngo shes par byas nas rtsol med ye grol
NK095(ce)001:10801: chen po ka dag ye bab sor bzhag gi dgongs
NK095(ce)001:10802: pas sam ma bcos rang bab chen po'i bzhag thabs
NK095(ce)001:10804: de yi yon tan ka dag chos sku'i dgongs pa
NK095(ce)001:10805: dang mi 'bral bar de nyid mngon du thob nas
NK095(ce)001:10806: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams thamsa cada kun
NK095(ce)001:10807: byed rgyal po byang chub sems kyi klong du rjes
NK095(ce)001:10808: med rang yal du song nas srid gsum ka dag
NK095(ce)001:10809: 'khor ba dong sprugs kyi dgongs pa mngon du byed
NK095(ce)001:10813: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las sku
NK095(ce)001:10814: gdung gtad pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'i 'grel ba'o
NK095(ce)001:10815: ////don brgyad pa chos thams cad sems nyid kun byed
NK095(ce)001:10816: de bzhin nyid du bstan pa'i le'u bco brgyad pa
NK095(ce)001:10817: la gnyis te / bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10820: de ltar sku gdung ring bsrel mi 'bral bar bzung
NK095(ce)001:10821: bar gdams pa de nas byang chub kyi sems pa
NK095(ce)001:10822: kun byed rgyal po des snang cha 'gag pa med
NK095(ce)001:10823: pa'i rol par shar ba'i srid zhi gnyis kyis bsdus
NK095(ce)001:10824: pa'i chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs chos nyid rang
NK095(ce)001:10825: byung gi ye shes de kun byed nga nyid yin
NK095(ce)001:10826: no // zhes ston par byed pa'i nges pa don gyi lung 'di gsungsa so //
NK095(ce)001:10828: sems nyid kun byed nyid sku gsum rtsol med du grub pas gzhan don 'bad med du 'byung tshul /
NK095(ce)001:10829: sku gsum sems nyid kyi ngang du ye nas lhun
NK095(ce)001:10830: gyis grub pas rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das tshul
NK095(ce)001:10831: / ye nas lhun gyis grub pas btsal mi dgos par bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:10832: gang btsal skyon du che bas rtsol sgrub re dogs las 'das tshul /
NK095(ce)001:10833: rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub kyis mi 'grub pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:10834: btsal bas 'grub par ston pa nyid drang don yin pas ma btsal shig par gdams tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:10836: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK095(ce)001:10837: 'di ltar snang srid snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:10838: thams cada kun gyi snang ba'i cha 'gags pa med
NK095(ce)001:10839: pa 'di ni kun byed nga yi ngo bor snang
NK095(ce)001:10840: ba yin pas longs sku yin la /
NK095(ce)001:10841: de yang don la gang yang grub pa med par
NK095(ce)001:10842: ye grol ka dag chen po gcig gi ngo bor
NK095(ce)001:10843: dag pa ste / de nyid gang du dag pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10844: yul ni kun byed nga yi rang bzhin chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:10845: bya rtsol dang bral ba'i dbyings su dag pa de
NK095(ce)001:10847: des rol rtsal las gdul bya gang zhig thabs gang
NK095(ce)001:10848: gis 'dul ba la sprul pa'i rol pa rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:10849: sna tshogs par ston pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:10850: de ltar sku gsum lhun grub tu gnas pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:10851: des na 'di ltar snang tshul la ma dag 'khor
NK095(ce)001:10852: ba ltar snang ba'i khams gsum rigs drug gis bsdus
NK095(ce)001:10853: pa'i gnas 'di thams cad don la sku gsum rgyal
NK095(ce)001:10854: ba'i zhing khams chen po yin zhing cir snang thams
NK095(ce)001:10855: cad gzugs sku'i rol pa las ma 'das pas na
NK095(ce)001:10856: brtan g.yo'i dngos po rnams kyi g.yo rtsol gyi bya
NK095(ce)001:10857: ba gang snang thams cad rgyal ba'i phrin las nyag
NK095(ce)001:10858: gcig gi mdzad pa yin phyir de ltar rtogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:10859: rnal 'byor pa rnams la gzhan don 'bad med du
NK095(ce)001:10861: 'o na bya byed gang snang thams cad rgyal ba'i
NK095(ce)001:10862: phrin las gdul bya'i gzhan don kho na yin na
NK095(ce)001:10863: / 'di ltar dmyal ba'i sems can rnams btso bsregs
NK095(ce)001:10864: byed pa sogs kyang gzhan don mdzad pa'i phrin las
NK095(ce)001:10866: de yang sems can rang rang gi las kyi sgrib
NK095(ce)001:10867: pas phyin ci log tu snang ba tsam las don
NK095(ce)001:10868: la chos sku skye ba med pa'i klong nas 'gags
NK095(ce)001:10869: med gzugs sku'i rol ba gang 'dul sgyu ma'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:10870: du snang ba'i mdzad pa yin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:10871: rin po che rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:10872: rang byung chos sku chen po de nyid ni //
NK095(ce)001:10873: dbyer med gcig yin bri gang med par chags //
NK095(ce)001:10874: gcig las mthong stangs tha dad byung bas na //
NK095(ce)001:10875: chos sku rang byung 'od gsal chen po des //
NK095(ce)001:10876: 'od gsal me ru mthong bas dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK095(ce)001:10877: ma g.yos chu ru mthong bas grang ba'i sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK095(ce)001:10878: sprul pa gshin rjer mthong bas sdug bsngal chen po'i rgyu //
NK095(ce)001:10879: don byed 'dren pa slar la srog gcod mthong //
NK095(ce)001:10880: gsung gi chos ston log pa'i sgra nyid 'byung //
NK095(ce)001:10881: brdeg gsod chod la sogs pa'i sgra ru thos //
NK095(ce)001:10882: gdul bya phyag mtshan spu gri la sogs mthong //
NK095(ce)001:10883: gcig las med kyang logs pa'i snang ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:10884: chos sku spros bral chen po dang //
NK095(ce)001:10885: rig pa'i ye shes dbyer med pas //
NK095(ce)001:10886: de gnyis chags par mthong ste 'dod chags dag tu mthong //
NK095(ce)001:10887: mthong ba'i bag chags zhen cing chags pa yis //
NK095(ce)001:10888: de yi rgyu mthun las kyi 'bras bu yin //
NK095(ce)001:10889: phyi pa'i snang ba sgrib pas rnag khrag dag tu mthong //
NK095(ce)001:10890: nang gi snang ba sgrib pas zas las me nyid 'byung //
NK095(ce)001:10891: sku nyid snang bas kha 'bar ma ru mthong //
NK095(ce)001:10892: 'dod chags dbang gis snang ba sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK095(ce)001:10893: rigs mthun sprul pa sdug bsngal sna tshogs myong //
NK095(ce)001:10894: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan pa bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:10896: de ltar kun byed chos sku'i dbyings nas sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:10897: gyi rol pa sna tshogs byung nas ni gdul bya
NK095(ce)001:10898: rang rang gi blo dang mtshams par theg pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:10899: gyi don ni ngo yang ston par byed cing /
NK095(ce)001:10900: des ni rgyu 'bras mtshan mar zhes pa'i blo can
NK095(ce)001:10901: rnams ni blang dor rtsol sgrub can gyi theg pa
NK095(ce)001:10903: rgyu 'bras blang dor thams cad las 'das pa yi
NK095(ce)001:10904: gang zag skal ldan rnams ni de lta bu'i yul
NK095(ce)001:10905: la mi ltos pas re dogs blang dor gyi sgo
NK095(ce)001:10906: nas rgyu la rtsol zhing mi sgrub cing 'bras bu
NK095(ce)001:10907: thob par mi 'dod pa de la ni spang gnyen
NK095(ce)001:10908: re dogs kyi 'dod pa med pa'i dgongs pa lhun
NK095(ce)001:10909: grub bya rtsol bral ba'i don dang /
NK095(ce)001:10910: chos sku bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin ma bcos lhun gyis grub par 'gyur ro //
NK095(ce)001:10912: rang rig 'di nyid rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor ba //
NK095(ce)001:10913: ye shes bcud nyid chos kyi gter du smin //
NK095(ce)001:10914: nam mkha' go yangs 'byung ba'i lam du bde //
NK095(ce)001:10915: rtogs pa'i go yangs sangs rgyas lam du bde //
NK095(ce)001:10916: gdams ngag go yangs sgom pa'i lam du bde //
NK095(ce)001:10917: dus gsum 'gyur med rang rig lta ba'i dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:10918: 'dod dgu rang las yon tan 'char ba'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:10919: rgyu 'bras gzhan la rag ma lus pas zab //
NK095(ce)001:10920: ye nas chos nyid ye shes rang byung la //
NK095(ce)001:10921: 'khor bar gnas kyang sgrib pas gos pa med //
NK095(ce)001:10922: de phyir don rtogs da lta nyid nas ni //
NK095(ce)001:10923: chos sku mngon du gyur pas sangs rgyas yin //
NK095(ce)001:10926: gong du bstan pa de ltar rang gi sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:10927: rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'di ye nas sku
NK095(ce)001:10928: gsum lhun grub kyi rang bzhin yin pa la da
NK095(ce)001:10929: gdod bya rtsol gang yang mi dgos shing don chos
NK095(ce)001:10930: rnams thams cad ye ji bzhin pa'i ngang du gnas
NK095(ce)001:10931: pa las sa lam bsgrod pa sogs kyis gong nas
NK095(ce)001:10932: gong du bskyod du med pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:10933: ye ji bzhin pa yi gnas lugs rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:10934: ye shes de la 'bras bu zhig gsar du bsgrub
NK095(ce)001:10935: mi dgos te chos thams cad kun gdod ma nyid
NK095(ce)001:10936: nas chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:10937: lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK095(ce)001:10938: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad sngar nas grub zin pas kyang /
NK095(ce)001:10939: kun byed rgyal po nga yi de las gzhan du
NK095(ce)001:10940: rtsol zhing sgrub dgos pa'i lung mi 'boga go zhes
NK095(ce)001:10941: gsungs te / de ltar na nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam las kyang /
NK095(ce)001:10942: bsam dang bral ba'i chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:10943: bsam zhing dpyad pas yul mi bskyod //
NK095(ce)001:10944: rang bzhag lhug pa'i ting 'dzin la //
NK095(ce)001:10946: ces ma bcos rang babs su 'jog par gdams pa bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:10948: gal te blang dor 'bad rtsol gyis btsal zhing bsgrub
NK095(ce)001:10949: par byas na gang btsal bar bya ba'i ting 'dzin
NK095(ce)001:10950: des gdod nas ye sangs rgyas par rtsol med lhun
NK095(ce)001:10951: gyis grub pa'i 'bras bu de mi 'grub par ma
NK095(ce)001:10952: zad ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsol sgrub de blang dor
NK095(ce)001:10953: re dogs gi nang du che ba yin pas re
NK095(ce)001:10954: dogs dang 'bad rtsol gang yang mi byed par gdams
NK095(ce)001:10955: pa ste / klong chen rab 'byams las /
NK095(ce)001:10956: bsam gtan ting 'dzin la sogs sangs rgyas sku la sgrib //
NK095(ce)001:10957: bsgom zhing bsgrub pa byas na bsam gtan min //
NK095(ce)001:10958: sangs rgyas mi 'grub bsgrubs na rtsol bar 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:10959: 'khor ba mi spang spangs na sangs mi rgya //
NK095(ce)001:10960: sangs rgyas gzhan na med do rig pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:10961: 'khor ba gzhan na med do rang sems yin //
NK095(ce)001:10962: 'dus byas dge ba mi bya byas na 'ching ba'i rgyu //
NK095(ce)001:10964: 'on kyang sgom sgrub rtsol ba la mtha' gcig tu
NK095(ce)001:10965: zhen pa'i rdzogs chen gyi gol sa bcad pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:10966: du sgom med du gsungs pa yin gyi /
NK095(ce)001:10967: rnam pa kun tu sgom pa la skyon du bltas nas dor byar bstan pa yang ma yin te /
NK095(ce)001:10968: gnas lugs yang dag pa rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK095(ce)001:10969: rnams kyis sgom kyang 'ching bar mi 'gyur te 'ching
NK095(ce)001:10970: bya 'ching byed kyi blo dang bral ba'i phyir sgyu
NK095(ce)001:10971: ma'i zhags pas sgyu ma'i glang chen 'ching du med
NK095(ce)001:10973: ma bsgom kyang yengs su med de gang shar thams
NK095(ce)001:10974: cad gzhi med rtsa bral du grol zin pas smig
NK095(ce)001:10975: rgyu'i chu la chu rag mi dgos pa lta bu
NK095(ce)001:10976: yin pas ji ltar byas kyang mi 'gal bar gsungs
NK095(ce)001:10978: rdzogs chen gol sa bcad phyir bsgom med de //
NK095(ce)001:10979: ye shes bsgom med dag tu rab rtogs na //
NK095(ce)001:10980: bsgoms kyang skyon med chos dbyings nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:10981: bsgom med des ni kun gyi re ba bskangs //
NK095(ce)001:10982: kun la khyab phyir ma rdzogs med mod kyi //
NK095(ce)001:10983: kun gyis gdams ngag ma 'phrad rtogs par dka' //zhes dang /
NK095(ce)001:10985: a ti lta ba phyogs ris med pa la //
NK095(ce)001:10986: bltas kyang skyon med rang byung rol ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:10987: ma bltas skyon med mtshan ma rang sar grol //
NK095(ce)001:10988: gnyis med lta ba rang byung rol pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:10989: lta ba bzang ngan 'byed pa'i mdud pa bor //
NK095(ce)001:10990: nga yi sgom pa dmigs gtad med pa la //
NK095(ce)001:10991: bsgoms kyang skyon med rang byung rol pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:10992: ma bsgoms skyon med mtshan ma rang sar grol //
NK095(ce)001:10993: rang grol gnyis med rang byung bsgom pa yis //
NK095(ce)001:10994: sgom pa ched du btsal ba'i mdud pa bkrol //
NK095(ce)001:10995: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan pa bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:10997: kye sems dapa'a chen po de ltar bsgoms sgrub rtsol
NK095(ce)001:10998: bas mi 'grub pa'i rgyu mtshan des na kun byed
NK095(ce)001:10999: nga nyid min pa'i sku gsum gyi ston pa thams
NK095(ce)001:11000: cad kyisa gdul bya 'dul bar bya ba'i phrin las
NK095(ce)001:11001: sna tshogs dang / rnam par rtog pas bsam zhing
NK095(ce)001:11002: sgoms pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa ji snyed
NK095(ce)001:11003: sna tshogs dang / yod pa dang / gdul bya'i
NK095(ce)001:11004: khams la thugs rje rtsol med du 'phro ba'i 'od
NK095(ce)001:11006: bdag med dang skye med spros bral la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:11007: theg pa so so'i lta ba'i yul ni gang dang
NK095(ce)001:11008: ci dmigs kyang / kun byed byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:11009: rang bzhin chos nyid ji bzhin pa la sngar bas
NK095(ce)001:11010: bzang du song ste g.yos pa cung zad kyang med
NK095(ce)001:11011: ci dmigs kyang / pas na / bya ba'i las
NK095(ce)001:11012: kyis ji srid bskal pa'i bar du sgrub kyang des
NK095(ce)001:11013: 'phrin las de grub pa ci yang med la /
NK095(ce)001:11014: bsam zhing sgom pa'i ting 'dzin rnams kyang chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:11015: kyi don la mi gnas pas yal bar 'gyur ba
NK095(ce)001:11016: dang / 'phro ba'i yul med pas thugs rjes 'od zer rnams kyang zhi bar 'gyur ba yin na /
NK095(ce)001:11017: gzhan du blta ba'i yul gang yang mthong ba med pa smos kyang ci dgos te /
NK095(ce)001:11018: des na re dogs 'bad rtsol gyis btsal ba'i las
NK095(ce)001:11019: gang yang ma byed par ma bcos rang babs chen
NK095(ce)001:11020: po'i ngang du zhog cig ces gdams pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:11022: kye sems dpa' chen po rang gi rang bzhin rig
NK095(ce)001:11023: pa byang chub sems kyi yin lugs ma shes par
NK095(ce)001:11024: yul gzhan las btsal bas 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi
NK095(ce)001:11025: go 'phang zhig grub pa'i lam 'grub par 'gyur ba'i
NK095(ce)001:11026: lung de ni rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa can
NK095(ce)001:11027: rnams kyis ston par byed pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:11028: de lta bu'i rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa can
NK095(ce)001:11029: de rnams kyis chos nyid dam mtshan nyid ni chos
NK095(ce)001:11030: can snang ba kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11031: chos nyid stong pa don dam gyi bden pa rnam
NK095(ce)001:11032: pa gnyis so sor phye ba'i sgo nas chos can
NK095(ce)001:11033: snang ba'i cha tshogs gnyis bsags pa la sogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11034: thabs kyis chos nyid don dam pa zhig tshol bar
NK095(ce)001:11035: byed pa ste / de ltar tshol bar byed pa
NK095(ce)001:11036: de ni drang don tsam las nges pa'i don la
NK095(ce)001:11037: de ltar tshol bas rnyed pa'i lung zhig bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:11038: med pas na de ltar 'tshol ba'i ngal ba ma
NK095(ce)001:11041: rang bzhin lhun rdzogs rdzogs chen nyid //
NK095(ce)001:11042: rdzogs pa chen por ye nas gnas //
NK095(ce)001:11043: thams cad rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK095(ce)001:11044: bzang ngan blang dor gnyis su med //
NK095(ce)001:11045: theg pa lam dang bsgom bsgrub brtson //
NK095(ce)001:11047: rgyu 'bras gnyis med rdo rje 'i sku //
NK095(ce)001:11048: skye shi med par lhun gyis grub //
NK095(ce)001:11049: gnas pa'i don la gnyis su med //
NK095(ce)001:11050: des na chos dang sangs rgyas med //
NK095(ce)001:11051: lta bas bltas pas 'khrul bar snang //
NK095(ce)001:11052: rgyu 'bras theg pa brtags pas nor //
NK095(ce)001:11055: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las btsal
NK095(ce)001:11056: bas mi 'grub pa'i le'u ste bco brgyad pa'i 'grel
NK095(ce)001:11057: ba'o ////don dgu pa sems nyid sku gsum du gnas
NK095(ce)001:11058: pas yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i le'u bcu dgu
NK095(ce)001:11063: de ltar sku gsum gyis mtshon pa'i chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:11064: kun byed byang chub sems su ye nas lhun gyis
NK095(ce)001:11065: grub pas re dogs 'bad rtsol gang yang mi byed
NK095(ce)001:11066: par gdams pa'i rjes de nas byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:11067: kun byed rgyal po des sems nyid ma btsal ji
NK095(ce)001:11068: bzhin du bzhag pas sku gsum ma bsgrubs lhun gyis
NK095(ce)001:11069: grub pa'i dgongs par ston pa'i le'u 'di gsungs so
NK095(ce)001:11071: sems nyid don gyi sangs rgyas nam mkha' bzhin du btsal bas mi 'grub par bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:11072: des rang bzhin ma btsal yang da lta nyid nas sku gsum lhun gyis grub tshul /
NK095(ce)001:11073: snang srid 'khor 'das thams cad sems kyi rol par 'du tshul /
NK095(ce)001:11074: sems kyi rang bzhin gang du'ang mi dmigs pas smra bsam brjod las 'das pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:11076: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:11077: po nga las byung ba'i ston pa sku gsum gyis
NK095(ce)001:11078: rang rang gi 'khor la bstan pa'i phyi nang gsang
NK095(ce)001:11079: ba'i theg pa rnam pa gsum bstan pa ni rgyu
NK095(ce)001:11080: 'bras rtsol sgrub can gyi lam zhig ma gtogs ston
NK095(ce)001:11081: pa gsum gyis ste gsum po de nyid kyis mi
NK095(ce)001:11082: rtsol lhun gyis grub pa'i lung ni ma bstan la
NK095(ce)001:11083: / kun byed nga yi theg mchog rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:11084: po nyag gcig spros pa dang bral ba'i tshul bstan
NK095(ce)001:11085: pa 'dir ni sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu la
NK095(ce)001:11086: re dogs 'bad rtsol gyis btsal bas sngar bas lhag
NK095(ce)001:11087: par grub tu yod pa'i don zhig byar med a
NK095(ce)001:11088: ti yo ga'i lung du ston pa ngas ma bstan
NK095(ce)001:11089: te gdod nas ye sangs rgyas pa rang byung 'dus
NK095(ce)001:11090: ma byas pa'i rang bzhin la bya rtsol gang yang
NK095(ce)001:11091: mi nus pa'i phyir ro zhes so //
NK095(ce)001:11093: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig kun byed byang
NK095(ce)001:11094: chub kyi sems stong gsal 'gags med kyi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:11095: nga yi rang bzhin 'di las gzhan du ma btsal
NK095(ce)001:11096: ba ra rang bzhin gyis lhun gyis grub pa yi
NK095(ce)001:11097: 'bras bu de ni gang zhe na dus gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:11098: rgyal ba ma lus pa kun gyi snying po'am rang
NK095(ce)001:11099: bzhin du gyur pa rig pa sku gsum gyi rang
NK095(ce)001:11100: bzhin can du gnas pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:11101: de gang zhe na 'di ltar byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:11102: nga yi rang bzhina ye stong chen po ma bcos
NK095(ce)001:11103: de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bor gnas pa 'di spros
NK095(ce)001:11104: bral chos kyi skur grub pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11105: nga yi ngo bo snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK095(ce)001:11107: ma skyes shing 'gags pa med pa /
NK095(ce)001:11108: yod med kyi mtha' las 'das pa /
NK095(ce)001:11109: ma bcos ye bab kyi ngo bor gnas pa 'di ni rang gsal longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK095(ce)001:11110: nga yi thugs rje 'gags pa med pa shar grol
NK095(ce)001:11111: ris med chen por mngon du phyung ba 'di ni
NK095(ce)001:11112: nges med rang shar sprul pa'i sku'o zhes pa 'dis
NK095(ce)001:11113: ni gzhi gnas rang byung gi ye shes kyi sku
NK095(ce)001:11115: rin po che rgyas pa las /
NK095(ce)001:11116: gzhi yi dus na chos rnams thams cad rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:11117: chos sku rang bzhin spros dang bral bas chos kyi sku nyid rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:11118: rig pa gsal la ma 'gags longs sku rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:11119: rtsal nyid cir yang snang bas sprul sku rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:11121: des na de lta bu'i rig pa rang gnas kyi
NK095(ce)001:11122: sku gsum po de nyid da lta nas rtsol med
NK095(ce)001:11123: lhun gyis grub pa las 'bad rtsol gyis btsal nas
NK095(ce)001:11124: grub par gyur pa'i 'bras bu rgyu rkyen gyis 'dus
NK095(ce)001:11125: byas pa'i mtshan nyid can ni gang yang bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:11128: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK095(ce)001:11129: 'di ltar sku gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad kun
NK095(ce)001:11130: byed nga ru ma btsal lhun grub kyi tshul du
NK095(ce)001:11131: 'dus pa ste / de'i tshul yang ji ltar na
NK095(ce)001:11132: phyi nang snod bcud du snang ba'i chos rnams thams
NK095(ce)001:11133: cad kun kun byed pa yi rang bzhin stong pa
NK095(ce)001:11134: nyid dang ngo bo gsal ba'i ye shes dang rol
NK095(ce)001:11135: rtsal 'gags pa med pa'i thugs rjes 'gro don spyod
NK095(ce)001:11136: pa ste ma bcos rang byung gi sku gsum po
NK095(ce)001:11137: las gzhan du med pas rgyal ba sku gsum po
NK095(ce)001:11138: de nga yi rang bzhin ma bcos de bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:11140: zhes rol pa'i sku gsum mam byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:11141: rol par shar ba'i chos rnams thams cad sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:11144: snang ba yul du grub pa nyid las sku gsum rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:11145: snang ba rang bzhin stong pa chos sku rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:11146: snang ba gsal bar gnas pas longs sku rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:11147: snang ba don dang mthun pas sprul sku rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:11148: gti mug chos kyi sku ru snang ba dang //
NK095(ce)001:11149: zhe sdang gsal ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ru snang //
NK095(ce)001:11150: 'dod chags dag pa sprul pa'i sku yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:11151: sku gsum rang byung dag tu shar ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:11152: thams cad sku gsum dag tu snang ba las //
NK095(ce)001:11153: dug gsum spangs pa'i pha rol na //
NK095(ce)001:11154: sku gsum dag ni yod ma yin //
NK095(ce)001:11155: tshogs brgyad yul du snang ba yang //
NK095(ce)001:11156: sku las ma gtogs gang yang med //
NK095(ce)001:11157: thams cad de bzhin nyid kyi snang ba de //
NK095(ce)001:11158: chos sku ris med chen po ste //
NK095(ce)001:11159: rang byung nam mkha' dag tu shar //
NK095(ce)001:11161: des na kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga dang
NK095(ce)001:11162: nga yi rang bzhin chos nyid de bzhin nyid spros
NK095(ce)001:11163: pa thams cad dang bral ba'i gnas lugs smra bsam
NK095(ce)001:11164: brjod du med pa'i bdag nyid can 'di las ni
NK095(ce)001:11165: gzhan du 'khor 'das kyi chos gang med pas na
NK095(ce)001:11166: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba'i yon tan gyis sgros 'dogs
NK095(ce)001:11168: sems can zhes bya ba'i skyon gyi rnam pa gang
NK095(ce)001:11169: yang med do zhes 'khor 'das thams cad bzang ngan
NK095(ce)001:11170: med par sems nyid gcig gi rol par bstan pa'o
NK095(ce)001:11172: gong du bshad pa'i rgyu mtshan des na chos thams
NK095(ce)001:11173: cad gnyis su med pa'i gnas lugs rig pa byang
NK095(ce)001:11174: chub kyi sems 'di ni 'khor 'das bzang ngan gang
NK095(ce)001:11175: du mi rtog pas rtog med mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:11176: rang bzhin du gnas pa las ye nas 'pho 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:11177: med pas ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis kyang de bzhin
NK095(ce)001:11178: nyid du gnas pa 'di las ma gtogs pa yi
NK095(ce)001:11179: don zhig ni gzhan na rnyed pa med pas na
NK095(ce)001:11180: / dus gsum gyi sangsa rgyas rnams kyis kyang rig
NK095(ce)001:11181: pa byang chub kyi sems ye nas bsal bzhag bral
NK095(ce)001:11182: ba 'di las lhag pa yi kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:11183: nga la ma nor nges pa'i don zab mo ston
NK095(ce)001:11184: par byed pa'i lung zhig mnos pa med la /
NK095(ce)001:11185: der ma zad phun sum tshogs pa'i chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:11186: byed pa'i mkhan po ston pa kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:11187: nga yis kyang mi rtog mnyam pa nyid kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:11188: bzhin sems nyid skye ba med pa chos nyid de
NK095(ce)001:11189: bzhin nyid kyi don 'di las lhag pa zhig kun
NK095(ce)001:11190: byed rgyal po nyid la kun byed rgyal po rang
NK095(ce)001:11191: nyid kyis bstan pa rdul tsam med do //
NK095(ce)001:11194: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las ma
NK095(ce)001:11195: btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i le'u ste bcu dagu pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11196: 'grel ba'o ////don bcu pa sems nyid kun byed thams
NK095(ce)001:11197: cad kyi 'byung gnas yin pa'i le'u nyi shu pa
NK095(ce)001:11198: la gnyis te / bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11201: de ltar sems nyid sku gsum gyi rang bzhin la
NK095(ce)001:11202: yon tan thams cad ye nas lhun gyis grub pas
NK095(ce)001:11203: gzhan nas btsal du med par bstan pa de nas
NK095(ce)001:11204: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po desa 'khor
NK095(ce)001:11205: 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thamsa cada kyi 'byung
NK095(ce)001:11206: khungs gzhan med par kun byed byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:11207: nyid kyi ngang las byung ba yin tshul 'di gsungsa
NK095(ce)001:11208: so // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:11209: chos thams cad kun byed yin par bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:11210: phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kun byed nyid las byung yang de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos pa /
NK095(ce)001:11211: thams cad dbyings gcig kun byed du bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:11213: yin tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11214: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:11216: kye gsang chen snying po'i chos kun sdud pa'i bka'
NK095(ce)001:11217: yi sdud pa po sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis
NK095(ce)001:11218: chos thams cad kun byed byang chub sems las ji
NK095(ce)001:11219: ltar byung ba'i tshul 'di nyon cig /de yang ji
NK095(ce)001:11220: ltar zhe na kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:11221: sems nga ni 'khor 'das kyi chos kun 'dus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11223: de bzhin du kun byed nga ni chos rnams ma
NK095(ce)001:11224: lus pa kun bskyed pa'i sa bon kyang yina la
NK095(ce)001:11225: / nga ni chos rnams kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas rgyu yang yin la /
NK095(ce)001:11226: nga ni yal ga lta bu'i chos rnams kun gang las gyes pa'i sdong po lta bu ste /
NK095(ce)001:11227: nga ni chos rnams thams cad kyi rten gzhir gyur pas gzhi ma yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11228: nga ni chos rnams ma lus shing lus pa med
NK095(ce)001:11229: pa thams cad kyi gnas lugs mthar thug pa yin
NK095(ce)001:11232: gnyis pa rgyas pa ra bshad pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:11233: de la gong du bshad pa de dag gi rgyu mtshan ci lta bu zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:11235: dper na rgya mtsho chen po las //
NK095(ce)001:11236: chu bran rnam pa mang po yang //
NK095(ce)001:11237: byung yang rgya mtsho nyid las byung //
NK095(ce)001:11238: byung yang rgya mtsho 'grib pa med //
NK095(ce)001:11241: de bzhin byang chub sems nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:11242: chos rnams sna tshogs byung ba yang //
NK095(ce)001:11243: byung yang byang chub sems las byung //
NK095(ce)001:11244: byung yang byang chub sems la 'grib pa med //
NK095(ce)001:11246: 'dus kyang byang chub sems la 'phel ba med //
NK095(ce)001:11247: ces gsungs pa ltar ji ltar snang ba'i chos snang
NK095(ce)001:11248: srid 'khor 'das kyi rol par snang ba 'di rnams
NK095(ce)001:11249: thams cad kun chos sku kun byed rgyal po rig
NK095(ce)001:11250: pa byang chub sems las gzhan du ma grub par
NK095(ce)001:11251: gang snang ci shar thams cad sems nyid rang byung
NK095(ce)001:11252: ye shes kyi klong du gnyis med mnyam pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:11253: du 'dus shing 'ub chub pa'i phyir na snang srid
NK095(ce)001:11254: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams ma lus pa kun gang
NK095(ce)001:11255: las 'byung ba dang gang du 'dus pa'i snying por
NK095(ce)001:11256: bshad pa ste / bang mdzod 'phrul sde las /
NK095(ce)001:11257: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:11258: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid yin //
NK095(ce)001:11259: mi snang ba la mngon du 'byin nus pa //
NK095(ce)001:11260: chos kyi snying po yin par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:11263: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun kun
NK095(ce)001:11264: byed byang chub kyi sems gdod nas skye ba med
NK095(ce)001:11265: pa las skye ba'i cho 'phrul du byung ba yin
NK095(ce)001:11266: pa'i phyir na chos rnams kyi bskyed pa'i sa bon
NK095(ce)001:11269: skye med dbyings las skye ba'i cho 'phrul rnams //
NK095(ce)001:11270: rnam dag byang chub sems kyi dbyings nas 'phro //
NK095(ce)001:11272: ji ltar snang ba'i chos 'khor 'das gnyis su snang
NK095(ce)001:11273: ba 'di rnams thams cad kun byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:11274: rtsal snang ngo shes pa dang ma shes pa'i dbang
NK095(ce)001:11275: gis 'khor 'das so sor 'byung zhing snang ba'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:11276: na chos rnams thams cad kun gang las 'byung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:11277: rgyu yang byang chub kyi sems yin te /
NK095(ce)001:11279: thams cad sems las 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:11280: kun gyi 'byung gnas yin par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:11282: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kyi yan lag gi
NK095(ce)001:11283: bye brag sangs rgyas dang sems can la sogs pa
NK095(ce)001:11284: kun 'byung bas de dag gi gzhi ma yin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11285: phyir na byang chub kyi sems ni yal ga thams
NK095(ce)001:11286: cad gang las gyes pa'i sdong po lta bu yin
NK095(ce)001:11287: te / rin po che 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:11288: ga bur dag gi rang bzhin la //
NK095(ce)001:11289: sman dug ming du ma btags kyang //
NK095(ce)001:11290: sman dug gnyis su snang ba ltar //
NK095(ce)001:11291: kun gzhi spyi sa gcig pa las //
NK095(ce)001:11292: 'char sgo gnyis su shugs kyis byung //
NK095(ce)001:11294: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun kun
NK095(ce)001:11295: byed byang chub kyi sems nga yi rang bzhin srid
NK095(ce)001:11296: zhi kun khyab chen po'i ngang la ye nas rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:11297: shing gnas pa de las g.yo ba med pas chos
NK095(ce)001:11298: thams cad brten pa'i gzhi ma yin te /
NK095(ce)001:11300: 'khor 'das thams cad kyi rten du gyur pas na gazhi'o //
NK095(ce)001:11303: thams cad sems la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:11304: kun gyi gzhi ma yin par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:11306: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun gdod
NK095(ce)001:11307: nas skye ba med pa kun byed byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:11308: sems nga yi rang bzhin yin pas na chos thams
NK095(ce)001:11309: cad kyi rtsa ba yin par bshad de /
NK095(ce)001:11311: gcig ni kun gyi rang bzhin te //
NK095(ce)001:11312: chos kyi dbyings sam byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:11313: yin pas rtsa ba'i don du bzhag /ces gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:11315: sku gsum byung tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11316: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum gyi byung tshul rgyas par bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:11317: bstan pa dang 'khor g.yos pa med pa dang rgyu
NK095(ce)001:11318: 'bras rtsol bas de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin mi
NK095(ce)001:11321: kye sems dpa' chen po rdo rje khyod nyon cig
NK095(ce)001:11322: /kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga yi ni rang
NK095(ce)001:11323: bzhin ma bcos pa rnam pa gsum gyi rtsal las
NK095(ce)001:11324: ming gis brjod pa tsam du rgyal ba sku gsum
NK095(ce)001:11325: gyi ston pa rnams byung tshul bstan na yang nges
NK095(ce)001:11326: par ste nges pa'i don la sku gsum gyi ston
NK095(ce)001:11327: pa yang chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang las
NK095(ce)001:11328: g.yos pa rdul tsam med pas kun byed nga yi
NK095(ce)001:11329: rang bzhin du rtag tu gnas pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:11330: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:11331: g.yang sa med pa'i byang chub sems nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:11332: rtsol ba med pa'i sku gsum lhun rdzogs kyang //
NK095(ce)001:11333: dbyings las ma g.yos lhun grub 'dus ma byas //
NK095(ce)001:11336: de yang kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga yi
NK095(ce)001:11337: ni rang bzhin stong pa'i cha ye nas ma skyes
NK095(ce)001:11338: shing gzung 'dzin dang bral ba las ni chos sku
NK095(ce)001:11339: skye ba med pa zhes pa'i ming tsam byung na
NK095(ce)001:11340: yang nges pa'i don mthar thug par na smra bsam
NK095(ce)001:11341: brjod pa thams cad dang bral ba kun zlum thig
NK095(ce)001:11342: le chen po gcig gi rang bzhin las med pas
NK095(ce)001:11343: na chos sku zhes brjod pa de yang ming gi
NK095(ce)001:11344: bla dwags tsam ste don la chos nyid de bzhin
NK095(ce)001:11345: nyid las g.yos pa rdul tsam yang med do //
NK095(ce)001:11346: de bzhin du kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga
NK095(ce)001:11347: yi ngo bo gsal ba'i cha zhes pa'i ming tsam
NK095(ce)001:11348: zhig mngon du byung ba la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11349: sku zhes ming gi tha snyad tsam gyi tshul du
NK095(ce)001:11350: brjod kyang don nges par ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11351: sku de de bzhin nyid spros mtha' thams cad dang
NK095(ce)001:11352: bral ba'i ngang las g.yos pa med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11353: kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga yis ni thugs
NK095(ce)001:11354: rje 'gag pa med pa sprul pa'i sku ru mngon
NK095(ce)001:11355: du phyung ba yang 'di ltar thugs rje ma bcos
NK095(ce)001:11356: pa'i rang bzhin gyi rtsal las ming tsam du sprul
NK095(ce)001:11357: pa'i sku yi tshul du byung ba'o zhes nges par
NK095(ce)001:11358: brjod pa tsam las don la byung sa byung mkhan
NK095(ce)001:11359: gyi chos su grub pa gang yang med pas sprul
NK095(ce)001:11360: pa'i sku de yang chos nyid de bzhin nyid las
NK095(ce)001:11361: gar yang g.yos pa med do zhes so //
NK095(ce)001:11363: de ltar de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin las sku
NK095(ce)001:11364: gsum gyi ston pa rnams skad cig kyang g.yos pa
NK095(ce)001:11366: ston pa sku gsum gyis bstan pa'i theg pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:11367: gyi chos rnams dang sku gsum gyi 'dus pa'i 'khor
NK095(ce)001:11368: dus gsum sangs rgyas la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:11369: des mtshon pa'i phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsdus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11370: chos rnams kun la'ang de bzhin nyid las g.yos pa
NK095(ce)001:11371: rdul tsam yang med pas gdod nas skye ba med
NK095(ce)001:11372: pa chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la rtag
NK095(ce)001:11374: de ltar chos thams cad snying po byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:11375: kyi klong las mo g.yosa mi g.yo g.yo ba med
NK095(ce)001:11376: pa yi chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa ye stong
NK095(ce)001:11377: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin yin pa la tshogs
NK095(ce)001:11378: gnyis bsags pa la sogs pa rgyu dang sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:11379: kyi go 'phang la 'bras bur sgro btags par byas
NK095(ce)001:11380: nas / de la zhen cing chags pa'i re dogs
NK095(ce)001:11381: kyis rgyu 'bras blang dor gyis rtsol ba dang bsgrub
NK095(ce)001:11382: pa byas nas ni rgyu las 'bras bu 'byung bar
NK095(ce)001:11383: 'dod pa rnams ni kun byed nga las rang byung
NK095(ce)001:11384: du byung bas ye nas byas zin pa yi chos
NK095(ce)001:11385: 'di rnams thams cad rgyu 'brasa rtsol sgrub kyi yul
NK095(ce)001:11387: de ltar ma rtogs pas rdzogs chen bya rtsol bral
NK095(ce)001:11388: ba'i don las gzhan du theg pa 'og ma blang
NK095(ce)001:11389: dor rtsol sgrub can gyi lam du gol ba yin
NK095(ce)001:11392: phun sum tshogs pa thams cad sems nyid kun byed
NK095(ce)001:11393: nyid yin pa la the tshom za ba spang ba
NK095(ce)001:11394: / sems nyid byang chub tu ye nas bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:11396: kye sems dpa' chen po khyod nyon cig /kun byed
NK095(ce)001:11397: nga yi rang bzhin rnam pa gsum las mngon du
NK095(ce)001:11398: byung ba'i sku gsuma gyi ston pa rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:11399: de bzhin du nga las byung ba'i dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:11400: nga las byung ba'i sku gsum gyi ston pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:11401: kyi 'khor gyi tshogs dang de dag gang du bzhugs
NK095(ce)001:11402: pa'i gnas dang nam gyi tshe lhan gcig tshogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11403: dus la sogs pa kun kyang ye nas ston pa
NK095(ce)001:11404: kun byed nga yi thugs rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:11405: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin las skad cig kyang
NK095(ce)001:11406: g.yo ma myong bar chos nyid de bzhin nyid du
NK095(ce)001:11407: gnas pa yin na semsa dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis
NK095(ce)001:11408: de la yin min du 'dzin pa'i the tshom gyis
NK095(ce)001:11409: rtog cig dpyod par byas pas mi rtog mnyam pa
NK095(ce)001:11410: nyid kyi don dang 'gal ba yin pas sems dpa'
NK095(ce)001:11411: rdo rje nyid kyis de la yin nam ma yin
NK095(ce)001:11412: snyam pa'i the tshom gyis ma rtog par chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:11413: gnyug ma'i ngang du mi rtogs mnyam pa nyid du
NK095(ce)001:11414: gnas par gyis zhig ces gdams pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:11416: 'di ltar ston pa nga ni ye nas kun byed rgyal po byang chub kyi sems yin la /
NK095(ce)001:11417: nga yis byas pa'am nga yi rtsal las shar ba'i chos kun kyang byang chub kyi sems yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:11418: de la byang chub kyi sems zhes pa'i don ni
