NK095(ce)001:11419: kun byed nga yi rang bzhin ye gdod nas sgrib
NK095(ce)001:11420: pa'i dri ma thams cad rnam par dag pas byang
NK095(ce)001:11421: ba dang / nga yis 'khor 'das kun la gnyis
NK095(ce)001:11422: med du khyab cing lhun rdzogs mnyam pa chen por
NK095(ce)001:11423: ye nas gnas pas chub pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11424: nga yi rang bzhin gsal la 'gags pa med par
NK095(ce)001:11425: 'char bas ye nas sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:11426: shes yin pa'am / yang byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ba'am /
NK095(ce)001:11427: byang chub ni dri ma thams cad yongs su dag
NK095(ce)001:11428: cing phyin ci ma log par khong du chub pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11429: ye shes dang / sems ni kun tu rtog pa'i rang bzhin can te /
NK095(ce)001:11430: de gnyis tha dad du bzhag pa ni dmigs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11431: mtshan nyid te dper na 'gal me nyid 'khor lor
NK095(ce)001:11432: 'khrul pa yin pas snang ba'i sgo nas gnyis ka
NK095(ce)001:11433: dus gcig la tha dad du mi snang yang dmigs
NK095(ce)001:11434: pa'i sgo nas 'gal me dang 'khor lo tha dad
NK095(ce)001:11436: ngo bo nyid kyi mtshan nyid ni tha dad min par gnyis su med pa'i mtshan nyid te /
NK095(ce)001:11437: dpe ra na 'gal me la 'khor lor snang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:11438: pa'i skabs na yang 'khor lo'i snang ba 'khrul pa
NK095(ce)001:11439: bslu zhing mi bden pa'i rang bzhin yin pas yod
NK095(ce)001:11440: ma myong bar 'gal me'i ngo bor grub pa ltar
NK095(ce)001:11441: sems kun tu rtog pa ltar snang bzhin pa na
NK095(ce)001:11442: yang de nyid 'khrul snang yin pas yod ma myong
NK095(ce)001:11443: bar byang chub sems kyi ngo bor grub pa yin
NK095(ce)001:11444: pas byang chub kyi sems zhes kyang gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:11445: ston pa nga ni gdod nas skye ba med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11446: phyir nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin gyis ye nas
NK095(ce)001:11447: chos thams cad la khyab cing gnas lugs 'dus ma
NK095(ce)001:11448: byas pa'i rang bzhin 'khor 'das thams cad kyi 'byung
NK095(ce)001:11449: gnas su gyur pa yin pa'i phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:11450: de lta bu'i byang chub kyi semsa de nyid kyis
NK095(ce)001:11451: ni dper na sgyu ma'i rdzas sngags la brten nas
NK095(ce)001:11452: rta glang la sogs pa snang ba lta bu'i 'jig
NK095(ce)001:11453: rten sgyu mar snang ba'i chos rnams kyi dpe bzhin
NK095(ce)001:11454: du sku gsum gyi ston pa dang dus gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:11455: sangsa rgyas rnams ston pa kun byed nga yi bu
NK095(ce)001:11456: dang tsha bo dang 'khor gyi tshul du mngon du
NK095(ce)001:11457: byung nas / phas bu la ma nor ba bden pa'i tshig gis gdams ngag 'bogs pa bzhin du /
NK095(ce)001:11458: don nor ba med pa rang gi rig pa byang
NK095(ce)001:11459: chub kyi sems ni nam mkha' bzhin du skye med
NK095(ce)001:11460: kun la khyab pa'i rang bzhin du bstan nas /
NK095(ce)001:11461: kun byed byang chub sems kyi rtsal las 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:11462: kyi rol pa byung tshul nam mkha' yi klong du
NK095(ce)001:11463: snod bcud thams cad skye med kyi dbyings las 'gags
NK095(ce)001:11464: med du byung ba bzhin du bstan pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:11466: de ltar nges par bstan pa'i mdo lung bcu dgos pa dang bcas pas /
NK095(ce)001:11467: sems nyid phun sum tshogs pa'i rang bzhin yin par
NK095(ce)001:11468: gtan tshigs dpe don dang bcas pas bstan pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:11469: bden par smra ba'i skye bos bka' phrin bsnyad pa
NK095(ce)001:11470: ltar ma nor nges pa'i don la yid ches par
NK095(ce)001:11472: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK095(ce)001:11473: chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems kun byed las
NK095(ce)001:11474: byung ba'i khungs kyi le'u ste nyi shu pa'i 'grel
NK095(ce)001:11475: ba'o ////don gnyis pa rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i le'u
NK095(ce)001:11476: bcus sems nyid kun byed rgyal po ye nas bya
NK095(ce)001:11477: btsal med par bstan pa'i le'u bcu las dang po
NK095(ce)001:11478: thams cad rang byung gi ye shes su gcig pas
NK095(ce)001:11479: ngo bo gcig la rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11480: le'u nyer gcig pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:11484: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsdus pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:11485: thams cad kun byed nyid yin par bstan pa de
NK095(ce)001:11486: nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po des
NK095(ce)001:11487: ston pa sku gsum gyis bstan pa'i chos thamsa cad
NK095(ce)001:11488: kyi 'byung gnas sam khungs kyi rgyal po kun byed
NK095(ce)001:11489: nyid yin pa'i phyir de thams cad nyid las byung
NK095(ce)001:11492: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes nyid kun las
NK095(ce)001:11493: khyad par 'phags pas rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das
NK095(ce)001:11495: de nyid gtan tshigs lngas 'das tshul rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11496: sems nyid spros bral brjod las 'das pas rgyu 'bras bya rtsol mi dgos pa'i don bsdu ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:11498: phun sum tshogs pa kun ye ldan lhun grub tu
NK095(ce)001:11499: gnas pas phyi nas bya btsal rgyu 'bras la mi
NK095(ce)001:11500: ltos pa dang / sems nyid skye 'gags gnas gsum
NK095(ce)001:11501: las grol bas sku gsum lhun rdzogs gtan tshigs lnga
NK095(ce)001:11504: kye semsa dpa' chen po rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod
NK095(ce)001:11505: kyis chos thams cad kyi khungs kun byed byang chub
NK095(ce)001:11506: kyi sems yin pa'i tshul 'di nyon cig dang bshad
NK095(ce)001:11508: de yang ji ltar na kun byed nga ni phun
NK095(ce)001:11509: sum tshogs pa'i chos rnams kun ma btsal lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:11510: kyi tshul du byed pa'i rgyal po yin pa ste
NK095(ce)001:11511: / 'di ltar sku gsum gyi ston pa rnams gang
NK095(ce)001:11512: las byung bar gyur pa'i pha ma nga nyid yin
NK095(ce)001:11513: / la / sku gsum gyi ston pa de las
NK095(ce)001:11514: byung ba'i dus gsum gyi sangsa rgyas kun gyi mes
NK095(ce)001:11515: po yang ston pa nga nyid yin zhing /
NK095(ce)001:11516: de dag gi 'khor gyi tshogs dang gnas dang dus
NK095(ce)001:11517: rnams kyi rang bzhin phun sum tshogs pa'i sgo nas
NK095(ce)001:11518: sku gsum pos bstan pa'i theg pa rnams gsal zhing
NK095(ce)001:11519: ston par byed pa'i sgron ma'ang nga nyid kyis byed
NK095(ce)001:11520: pa ste / de ltar na kun byed nga yi
NK095(ce)001:11521: rang bzhin rnam pa gsum las sku gsum gyi ston
NK095(ce)001:11522: pa rnams nga yi rtsal las thugs rje phyi gsal
NK095(ce)001:11523: gyi char byung ba yin pa'i rgyu mtshan de bas
NK095(ce)001:11524: pa ste / na / phun sum tshogs pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:11525: thams cad ni ye nas byang chub kyi sems su
NK095(ce)001:11526: lhun gyis grub zin pas gsar du 'bad rtsol rgyu
NK095(ce)001:11528: des na sku gsum gyi ston pa rnams kyis bstan
NK095(ce)001:11529: pa'i rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa sna tshogs gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:11530: de yi bshad lugsa chos skus byin gyis rlabs kyis
NK095(ce)001:11531: bshad pa la sogs pa rnam pa gsum gyis dbye
NK095(ce)001:11532: bas chos rnams kyi bshad lugsa rnam pa gsum yang
NK095(ce)001:11533: bstan pa de yang ston par byed pa po gzhan
NK095(ce)001:11534: su yang med par kun byed nga yis bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:11537: kun byed rgyal po nga yi rang bzhin 'di nyid
NK095(ce)001:11538: ni ye nas skye 'gags gnas gsum dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:11539: rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i bdag nyid rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:11540: rtsol sgrub kun las 'das pa yin pas ston pa
NK095(ce)001:11541: gzhan kun las khyad par du 'phags pa yin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11542: phyir na sku gsum lhun rdzogs rang byung chen po
NK095(ce)001:11543: la rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub mi dgos pa'i gtan tshigs
NK095(ce)001:11544: don gyi bshad lugs rnam pa lngas sgo nas kun
NK095(ce)001:11545: byed byang chub sems kyi don ma nor ba ji
NK095(ce)001:11546: lta ba bzhin nges par byed pa'i gtan tshigs kyi
NK095(ce)001:11547: khungs kyang kun byed ngas bstan to //
NK095(ce)001:11550: lo rgyus don gyi bshad lugs dang //
NK095(ce)001:11551: rtsa ba don gyi bshad lugs dang //
NK095(ce)001:11552: yo ga don gyi bshad lugs dang //
NK095(ce)001:11553: dgos ched don gyi bshad lugs dang //
NK095(ce)001:11554: tshig gi don gyi bshad lugs so //
NK095(ce)001:11556: bshad tshul gnyis mdor bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11557: kun byed byang chub kyi sems sku gsum ston pa gsum gyis bshad tshul gnyis rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:11559: kye sems dpa' chen po 'di ltar kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:11560: po zhes bya ba ni byang chub kyi sems 'di
NK095(ce)001:11561: nyid yin la / rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:11562: de la ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye
NK095(ce)001:11563: nas rdzogs shing che ba lnga'i ngo bo sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:11564: pa yin pas rdzogs pa che ba'am chen po yin
NK095(ce)001:11565: zhing de lta ba'i sems nyid rdzogs pa chen po
NK095(ce)001:11566: rang byung gi ye shes de ni ye nas rgyu
NK095(ce)001:11567: 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:11568: des na rgyu 'bras bya rtsol gyi yul las 'das pa'i bshad lugs bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11569: kun byed byanga chub semsa kyi rang bzhin lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:11570: rnam pa gsum las rgyal ba sku gsum gyi ston
NK095(ce)001:11571: pa rnams byung nas rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:11572: gsungs pa'i bshad lugsa bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11573: rnam pa gnyis kyi bshad lugsa bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:11575: de la kun byed byang chub sems kyi bshad lugs ni gang zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:11576: 'di ltar byang chub kyi sems de ni rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:11577: rtsol sgrub kun las 'das pa'i phyir na gtan tshigs
NK095(ce)001:11578: don gyi bshad lugs lnga yis bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11579: sku gsum ston pa gsum gyi bshad lugs ni rang
NK095(ce)001:11580: rang gi phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa lnga yi
NK095(ce)001:11581: nang du bsdus nas bshad pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:11582: 'di ltar ston pa chos kyi sku yis ni nyid
NK095(ce)001:11583: las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshogs
NK095(ce)001:11584: rnams la skye med don gyi gsung la brten nas
NK095(ce)001:11585: thugs rang byung ye shes kyi rgyud chen po lnga
NK095(ce)001:11586: dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i byin gyisa brlabs kyis
NK095(ce)001:11589: ston pa 'gyur med chos kyi sku //
NK095(ce)001:11590: bstan pa mi nub rgyal mtshan ni //
NK095(ce)001:11591: gsang ba'i rig pa rgyud chen lnga //
NK095(ce)001:11592: 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs nyid las mi gzhan pa'i //
NK095(ce)001:11593: rigs lnga'i bde gshegs 'od du 'bar ba la //
NK095(ce)001:11594: bzhugs gnas skye med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:11595: dus ni 'das dang ma byon sngon rol na //
NK095(ce)001:11596: rtog med ston pas byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11597: nyid las mi gzhan sku lnga rang rang gi //
NK095(ce)001:11598: rgyud chen byin gyis brlabs kyis go //
NK095(ce)001:11600: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku bde gshegs rigs
NK095(ce)001:11601: lnga'i tshogs kyis rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor
NK095(ce)001:11602: tshogs rnams la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK095(ce)001:11603: kyi bsdus pa'i rgyud chen po lnga ston pa rang
NK095(ce)001:11604: rang gi sku yi ngo bo mngon sum du bstan
NK095(ce)001:11605: pa'i sgo nas dgongs pa brda yi gsung gis ston
NK095(ce)001:11606: pa'i tshul kyang / de nyid las /
NK095(ce)001:11607: ston pa rigs lnga bde gshegs lnga //
NK095(ce)001:11608: bstan pa gsang ba'i rgyud chen lnga //
NK095(ce)001:11609: 'dus pa'i 'khor ni sems dpa' sems ma'i tshogs //
NK095(ce)001:11610: bzhugs pa'i gnas ni ye shes gzhal med 'od kyi klong //
NK095(ce)001:11611: dus ni de rnams rig pa yul la shar ba'i tshe //
NK095(ce)001:11612: tshig dang yi ge'i sgo nas mi 'chad par //
NK095(ce)001:11613: sku yi cha byad sgo nas ston //
NK095(ce)001:11615: ston pa sprul pa'i sku rdo rje sems dpas gong
NK095(ce)001:11616: du bstan pa'i gsang ba'i rgyud chen lngas mtshon pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11617: phyi nang gsang ba'i rgyud sde bsam gyis mi khyab
NK095(ce)001:11618: pa sangs rgyas rab bdun la sogs pa'i 'khor tshogs
NK095(ce)001:11619: rnams ni yan lag drug cu'i gsung gis don rnams
NK095(ce)001:11620: sgra tshig tu brjod cing sdeba sbyor legs pa'i sgo
NK095(ce)001:11623: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' ngas //
NK095(ce)001:11624: bstan pa'i snying po gsang ba'i rgyud chen lnga //
NK095(ce)001:11625: de sogs phyi nang gsang bas bsdus pa rnams //
NK095(ce)001:11626: thugs kyi klong du shes rab chen pos bkrol //
NK095(ce)001:11627: mgur gyi bum par ye shes rlung gis dril //
NK095(ce)001:11628: zhal gyi ljags la ma 'dres gsal bar bkram //
NK095(ce)001:11629: tshem gyi bar nas tshig don so sor bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11630: yan lag drug cu'i sdeb sbyor legs par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11631: khyung chen lding thabs don gyi spyi khog dbub //
NK095(ce)001:11632: stag mo'i mchongs stabs lta bu'i dkyus kyi sa rnams bcad //
NK095(ce)001:11633: ru sbal 'gros kyis tshig gi 'bru rnams gzhom //
NK095(ce)001:11634: seng ge'i gdangs skad lta bu'i theg brgyad zil gyis gnon //
NK095(ce)001:11635: glag mo'i gzan 'jum lta bus don gyi man ngag dril //
NK095(ce)001:11636: 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs sangs rgyas rab bdun la //
NK095(ce)001:11637: lha gnas gsum du bdud rtsi'i char chen phab //
NK095(ce)001:11638: pad+ma brtsegs pa'i gnas mchog rnam gsum mo //
NK095(ce)001:11640: gzhan yang ston pa thub pa'i dbang po la sogs
NK095(ce)001:11641: pas sde snod gsum gyi chos 'khor bskor ba thams
NK095(ce)001:11642: cad sprul sku'i sdeb sbyor legs par gsungs pa ste
NK095(ce)001:11643: / ri bo brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:11644: khang bzang gnas su sprul sku'i ston pa yis //
NK095(ce)001:11645: mos tshad kun dga' bo la sde snod rnam gsum bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11646: sprul skus tshig tu sdebs te bshad pa'i dus //
NK095(ce)001:11648: de dag ni sku gsum gyis ston pas bstan pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11649: chos rnams kyi bshad lugs rnam pa gsum ste don
NK095(ce)001:11650: la kun byed nga yi rang bzhin rnam pa gsum
NK095(ce)001:11651: las gzhan pa'i sku gsum gyi ston pa zhig med
NK095(ce)001:11652: pas na de yi bshad lugs bstan pa yiin no
NK095(ce)001:11653: // de bzhin du rgyu 'bras 'das pa'i bshad lugs
NK095(ce)001:11654: ni ji ltar na kun byed byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:11655: nga ni ye nas rang byung 'dus ma byas pa
NK095(ce)001:11656: sku gsum lhun rdzogs chen po'i bdag nyid yin pas
NK095(ce)001:11658: de ltar rgyu 'bras las 'das pas lus kyi bya
NK095(ce)001:11659: byed dang ngag gis smra brjod dang sems kyis bsam
NK095(ce)001:11660: dpyod sogs sgo gsum gyi spyod yul kun las 'das
NK095(ce)001:11661: pa yin la / de ltar rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:11662: kun gyi yul las 'das pa'i chos nyid nam mkha'
NK095(ce)001:11663: lta bu de ni byang chuba kyi sems yin pas
NK095(ce)001:11664: na byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po nyid
NK095(ce)001:11665: ni sku gsum gyi phun sum tshogs pas bsdus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11666: chos thams cad kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11668: de ltar chos thams cad gang las byung ba'i snying
NK095(ce)001:11669: po yin par bstan pas lo rgyus don gyi sgo
NK095(ce)001:11670: nas bstan pa gang las byung ba'i tshul la yid
NK095(ce)001:11671: ches kyi khungs kyang bstan pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:11673: thams cad sems las byung ba'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:11674: kun gyi 'byung gnas yin par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:11676: rgyu las ma byung rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas //
NK095(ce)001:11677: rang byung ye shes yin par yid kyang ches //
NK095(ce)001:11680: 'di ltar byang chub kyi sems ni 'khor 'das kyi
NK095(ce)001:11681: chos thams cad kun gyi gang las snang ba'i gazhi'am
NK095(ce)001:11682: rtsa ba ste / de ltar rtsa ba yin pas
NK095(ce)001:11683: na phyi nang snang srid kyi chos thams cad kun
NK095(ce)001:11684: gyi don yang byang chub sems su 'dus pa yin
NK095(ce)001:11685: rtsa ba ste / te / chos dbyings mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:11686: thams cad kun 'dus byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK095(ce)001:11687: byang chub sems las ma gtogs chos med pas //
NK095(ce)001:11688: chos kun byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:11690: des na chos thams cad rtsa ba byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:11691: sems su bsdus shing de las gzhan du med par
NK095(ce)001:11692: ye gdod ma nyid nas snying po byang chub sems
NK095(ce)001:11693: kyi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:11694: da blang dor 'bad rtsol gyi sgo nas lam gyis
NK095(ce)001:11695: bcos shing sgrub tu med par ston pa ni rtsa
NK095(ce)001:11696: ba'i don gyis bshad pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:11698: rtsa ba'i don du bshad pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:11699: rang rig ye shes chen por bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11702: kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni rgyu
NK095(ce)001:11703: 'bras rtsol sgrub kun las 'das pa'i phyir na rgyu
NK095(ce)001:11704: 'bras rtsol sgrub can gyi theg pa gong 'og gi
NK095(ce)001:11705: khyad par kun las 'phags pa yin la /
NK095(ce)001:11706: de ltar theg pa kun las khyad par 'phagsa pa yin pas na /
NK095(ce)001:11707: rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhung gis theg pa thams cad
NK095(ce)001:11708: kyi grub pa'i mtha' so sor ma 'dres par shan
NK095(ce)001:11709: yang 'byed cing de dag gis rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:11710: byed pa dang grub mtha'i blo skyon thams cad sun
NK095(ce)001:11711: dbyung zhing rdzogs pa chen po rgyu 'bras 'bad rtsol
NK095(ce)001:11712: kun las 'das par la bzla ba'i tshul gyis bshad
NK095(ce)001:11713: pa ni yo ga'i don gyi bshad pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:11715: yo ga'i don du bshad pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:11716: theg pa'i la shan phye la bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11719: byang chub semsa kyi yin lugs rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:11720: gang yang mi dgos par gdod nas mngon par byang
NK095(ce)001:11721: chub pas ma bcos rnal bzhag chen po'i don 'di
NK095(ce)001:11722: rtogs par gyur na chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:11723: klong du 'khor 'das kyi chos kun kyang ye nas
NK095(ce)001:11724: sangs rgyas par rtogs pa des na skal ldan dbang
NK095(ce)001:11725: rab rnams blang dor 'bad rtsol gyis gdung ba med
NK095(ce)001:11726: par rtsol med du grol ba'i ched du bshad pa
NK095(ce)001:11727: ni dgos ched don gyis bstan pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:11729: bla med byang chub chen po 'di //
NK095(ce)001:11730: btsal bas 'grub pa ma yin te //
NK095(ce)001:11731: ma btsal rnal du bzhag pas grub //
NK095(ce)001:11732: gdod nas snying po byang chub la //
NK095(ce)001:11733: btsal kyang dbyings las bskyod pa med //
NK095(ce)001:11734: btsal na rtsol ba'i nad du 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:11735: zhes gsungs pa lta bu'i skyon dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:11737: 'di ltar byang chub semsa kyi rang bzhin ni spros
NK095(ce)001:11738: pa thams cad dang bral zhing bsam brjod kyi yul
NK095(ce)001:11739: las 'das pa yin pas na de'i ngo bo 'di
NK095(ce)001:11740: lta bu'o zhes tshig tu dngos su brjod du med
NK095(ce)001:11741: de brjod med don gyi gnas lugs yin na yang
NK095(ce)001:11742: / 'on kyang mdzub mos zla ba ltar mtshon par
NK095(ce)001:11743: byed pa'i tshig tsam zhig ma brjod du zin na
NK095(ce)001:11744: yang chos nyid byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin mi
NK095(ce)001:11745: snang zhing rtogs par mi 'gyur bas na yod med
NK095(ce)001:11746: dang yin min la sogs pa spros pa'i mtha' gang
NK095(ce)001:11747: du'ang mi snang zhing dpe dang gtan tshigs sogs kyis
NK095(ce)001:11748: mtshon du med do ces pa lta bus ma brjod
NK095(ce)001:11749: pa'am brjod par ma byas na gang zag kun kyang
NK095(ce)001:11750: rang gi sems kyi chos nyid ma mthong bar rgyu
NK095(ce)001:11751: 'bras rtsol sgrub byed pa'i lam du gol ba'i nyen
NK095(ce)001:11752: yod pa'i rgyu mtshan des na rdzogs chen a ti
NK095(ce)001:11753: yo ga brjod du med pa'i tshig gi don yang
NK095(ce)001:11754: / bshad te / de yang ji ltar bshad na don gyi khog phub /
NK095(ce)001:11756: tshig gi 'bru bcom ste bshad par bya ste /
NK095(ce)001:11758: khyung chen gshogs rdzogs lta bu'i blos //
NK095(ce)001:11759: don gyi spyi khog phub ste bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11760: stag gi mchongs stabs lta bu'i blos //
NK095(ce)001:11761: dkyus kyi sa rnams bcad de bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11762: rus sbal nur 'gros lta bu'i blos //
NK095(ce)001:11763: yi ge'i 'bru rnams bcom par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:11766: gong du bshad pa lta bu'i rgyu mtshan des na
NK095(ce)001:11767: gtan tshig don gyi bshad lugs rnam pa lnga po
NK095(ce)001:11768: 'dis kun byed rgyal po byang chub sems kyi don
NK095(ce)001:11769: byar med lhun gyis grub pa'i yin lugs ma nor
NK095(ce)001:11770: ba ji lta ba bzhin du nges par gtan la
NK095(ce)001:11771: 'bebsa par byed pa des ni rgyu 'bras blang dor
NK095(ce)001:11772: kyang med par chos nyid mnyam pa chen po gcig
NK095(ce)001:11773: gi rang bzhin du gtan la phab pa yin pas
NK095(ce)001:11774: 'khor 'das su snang ba'i chos thams cad la bzang
NK095(ce)001:11775: ngan dang spang blang gi dbye ba med pa kun
NK095(ce)001:11776: byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin yin par yid
NK095(ce)001:11778: de ltar chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems yina
NK095(ce)001:11779: zhing sems nyid ye nas spros bral mnyam pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:11780: du sangs rgyas par yid ches pas /
NK095(ce)001:11781: da lta'i snang ba 'di las gzhan du sems la btsal du med par yid kyang ches la /
NK095(ce)001:11782: btsal du ye nas med par yid ches shing blo
NK095(ce)001:11783: thag gting nas chod pas lam la mi rtsol zhing
NK095(ce)001:11784: gnyen pos mi bsgrub par rtsol med bde ba chen
NK095(ce)001:11785: po'i ngang la gnas shing spros bral rang byung gi
NK095(ce)001:11786: ye shes ye nas 'dus ma byas pa kun bzang
NK095(ce)001:11787: chos sku'i rang zhal mngon du mthong bar 'gyur ba
NK095(ce)001:11788: ste / des na kun byed byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:11789: nga yi rang bzhin de ltar du gnas pa yin
NK095(ce)001:11790: pas na kun byed nga las sangs rgyas zhes bya
NK095(ce)001:11791: ba gang yang gzhan nas btsal du med do //
NK095(ce)001:11794: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las gtan
NK095(ce)001:11795: tshigs bshad lugs kyi le'u ste nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK095(ce)001:11796: pa'i 'grel ba'o ////don gnyis pa sems nyid mtha' gang
NK095(ce)001:11797: du yang mi gnas shing dmigs pa'i yul med pas
NK095(ce)001:11798: rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i don rgyu 'bras
NK095(ce)001:11799: dag grol du 'dzin pas mi rtogs par gsang ba
NK095(ce)001:11800: dam pa'i le'u nyer gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:11804: rdzogs pa chen po gtan tshigs dang ldan pas ji ltar bshad pa'i tshul bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:11805: de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po des /
NK095(ce)001:11806: rjes 'jug skal pa dang ldan pa a ti rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:11807: pa chen po'i gdul byar gyur pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK095(ce)001:11808: rnams kyi sems nyid ma bcos rnal du bzhag pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11809: phyir du blang dor bya rtsol la ltos pa med
NK095(ce)001:11810: par 'bras bu'i chos thams cad ye rdzogs lhun gyis
NK095(ce)001:11811: grub pa'i lung khungsa rtsol bcas kyi theg pa brgyad
NK095(ce)001:11812: las khyad du 'phags pa'i chen po bla na med
NK095(ce)001:11815: sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu bcos bsgyur gnyen po las 'das pa'i don mdor bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:11816: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:11817: thams cad sems nyid kyi rol pa spang blang las
NK095(ce)001:11818: 'das pa'i snying po kun la khyab tshul gyis don
NK095(ce)001:11820: kye semsa dpa' chen po rdo rje khyod nyon cig
NK095(ce)001:11821: dang byar med ye nas rdzogs pa'i man ngag zab
NK095(ce)001:11824: de yang ji ltar zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:11825: kye blang dor bya rtsol la ltos pa med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11826: yul chos kyi dbyings 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11827: ye shes ni spros pa'i mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas
NK095(ce)001:11828: pa'i phyir na nam mkha' dang 'dra ba yin la
NK095(ce)001:11829: / de ltar mtha' gang la'ang mi gansa shing gzung
NK095(ce)001:11830: 'dzin rnam rtog gis dmigsa pa'i yul du grub pa
NK095(ce)001:11831: med pa de yi phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:11832: theg pa 'og ma pa ltar spong 'gogs sbyong bsgyur
NK095(ce)001:11833: la sogs pa'i rnam pa cir yanga mi rtog par
NK095(ce)001:11834: ma bcos rang bab tu gnas pa ni chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:11835: kyi ngo bo ye nas bgrod du med pas ma
NK095(ce)001:11836: nor ba'i lam ye ji bzhin pa'i ngang du gnas
NK095(ce)001:11837: pa yin te / rtse mo byung rgyal las /
NK095(ce)001:11838: mnyam sbyor kun tu bzang po nyid kyi dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:11839: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol dgongs pa'i thugs //
NK095(ce)001:11840: bgrod med rnal 'byor rdzogs pa chen po'i lam //
NK095(ce)001:11841: byar med lhun rdzogs skye med chos kyi dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:11843: de las gzhan du sgom rtsol la re ba'i rtog
NK095(ce)001:11844: pa ni bsngo ba'i cha shas phra mo zhes bsngo
NK095(ce)001:11845: ba ni smon cing 'dun pa'i mtshan nyid yin la
NK095(ce)001:11846: / re smon gyi mtha' la gnas pa ni de'i
NK095(ce)001:11847: cha shas phra mo'i rang bzhin gang zhig blang dor
NK095(ce)001:11848: gyi yul la dmigs nas byung ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:11849: de lta bu'i blo rnam par rtog pa'i sgom pa
NK095(ce)001:11850: de ci tsam brtan par gyur kyang chos kyi sku
NK095(ce)001:11851: ni sems kyi 'khrul snang 'di las khyad par du
NK095(ce)001:11852: byung zhing lhag par gyur pa'i don gzhan zhig med
NK095(ce)001:11853: de 'khrul snang gi ngo bo gang yin pa de
NK095(ce)001:11854: nyid chos sku yin pa'i phyir te /
NK095(ce)001:11855: 'di ltar 'khrul snang yang sems yin la sems rang
NK095(ce)001:11856: gi ngo bo ma grub pasa rtog pa rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:11858: des na yul gyi rnam pa gang snang sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:11859: rtog pa ci skye'ang rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal bas
NK095(ce)001:11860: rang byung gi ye shes rang shar ba mi rtog
NK095(ce)001:11861: chos sku'i rang bzhin du dus dang rnam pa kun
NK095(ce)001:11862: tu ji bzhin du gnas pa de ni 'bad rtsol
NK095(ce)001:11863: gyi bya ba dang bral ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:11864: yul gang la'ang mi gansa shing gnyen pos bcos su
NK095(ce)001:11865: meda pas byar med ye 'byams kyi rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:11866: bstan pa ste / rdzogs pa spyi gcod las /
NK095(ce)001:11867: snang srid ma lus ye nas dag pas na //
NK095(ce)001:11868: rang gi sems nyid rgyal ba sangs rgyas yin //
NK095(ce)001:11869: rdo rje sems dpa' dbyer med ye sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:11870: ye nas dag pas chos sku bde ba'i mchog /ces gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK095(ce)001:11871: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:11872: sems nyid rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:11873: theg pa brgyad kyis mi rtogs pa'i tshul rgyas par
NK095(ce)001:11874: bshad pa / sems nyid a tir rang gnas chos
NK095(ce)001:11875: sku de bzhin nyid kyi dgongs pa rang la ye
NK095(ce)001:11876: nas gnas pa'i tshul rgyas par bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:11877: theg pa brgyad po a tir 'jug pa'i thabs su
NK095(ce)001:11878: che 'bring gnyen po'i rim pas gsungs tshul rgyas par
NK095(ce)001:11879: bshad pa / sems nyid a ti kun byed nyid
NK095(ce)001:11880: ma bcos rnal du bzhag thabs 'bras bu dang bcas
NK095(ce)001:11883: theg brgyad so so'i lam gyis snying po'i don mi mthong bar bye brag tu bshad pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11884: de thams cad rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i nad kyis sems
NK095(ce)001:11885: nyid ji bzhin pa'i lus gdung ba spyir bshad pa'o
NK095(ce)001:11887: sems nyid gdod nas dag pa'i snying po la rten
NK095(ce)001:11888: 'brel 'byung ldog gis bsgom kyang gsar du dag pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11889: 'bras bu mi thob ste ye nas chos skur gnas
NK095(ce)001:11890: pa'i tshul dang / nyan thos pas gzung yul dngos
NK095(ce)001:11891: po dang 'dzin byed shes pa rdul phran cha med
NK095(ce)001:11892: dang skad cig ma don dam du bzhag nas bdag
NK095(ce)001:11893: med du bsgoms kyang sems nyid yangs ba'i don mi
NK095(ce)001:11895: byang chub sems dpa' yul bdag med du bsgom kyang
NK095(ce)001:11896: de nyid las log pa'i don mngon sum du mi
NK095(ce)001:11898: kri yas sems las gzhan pa'i lha tha dad du
NK095(ce)001:11899: bsgom kyang de nyid sems nyid yin pas dbyings thug
NK095(ce)001:11900: med du gnas pa'i tshul dang /
NK095(ce)001:11901: u pas gnyis bcas su bsgom kyang sems las lhag pa'i ye shes gzhan na med pa'i tshul dang /
NK095(ce)001:11902: yo gas bdag dam tshig pa la ye shes sems
NK095(ce)001:11903: dpa' gzhan nas bstim nas dbyer med du bsgom bya
NK095(ce)001:11904: sgom byed gnyis su mi mthong ba'i tshul dang /
NK095(ce)001:11905: ma h+aas snang bcas bskyed pa'i rim pas rang byung
NK095(ce)001:11906: gi ye shes gcig la lha dang gzhal yas khang
NK095(ce)001:11907: du rtog kyang lus dang grib ma ltar gnyis bcas
NK095(ce)001:11909: a nus bde stong rdzogs rim gyi ye shes dbyings
NK095(ce)001:11910: las rang byung du bsgom kyang rjes chags rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:11913: 'di ltar rang rgyal lam du zhugs pa rnams kyis
NK095(ce)001:11914: phyi nang gi rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis lugs
NK095(ce)001:11915: 'byung du mched pa'i sgo nas 'khor ba'i chos phyi
NK095(ce)001:11916: snod kyi 'jig rten dang nang bcud kyi 'gro ba
NK095(ce)001:11917: gnas ris mtho dman sna tshogs su snang ba ste
NK095(ce)001:11918: / mdor na 'khor ba'i chos thams cad kyi rtsa
NK095(ce)001:11919: ba rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi dbang gis byung ba
NK095(ce)001:11921: de nyid lugs ldog tu bsgom pa'i sgo nas rang
NK095(ce)001:11922: byung snying po'i yul lam chos thams cad kyi snying
NK095(ce)001:11923: po'i rang bzhin du gyur pa'i gnas lugs yang dag
NK095(ce)001:11924: pa zhig yul du byas nas tshol zhing bsgom du
NK095(ce)001:11925: yod par rlom nas rnam pa cir yang mi rtog
NK095(ce)001:11926: par rtse gcig tu gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK095(ce)001:11927: mnyam par 'jog pa'i thabs kyis snying po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:11928: kyi sems de la rol zhing 'jug par rtsol na
NK095(ce)001:11929: yang rnam par mi rtog pa sgom pa de ni
NK095(ce)001:11930: rtog pa la ltos nas bzhag pa tsam yin kyang
NK095(ce)001:11931: / rtog pa ni gdod nas yod ma myong bas
NK095(ce)001:11932: na de la ltos pa'i mi rtog pa yang ji
NK095(ce)001:11933: ltar grub ste mi 'grub pas na kun brtags kho
NK095(ce)001:11934: / na yin zhing / snying po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:11935: rang bzhin ni de lta bu'i rgyu rkyen la rag
NK095(ce)001:11936: ma lus par gdod nas ye sangs rgyas pa'i ngo
NK095(ce)001:11937: bor bzhugs pa nyid rnal 'byor ba rnams la rig
NK095(ce)001:11938: pa rang gsal gyi tshul du mngon du 'byung zhing
NK095(ce)001:11939: 'char ba yin pa'i rgyu mtshan de basa na 'bras
NK095(ce)001:11940: bu chos sku de nyid gazhana na btsal du med
NK095(ce)001:11941: / na yin zhing / par gsungs pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK095(ce)001:11942: 'di ltar chos thams cad ni gdod nas snying po
NK095(ce)001:11943: byang chub sems kyi rtsal las rang shar ba med
NK095(ce)001:11944: snang stong gzugs kyi rol pa tsam las yod ma
NK095(ce)001:11945: myong bas chos nyid skye ba med pa don dam
NK095(ce)001:11946: blo 'das chen po'i ngo bor gnas pa la /
NK095(ce)001:11947: nyan thos pa rnams kyis bem shes rang mtshan pa'i ngo bor bltas te /
NK095(ce)001:11948: de yang gzugs mtha' rdul phran cha med dang shes
NK095(ce)001:11949: mtha' skad cig cha med gnyis don dam du bzhag
NK095(ce)001:11950: nas / de la gang zag gi bdag med par
NK095(ce)001:11951: gtan la phab ste bsgom par byed pa de ni
NK095(ce)001:11952: chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i don min te /
NK095(ce)001:11953: ci'i phyir na rdul phran cha med gcig la phyogs
NK095(ce)001:11954: bcu'i rdul phran bcus cig char du bskor te gtses
NK095(ce)001:11955: pa'am brtags shing dpyad na phyogs bcu yi cha kun
NK095(ce)001:11956: dang bral bas don la ma grub pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:11957: de bzhin du shes pa skad cig snga phyi la brtags kyang ma grub la /
NK095(ce)001:11958: gang zag gi bdag med bsgom pa yang gzhan sel
NK095(ce)001:11959: gyi cha blo rnam rtog gi gzugs brnyan tsam las
NK095(ce)001:11960: don la ma reg pa'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:11961: 'o na gnas lugs ji bzhin pa'i don de ji lta bu zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:11962: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs gdod nas skye ba
NK095(ce)001:11963: med cing spros pa'i mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11964: don dam byang chub sems kyi chos nyid nor ba
NK095(ce)001:11965: med pas legs pa'am yang dag pa'i ye shes ni
NK095(ce)001:11966: rgyu rkyen gzhan la ltos pa med par 'dus ma
NK095(ce)001:11967: byas pa'i ngo bor rang gsal du 'byung ba ste
NK095(ce)001:11968: / des na rang rig pa'i mngon sum mam so
NK095(ce)001:11969: so rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi spyod yul tsam
NK095(ce)001:11970: las theg pa 'og ma ltar phyi nang gi chos
NK095(ce)001:11971: kun la de dang der rtog cing cha med gnyis
NK095(ce)001:11972: sogs brtags par mi byed pas rnam par mi rtog
NK095(ce)001:11973: pa'i rang bzhin chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su
NK095(ce)001:11974: / gyur pas / chos dbyings yangs pa chen po spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i bdag nyid /
NK095(ce)001:11975: kun gyi dngos gzhi dam par gyur pas snying po byang chub kyi rang bzhin yin la /
NK095(ce)001:11976: de la las dang nyon mongs sogs ma grub par
NK095(ce)001:11977: gdod nas rnam par dag pas ma bgrod ye nas
NK095(ce)001:11978: phyin pa'i 'khor 'das yongs kyi spyi lam chen po
NK095(ce)001:11979: der zhugs nas zhes ye nas de'i ngang las 'da'
NK095(ce)001:11980: ba med pa'i rang bzhin du shes na chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:11981: mnyam pa'i rgyal po kun byed chos sku'i dgongs pa
NK095(ce)001:11982: ji bzhin pa mngon du thob par 'gyur ro zhes
NK095(ce)001:11983: so // de ltar yang mdo bcu las /
NK095(ce)001:11984: kun dang mi mthun spang ba'i chos //
NK095(ce)001:11985: nyon mongs lnga dang mtshams med lnga //
NK095(ce)001:11986: de ni rnam dag chen po ste //
NK095(ce)001:11987: gar bzhugs mnyam pa'i rgyal po thob //
NK095(ce)001:11990: byang chub kyi sems ni gong du bshad pa de
NK095(ce)001:11991: ltar 'dus byas skad cig ma'i chos su ma grub
NK095(ce)001:11992: par rang byung 'dus ma byas pa'i ngo bo yin
NK095(ce)001:11993: pas rang gi ngo bo mi 'gyur ba'i phyir dang
NK095(ce)001:11994: / snying po byang chub kyi rang bzhin du ye
NK095(ce)001:11995: nas sangs rgyas pa'i phyir na da gsar du sgom
NK095(ce)001:11996: sgrub rtsol ba la brten nas sngar bas lhag pa'i
NK095(ce)001:11997: gnas 'gyur te 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:11998: thob pa med pas rgyu rkyen gyis 'gyur ba med
NK095(ce)001:11999: / la / de med pas de ltar thob par
NK095(ce)001:12000: smon pa'i re 'dod kyis chags pa'i gnas kyang med
NK095(ce)001:12001: de de'i yul du ma gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:12002: de bzhina du gzung zhing rtogs par bya ba'i yul
NK095(ce)001:12003: chos kyi dbyings zhes pa'ang gzhan du med cing thob
NK095(ce)001:12004: par bya ba sems kyi gnas lugs chos sku'i go
NK095(ce)001:12005: 'phang nyid kyang rang byung gi ye shes de las
NK095(ce)001:12007: mtshan nyid byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ba rnams
NK095(ce)001:12008: kyis yul chos kyi dbyings de yul can bdag med
NK095(ce)001:12009: gnyis rtogs kyi ye shes kyis mngona sum du mthong
NK095(ce)001:12010: ba'i sgo nas sa bcu rim gyis bgrod de 'bras
NK095(ce)001:12011: bu sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang zhig gsar du thob
NK095(ce)001:12012: par 'dod nas / de'i rgyu bdag med pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:12013: la rtag tu bsgom par byeed pa ni sgom pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12014: ro la chagsa zhing bde ba thob par 'dod pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12015: re smon dang ma bral bas /
NK095(ce)001:12016: de lta bu'i gang zag de la 'khor 'das mnyam
NK095(ce)001:12017: nyid du rtogs pa'i don mi 'byung bar gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:12019: sa bcu mtha' phyin pa nyid de 'dzin de rtog pas //
NK095(ce)001:12020: de la'ang mi gnas gnas pa'i gnas dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:12021: lam med lam du 'dod pas 'gro ba 'khrul //
NK095(ce)001:12022: 'bras bu thob re 'jigs pas don mi mthong //
NK095(ce)001:12023: yang dag mtha' la bsnyeg pas yul dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:12024: de bzhin dbyings su 'dod pas bde mi rnyed //
NK095(ce)001:12025: 'dod yon nyon mongs spangs bas byang mi chub //
NK095(ce)001:12026: 'khor ba rgyab phyogs mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //sa dang pha rol phyin lam zad mtha' med //
NK095(ce)001:12029: sngags kyi theg pa phyi rgyud sde gsum las kri
NK095(ce)001:12030: ya bas bdag dang lha ye shes pa gnyis la
NK095(ce)001:12031: bzang ngan tha dad du bltas nas rje khol gyi
NK095(ce)001:12032: tshul du bsgoms pas 'bras bu lha la brten nas
NK095(ce)001:12034: chos sku thig le nyag gcig rig pa byang chub
NK095(ce)001:12035: sems kyis 'khor 'das kyi chos kun la bzang ngan
NK095(ce)001:12036: blang dor med par mnyam nyid du khyab cing 'pho
NK095(ce)001:12037: 'gyur med par gnas pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:12038: de las gzhan pa'i lha ye shes pa zhig gis
NK095(ce)001:12039: mchog thun gyi dngos grub lhag pa zhig stsol zhing
NK095(ce)001:12040: bsnan pa'i chos gang yang med de /
NK095(ce)001:12042: dngos grub ka dag ye gsal blo 'das te //
NK095(ce)001:12043: dngos med bsam bral rang la grub pa las //
NK095(ce)001:12044: lha yis gnang zhing gzhan nas theb pa med //
NK095(ce)001:12046: des na chos nyid byang chub kyi sems nam mkha'i
NK095(ce)001:12047: khams ltar mtha' la thug cing zad pa med pas
NK095(ce)001:12048: 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab cing thams cad de'i
NK095(ce)001:12049: klong las 'da' ba med phyir 'bras bu sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:12050: kyi sa la gzhan du bgrod par 'dod pas sgom
NK095(ce)001:12051: sgrub rtsol ba la ci tsam 'bad par byas kyang
NK095(ce)001:12052: chos dbyings byang chub kyi sems la ma dag 'khrul
NK095(ce)001:12053: pa'i cha bri zhing zad pa dang sngar bas lhag
NK095(ce)001:12054: pa'i yon tan zhig 'phel zhing gang ba med pas
NK095(ce)001:12055: rdzogs chen bya rtsol dang bral ba'i lam las gzhan
NK095(ce)001:12058: chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK095(ce)001:12059: bgrod pas phyin par 'dod pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:12060: khyung chen nam mkha'i mtha' tshol 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:12062: mdongs bas nam mkha' bsnyegs pa 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:12063: sa dang lam la bgrod byed pa //
NK095(ce)001:12064: bya bral don dang mthun pa med //
NK095(ce)001:12067: u pa yas lta ba yo ga dang spyod pa
NK095(ce)001:12068: kri ya dang mthun par gnyis bcas kyi lam la
NK095(ce)001:12069: brten te lta ba chos kyi dbyings mtha' thams cad
NK095(ce)001:12070: bral ba'i rol ba dag pa lha'i rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:12071: bsgom pas ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams khyad par du
NK095(ce)001:12072: phag pa'am 'phags pa'i sgo nas 'bras bu rigs bzhi
NK095(ce)001:12073: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i go 'phang thob par 'dod pa
NK095(ce)001:12074: de yang / sngar bas lhag pa'i gnas sam sangs
NK095(ce)001:12075: rgyas kyi sa gzhan zhig la phyin pa med de
NK095(ce)001:12076: de yang / / sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:12077: shes ye nas che ba lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:12078: pas khyad par du 'phags pa'i yul la sems can
NK095(ce)001:12079: nas sangs rgyas kyi bar kun tu khyad par rdul
NK095(ce)001:12080: tsam med par ye ji bzhin du gnas pa'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:12081: de yang / / te / rgyal tshab chen pos /
NK095(ce)001:12082: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:12083: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK095(ce)001:12086: rnal 'byor yo ga bas don dam mtshan ma med
NK095(ce)001:12087: pa'i rtsal snang kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil
NK095(ce)001:12088: 'khor ram rigs lnga stug po bkod pa'i zhing ngo
NK095(ce)001:12089: matshara rmad du byung ba zhig mthong bar re ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12090: blos bdag dam tshig sems dpa' la lha ye shes
NK095(ce)001:12091: sems dpa' chu la chu bzhag pa ltar dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:12092: du bstim zhing bsgom pa'i rtsol ba byed pa de
NK095(ce)001:12093: yang / rdzogs pa chen pos bsgom bya'i yul lha
NK095(ce)001:12094: dang yul can sgom byed kyi blo gnyis su med
NK095(ce)001:12095: par byang chub kyi sems gcig gi rang bzhin las
NK095(ce)001:12096: gzhan du med par rtogs pas ci yang mi bsgom
NK095(ce)001:12097: yang / zhing / byang chub kyi sems de la
NK095(ce)001:12098: spros pa'i mtshan ma gang yang mi dmigs pas ya
NK095(ce)001:12099: mtshan chen po'i 'bras bu gsar du mthong ba yang
NK095(ce)001:12101: de ltar gang yang ma mthong ba de ni mthong
NK095(ce)001:12102: ba'i dam pa yin pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i mig
NK095(ce)001:12103: gam spyan yin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:12105: thogs pa med pa'i ye shes ni //
NK095(ce)001:12106: bsam pa kun dang bral ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:12107: ngang gis mi g.yo rmug pa de //
NK095(ce)001:12108: ting 'dzin dag gi rgyal por gnas //
NK095(ce)001:12109: ting 'dzin ye shes mngon sum spyan //
NK095(ce)001:12110: mthong bas dmigs pa'i yul dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:12111: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan zhes bya //
NK095(ce)001:12113: de lta bu'i mthong bya mthong byed dang bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12114: gnas lugs rang byung gi ye shes de yul med
NK095(ce)001:12115: rang gsal gyi ngo bo ye nas gnas pa gang
NK095(ce)001:12117: ston pa po gang dag gi gsung la brten nas thos par mi rigs te /
NK095(ce)001:12118: ci'i phyir na tshig gis brnyad pa kun dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:12119: des na byang chub kyi sems smra bsam brjod pa
NK095(ce)001:12120: dang bral ba de la mtshan nyid sgyu mar snang
NK095(ce)001:12121: ba kun rdzob kyi chos dang mtshan nyid kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:12122: gang yang grub pa min pa don dam stong pa
NK095(ce)001:12123: nyid gnyis tha dad du grub pa med pas zhes
NK095(ce)001:12124: sam chos dge ba dang chos min mi dge ba
NK095(ce)001:12125: la sogs pa'i gnyis chos thams cad gnyis med mnyam
NK095(ce)001:12126: pa nyid du rtag tu 'dres shing dbyer med pas
NK095(ce)001:12128: rnal 'byor yo ga ba'i 'dod pa ltar don dam
NK095(ce)001:12129: mtshan ma med pa'i chos shes bya ba kun rdzob
NK095(ce)001:12130: sgyu ma lta bas snang ba 'di las lhag par
NK095(ce)001:12131: gyur pa'i rtogs bya'i gnas shes bya ba zhig don
NK095(ce)001:12132: la grub pa lta ci tshig gis bshad pa tsam
NK095(ce)001:12135: ston pa'i lung gi tshig rnams la //
NK095(ce)001:12136: lam du de mthong 'jug pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:12137: rtogs pa'i lam zhugs smig rgyur bsnyegs //
NK095(ce)001:12138: yang dag lam ni 'di yin zhes //
NK095(ce)001:12139: tshig dang yi ges mtshon du med //
NK095(ce)001:12140: yang dag 'di yin ston pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:12141: rdo rje sems dpa' nga nyid 'khrul //
NK095(ce)001:12142: dag pa dang ni ma dag pa //
NK095(ce)001:12143: ye nas gnyis med 'dres shing mtshungs //
NK095(ce)001:12144: sems nyid kun gyi gnas su'o //
NK095(ce)001:12147: 'di ltar ma h+aa yo ga'i lam nas kun rdzob
NK095(ce)001:12148: 'khrul pa'i snang ba tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa
NK095(ce)001:12150: de'i gnyen por phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dag pa
NK095(ce)001:12151: gzhal yas khang dang nang bcud kyi sems can dag
NK095(ce)001:12152: pa gdan gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom te byang
NK095(ce)001:12153: chub kyi lam bsgrub par byed pa de yang blo
NK095(ce)001:12154: rnam par rtog pa'i sgom pa yin pas rtog med
NK095(ce)001:12155: mnyam pa nyid kyi 'bras bu ni des kyang thob
NK095(ce)001:12156: pa'ang med de / ci'i phyir na rtogs bya chos
NK095(ce)001:12157: kyi dbyings smra bsam brjod pa kun dang bral bar
NK095(ce)001:12158: ma zad rtogs byed rang byung gi ye shes nyid
NK095(ce)001:12159: kyang blos bsam pa dang tshig gi lam nas brjod
NK095(ce)001:12160: pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral zhing yul yul can
NK095(ce)001:12161: gnyis su med par bdag nyid chen por ye nas
NK095(ce)001:12162: sangsa rgyas pa'i bdag nyid du 'gro ba kun la
NK095(ce)001:12163: rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyi yul du gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:12164: pa'ang med de / la / dper na grib ma
NK095(ce)001:12165: la gzugs dngos su 'khrul pa'i rtog pa byung ba
NK095(ce)001:12166: de don dang mi mthun pas gzugs kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:12167: du bzung du med pa'i dpe bzhin du rtog med
NK095(ce)001:12168: mnyam pa chen po rtsol med rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:12169: shes de la rtsol sgrub kyi rtog pa byung ba
NK095(ce)001:12170: ni byar med rdzogs chen gyi don dang mi mthun
NK095(ce)001:12171: pa'ang med de / la / pa'i phyir te / de nyid las /
NK095(ce)001:12172: 'khrul par gyur pa'i byang chub lam de ni //
NK095(ce)001:12173: rtogs par gyur pas 'bras bu thob pa med //
NK095(ce)001:12174: rang byung rgyu rkyen ma bskyed sems nyid kyang //
NK095(ce)001:12175: tshig gi brjod pas mi pheb mtha' dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:12176: ye nas bya btsal bral bas bdag nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:12177: rang rig mngon sum ngang gis btsal med gnas phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:12178: grib ma las byung gzugs kyi dpe bzhin du //
NK095(ce)001:12179: mi rtog ye shes de las rtog pa 'byung bar zad //
NK095(ce)001:12182: da yang 'dus pa'i snying po nyon //
NK095(ce)001:12183: de don lam gyi rim pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:12184: thabs dang shes rab sgor zhugs nas //
NK095(ce)001:12185: ting 'dzin gsum gyi lha bsgoms pas //
NK095(ce)001:12186: grib ma gzugs su bsgyur ba 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:12189: 'di ltar snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:12190: ye nas yod ma myong ba gzhi meda rtsa bral
NK095(ce)001:12192: de nyid ci yang meda pa phyangs chad pa lta
NK095(ce)001:12193: bu yang ma yin par med pa'i snying po snang
NK095(ce)001:12194: ba 'gag med du 'byung ba'am 'char du yang yod
NK095(ce)001:12195: la / de ltar 'char bzhin pa'i dus na yang
NK095(ce)001:12196: snying po rang byung gi ye shes kyi rtsal rang
NK095(ce)001:12197: byung ba tsam las ma dag mtshan ma'i chos su
NK095(ce)001:12198: grub pa med pas stong pa nyid du gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:12200: 'khor 'das tshig las 'das pa'i ye shes ni //
NK095(ce)001:12201: dbyibs dang kha dog dbang po'i spyod yul du //
NK095(ce)001:12202: sangs rgyas nyid kyis bstan cing mtshon du med //
NK095(ce)001:12203: mtshon cing brtags par dka' ba'i rang sems don //
NK095(ce)001:12204: yod med dbus las 'das pa'i byang chub de //
NK095(ce)001:12205: dngos med yid la dran pa'i ye shes ni //
NK095(ce)001:12206: kun bzang nyid kyis mi gzigs blta ba'i mchog /ces gsungs pa ltar yin la /
NK095(ce)001:12207: 'on kyang stong pa nyi tshe ba tsam ma yin
NK095(ce)001:12208: par snang stong 'du 'bral med pas smra brjod spros
NK095(ce)001:12209: pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i yul la ye
NK095(ce)001:12210: nas gnas pas ngo bo ngos bzung dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:12211: nam mkha'i rang bzhin lta bu de la /
NK095(ce)001:12212: rjes su rnal 'byor a nu yo ga ba rnams
NK095(ce)001:12213: kyis rjes chags kyi lam la brten nas bde stong
NK095(ce)001:12214: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyid da gdod 'byung
NK095(ce)001:12215: bar re ba'i dran pa'am 'dun pa skye ba ni
NK095(ce)001:12216: / bya rtsol thams cad dang bral bar ye nas
NK095(ce)001:12217: grub zin pa'i chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:12218: zug rngu'i tshor ba gang yang med pas bde ba
NK095(ce)001:12219: chen po'i ngo bor gyur pa de ni thob 'dod
NK095(ce)001:12220: kyi 'dun pa dang rtsol ba la ltos pa med
NK095(ce)001:12221: par ye nas 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:12222: gnas pas da dung yang nas yang du len du
NK095(ce)001:12223: / med bzhin du / gza' gtad thams cad dang
NK095(ce)001:12224: bral ba'i rang bzhin gzung 'dzin rtog pa'i spyod yul
NK095(ce)001:12225: du med pa de la bde ba chen po'i ye
NK095(ce)001:12226: shes gsar du 'byung ba yi ched du brtsom pa
NK095(ce)001:12227: yin pas rtsol sgrub phra ba las ma 'das pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12228: phyir na a ti rdzogs pa chen po la ltos
NK095(ce)001:12229: na theg pa dman pa'i nang du gtogs zhing /
NK095(ce)001:12230: de lta bu'i theg pa 'og ma thams cad bya
NK095(ce)001:12231: bral rdzogs pa chen po'i lta bas zil gyis gnon
NK095(ce)001:12234: theg pa'i yang rtse a ti klong chen po //
NK095(ce)001:12235: ri rgyal lta bur kun gyi rtser gyur pas //
NK095(ce)001:12236: ri phran thams cad 'og tu non pa ltar //
NK095(ce)001:12237: lta sgom theg pa kun gyi rtser gyur pas //
NK095(ce)001:12238: a nu phyi nang kun bzang mkha' rol rnams //
NK095(ce)001:12239: a ti chen po kun bzang yangs pa'i klong //
NK095(ce)001:12240: rang skad ston pas theg dman klong du thim //
NK095(ce)001:12241: dper na rtsal gsum ldan pa'i seng ge yis //
NK095(ce)001:12242: wa sogs gcan gzan zil gyis gnon pa ltar //
NK095(ce)001:12243: a ti rang rtsal rig pa yul med shar //
NK095(ce)001:12244: mtshan ma rang grol klong yangs phyam brdal bas //
NK095(ce)001:12245: a nu la sogs theg pa phyogs zhen can //
NK095(ce)001:12246: yul dang yul can 'dod kun klong du grol //
NK095(ce)001:12247: de bzhin rig pa ti la mtha' bral klong //
NK095(ce)001:12248: bya bral lhun grub rdzogs chen shar grol la //
NK095(ce)001:12249: grol dang ma grol gnyis med rgyan du che //
NK095(ce)001:12250: dper na 'dab chags rgyal po khyung chen de //
NK095(ce)001:12251: mngal na gnas kyang klu rnams zil gyis gnon //
NK095(ce)001:12252: sgong nga'i nang du 'dab gshog tshad du phyin //
NK095(ce)001:12253: sgong rgya ral nas spyi rgya rlabs kyis chod //
NK095(ce)001:12254: 'dab chags gzhan la ci ste ga la rigs //
NK095(ce)001:12255: khyung chen rang la rigs te mkha' la bde //
NK095(ce)001:12256: a ti chen po klong chen brdal khyab pa //
NK095(ce)001:12257: rang skad ston cing theg dgu zil gyis gnon //
NK095(ce)001:12258: kun bzang klong du sa lam sbyang bgrod grol //
NK095(ce)001:12259: 'khor ba'i klong na lus rgya ma bral kyang //
NK095(ce)001:12260: gol sa g.yang chod ka dag klong na yan //
NK095(ce)001:12262: gnyis pa de thams cad rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i nad kyis gdung ba la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:12263: ji srid lam du 'dzin pa thams cad chags zhen du bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12264: ji tsam 'bad pa 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras su bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:12265: med snang 'khrul pa'i rang bzhin lam brgyad kyis mi rtogs pa'i dape'o //
NK095(ce)001:12267: de ltar theg rim brgyad po rnams las gang yin
NK095(ce)001:12268: kyang rang gnas snying po'i ye shes bsal bzhag dang
NK095(ce)001:12269: bral ba ma rtogs par ma zad sngon gyi drang
NK095(ce)001:12270: srong chen po sangs rgyas rnams kyi rjes su ting
NK095(ce)001:12271: nge 'dzin bsgom pa sogs lam la slob pa'i sgo
NK095(ce)001:12272: nas 'bras bu sngon med gsar byung zhig thob par
NK095(ce)001:12273: 'dod pa'i chags pa'i yid kyang 'jog par byed pa
NK095(ce)001:12274: ni / de 'dra'i rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub kyi lam
NK095(ce)001:12275: la rnam par rtsol ba dang 'bad pa'i gdung bas
NK095(ce)001:12276: dus rnams kun tu zin par 'gyur ta re zhes
NK095(ce)001:12277: 'gyur ba'i nyen yod pas rgyu 'bras bya rtsol bral
NK095(ce)001:12278: ba'i rang bzhin ma rtogs par de lta bu'i rgyu
NK095(ce)001:12279: 'bras blang dor la zhen pa'i theg pa brgyad kyi
NK095(ce)001:12280: lam der zhugs pas 'bras bu thams cada mkhyen pa
NK095(ce)001:12281: yi go 'phang thob tu med par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:12282: rus sbal rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:12283: 'di tshol rnams kyis gzhan nas 'di ma btsal //
NK095(ce)001:12284: rang la gnas shing gzhan nas 'di tshol na //
NK095(ce)001:12285: bskal pa gsum du 'di btsal rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:12286: gang zhig sangs rgyas rnams kyis 'di ma btsal //
NK095(ce)001:12287: de bzhin sems can 'di tshol btsal mi rnyed //
NK095(ce)001:12288: mi tshol ngo bo nyid du thams cad gnas //
NK095(ce)001:12289: rtsol grub lam la gnas pa'i gang zag rnams //
NK095(ce)001:12290: dngul la gser zhun byas kyang gser mi btub //
NK095(ce)001:12291: mtshon pa tshig tu ston pa lam las nyams //
NK095(ce)001:12292: rdzogs chen 'di yi don du ga la 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:12295: der ma zad yod med rtag chad la sogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12296: spros pa thams cad bral ba'i gnas lugs ye ji
NK095(ce)001:12297: bzhin pa ni 'di lta bu yin no zhes dmigs
NK095(ce)001:12298: gtad thams cad dang bral ba zhig la blo rten
NK095(ce)001:12299: 'chang bar byed cing bsgom na yang de yang blang
NK095(ce)001:12300: dor re dogs kyi rnam rtog phra mo bsgom pa
NK095(ce)001:12301: yin pa de yi phyir na slar yang rnam rtog
NK095(ce)001:12302: phyir phyir 'phel zhing rang gis rang nyid 'ching bar
NK095(ce)001:12303: byed pa las rdzogs chen a ti yo ga'i ma
NK095(ce)001:12304: bcos gnyug ma'i bsgom pa min par bde ba chen
NK095(ce)001:12305: po chos sku'i dgongs pa mngon du thob par 'dod
NK095(ce)001:12306: pa'i re smon dang bcas pas chags pa'i gcong snying
NK095(ce)001:12307: chen po'i nad kyis zin pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:12309: btsal du med pas bsgom pa'i tshig dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:12310: tshig las 'das pas brjod pa'i tha snyad med //
NK095(ce)001:12311: ye sangs rgyas pas blta ba'i dmigs med de //
NK095(ce)001:12312: snying po byang chub dgongs su med pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:12313: rnal 'byor blta dmigs tshol ba don las nyams //
NK095(ce)001:12314: mi blta mi tshol don de nyid yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:12315: don la mi blta bltar med 'khrul pa med //
NK095(ce)001:12316: bde ba chen po gang zhig tshol ba 'khrul //
NK095(ce)001:12317: zhes gsungs pa lta bu yin pa des na re
NK095(ce)001:12318: smon chags pa'i nad de nyid kyi gnyen por ka
NK095(ce)001:12319: dag kun tu bzang po'i dgongs klong chos nyid yangs
NK095(ce)001:12320: pa chen po'i mkha' dbyings su 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:12321: thams cad gzhi med rtsa bral gyi rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:12322: gdod nas grol zin pa las nam yang mi g.yo
NK095(ce)001:12323: bar mnyam nyid blang dor med par gnas pas re
NK095(ce)001:12324: dogs 'bad rtsol ci yang mi dgos pa'i rang babs
NK095(ce)001:12325: gnyug ma'i bsam gtan gyi sman chen pos gso bar
NK095(ce)001:12326: ma byas na / dmigs gtad can gyi lam des
NK095(ce)001:12327: bsam gzugs kyi gnas su 'phen pa tsam las med
NK095(ce)001:12328: pas mtho ris kyi gnas su bgrod par byed pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12329: rgyu blang dor dang 'dzin zhen can gyi lam des
NK095(ce)001:12330: nyon mongs pa'i nad kyis zin par 'gyur ba las
NK095(ce)001:12333: des na byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin spros pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12334: grwa zur dang bral bas smra bsam brjod las 'das
NK095(ce)001:12335: pa la lam gyis bgrod du med pa yin bzhin
NK095(ce)001:12336: theg brgyad kyi lam du zhugs pa rnams kyi nang
NK095(ce)001:12337: du che ba re dogs 'bad rtsol gyi lam des
NK095(ce)001:12338: 'bras bu myang 'das kyi sar phyin par 'dod pa
NK095(ce)001:12339: ni gang yang grub pa med pas dper na ri
NK095(ce)001:12340: dwags skom gyis gdung bas smig rgyu la chu ru
NK095(ce)001:12341: 'khrul nas de'i rjes su bsnyegs pa dang 'dra bar
NK095(ce)001:12342: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang zhig gzhan nas
NK095(ce)001:12343: rnyed pa'i yul med pas 'jig rten gsum du gnas
NK095(ce)001:12344: shing 'khor ba'i 'dams su tshud pa las mya ngan
NK095(ce)001:12345: las 'das pa'i sar mi 'byung zhing sa bcu rim
NK095(ce)001:12346: par bgrod pa la ltos bca' bar byed pa'i gnas
NK095(ce)001:12347: kyang byang chub chen po bgrod du med pa'i gnas
NK095(ce)001:12348: mi mthong bar byed pa'i sgrib pa yin par bstan
NK095(ce)001:12350: lam med lam du 'jug pas lam 'di mi rnyed de //
NK095(ce)001:12351: chu gdung glang chen smig rgyu bsnyegs pa'ang //
NK095(ce)001:12352: bskal par bgrod kyang snyed par rab tu dka' //zhes dang /
NK095(ce)001:12354: de bas bgrod lam med des phyin pa med pas na //
NK095(ce)001:12355: lam de gang zag rnams kyi nad du che bas na //
NK095(ce)001:12356: de nyid mya ngan 'das sar phyin par 'dod pa des //
NK095(ce)001:12357: ri dwags smig rgyu chu ru 'du shes bsnyegs pa 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:12358: de bas gang yang rnyed par 'gyur ba'i yul med de //
NK095(ce)001:12359: de bzhin gang ltar bgrod kyang khams gsum de las yongs mi 'byung //
NK095(ce)001:12360: sa bcu gong nas gong du ltos pa'i rten bcas kyang //
NK095(ce)001:12361: byang chub chen po dag la sgrib par 'gyur ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:12363: gnyis pa sems nyid a ti'i dgongs pa ye nas rang la gnas tshul bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:12364: gzhi lhun gyis grub pas nor bu ltar yon tan gzhan nas btsal du med pa /
NK095(ce)001:12365: btang bzhag med pa'i don rang gi rig pas dge ba'i bshes gnyen du shar ba /
NK095(ce)001:12366: de'i ngang las mi g.yo ba brjod med chos sku'i ngo bo ye nas rang la gnas pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:12368: 'di ltar rdzogs pa chen po'i lam du rang byung
NK095(ce)001:12369: gi ye shes nyid ma bcos thad kar rang ngo
NK095(ce)001:12370: sprad pa'i ngang du rang babs la bzhag pa tsam
NK095(ce)001:12371: las theg pa 'og ma lta bu'i rtsol sgrub gang
NK095(ce)001:12372: yang mi dgos par sa lam thams cad ma bgrod
NK095(ce)001:12373: ye nas non pa yin pas shin tu myur ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12375: de ni smra bsam brjod pa kun dang bral ba'i gnas lugs /
NK095(ce)001:12376: ma bcos lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes /
NK095(ce)001:12377: ma bsgom ngang gis gnas pa'i ting 'dzin /
NK095(ce)001:12378: gdod nas 'char nub bral ba'i rig pa /
NK095(ce)001:12379: ma sbyangs ye nas dag pa'i chos sku ye grol
NK095(ce)001:12380: gyi dgongs pa gang zhig /mtha' yas pa'i 'gro ba
NK095(ce)001:12381: ma lus pa dmigs med brtse ba'i thugs rjes skyongs
NK095(ce)001:12382: zhing phan bde'i legs tshogs thams cad kyi 'byung gnas
NK095(ce)001:12383: su gyur cing gsang chen a ti yo ga'i dgongs
NK095(ce)001:12384: pa ma nor ba mngon sum du ston par mdzad
NK095(ce)001:12385: pa po rig 'dzin dga' rab rdo rje dang rgyal
NK095(ce)001:12386: dbang pad+ma ka r+aa la sogs pa bshes gnyen dam
NK095(ce)001:12387: pa kun gyi thugs 'od gsal chos sku'i rgya mtsho
NK095(ce)001:12388: chen po las 'byung ba'i nor bu rin chen thams
NK095(ce)001:12389: cad kyi nang nas khyad par 'phags pa 'dod 'byung
NK095(ce)001:12390: yid bzhin dbang gi rgyal po ji lta ba bzhin
NK095(ce)001:12391: du sems rnam rtog gis dmigs pa dang zhen pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12392: dri ma med cing lam sbyang bgrod sogs kyis je
NK095(ce)001:12393: bzang du 'gyur ba'i gnas la mi ltos par rig
NK095(ce)001:12394: pa rang byung gi ye shes rang gi rang bzhina
NK095(ce)001:12395: la legs pa'i yon tan thams cad ye nas gzhi
NK095(ce)001:12396: rdzogs lhun gyis grub pas rgyu rkyen gzhan la mi
NK095(ce)001:12397: ltos par rig pa rang la shar bas re ba
NK095(ce)001:12398: thams cad yid bzhin du skong ba yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:12399: de lta bu'i man ngag zab mo ston pa'i bshes
NK095(ce)001:12400: gnyen dam pa gtsug gi nor bu ltar brten par
NK095(ce)001:12402: de phyir bshes gnyen yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas te //
NK095(ce)001:12403: nor bu rin chen bzhin du spyi bo'i gtsug tu bkur //
NK095(ce)001:12406: snying po byang chub kyi sems ni brtags shing dpyad
NK095(ce)001:12407: na spros pa'i mtha' gang du'ang grub pa med pas
NK095(ce)001:12408: ye stong spros pa dang bral ba nam mkha'i dbyings
NK095(ce)001:12410: ma brtags rang babs su bzhag na rang byung ye
NK095(ce)001:12411: shes chen po'i rang zhal dbyings na sgrib med du
NK095(ce)001:12412: gsal bas legsa pa'i yon tan ma lus pa rtsol
NK095(ce)001:12413: med lhun grub tu 'byung ba yin pas rgya che
NK095(ce)001:12414: ba'am che ba'i yon tan dang ldan pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:12415: de nyid dngos po mtshan ma'i chos su ma grub
NK095(ce)001:12416: cing rtog pa'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas ngo
NK095(ce)001:12417: bo cir yang mi snang bzhin du gdul bya yal
NK095(ce)001:12418: bar mi 'dor bar thugs rjes rjes su chags pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12419: cha lugs 'char ba ltar rtsal snang 'gags med du
NK095(ce)001:12420: shar ba'i snang ba thams cad brda bral rang grol
NK095(ce)001:12421: gyi man ngag gis bcos bsgyur spang blang med par
NK095(ce)001:12422: shar grol ris med kyi dgongs pa kun la ston
NK095(ce)001:12423: cing a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i snod du gyur
NK095(ce)001:12424: pa'i yang rab skal ba dang ldan pa rnams kyis
NK095(ce)001:12425: de bzhin du rtogs par yang 'gyur la /
NK095(ce)001:12426: gzhan rnams kyis ji bzhin ma rtogs kyang yongs kyi rgyud la sbas pa med par ston te /
NK095(ce)001:12428: rnam par mi rtog ye shes snying po 'di //
NK095(ce)001:12429: theg pa yongs kyi chos la sbas pa med //
NK095(ce)001:12430: sangs rgyas gsung gi rgyud la sbas pa med //
NK095(ce)001:12431: bgrod rtsol lam la sbyangs bas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:12432: mi len mi spang byang chub spyod rnams la //
NK095(ce)001:12433: rnam pa kun tu rang bzhin ji bzhin gnas //
NK095(ce)001:12435: de ltar bdag dang gzhan du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa
NK095(ce)001:12436: kun dang bral ba'i bdag nyid can 'khor 'das kyi
NK095(ce)001:12437: snang cha mu med par snang ba thams cad rig
NK095(ce)001:12438: pa'i rang mdangs kho na yin pas rang byung ye
NK095(ce)001:12439: shes kyi snang ba kun la ston par mdzad pas
NK095(ce)001:12440: ston mkhan dge ba'i bshes gnyen du shar ba'i kun
NK095(ce)001:12441: byed rgyal po de ni gsang sngags kun gyi gter
NK095(ce)001:12442: du gyur pas nor bu rin chen gyi mdzod lta
NK095(ce)001:12443: bu des blang dor 'bad rtsol la mi ltos par
NK095(ce)001:12444: rang gzhan gyi don thams cad ma btsal lhun gyis
NK095(ce)001:12445: grub pa'i yul la gdod nas gnas pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:12446: zhes theg mchog a ti'i dgongs pa 'gro ba kun
NK095(ce)001:12447: la bdag 'dzin gyi dmigs pa med pa'i snying rjes
NK095(ce)001:12448: sam rang bzhin byin gyi rlabs kyis bstan par mdzad
NK095(ce)001:12450: ma nor nges pa'i slob dpon ni //
NK095(ce)001:12451: rang sems bla ma rin po che //
NK095(ce)001:12452: byin rlabs brgyud pa kun gyi bdag /rang grol man ngag byin rlabs ston //
NK095(ce)001:12455: de lta bu'i rig pa byang chub kyi sems ji
NK095(ce)001:12456: bzhin rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams nang nas te
NK095(ce)001:12457: nang gnas snying po'i ye shes las skad cig tsam
NK095(ce)001:12458: yang ma g.yos kyang dmigs pa nang du bsdus nas
NK095(ce)001:12459: gnas lugs zab mo'i ngo bo 'di lta bu'o zhes
NK095(ce)001:12460: btsal ba'i gnas dang btsal byed kyi rtog pa yang
NK095(ce)001:12461: med de gza' gtad kyi blo dang bral ba'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:12462: ro // de bzhin du yul sems can rnams sdug
NK095(ce)001:12463: bsngal las skyabs pa'i phyir du dmigs pa med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12464: thugs rjes 'gro la rjes su chags pa ltar yang
NK095(ce)001:12465: ro // snang la / yul de la bsngo ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12466: dmigs pa'am zhen cing 'dzin pa med pas yul la
NK095(ce)001:12467: rnam par rtog pa mi 'byung zhing mnyam nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:12468: don la ched du mi 'jug pas bdag tu dmigs
NK095(ce)001:12469: pa med pa'i snying rje chen po spro bsdu dang
NK095(ce)001:12470: bral ba de yis ni rang gi rang zhal ston
NK095(ce)001:12471: pa las gzhan gyi dngos nor ston pa lta bu
NK095(ce)001:12472: min pas rang gnas snying po'i ye shes de ni
NK095(ce)001:12473: sngon med gsar du mi 'ong bar ye nas rang
NK095(ce)001:12474: la gnas pa'i chos nyid 'pho 'gyur med pa yin
NK095(ce)001:12475: ro // snang la / te / khyung chen las /
NK095(ce)001:12476: rang rig byang chub sems nyid sangs rgyas sku //
NK095(ce)001:12477: gzhan gyi nor min ye nas gnas pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:12479: gsum pa theg pa brgyad a tir 'jug thabs la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:12480: theg brgyad rang lam gyi ngo bo rnal don mthar thug ma yin pas 'jug dgos pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12483: 'di ltar rtsol bcas kyi theg pa brgyad pos rang
NK095(ce)001:12484: lam gyi 'bras bu dgra bcom nas brdal ba chos
NK095(ce)001:12485: nyid kyi sa'i bar gyi mthar 'bras kyi bde ba
NK095(ce)001:12486: thob par 'dod nas rtsol bar byas na 'gyur med
NK095(ce)001:12487: bde ba chen po 'od gsal gnyug ma'i ye shes
NK095(ce)001:12488: nas rang la gnas pa'i kun bzang dbye ba med
NK095(ce)001:12489: pa'am rdzogs pa spyir chib chen po'i sa la rgyab
NK095(ce)001:12491: ci'i phyir na de lta bu'i chos sku lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:12492: chen po ye bde 'pho 'gyur dang bral bas sngar
NK095(ce)001:12493: nas zin yod pa'i don de bor ba'am de 'dra'i
NK095(ce)001:12494: bde bas blo ma tshim nas sngon med gsar byung
NK095(ce)001:12495: gi bde ba zhig tshol ba de ni 'bras bu
NK095(ce)001:12496: byang chub kyi bde ba gzhan thob 'dod kyi 'khrul
NK095(ce)001:12497: pa yi dbang du song ba yin pas gdod nas
NK095(ce)001:12498: ye sangs rgyas pa'i don ma rtogs par rngam zhing
NK095(ce)001:12499: chags pas chos la dbang za ba ste /
NK095(ce)001:12500: 'di lta bu'i 'bras bu gzhan nas tshol bar 'dod
NK095(ce)001:12501: pa'i yul cana gzung 'dzin gyi blo dang ldan pa
NK095(ce)001:12502: rnams kyis ci tsam 'bad kyang 'bras bu sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:12503: nyid mthong ba med pas brjod med a ti'i lam
NK095(ce)001:12505: de'i rgyu mtshan rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'di
NK095(ce)001:12506: las ma gtogs pa'i sangs rgyas zhes pa rang mtshan
NK095(ce)001:12507: pa zhig grub pa med pas de brjod byed kyi
NK095(ce)001:12508: tshig sangs rgyas zhes pa'i ming yanga med de gdags
NK095(ce)001:12509: gzhi dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:12510: 'o na rgyal ba'i bka' las sangs rgyas kyi go
NK095(ce)001:12511: 'phang bsgrub tu yod par gsungs pa de ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:12512: yin snyam na / de ni gdul bya rnams lam
NK095(ce)001:12513: la rim gyis dkri ba'i ched du sangsa rgyas zhes
NK095(ce)001:12514: ston pas ming du btags pa drang don dgongs pa
NK095(ce)001:12515: can gyi tshig yin pa la de nyid sgra ji
NK095(ce)001:12516: bzhin du bzung na nor ba yin phyir /
NK095(ce)001:12517: de dang rjes su mthun par sangs rgyas gzhan nas
NK095(ce)001:12518: thob par 'dod nas rtsol sgrub byed pa'i lam thams
NK095(ce)001:12519: cad kyang nor ba'i lam kho na yin te /
NK095(ce)001:12520: byang chub kyi sems ni gzugsa su grub pa med
NK095(ce)001:12521: kyang ngo bo ngos bzung dang bral bas cir yang
NK095(ce)001:12522: grub pa med bzhin rtsal snang 'gag pa med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12523: cho 'phrul du 'khor 'das kyi chos kun snang yang
NK095(ce)001:12524: de ltar snang ba'i dus nyid nas mtha' brgyad spros
NK095(ce)001:12525: pa dang bral ba'i ngang las 'da' ba med pas
NK095(ce)001:12526: de lam 'bad rtsol gyis bsgrub tu yod par bshad
NK095(ce)001:12527: pa rdul tsam yang med de smra bsam brjod pa
NK095(ce)001:12528: thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK095(ce)001:12529: ye shes nam mkha'i rgyal po las /
NK095(ce)001:12530: mtshan nyid med pa'i chos nyid chen po 'di ///chos kyi dbyings su sgyu ma'i gar bsgyur kyang //
NK095(ce)001:12531: sgyu ma'i lam du rgyal bas basngagasa pa med //
NK095(ce)001:12532: mi gnas chos sku brjod med las 'das kyang //
NK095(ce)001:12533: dbu ma'ang brjod du med de don dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:12536: sangs rgyas zhes ni gzhan nas thob byed pa //
NK095(ce)001:12537: de nyid smig rgyu bzhin te nor ba'i lam //
NK095(ce)001:12538: kha dog dbyibs kyi gzugs ni yod min pas //
NK095(ce)001:12539: chos kun bshad pa rdul cha tsam yang med //
NK095(ce)001:12542: theg pa brgyad kyi dbye ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:12543: rdzogs pa chen po'i lam du 'jug pa'i rim pa
NK095(ce)001:12544: chung 'bring che gsum du bstan nas 'jug tshul lo
NK095(ce)001:12546: de la theg pa brgyad kyi lam nas sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:12547: kyi go 'phang tshol ba'i tshul yang 'di ltar a
NK095(ce)001:12548: nu yo ga bas snang srid kyi chos thams cad
NK095(ce)001:12549: ye nas dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin du grub
NK095(ce)001:12550: zin par lta ba'i lta bas tshol ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:12551: ma h+aa yo ga bas yab yum mnyam par rol
NK095(ce)001:12552: ba'i 'dod chags chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi thabs
NK095(ce)001:12554: rnal 'byor yo ga bas mtshan bcas dang mtshan med
NK095(ce)001:12555: kyi rnal 'byor la brten nas kun rdzob 'khrul ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12556: snang ba dang bral ba'i sgo nas thob par 'dod
NK095(ce)001:12557: pa dang / bya byed gnyis kyis sngags dang phyag
NK095(ce)001:12558: rgya'i ting nge 'dzin gyis ma dag las nyon gyi
NK095(ce)001:12559: cha zhi bar byed pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12560: dbu ma pas dngos po kun rdzob tu snang ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12561: chos thams cad grub pa med pa don dam spros
NK095(ce)001:12562: pa dang bral bar bsgom pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12563: nyan rang gnyis kyis mthong sgom gyi lam la brten
NK095(ce)001:12564: nas sdug kun gyi chos rnams rnam par spong bar
NK095(ce)001:12565: rtsom pa de thams cad bya rtsol bral ba'i don
NK095(ce)001:12567: ci'i phyir na 'khor ba'i gcong nad thams cad kyi
NK095(ce)001:12568: gnyen por gyur pa rig pa byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:12569: bdud rtsi bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin gyis 'khor
NK095(ce)001:12570: ba'i gcong nad kyi zug rngu'i tshor ba thams cad
NK095(ce)001:12571: ye nas bcoms zin pas khams gsum yongs grol chen
NK095(ce)001:12572: po'i dgongs par gnas pa la /
NK095(ce)001:12573: 'og ma'i theg pa de dag gis 'bad rtsol la
NK095(ce)001:12574: brten nas bza' ba'i thabs sam spong 'gog sbyong bsgyur
NK095(ce)001:12575: la sogs pa byed pa'i thabs la rag lus pa
NK095(ce)001:12577: de ltar yang klong chen rab 'byams las /
NK095(ce)001:12580: mkhas pa rnams la ye shes shar //
NK095(ce)001:12581: mi mkhas pa la mun pa snang //
NK095(ce)001:12582: 'di bor bdud rtsi gzhan na med //
NK095(ce)001:12585: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad sems nyid skye
NK095(ce)001:12586: ba med pa nam mkha' lta bu'i klong du rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:12587: shing che ba rnam pa lnga'i tshul du sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:12588: pa'i phyir yangs so che'o zhes smos pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:12589: de lta bu'i don rjen cer du ston par byed
NK095(ce)001:12590: pa'i chos rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga
NK095(ce)001:12591: 'di nyid theg pa chung ngu rnams kyi lta ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12592: 'dzin zhen thams cad sun 'byin par byed pa'i gnyen
NK095(ce)001:12593: po yin la / 'o na theg pa 'og ma'i
NK095(ce)001:12594: lta ba sun 'byin cing rdzogs chen rang gi che
NK095(ce)001:12595: ba la dmigs pa'i blo dang ma bral bas de
NK095(ce)001:12596: yang dgag sgrub blang dor gyi lam du mi 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:12597: po yin la / ram snyam na / de lta
NK095(ce)001:12598: bu'i bzang ngan che chung du dmigs pa'i blo yod
NK095(ce)001:12599: na dgag sgrub blang dor dang bcas pa yin par
NK095(ce)001:12600: shin tu bden te de nyid rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:12601: lam du yang mi 'gyur ba'i tshul /
NK095(ce)001:12603: theg brgyad thams cad khyad bsad nas //
NK095(ce)001:12604: nga ni rtsol ba bral lo zer //
NK095(ce)001:12605: phyogs zhen de yis sangs mi rgya //
NK095(ce)001:12607: theg 'og khyad bsad rang che brjod //
NK095(ce)001:12608: de yis 'di la gtan mi pheb //
NK095(ce)001:12609: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta sgom spyod //
NK095(ce)001:12610: chen po nga nyid mnyam nyid dang //
NK095(ce)001:12611: mtho dman dbye ba'i gdams gzhi bral //
NK095(ce)001:12613: des na chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi klong du
NK095(ce)001:12614: che chung mtho dman gyi cha bsnyams nas ma grub
NK095(ce)001:12615: pa'i phyir na chung ngu dang che ba de rnams
NK095(ce)001:12616: kyi dmigs pa dang bral ba yin mod /
NK095(ce)001:12617: dper na nyi ma'i mdun na mun pa gar yang
NK095(ce)001:12618: ma spangs bzhin du ngang gis mi gnas pa ltar
NK095(ce)001:12619: byar med ye grol gyi lta ba la 'og ma'i
NK095(ce)001:12620: zhen 'dzin thams cad mi spangs la ngang gis mi
NK095(ce)001:12621: gnas pas spangs pa'i tha snyad btags pa tsam las
NK095(ce)001:12622: ched du spangs pa min te 'og ma'i theg pa
NK095(ce)001:12623: thams cad a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyan du
NK095(ce)001:12626: 'byung lnga 'gro drug theg dgu thams cad kyang //
NK095(ce)001:12627: dbyings la dbyings shar cho 'phrul yin pas na //
NK095(ce)001:12628: de yi rgyan yin bdag dang mthong mdzes bral //
NK095(ce)001:12629: yo ga mdud pa can gyi lta ba te //
NK095(ce)001:12630: don dam snang la rang bzhin med pa la //
NK095(ce)001:12631: kun rdzob tsam snang lha dang lha mo yang //
NK095(ce)001:12632: mtshan ma ye shes mnyam pa'i chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:12633: lha dang lha mor 'dzin pa mchog 'dzin bdud //
NK095(ce)001:12634: gnyis ka rang shar gnyis ka rang grol bas //
NK095(ce)001:12635: yo ga ma spangs rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyan //
NK095(ce)001:12636: ma h+aa mdud pa can gyi lta ba ni //
NK095(ce)001:12637: thabs kyi mchog gyur lhag pa'i kun rdzob la //
NK095(ce)001:12638: shes rab mchog gyur lhag pa'i don dam pas //
NK095(ce)001:12639: gnyis med mchog gyur bde ba mchog tu blta //
NK095(ce)001:12640: dbye ru yod kyang mnyam yang mnyam nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:12641: dbyer med spyod yul bral ba phyogs 'dzin bdud //
NK095(ce)001:12642: a ti mnyam pa ris med chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:12643: gnyis ka rang shar gnyis ka rang grol bas //
NK095(ce)001:12644: ma h+aa ma spangs rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyan //
NK095(ce)001:12645: a nu mdud pa can gyii lta ba ni //
NK095(ce)001:12646: phar snang shes pa kun tu bzang mo'i klong //
NK095(ce)001:12647: tshur snang yul ni kun tu bzang po'i yul //
NK095(ce)001:12648: gnyis su med pa'i bde ba chen por blta //
NK095(ce)001:12649: gnyis dang sdug bsngal mnyam pa'i chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:12650: gnyis med bde chen yid dpyod re ba'i bdud //
NK095(ce)001:12651: a ti rgya chad med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:12652: gnyis kar rang shar gnyis kar rang grol bas //
NK095(ce)001:12653: a nu ma spangs rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyan //
NK095(ce)001:12655: des na theg pa 'og ma'i zhen rtog thams cad
NK095(ce)001:12656: rdzogs pa chen po'i lam la brten nas spongs pa
NK095(ce)001:12657: dang yon tan thams cad yar ldan gyi tshul du
NK095(ce)001:12658: rdzogs par 'gyur bas na theg pa'i yang rtse 'dir
NK095(ce)001:12659: 'jug dgos la / de la 'jug bya'i theg pa de dag bsdu na gsum du gnas te /
NK095(ce)001:12660: gang zhe na rgyal ba'i gsung rab la brten nas
NK095(ce)001:12661: 'bras bu dgra bcom gyi go 'phang thob par 'dod
NK095(ce)001:12662: pa theg dman nyan rang gi lam dang /
NK095(ce)001:12663: byang chub kyi spyod pa la bskal pa grangs med
NK095(ce)001:12664: gsum sogs su spyod pa'i mthar sangs rgyas kyi go
NK095(ce)001:12665: 'phang thob par 'dod pa mtshan nyid theg chen pa
NK095(ce)001:12666: dang / lha sngags ting nge 'dzin gyi dmigs pa
NK095(ce)001:12667: dang ldan pas ma dag 'khrul pa'i snang ba thams
NK095(ce)001:12668: cad sbyangs nas dag pa lha'i rang bzhin du myur
NK095(ce)001:12669: du snang bar 'dod pa a nu man chad kyi
NK095(ce)001:12671: de rnams ni dper na sgyu ma mkhan gyis sprul
NK095(ce)001:12672: pa'i sgyu ma'i rnam pa med bzhin du snang ba
NK095(ce)001:12673: dang / ri mo'i rnam pa rnams ni mtho dman
NK095(ce)001:12674: med bzhin du mtho dman du snang ba ltar 'khor
NK095(ce)001:12675: ba las nges par 'byung zhing 'bras bu myang 'das
NK095(ce)001:12676: kyi sar 'jug tu med par rang byung ye shes
NK095(ce)001:12677: chen po gcig gi bdag nyid srid zhi mnyam pa
NK095(ce)001:12679: de ltar ma rtogs par 'khor 'das la bzang ngan
NK095(ce)001:12680: blang dor du snang bas rmug par byas pa yis
NK095(ce)001:12681: theg pa so so'i rtsol sgrub kyi lam la zhen
NK095(ce)001:12682: cing / de yi dbang las slar yang rtog pa
NK095(ce)001:12683: skye zhing 'phel bar 'gyur bas na de dag las
NK095(ce)001:12684: gzhan pa'i rtsol med ye grol gyi theg pa a
NK095(ce)001:12685: ti rdzogs chen gyi lam la 'jug par bya ste
NK095(ce)001:12686: cing / / de yang ji ltar zhe na a
NK095(ce)001:12687: ti rdzogs pa chen po 'di ni theg pa kun
NK095(ce)001:12688: gyi rgyal po yin pa'i phyir 'og ma'i theg pa
NK095(ce)001:12689: ltar spong 'gogs sbyong bsgyur gyi 'dzin zhen gang yang
NK095(ce)001:12690: med pas btang ngo ste rtsol bar mi byed la
NK095(ce)001:12691: cing / / / de ltar 'dzin rtsol thams cad
NK095(ce)001:12692: dang bral ba de ni chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12693: ngang la gnas pa yin pas bzhag go zhes gsungs
NK095(ce)001:12695: 'jog byed kyi rtsol ba la ltos pa min kyang
NK095(ce)001:12696: btang snyoms chen po'i ngang las mi 'da' ba'i don
NK095(ce)001:12697: te don du btang bzhag thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12698: rang bzhin du gsungs pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:12699: de lta bu'i btang bzhag bral ba'i gnas lugs 'dus
NK095(ce)001:12700: ma byas pa'i ye shes de la shes shing rtogs
NK095(ce)001:12701: par bya ba dang bsgrub cing mngon du bya ba
NK095(ce)001:12702: gang yang med pas 'doda cing zhen pa med cing
NK095(ce)001:12703: spyod cing len pa med la /
NK095(ce)001:12704: 'bras bu la thob par smon pa'i brod pa rdul
NK095(ce)001:12705: tsam yang mi bskyed do zhes bcos bsgyur dang blang
NK095(ce)001:12706: dor gyi re dogs kun dang bral ba de rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:12707: chen gyi don la zhugs pa yin gyis /
NK095(ce)001:12708: gzhan du spang blang la sogs pa'i zhen pa rdul
NK095(ce)001:12709: tsam yod kyang a ti'i lam dang 'gal bar gsungs
NK095(ce)001:12710: te / nam mkha'i rgyal po las /
NK095(ce)001:12711: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i thabs chen la //
NK095(ce)001:12712: sgyu bcos spyod pa thabs chen ma yin te //
NK095(ce)001:12713: sgyu 'chang thabs kyis bcos dang ma bral na //
NK095(ce)001:12714: mi rtog thabs chen de yi ci zhig bya //
NK095(ce)001:12716: bzhi pa sems nyid a ti ma bcos rnal du
NK095(ce)001:12717: bzhag thabs 'bras bu dang bcas pa la gsum ste
NK095(ce)001:12718: / khyung nam mkhar lding ba'i dpes tha mal shes pa rang 'gros btang bzhag med par bzhag tshul /
NK095(ce)001:12719: de nyid goms pa las gnas skabs spyan dang mngon shes la sogs pa'i drod rtags 'char tshul /
NK095(ce)001:12720: shin tu goms pa las sems nyid gzhi thog tu
NK095(ce)001:12721: pheb tshul las chos sku ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyal
NK095(ce)001:12722: po dang longs sprul snang ba'i rgya mtsho kun tu
NK095(ce)001:12725: dper na 'dab chags mkha' lding rgyal po khyung chen
NK095(ce)001:12726: nam mkha' la lding nas 'gro ba yi tshe na
NK095(ce)001:12727: 'dab gshog spro bsdu med cing mkha' dbyings lam du
NK095(ce)001:12728: bde ba dang / thams cad khobs 'og tu chub cing klu rnams zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12729: phyi rgya rlabs kyis gcod cing g.yang sar lhung dogs med pa bzhin du /
NK095(ce)001:12730: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:12731: kyis tha mal gyi shes pa 'di la bcos bsgyur
NK095(ce)001:12732: spu tsam med par rang 'gros su btang ba las
NK095(ce)001:12733: dmigs pa'i yul ma grub pas phar spro zhing btang
NK095(ce)001:12734: ba med cing / 'dzin pa'i rtod phur bud pas
NK095(ce)001:12735: nang du dmigs shing bsdu ba med par byar med
NK095(ce)001:12737: thams cad rig pa'i klong du 'ub chub cing mtshan rtog zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12738: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chod pas ltung ba'i nyam nga med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12739: 'bras bu la thob re med pas lam la stor bar mi dogs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:12740: de nyid kyi phyir na bza' ba'am gza' gtang dang
NK095(ce)001:12741: rtsol ba thams cad ngang gis zhi zhing med pas
NK095(ce)001:12742: ma bcos shugs 'byung gi spyod pa thams cad ci
NK095(ce)001:12743: shar chos nyid kyi rol par spyod par gsungs te
NK095(ce)001:12745: khyung chen gshog rdzogs mkha' la lding ba bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:12746: chu rlung ri brag gyen thur nyam mi nga //
NK095(ce)001:12747: bar snang nam mkha'i khams kun lam du bde //
NK095(ce)001:12748: gang du dmigs pa'i sa kun gcod par byed //
NK095(ce)001:12749: de bzhin ye nas blo sbyangs rnal 'byor thugs //
NK095(ce)001:12750: byang chub snying por 'gro ba'i skal ldan no //
NK095(ce)001:12751: sangs rgyas mngon du grub pa'i man ngag can //
NK095(ce)001:12752: byang chub sems rtogs yon tan khyad par 'phags //
NK095(ce)001:12753: bdag dang gzhan don lhun grub ma spangs pa //
NK095(ce)001:12754: spyod pa rgya mtsho sna tshogs ci bder spyod //
NK095(ce)001:12757: 'di ltar dper na rgya mtsho chen po ni rnyogs ma med pas dwangs zhing gting zab pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12758: rlabs mi zad cing 'phel 'bri med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12759: rgya che zhing nor bu rin po che'i 'byung gnas
NK095(ce)001:12760: su gyur pa bzhin du snying po byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:12761: sems ni rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal zhing kun gyis
NK095(ce)001:12763: yon tan mi zad cing 'phel 'bri med pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12764: mtha' dbus dang bral bas rgya che ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:12765: 'dod pa thams cad skong ba'i bdag nyid du ye nas gnas pa la /
NK095(ce)001:12766: bcos bsgyur spang blang med pa'i gnad kyis goms par
NK095(ce)001:12767: byas na rig rtsal so sor rtog pa'i rtsal las
NK095(ce)001:12768: zab pa dang rgya che ba'i chos rnams sna tshogs
NK095(ce)001:12769: pa klong rdol du 'byung bar 'gyur bas 'gro ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12770: khams la chos kyi char chen po 'beb par byed
NK095(ce)001:12772: rnal 'byor dam pa skyes mchog dam can la //
NK095(ce)001:12773: rtogs pas bar ma chod pas ye shes klong //
NK095(ce)001:12774: mnyam nyid mthar phyin lam chen kun bsgral bas //
NK095(ce)001:12775: ci spyod ting 'dzin las ni ma nyams klong //
NK095(ce)001:12776: goms pa'i klong du shin tu gsal 'gyur te //
NK095(ce)001:12777: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa chos nyid rang byung klong //
NK095(ce)001:12778: bdag gzhan gnyis su mthong ba ci yang med //
NK095(ce)001:12779: de phyir klong gsum ldan pa'i ye shes bshad //
NK095(ce)001:12780: ces gsungs pa lta bu'i ye shes gsum ldan gyi
NK095(ce)001:12781: klong ngam ting nge 'dzin nyams pa med klong ngam
NK095(ce)001:12782: rtsal las spyan lnga dang mngon shes drug dang gzungs
NK095(ce)001:12783: dang ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i yon tan gyi
NK095(ce)001:12784: tshogs grangs dang tshad gzhal du med pas nam mkha'i
NK095(ce)001:12786: rig gdangs ma 'gags pa'i rtsal snang rang shar ba
NK095(ce)001:12787: tsam las yon tan de dag bsdu ba'i gnas sam
NK095(ce)001:12788: khong du chud par bya ba'i gnas su nges par
NK095(ce)001:12789: bzung zhing zhen pa dang des rlom sems pa yang
NK095(ce)001:12792: de ltar rdzogs chen bya rtsol bral ba'i don la
NK095(ce)001:12793: shin tu goms pa mthar phyin pas sems nyid gzhi
NK095(ce)001:12794: thog tu phebs pa'am byang chub snying por phyin pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12795: de ma thag tu rang gnas chos sku'i dgongs pa
NK095(ce)001:12796: la mnyam rjes kyi dbye ba med par chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:12797: kyi ngang las rtag tu g.yo ba med pas ting
