NK095(ce)001:12798: nge 'dzin thams cad kyi phul du phyin pa'i rgyal
NK095(ce)001:12799: po chen po 'byung zhing chos sku 'dus ma byas
NK095(ce)001:12800: pa skye 'chi 'pho 'gyur med pa'i don mngon du
NK095(ce)001:12802: de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin de la mtshan gyi rnam grangs yang /
NK095(ce)001:12803: mi gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK095(ce)001:12804: mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK095(ce)001:12805: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK095(ce)001:12806: snang ba med pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK095(ce)001:12807: thod rgal gyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK095(ce)001:12808: snang ba chen po'i ting nge 'dzin zhes kyang gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:12809: de ltar chos sku'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur pa'i tshe na /
NK095(ce)001:12811: mi snang rgyun gyi chos sku dang //
NK095(ce)001:12812: snang ba gzugs sku'i thugs rje yang //
NK095(ce)001:12813: rgyun chad med par 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:12814: nam mkha'i klong nas cho 'phrul bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:12815: zhes gsungs pa ltar chos sku'i dgongs pa las ma
NK095(ce)001:12816: g.yos bzhin du de'i rtsal snang longs sku dang sprul
NK095(ce)001:12817: sku'i rol pa tshad med pa rgya mtsho chen po
NK095(ce)001:12818: la gza' skar bkra ba bzhin du 'gag med du
NK095(ce)001:12819: 'char zhing 'gro ba'i don rtag khyab lhun grub chen
NK095(ce)001:12820: po'i tshul du mdzad na yang /
NK095(ce)001:12821: rnam rtog gi spros pa dang bya byed rtsol ba
NK095(ce)001:12822: med par mi rtoga mnyam pa chen po'i ngang las
NK095(ce)001:12823: rtsol med du shar bas nam mkha'i mtha' ltar rgya
NK095(ce)001:12825: de yang ma dag pa'i chos zhig spangs nas gdod
NK095(ce)001:12826: dag pa mngon du thob pa lta bu min par
NK095(ce)001:12827: chos 'di dag thams cad gdod nas kun tu bzang
NK095(ce)001:12828: po'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pas spyod yul thams cad
NK095(ce)001:12829: yongs su dag par gnas pa la skye zhing 'byung
NK095(ce)001:12830: ba dang 'pho zhing 'gyur ba'i chos su grub pa
NK095(ce)001:12831: med par ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don de rnal
NK095(ce)001:12832: 'byor bas mngon du rtogs pa tsam ste /
NK095(ce)001:12834: sems can thams cad byang chub snying po la //
NK095(ce)001:12835: rang gi sems nyid sangs rgyas mngon sum na //
NK095(ce)001:12836: gzhan nas bsgrub pa'i rgyal ba rdul tsam med //
NK095(ce)001:12837: 'gro ba skal ldan rnams kyi don tsam du //
NK095(ce)001:12838: bsgom zhing bsgrub pa'i tha snyad lung du bstan //
NK095(ce)001:12839: de lta bas na mi 'grub gang yang med //
NK095(ce)001:12840: de lta de bzhin chos kyi dbyings rig na //
NK095(ce)001:12841: ma rig rnams la snying rje chen po skye //
NK095(ce)001:12842: snying rje skyes nas sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK095(ce)001:12843: 'gro don thabs la spyod pa sna tshogs ston //
NK095(ce)001:12844: bdag dang gzhan du rtog pa med pa'i phyir //
NK095(ce)001:12845: ye nas gnyis med don gcig chos kyi sku //
NK095(ce)001:12846: chos sku skye med rtogs nas 'gro don du //
NK095(ce)001:12847: skye ba'i cho 'phrul yang nas yang du bstan //
NK095(ce)001:12848: mdzad pa bcu gnyis 'gro don mthar phyin pa //
NK095(ce)001:12849: cir yang 'gyur ba'i gzugs can sprul pa'i sku //
NK095(ce)001:12850: thugs rje cho 'phrul sna tshogs cir yang gsal //
NK095(ce)001:12851: thugs rje'i sprul pas gdul bya kun 'dul pas //
NK095(ce)001:12852: sgyu ma'i blo ldan rlom sems rdul tsam med //
NK095(ce)001:12854: gsum pa don bsdu ba la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:12855: theg brgyad kyi rang bzhin spang blang du bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:12856: rdzogs chen ro gcig tu rtogs pa la dge sdig chos nyid du 'char tshul /
NK095(ce)001:12857: dran bsam skye med du sgom pas rnal don chos nyid du mi mthong ba /
NK095(ce)001:12858: sems nyid chos sku yin pas kun la khyab kyang
NK095(ce)001:12859: ma rtogs pa nyid rdzogs chen spyod pa'i rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:12860: pa la mngon sum du snang tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:12862: 'di ltar sems can rnams ye nas 'khrul ma myong
NK095(ce)001:12863: par snying po byang chub kyi klong du sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:12865: phyi nang snang srid kyi chos 'di dag sa bon
NK095(ce)001:12866: myu gu la sogs pa rgyu dang 'brel ba drug
NK095(ce)001:12867: dang sa chu me rlung la sogs pa rkyen dang
NK095(ce)001:12868: 'brel ba drug ste phyi'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis dang
NK095(ce)001:12869: ma rig pa nas rga shi'i bar gyi nang gi
NK095(ce)001:12870: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis po ye
NK095(ce)001:12871: dbang gis 'khrul ba snang tshul dang /
NK095(ce)001:12872: de nyid ldog pa'i phyir du theg pa brgyad kyi
NK095(ce)001:12873: chos bstan pa thams cad rtsol med ye grol gyi
NK095(ce)001:12874: gshis lugs snying po rang byung gi ye shes rgyu
NK095(ce)001:12875: rkyen dang bral ba khong du mi chud par de
NK095(ce)001:12876: lta ma yin no zhes skur pas spong bar byed
NK095(ce)001:12877: pa dang brtags pas sgro 'dogs pa rnams kyi ched
NK095(ce)001:12878: du rgyu 'bras spang blang can du bshad pa yin
NK095(ce)001:12879: pas / de lta bu'i gdul bya 'khrul pa can
NK095(ce)001:12880: rnams kyi don du lam la rim gyis 'jug pa'i
NK095(ce)001:12881: sgo tsam du bstan pa las rang rig pa byang
NK095(ce)001:12882: chub kyi snying po ni rgyu rkyen rtsol bsgrub la
NK095(ce)001:12883: ltos pa med par gzhi rdzogs 'pho 'gyur bral ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12884: rang bzhin du rdzogs chen gyi gzhung nas ji ltar
NK095(ce)001:12885: bstan pa ltar yang rab a ti'i skal ba dang
NK095(ce)001:12886: ldan pa'i mkhas pa don gyi gnas lugs mthar thug
NK095(ce)001:12887: pa rtogs par nus pa'i blo gros dang ldan pas
NK095(ce)001:12888: de ji lta ba bzhin du shesa par gyis shig
NK095(ce)001:12889: pas / ces pa ste / khyung chen las /
NK095(ce)001:12890: 'khrul pa rnams kyi sgo tsam nyid du ni //
NK095(ce)001:12891: tshig dang yi ger ston pas bshad pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:12892: rang rig byang chub snying po chos kyi dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:12893: chos dbyings gzhan nas mi rnyed de bzhin nyid //
NK095(ce)001:12894: mkhas pa rnams kyis de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK095(ce)001:12896: des na 'di ltar 'gro ba rgyud drug tu skye
NK095(ce)001:12897: shi'i kha brgyud cing 'khrul snang gi duhkha la spyod
NK095(ce)001:12898: pa ltar snang ba'i 'gro ba ma lus pa yang
NK095(ce)001:12899: dang po'i lam du ste dang por gang las snang
NK095(ce)001:12900: ba'i gzhi chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i ngang las
NK095(ce)001:12901: skad cig kyang g.yo ma myong bar shes par bya
NK095(ce)001:12902: ba ni gnas lugs mthar thug pa rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:12903: po'i dgongs pa ma nor ba yin mod /
NK095(ce)001:12904: 'on kyang de ltar ma rtogs par 'dod pa'i yul
NK095(ce)001:12905: lnga la chags sdang rang mtshan par spyod pa'i 'gro
NK095(ce)001:12906: ba rnams la dmigs pa med pa'i snying rjes thugs
NK095(ce)001:12907: rgyud brlan pa'i rgyal ba thabs la mkhas pas gdul
NK095(ce)001:12908: bya'i blo dang 'tshams par theg pa rim gyis ma
NK095(ce)001:12909: bstan na / dbang po dman pa'i rigs can rnams
NK095(ce)001:12910: kyis dang po nas rdzogs chen byar med kyi don
NK095(ce)001:12911: rtogs dka' ba la dgongs nas gdul bya rang rang
NK095(ce)001:12912: theg pa gang du dga' bar ste mos pa dang
NK095(ce)001:12913: mthun par byang chub kyi lam la spyod pa'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:12914: ston pa'i theg pa 'og ma thams cad rdzogs pa
NK095(ce)001:12915: chen po'i lam stegs min pa med la /
NK095(ce)001:12916: spang blang dang bcas pa'i lam de dag gis byar
NK095(ce)001:12917: med ye bab sor bzhag gi don dngos su rtogs
NK095(ce)001:12918: par mi nus pas na mthar thug mthar thug rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:12919: chen la 'jug par bya dgos te /
NK095(ce)001:12921: gnas lugs de ni 'dus ma byas //
NK095(ce)001:12922: 'bras bu sku gsum mtha' ru thug /rgyu 'bras gnyis la mi ltos dang //
NK095(ce)001:12923: byas pa'i chos kyi sangs mi rgya //
NK095(ce)001:12924: ye nas gnas pa'i don rtogs na //
NK095(ce)001:12925: ma byas chos kyi sangs rgyas dang //
NK095(ce)001:12926: cig char 'jug pa'i lam yin pas //
NK095(ce)001:12927: nges don phyin ci ma log pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:12930: des na rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs don ji bzhin
NK095(ce)001:12931: pa chos thams cad rang byung rig pa'i ngang du
NK095(ce)001:12932: gnyis med ro gcig tu rtogs pa'i tshe na rgyu
NK095(ce)001:12933: 'bras blang dor gang la'ang ltos pa med de /
NK095(ce)001:12934: 'di ltar sems can stong phrag mang po'i srog gcod par byed pa shan pa'i las byed pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12935: 'dod log gi las la rtag tu zhugs pa smad 'tshong gi las byed pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12936: pha ma gsod pa sogs mtshams med pa lnga dang
NK095(ce)001:12937: nye ba'i mtshams med pa lnga la sogs shin tu
NK095(ce)001:12938: lci ba'i las bcas pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:12939: rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba 'jig rtena
NK095(ce)001:12940: dkar phyogs rnams dang theg pa 'og ma pa rnams
NK095(ce)001:12941: kyis spong bar byed pa'i log spyod mi dge ba'i
NK095(ce)001:12942: las rnams kyang don la ming tsam yang ma grub
NK095(ce)001:12943: par rig stong 'gyur ba med pa chos nyid skye
NK095(ce)001:12944: ba med pa'i klong du gnyis med ye shes chen
NK095(ce)001:12945: po'i ngo bor yongs su rdzogsa pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:12946: ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:12947: da yang 'dus pa'i snying po nyon //
NK095(ce)001:12948: ngo bo nyid kyi sku shes pas //
NK095(ce)001:12949: mi len mi spang ye mnyam phyir //
NK095(ce)001:12950: re dogs med pas rang byung sku //
NK095(ce)001:12951: de phyir kun bzang gdal ba la //
NK095(ce)001:12952: gang yang mi 'gag rol par shar //
NK095(ce)001:12953: srog gcod ma byin len pa dang //
NK095(ce)001:12954: mi tshangs spyod dang rdzun tu smra //
NK095(ce)001:12955: mtshams med la sogs sdig byas kyang //
NK095(ce)001:12956: nyes par mi 'gyur dpal du che //
NK095(ce)001:12957: stong gsum ma lus tshig gyur kyang //
NK095(ce)001:12958: nam mkha' me chus mi tshugs 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:12959: zhes gsungs pa de lta bu'i phyir na las nyon
NK095(ce)001:12960: rnam rtog gi bdud thams cad 'jom par byed pa
NK095(ce)001:12961: chos nyid kyi rtsis theb pas ye nas rnam par
NK095(ce)001:12962: dag pa 'gyur ba'i zug rngu gang yang med pas
NK095(ce)001:12963: bde ba che ba'am chen po rang byung zag pa
NK095(ce)001:12964: med pa'i ye shes las gzhan du gyur pa rdul
NK095(ce)001:12965: tsam yang med pas dge sdig thams cad chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:12966: mnyam pa chen po'i klong du la bzla bar byed
NK095(ce)001:12967: pa nyid do // khyung chen las /
NK095(ce)001:12968: phyi dang nang med ye shes yangs pa'i mkha' //dus gsum dus med gcig ste khyad par med //
NK095(ce)001:12969: sngon med phyis med gdod nas dag pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:12970: lta bas bltar med lta ba'i tshig las 'das //
NK095(ce)001:12971: yid kyis 'jog med sgom pa chen po'i klong //
NK095(ce)001:12972: gdod nas dag pa'i bdud rtsi de ltar gnas //
NK095(ce)001:12973: rnam rtog 'khor ba bcad pa de yi las //
NK095(ce)001:12974: rgyu 'bras ro gcig mnyam gnas mchog tu gnas //
NK095(ce)001:12975: gang la'ang mi gnas byang chub sems la gnas //
NK095(ce)001:12976: rgyu dang rkyen las ma byung skye shi med //
NK095(ce)001:12977: rang bzhin 'od gsal bdud rtsi chen po 'di //
NK095(ce)001:12978: su yis rtogs pas dngos grub chen por gsungs //
NK095(ce)001:12981: shan pa smad 'tshong mtshams med byed pa de //
NK095(ce)001:12982: 'jig rten kha na ma tho spangs pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:12983: de nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i bdud rtsi ste //
NK095(ce)001:12984: bde ba chen po nyid dang dbyer med phyir //
NK095(ce)001:12985: rnam par mi rtog snying po zhes kyang bya //
NK095(ce)001:12987: de nyid theg pa dman pa'i rigs can rnams kyis
NK095(ce)001:12988: shin tu rtogs par dka' bas gsang ba mchog gi
NK095(ce)001:12989: dam tshig tu bstan pa dang skal ldan rnams la
NK095(ce)001:12992: bsam gtan brjod med mchog gi bdud rtsi 'di //
NK095(ce)001:12993: phal gyis mi thob ris su chad med do //
NK095(ce)001:12994: rnam pa can la shin tu gsang bar 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:12995: blta yang mi dgos lta ba mchog tu grags //
NK095(ce)001:12996: ci spyod mi rtog skye ba 'di yi don //
NK095(ce)001:12997: nyam nga skyon gyis mi sgrib 'di yi lam //
NK095(ce)001:12998: gtsang sme'i blo rtog bor nas don la bsnyegs //
NK095(ce)001:12999: ma sring kun sbyor mtshams med kun spyod cing //
NK095(ce)001:13000: cha shes phra ba'ang ma rig nyan thos ni //
NK095(ce)001:13001: shin tu gsang ba 'di ni dam tshig mchog /chu srin rdzas 'dzin tshul du mi gtong na //
NK095(ce)001:13002: khyad par gyur pa'i bdud rtsi mchog nyid grub //
NK095(ce)001:13005: gong du bstan pa'i spyod pa de dag las gzhan
NK095(ce)001:13006: yang snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK095(ce)001:13007: cad kyang chos nyid bde ba chen po byang chub
NK095(ce)001:13008: sems kyi rang bzhin las gzhan du med pa'i rgyu
NK095(ce)001:13009: mtshan de bas na chos thams cad kyii rang bzhina
NK095(ce)001:13010: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo gdod nas skye ba
NK095(ce)001:13011: med pa de yi rang bzhin du grub zin pa
NK095(ce)001:13012: yin pas / da chos nyid skye ba med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:13013: don de bsgom bsgrub rtsol ba'i thabs kyis chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:13014: ye nas rang la gnas pa'i don gzhan nas btsal
NK095(ce)001:13015: ba dang rtogs su re ba ni dper na nam
NK095(ce)001:13016: mkhas ma khyab pa gang yang med pas rang nyid
NK095(ce)001:13017: kyang nam mkha'i klong na gnas bzhin du nam mkha'
NK095(ce)001:13018: gzhan du btsal ba dang 'dra la /
NK095(ce)001:13019: rgyu rkyen rtsol sgrub la sogs pa gzhan la ltos
NK095(ce)001:13020: pa'i sgo nas las nyon ma rig pa'i bsgrib pa
NK095(ce)001:13021: bsal nas chos nyid bde ba chen po gsar du
NK095(ce)001:13022: thob par 'dod pa ni me yis me gsod par
NK095(ce)001:13023: 'dod pa dang 'dra ste grub 'bras thob pa med
NK095(ce)001:13024: pas shin tu dka' ba'i las la brtson par byed
NK095(ce)001:13026: 'di ltar sems can rnams kyi rgyud kyi tha mal
NK095(ce)001:13027: gyi shes pa spu ma barjesa mdog ma bsgyur ba
NK095(ce)001:13028: 'di ka chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK095(ce)001:13029: shes snying po byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin yin
NK095(ce)001:13030: pas 'di nyid sems can yongs kyi rgyud la sbas
NK095(ce)001:13031: shing gab pa med kyang rang gsang thabs kyis chod
NK095(ce)001:13033: rdzogs pa chen po'i don la the tshom dang bral
NK095(ce)001:13034: ba'i rnal 'byor pa gang gis ci yang mi len
NK095(ce)001:13035: gang yang mi spong bar re dogs rtsol sgrub dang
NK095(ce)001:13036: bral bar gnas pa ni byang chub kyi spyod pa
NK095(ce)001:13038: de lta bu'i skal pa dang ldan pa rnams la
NK095(ce)001:13039: chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes chos
NK095(ce)001:13040: sku rang gnas kyi dgongs pa dus dang rnam pa
NK095(ce)001:13041: kun tu rang bzhin gsal 'grib med par rtag tu
NK095(ce)001:13043: kun tu bzang po rig pa rang gi rtsal shar ba'i rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:13044: rin chen gling dang nyi ma ltar //
NK095(ce)001:13045: rang gsal 'gag med rtog dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:13046: 'khor ba'i gnas nyid ye sangs rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:13047: rang sems rig pa gang snang ba //
NK095(ce)001:13048: bsam pa ci 'gyus ye shes dang //
NK095(ce)001:13049: lhun grub gzhi 'dzin rig pa la //
NK095(ce)001:13050: sems can chos nyid gang yang med //
NK095(ce)001:13051: dbus dang mtha' bral dkyil du rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:13052: rtag pa ma yin chad mtha' min //
NK095(ce)001:13053: mi rtag ma yin bdag mtha' med //
NK095(ce)001:13055: bya byed med cing rtsol sems dag /bgrod med rtsol bral rig pa'i klong //
NK095(ce)001:13058: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las bya
NK095(ce)001:13059: med rdzogs pa'i lung bcu las mi gnas yul med
NK095(ce)001:13060: kyi le'u ste nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa'i 'grel pa'o
NK095(ce)001:13061: ////don gsum pa sems nyid bya btsal med par blta
NK095(ce)001:13062: ba'i yul las 'das pas rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las
NK095(ce)001:13063: 'das pa'i le'u nyer gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:13066: de ltar rgyu 'bras bya rtsol las 'das pa ye
NK095(ce)001:13067: rdzogs lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa de
NK095(ce)001:13068: nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po des
NK095(ce)001:13069: sems las shar ba'i phyi nang 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:13070: thams cad rtog med mnyam pa chen po yul med
NK095(ce)001:13071: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin yin phyir lta ba
NK095(ce)001:13072: yul med kyi lung 'di gsungs so //
NK095(ce)001:13074: snang srid sems kyi cho 'phrul yin pas brtags na yul med nam mkha' ltar gnas pa /
NK095(ce)001:13075: yul lngar snang dus rang gsal rtog pa med pas yul med nam mkha' ltar gnas pa /
NK095(ce)001:13076: tshig dang yi ger bstan pa thams cad kyang sems yin pas yul med nam mkha' ltar gnas pa /
NK095(ce)001:13077: rnal don smra bsam brjod du med pas nam mkha'i dgongs par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13079: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /ji ltar snang
NK095(ce)001:13080: ba'i chos phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa 'di
NK095(ce)001:13081: rnams ni rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:13082: kyi rtsal las shar ba'i cho 'phrul tsam las don
NK095(ce)001:13083: la cir yang grub pa med pa gzhi med rtsa
NK095(ce)001:13084: bral chen po'i rang bzhin yin pas de la blta
NK095(ce)001:13085: ba'i yul zhig ma mchis pa'i phyir sems kyis gang
NK095(ce)001:13086: du yang rtog par mi bya la /
NK095(ce)001:13087: de ltar 'khor 'das bzang ngan bde sdug la sogs
NK095(ce)001:13088: pa thams cad don la med bzhin sems kyis brtags
NK095(ce)001:13090: sems kyis cir yang rnam par mi rtog par 'dzin
NK095(ce)001:13091: zhen thams cad dang bral bar rang bab la bzhag
NK095(ce)001:13092: na chos de dag thams cad bdag gzhan dang 'khor
NK095(ce)001:13093: 'das skyon yon sogs kyi dbye ba med pas na
NK095(ce)001:13094: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin nam mkha'
NK095(ce)001:13096: des na de lta bu'i chos nyid de ji lta
NK095(ce)001:13097: ba bzhin du rtogs pa ni chos nyid ye stong
NK095(ce)001:13098: chen po stong gsal nam mkha'i dbyings lta bu'i dgongs
NK095(ce)001:13099: pa la gnas pa ste re dogs spang blang gi
NK095(ce)001:13100: rtog pa gang yang med pa yin pas klong chen
NK095(ce)001:13101: nam mkha' lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa zhes bya ba
NK095(ce)001:13102: ni de lta bu la 'dogs par bya'o zhes pa
NK095(ce)001:13104: rig pa mtha' bral stong pa nyid //
NK095(ce)001:13106: gzung 'dzin med pas mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK095(ce)001:13107: rol pa'i cho 'phrul cir yang ston //
NK095(ce)001:13108: cho 'phrul bstan yang rang rgyud bral //
NK095(ce)001:13109: rig pa sgyu ma chu zla 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:13110: kun tu 'char zhing lhun gyis grub //
NK095(ce)001:13112: rig pa ma bslad dri ma bral //
NK095(ce)001:13113: nam mkha' lta bu'i rig pa la //
NK095(ce)001:13114: nam mkha'i dbyings ltar bsam dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:13115: bsam med blo bde nam mkha' bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:13116: rang byung ye shes bsam dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:13117: mi skye mi 'gag cir mi gnas //
NK095(ce)001:13118: rig pa'i rgyal po blta ba yiin //
NK095(ce)001:13119: bltar med yengs med blta ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:13122: 'di ltar mig rna la sogs pa'i dbang po lnga
NK095(ce)001:13123: la snang ba yi yul gzugs sgra la sogs pa'i
NK095(ce)001:13124: yul snang rnams kyang rig pa'i rtsal ma 'gags par
NK095(ce)001:13125: shar ba tsam las gang yang grub pa med pas
NK095(ce)001:13126: yul med rang gsal gyi snang ba gzhi med stong
NK095(ce)001:13127: gzugs kyi rol pa d+ha du ra'i snang ba lta
NK095(ce)001:13128: bu yin pas / de la 'dzin zhen gyis bzang
NK095(ce)001:13129: ngan blang dor la sogs pa gang du'ang mi rtog
NK095(ce)001:13130: cing spong 'gog sbyong bsgyur ci yang mi byed par
NK095(ce)001:13131: rang babs la bzhag pas gtad med rgya grol la
NK095(ce)001:13132: song ba de yang chos nyid nam mkha'i dgongs pa
NK095(ce)001:13133: la gnas pa yin pas rdzogs chen a ti'i rnal
NK095(ce)001:13134: 'byor pa rnams kyis de bzhin nyid du gnas par
NK095(ce)001:13135: byas na phyi nang gzung 'dzin gyi spros pa thams
NK095(ce)001:13136: cad yul med zang thal du dengs te chos sku
NK095(ce)001:13137: rgyal po'i gtan srid zin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:13138: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:13139: gzhi bzhag mi g.yo mnyam pa'i dgongs pa la //
NK095(ce)001:13140: phyi dang nang med gzung 'dzin spros dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:13141: yul zhes gzhan du zhen pa'i sems med pas //
NK095(ce)001:13142: gzung ba'i chos med snod bcud snang zhen bral //
NK095(ce)001:13143: 'khor bar skye ba'i yul med nam mkha' 'dra //
NK095(ce)001:13144: rang zhes sems la nang du mi rtog pas //
NK095(ce)001:13145: 'dzin pa'i chos med srid pa'i kun rtog zhi //
NK095(ce)001:13146: 'khor bar skye ba'i mkhan po rtsad nas chod //
NK095(ce)001:13147: de tshe mkha' 'dra phyii nang 'khrul pa'i chos //
NK095(ce)001:13148: gang yang mi dmigs chos sku'i dgongs par phyin //
NK095(ce)001:13151: 'di ltar rgyal ba thabs mkhas la thugs rje dang
NK095(ce)001:13152: ldan pa rnams kyis gdul bya sems can rnams la
NK095(ce)001:13153: chos sgo ji snyed gsungs pa thams cad chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:13154: nam mkha' lta bu'i don mtshon byed du bstan pa
NK095(ce)001:13155: yin pas / dper na 'dzub mo'i zla ba mtshon
NK095(ce)001:13156: pa ltar dang por brjod byed kyi tshig dang yi
NK095(ce)001:13157: ge'i don la brtags shing dpyad pas chos nyid ji
NK095(ce)001:13158: bzhin pa'i ngo bo tshig yig ste tshig dang yi
NK095(ce)001:13159: ge'i don la brtags su med par smra bsam brjod
NK095(ce)001:13160: pa dang bral ba'i rang bzhin mthong ba'am rtogs pas
NK095(ce)001:13161: zla ba dngos su mthong zin nas 'dzub mo la
NK095(ce)001:13162: ltos pa med par ltar tshig dang yi ge'i mtha'
NK095(ce)001:13163: la mi gnas par rtog med mnyam pa chen po
NK095(ce)001:13164: chos nyid de bzhin nyid du bcos bsgyur spong blang
NK095(ce)001:13165: med par gnas pa de yang kun byed chos sku'i
NK095(ce)001:13166: thugs klong chos nyid nam mkha'i dgongs pa la gnas
NK095(ce)001:13167: yin pas / pa yin no // de ltar yang ru sbal rtsa rgyud las /
NK095(ce)001:13168: ma brtags ji bzhin gnas pa de bzhin nyid //
NK095(ce)001:13169: mi rtog mi brtags brtags pa'i yul las 'das //
NK095(ce)001:13170: brtags med yul las 'das pa mkha' gsal nam mkha'i klong //
NK095(ce)001:13171: nam mkha'i klong ni ye nas de bzhin nyid //
NK095(ce)001:13172: brtags pas dngos po dbyibs dang kha dog ste //
NK095(ce)001:13173: 'di la dbyibs dang kha dog ma grub dngos med nam mkha'i klong //
NK095(ce)001:13174: cir yang bsgyur du med pa de bzhin nyid //
NK095(ce)001:13175: de bzhin nyid ni mtshon pa yongs dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:13176: 'dzub khrid zla ba lta bur bstan pa de //
NK095(ce)001:13177: de bstan zla 'dzub mi gcig thag ring 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:13178: de bzhin de dang de gnyis thag ring yang //
NK095(ce)001:13179: ji bzhin pa nyid nges par rang la 'char //
NK095(ce)001:13180: de bzhin rtogs pa sangs rgyas nyag gcig pa //
NK095(ce)001:13183: de ltar mdor na snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus
NK095(ce)001:13184: pa'i chos thams cad sems kyi rtsal snang tsam las
NK095(ce)001:13186: sems kyi rang bzhin ni gdod nas skye ba med
NK095(ce)001:13187: cing spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral bas smra
NK095(ce)001:13188: bsam brjod du med par gnas pa'i don 'di ni
NK095(ce)001:13189: srid zhi kun la khyab cing chos kun klong du
NK095(ce)001:13190: chub pa dang ye stong 'dus ma byas pa'i bdag
NK095(ce)001:13191: nyid yin pas nam mkha' bzhin du ye nas gnas
NK095(ce)001:13192: so // de lta bu'i chos nyid mnyam pa chen
NK095(ce)001:13193: po nam mkha' lta bu'i ngo bo ji bzhin pa
NK095(ce)001:13194: la blang dor bcos bsgyur gang yang mi byed par
NK095(ce)001:13195: de bzhin nyid du 'jog par byed pa ni nam
NK095(ce)001:13196: mkha' lta bu'i dgongs pa la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:13197: ba yin no zhes gsungsa so //
NK095(ce)001:13199: bsam du med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK095(ce)001:13200: kun la khyab pa'i bdag nyid du //
NK095(ce)001:13201: nam mkha' bzhin du ye gnas pa //
NK095(ce)001:13202: de bzhin nam mkha'i dgongs par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:13203: ji bzhin pa yi chos nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:13204: ma bcos pa yi blo bzhag ste //
NK095(ce)001:13205: mi g.yo mnyam pa'i sems gnas pa //
NK095(ce)001:13206: de bzhin nam mkha'i dgongs par bshad //
NK095(ce)001:13209: bya med rdzogs pa las lta ba yul med kyi
NK095(ce)001:13210: nam mkha'i dgongs pa bstana pa'i le'u ste rtsa gsum
NK095(ce)001:13211: pa'i 'grel pa'o ////don bzhi pa kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:13212: chos thams cad la ye khyab 'gyur ba med par
NK095(ce)001:13213: bzhugs pas rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i le'u
NK095(ce)001:13214: nyer bzhi pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:13218: de ltar rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba yul med
NK095(ce)001:13219: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin du bstan pa'i rjes
NK095(ce)001:13220: de nasa byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:13221: des blang dor rtsol sgrub kyi bya ba gang yang
NK095(ce)001:13222: med par sku gsum de bzhin nyid du ye nas
NK095(ce)001:13223: rdzogs pa'i lung sku gsum 'gyur ba med pa'i dgongs
NK095(ce)001:13224: pa nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin las nam yang
NK095(ce)001:13225: 'da' ba med pa'i phyag rgya bzhugs tshul gyi le'u
NK095(ce)001:13226: 'di bstan to // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:13227: rang bzhin 'pho 'gyur med pa'i bzhugs tshul mdor bstan /
NK095(ce)001:13231: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /rang gi sems
NK095(ce)001:13232: nyid rang byung gi ye shes 'di nyid ye nas
NK095(ce)001:13233: 'khrul ma myong bas na dang po'i sangs rgyas dus
NK095(ce)001:13234: gsum rgyal ba kun gyi spyi dpal rang byung kun
NK095(ce)001:13235: tu bzang po sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa yi
NK095(ce)001:13237: de nyid ye nas 'pho 'gyur med pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:13238: du ji ltar bzhugs pa'i tshul lam gnas tshul bstan
NK095(ce)001:13239: pa ni 'di lta ste zhes so /
NK095(ce)001:13241: gnyis med gdod nas dag pa'i ngo bo nyid byang chub sems kyi bzhugs tshul /
NK095(ce)001:13242: gzung 'dzin gnyis su med pa'i ye shes chos kyi sku'i bzhugs tshul /
NK095(ce)001:13243: yul sems snang ba ma 'gags pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i bzhugs tshul /
NK095(ce)001:13244: rig rtsal sna tshogs su shar grol sprul sku'i bzhugs tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:13246: de la rang byung rig pa'i ye shes chos sku
NK095(ce)001:13247: kun byed rgyal po de nyid gzhi dbyings 'pho 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:13248: bral ba rig pa byang chub sems su bzhugs tsam
NK095(ce)001:13249: na snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams thams cad
NK095(ce)001:13250: kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas kun gyi snying
NK095(ce)001:13253: byang chub sems su bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:13254: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK095(ce)001:13255: mi snang ba la mngon du 'byin nus pas //
NK095(ce)001:13256: chos rnams kun gyi snying por bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:13258: de lta bu'i snying po byang chub sems kyi gnas
NK095(ce)001:13259: lugs ma bcos pa de nyid rtogsa pa'i gang zag
NK095(ce)001:13260: ni ston pa kun byed rgyal po dang ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:13262: kun byed rgyal po ni ye nas 'gyur ba med
NK095(ce)001:13263: pa'i chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa'i bdag nyid yin
NK095(ce)001:13264: pa des na de nyid dang ngo bo dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:13265: pa'i gang zag rnal 'byor pa de yang skye shi'i
NK095(ce)001:13266: 'gyur ba med par 'gyur med bde ba chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:13267: ngang la gnas pa yin par bstana pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13269: kun byed byang chub kyi sems de skye med rang
NK095(ce)001:13270: byung gi ngo bo rtog med chos kyi sku ru
NK095(ce)001:13271: bzhugs tsam na gzung 'dzin rnam rtog gi spros pa
NK095(ce)001:13272: dang ngang gis bral nas blo 'das bsam brjod dang
NK095(ce)001:13273: bral bar bzhugs pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:13275: chos kyi sku ru bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:13276: mi rtog mnyam pa'i ngo bor bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:13278: de yang da lta rtog pa 'gyu bzhin pa'i skabs
NK095(ce)001:13279: na gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa zhig gtan nas yod
NK095(ce)001:13280: ma myong bar rtog med mnyam pa chen po chos
NK095(ce)001:13281: sku spros pa dang bral ba'i rang bzhin du bzhugs
NK095(ce)001:13282: yod par shes dgos kyi mi rtog pa'i ting nge
NK095(ce)001:13283: 'dzin bsgom pa sogs kyis gzod rtog bral chos sku'i
NK095(ce)001:13284: dgongs pa zhig mngon du 'gyur bar 'dod pa ni
NK095(ce)001:13285: byis pa'i blo can yin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:13287: ji ltar grogs gang byis pa dag /sprin 'dus pa yi phung po la //
NK095(ce)001:13288: kha yi dbugs kyis dengs par 'dod //
NK095(ce)001:13289: 'byung chen rlung gis ma gtor na //
NK095(ce)001:13290: de nyid dengs par ga la 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:13291: de bzhin rnal 'byor byis pa'i blos //
NK095(ce)001:13293: mi rtog gnyen pos dengs par 'dod //
NK095(ce)001:13294: rnam rtog ye shes ma shar na //
NK095(ce)001:13295: mi rtog gnyen pos gtan mi zhi //
NK095(ce)001:13297: de ltar gzung 'dzin rnam rtog gi spros pa kun
NK095(ce)001:13298: dang brala ba nam mkha' lta bu la 'gyur bcas
NK095(ce)001:13299: glo bur ba'i chos su grub pa gang yang med
NK095(ce)001:13300: pas 'gyur med bde ba chen po rang byung 'dus
NK095(ce)001:13301: ma byas pa'i bdag nyid du gnas pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:13303: byang chub kyi sems de nyid kyi ngo bo gsal
NK095(ce)001:13304: ba'i rang gdangs 'gag pa med pa longs spyod rdzogs
NK095(ce)001:13305: pa'i skur mngon du snang nas bzhugs tsam na rig
NK095(ce)001:13306: pa'i rtsal las rang shar ba'i tshogs drug yul gyi
NK095(ce)001:13307: snang ba thams cad ma 'gags pa 'dod pa'i yon
NK095(ce)001:13308: tan lnga po ma spang rgyan du shar ba'i longs
NK095(ce)001:13309: spyod dang ldan pas ji ltar 'dod pa thams cad
NK095(ce)001:13310: byang chub sems kyi rol rtsal las rang 'char bas
NK095(ce)001:13311: rtsol sgrub med par ye nas phun sum tshogs pa
NK095(ce)001:13312: dang ldan para bzhugs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:13314: longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:13315: sna tshogs chos la longs spyod cing //
NK095(ce)001:13316: ma spangs ye shes rgyan du bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:13319: de las thugs rje'i rol rtsal gang 'dul du snang
NK095(ce)001:13320: ba sprul pa'i sku ru 'phro zhing bzhugs tsam na
NK095(ce)001:13321: lha la sogs pa'i 'gro ba rigs drug gi gdul
NK095(ce)001:13322: bya rnams thabs gang gis 'dul ba'i dus la bab
NK095(ce)001:13323: tsam na gdul bya gang la mchog gi sprul pa
NK095(ce)001:13324: nas sna tshogs sprul pa'i bar gang dang ci lta
NK095(ce)001:13325: bu'i rnam par bstan nas 'dul dgos pa de dang
NK095(ce)001:13326: de lta bu'i sku ru sprul nas gdul bya de
NK095(ce)001:13327: dag thabs ji lta bu'i 'dul dgos pa yi phrin
NK095(ce)001:13328: las phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par bzhugs so
NK095(ce)001:13330: sprul pa'i sku ru bzhugs tsam na //
NK095(ce)001:13331: gang la gang 'dul der sprul nas //
NK095(ce)001:13332: dgongs pa phun sum tshogs par bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:13334: gsum pa don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:13335: thams cad ji bzhin par gdod nas lhun grub tu
NK095(ce)001:13336: gnas pas rtsol sgrub bcos bslad mi dgos pa dang
NK095(ce)001:13337: / byas na tshi chad pas nam yang grub pa med pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13339: de ltar sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i rang byung
NK095(ce)001:13340: rig pa'i ye shes sems nyid kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:13341: de dus gsum du 'gyur ba med par bzhugs shing
NK095(ce)001:13342: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kun la chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:13343: byang chub kyi sems de'i phyag rgya yis theb pas
NK095(ce)001:13344: chos thams cad kun ye stong spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:13345: ba nam mkha'i mtshan nyid du gnas pa nyid de
NK095(ce)001:13346: / 'o na nam mkha' de ji lta bu zhe na /
NK095(ce)001:13349: mtshan dpe nyid kyang 'di zhes byar med na //
NK095(ce)001:13350: mtshan dpe'i don la bsam brjod ga la srid //
NK095(ce)001:13351: zhes pa ltar nam mkha'i mtshan nyid kyang smra bsam
NK095(ce)001:13352: brjod pa dang bral ba chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:13353: du gnas la / sku gsum gyi mtshan nyid kyang
NK095(ce)001:13354: de bzhin nyid du gnas pas chos thams cad de
NK095(ce)001:13355: bzhin nyid du gnas pa des phyir ji ltar snang
NK095(ce)001:13356: ba'i chos kun ni chos nyid ji bzhin pa ru
NK095(ce)001:13357: gnas pa las de la btsas su rdul tsam yang
NK095(ce)001:13360: de ltar bcos bsgyur spang blang las 'das pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:13361: la btsal zhing sgrub par 'dod pa thams cad kyis
NK095(ce)001:13362: rtsol ba'i nad kyis zin par 'gyur ba las /
NK095(ce)001:13363: snga ba 'das pa'i dus su rtsol sgrub kyis lam
NK095(ce)001:13364: la bgrod pas gdod ma'i sa ru phyin pa gcig
NK095(ce)001:13365: kyang med la / de bzhin du ye nas mngon
NK095(ce)001:13366: par sangs rgyas pa de las lhag par snga ma
NK095(ce)001:13367: rtsol sgrub byas pas 'bras bu khyad par ba zhig
NK095(ce)001:13368: thob zin pa gcig kyang med pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:13369: de ltar bsgrubs shing btsal bas snga ma grub pa
NK095(ce)001:13370: gcig kyang med pa de phyir chos thams cad ye
NK095(ce)001:13371: ji bzhin pa ru gnas pa de la rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:13372: byas pas gzhan du 'gyur ba med do //
NK095(ce)001:13375: byang chub kyii sems kun byed rgyal po las bya
NK095(ce)001:13376: med rdzogs pa phyag rgya 'gyur med kyi lung gi
NK095(ce)001:13377: le'u ste rtsa bzhi pa'i 'grel pa'o ////don lnga pa
NK095(ce)001:13378: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid kun byed rang gi
NK095(ce)001:13379: sems nyid la snang ba snang dus nyid nas spros
NK095(ce)001:13380: pa'i mtha' bral de bzhin nyid du ston pa cir
NK095(ce)001:13381: snang ston par shar ba'i le'u nyer lnga pa la
NK095(ce)001:13385: de ltar sku gsum 'pho 'gyur med pa chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:13386: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin du bzhugs pa la
NK095(ce)001:13387: bcos su med par bstan pa de nas byang chub
NK095(ce)001:13388: kyi sems kun byed rgyal po des khams gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:13389: sems can thams cad la rang gi sems nyid rang
NK095(ce)001:13390: byung gi ye shes 'di nyid ston pa'i ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:13391: yin kyang de ltar yin par ma shes pas 'khrul
NK095(ce)001:13392: bar gyur pa la rang sems ston pa yin par
NK095(ce)001:13393: mngon du phyung nas bstan pa yi tshul 'di gsungsa
NK095(ce)001:13394: so // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:13395: 'byung lnga snang dus de'i ngo bo mnyam nyid mi
NK095(ce)001:13396: rtog pa'i rang bzhin rang gi sems la ston par
NK095(ce)001:13397: shar ba ngo shes pa gyis par gdams pa /
NK095(ce)001:13398: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par gdams pa /
NK095(ce)001:13399: de ltar mnyam nyid gzung 'dzin bral ba'i don goms
NK095(ce)001:13400: pa mthar phyin pa na bdag gzhan 'khor 'das su
NK095(ce)001:13401: snang ba chos nyid du grol bar gdams pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13403: kye zhes khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kun
NK095(ce)001:13404: la bos nas 'di ltar sems can rnams kyi rang
NK095(ce)001:13405: rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems de ni
NK095(ce)001:13406: sems nyid rang gi ngo bo ma sgrib rang gsal
NK095(ce)001:13407: du ston pa'i ston pa yin par mngon sum du
NK095(ce)001:13409: 'on kyang sems can rnams kyis bskal pa brgya phrag
NK095(ce)001:13410: stong du ste mang po'i bar du ni rang gi
NK095(ce)001:13411: sems 'di nyid kun byed chos sku'i ston pa yin
NK095(ce)001:13412: par ma mthong zhing rang ngo ma shes pa de'i
NK095(ce)001:13413: dbang gis 'khrul snang stong gzugs kyi rol pa med
NK095(ce)001:13414: snang 'khor ba'i duhkha la spyod pa des phyir na
NK095(ce)001:13415: / ston pa kun byed rgyal po nga yis ni
NK095(ce)001:13416: sems can rnams kyi rang gi rig pa byang chub
NK095(ce)001:13417: kyi sems 'di nyid ston pa 'byung ba chen po
NK095(ce)001:13418: lnga'i tshul du mngon du phyung bas te mngon du
NK095(ce)001:13419: phyung nas bstan par byas pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:13420: des na rang sems ston pa yin pa'i tshul la
NK095(ce)001:13421: gdams pa'i man ngag zab mo'i chos 'di nyid nyon
NK095(ce)001:13422: cig ces nyan par bskul te /
NK095(ce)001:13423: de yang rang gi sems ston pa'am bla ma yin
NK095(ce)001:13424: pa'i tshul la dbye ba rnam pa gsum du gsungs
NK095(ce)001:13425: te / da lta thos bsam phyin ci ma log
NK095(ce)001:13426: pa la brten nas dge sdig blang dor gyi skyon
NK095(ce)001:13427: yon la nges pa 'drongs pa'i dad pa dang ldan
NK095(ce)001:13428: pas yang dag pa'i lam la brtson zhing shes rab
NK095(ce)001:13429: zab mo dang ting nge 'dzin la brten nas mthar
NK095(ce)001:13430: thug 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang mngon du
NK095(ce)001:13431: thob par byed pa sems nyid rgyu yi bla ma
NK095(ce)001:13432: te / dang / sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK095(ce)001:13433: shes rig pa sku gsum gyi rang bzhin da lta
NK095(ce)001:13434: nyid nas ston pa sku gsum gyi ngo bor bzhugs
NK095(ce)001:13435: pa ni 'bras bu sems kyi bla ma dang /
NK095(ce)001:13436: 'byung lnga la sogs pa cir snang gi dngos po
NK095(ce)001:13437: thams cad sems nyid kyi rtsal las rang shar ba
NK095(ce)001:13438: yin pas byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin du ye
NK095(ce)001:13439: nas sangs rgyas shing chos nyid mnyam pa chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:13440: don rang gi ngo bo brda dang dpe ru 'char
NK095(ce)001:13441: ba'i tshul gyis ston pa ni rang snang chos kyi
NK095(ce)001:13442: bla ma yiin par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:13444: rang sems bla mar snang ba la //
NK095(ce)001:13445: de la rnam pa gsum yod de //
NK095(ce)001:13446: sems nyid rgyu yi bla ma dang //
NK095(ce)001:13447: 'bras bu sems kyi bla ma dang //
NK095(ce)001:13448: rang snang chos kyi bla ma'o //
NK095(ce)001:13449: sems nyid rgyu yi bla ma ni //
NK095(ce)001:13450: rtog ge sgam po rig chad pa //
NK095(ce)001:13451: log sred can ni ma yin te //
NK095(ce)001:13452: rtog pa ye shes blo dman gyis //
NK095(ce)001:13454: bde dang sdug bsngal gnyis su mthong //
NK095(ce)001:13455: bde sdug gnyis la brtags byas pas //
NK095(ce)001:13456: dge sdig gnyis las byung bar dran //
NK095(ce)001:13457: dran pa'i sems kyis dad pa bskul //
NK095(ce)001:13458: dad pa'i sems kyis brtson 'grus bskul //
NK095(ce)001:13459: brtson 'grus chen po'i bla ma des //
NK095(ce)001:13460: shes rab rnam gsum blo byas te //
NK095(ce)001:13461: ting 'dzin don la nan tan bsgom //
NK095(ce)001:13462: ting 'dzin mthu brtas ye shes rgyas //
NK095(ce)001:13463: ye shes mngon gyur chos kyi sku //
NK095(ce)001:13464: de las gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis //
NK095(ce)001:13465: nyi zla'i 'od dang gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:13466: thogs pa med par shugs kyis 'byung //
NK095(ce)001:13467: bstan pa theg pa kun bkod nas //
NK095(ce)001:13468: gar thad yul la 'debs su bzhugs //
NK095(ce)001:13469: 'bras bu sems kyi bla ma ni //
NK095(ce)001:13470: shes pa so ma ma bcos pa //
NK095(ce)001:13471: 'bras bu rang snang sku gsum tshul //
NK095(ce)001:13472: rang bzhin chos kyi sku ru snang //
NK095(ce)001:13473: ngo bo longs spyod rdzogs skur snang //
NK095(ce)001:13474: thugs rje sprul pa'i sku ru snang //
NK095(ce)001:13475: sems rgyud gcig gi ngo bo la //
NK095(ce)001:13476: ston pa sku gsum rang bzhin gnas //
NK095(ce)001:13477: rang snang chos kyi bla ma ni //
NK095(ce)001:13478: 'byung chen lnga yi bla ma dang //
NK095(ce)001:13479: 'dod yon lnga sogs bla ma yis //
NK095(ce)001:13480: tshig dang yi ges mi ston par //
NK095(ce)001:13481: rang gi ngo bos chos ston pa //
NK095(ce)001:13482: bdag gzhan gnyis su mi rtog pa //
NK095(ce)001:13483: rang snang ngo bos chos ston to //
NK095(ce)001:13484: zhes gsungs pa las 'dir ni gtso bo rang snang
NK095(ce)001:13485: chos kyi bla ma 'byung ba chen po lngar snang
NK095(ce)001:13486: ba de nyid kyis chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:13487: don ji ltar ston pa'i tshul gsungs pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:13488: de yang ji ltar na chos sku kun byed rgyal
NK095(ce)001:13489: po nga yis ni chos rnams thams cad kun gang
NK095(ce)001:13490: las 'byung ba'i rgyu byang chub sems kyi rtsal 'gag
NK095(ce)001:13491: pa med par las ni sems kyi ngo bo snang
NK095(ce)001:13492: ba'i cha 'byung ba chen po lnga ru snang ba
NK095(ce)001:13493: de ni / ston pa byang chub kyi sems rgyal ba rigs lnga ru byung ba yin te /
NK095(ce)001:13494: de la ston pa lnga po de sku gsum las
NK095(ce)001:13495: gang yin snyam na sku ni ngo bo gsal la
NK095(ce)001:13496: 'gags pa med pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin
NK095(ce)001:13497: la / chos ni mi rtog mnyam pa chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:13498: rang bzhin 'byung ba lnga po rang rang gi ngo
NK095(ce)001:13499: bos mtshon nas dgongs pa brda' yi gsung gis 'chad
NK095(ce)001:13500: la / par byed cing / ston par bya ba'i
NK095(ce)001:13501: don ni 'byung lnga rang gii rang bzhin stong gsal
NK095(ce)001:13503: khyab gdal phyogs lhung dang bral ba /
NK095(ce)001:13504: mnyam nyid blang dor dang bral ba /
NK095(ce)001:13505: yod med bsam yul las 'das pa'i mi rtog mnyam
NK095(ce)001:13506: pa nyid kyi rang bzhin du ston pa yin no
NK095(ce)001:13508: 'byung lngar snang dus mi rtog pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ston pa yin par mdor bstan /
NK095(ce)001:13513: nam mkha'i rnam par snang dus nyid nas mi rtog mnyam pa nyid du rgyas par bshad pa /
NK095(ce)001:13514: 'byung lnga'i rang bzhin las snang srid sna tshogs su
NK095(ce)001:13515: snang yang ngo bo ye nas ma skyes pa kun
NK095(ce)001:13516: byed nyid du don bsdu ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:13518: gong du bstan pa de lta bu'i ston pa longs
NK095(ce)001:13519: spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rigs lnga yi rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:13520: snang ba de rnams kyis mi g.yo mnyam pa chen
NK095(ce)001:13521: po'i dgongs pa ni ji ltar ston na tshul bdag
NK095(ce)001:13522: nyid kyi ngo bo la nyid kyi rang bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:13524: phar yul snang gi chos gzhan rnams la'ang de dang
NK095(ce)001:13525: de nyid du rtog par mi byed pa'i tshul gyis
NK095(ce)001:13526: byang chub sems kyi ston pa lnga po de yis
NK095(ce)001:13527: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos kun kyang bdag gzhan
NK095(ce)001:13528: mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin blo 'das spros pa
NK095(ce)001:13529: dang bral ba / chos nyid de bzhin nyid du
NK095(ce)001:13530: rnam par mi rtog pa'i brda yi gsung de la
NK095(ce)001:13531: brten nas ston par byed do zhes so //
NK095(ce)001:13532: gnyis pa gong gsal ltar lnga las /
NK095(ce)001:13534: 'di ltar byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal
NK095(ce)001:13535: spros pa dang bral ba'i rang mdangs ye shes rang
NK095(ce)001:13536: gsal ba'i cha de'i rtsal las longs spyod rdzogs sku'i
NK095(ce)001:13537: ston pa sa yi skur mngon du byung nas /
NK095(ce)001:13538: sgra tshig brjod pa las 'das pa'i chos nyid mnyam
NK095(ce)001:13539: pa chen po rnam par mi rtog pa'i don tshig
NK095(ce)001:13540: dang yi ges mi ston te /
NK095(ce)001:13541: 'byung ba rang gi rang bzhin ji lta ba bzhin
NK095(ce)001:13542: du snang ba'i sgo nas ston par byed pa ste
NK095(ce)001:13543: / 'di ltar rang gi rang bzhin ni ye nas
NK095(ce)001:13544: rnam par rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba yin
NK095(ce)001:13545: pas 'di ni bdag go snyam du nang gi bdag
NK095(ce)001:13546: nyid dam gang zag tu mi rtog la /
NK095(ce)001:13547: 'di ni gzhan no snyam du phyi rol gyii yul
NK095(ce)001:13548: du mi rtog pas mtshon spros pa'i mtha' gang du'ang
NK095(ce)001:13549: mi rtog par chos nyid mnyam pa'i dgongs pa ston
NK095(ce)001:13550: par byed cing / khams gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems
NK095(ce)001:13551: can thams cad kyis mi rtog mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK095(ce)001:13552: don de ji lta ba bzhin du rtogs pas sangs
NK095(ce)001:13553: rgyas kun dang dgongs pa mnyam par 'gyur ba yin
NK095(ce)001:13554: pas theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyis rtsol zhing
NK095(ce)001:13555: sgrub pas grub par re ba'i chos nyid de ni
NK095(ce)001:13556: par byed cing / / a ti rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:13557: po'i lam 'dir ma btsal lhun gyis 'grub par 'gyur
NK095(ce)001:13560: de bzhin du byang chub sems kyi ngo bo rang
NK095(ce)001:13561: byung gi ye shes des rang gi ngo bo ston
NK095(ce)001:13562: pa chu yi skur mngon du byung nas chos kyi
NK095(ce)001:13563: don tshig dang yi ges mi ston te /
NK095(ce)001:13564: chu de nyid rang gi ngo bos mtshon cing ston par byed pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:13565: de yang nang bdag tu mi rtog cing phyi rol
NK095(ce)001:13566: gyi chos gzhan la mi rtog pas mi rtog mnyam
NK095(ce)001:13567: pa'i dgongs pa ston par byed cing khams gsum gyi
NK095(ce)001:13568: sems can thams cad kyis don de ltar rtogs pas
NK095(ce)001:13569: sangs rgyas kun dang dgongs pa mnyam par gyur nas
NK095(ce)001:13570: rtsol ba'i chos rnams ni ma btsal lhun gyis grub
NK095(ce)001:13572: rig pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin rang byung
NK095(ce)001:13573: ye shes chen po des ston pa me yi rnam
NK095(ce)001:13574: pa'i skur byung nas tshig dang yi ges chos mi
NK095(ce)001:13575: ston te / me rang gi ngo bosa chos ston
NK095(ce)001:13576: pa yi tshul ni nang bdag tu mi rtog cing
NK095(ce)001:13577: phyi'i chos la gzhan du'ang mi rtog par /
NK095(ce)001:13578: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngo bo chos nyid mnyam
NK095(ce)001:13579: pa'i dgongs pa rang gi ngo bos ston zhing khams
NK095(ce)001:13580: gsum sems can thams cad kyis de ltar rtogs pas
NK095(ce)001:13581: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam par rtsol ba'i chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:13582: ma btsal bar ngang gis grub par 'gyur ro //
NK095(ce)001:13584: ston pa byang chub sems kyi ye shes des ston
NK095(ce)001:13585: pa longs spyod rdzogs sku rlung gi skur byung nas
NK095(ce)001:13586: sgra tshig dang yi ges chos mi ston par rang
NK095(ce)001:13587: gi ngo bos mtshon de chos ston pa yi tshul
NK095(ce)001:13588: ni / bdag gzhan gnyis su mi rtog par cir
NK095(ce)001:13589: yang mi rtog pa'i mnyam pa'i dgongs pa ston la
NK095(ce)001:13590: khams gsum gyi sems cana thams cad kyis don de
NK095(ce)001:13591: rtogsa pa tsam gyis sangs rgyas kun dang dgongs pa
NK095(ce)001:13592: mnyam par gyur te rtsol ba'i chos rnams ni ma
NK095(ce)001:13593: btsal bar rtsol med lhun gyis grub par gsungs pa'o
NK095(ce)001:13595: kun byed byang chub sems kyi ye shes des ston
NK095(ce)001:13596: pa nam mkha'i skur byung nas tshig dang yi ges
NK095(ce)001:13598: nam mkha' rang gi ngo bosa chos nyid kyi don
NK095(ce)001:13599: brda la brten nas ston par byed pa ni bdag
NK095(ce)001:13600: gzhan gnyis su rnam par rtog cing 'dzin pa'i chos
NK095(ce)001:13601: su mi ston par bdag gzhan dang 'khor 'das bzang
NK095(ce)001:13602: ngan blang dor sogs cir yang mi 'byed par nyag
NK095(ce)001:13603: cig spros pa dang bral bas rtog med mnyam pa
NK095(ce)001:13604: chen po yi dgongs pa ston par byed la /
NK095(ce)001:13605: de ltar khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis
NK095(ce)001:13606: don de ji bzhin du rtogs pas dus gsum sangs
NK095(ce)001:13607: rgyas kun dang dgongs pa dbyer med pa mnyam pa
NK095(ce)001:13608: nyid du gyur nas 'og ma'i theg pa rnams kyis
NK095(ce)001:13609: rtsol ba'i yul du byed pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa'i
NK095(ce)001:13610: yon tan thams cad ma btsal lhun gyis grub par
NK095(ce)001:13611: 'gyur ba ste / des na kun byed byang chub
NK095(ce)001:13612: sems las mngon du byung ba'i ston pa longs spyod
NK095(ce)001:13613: rdzogs pa'i sku de rnams kyis rang rang gi ngo
NK095(ce)001:13614: bos chos 'chad pa 'di yisa chos rnams kun gyi
NK095(ce)001:13615: don kyang gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i spros pa kun dang
NK095(ce)001:13616: bral ba'i rtog med mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:13617: 'gyur ba ste / / chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK095(ce)001:13618: bcos bsgyur spang blang thams cad bral bar rig par
NK095(ce)001:13619: gyis shig ces gdams pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:13620: de ltar 'byung ba lnga po 'byung gyur dang bcas
NK095(ce)001:13621: pa'i phyi nang snod bcud du snang ba'i chos 'di
NK095(ce)001:13622: thams cad ye nas byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:13623: du mngon par byang chub cing rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:13626: chen po lnga nyid sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid do //
NK095(ce)001:13630: da ltar byung ba rnams dang /
NK095(ce)001:13631: dus dang dus kyi so sor gyur pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:13632: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad dang /
NK095(ce)001:13636: chen po lnga dang 'byung ba bzhi las byung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:13637: chos thams cad sku lnga rnam par dag pa las
NK095(ce)001:13638: ma byung ba gcig kyang med do //
NK095(ce)001:13639: de dag thams cad sku lnga las byung bas na
NK095(ce)001:13640: thams cad nas thams cad du sku lnga nyid du
NK095(ce)001:13641: ma gyur pa gcig kyang med do //
NK095(ce)001:13642: des phyir sangs rgyas su ma gyur pa gcig kyang med do //
NK095(ce)001:13645: kye khams gsum na 'khod pa'i sems can thams cad
NK095(ce)001:13646: kun chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa'i
NK095(ce)001:13647: snying po byang chub kyi sems ston pa kun byed
NK095(ce)001:13648: rgyal po nga yis ni 'khor 'das thams cad rang
NK095(ce)001:13649: rtsal 'gag pa med pa las sprul cing mngon du
NK095(ce)001:13650: phyung ba yin pas sems can khyeda rnams thams cad
NK095(ce)001:13651: nga yis byas pa yin pa'i phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:13652: 'gro ba khyed rnams thams cad kun byed rgyal po nga yi sras yin pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:13653: don la tha dad med pas nga dang mnyam pa'ang
NK095(ce)001:13654: yin la kun byed nga dang ngo bo mi gnyis
NK095(ce)001:13655: par nga nyid dngos kyang yin pa'i phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:13656: nga yis khyed rnams la tshul de ltar ston par
NK095(ce)001:13657: byed pa'i ched du kun byed byang chub sems las
NK095(ce)001:13658: mngon du phyung ba yi rang bzhin /
NK095(ce)001:13659: don la nga yi ngo bo dngos su snang ba'i ston pa 'byung chen rnam pa lngas /
NK095(ce)001:13660: sra zhing brtan pa dang rlan zhing gsher ba la
NK095(ce)001:13661: sogs pa'i tshul du snang ba 'di'i rang bzhin rnama
NK095(ce)001:13662: pa lnga po mi rtog mnyam pa nyid chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:13663: byang chub kyi sems gcig tu bstan la /
NK095(ce)001:13664: de lta bu'i chos nyid mnyam pa nyid rtsol sgrub
NK095(ce)001:13665: las 'das pa'i rang bzhin gcig po de ni kun
NK095(ce)001:13666: byed nga nyid yin gyis de las gzhan zhig min
NK095(ce)001:13667: pa de bzhin du khams gsum rgyud drug tu gnas
NK095(ce)001:13668: pa'i sems can khyod rnams kyang chos nyid gcig po
NK095(ce)001:13669: de las gzhan du med par yid ches par gyis
NK095(ce)001:13672: kye khams gsum gyi sems can ji snyed yod pa ma lus pa kun /
NK095(ce)001:13673: kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga yi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:13674: gdod nas skye ba med pa ye stong spros bral
NK095(ce)001:13675: chen po bya rtsol blo las 'das pa'i rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:13676: las grub pa rdul tsam yang med la /
NK095(ce)001:13677: de ltar na dper na sgyu ma mkhan med na
NK095(ce)001:13678: des sprul pa'i sgyu ma'i snang ba rnams kyang med
NK095(ce)001:13679: pa bzhin du nga yi byas pa'i sems can khyed
NK095(ce)001:13681: khyed rnams med par gyur pa tsam gyi dus de
NK095(ce)001:13682: tsam na ston pa 'byung chen lnga yang su yi
NK095(ce)001:13683: ngor snang zhing 'byung bar 'gyur te snang bar mi
NK095(ce)001:13684: 'gyur zhing / mi rtog mnyam pa nyid kyi chos
NK095(ce)001:13685: kyang gang gis gang la ston par 'gyur te mi
NK095(ce)001:13686: 'gyur ba des na de lta bu'i chos nyid mnyam
NK095(ce)001:13687: pa'i don de la gom pa mthar phyin par gyis
NK095(ce)001:13688: shig dang snang srid kyi chos thams cad chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:13689: gcig gi klong du rang grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK095(ce)001:13692: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las rang
NK095(ce)001:13693: sems ston par byung ba'i le'u ste rtsa lnga pa'i
NK095(ce)001:13694: 'grel pa'o ////don drug pa sems nyid sgom du med
NK095(ce)001:13695: pas rgyu 'bras bya brtsal las 'das pa'i le'u nyer
NK095(ce)001:13699: de ltar rig pa byang chub sems kyi rtsal snang
NK095(ce)001:13700: 'byung ba chen po lngas rtog med mnyam pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:13701: kyi don rang gi ngo bos ston pas rang sems
NK095(ce)001:13702: ston par mngon du phyung ba yin tshul gsungs pa
NK095(ce)001:13703: de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal pos
NK095(ce)001:13704: sems las byung ba'i chos 'byung ba chen po lnga
NK095(ce)001:13705: ston par byung ba'i rtags su longs sku 'byung ba
NK095(ce)001:13706: lnga po de gang las snang ba'i gzhi chos sku
NK095(ce)001:13707: spros dang bral ba'i rang bzhin gdod nas ma skyes
NK095(ce)001:13708: pa'i rig pa byang chub kyi sems ston pa yin
NK095(ce)001:13709: par zhal gyis bzhes pa 'di gsungs so zhes ston
NK095(ce)001:13710: pa chos sku'i rtsal las mngon du phyung ba yin
NK095(ce)001:13711: na gdul bya la lam ston pa'i gzugs sku yin
NK095(ce)001:13712: par grub pa'i gtan tshigs grub pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13714: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyis mtshon te bstan pa dang /
NK095(ce)001:13715: de dag thams cad thig le gcig tu dbyer med du bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13721: dang po lta ba la bzhi ste /
NK095(ce)001:13722: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i ngo bo lta bar bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:13723: de nyid yon tan gyi 'byung khungs yin pa /
NK095(ce)001:13724: de'i rang bzhin spros pa'i mtha' dang bral ba /
NK095(ce)001:13725: rtse gcig 'dzin pa'i sems gnas tsam gyis mi rtogs par bshad pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13727: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK095(ce)001:13728: 'di ltar sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas dag pa'i
NK095(ce)001:13729: ngo bo yid kyi bsam pa las 'das shing ngag
NK095(ce)001:13730: gis brjod du med pa'i byang chub kyi sems ni
NK095(ce)001:13731: ston pa sku gsum gyi rgyal ba ma lus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:13732: ston pa kun byed chos sku'i ngo bo ma rig
NK095(ce)001:13733: pa'i mun pa thams cad sel bar byed pa'i snang
NK095(ce)001:13734: byed kyi sgron mar gyur pa yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:13735: de nyid kyi yon tan dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:13736: kun gyis rab tu basngagasa pa ni ji ltar na
NK095(ce)001:13737: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs mthar thug yin pas
NK095(ce)001:13739: spros pa'i grwa zur dang bral ba dang ji bzhin
NK095(ce)001:13740: rtog par gyur na srid zhi'i dpal du 'gyur bas
NK095(ce)001:13742: med pas gzhon nu nyid te /
NK095(ce)001:13743: de ni bya rtsol thams cad dang bral ba lhun
NK095(ce)001:13744: grub rdzogs pa chen po bde chen 'gyur ba med
NK095(ce)001:13745: pa spros pa dang bral ba'i lhun la gnas pa'am
NK095(ce)001:13746: klong na ye nas gnas pa ni rdzogs pa chen
NK095(ce)001:13747: po ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i lta ba yin
NK095(ce)001:13748: no // tshul de dang mthun par mdo bcu las /
NK095(ce)001:13749: snying po byang chub sems 'di la //
NK095(ce)001:13751: brjod du med pa'i ngang la gnas //
NK095(ce)001:13752: de ltar snying po byang chub sems //
NK095(ce)001:13753: ston pa'i sgron mar gyur pas na //
NK095(ce)001:13754: sangs rgyas kun gyi rab tu basngagasa //
NK095(ce)001:13755: chos rnams kun gyi snying po bas //
NK095(ce)001:13756: mkhyen rab 'jam dpal gzhon nu nyid //
NK095(ce)001:13757: bya byed rtsol sgrub mi mnga' bar //
NK095(ce)001:13758: bde chen klong na ji bzhin gnas //
NK095(ce)001:13761: de lta bu'i byang chub kyi sems de ni tshul
NK095(ce)001:13762: khrimas bsrung ba dang bzod pa sgom pa la sogs
NK095(ce)001:13763: pa'i byang chub kyi spyod pa rgya mtsho lta bu'i
NK095(ce)001:13764: rten gzhir gyur pa'i rang bzhin yin pas /
NK095(ce)001:13765: ji snyed rnam par grol ba'am rnam par grol ba'i
NK095(ce)001:13766: lam nyan thos nas gsang sngags kyi bar ji snyed
NK095(ce)001:13767: cig bstan pa thams cad kyi rtsa ba yang /
NK095(ce)001:13768: bde bar gshegs pa ma lus pa kun 'byung ba'i
NK095(ce)001:13769: gnas su gyur pas rgyal yum shes rab kyi pha
NK095(ce)001:13770: rol du phyin pa'i ngo bor gyur cing dus gsum
NK095(ce)001:13771: gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi mtshungs pa'am bgrod pa gcig
NK095(ce)001:13772: pu'i lam kun byed byang chub kyi sems 'di nyid
NK095(ce)001:13773: yiin de / ci'i phyir na rig stong gnyis su
NK095(ce)001:13774: med pa'i ye shes kun byed byang chub kyi sems
NK095(ce)001:13775: de nyid med par gong du bstan pa'i lam de
NK095(ce)001:13776: kun gyis gtan la dbab par bya ba'i gzhi dang
NK095(ce)001:13777: bsgom bya'i lam dang thob bya'i 'bras bu thams cad
NK095(ce)001:13778: med pas lam de kun mi 'byung ba de yi
NK095(ce)001:13779: phyir na byang chub kyi sems de ni rnam grol
NK095(ce)001:13780: mchog gi lam thams cad kyi 'byung gnas sam gzhir
NK095(ce)001:13781: gyur pa yin par bstan pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13783: de lta bu'i sems nyid ye nas rnam par dag
NK095(ce)001:13784: pa de ni rtog pa'i yul du ma gyur pas
NK095(ce)001:13785: shin tu phra zhing shes par dka' la gshegs bzhugs
NK095(ce)001:13786: 'byon 'gyur gyi sangs rgyas ma lus pa kun gyi
NK095(ce)001:13787: spyi lam chen por gyur pa ste /
NK095(ce)001:13788: de'i ngo bo ni rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK095(ce)001:13789: shes gang zhig rtog pa'i yul las 'das shing mi
NK095(ce)001:13790: rtog pa tsam du'ang bsgom du med pas yul gang
NK095(ce)001:13791: la'ang mi gnas shing blos cir yang mi dmigs pa
NK095(ce)001:13792: / yod med la sogs pa'i spros pa'i mtha' gang
NK095(ce)001:13793: du yang grub pa med cing rtog dpyod kyi bsam
NK095(ce)001:13795: smra brjod kyi yul las 'das pas ngag tshig gis gtan la mi phebs shing /
NK095(ce)001:13796: gru bzhi zlum po la sogs pa'i dbyibs dang sngo
NK095(ce)001:13797: ser dkar dmar la sogs pa'i kha dog dang rgyal
NK095(ce)001:13798: rigs rje rigs la sogs pa'i rigs rus sogs blo'i
NK095(ce)001:13799: spyod yul du gyur pa gang yang med pas gzhan
NK095(ce)001:13800: la bstan cing dmigs pa rnams kyi tshul gyiis brtags
NK095(ce)001:13801: par dka' la tshig gis brjod du yang rdul tsam
NK095(ce)001:13802: med pas spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba
NK095(ce)001:13804: sems kyi ngo bo 'di yin zhes //
NK095(ce)001:13805: che chung mtshan ma'i ngo bo dang //
NK095(ce)001:13806: dbyibs dang kha dog spyod yul du //
NK095(ce)001:13807: ston pa nga yis bstan pa med //
NK095(ce)001:13810: de lta bu'i snying po rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:13811: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid du gdod nas mngon par
NK095(ce)001:13812: sangs rgyas zin pas rtsol sgrub gang yang mi dgos
NK095(ce)001:13813: pa la de ltar ma rtogs par sngon gyi drang
NK095(ce)001:13814: srong chen po sangs rgyas rnams kyi dka' thub kyi
NK095(ce)001:13815: lam du gang zag gang zhig zhugs nas ting nge
NK095(ce)001:13816: 'dzin rtse gcig tu bsgom par 'dod pa rnams ni
NK095(ce)001:13817: sgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyis ro la chags shing
NK095(ce)001:13818: dmigs pa la rtse gcig tu 'dzin pa'i sems gnas
NK095(ce)001:13819: tsam gyi lam re dogs dang dgag sgrub spang blang
NK095(ce)001:13820: la sogs pa'i zug rngu can gyi nad kyis zin
NK095(ce)001:13821: par 'gyur ta re zhes 'gyur nyen che ba des
NK095(ce)001:13822: na dbang po dman pa rnams lam la rim gyis
NK095(ce)001:13823: dkri ba'i ched du dka' spyad dang sgom sgrub la
NK095(ce)001:13824: sogs pa dgos tshul gsungs pa ston pa'i drang don
NK095(ce)001:13825: gyii lung bzhin du tshig gi mtha' la spyod cing
NK095(ce)001:13826: bya rtsol dang bcas pas bsgrub pa'i lam du chos
NK095(ce)001:13828: gang zag de ni rtog pa'i rgyun bkag pa'i zhi
NK095(ce)001:13829: gnas rtse gcig pa'i rjes su 'brangs ba dper na
NK095(ce)001:13830: ri dwags smig rgyu yi chu la snyegs pa dang
NK095(ce)001:13831: 'dra bas chos nyid kyi don mi rtogs par gsungs
NK095(ce)001:13832: so // des na chos nyid yang dag pa'i don
NK095(ce)001:13833: snying po byang chub kyi sems smra bsam brjod pa
NK095(ce)001:13834: kun las 'das pas yang dag pa'i lam ni 'di
NK095(ce)001:13835: so // lta bu'o // zhes tshig gis mtshon du
NK095(ce)001:13836: med pa'i phyir na yang dag pa nyid du bstan
NK095(ce)001:13838: yang dag pa'i lam ni 'adi'o zhes de ltar bstan
NK095(ce)001:13839: par byas na ni chos sku kun byed rgyal po
NK095(ce)001:13840: nga yisa kyang nor zhing 'khrul pa yin no zhes
NK095(ce)001:13842: yang dag lam ni 'di yin zhes //
NK095(ce)001:13843: tshig dang yi ges mtshon du med //
NK095(ce)001:13844: yang dag 'di yin ston pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:13845: rdo rje sems dpa' nga nyid 'khrul //
NK095(ce)001:13847: gnyis pa sgom pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:13848: ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyal po dngas shing gsal la rtog pa med pa'i zhi gnas dang /
NK095(ce)001:13849: chos sku dri ma med pa'i spyan snang yul 'gags med du gsal ba'i lhag mthong ngo //
NK095(ce)001:13851: gong du bstan pa'i rgyu mtshan des na dag pa
NK095(ce)001:13852: sku dang ye shes dang ma dag pa 'khor ba'i
NK095(ce)001:13853: snang ba thams cad bzang ngan gyi dbye ba gnyis
NK095(ce)001:13854: su gdod nas ma grub cing med pas dbyer med
NK095(ce)001:13855: gcig tu 'dres shing chos nyid mnyam pa chen po'i
NK095(ce)001:13856: rang bzhin du mtshungs pa'i phyir na /
NK095(ce)001:13857: rnam pa bzang ngan cir yang mi 'byed par rgya
NK095(ce)001:13858: mtsho la gza' skar bkra ba bzhin du ye shes
NK095(ce)001:13859: rang gsal gyi ngo bor gnas pa de la gzung
NK095(ce)001:13860: 'dzin gnyis snang gi rtog pa ngang gis zhi bas
NK095(ce)001:13861: gti mug zhes brjod pa de yi ngang du thog
NK095(ce)001:13862: med nas gsal ba'am ye nas rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK095(ce)001:13863: gsal ba'i rang byung rig pa'i ye shes kyi mar
NK095(ce)001:13864: me blo rnam rtog gis bsam pa dang brjod pa
NK095(ce)001:13865: kun dang bral ba'i rang bzhin de /
NK095(ce)001:13866: dper na rgyal po chen po gdan las mi g.yo
NK095(ce)001:13867: bar 'khor 'bangs thams cad mnga' 'og tu bsdu zhing
NK095(ce)001:13868: dbang bsgyur ba ltar 'khor 'das thams cad chos nyid
NK095(ce)001:13869: gcig gi klong du bsdu zhing rig rtsal 'gags pa
NK095(ce)001:13870: med pas dbang bsgyur yang rang gnas chos sku'i dgongs
NK095(ce)001:13871: pa las ngang gis mi g.yo zhing gang la'ang mi
NK095(ce)001:13872: rtog pas rmugs shing 'dzin zhen thams cad dang bral
NK095(ce)001:13873: bar gnas pa ni ting nge 'dzin thams cad kyi
NK095(ce)001:13874: rgyal po rang bab gnyug ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyii
NK095(ce)001:13875: ngo bor gnas pa yin par gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13877: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems las gzhan du ma gyur cing /
NK095(ce)001:13878: byang chub kyi sems ni dmigs mtshan spros pa thams
NK095(ce)001:13879: cad dang bral ba yin pas mngon sum gyi yul
NK095(ce)001:13880: du dmigs shing mthong bar bya ba ci yang med
NK095(ce)001:13881: pa de bas na gang yang mthong ba med par
NK095(ce)001:13882: mthong ba de ni chos nyid byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:13883: rang bzhin mngon sum du mthong ba'i chos sku dri
NK095(ce)001:13884: ma med pa'i mig thob pa yin pas mthong ba'i
NK095(ce)001:13887: mi mthong pa nyid mthong ba yin //
NK095(ce)001:13888: cir yang mi dmigs gti mug ste //
NK095(ce)001:13889: ma rig pa ni ye shes gsal //
NK095(ce)001:13891: de lta bu'i zhi lhag zung du 'jug pa'i ye
NK095(ce)001:13892: shes de'i chos thams cad snang cha ma 'dres par
NK095(ce)001:13893: so sor gsal na yang gdod nas skye ba med
NK095(ce)001:13894: pa chos nyid byang chub kyi sems gcig gi rang
NK095(ce)001:13895: bzhin du rtogs pas 'khor ba myang 'das su shar
NK095(ce)001:13896: ba de ni chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs ji
NK095(ce)001:13897: bzhin par gzigs pa yin pa'i phyir na thams cad
NK095(ce)001:13898: mkhyen pa'i spyan zhes pa yang lhag mthong so sor
NK095(ce)001:13899: rtog pa'i ye shes de la brjod par bya'o zhes
NK095(ce)001:13900: pa ste / nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa las /
NK095(ce)001:13901: mthong ba'i skabs na don mi mthong //
NK095(ce)001:13902: mi mthong bas na don mthong ste //
NK095(ce)001:13903: gnyis ka ma bcos rang rig la //
NK095(ce)001:13904: mthong dang ma mthong rjes mi 'jug /thams cad byang chub sems nyid la //
NK095(ce)001:13905: log rtog rtsol ba'i chos mi gnas //
NK095(ce)001:13906: rang byung mtshan mar mi 'jug pas //
NK095(ce)001:13907: gang ltar gsal yang dmigs dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:13909: ji bzhin nyid kyi don la rtogs //
NK095(ce)001:13910: lta bral gzigs med ye shes spyan //
NK095(ce)001:13911: chos rnams byang chub sems su gsal //
NK095(ce)001:13913: gsum pa spyod pa la gsum ste /
NK095(ce)001:13914: ngo bo chos nyid las mi 'gyur bas cir snang
NK095(ce)001:13915: skye med du grol bar rang bzhin shugs kyi spyod
NK095(ce)001:13916: pa / nyon mongs ye shes su grol ba sna tshogs thabs lam gyi spyod pa /
NK095(ce)001:13917: theg pa gzhan ltar blang dor du spyod pa dgag pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:13919: 'di ltar chos nyid byang chub kyi sems ni chos
NK095(ce)001:13920: dbyings spros pa dang bral ba mtha' dang dbus med
NK095(ce)001:13921: pa'i rang bzhin yin pas yangs shing rgya che ba'i
NK095(ce)001:13922: klong du chos thams cad gnyis med mnyam pa nyid
NK095(ce)001:13923: du rdzogs shing de thams cad kyi snying po chos
NK095(ce)001:13924: sku'i ngo bor gnas pa yin pas de la bzang
NK095(ce)001:13925: ngan la sogs pa gnyis chos kyi dbye ba gang
NK095(ce)001:13926: yang med pa'i phyir bzang po dang du mi len
NK095(ce)001:13927: zhing ngan pa phyir mi 'dor bar chos nyid gcig
NK095(ce)001:13928: gi ngo bor dbang bsgyur bas mnyam pa'i rgyal por
NK095(ce)001:13929: gnas pa ste / des na chos nyid byang chub
NK095(ce)001:13930: kyi sems dang bag chags 'khrul pa'i snang ba gnyis
NK095(ce)001:13931: su ming gi bla dwags tsam du so sor phye
NK095(ce)001:13932: gnas pa ste / na yang / don la bag
NK095(ce)001:13933: chags 'khrul pa'i snang ba thams cad d+ha du ra
NK095(ce)001:13934: zos pa'i snang ba ltar rdzas su grub pa med
NK095(ce)001:13935: pas dbye gzhi zad pa'i dbyer med chen po ru
NK095(ce)001:13936: 'dres shing chos nyid gcig gi rang bzhin du mtshungs
NK095(ce)001:13937: gnas pa ste / na yang / pa yin te / yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:13938: kun rdzob rnam chad rnam dbye'i yul 'das pas //
NK095(ce)001:13939: btags pa'i bden gnyis 'das phyir spros kun zhi //
NK095(ce)001:13940: dbyings la snang stong rang bzhin gnyis med pas //
NK095(ce)001:13941: bden pa de yang dbyer med ces su brjod //
NK095(ce)001:13943: des na 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams don la
NK095(ce)001:13944: cir yang grub pa med bzhin gzung 'dzin du zhen
NK095(ce)001:13945: pa'i rtog pas rnam par brtags shing rmi lam gyi
NK095(ce)001:13946: rol pa ltar sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos rnams
NK095(ce)001:13947: ni / rig pa rang gi rtsal snang 'gag med
NK095(ce)001:13948: du shar ba chos nyid kyi rgyan du snang bas
NK095(ce)001:13949: mtshan 'dzin rtog pa'i blo yis mi 'dor bas spong
NK095(ce)001:13951: de bzhin du bsgrub cing dang du yang mi len
NK095(ce)001:13952: pas cir yang mi dgos pa'am mi rtog pa'i thabs
NK095(ce)001:13953: kyis gang snang ba'i chos thams cad po de la
NK095(ce)001:13954: chos nyid du rol pa de ni kun tu bzang
NK095(ce)001:13955: po blang dor med pa'i spyod pa'am rang bzhin shugs
NK095(ce)001:13958: spyod pa blang dor med pa ni //
NK095(ce)001:13959: sems nyid rdzogs pa chen po la //
NK095(ce)001:13960: snang ba'i chos dang srid pa'i chos //
NK095(ce)001:13961: thams cad byang chub sems yiin pas //
NK095(ce)001:13962: sems nyid ye shes spyod pa la //
NK095(ce)001:13966: 'di ltar rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs don ji bzhin
NK095(ce)001:13967: du rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams la chos thams
NK095(ce)001:13968: cad rig pa nyag cig gi ngo bor grol ba
NK095(ce)001:13969: yin pas 'og ma'i theg pa kun dang mi mthun
NK095(ce)001:13970: pas blang dor gyi lam la zhen pa yongs kyis
NK095(ce)001:13971: spong 'gog sbyong bsgyur la sogs par lta ba'i chos
NK095(ce)001:13972: nyon mongs pa dug lnga dang des kun nas bslang
NK095(ce)001:13974: mtshams med pa lnga poo la sogs pa yi rang
NK095(ce)001:13975: bzhin ni gdod nas chos dbyings skye ba med pa'i
NK095(ce)001:13976: ngang nas rang shar ba'i rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:13977: lnga yi rol rtsal yin phyir spang bya ma dag
NK095(ce)001:13978: pa'i chos su grub pa rdul tsam med par ye
NK095(ce)001:13979: nas rnam par dag pa sna tshogs thabs lam gyi
NK095(ce)001:13980: spyod pa yin pas 'ching byed du mi 'gyur bar
NK095(ce)001:13981: ma zad / lam dera zhugs par byas nas chos
NK095(ce)001:13982: nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don la dbang bsgyur bar
NK095(ce)001:13983: byed pa'i rgyal po kun bzang chos sku'i gtan srid
NK095(ce)001:13984: la mnga' dbang thob par 'gyur bas na bud med
NK095(ce)001:13985: la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yul kun kyang spong bar
NK095(ce)001:13988: rdzogs chen a ti'i ngo bo la //
NK095(ce)001:13989: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos rnams rdzogs //
NK095(ce)001:13990: dge ba byar med sdig pa spang du med //
NK095(ce)001:13991: dge sdig gnyis dang bral ba'i rig pa chos kyi sku //
NK095(ce)001:13992: dge ba mi bya byas na sangs rgyas min //
NK095(ce)001:13993: sdig pa mi spang spangs na sangs rgyas 'grub mi 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:13996: de las gzhan du rtsol bcas kyi theg pa gzhan
NK095(ce)001:13997: ltar blang dor rtsol sgrub la spyod pa'i lo rgyus
NK095(ce)001:13998: 'chad pa'i lung gi tshig tsam la brten nas rgyu
NK095(ce)001:13999: 'bras blang dor gyi sgo nas rang bzhin gyi don
NK095(ce)001:14000: gnyis 'grub tu yod par gsungs pa de tshad ma'i
NK095(ce)001:14001: blor bzhag pa'am tshad mar bzung nas ma h+aa yo
NK095(ce)001:14002: ga bas ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum po brtan par
NK095(ce)001:14003: bsgom pa la sogs pa lam rim gyis bgrod nas
NK095(ce)001:14004: 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa'i theg pa rang rang
NK095(ce)001:14005: gi grub pa'i mtha' la spyod cing nyams su blang
NK095(ce)001:14006: bas 'bras bu thob par re ba 'jog pa de
NK095(ce)001:14007: ni 'dir rtsol bral a ti'i lung las gzhan du
NK095(ce)001:14008: gol ba yin no zhes rang byung gi ye shes
NK095(ce)001:14009: rgyu rkyen la ma ltos par ye nas sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:14010: pa yin pa'i don ma rtogs par rtsol ba la
NK095(ce)001:14011: brten nas 'khor ba spangs nas sangs rgyas thob par
NK095(ce)001:14012: lta ba ni 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du ma rtogs
NK095(ce)001:14013: pas 'khrul pa yina par gsungs pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:14014: des na 'khor 'das thams cad sems dang rig pa'i
NK095(ce)001:14015: rol pa tsam las gzhan du med pas spang blang
NK095(ce)001:14016: re dogs gang yang mi bya bar bzhag na chos
NK095(ce)001:14017: thams cad ma byas ye zin du gnas par gsungs
NK095(ce)001:14019: bsam gtan ting 'dzin la sogs sangs rgyas sku la sgrib //
NK095(ce)001:14020: bsgom zhing sgrub pa byas na bsam gtan min //
NK095(ce)001:14021: sangs rgyas mi bsgrub bsgrub na rtsol bar 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:14022: 'khor ba mi spang spangs na sangs mi rgya //
NK095(ce)001:14023: sangs rgyas gzhan na med do rig pa yin //
NK095(ce)001:14024: 'khor ba gzhan na med do rang sems yin //
NK095(ce)001:14025: 'dus byas dge ba mi bya byas na 'ching ba'i rgyu //
NK095(ce)001:14026: mchod rten lha khang la sogs 'dus byas dge rtsa yin //
NK095(ce)001:14027: chos ni byas pas mi zin bzhag pas zin par 'gyur //
NK095(ce)001:14029: bzhi pa 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:14030: sems ji bzhin pa ma bcos par bzhag pa de
NK095(ce)001:14031: bzhin nyid rang byung gi ye shes su lhun gyis
NK095(ce)001:14032: grub tshul dang / de ltar bzhag pas rtsol sgrub zhen pa'i sdug bsngal las grol ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:14034: des na bya byed rtsol ba thams cad dang bral
NK095(ce)001:14035: bar sems nyid ji bzhin pa ma bcos rnal mar
NK095(ce)001:14036: bzhag pa'i chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du
NK095(ce)001:14037: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ma brtsal lhun grub
NK095(ce)001:14038: kyi tshul du rdzogs shing gdod nas ye sangs rgyas
NK095(ce)001:14039: pa chos dbyings bde ba chen po mtha' grol phyogs
NK095(ce)001:14040: lhung dang bral ba'i lhun la ye nas gnas pas
NK095(ce)001:14041: sa lam sbyang bgrod sogs la mi ltos par da
NK095(ce)001:14042: lta nyid nas rang byung kun tu bzang po'i ngo
NK095(ce)001:14044: de yang ye nas chos nyid byang chub sems kyi
NK095(ce)001:14045: gshis lugs de ltar du gnas pa nyid rnal 'byor
NK095(ce)001:14046: pa la mngon du shar ba las blang dor rtsol
NK095(ce)001:14047: sgrub kyis grub pa ma yin te /
NK095(ce)001:14048: ci'i phyir na rig pa'i ye shes chen po rgyu
NK095(ce)001:14049: rkyen gang gis kyang ma bskyed pas rang byung 'dus
NK095(ce)001:14050: ma byas pa srid zhi kun la khyab cing kun
NK095(ce)001:14051: gyi chos nyid du gyur pas che ba'i snying po
NK095(ce)001:14052: nyid du gyur pa de ni rkyen gyis mi g.yo
NK095(ce)001:14053: zhing ngo bo mi 'gyur bar blo 'das chos sku'i
NK095(ce)001:14054: ngo bo smra bsam spros pa kun las 'das pas
NK095(ce)001:14055: na tshig gi bsnyad pa kun dang bral ba'i phyir
NK095(ce)001:14057: 'di ltar bya byed rtsol bas ma bsgrub par ye
NK095(ce)001:14058: nas lhun gyis grub zin pa'i rig pa rang byung
NK095(ce)001:14059: gi ye shes spang blang re dogs kyi nad thams
NK095(ce)001:14060: cad sel bar byed pa'i bdud rtsisa te bdud rtsi
NK095(ce)001:14061: lta bu'i rang bzhin du gyur pa des theg pa
NK095(ce)001:14062: 'og ma'i bya rtsol gyis gdung ba'i sdug bsngal gyi
NK095(ce)001:14063: nad kun 'joms par byed cing rang gi ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:14064: bya ba thams cad dang bral bar ye nas grub
NK095(ce)001:14065: zin pa'i chos nyid yangs pa chen po'i yul la
NK095(ce)001:14066: 'pho 'gyur med par sngon ji lta ba bzhin du
NK095(ce)001:14067: phyis kyang de ltar du gnas pa yin no //
NK095(ce)001:14068: tshul de dang mthun par mdo bcu las kyang /
NK095(ce)001:14069: bya bral bde ba'i lhun la gnas //
NK095(ce)001:14070: ye nas byas zin bdud rtsi yis //
NK095(ce)001:14071: rtsol ba dag gi sdug bsngal 'joms //
NK095(ce)001:14073: gnyis pa thig le nyag gcig gi rang bzhin dbyer med du bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK095(ce)001:14074: ji bzhin pa'i sems nyid rang gnas su gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:14075: la skye 'gags gnas gsum gyi zhen pa med pas
NK095(ce)001:14076: lta sgom spyod 'bras su dbye ba dang /
NK095(ce)001:14077: rnal don nam mkha' bzhin du grub pas smra bsam las 'das pa'o //
NK095(ce)001:14079: kyee sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK095(ce)001:14080: 'di ltar snang ba'i 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams thams
NK095(ce)001:14081: cad ni ji bzhin pa'i sems nyid chos sku thig
NK095(ce)001:14082: le chen po'i rang bzhin las gzhan du grub pa
NK095(ce)001:14083: gang yang med par de'i rang bzhin yin pas na
NK095(ce)001:14084: / gong du bshad pa'i lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi
NK095(ce)001:14085: po de yang gdul bya'i ngor rig pa'i ngo bo
NK095(ce)001:14086: gcig la lta sgom spyod 'bras thams cad ma btsal
NK095(ce)001:14087: lhun grub kyi tshul du rdzogs shing tshangs pa'i tshul
NK095(ce)001:14088: tshig gis mtshon nas bstan pa tsam las /
NK095(ce)001:14089: don la de dag phar spros shing dbye bar byed
NK095(ce)001:14090: pa gang yang med cing chos so so ba bzhi
NK095(ce)001:14091: rig pa gcig gi ngo bor tshur bsdu ba yang
NK095(ce)001:14092: med do // de bzhin du chos 'di dag thams
NK095(ce)001:14093: cad dang po skye ba med cing mthar 'gag pa
NK095(ce)001:14094: med par ka dag skye ba med pa chos sku
NK095(ce)001:14095: thig le nyag gcig gi ngang las ma g.yos bzhin
NK095(ce)001:14096: du rang gdangs lhun grub kyi snang cha ru 'khor
NK095(ce)001:14097: 'das kyi snang cha sna tshogs pa 'gog pa med
NK095(ce)001:14098: med do // par 'char zhing / de ltar 'char
NK095(ce)001:14099: ba'i dus nyid nas grub pa rdul tsam med par
NK095(ce)001:14100: gnyis med mnyam pa chen po'i rang bzhin du ji
NK095(ce)001:14101: ltar sngar bzhin phyis kyang de bzhin du gnas pa
NK095(ce)001:14102: yin pas snang stong dbyer med spros pa dang bral
NK095(ce)001:14105: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud kyi lta ba'i gzhi //
NK095(ce)001:14106: snang ba 'di nyid ye nas skye ba med //
NK095(ce)001:14107: skye med nyid na gang yang thams cad skyes //
NK095(ce)001:14108: skyes tsam nyid na rang sems ngang gis stong //
NK095(ce)001:14109: dper na chu dang me long gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK095(ce)001:14110: snang dang stong pa dbyer med gdod nas dag /ces gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK095(ce)001:14112: de ltar yod med skye 'gag la sogs pa spros
NK095(ce)001:14113: pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral zhing rtog pa'i spyod
NK095(ce)001:14114: yul las 'das pas gang du'ang rnam par mi rtog
NK095(ce)001:14115: pa chos kyi dbyings dang dbyer med pa'i sems nyid
NK095(ce)001:14116: rang byung gi ye shes 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams
NK095(ce)001:14117: kyi snying po btsal ba med par ye nas sangs
NK095(ce)001:14118: rgyas pa'i rang bzhin can 'di ni nam mkha' bzhin
NK095(ce)001:14119: du chos thams cad la ye nas khyab cing dus
NK095(ce)001:14120: gsum 'pho 'gyur med par gnas pas na rtog pa'i
NK095(ce)001:14121: grwa zur dang bral zhing smra bsam gyi yul kun
NK095(ce)001:14123: nam mkha'i rgyal po las kyang /
NK095(ce)001:14124: bsam dang bral ba'i sems de nam mkha' nyid //
NK095(ce)001:14125: nam mkha' 'dra ba'i sems de nyid dang bral //
NK095(ce)001:14126: yod med dbu ma'ang mi dmigs brjod med na //
NK095(ce)001:14127: nam mkha' mi dmigs brjod du med las 'das //
NK095(ce)001:14128: sems la tshig tu brjod med sku yang med //
NK095(ce)001:14131: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las bya
NK095(ce)001:14132: med rdzogs pa bsgom du med pa'i le'u ste rtsa
NK095(ce)001:14133: drug pa'i 'grel pa'o ////don bdun pa sems nyid kun
NK095(ce)001:14134: byed dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pas rgyu 'bras bya
NK095(ce)001:14135: btsal las 'das pa'i le'u nyer bdun pa la gnyis
NK095(ce)001:14139: de ltar rig pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK095(ce)001:14140: ston pa'i ngo bor gnas pa de ye nas bsgom
NK095(ce)001:14141: du med pas rgyu 'bras bya btsal las 'das pa
NK095(ce)001:14142: bstan pa de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed
NK095(ce)001:14143: rgyal po des nyid kyi ngo bo la 'khor 'das
NK095(ce)001:14144: spang blang gang yang ma grub par rang bzhin gyis
NK095(ce)001:14145: rnam par dag pas rgyu 'bras rtsol sgrub kyis mi
NK095(ce)001:14146: 'grub par rtsol med lhun gyis grub par ston pa'i
NK095(ce)001:14147: gdams ngag phog pa dang mthun cing gnyis su med
NK095(ce)001:14148: pa'i lung theg pa 'og ma las khyad par du
NK095(ce)001:14149: 'phags pas chen po zhes gsungs pa 'di nyid 'chad
NK095(ce)001:14150: 'gyur gyi sa bcad bdun po'i go rim ltar rim
NK095(ce)001:14151: gyis bstana pa ni 'di nyid yin te zhes lhag
NK095(ce)001:14152: bcas kyi tshig gi gong 'og mtshams sbyar ba'o //
NK095(ce)001:14154: sems nyid kun byed ye nas dag pa'i dbyings su bstan pa /
NK095(ce)001:14155: snang srid chos nyid kyi rol pa yin pas 'khor
NK095(ce)001:14156: 'das blang dor du byed pa'i lam ma grub pa
NK095(ce)001:14157: / chos dbyings smon pa med pas sems las gzhan pa'i sangs rgyas grub tu med pa /
NK095(ce)001:14158: srid gsum ye grol du rtogs pas 'khor ba spang du med pa /
NK095(ce)001:14159: rtsol sgrub rgyu 'bras kyi lam gyis nam yang sangs rgyas mi 'grub pa /
NK095(ce)001:14160: rtsol sgrub rgyu 'bras ston pa'i slob dpon spang ba /
NK095(ce)001:14161: 'bad med ye grol du 'chad pa'i bla ma brten tshul lo //
NK095(ce)001:14163: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig 'di ltar snang
NK095(ce)001:14164: srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams thams cad
NK095(ce)001:14165: ni kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga las byung
NK095(ce)001:14166: ba yin pas na byang chub kyi sems ye nas
NK095(ce)001:14167: rnam par dag pa bzhin du de'i ngang las shar
NK095(ce)001:14168: ba'i ji ltar snang ba'i phyi nang snang srid kyis
NK095(ce)001:14169: bsdus pa'i chos rnams thams cad kun kyang /
NK095(ce)001:14170: rtsol sgrub bya byed la ma ltos par ye nas
NK095(ce)001:14171: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa ka dag dbyings
NK095(ce)001:14172: kyi ngang las skad cig kyang g.yo ma myong bar
NK095(ce)001:14173: lung du bstana pa yin te /
NK095(ce)001:14174: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK095(ce)001:14175: sku gsum klong las 'khor 'das rang shar kyang //
NK095(ce)001:14176: dbyings las ma g.yos chos nyid bde ba'i zhing //
NK095(ce)001:14177: sems nyid klong chen 'gyur med nam mkha'i ngang //
NK095(ce)001:14178: rol pa nges med thugs rje cho 'phrul klong //
NK095(ce)001:14179: thams cad dbyings kyi rgyan las logs na med //
NK095(ce)001:14182: 'di ltar 'byung ba chen po lngas bsdus pa'i phyi
NK095(ce)001:14183: snod kyi 'jig rten dang phung po lngas bsdus pa'i
NK095(ce)001:14184: nang bcud kyi sems can du snang ba 'di kun
NK095(ce)001:14185: ye nas spros bral chos kyi dbyings rig pa byang
NK095(ce)001:14186: chub sems kyi rang bzhin du dbyer med pa yin
NK095(ce)001:14187: la / chos kyi dbyings de la ni gzung 'dzin
NK095(ce)001:14188: rnam rtog gi bsgrib pa zhig gshis la zhugs ma
NK095(ce)001:14189: myong bas ye nas rnam par dag pa'i spyod yul
NK095(ce)001:14191: de la dag pa sangsa rgyas dang ni ma dag
NK095(ce)001:14192: pa sems can gnyis su grub pa med cing 'khor
NK095(ce)001:14193: 'das blang dor du 'byed pa'i sgo nas sa lam
NK095(ce)001:14194: rim gyis bgrod pa dang rgyu 'bras blang dor la
NK095(ce)001:14195: sogs pa'i gnyen pos bcos su ga la yod de
NK095(ce)001:14196: bcos bsgyur spang blang gang yang med par ye nas
NK095(ce)001:14197: bsgrub med rtsol sprugs chen por gnas pa'i phyir te
NK095(ce)001:14199: phyi dang nang med thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK095(ce)001:14200: rnam par dag pa'i spyod yul gnyis med la //
NK095(ce)001:14201: sangs rgyas sems can yongs kyis med pa ste //
NK095(ce)001:14202: bsgrub med rtsal sprugs smon pa med pa yi //
NK095(ce)001:14203: ma nor dam pa'i lam chen lhun rdzogs pa //
NK095(ce)001:14205: 'di la mdo bcu las 'byung ba chen po lnga
NK095(ce)001:14206: dang snang srid thams cad phyi dang byang chub kyi
NK095(ce)001:14207: sems dang chos nyid nang ste de dag thams cad
NK095(ce)001:14208: chos kyi dbyings su dbyer med par gsungs te /
NK095(ce)001:14210: phyi dang nang gi chos nyid 'di //
NK095(ce)001:14211: 'byung chen lnga dang snang srid phyi //
